#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/bank/loans.rst:3
msgid "Loans management"
msgstr "Manajemen pinjaman"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/bank/loans.rst:5
msgid ""
"Odoo's loan management gives a comprehensive list of all loans undertaken by "
"your company in order to maintain a holistic and forecasted view of upcoming "
"due dates (e.g., cash forecast). Set up amortization schedules—or import them"
"—and let Odoo automatically handle monthly interest and principal "
"adjustments so that your financial reports are always accurate with minimal "
"effort."
msgstr ""
"Manajemen pinjaman Odoo memberikan daftar lengkap dari semua pinjaman yang "
"diambil oleh perusahaan Anda untuk mempertahankan pandangan holistik dan "
"perkiraan tanggal jatuh tempo yang akan datang (misalnya, perkiraan kas). "
"Atur jadwal amortisasi—atau impor—dan biarkan Odoo secara otomatis menangani "
"penyesuaian bunga dan pokok bulanan sehingga laporan keuangan Anda selalu "
"akurat dengan upaya minimal."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/bank/loans.rst:11
msgid "Create a new loan"
msgstr "Buat pinjaman baru"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/bank/loans.rst:13
msgid ""
"Create a new loan by going to :menuselection:`Accounting --> Accounting --> "
"Loans`. When creating a new loan, there are three options for how to create "
"amortization schedules:"
msgstr ""
"Buat pinjaman baru dengan membuka :menuselection:`Akuntansi --> "
"Akuntansi --> Pinjaman`. Saat membuat pinjaman baru, ada tiga opsi untuk "
"cara membuat jadwal amortisasi:"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/bank/loans.rst:16
msgid "importing it from a supported file;"
msgstr "mengimpornya dari file yang didukung;"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/bank/loans.rst:17
msgid ""
"calculating it from multiple input values (e.g., the :guilabel:`Amount "
"Borrowed`, the :guilabel:`Duration`, etc.) using the :guilabel:`Compute` "
"button;"
msgstr ""
"menghitungnya dari beberapa nilai input (misalnya, :guilabel:`Jumlah "
"Pinjaman`, :guilabel:`Durasi`, dll.) menggunakan tombol :guilabel:`Hitung`;"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/bank/loans.rst:19
msgid "manually filling in the lines of the schedule."
msgstr "mengisi baris jadwal secara manual."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/bank/loans.rst:21
msgid ""
"In each case, three different fields are required for each line of the "
"amortization schedule: the :guilabel:`Date`, the :guilabel:`Principal`, and "
"the :guilabel:`Interest`."
msgstr ""
"Dalam setiap kasus, tiga bidang berbeda diperlukan untuk setiap baris jadwal "
"amortisasi: :guilabel:`Tanggal`, :guilabel:`Pokok`, dan :guilabel:`Bunga`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/bank/loans.rst:24
msgid ""
"The :guilabel:`Amount Borrowed`, :guilabel:`Interest`, "
"and :guilabel:`Duration` fields will be red if the sum of the lines does not "
"match the total of the amortization schedule lines."
msgstr ""
"Bidang :guilabel:`Jumlah Pinjaman`, :guilabel:`Bunga`, dan "
":guilabel:`Durasi` akan berwarna merah jika jumlah baris tidak sesuai dengan "
"total baris jadwal amortisasi."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/bank/loans.rst:28
msgid "Loan entries mechanism"
msgstr "Mekanisme entri pinjaman"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/bank/loans.rst:30
msgid ""
"When the amount borrowed is credited to a bank account, it should be "
"transferred to a long-term account (defined in the :guilabel:`Loan Settings` "
"tab). Then, upon the validation of the loan, Odoo creates the necessary "
"journal entries so that there is always a holistic and forecasted view of "
"upcoming due dates. The entire process is completely automated with a long-"
"term and short-term principal reclassification mechanism."
msgstr ""
"Ketika jumlah pinjaman dikreditkan ke akun bank, jumlah tersebut harus "
"ditransfer ke akun jangka panjang (didefinisikan di tab "
":guilabel:`Pengaturan Pinjaman`). Kemudian, setelah validasi pinjaman, Odoo "
"membuat entri jurnal yang diperlukan sehingga selalu ada pandangan holistik "
"dan perkiraan tanggal jatuh tempo yang akan datang. Seluruh proses "
"sepenuhnya otomatis dengan mekanisme reklasifikasi pokok jangka panjang dan "
"jangka pendek."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/bank/loans.rst:36
msgid ""
"For each line of the amortization schedule, Odoo creates the following "
"entries:"
msgstr "Untuk setiap baris jadwal amortisasi, Odoo membuat entri berikut:"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/bank/loans.rst:42
msgid "A payment entry on the same date that"
msgstr "Entri pembayaran pada tanggal yang sama yang"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/bank/loans.rst:39
msgid "debits the principal amount to the long-term account;"
msgstr "mendebit jumlah pokok ke akun jangka panjang;"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/bank/loans.rst:40
msgid "debits the interest amount to the expense account;"
msgstr "mendebit jumlah bunga ke akun biaya;"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/bank/loans.rst:41
msgid ""
"credits the payment amount to the short-term account: this is the amount "
"that will be withdrawn by the bank."
msgstr ""
"mengkredit jumlah pembayaran ke akun jangka pendek: ini adalah jumlah yang "
"akan ditarik oleh bank."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/bank/loans.rst:46
msgid "A reclassification entry on the same date that"
msgstr "Entri reklasifikasi pada tanggal yang sama yang"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/bank/loans.rst:45
msgid ""
"debits the sum of the principal amounts of the next 12 months to the long-"
"term account;"
msgstr "mendebit jumlah pokok untuk 12 bulan ke depan ke akun jangka panjang;"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/bank/loans.rst:46
msgid ""
"credits the sum of the principal amounts of the next 12 months to the short-"
"term account."
msgstr "mengkredit jumlah pokok untuk 12 bulan ke depan ke akun jangka pendek."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/bank/loans.rst:48
msgid ""
"A reversed entry of the reclassification entry on *the next day* that simply "
"reverses the previous one."
msgstr ""
"Entri pembalikan dari entri reklasifikasi pada *hari berikutnya* yang "
"membalik entri sebelumnya."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/bank/loans.rst:51
msgid ""
"With this mechanism, month after month, the short-term account is always up "
"to date with the current short-term due amounts."
msgstr ""
"Dengan mekanisme ini, bulan demi bulan, akun jangka pendek selalu up to date "
"dengan jumlah jatuh tempo jangka pendek saat ini."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/bank/loans.rst:55
msgid "Closing a loan"
msgstr "Menutup pinjaman"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/bank/loans.rst:57
msgid ""
"By default, a loan will be closed whenever its last payment entry is posted. "
"However, it can also be manually closed (e.g., because it is being paid off "
"early) by clicking on the :guilabel:`Close` button. A wizard will appear "
"asking from which date the loan should be closed. All draft entries after "
"this date will be deleted too."
msgstr ""
"Secara default, pinjaman akan ditutup ketika entri pembayaran terakhirnya "
"diposting. Namun, pinjaman juga dapat ditutup secara manual (misalnya karena "
"dilunasi lebih awal) dengan mengklik tombol :guilabel:`Close`. Wizard akan "
"muncul menanyakan dari tanggal berapa pinjaman harus ditutup. Semua entri "
"draft setelah tanggal ini juga akan dihapus."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/bank/loans.rst:62
msgid ""
"A loan can also be cancelled. In that case, all entries will be deleted even "
"if they were already posted."
msgstr ""
"Pinjaman juga dapat dibatalkan. Dalam hal ini, semua entri akan dihapus "
"meskipun sudah diposting."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/bank/loans.rst:66
msgid "Loans Analysis Report"
msgstr "Laporan Analisis Pinjaman"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/bank/loans.rst:68
msgid ""
"By going to :menuselection:`Accounting --> Review --> Loans Analysis`, you "
"can access a report with a pivot view of your ongoing loans. By default, the "
"report shows the principal, interest, and total payment for each year for "
"the duration of the loan."
msgstr ""
"Dengan membuka :menuselection:`Accounting --> Review --> Loans Analysis`, "
"Anda dapat mengakses laporan dengan tampilan pivot dari pinjaman yang sedang "
"berjalan. Secara default, laporan menampilkan pokok, bunga, dan total "
"pembayaran untuk setiap tahun selama durasi pinjaman."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/bank/reconciliation.rst:3
#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/payments/batch.rst:49
msgid "Bank reconciliation"
msgstr "Rekonsiliasi bank"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/bank/reconciliation.rst:5
msgid ""
"**Bank reconciliation** is the process of validating :doc:`bank transactions "
"<transactions>`. Many of these transactions are matched with counterpart "
"items related to business records such as :doc:`customer invoices <../"
"customer_invoices>`, :doc:`vendor bills <../vendor_bills>`, "
"and :doc:`payments <../payments>`, while others that may not have a matching "
"counterpart item (such as bank fees) can be written off :ref:`manually "
"<accounting/reconciliation/set-account>` or with :ref:`reconciliation models "
"<accounting/reconciliation/model>`. Not only is bank reconciliation "
"compulsory for most businesses, but it also offers several benefits, such as "
"reduced risk of errors in financial reports, detection of fraudulent "
"activities, and improved cash flow management."
msgstr ""
"**Rekonsiliasi bank** adalah proses validasi :doc:`transaksi bank "
"<transactions>`. Banyak dari transaksi ini dicocokkan dengan item lawan yang "
"terkait dengan catatan bisnis seperti :doc:`faktur pelanggan <../"
"customer_invoices>`, :doc:`tagihan vendor <../vendor_bills>`, dan "
":doc:`pembayaran <../payments>`, sementara yang lain yang mungkin tidak "
"memiliki item lawan yang cocok (seperti biaya bank) dapat dihapuskan "
":ref:`secara manual <accounting/reconciliation/set-account>` atau dengan "
":ref:`model rekonsiliasi <accounting/reconciliation/model>`. Rekonsiliasi "
"bank tidak hanya wajib bagi sebagian besar bisnis, tetapi juga menawarkan "
"beberapa manfaat, seperti mengurangi risiko kesalahan dalam laporan "
"keuangan, mendeteksi aktivitas penipuan, dan meningkatkan manajemen arus kas."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/bank/reconciliation.rst:14
msgid ""
"Thanks to the :ref:`default matching rules <accounting/reconciliation/"
"reconcile>` and customizable bank :doc:`reconciliation models "
"<reconciliation_models>`, Odoo selects the matching items automatically when "
"possible."
msgstr ""
"Berkat :ref:`aturan pencocokan default <accounting/reconciliation/reconcile>"
"` dan :doc:`model rekonsiliasi <reconciliation_models>` bank yang dapat "
"disesuaikan, Odoo memilih item yang cocok secara otomatis bila memungkinkan."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/bank/reconciliation.rst:19
msgid ""
"`Odoo Tutorials: Bank reconciliation <https://www.odoo.com/slides/slide/bank-"
