#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/bank/transactions.rst:33
msgid "A button linked to the chatter. The icon of this button can vary:"
msgstr "Tombol yang terhubung ke chatter. Ikon tombol ini dapat bervariasi:"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/bank/transactions.rst:35
msgid ""
"The :icon:`fa-comments-o` :guilabel:`(comments)` icon displays only on hover "
"and indicates that there are no attachments or activities for the "
