msgstr ""
"Hingga dua :ref:`tombol tindakan <accounting/reconciliation/action-buttons>"
"`, tergantung pada detail transaksi"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/bank/transactions.rst:46
msgid "The balance of the transaction"
msgstr "Saldo transaksi"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/bank/transactions.rst:49
msgid ""
"When the chatter of a transaction is open, a blue tag highlights the related "
"transaction."
msgstr ""
"Ketika chatter suatu transaksi dibuka, tag biru menyoroti transaksi terkait."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/bank/transactions.rst:50
msgid ""
"The chatter can be opened and closed by clicking the :icon:`fa-comments-"
"o` :guilabel:`(comments)` icon and the :icon:`fa-times` :guilabel:`(close)` "
"icon in the top right of the view."
msgstr ""
"Chatter dapat dibuka dan ditutup dengan mengklik ikon :icon:`fa-comments-o` "
":guilabel:`(komentar)` dan ikon :icon:`fa-times` :guilabel:`(tutup)` di "
"sudut kanan atas tampilan."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/bank/transactions.rst:53
msgid ""
"Once a transaction is :doc:`reconciled <reconciliation>`, its action buttons "
"are replaced with the labels of the item(s) it was reconciled with or the "
"account if it was reconciled with the :guilabel:`Set Account` action button."
msgstr ""
"Setelah transaksi :doc:`direkonsiliasi <reconciliation>`, tombol tindakannya "
"diganti dengan label item yang direkonsiliasikan dengannya atau akun jika "
"direkonsiliasi dengan tombol tindakan :guilabel:`Set Account`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/bank/transactions.rst:62
msgid ""
"Duplicate transactions occur when either by human error or :doc:`bank sync "
"<bank_synchronization>` error, the same transaction is created multiple "
"times. The duplicate transaction view identifies potential duplicate "
"transactions so they can be selected and deleted. To access the duplicate "
"transaction view, first access the :guilabel:`Bank Matching` view by going "
"to the :guilabel:`Accounting Dashboard` and clicking the bank journal's "
"name, then open the :icon:`fa-cog` :guilabel:`Actions` menu and "
"click :guilabel:`Find Duplicate Transactions`."
msgstr ""
"Transaksi duplikat terjadi ketika baik karena kesalahan manusia atau "
"kesalahan :doc:`sinkronisasi bank <bank_synchronization>`, transaksi yang "
"sama dibuat beberapa kali. Tampilan transaksi duplikat mengidentifikasi "
"potensi transaksi duplikat sehingga dapat dipilih dan dihapus. Untuk "
"mengakses tampilan transaksi duplikat, pertama akses tampilan "
":guilabel:`Bank Matching` dengan membuka :guilabel:`Dashboard Akuntansi` dan "
"mengklik nama jurnal bank, lalu buka menu :icon:`fa-cog` "
":guilabel:`Tindakan` dan klik :guilabel:`Temukan Transaksi Duplikat`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/bank/transactions.rst:69
msgid ""
"Potential duplicate transactions are identified based on their amount, date, "
"and account number, or (if the transaction is created via :doc:`bank sync "
"<bank_synchronization>`) the transaction ID."
msgstr ""
"Potensi transaksi duplikat diidentifikasi berdasarkan jumlah, tanggal, dan "
"nomor rekening, atau (jika transaksi dibuat melalui :doc:`sinkronisasi bank "
"<bank_synchronization>`) ID transaksi."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/bank/transactions.rst:72
msgid ""
"Select a :guilabel:`Starting Date` to view the corresponding potential "
"duplicate transactions, then select the transactions to delete and "
"click :icon:`fa-trash` :guilabel:`Delete Selected`."
msgstr ""
"Pilih :guilabel:`Starting Date` untuk melihat transaksi duplikat potensial "
"yang sesuai, kemudian pilih transaksi yang akan dihapus dan klik :icon:`fa-"
"trash` :guilabel:`Delete Selected`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/bank/transactions.rst:76
msgid ""
"Any transactions created by :doc:`bank sync <bank_synchronization>` that the "
"bank sync provider determines to be potential duplicates are displayed in "
"the :guilabel:`Provider Duplicates` tab. This tab is only visible if there "
"are any potential duplicates according to the provider."
msgstr ""
"Setiap transaksi yang dibuat oleh :doc:`sinkronisasi bank "
"<bank_synchronization>` yang ditentukan oleh penyedia sinkronisasi bank "
"sebagai duplikat potensial ditampilkan di tab :guilabel:`Provider "
"Duplicates`. Tab ini hanya terlihat jika ada duplikat potensial menurut "
"penyedia."

