msgid ""
"To import a file, go to the :guilabel:`Accounting Dashboard`, click "
"the :icon:`fa-ellipsis-v` :guilabel:`(ellipsis)` icon on "
"the :guilabel:`Bank` journal, and select :guilabel:`Import file`. Next, "
