#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/customer_invoices.rst:127
msgid ""
"If no preferred :guilabel:`Invoice sending` method was set in the contact "
"form, select the method to use for sending the invoice to the customer."
msgstr ""
"Jika metode :guilabel:`Pengiriman faktur` yang disukai tidak diatur di "
"formulir kontak, pilih metode yang akan digunakan untuk mengirim faktur ke "
"pelanggan."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/customer_invoices.rst:130
msgid ""
"Click :guilabel:`Send` if the :guilabel:`by Email` option is selected, or "
"click :guilabel:`Download`."
