#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/customer_invoices.rst:196
msgid ""
"To review outstanding customer invoices and their related due dates, use "
"the :ref:`Aged Receivable <accounting/reporting/aged-receivable>` report. To "
"access it, go to :menuselection:`Accounting --> Reporting --> Aged "
"Receivable`."
msgstr ""
"Untuk meninjau faktur pelanggan yang belum dibayar dan tanggal jatuh tempo "
"terkait, gunakan laporan :ref:`Piutang Jatuh Tempo <accounting/reporting/"
"aged-receivable>`. Untuk mengaksesnya, buka :menuselection:`Akuntansi --> "
"Pelaporan --> Piutang Jatuh Tempo`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/customer_invoices.rst:203
#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/reporting.rst:110
