#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/customer_invoices/electronic_invoicing.rst:168
msgid ""
"The status is updated to :guilabel:`Done` once the invoices have been "
"successfully delivered to the contact's access point."
msgstr ""
"Status diperbarui menjadi :guilabel:`Done` setelah faktur berhasil dikirim "
"ke access point kontak."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/customer_invoices/electronic_invoicing.rst:174
msgid "Receive vendor bills"
msgstr "Terima tagihan vendor"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/customer_invoices/electronic_invoicing.rst:176
msgid ""
"New documents received via Peppol are checked multiple times a day. "
"Depending on the :ref:`registration settings <accounting/e-invoicing/peppol-"
"registration>`, received documents are automatically:"
msgstr ""
"Dokumen baru yang diterima melalui Peppol diperiksa beberapa kali sehari. "
"Tergantung pada :ref:`pengaturan registrasi <accounting/e-invoicing/peppol-"
"registration>`, dokumen yang diterima secara otomatis:"

