msgid ""
"either imported into the purchase journal set in the :guilabel:`PEPPOL "
"Electronic Invoicing` section, and corresponding vendor bills are created as "
"drafts;"
msgstr ""
"diimpor ke dalam jurnal pembelian yang diatur di bagian :guilabel:`PEPPOL "
"Electronic Invoicing`, dan tagihan vendor terkait dibuat sebagai draf;"

