msgid ""
"or received via the :ref:`Documents app <accounting/e-invoicing/receive-"
"vendor-bills-documents-app>`."
msgstr ""
"atau diterima melalui :ref:`aplikasi Documents <accounting/e-invoicing/"
"receive-vendor-bills-documents-app>`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/customer_invoices/electronic_invoicing.rst:186
msgid ""
"To manually trigger the scheduled action used to retrieve incoming Peppol "
"documents, enable :ref:`developer mode <developer-mode>`, open the Settings "
"app, go to :menuselection:`Settings --> Technical --> Scheduled actions`, "
"and search for :guilabel:`Peppol: retrieve new documents`. Open the "
"scheduled action, then click :guilabel:`Run Manually`."
msgstr ""
"Untuk memicu tindakan terjadwal yang digunakan untuk mengambil dokumen "
"Peppol yang masuk secara manual, aktifkan :ref:`mode pengembang <developer-"
"mode>`, buka aplikasi Settings, buka :menuselection:`Settings --> "
"Technical --> Scheduled actions`, dan cari :guilabel:`Peppol: retrieve new "
"documents`. Buka tindakan terjadwal, lalu klik :guilabel:`Run Manually`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/customer_invoices/electronic_invoicing.rst:194
msgid "Vendor bills reception in Documents"
msgstr "Penerimaan tagihan vendor di Documents"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/customer_invoices/electronic_invoicing.rst:197
