"aktifkan :ref:`file centralization <documents/file-centralization>` untuk "
"dokumen :guilabel:`Accounting`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/customer_invoices/electronic_invoicing.rst:205
msgid ""
"Open the Accounting app, go to :menuselection:`Accounting --> Configuration "
