"merekomendasikan untuk berkonsultasi dengan penasihat pajak atau profesional "
"hukum yang familiar dengan peraturan e-invoicing Argentina untuk memastikan "
"kepatuhan yang disesuaikan dengan kebutuhan bisnis spesifik Anda."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/customer_invoices/electronic_invoicing/austria.rst:5
msgid "Odoo electronic invoicing in Austria"
msgstr "E-invoicing elektronik Odoo di Austria"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/customer_invoices/electronic_invoicing/austria.rst:7
msgid ""
"Odoo Invoicing is your trusted partner for safe, efficient, and legally "
"compliant e-invoicing solutions tailored to Austria's regulatory standards, "
"and compatible with the European `Peppol <https://peppol.org/about/>`_ "
"framework."
msgstr ""
"Odoo Penagihan adalah mitra terpercaya Anda untuk solusi e-invoicing yang "
"aman, efisien, dan patuh secara hukum yang disesuaikan dengan standar "
"regulasi Austria, dan kompatibel dengan kerangka kerja `Peppol <https://"
"peppol.org/about/>`_ Eropa."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/customer_invoices/electronic_invoicing/austria.rst:12
msgid "Legal framework for e-invoicing in Austria"
msgstr "Kerangka hukum untuk e-invoicing di Austria"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/customer_invoices/electronic_invoicing/austria.rst:14
msgid ""
"In Austria, businesses must adhere to e-invoicing laws that ensure secure, "
"authentic, and storable transactions. The main regulation governing e-"
"invoicing requirements in Austria is the `Austrian VAT Act (UStG) <https://"
"www.ris.bka.gv.at/GeltendeFassung.wxe?"
"Abfrage=Bundesnormen&Gesetzesnummer=10004873>`_ and its related e-invoicing "
"standards for public procurement (`BGBI. I Nr. 32/2019 <https://"
"360.lexisnexis.at/d/rechtsnorm-ris/"
"32_bundesgesetz_mit_dem_das_beamten_dienstrechtsge/"
"b_bgbl_2019_2019_I_32_46c550bf37>`_), which aligns with `EU Directive "
"2014/55/EU <https://eur-lex.europa.eu/legal-content/EN/TXT/?"
"uri=CELEX%3A32014L0055>`_. These laws mandate that all businesses engaged "
"in :abbr:`B2G (business-to-government)` transactions must use e-invoicing, "
"and increasingly, e-invoicing is encouraged for B2B transactions to improve "
"tax compliance and transparency."
msgstr ""
"Di Austria, bisnis harus mematuhi hukum e-invoicing yang memastikan "
"transaksi yang aman, autentik, dan dapat disimpan. Peraturan utama yang "
"mengatur persyaratan e-invoicing di Austria adalah `Austrian VAT Act (UStG) "
"<https://www.ris.bka.gv.at/"
"GeltendeFassung.wxe?Abfrage=Bundesnormen&Gesetzesnummer=10004873>`_ dan "
"standar e-invoicing terkait untuk pengadaan publik (`BGBI. I Nr. 32/2019 "
"<https://360.lexisnexis.at/d/rechtsnorm-ris/"
"32_bundesgesetz_mit_dem_das_beamten_dienstrechtsge/"
"b_bgbl_2019_2019_I_32_46c550bf37>`_), yang selaras dengan `EU Directive 2014/"
"55/EU <https://eur-lex.europa.eu/legal-content/EN/TXT/"
"?uri=CELEX%3A32014L0055>`_. Hukum ini mewajibkan semua bisnis yang terlibat "
"dalam transaksi :abbr:`B2G (business-to-government)` untuk menggunakan e-"
"invoicing, dan semakin banyak e-invoicing didorong untuk transaksi B2B untuk "
"meningkatkan kepatuhan pajak dan transparansi."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/customer_invoices/electronic_invoicing/austria.rst:24
msgid "Compliance with Austrian e-invoicing regulations"
msgstr "Kepatuhan terhadap peraturan e-invoicing Austria"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/customer_invoices/electronic_invoicing/austria.rst:26
#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/customer_invoices/electronic_invoicing/belgium.rst:28
#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/customer_invoices/electronic_invoicing/croatia.rst:27
#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/customer_invoices/electronic_invoicing/estonia.rst:26
msgid ""
"Odoo Invoicing makes it easy for businesses to send, store, and ensure the "
"integrity of their invoices. Here is how Odoo ensures compliance:"
msgstr ""
"Odoo Penagihan memudahkan bisnis untuk mengirim, menyimpan, dan memastikan "
"integritas invoice mereka. Berikut adalah bagaimana Odoo memastikan "
"kepatuhan:"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/customer_invoices/electronic_invoicing/austria.rst:29
msgid ""
"**Supported format**: Odoo supports standard e-invoice formats such as PDF "
"with digital signatures and XML in :abbr:`UBL (Universal Business Language)` "
"format, which are fully compatible with e-rechnung.gv.at, Austria's central "
"electronic invoicing platform for public procurement transactions. Any "
"platform can be used if connected to the authentication services of the "
"Federal Service Portal (:abbr:`USP (Unternehmensserviceportal)`) e-"
"rechnung.gv.at for e-invoicing transmission."
msgstr ""
"**Format yang didukung**: Odoo mendukung format e-invoice standar seperti "
"PDF dengan tanda tangan digital dan XML dalam format :abbr:`UBL (Universal "
"Business Language)`, yang sepenuhnya kompatibel dengan e-rechnung.gv.at, "
"platform e-invoicing elektronik pusat Austria untuk transaksi pengadaan "
"publik. Platform apa pun dapat digunakan jika terhubung ke layanan "
"autentikasi Federal Service Portal (:abbr:`USP (Unternehmensserviceportal)`) "
"e-rechnung.gv.at untuk transmisi e-invoicing."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/customer_invoices/electronic_invoicing/austria.rst:35
msgid ""
"**Secure storage and retrieval**: In accordance with the Austrian "
"requirement to store invoices for a minimum of seven years, Odoo securely "
"archives all invoices in a tamper-proof system, ensuring that they can be "
"easily retrieved during audits."
msgstr ""
"**Penyimpanan dan pengambilan yang aman**: Sesuai dengan persyaratan Austria "
"untuk menyimpan invoice minimal tujuh tahun, Odoo mengarsipkan semua invoice "
"dengan aman dalam sistem yang tahan manipulasi, memastikan bahwa mereka "
"dapat dengan mudah diambil selama audit."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/customer_invoices/electronic_invoicing/austria.rst:38
msgid ""
"**Automatic VAT calculation and reporting**: Odoo Invoicing helps businesses "
"stay in line with Austrian VAT requirements by automatically calculating and "
"including VAT in invoices and ensuring that each invoice follows the legal "
"format for B2B and :abbr:`B2G (business-to-government)` transactions."
msgstr ""
"**Perhitungan dan pelaporan PPN otomatis**: Odoo Penagihan membantu bisnis "
"tetap sejalan dengan persyaratan PPN Austria dengan secara otomatis "
"menghitung dan memasukkan PPN dalam invoice dan memastikan bahwa setiap "
"invoice mengikuti format hukum untuk transaksi B2B dan :abbr:`B2G (business-"
"to-government)`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/customer_invoices/electronic_invoicing/austria.rst:44
msgid ""
":doc:`Austria fiscal localization documentation <../../../"
"fiscal_localizations/austria>`"
msgstr ""
