#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/customer_invoices/electronic_invoicing/ireland.rst:11
msgid "Legal framework for e-invoicing in Ireland"
msgstr "Kerangka hukum untuk e-invoicing di Irlandia"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/customer_invoices/electronic_invoicing/ireland.rst:13
msgid ""
"In Ireland, businesses must comply with e-invoicing regulations to ensure "
"secure, authentic, and storable transactions. The legal framework for e-"
"invoicing is primarily shaped by `EU Directive 2014/55/EU <https://eur-"
"lex.europa.eu/legal-content/EN/TXT/?uri=CELEX%3A32014L0055>`_, which "
"mandates the use of electronic invoicing in :abbr:`B2G (business-to-"
"government)` transactions. Irish public sector bodies must accept electronic "
"invoices that comply with the European Standard EN 16931. E-invoicing in the "
"public sector is facilitated through the Peppol network, providing a "
"streamlined and standardized platform for invoicing. While not mandatory for "
"B2B transactions, e-invoicing is increasingly encouraged to enhance "
"efficiency, transparency, and compliance."
msgstr ""
"Di Irlandia, bisnis harus mematuhi peraturan e-invoicing untuk memastikan "
"transaksi yang aman, autentik, dan dapat disimpan. Kerangka hukum untuk e-"
"invoicing terutama dibentuk oleh `Direktif UE 2014/55/EU <https://eur-"
"lex.europa.eu/legal-content/EN/TXT/?uri=CELEX%3A32014L0055>`_, yang "
"mengamanatkan penggunaan faktur elektronik dalam transaksi :abbr:`B2G "
"(business-to-government)`. Badan sektor publik Irlandia harus menerima "
"faktur elektronik yang mematuhi Standar Eropa EN 16931. E-invoicing di "
"sektor publik difasilitasi melalui jaringan Peppol, menyediakan platform "
"yang efisien dan terstandarisasi untuk penagihan. Meskipun tidak wajib untuk "
"transaksi B2B, e-invoicing semakin didorong untuk meningkatkan efisiensi, "
"transparansi, dan kepatuhan."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/customer_invoices/electronic_invoicing/ireland.rst:23
msgid "Compliance with Irish e-invoicing regulations"
msgstr "Kepatuhan terhadap peraturan e-invoicing Irlandia"

