#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/get_started/chart_of_accounts.rst:5
msgid ""
"The **chart of accounts (COA)** is the list of all the accounts used to "
"record financial transactions in the general ledger of an organization. The "
"chart of accounts can be found under :menuselection:`Accounting --> "
"Configuration --> Chart of Accounts`."
msgstr ""
"**Bagan Akun (COA)** adalah daftar semua akun yang digunakan untuk merekam "
"transaksi finansial di buku besar umum organisasi. Bagan akun dapat "
"ditemukan di :menuselection:`Akuntansi --> Konfigurasi --> Bagan Akun`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/get_started/chart_of_accounts.rst:9
msgid ""
"When browsing your chart of accounts, you can sort the accounts "
"by :guilabel:`Code`, :guilabel:`Account Name`, or :guilabel:`Type`, but "
"other options are available in the drop-down menu"
msgstr ""
"Saat melihat bagan akun, Anda dapat menyortir akun "
"berdasarkan :guilabel:`Kode`, :guilabel:`Nama Akun`, atau :guilabel:`Tipe`, "
"tapi opsi lain tersedia di menu drop-down"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/get_started/chart_of_accounts.rst:None
msgid "Drop-down toggle button"
msgstr "Tombol toggle drop-down"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/get_started/chart_of_accounts.rst:None
msgid "Group the accounts by type in Odoo Accounting"
msgstr "Kelompokkan akun berdasarkan tipe di Akuntansi Odoo"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/get_started/chart_of_accounts.rst:21
msgid "Configuration of an account"
msgstr "Konfigurasi akun"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/get_started/chart_of_accounts.rst:23
msgid ""
"The country you select during the creation of your database (or additional "
"company in your database) determines which :doc:`fiscal localization package "
"<../../fiscal_localizations>` is installed by default. This package adds a "
"standard chart of accounts already configured according to the country's "
"regulations, including expense accounts that may be :ref:`linked to default "
"asset models <chart-of-account/assets>`. You can use the chart of accounts "
"directly or modify it according to your company's needs."
msgstr ""
"Negara yang Anda pilih saat pembuatan database (atau perusahaan tambahan di "
"database Anda) menentukan :doc:`paket fitur lokal fiskal <../../"
"fiscal_localizations>` yang diinstal secara default. Paket ini menambahkan "
"bagan akun standar yang sudah dikonfigurasi sesuai dengan peraturan negara, "
"termasuk akun beban yang mungkin :ref:`dihubungkan ke model aset default "
"<chart-of-account/assets>`. Anda dapat menggunakan bagan akun secara "
"langsung atau mengubahnya sesuai dengan kebutuhan perusahaan Anda."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/get_started/chart_of_accounts.rst:30
msgid ""
"To create a new account, go to :menuselection:`Accounting --> Configuration "
"--> Chart of Accounts`, click :guilabel:`Create`, and fill in (at the "
"minimum) the required fields (:guilabel:`Code, Account Name, Type`)."
msgstr ""
"Untuk membuat akun baru, kunjungi :menuselection:`Akuntansi --> Konfigurasi "
"--> Bagan Akun`, klik :guilabel:`Buat`, dan isi (minimal) field-field yang "
"diperlukan (:guilabel:`Kode, Nama Akun, Tipe`)."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/get_started/chart_of_accounts.rst:35
msgid ""
"It is not possible to modify the **fiscal localization** of a company once a "
"journal entry has been posted."
msgstr ""
"Anda tidak dapat memodifikasi **fitur lokal fiskal** perusahaan setelah "
"entri jurnal telah diposting."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/get_started/chart_of_accounts.rst:39
