":guilabel:`Jumlah` di jendela :guilabel:`Bayar`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/payments.rst:367
msgid ""
"In the case of a partial payment (when the :guilabel:`Amount` paid is less "
"than the total remaining amount on the invoice or the bill), "
"the :guilabel:`Payment Difference` field displays the outstanding balance. "
"There are two options:"
msgstr ""
"Dalam kasus pembayaran parsial (ketika :guilabel:`Jumlah` yang dibayarkan "
"kurang dari total jumlah tersisa pada faktur atau tagihan), bidang "
":guilabel:`Selisih Pembayaran` menampilkan saldo terutang. Ada dua opsi:"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/payments.rst:371
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Keep open`: Keep the invoice or the bill open and mark it with "
"a :guilabel:`Partial` banner;"
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Tetap buka`: Biarkan faktur atau tagihan tetap terbuka dan tandai "
"dengan banner :guilabel:`Parsial`;"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/payments.rst:373
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Mark as fully paid`: Select an account in the :guilabel:`Post "
"Difference In` field and change the :guilabel:`Label` if needed. A journal "
"entry will be created to balance the accounts payable or receivable with the "
"selected account."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Tandai sebagai lunas`: Pilih akun di bidang :guilabel:`Posting "
"Selisih Ke` dan ubah :guilabel:`Label` jika diperlukan. Entri jurnal akan "
"dibuat untuk menyeimbangkan akun utang atau piutang dengan akun yang dipilih."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/payments.rst:0
msgid "register a partial payment"
msgstr "mendaftarkan pembayaran parsial"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/payments.rst:383
msgid "Reconciling payments with bank transactions"
msgstr "Merekonsiliasi pembayaran dengan transaksi bank"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/payments.rst:389
msgid ""
"Once a payment has been registered, the status of the invoice or bill "
"is :guilabel:`In payment`. The next step is :doc:`reconciling <bank/"
"reconciliation>` the related :doc:`bank transaction <bank/transactions>` "
"line with the invoice or bill to finalize the payment workflow and mark the "
"invoice or bill as :guilabel:`Paid`."
msgstr ""
"Setelah pembayaran didaftarkan, status faktur atau tagihan adalah "
":guilabel:`Dalam pembayaran`. Langkah selanjutnya adalah "
":doc:`merekonsiliasi <bank/reconciliation>` baris :doc:`transaksi bank <bank/"
"transactions>` terkait dengan faktur atau tagihan untuk menyelesaikan alur "
"kerja pembayaran dan menandai faktur atau tagihan sebagai :guilabel:`Lunas`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/payments.rst:396
msgid ""
"Once a payment has been registered, the status of the invoice or bill "
"is :guilabel:`In payment`. The next step is :doc:`reconciling <bank/"
"reconciliation>` the payment with the related :doc:`bank transaction <bank/"
"transactions>` line to finalize the payment workflow and mark the invoice or "
"bill as :guilabel:`Paid`."
msgstr ""
"Setelah pembayaran didaftarkan, status faktur atau tagihan adalah "
":guilabel:`Dalam pembayaran`. Langkah selanjutnya adalah "
":doc:`merekonsiliasi <bank/reconciliation>` pembayaran dengan baris "
":doc:`transaksi bank <bank/transactions>` terkait untuk menyelesaikan alur "
"kerja pembayaran dan menandai faktur atau tagihan sebagai :guilabel:`Lunas`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/payments/batch.rst:3
#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/australia.rst:410
msgid "Batch payments"
msgstr "Pembayaran batch"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/payments/batch.rst:5
msgid ""
"Batch payments allow grouping payments from multiple customers or vendors "
"into a single batch and generating a detailed deposit slip or payment file "
"with a batch reference. This reference can be used "
"during :doc:`reconciliation <../bank/reconciliation>` to match bank "
"transactions with the corresponding payments. This feature is particularly "
"useful for submitting :doc:`SEPA Direct Debit payments <batch_sdd>`, "
"depositing cash payments or :ref:`checks <accounting/payments/checks>`, or "
"generating outgoing payment files, such as :doc:`SEPA <pay_sepa>` "
"or :ref:`NACHA <l10n_us/nacha>`."
msgstr ""
"Pembayaran batch memungkinkan pengelompokan pembayaran dari beberapa "
"pelanggan atau vendor ke dalam satu batch dan menghasilkan slip setoran "
"terperinci atau file pembayaran dengan referensi batch. Referensi ini dapat "
"digunakan selama :doc:`rekonsiliasi <../bank/reconciliation>` untuk "
"mencocokkan transaksi bank dengan pembayaran yang sesuai. Fitur ini sangat "
"berguna untuk mengirimkan :doc:`pembayaran SEPA Direct Debit <batch_sdd>`, "
"menyetorkan pembayaran tunai atau :ref:`cek <accounting/payments/checks>`, "
"atau menghasilkan file pembayaran keluar, seperti :doc:`SEPA <pay_sepa>` "
"atau :ref:`NACHA <l10n_us/nacha>`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/payments/batch.rst:15
msgid ""
"To enable batch payments, go to :menuselection:`Accounting --> Configuration "
"--> Settings`, scroll down to the :guilabel:`Customer Payments` section, and "
"enable :guilabel:`Batch Payments`."
msgstr ""
"Untuk mengaktifkan pembayaran batch, buka :menuselection:`Akuntansi --> "
"Konfigurasi --> Pengaturan`, gulir ke bawah ke bagian :guilabel:`Pembayaran "
"Pelanggan`, lalu aktifkan :guilabel:`Pembayaran Batch`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/payments/batch.rst:21
msgid "Batch creation"
msgstr "Pembuatan batch"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/payments/batch.rst:23
msgid "To create a batch payment, follow these steps:"
msgstr "Untuk membuat pembayaran batch, ikuti langkah-langkah berikut:"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/payments/batch.rst:25
msgid ""
"Make sure all payments to be included in the batch have "
"been :ref:`registered <accounting/payments/from-invoice-bill>`."
msgstr ""
"Pastikan semua pembayaran yang akan dimasukkan dalam batch telah "
":ref:`didaftarkan <accounting/payments/from-invoice-bill>`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/payments/batch.rst:27
msgid "Go to :menuselection:`Accounting --> Customers --> Payments`."
msgstr "Buka :menuselection:`Akuntansi --> Pelanggan --> Pembayaran`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/payments/batch.rst:28
msgid "Select the payments to include in the batch."
msgstr "Pilih pembayaran yang akan dimasukkan dalam batch."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/payments/batch.rst:31
msgid ""
"All payments in the batch must use the same payment method. If needed, "
"payments can be grouped using the :guilabel:`Payment Method Line`."
msgstr ""
"Semua pembayaran dalam batch harus menggunakan metode pembayaran yang sama. "
"Jika diperlukan, pembayaran dapat dikelompokkan menggunakan "
":guilabel:`Payment Method Line`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/payments/batch.rst:34
msgid ""
"Click :guilabel:`Create batch` or click :icon:`fa-cog` :guilabel:`Actions` "
"and select :guilabel:`Create batch payment`."
msgstr ""
"Klik :guilabel:`Create batch` atau klik :icon:`fa-cog` :guilabel:`Actions` "
"dan pilih :guilabel:`Create batch payment`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/payments/batch.rst:36
msgid ""
"In the batch payment form, review the selected payments. If any individual "
"payments were missed, click :guilabel:`Add a line` and select the missing "
"payments to be included in the batch."
msgstr ""
"Pada formulir batch payment, tinjau pembayaran yang dipilih. Jika ada "
"pembayaran individual yang terlewat, klik :guilabel:`Add a line` dan pilih "
"pembayaran yang hilang untuk dimasukkan ke dalam batch."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/payments/batch.rst:38
msgid ""
"Once all relevant payments are included, click :guilabel:`Validate` to "
"finalize the batch."
msgstr ""
"Setelah semua pembayaran yang relevan disertakan, klik :guilabel:`Validate` "
"untuk menyelesaikan batch."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/payments/batch.rst:41
msgid "Once validated, no additional payments can be added to a batch."
msgstr ""
"Setelah divalidasi, tidak ada pembayaran tambahan yang dapat ditambahkan ke "
"batch."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/payments/batch.rst:44
msgid "Click :guilabel:`Print` to download a list of the included payments."
msgstr ""
"Klik :guilabel:`Print` untuk mengunduh daftar pembayaran yang disertakan."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/payments/batch.rst:45
msgid ""
"To view existing batch payments, go to :menuselection:`Accounting --> "
"Customers --> Batch Payments`."
msgstr ""
"Untuk melihat batch payment yang ada, buka :menuselection:`Akuntansi --> "
"Pelanggan --> Batch Payments`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/payments/batch.rst:51
msgid ""
"Once the bank transactions :doc:`have been created <../bank/transactions>` "
"in your database, you can :ref:`reconcile <accounting/reconciliation/"
"reconcile>` them with the batch payment."
msgstr ""
"Setelah transaksi bank :doc:`dibuat <../bank/transactions>` di database "
"Anda, Anda dapat :ref:`merekonsiliasi <accounting/reconciliation/reconcile>` "
"dengan batch payment."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/payments/batch.rst:56
msgid ":doc:`batch_sdd`"
msgstr ":doc:`batch_sdd`"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/payments/batch_sdd.rst:3
msgid "SEPA Direct Debit (SDD) customer payments"
msgstr "Pembayaran pelanggan SEPA Direct Debit (SDD)"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/payments/batch_sdd.rst:7
msgid ""
"SEPA (Single Euro Payments Area) is a payment-integration initiative of the "
"European Union that facilitates standardized and simplified electronic "
"payments in euros across participating countries. With **SEPA Direct Debit** "
"(SDD), customers sign a mandate that authorizes you to collect future "
"payments from their bank accounts. This is particularly useful for recurring "
"payments based on a :doc:`subscription </applications/sales/subscriptions>`."
msgstr ""
"SEPA (Single Euro Payments Area) adalah inisiatif integrasi pembayaran Uni "
"Eropa yang memfasilitasi pembayaran elektronik standar dan disederhanakan "
"dalam euro di seluruh negara yang berpartisipasi. Dengan **SEPA Direct "
"Debit** (SDD), pelanggan menandatangani mandat yang mengotorisasi Anda untuk "
"mengumpulkan pembayaran di masa mendatang dari rekening bank mereka. Ini "
"sangat berguna untuk pembayaran berulang berdasarkan :doc:`langganan </"
"applications/sales/subscriptions>`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/payments/batch_sdd.rst:13
msgid ""
"You can record customer |sdd| mandates in Odoo and generate XML files "
"listing payments to be collected with the mandates. :ref:`Uploading these "
"files to your bank <accounting/batch_sdd/XML>` instructs them to collect "
"these payments from your customers."
msgstr ""
"Anda dapat mencatat mandat |sdd| pelanggan di Odoo dan menghasilkan file XML "
"yang berisi daftar pembayaran yang akan dikumpulkan dengan mandat. "
":ref:`Mengunggah file ini ke bank Anda <accounting/batch_sdd/XML>` "
"menginstruksikan mereka untuk mengumpulkan pembayaran ini dari pelanggan "
"Anda."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/payments/batch_sdd.rst:18
msgid ""
"|sdd| is supported by all SEPA countries, which includes the 27 member "
"states of the European Union as well as additional countries."
msgstr ""
"|sdd| didukung oleh semua negara SEPA, yang mencakup 27 negara anggota Uni "
"Eropa serta negara tambahan."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/payments/batch_sdd.rst:20
msgid ""
"`List of all SEPA countries <https://www.europeanpaymentscouncil.eu/document-"
"library/other/epc-list-sepa-scheme-countries>`_."
msgstr ""
"`Daftar semua negara SEPA <https://www.europeanpaymentscouncil.eu/document-"
"library/other/epc-list-sepa-scheme-countries>`_."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/payments/batch_sdd.rst:29
msgid "Creditor identifier"
msgstr "Identifier kreditor"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/payments/batch_sdd.rst:31
msgid ""
"To enable |sdd| for customer payments, go to :menuselection:`Accounting --> "
"Configuration --> Settings`, scroll to the :guilabel:`Customer Payments` "
"section, enable :guilabel:`SEPA Direct Debit (SDD)`, and "
"click :guilabel:`Save`. Then, scroll to the :guilabel:`Customer Payments` "
"section again, set the company's :guilabel:`Creditor Identifier`, and "
"click :guilabel:`Save`."
msgstr ""
"Untuk mengaktifkan |sdd| untuk pembayaran pelanggan, buka "
":menuselection:`Akuntansi --> Konfigurasi --> Pengaturan`, gulir ke bagian "
":guilabel:`Customer Payments`, aktifkan :guilabel:`SEPA Direct Debit (SDD)`, "
"dan klik :guilabel:`Save`. Kemudian, gulir ke bagian :guilabel:`Customer "
"Payments` lagi, atur :guilabel:`Creditor Identifier` perusahaan, dan klik "
":guilabel:`Save`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/payments/batch_sdd.rst:37
msgid ""
"The creditor identifier is provided by your bank or the authority "
"responsible for delivering them in your country. For testing purposes, you "
"can use the test creditor identifier `DE98ZZZ09999999999`."
msgstr ""
"Identifier kreditor disediakan oleh bank Anda atau otoritas yang bertanggung "
"jawab untuk mengeluarkannya di negara Anda. Untuk tujuan pengujian, Anda "
"dapat menggunakan identifier kreditor uji `DE98ZZZ09999999999`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/payments/batch_sdd.rst:42
msgid "PAIN file version"
msgstr "Versi file PAIN"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/payments/batch_sdd.rst:44
msgid ""
"By default, the :ref:`SEPA-compliant XML files <accounting/batch_sdd/XML>` "
"generated by Odoo use the |sdd| **PAIN.008.001.02** format. If your bank "
"requires the updated 2023 version, go to :menuselection:`Accounting --> "
"Configuration --> Journals` and select the :guilabel:`Bank` journal. Then, "
"in the :guilabel:`Incoming Payments` tab, set the :guilabel:`SEPA Pain "
"version` field to :guilabel:`Updated 2023 (Pain 008.001.08)`."
msgstr ""
"Secara default, :ref:`file XML yang sesuai dengan SEPA <accounting/batch_sdd/"
"XML>` yang dihasilkan oleh Odoo menggunakan format |sdd| "
"**PAIN.008.001.02**. Jika bank Anda memerlukan versi 2023 yang diperbarui, "
"buka :menuselection:`Akuntansi --> Konfigurasi --> Jurnal` dan pilih jurnal "
":guilabel:`Bank`. Kemudian, di tab :guilabel:`Incoming Payments`, atur "
"bidang :guilabel:`SEPA Pain version` ke :guilabel:`Updated 2023 (Pain "
"008.001.08)`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/payments/batch_sdd.rst:51
msgid ""
"`SEPA Direct Debit Core Customer-to-PSP Implementation Guidelines <https://"
"www.europeanpaymentscouncil.eu/document-library/implementation-guidelines/"
"sepa-direct-debit-core-customer-psp-implementation-0>`_."
msgstr ""
"`SEPA Direct Debit Core Customer-to-PSP Implementation Guidelines <https://"
"www.europeanpaymentscouncil.eu/document-library/implementation-guidelines/"
"sepa-direct-debit-core-customer-psp-implementation-0>`_."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/payments/batch_sdd.rst:57
msgid "SEPA Direct Debit Mandates"
msgstr "Mandat SEPA Direct Debit"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/payments/batch_sdd.rst:59
msgid ""
"An |sdd| mandate is a legal document authorizing a company to debit funds "
"from a customer's bank account. It includes key information, such as the "
"customer's name and IBAN, the mandate's start and end date, and the "
"mandate's unique identifier. The mandate form must be filled in and signed "
"by the customer."
msgstr ""
"Mandat |sdd| adalah dokumen legal yang mengotorisasi perusahaan untuk "
"mendebit dana dari rekening bank pelanggan. Ini mencakup informasi penting, "
"seperti nama pelanggan dan IBAN, tanggal mulai dan akhir mandat, dan "
"identifier unik mandat. Formulir mandat harus diisi dan ditandatangani oleh "
"pelanggan."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/payments/batch_sdd.rst:65
msgid "Creating mandates"
msgstr "Membuat mandat"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/payments/batch_sdd.rst:67
msgid "To create an |sdd| mandate:"
msgstr "Untuk membuat mandat |sdd|:"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/payments/batch_sdd.rst:69
msgid ""
"Go to :menuselection:`Accounting --> Customers --> Direct Debit Mandates`."
msgstr ""
"Buka :menuselection:`Akuntansi --> Pelanggan --> Mandat Debit Langsung`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/payments/batch_sdd.rst:70
msgid "Click :guilabel:`New` and fill out the fields."
msgstr "Klik :guilabel:`Baru` dan isi kolom-kolomnya."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/payments/batch_sdd.rst:71
msgid ""
"Click :guilabel:`Send & Print`, optionally edit the email, then "
"click :guilabel:`Send & Print` to email the mandate form to the customer for "
"signature."
msgstr ""
"Klik :guilabel:`Kirim & Cetak`, opsional edit emailnya, lalu klik "
":guilabel:`Kirim & Cetak` untuk mengirim email formulir mandat ke pelanggan "
"untuk ditandatangani."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/payments/batch_sdd.rst:73
msgid "Click :guilabel:`Validate` to activate the mandate."
msgstr "Klik :guilabel:`Validasi` untuk mengaktifkan mandat."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/payments/batch_sdd.rst:76
msgid ""
"A valid IBAN must be defined in the :guilabel:`Account Number` field of "
"the :doc:`bank journal <../bank>` used to receive |sdd| payments for the "
"mandate."
msgstr ""
"IBAN yang valid harus didefinisikan di kolom :guilabel:`Nomor Akun` dari "
":doc:`jurnal bank <../bank>` yang digunakan untuk menerima pembayaran |sdd| "
"untuk mandat."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/payments/batch_sdd.rst:80
msgid ""
"To print the mandate form after the mandate has been validated, click "
"the :icon:`fa-cog` (:guilabel:`gear`) icon, then select :guilabel:`Mandate "
"form`."
msgstr ""
"Untuk mencetak formulir mandat setelah mandat divalidasi, klik ikon "
":icon:`fa-cog` (:guilabel:`roda gigi`), lalu pilih :guilabel:`Formulir "
"mandat`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/payments/batch_sdd.rst:82
msgid ""
"The :guilabel:`SDD Scheme` depends on the type of customer: "
"Select :guilabel:`CORE` for B2C customers and :guilabel:`B2B` for B2B "
"customers."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Skema SDD` tergantung pada jenis pelanggan: Pilih "
":guilabel:`CORE` untuk pelanggan B2C dan :guilabel:`B2B` untuk pelanggan B2B."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/payments/batch_sdd.rst:84
msgid ""
"|sdd| mandates are created automatically for :ref:`online payments made with "
"SDD <payment_providers/bank_payments/sdd>`."
msgstr ""
"Mandat |sdd| dibuat secara otomatis untuk :ref:`pembayaran online yang "
"dilakukan dengan SDD <payment_providers/bank_payments/sdd>`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/payments/batch_sdd.rst:87
msgid ""
"Once an |sdd| mandate is active, subsequent |sdd| payments can be generated "
"via Odoo and :ref:`uploaded to your online banking interface <accounting/"
"batch_sdd/XML>`. Customers with an active |sdd| mandate can also use this "
"payment method for :ref:`online purchases <payment_providers/bank_payments/"
"sdd>`."
msgstr ""
"Setelah mandat |sdd| aktif, pembayaran |sdd| berikutnya dapat dibuat melalui "
"Odoo dan :ref:`diunggah ke antarmuka perbankan online Anda <accounting/"
"batch_sdd/XML>`. Pelanggan dengan mandat |sdd| aktif juga dapat menggunakan "
"metode pembayaran ini untuk :ref:`pembelian online <payment_providers/"
"bank_payments/sdd>`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/payments/batch_sdd.rst:95
msgid "Closing or revoking a mandate"
msgstr "Menutup atau mencabut mandat"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/payments/batch_sdd.rst:97
msgid ""
"|sdd| mandates are closed automatically after their :guilabel:`End Date`. If "
"this field is left empty, the mandate remains active until it is closed or "
"revoked. To close or revoke a mandate, go to :menuselection:`Accounting --> "
"Customers --> Direct Debit Mandates`, select the relevant mandate, and "
"click :guilabel:`Close` or :guilabel:`Revoke`."
msgstr ""
"Mandat |sdd| ditutup secara otomatis setelah :guilabel:`Tanggal Berakhir`. "
"Jika kolom ini dibiarkan kosong, mandat tetap aktif hingga ditutup atau "
"dicabut. Untuk menutup atau mencabut mandat, buka "
":menuselection:`Akuntansi --> Pelanggan --> Mandat Debit Langsung`, pilih "
"mandat yang relevan, dan klik :guilabel:`Tutup` atau :guilabel:`Cabut`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/payments/batch_sdd.rst:102
msgid ""
"**Closing** a mandate updates the mandate's end date to the current day. "
"Invoices issued after the present day will not be processed with an |sdd| "
"payment. **Revoking** a mandate disables the mandate immediately. No |sdd| "
"payment can be registered anymore, regardless of the invoice's date. "
"However, payments that have already been registered are still included in "
"the next :ref:`SDD XML file <accounting/batch_sdd/XML>`."
msgstr ""
"**Menutup** mandat memperbarui tanggal akhir mandat menjadi hari ini. Faktur "
"yang diterbitkan setelah hari ini tidak akan diproses dengan pembayaran "
"|sdd|. **Mencabut** mandat menonaktifkan mandat segera. Tidak ada pembayaran "
"|sdd| yang dapat didaftarkan lagi, terlepas dari tanggal faktur. Namun, "
"pembayaran yang telah didaftarkan masih disertakan dalam :ref:`file XML SDD "
"<accounting/batch_sdd/XML>` berikutnya."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/payments/batch_sdd.rst:109
msgid ""
"Mandates are automatically closed 36 months after the date of the last "
"collection."
msgstr ""
"Mandat ditutup secara otomatis 36 bulan setelah tanggal penagihan terakhir."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/payments/batch_sdd.rst:110
msgid "Closed or revoked mandates cannot be reactivated."
msgstr "Mandat yang ditutup atau dicabut tidak dapat diaktifkan kembali."

