msgstr ""
"Unduh file XML dan unggah ke antarmuka perbankan online Anda untuk memproses "
"pembayaran."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/payments/batch_sdd.rst:130
msgid ""
"Once the |sdd| batch payment has been received, :doc:`reconcile the "
"transaction <../bank/reconciliation>` with the batch payment to mark the "
