"bank/reconciliation>` dengan pembayaran batch untuk menandai faktur terkait "
"sebagai :guilabel:`Dibayar`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/payments/batch_sdd.rst:135
msgid ""
"To view the payments and invoices linked to a specific |sdd| mandate, click "
"the :guilabel:`Collections` and :guilabel:`Invoices Paid` smart button on "
"the :ref:`Direct Debit Mandate <accounting/batch_sdd/sdd_mandates>` form."
msgstr ""
"Untuk melihat pembayaran dan faktur yang terkait dengan mandat |sdd| "
"tertentu, klik tombol pintar :guilabel:`Penagihan` dan :guilabel:`Faktur "
"Dibayar` pada formulir :ref:`Mandat Debit Langsung <accounting/batch_sdd/"
"sdd_mandates>`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/payments/batch_sdd.rst:138
msgid ""
"Click :guilabel:`Re-generate Export file` in the batch payment form to "
"regenerate the XML file."
msgstr ""
"Klik :guilabel:`Buat Ulang file Ekspor` di formulir pembayaran batch untuk "
"membuat ulang file XML."

