#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/payments/batch_sdd.rst:147
msgid "|sdd| rejections"
msgstr "Penolakan |sdd|"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/payments/batch_sdd.rst:149
msgid ""
"|sdd| rejections can occur for several reasons, the most common being "
"insufficient funds in the customer's account. With |sdd|, the recipient's "
"account is credited before the funds are actually debited from the "
"customer's account. As a result, if an |sdd| payment is later rejected, the "
"bank automatically withdraws the amount of that payment from the recipient's "
"account, and a new transaction for a negative amount is created to reflect "
"the |sdd| rejection."
msgstr ""
"Penolakan |sdd| dapat terjadi karena beberapa alasan, yang paling umum "
"adalah dana tidak mencukupi di akun pelanggan. Dengan |sdd|, akun penerima "
"dikreditkan sebelum dana benar-benar didebit dari akun pelanggan. Akibatnya, "
"jika pembayaran |sdd| kemudian ditolak, bank secara otomatis menarik jumlah "
"pembayaran tersebut dari akun penerima, dan transaksi baru untuk jumlah "
"negatif dibuat untuk mencerminkan penolakan |sdd|."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/payments/batch_sdd.rst:155
msgid ""
"|sdd| rejections are handled differently depending on "
"whether :ref:`outstanding accounts <accounting/journals/outstanding-"
"accounts>` are configured or not for the |sdd| payment method."
msgstr ""
"Penolakan |sdd| ditangani secara berbeda tergantung pada apakah :ref:`Akun "
"Belum Lunas <accounting/journals/outstanding-accounts>` dikonfigurasi atau "
"tidak untuk metode pembayaran |sdd|."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/payments/batch_sdd.rst:159
msgid ""
"The following procedures assume that the incoming |sdd| payment's bank "
"transaction has already been :ref:`reconciled <accounting/reconciliation/"
"reconcile>` with the payments or invoices."
msgstr ""
"Prosedur berikut mengasumsikan bahwa transaksi bank pembayaran |sdd| yang "
"masuk telah :ref:`direkonsiliasi <accounting/reconciliation/reconcile>` "
"dengan pembayaran atau faktur."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/payments/batch_sdd.rst:166
msgid ""
"If no :ref:`outstanding accounts <accounting/journals/outstanding-accounts>` "
"are configured for the |sdd| payment method, no journal entry is created. In "
"this case, you must cancel and unreconcile the payment."
msgstr ""
"Jika tidak ada :ref:`Akun Belum Lunas <accounting/journals/outstanding-"
"accounts>` yang dikonfigurasi untuk metode pembayaran |sdd|, tidak ada entri "
"jurnal yang dibuat. Dalam hal ini, Anda harus membatalkan dan membatalkan "
"rekonsiliasi pembayaran."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/payments/batch_sdd.rst:170
#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/payments/batch_sdd.rst:189
msgid "Access the invoice linked to the rejected |sdd| payment."
msgstr "Akses faktur yang terkait dengan pembayaran |sdd| yang ditolak."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/payments/batch_sdd.rst:171
msgid ""
"Click the :guilabel:`Payments` smart button to access the payment associated "
"with the invoice."
msgstr ""
"Klik tombol pintar :guilabel:`Payments` untuk mengakses pembayaran yang "
"terkait dengan faktur."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/payments/batch_sdd.rst:173
msgid "Click :guilabel:`Reset to draft`, then :guilabel:`Cancel`."
msgstr "Klik :guilabel:`Reset to draft`, lalu :guilabel:`Cancel`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/payments/batch_sdd.rst:174
msgid ""
"Go back to the invoice and click the :icon:`fa-info-"
"circle` :guilabel:`(information)` icon in the footer of "
"the :guilabel:`Invoice Lines` tab, then click :guilabel:`Unreconcile`."
msgstr ""
"Kembali ke faktur dan klik ikon :icon:`fa-info-circle` :guilabel:`"
"(information)` di footer tab :guilabel:`Invoice Lines`, lalu klik "
":guilabel:`Unreconcile`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/payments/batch_sdd.rst:176
msgid ""
":ref:`Access the bank journal's reconciliation view <accounting/"
"reconciliation/access>` and :ref:`reconcile <accounting/reconciliation/"
"reconcile>` the transaction created for the |sdd| rejection with the debit "
"(negative journal item) to the account receivable on the incoming bank "
"transaction."
msgstr ""
":ref:`Akses tampilan rekonsiliasi jurnal bank <accounting/reconciliation/"
"access>` dan :ref:`rekonsiliasi <accounting/reconciliation/reconcile>` "
"transaksi yang dibuat untuk penolakan |sdd| dengan debit (item jurnal "
"negatif) ke akun piutang pada transaksi bank yang masuk."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/payments/batch_sdd.rst:183
msgid ""
"If an :ref:`outstanding account <accounting/journals/outstanding-accounts>` "
"is set on the |sdd| payment method, |sdd| payments create journal entries. "
"If an |sdd| payment is rejected, you must reverse the journal entry "
"associated with the rejected payment and reconcile the reversal of the "
"journal entry with the transaction for the |sdd| rejection. To do so, follow "
"these steps:"
msgstr ""
"Jika :ref:`Akun Belum Lunas <accounting/journals/outstanding-accounts>` "
"diatur pada metode pembayaran |sdd|, pembayaran |sdd| membuat entri jurnal. "
"Jika pembayaran |sdd| ditolak, Anda harus membalik entri jurnal yang terkait "
"dengan pembayaran yang ditolak dan merekonsiliasi pembalikan entri jurnal "
"dengan transaksi untuk penolakan |sdd|. Untuk melakukannya, ikuti langkah-"
"langkah berikut:"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/payments/batch_sdd.rst:190
msgid ""
"Click the :icon:`fa-info-circle` :guilabel:`(information)` icon in the "
"footer of the :guilabel:`Invoice Lines` tab, then click :guilabel:`View` to "
"access the payment associated with the invoice."
msgstr ""
"Klik ikon :icon:`fa-info-circle` :guilabel:`(information)` di footer tab "
":guilabel:`Invoice Lines`, lalu klik :guilabel:`View` untuk mengakses "
"pembayaran yang terkait dengan faktur."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/payments/batch_sdd.rst:193
msgid ""
"Click the :guilabel:`Journal entry` smart button to access the related "
"journal entry."
msgstr ""
"Klik tombol pintar :guilabel:`Journal entry` untuk mengakses entri jurnal "
"terkait."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/payments/batch_sdd.rst:194
msgid ""
"Click :guilabel:`Reverse entry`, optionally edit the fields in the popup, "
"then click :guilabel:`Reverse`. A reversal entry is created with "
"a :guilabel:`Reference` mentioning the initial journal entry. As a result, "
"the invoice is marked as :guilabel:`Not paid`."
msgstr ""
"Klik :guilabel:`Reverse entry`, secara opsional edit bidang di popup, lalu "
"klik :guilabel:`Reverse`. Entri pembalikan dibuat dengan "
":guilabel:`Reference` yang menyebutkan entri jurnal awal. Akibatnya, faktur "
"ditandai sebagai :guilabel:`Not paid`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/payments/batch_sdd.rst:197
msgid ""
":ref:`Access the bank journal's reconciliation view <accounting/"
"reconciliation/access>` and :ref:`reconcile <accounting/reconciliation/"
"reconcile>` the transaction created for the |sdd| rejection with the "
"reversal of the entry related to the payment."
msgstr ""
":ref:`Akses tampilan rekonsiliasi jurnal bank <accounting/reconciliation/"
"access>` dan :ref:`rekonsiliasi <accounting/reconciliation/reconcile>` "
"transaksi yang dibuat untuk penolakan |sdd| dengan pembalikan entri yang "
"terkait dengan pembayaran."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/payments/follow_up.rst:3
msgid "Follow-up on invoices"
msgstr "Tindak-lanjut pada faktur"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/payments/follow_up.rst:5
msgid ""
"Follow-up messages can be sent to customers when payments are overdue. Odoo "
"helps identify late payments and allows scheduling and sending the "
"appropriate reminders using **follow-up actions** according to the number of "
"overdue days. Follow-ups can be sent through different methods, including "
"email, WhatsApp message, SMS, or post."
msgstr ""
"Pesan tindak lanjut dapat dikirim ke pelanggan ketika pembayaran terlambat. "
"Odoo membantu mengidentifikasi pembayaran yang terlambat dan memungkinkan "
"penjadwalan serta pengiriman pengingat yang sesuai menggunakan **tindakan "
"tindak lanjut** sesuai dengan jumlah hari keterlambatan. Tindak lanjut dapat "
"dikirim melalui berbagai metode, termasuk email, pesan WhatsApp, SMS, atau "
"pos."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/payments/follow_up.rst:11
msgid ""
"`Odoo Tutorials: Payment Follow-up <https://www.youtube.com/watch?"
"v=50qy2ygS7eM>`_"
msgstr ""
"`Odoo Tutorials: Payment Follow-up <https://www.youtube.com/"
"watch?v=50qy2ygS7eM>`_"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/payments/follow_up.rst:12
msgid ":doc:`/applications/finance/accounting/customer_invoices/payment_terms`"
msgstr ":doc:`/applications/finance/accounting/customer_invoices/payment_terms`"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/payments/follow_up.rst:19
msgid ""
"To configure :guilabel:`Follow-up actions`, go to :menuselection:`Accounting "
"--> Configuration --> Follow-up Levels`. In the :guilabel:`Follow-up Levels` "
"list view, several follow-up levels and actions are configured by default."
msgstr ""
"Untuk mengonfigurasi :guilabel:`Follow-up actions`, buka "
":menuselection:`Accounting --> Configuration --> Follow-up Levels`. Dalam "
"tampilan daftar :guilabel:`Follow-up Levels`, beberapa tingkat dan tindakan "
"tindak lanjut dikonfigurasi secara default."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/payments/follow_up.rst:23
msgid ""
"To modify a follow-up level, click on the record. From the form view, edit "
"the :guilabel:`Description` or adjust the number of days before a reminder "
"is sent. In the :guilabel:`Notification` tab, select :guilabel:`Actions` "
"such as :guilabel:`Send Email`, :doc:`Send WhatsApp message </applications/"
"productivity/whatsapp>`, :ref:`Send SMS Message <pricing/pricing_and_faq>`, "
"and :ref:`Send a Letter <customer_invoices/snailmail>`."
msgstr ""
"Untuk memodifikasi tingkat tindak lanjut, klik pada record. Dari tampilan "
"formulir, edit :guilabel:`Description` atau sesuaikan jumlah hari sebelum "
"pengingat dikirim. Di tab :guilabel:`Notification`, pilih "
":guilabel:`Actions` seperti :guilabel:`Send Email`, :doc:`Send WhatsApp "
"message </applications/productivity/whatsapp>`, :ref:`Send SMS Message "
"<pricing/pricing_and_faq>`, dan :ref:`Send a Letter <customer_invoices/"
"snailmail>`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/payments/follow_up.rst:30
msgid ""
"Sending letters and WhatsApp or SMS messages in Odoo requires :doc:`In-App "
"Purchase (IAP) </applications/essentials/in_app_purchase>` credit or tokens."
msgstr ""
"Mengirim surat dan pesan WhatsApp atau SMS di Odoo memerlukan kredit atau "
"token :doc:`In-App Purchase (IAP) </applications/essentials/in_app_purchase>"
"`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/payments/follow_up.rst:33
msgid ""
"To use a pre-filled template when sending an email or letter, select "
"a :guilabel:`Content Template`. To modify it, click the :icon:`oi-arrow-"
"right` :guilabel:`(internal link arrow)` icon next to the :guilabel:`Content "
"Template` field. If enabled, WhatsApp and SMS messages use a "
"specific :guilabel:`WhatsApp Template` or :guilabel:`Sms Template` field "
"that can be modified by clicking the :icon:`oi-arrow-"
"right` :guilabel:`(internal link arrow)` icon."
msgstr ""
"Untuk menggunakan templat yang sudah diisi sebelumnya saat mengirim email "
"atau surat, pilih :guilabel:`Content Template`. Untuk memodifikasinya, klik "
"ikon :icon:`oi-arrow-right` :guilabel:`(internal link arrow)` di sebelah "
"bidang :guilabel:`Content Template`. Jika diaktifkan, pesan WhatsApp dan SMS "
"menggunakan bidang :guilabel:`WhatsApp Template` atau :guilabel:`Sms "
"Template` spesifik yang dapat dimodifikasi dengan mengklik ikon :icon:`oi-"
"arrow-right` :guilabel:`(internal link arrow)`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/payments/follow_up.rst:39
msgid ""
"Other options can be enabled in the :guilabel:`Options` section within the "
"specific follow-up level:"
msgstr ""
"Opsi lain dapat diaktifkan di bagian :guilabel:`Options` dalam level tindak "
"lanjut spesifik:"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/payments/follow_up.rst:41
msgid "Automate the reminder with the :guilabel:`Automatic` option."
msgstr "Otomatiskan pengingat dengan opsi :guilabel:`Automatic`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/payments/follow_up.rst:42
msgid ":guilabel:`Attach Invoices` that are overdue in the reminder."
msgstr ":guilabel:`Attach Invoices` yang jatuh tempo dalam pengingat."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/payments/follow_up.rst:43
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Add followers` on the related customer to receive notifications "
"about any email reply made on the reminder's email."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Add followers` pada pelanggan terkait untuk menerima notifikasi "
"tentang balasan email yang dibuat pada email pengingat."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/payments/follow_up.rst:46
msgid ""
"In the :guilabel:`Activity` tab, enable the option to automatically "
"schedule :doc:`activities </applications/essentials/activities>` when the "
"follow-up level is triggered. Select the :guilabel:`Responsible` user and "
"the :guilabel:`Activity Type`, and enter a :guilabel:`Summary`."
msgstr ""
"Di tab :guilabel:`Activity`, aktifkan opsi untuk menjadwalkan "
":doc:`activities </applications/essentials/activities>` secara otomatis "
"ketika level tindak lanjut dipicu. Pilih user :guilabel:`Responsible` dan "
":guilabel:`Activity Type`, lalu masukkan :guilabel:`Summary`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/payments/follow_up.rst:50
msgid ""
"To add a new :guilabel:`Follow-up Level`, click :guilabel:`New` and fill in "
"the fields."
msgstr ""
"Untuk menambahkan :guilabel:`Follow-up Level` baru, klik :guilabel:`New` dan "
"isi kolom-kolomnya."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/payments/follow_up.rst:53
msgid ""
"Set a negative number of days to send a reminder before the invoice due date."
msgstr ""
"Tetapkan jumlah hari negatif untuk mengirim pengingat sebelum tanggal jatuh "
"tempo faktur."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/payments/follow_up.rst:58
msgid "Invoice follow-ups"
msgstr "Tindak lanjut faktur"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/payments/follow_up.rst:61
msgid ""
"Reconcile all bank transactions before starting the follow-up process to "
"avoid sending reminders for invoices that have already been paid."
msgstr ""
"Rekonsiliasi semua transaksi bank sebelum memulai proses tindak lanjut untuk "
"menghindari pengiriman pengingat untuk faktur yang sudah dibayar."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/payments/follow_up.rst:64
msgid ""
"To view all overdue invoices, go to :menuselection:`Accounting --> Customers "
"--> Invoices`. In the :guilabel:`Invoices` list view, click into the search "
"bar and filter on :guilabel:`Overdue`."
msgstr ""
"Untuk melihat semua faktur yang jatuh tempo, buka "
":menuselection:`Accounting --> Customers --> Invoices`. Di tampilan daftar "
":guilabel:`Invoices`, klik bilah pencarian dan filter pada "
":guilabel:`Overdue`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/payments/follow_up.rst:70
msgid "Follow-ups for one customer"
msgstr "Tindak lanjut untuk satu pelanggan"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/payments/follow_up.rst:72
msgid ""
"For a detailed overview of a customer's invoice follow-up status, go "
"to :menuselection:`Accounting --> Customers --> Customers`. Open the "
"customer's form and click the :guilabel:`Accounting` tab. In "
"the :guilabel:`Invoice follow-ups` section, click on the different levels to "
"view the :guilabel:`Follow-up Status` of each level. If actions are needed, "
"click :guilabel:`Overdue Invoices` to have a detailed list of the overdue "
"invoices."
msgstr ""
"Untuk tinjauan detail tentang status tindak lanjut faktur pelanggan, buka "
":menuselection:`Accounting --> Customers --> Customers`. Buka formulir "
"pelanggan dan klik tab :guilabel:`Accounting`. Di bagian :guilabel:`Invoice "
"follow-ups`, klik level yang berbeda untuk melihat :guilabel:`Follow-up "
"Status` dari setiap level. Jika tindakan diperlukan, klik :guilabel:`Overdue "
"Invoices` untuk mendapatkan daftar detail faktur yang jatuh tempo."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/payments/follow_up.rst:78
msgid "Additional options can be set:"
msgstr "Opsi tambahan dapat diatur:"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/payments/follow_up.rst:80
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Reminders`: These are either :guilabel:`Automatic` "
"or :guilabel:`Manual`."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Reminders`: Ini dapat berupa :guilabel:`Automatic` atau "
":guilabel:`Manual`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/payments/follow_up.rst:81
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Next reminder`: The date by which the next follow-up actions "
"should be taken is automatically set when follow-ups are processed, but can "
"be manually adjusted if needed."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Next reminder`: Tanggal kapan tindakan tindak lanjut berikutnya "
"harus diambil secara otomatis diatur ketika tindak lanjut diproses, tetapi "
