"To get a comprehensive overview of a customer's account status, click "
"the :guilabel:`Customer Statement` smart button on the customer's form. This "
"statement corresponds to the :ref:`Partner Ledger <accounting/invoices/"
"partner-ledger>` report's portion specific to that customer."
