":guilabel:`Template Email` jika diperlukan, dan klik :guilabel:`Cetak & "
"Kirim`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/payments/follow_up.rst:139
msgid ""
"To view the customer statements for multiple customers at once, select the "
"customers from the :guilabel:`Customers` list view, click :icon:`fa-"
"cog` :guilabel:`(Actions)`, and select :guilabel:`Open Customer Statements`."
msgstr ""
"Untuk melihat laporan pelanggan untuk beberapa pelanggan sekaligus, pilih "
"pelanggan dari tampilan daftar :guilabel:`Pelanggan`, klik :icon:`fa-cog` "
":guilabel:`(Tindakan)`, dan pilih :guilabel:`Buka Laporan Pelanggan`."

