#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/reporting/tax_returns.rst:93
msgid ""
"Setting a tax lock date prevents changes that could impact VAT-related "
"journal entries. Locking the period before processing the :guilabel:`Closing "
"Journal Entry` helps ensure the accuracy of the final report and reduces the "
"risk of tax errors."
msgstr ""
"Menetapkan tanggal kunci pajak mencegah perubahan yang dapat memengaruhi "
"entri jurnal terkait PPN. Mengunci periode sebelum memproses "
":guilabel:`Entri Jurnal Penutupan` membantu memastikan keakuratan laporan "
"akhir dan mengurangi risiko kesalahan pajak."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/reporting/tax_returns.rst:97
msgid ""
"To view or edit the current :guilabel:`Lock Tax Return` date, go "
"to :menuselection:`Accounting --> Accounting --> Lock Dates`."
msgstr ""
"Untuk melihat atau mengedit tanggal :guilabel:`Kunci Pengembalian Pajak` "
"saat ini, buka :menuselection:`Akuntansi --> Akuntansi --> Tanggal Kunci`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/reporting/tax_returns.rst:101
msgid ""
"Any new transaction whose accounting date is before the :guilabel:`Lock Tax "
"Return` date has its tax values moved to the next open tax period, "
"preventing any changes to a report after its period is closed."
msgstr ""
"Setiap transaksi baru yang tanggal akuntansinya sebelum tanggal "
":guilabel:`Kunci Pengembalian Pajak` akan memiliki nilai pajaknya "
"dipindahkan ke periode pajak terbuka berikutnya, mencegah perubahan apa pun "
"pada laporan setelah periodenya ditutup."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/reporting/tax_returns.rst:110
msgid ""
"On the Accounting Dashboard, the :guilabel:`Tax Returns` journal displays "
"automatic reminders to avoid missing important tasks and deadlines."
msgstr ""
