#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/reporting/tax_returns.rst:113
msgid ""
"After completing all :ref:`configurations <accounting/tax-returns/"
"configuration>` and posting all tax-related transactions for the reporting "
"period, click :guilabel:`Tax Returns` on the :guilabel:`Tax Returns` journal "
"from the Accounting dashboard. Alternatively, go "
"to :menuselection:`Accounting --> Accounting --> Tax Returns`."
msgstr ""
