#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/reporting/tax_returns.rst:180
#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/reporting/year_end.rst:288
msgid "Review"
msgstr "Tinjauan"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/reporting/tax_returns.rst:182
msgid ""
"To start the review of a tax return, click on the relevant tax return line:"
msgstr ""
"Untuk memulai peninjauan pengembalian pajak, klik pada baris pengembalian "
"pajak yang relevan:"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/reporting/tax_returns.rst:184
msgid ""
"If all automatic tax validation checks have passed, "
"click :guilabel:`Validate` to complete the :guilabel:`Review` step. "
"The :ref:`Lock Tax Return <accounting/tax-returns/lock-date>` date is "
"automatically updated, and the closing journal entry is posted in "
"the :guilabel:`Tax Returns` journal. The tax return can then "
"be :ref:`submitted <accounting/tax-returns/vat-return-submit>`."
msgstr ""
"Jika semua pemeriksaan validasi pajak otomatis telah lolos, klik "
":guilabel:`Validasi` untuk menyelesaikan langkah :guilabel:`Tinjau`. Tanggal "
":ref:`Kunci Pengembalian Pajak <accounting/tax-returns/lock-date>` secara "
"otomatis diperbarui, dan entri jurnal penutupan diposting di jurnal "
":guilabel:`Pengembalian Pajak`. Pengembalian pajak kemudian dapat "
":ref:`dikirim <accounting/tax-returns/vat-return-submit>`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/reporting/tax_returns.rst:188
msgid ""
"If any automatic tax validation checks are pending, the :guilabel:`Tax "
"Checks` view displays the following, depending on the :doc:`fiscal "
"localization <../../fiscal_localizations>`:"
msgstr ""
"Jika ada pemeriksaan validasi pajak otomatis yang tertunda, tampilan "
":guilabel:`Pemeriksaan Pajak` menampilkan hal berikut, tergantung pada "
":doc:`lokalisasi fiskal <../../fiscal_localizations>`:"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/reporting/tax_returns.rst:191
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Bank Matching`: This check is used to identify any missing bills; "
"it is optional for VAT reports."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Pencocokan Bank`: Pemeriksaan ini digunakan untuk "
"mengidentifikasi tagihan yang hilang; ini opsional untuk laporan PPN."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/reporting/tax_returns.rst:193
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Bill attachments`: Bills must have attached documents as proof in "
"case of an audit."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Lampiran Tagihan`: Tagihan harus memiliki dokumen terlampir "
"sebagai bukti jika terjadi audit."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/reporting/tax_returns.rst:194
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Company data`: Missing information (e.g., VAT number or country) "
"can lead to errors in tax reports or exemptions."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Data Perusahaan`: Informasi yang hilang (misalnya, nomor PPN atau "
"negara) dapat menyebabkan kesalahan dalam laporan pajak atau pengecualian."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/reporting/tax_returns.rst:196
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Draft entries`: Any draft invoices and bills within the "
"corresponding period must be reviewed and posted, or assigned a different "
"accounting date."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Entri Draf`: Setiap faktur dan tagihan draf dalam periode yang "
"sesuai harus ditinjau dan diposting, atau diberi tanggal akuntansi yang "
"berbeda."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/reporting/tax_returns.rst:198
msgid ""
":guilabel:`No negative amount in VAT report`: Some countries only allow "
"positive values in tax returns, as a negative amount could indicate "
"misconfigurations."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Tidak ada jumlah negatif dalam laporan PPN`: Beberapa negara "
"hanya mengizinkan nilai positif dalam pengembalian pajak, karena jumlah "
"negatif dapat mengindikasikan kesalahan konfigurasi."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/reporting/tax_returns.rst:200
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Taxes and countries matching`: Taxes applied on invoices and "
"bills must match the customer’s country."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Pajak dan pencocokan negara`: Pajak yang diterapkan pada faktur "
"dan tagihan harus sesuai dengan negara pelanggan."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/reporting/tax_returns.rst:203
msgid ""
"Each check card is either highlighted in green (Reviewed or Supervised), red "
"(Anomaly) or grey (To review). If a check fails, there are two options:"
msgstr ""
"Setiap kartu pemeriksaan disorot dengan warna hijau (Ditinjau atau Diawasi), "
"merah (Anomali) atau abu-abu (Untuk ditinjau). Jika pemeriksaan gagal, ada "
"dua opsi:"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/reporting/tax_returns.rst:206
msgid "Click on the failed check's card to fix the issue."
msgstr "Klik pada kartu pemeriksaan yang gagal untuk memperbaiki masalah."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/reporting/tax_returns.rst:207
#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/reporting/year_end.rst:326
msgid ""
"Click :guilabel:`Anomaly` and select :guilabel:`Reviewed` "
"or :guilabel:`Supervised` to pass the check without fixing the issue."
msgstr ""
"Klik :guilabel:`Anomali` dan pilih :guilabel:`Ditinjau` atau "
":guilabel:`Diawasi` untuk melewati pemeriksaan tanpa memperbaiki masalah."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/reporting/tax_returns.rst:210
msgid ""
"Once all checks have passed, click :guilabel:`Validate`. Then, depending on "
"the :doc:`fiscal localization <../../fiscal_localizations>`, "
"click :guilabel:`Lock` in the :guilabel:`Lock` window."
msgstr ""
"Setelah semua pemeriksaan berhasil, klik :guilabel:`Validasi`. Kemudian, "
"tergantung pada :doc:`lokalisasi fiskal <../../fiscal_localizations>`, klik "
":guilabel:`Kunci` di jendela :guilabel:`Kunci`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/reporting/tax_returns.rst:213
msgid ""
"On validating the tax return, the :ref:`Lock Tax Return <accounting/tax-"
"returns/lock-date>` date is automatically updated, and the closing journal "
"entry is posted in the :guilabel:`Tax Returns` journal."
msgstr ""
"Pada saat memvalidasi pengembalian pajak, tanggal :ref:`Kunci Pengembalian "
"Pajak <accounting/tax-returns/lock-date>` secara otomatis diperbarui, dan "
"entri jurnal penutup diposting di jurnal :guilabel:`Pengembalian Pajak`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/reporting/tax_returns.rst:218
#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/reporting/year_end.rst:334
msgid ""
"To add customized checks, activate :ref:`developer mode <developer-mode>`, "
"and go to :menuselection:`Accounting --> Configuration --> Check`. Then, "
"click :guilabel:`New` and complete the necessary fields."
msgstr ""
"Untuk menambahkan pemeriksaan yang disesuaikan, aktifkan :ref:`mode "
"pengembang <developer-mode>`, dan buka :menuselection:`Akuntansi --> "
"Konfigurasi --> Pemeriksaan`. Kemudian, klik :guilabel:`Baru` dan lengkapi "
"kolom yang diperlukan."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/reporting/tax_returns.rst:221
#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/reporting/year_end.rst:337
msgid "All check status changes are logged in the chatter."
msgstr "Semua perubahan status pemeriksaan dicatat di chatter."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/reporting/tax_returns.rst:224
msgid ""
"If the :guilabel:`Lock Tax Return` date is not locked before reviewing the "
"tax return, the fiscal period is automatically locked on the same date as "
"the accounting date of the closing journal entry. While this feature helps "
"prevent certain fiscal errors, it is recommended to set the :ref:`Lock Tax "
"Return date <accounting/tax-returns/lock-date>` manually beforehand."
msgstr ""
"Jika tanggal :guilabel:`Kunci Pengembalian Pajak` tidak dikunci sebelum "
"meninjau pengembalian pajak, periode fiskal secara otomatis dikunci pada "
"tanggal yang sama dengan tanggal akuntansi dari entri jurnal penutup. "
"Meskipun fitur ini membantu mencegah kesalahan fiskal tertentu, disarankan "
"untuk menetapkan :ref:`tanggal Kunci Pengembalian Pajak <accounting/tax-"
"returns/lock-date>` secara manual sebelumnya."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/reporting/tax_returns.rst:230
msgid ""
"After the tax report for a period has been posted, that period is locked to "
"prevent new VAT-related journal entries from being created. Corrections to "
"customer invoices or vendor bills must be recorded in the following period."
msgstr ""
"Setelah laporan pajak untuk suatu periode telah diposting, periode tersebut "
"dikunci untuk mencegah entri jurnal terkait PPN baru dibuat. Koreksi untuk "
"faktur pelanggan atau tagihan vendor harus dicatat dalam periode berikutnya."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/reporting/tax_returns.rst:237
#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/reporting/year_end.rst:342
msgid "Submit"
msgstr "Menyerahkan"

