msgid ""
"In the :guilabel:`Tax Return` view, click the local VAT report button "
"(e.g., :guilabel:`VAT Return (BE)` or :guilabel:`Tax Report (US)`, depending "
"on the :doc:`fiscal localization <../../fiscal_localizations>`) or "
"the :guilabel:`Generic Tax report` button on the relevant tax return line to "
