msgstr ""
"Dalam tampilan :guilabel:`Pengembalian Pajak`, klik tombol laporan PPN lokal "
"(misalnya, :guilabel:`Pengembalian PPN (BE)` atau :guilabel:`Laporan Pajak "
"(AS)`, tergantung pada :doc:`lokalisasi fiskal <../../fiscal_localizations>"
"`) atau tombol :guilabel:`Laporan pajak generik` pada baris pengembalian "
"pajak yang relevan untuk melihat pratinjau laporan pengembalian pajak."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/reporting/tax_returns.rst:246
msgid ""
"Once the tax return report has been verified, go back to the :guilabel:`Tax "
"Return` view and click :guilabel:`Submit`."
msgstr ""
"Setelah laporan pengembalian pajak telah diverifikasi, kembali ke tampilan "
":guilabel:`Pengembalian Pajak` dan klik :guilabel:`Kirim`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/reporting/tax_returns.rst:248
msgid ""
"If a :guilabel:`Submission Instructions` pop-up window appears, follow the "
"local :guilabel:`Instructions`, and click :guilabel:`Mark as Submitted` "
"or :ref:`Mark Paid <accounting/tax-returns/vat-return-pay>`."
msgstr ""
"Jika jendela pop-up :guilabel:`Instruksi Pengiriman` muncul, ikuti "
":guilabel:`Instruksi` lokal, dan klik :guilabel:`Tandai sebagai Terkirim` "
"atau :ref:`Tandai Dibayar <accounting/tax-returns/vat-return-pay>`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/reporting/tax_returns.rst:252
msgid ""
"The submitted tax return contains all the values tax authorities need, and "
"the amount to be paid or refunded."
msgstr ""
"Pengembalian pajak yang dikirimkan berisi semua nilai yang dibutuhkan "
"otoritas pajak, dan jumlah yang harus dibayar atau dikembalikan."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/reporting/tax_returns.rst:256
msgid ""
"To display all posted closing journal entries, click the :guilabel:`Tax "
