":icon:`fa-ellipsis-v` :guilabel:`(elipsis vertikal)` dan pilih "
":guilabel:`View Entry`. Opsi berikut tersedia jika diperlukan:"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/reporting/tax_returns.rst:262
msgid ":guilabel:`Reverse Entry`"
msgstr ":guilabel:`Reverse Entry`"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/reporting/tax_returns.rst:263
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Reset to Draft`: The :guilabel:`Lock Tax Return` date must be "
"manually removed using a :ref:`lock date exception <accounting/year-end/lock-"
"date-exception>` to reset a tax return entry to draft."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Reset to Draft`: Tanggal :guilabel:`Lock Tax Return` harus "
"dihapus secara manual menggunakan :ref:`pengecualian tanggal kunci "
"<accounting/year-end/lock-date-exception>` untuk mereset entri pengembalian "
"pajak ke draf."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/reporting/tax_returns.rst:270
msgid "Pay"
msgstr "Bayar"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/reporting/tax_returns.rst:272
msgid ""
"Once a tax return is submitted, a :guilabel:`Payment` window appears if a "
"tax payment is required. It displays all necessary payment details to "
"complete the transaction, including a QR code for the banking app, if "
"available for the country's :doc:`fiscal localization <../../"
"fiscal_localizations>` package. There are three options:"
msgstr ""
"Setelah pengembalian pajak dikirimkan, jendela :guilabel:`Payment` akan "
"muncul jika pembayaran pajak diperlukan. Jendela ini menampilkan semua "
"detail pembayaran yang diperlukan untuk menyelesaikan transaksi, termasuk "
"kode QR untuk aplikasi perbankan, jika tersedia untuk paket :doc:`lokalisasi "
"fiskal <../../fiscal_localizations>` negara. Ada tiga opsi:"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/reporting/tax_returns.rst:277
msgid ""
"Click :guilabel:`Mark Paid` after completing the payment: the corresponding "
"tax return line disappears from the :guilabel:`Tax Return` view."
msgstr ""
"Klik :guilabel:`Mark Paid` setelah menyelesaikan pembayaran: baris "
"pengembalian pajak yang sesuai akan menghilang dari tampilan :guilabel:`Tax "
"Return`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/reporting/tax_returns.rst:279
msgid ""
"Click :guilabel:`Send` to email all payment information. Once sent, the tax "
"return completes the :guilabel:`Pay` step, and its corresponding line "
"disappears from the :guilabel:`Tax Return` view."
msgstr ""
"Klik :guilabel:`Send` untuk mengirim email semua informasi pembayaran. "
"Setelah dikirim, pengembalian pajak menyelesaikan langkah :guilabel:`Pay`, "
"dan baris yang sesuai menghilang dari tampilan :guilabel:`Tax Return`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/reporting/tax_returns.rst:281
msgid ""
"Click :guilabel:`Discard`: the corresponding tax return line remains visible "
"in the :guilabel:`Tax Return` view, indicating the amount due. Click "
