#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/reporting/year_end.rst:144
msgid "Current year earnings"
msgstr "Laba tahun berjalan"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/reporting/year_end.rst:147
msgid ""
"In versions before Odoo 19, current year earnings were handled differently. "
"For consistency in your reporting history, upgrading users should revisit "
"past fiscal years and explicitly book the results that were previously "
"handled implicitly by the system. These :ref:`manual journal entries "
"<accounting/year-end/manual-je>` should be made in chronological order. For "
"more information on why this change was made and how versions before Odoo 19 "
"compare to versions after it, see this `blog post <https://www.odoo.com/blog/"
"business-hacks-1/how-to-manage-current-years-earnings-in-odoo-19-compared-to-"
"previous-versions-2107>`_."
msgstr ""
"Dalam versi sebelum Odoo 19, laba tahun berjalan ditangani secara berbeda. "
"Untuk konsistensi dalam riwayat pelaporan Anda, pengguna yang melakukan "
"upgrade harus meninjau kembali tahun fiskal sebelumnya dan secara eksplisit "
"membukukan hasil yang sebelumnya ditangani secara implisit oleh sistem. "
":ref:`Entri jurnal manual <accounting/year-end/manual-je>` ini harus dibuat "
"secara kronologis. Untuk informasi lebih lanjut tentang mengapa perubahan "
"ini dilakukan dan bagaimana versi sebelum Odoo 19 dibandingkan dengan versi "
"sesudahnya, lihat `postingan blog ini <https://www.odoo.com/blog/business-"
"hacks-1/how-to-manage-current-years-earnings-in-odoo-19-compared-to-previous-"
"versions-2107>`_."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/reporting/year_end.rst:154
msgid ""
"At the end of a fiscal year, a company will almost always have a net profit "
"or a net loss that is calculated by summing the income and expenses accounts "
"of the profit and loss statement. Odoo displays the result for year **N** as "
"a **dynamic line** called *Result Brought Forward* in the trial balance and "
"general ledger of the year **N+1**. To clear this dynamic line, create "
"a :ref:`manual journal entry <accounting/year-end/manual-je>` in year **N** "
"for the end-of-year result using a :ref:`Current Year Earnings type account "
"<accounting/year-end/appropriation>`."
msgstr ""
"Pada akhir tahun fiskal, perusahaan hampir selalu memiliki laba bersih atau "
"rugi bersih yang dihitung dengan menjumlahkan akun pendapatan dan "
"pengeluaran dari laporan laba rugi. Odoo menampilkan hasil untuk tahun **N** "
"sebagai **baris dinamis** yang disebut *Hasil yang Dibawa ke Depan* di "
"neraca saldo dan Buku Besar tahun **N+1**. Untuk menghapus baris dinamis "
"ini, buat :ref:`entri jurnal manual <accounting/year-end/manual-je>` di "
"tahun **N** untuk hasil akhir tahun menggunakan :ref:`akun tipe Laba Tahun "
"Berjalan <accounting/year-end/appropriation>`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/reporting/year_end.rst:164
msgid "Balancing the trial balance"
msgstr "Menyeimbangkan neraca saldo"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/reporting/year_end.rst:166
msgid ""
"A trial balance is, by default, always balanced (meaning the sum of debits "
"equals the sum of credits) because it records the sum of all journal entries "
"which are themselves balanced. However, **balance sheet accounts** (assets, "
"liabilities, and equity) carry over their balances from previous fiscal "
"years, whereas **profit and loss accounts** (income, expense, "
"and :ref:`appropriation accounts <accounting/year-end/appropriation>`) reset "
"to zero at the start of a new fiscal year. This difference in account "
"behavior would leave the trial balance unbalanced if it were not for the "
"dynamic line - *Result Brought Forward* - that balances this difference "
"temporarily until an explicit, :ref:`manual journal entry <accounting/year-"
"end/manual-je>` is made to appropriate the profit or the loss. Posting an "
"explicit entry to a :ref:`current year earnings account <accounting/year-end/"
"appropriation>` at year-end \"neutralizes\" the dynamic line and ensures the "
"trial balance is balanced by actual journal items. This manual journal entry "
"does not need to be made immediately following the end of the fiscal year "
"because the trial balance is always balanced, but whenever the company's "
"profit/loss is ready to be appropriated, this manual journal entry replaces "
"the dynamic line."
msgstr ""
"Neraca saldo secara default selalu seimbang (artinya jumlah debit sama "
"dengan jumlah kredit) karena mencatat jumlah semua entri jurnal yang juga "
"seimbang. Namun, **akun neraca keuangan** (aset, liabilitas, dan ekuitas) "
"membawa saldo mereka dari tahun fiskal sebelumnya, sedangkan **akun laba "
"rugi** (pendapatan, pengeluaran, dan :ref:`akun apropriasi <accounting/year-"
"end/appropriation>`) direset ke nol pada awal tahun fiskal baru. Perbedaan "
"perilaku akun ini akan membuat neraca saldo tidak seimbang jika bukan karena "
"baris dinamis - *Hasil yang Dibawa ke Depan* - yang menyeimbangkan perbedaan "
"ini sementara hingga dibuat :ref:`entri jurnal manual <accounting/year-end/"
"manual-je>` eksplisit untuk mengapropriasi laba atau rugi. Memposting entri "
"eksplisit ke :ref:`akun laba tahun berjalan <accounting/year-end/"
"appropriation>` pada akhir tahun \"menetralkan\" baris dinamis dan "
"memastikan neraca saldo diseimbangkan oleh item jurnal aktual. Entri jurnal "
"manual ini tidak perlu dibuat segera setelah akhir tahun fiskal karena "
"neraca saldo selalu seimbang, tetapi setiap kali laba/rugi perusahaan siap "
"untuk diapropriasi, entri jurnal manual ini menggantikan baris dinamis."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/reporting/year_end.rst:184
msgid "Appropriation (current year earnings) accounts"
msgstr "Akun apropriasi (laba tahun berjalan)"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/reporting/year_end.rst:186
msgid ""
"Appropriation accounts (also called by their account type, current year "
"earnings) are used to allocate a company's profit or loss, whether that "
"allocation is to reserves, dividends, or any other destination. There are "
"several key pieces of information to know about these accounts and how they "
"function:"
msgstr ""
"Akun apropriasi (juga disebut dengan jenis akunnya, laba tahun berjalan) "
"digunakan untuk mengalokasikan laba atau rugi perusahaan, baik alokasi "
"tersebut ke cadangan, dividen, atau tujuan lainnya. Ada beberapa informasi "
"penting yang perlu diketahui tentang akun ini dan cara kerjanya:"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/reporting/year_end.rst:191
msgid ""
"**Annual reset**: Like the income and expenses accounts that are also found "
"on the profit and loss statement, allocation accounts have their opening "
"balances reset at the beginning of a fiscal year."
msgstr ""
"**Reset tahunan**: Seperti akun pendapatan dan pengeluaran yang juga "
"ditemukan pada laporan laba rugi, akun alokasi memiliki saldo awal yang "
"direset di awal tahun fiskal."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/reporting/year_end.rst:194
msgid ""
"**P&L presentation**: These accounts appear at the bottom of the **profit "
"and loss** statement."
msgstr ""
"**Presentasi L/R**: Akun ini muncul di bagian bawah laporan **laba rugi**."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/reporting/year_end.rst:195
msgid ""
"**No profit effect**: Unlike income and expenses accounts, these accounts "
"**do not affect** the calculation of the net profit."
msgstr ""
"**Tidak mempengaruhi laba**: Tidak seperti akun pendapatan dan pengeluaran, "
"akun ini **tidak mempengaruhi** perhitungan laba bersih."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/reporting/year_end.rst:197
msgid ""
"**Balance sheet counterparts**: Only the *counterparts* of the journal items "
"that debit or credit appropriations accounts (e.g., the dividends payable or "
"the reserve accounts) appear on the balance sheet. This maintains a strict "
"separation between the process of distributing profit and the resulting "
"liabilities or equity."
msgstr ""
"**Rekanan neraca keuangan**: Hanya *rekanan* dari item jurnal yang mendebit "
"atau mengkredit akun apropriasi (misalnya, dividen yang harus dibayar atau "
"akun cadangan) yang muncul di neraca keuangan. Ini mempertahankan pemisahan "
"yang ketat antara proses distribusi laba dan liabilitas atau ekuitas yang "
"dihasilkan."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/reporting/year_end.rst:205
msgid "Manual journal entry"
msgstr "Entri jurnal manual"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/reporting/year_end.rst:207
msgid ""
"To roll up income and expenses and replace the dynamic *Result Brought "
"Forward* line with an explicit journal item that balances the trial balance, "
"create a manual journal entry by following these steps:"
msgstr ""
"Untuk merangkum pendapatan dan pengeluaran serta mengganti baris dinamis "
"*Hasil yang Dibawa ke Depan* dengan item jurnal eksplisit yang "
"menyeimbangkan neraca saldo, buat entri jurnal manual dengan mengikuti "
"langkah-langkah berikut:"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/reporting/year_end.rst:211
msgid "Go to :menuselection:`Accounting --> Accounting --> Journal Entries`."
msgstr "Buka :menuselection:`Accounting --> Accounting --> Journal Entries`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/reporting/year_end.rst:212
#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/vendor_bills.rst:146
#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/turkiye.rst:175
msgid "Click the :guilabel:`New` button."
msgstr "Klik tombol :guilabel:`Baru`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/reporting/year_end.rst:213
msgid ""
"Add a :guilabel:`Reference` such as `Annual Closing [YEAR]`, replacing "
"`[YEAR]` with the current year."
msgstr ""
"Tambahkan :guilabel:`Reference` seperti `Annual Closing [YEAR]`, ganti "
"`[YEAR]` dengan tahun berjalan."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/reporting/year_end.rst:215
msgid ""
"Set the :guilabel:`Accounting Date` to the end of the fiscal year in which "
"the profit or loss was incurred."
msgstr ""
"Atur :guilabel:`Accounting Date` ke akhir tahun fiskal di mana laba atau "
"rugi terjadi."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/reporting/year_end.rst:217
msgid ""
"In the :guilabel:`Journal Items` tab, add the necessary appropriation lines. "
"In the case of recording a profit, debit one or more appropriation (current "
"year earnings) accounts. In the case of recording a loss, credit one or more "
"appropriation (current year earnings) accounts. Either way, to fully "
"distribute the year's profit or loss, the amount should sum to the amount "
"that is on the dynamic :guilabel:`Result Brought Forward` line of the trial "
"balance **for the year after the profit or loss was incurred**."
msgstr ""
"Di tab :guilabel:`Journal Items`, tambahkan baris apropriasi yang "
"diperlukan. Dalam kasus mencatat laba, debit satu atau lebih akun apropriasi "
"(laba tahun berjalan). Dalam kasus mencatat rugi, kredit satu atau lebih "
"akun apropriasi (laba tahun berjalan). Bagaimanapun, untuk mendistribusikan "
"sepenuhnya laba atau rugi tahun tersebut, jumlahnya harus sama dengan jumlah "
"yang ada pada baris dinamis :guilabel:`Result Brought Forward` dari neraca "
"saldo **untuk tahun setelah laba atau rugi terjadi**."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/reporting/year_end.rst:223
msgid ""
"Add one or more additional lines that credit (in the case of a profit) or "
"debit (in the case of a loss) one or more destination accounts to balance "
"the journal entry. Depending on the localization and the situation, the "
"destination account(s) will vary, but they could be other appropriation "
"(current year earnings) accounts, equity accounts, current liabilities "
"accounts, or a combination thereof. The sum of these lines must balance the "
"line(s) from the previous step."
msgstr ""
"Tambahkan satu atau lebih baris tambahan yang mengkredit (dalam kasus laba) "
"atau mendebit (dalam kasus rugi) satu atau lebih akun tujuan untuk "
"menyeimbangkan entri jurnal. Tergantung pada lokalisasi dan situasinya, akun "
"tujuan akan bervariasi, tetapi bisa berupa akun apropriasi (laba tahun "
"berjalan) lainnya, akun ekuitas, akun liabilitas lancar, atau kombinasinya. "
"Jumlah baris ini harus menyeimbangkan baris dari langkah sebelumnya."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/reporting/year_end.rst:228
msgid "Click :guilabel:`Post`."
msgstr "Klik :guilabel:`Post`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/reporting/year_end.rst:231
msgid ""
"Depending on the localization and the situation, the accounts involved will "
"vary. The following example illustrates one potential journal entry using "
"accounts from the Belgian :abbr:`GAAP (generally accepted accounting "
"principles)` / :abbr:`CSA-WVV (code des sociétés et des associations - "
"wetboek van vennootschappen en verenigingen)`. This example debits three "
"different allocation (current year earnings) accounts and credits three "
"different destination accounts (two equity accounts and one current "
"liabilities account)."
msgstr ""
"Tergantung pada lokalisasi dan situasinya, akun yang terlibat akan "
"bervariasi. Contoh berikut mengilustrasikan satu entri jurnal potensial "
"menggunakan akun dari :abbr:`GAAP (prinsip akuntansi yang diterima secara "
"umum)` / :abbr:`CSA-WVV (code des sociétés et des associations - wetboek van "
"vennootschappen en verenigingen)` Belgia. Contoh ini mendebit tiga akun "
"alokasi (laba tahun berjalan) yang berbeda dan mengkredit tiga akun tujuan "
"yang berbeda (dua akun ekuitas dan satu akun liabilitas lancar)."

