#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/reporting/year_end.rst:260
msgid ""
"To complete the fiscal year-end process and finalize the annual closing, go "
"to the Accounting dashboard and click :guilabel:`Tax Returns` on "
"the :guilabel:`Tax Returns` journal from the Accounting dashboard. "
