"jurnal :guilabel:`Laporan Pajak` dari Dashboard Akuntansi. Atau, buka "
":menuselection:`Akuntansi --> Akuntansi --> Laporan Pajak`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/reporting/year_end.rst:265
