":ref:`pembayaran di muka <accounting/tax-returns/advance-payments>` "
"(berdasarkan :doc:`lokalisasi fiskal <../../fiscal_localizations>`), dan "
"penutupan tahunan. :guilabel:`Penutupan Tahunan` yang tertunda mengikuti dua "
"langkah: :ref:`tinjau <accounting/year-end/annual-closing/review>` dan "
":ref:`kirim <accounting/year-end/annual-closing/submit>`. Item "
":guilabel:`Penutupan Tahunan` mencakup:"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/reporting/year_end.rst:272
msgid "A period (year)."
msgstr "Periode (tahun)."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/reporting/year_end.rst:275
msgid ""
"Action steps, such as :ref:`Review <accounting/year-end/annual-closing/"
"review>` and :ref:`Submit <accounting/year-end/annual-closing/submit>`, "
"which turn green when completed."
msgstr ""
"Langkah tindakan, seperti :ref:`Tinjau <accounting/year-end/annual-closing/"
