"berubah hijau setelah selesai."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/reporting/year_end.rst:277
msgid "Action buttons for key tasks."
msgstr "Tombol tindakan untuk tugas-tugas utama."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/reporting/year_end.rst:281
msgid ""
"Before the annual closing is reviewed, the number of :guilabel:`Pending` "
"or :guilabel:`Passed` closing validation checks is displayed in red or "
"green, respectively."
msgstr ""
"Sebelum penutupan tahunan ditinjau, jumlah pemeriksaan validasi penutupan "
"yang berstatus :guilabel:`Tertunda` atau :guilabel:`Lolos` ditampilkan dalam "
"warna merah atau hijau."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/reporting/year_end.rst:290
msgid ""
"To start reviewing an annual closing, click the annual closing line. The "
"annual closing checks view displays the following, depending on "
"the :doc:`fiscal localization <../../fiscal_localizations>`:"
msgstr ""
"Untuk mulai meninjau penutupan tahunan, klik baris penutupan tahunan. "
"Tampilan pemeriksaan penutupan tahunan menampilkan hal berikut, tergantung "
"pada :doc:`lokalisasi fiskal <../../fiscal_localizations>`:"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/reporting/year_end.rst:293
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Aged payables per partner`: Review payables without a partner."
msgstr ":guilabel:`Hutang berumur per mitra`: Tinjau hutang tanpa mitra."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/reporting/year_end.rst:294
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Aged receivables per partner`: Review receivables without a "
"partner."
msgstr ":guilabel:`Piutang berumur per mitra`: Tinjau piutang tanpa mitra."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/reporting/year_end.rst:295
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Bank Reconciliation`: Reconcile all bank account transactions up "
"to year-end."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Rekonsiliasi Bank`: Rekonsiliasi semua transaksi akun bank hingga "
"akhir tahun."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/reporting/year_end.rst:296
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Deferred Entries`: Ensure start and end dates are correctly set "
"on bills and invoices."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Entri Ditangguhkan`: Pastikan tanggal mulai dan akhir telah "
"diatur dengan benar pada tagihan dan faktur."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/reporting/year_end.rst:298
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Earnings Allocation`: After adjustments, transfer the result "
"brought forward to an equity account."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Earnings Allocation`: Setelah penyesuaian, transfer hasil yang "
"dibawa ke depan ke akun ekuitas."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/reporting/year_end.rst:300
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Fixed Assets`: Ensure assets are properly registered for "
"automatic depreciation calculation."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Aset Tetap`: Pastikan aset terdaftar dengan benar untuk "
"perhitungan penyusutan otomatis."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/reporting/year_end.rst:302
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Loans`: Ensure loans are properly registered for automatic "
"amortization calculations."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Pinjaman`: Pastikan pinjaman terdaftar dengan benar untuk "
"perhitungan amortisasi otomatis."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/reporting/year_end.rst:303
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Manual Adjustments`: Complete any necessary manual adjustments "
"and internal checks."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Penyesuaian Manual`: Selesaikan penyesuaian manual dan "
"pemeriksaan internal yang diperlukan."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/reporting/year_end.rst:304
msgid ""
":guilabel:`No draft entries`: Review and post draft invoices, bills, and "
"entries in the period, or change their accounting date."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Tidak ada entri draft`: Tinjau dan posting faktur draft, tagihan, "
"dan entri dalam periode, atau ubah tanggal akuntansinya."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/reporting/year_end.rst:306
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Overdue payables`: Review overdue payables aged over 60 days and "
"assess the need for an allowance for uncertain liabilities."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Hutang jatuh tempo`: Tinjau hutang jatuh tempo yang berumur lebih "
"dari 60 hari dan nilai kebutuhan penyisihan untuk kewajiban tidak pasti."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/reporting/year_end.rst:308
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Overdue receivables`: Review overdue receivables aged over 60 "
"days and assess the need for an allowance for doubtful accounts or expected "
"credit loss provision, as per IFRS 9 guidelines."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Piutang jatuh tempo`: Tinjau piutang jatuh tempo yang berumur "
"lebih dari 60 hari dan nilai kebutuhan penyisihan piutang ragu-ragu atau "
"provisi kerugian kredit yang diharapkan, sesuai pedoman IFRS 9."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/reporting/year_end.rst:311
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Total Receivables`: Verify that the total aged receivables equals "
"the customer account balance."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Total Piutang`: Verifikasi bahwa total piutang berumur sama "
"dengan saldo akun pelanggan."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/reporting/year_end.rst:313
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Total payables`: Verify that the total aged payables equals the "
"vendor account balance."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Total hutang`: Verifikasi bahwa total hutang berumur sama dengan "
"saldo akun vendor."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/reporting/year_end.rst:316
msgid ""
"Some of the checks are performed automatically, while others serve as "
"reminders to review essential tasks. Each check card is either labeled as:"
msgstr ""
"Beberapa pemeriksaan dilakukan secara otomatis, sementara yang lain "
"berfungsi sebagai pengingat untuk meninjau tugas-tugas penting. Setiap kartu "
"pemeriksaan diberi label sebagai:"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/reporting/year_end.rst:319
msgid ":guilabel:`Reviewed` (highlighted in green): The check has passed."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Ditinjau` (disorot dengan warna hijau): Pemeriksaan telah "
"berhasil."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/reporting/year_end.rst:320
msgid ""
":guilabel:`To review` (highlighted in grey): Action is required before the "
"check can be manually marked as :guilabel:`Reviewed` "
"or :guilabel:`Supervised`."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Untuk ditinjau` (disorot dengan warna abu-abu): Tindakan "
"diperlukan sebelum pemeriksaan dapat ditandai secara manual sebagai "
":guilabel:`Ditinjau` atau :guilabel:`Diawasi`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/reporting/year_end.rst:322
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Anomaly` (highlighted in red): The automatic check detects an "
"issue. There are two options:"
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Anomali` (disorot dengan warna merah): Pemeriksaan otomatis "
"mendeteksi masalah. Ada dua opsi:"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/reporting/year_end.rst:325
msgid "Click the failed check's card to fix the issue."
msgstr "Klik kartu pemeriksaan yang gagal untuk memperbaiki masalah."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/reporting/year_end.rst:329
msgid ""
"Once all closing validation checks have passed, either labeled "
"as :guilabel:`Reviewed` or :guilabel:`Supervised`, "
"click :guilabel:`Validate` to complete the :guilabel:`Review` step. The "
"annual closing can then be :ref:`submitted <accounting/year-end/annual-"
"closing/submit>`."
msgstr ""
"Setelah semua pemeriksaan validasi penutupan berhasil, baik diberi label "
"sebagai :guilabel:`Ditinjau` atau :guilabel:`Diawasi`, klik "
":guilabel:`Validasi` untuk menyelesaikan langkah :guilabel:`Tinjauan`. "
"Penutupan tahunan kemudian dapat :ref:`diajukan <accounting/year-end/annual-"
"closing/submit>`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/reporting/year_end.rst:344
msgid ""
"Once a tax return has completed the :ref:`Review <accounting/tax-returns/vat-"
"return-review>` step, click :guilabel:`Submit`."
msgstr ""
"Setelah pengembalian pajak menyelesaikan langkah :ref:`Tinjauan <accounting/"
"tax-returns/vat-return-review>`, klik :guilabel:`Ajukan`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/reporting/year_end.rst:347
msgid ""
"If a :guilabel:`Submission Instructions` pop-up window appears, depending on "
"the :doc:`fiscal localization <../../fiscal_localizations>`, follow the "
"local :guilabel:`Instructions`, and click :guilabel:`Mark as Submitted`."
msgstr ""
"Jika jendela pop-up :guilabel:`Instruksi Pengajuan` muncul, tergantung pada "
":doc:`lokalisasi fiskal <../../fiscal_localizations>`, ikuti "
":guilabel:`Instruksi` lokal, dan klik :guilabel:`Tandai sebagai Diajukan`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/reporting/year_end.rst:352
msgid ""
"To review checks before submitting the annual closing, click the :icon:`fa-"
"ellipsis-v` :guilabel:`(vertical ellipsis)` icon on the annual closing line "
"and select :guilabel:`Reset`."
msgstr ""
"Untuk meninjau pemeriksaan sebelum mengajukan penutupan tahunan, klik ikon "
":icon:`fa-ellipsis-v` :guilabel:`(ellipsis vertikal)` pada baris penutupan "
"tahunan dan pilih :guilabel:`Atur Ulang`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/taxes.rst:7
msgid ""
"Tax regulations generally require companies to compute tax amounts on sales, "
"keep a record of accumulated tax debit and credit, and periodically file "
"this information in tax returns."
msgstr ""
"Peraturan perpajakan umumnya mengharuskan perusahaan untuk menghitung jumlah "
"pajak atas penjualan, menyimpan catatan akumulasi debit dan kredit pajak, "
"dan secara berkala melaporkan informasi ini dalam laporan pajak."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/taxes.rst:11
msgid "Overview"
msgstr "Gambaran Umum"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/taxes.rst:13
