msgstr ""
"Secara umum, mengelola pajak di Odoo melibatkan langkah-langkah berikut:"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/taxes.rst:15
msgid ""
"Taxes are added on individual lines of documents created via the Sales, "
"Purchase, Accounting, and Point of Sale apps."
msgstr ""
"Pajak ditambahkan pada baris individual dokumen yang dibuat melalui aplikasi "
"Penjualan, Pembelian, Akuntansi, dan POS."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/taxes.rst:17
msgid "Odoo automatically computes tax amounts on the documents."
msgstr "Odoo secara otomatis menghitung jumlah pajak pada dokumen."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/taxes.rst:18
msgid ""
"On accounting documents, Odoo generates journal items to keep track of tax "
"debit and tax credit."
msgstr ""
"Pada dokumen akuntansi, Odoo menghasilkan item jurnal untuk melacak debit "
"pajak dan kredit pajak."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/taxes.rst:19
msgid ""
"The total base, tax debit, and tax credit for a period can be viewed in the "
"tax return report and used to file a tax return."
msgstr ""
"Total dasar, debit pajak, dan kredit pajak untuk suatu periode dapat dilihat "
"di laporan pengembalian pajak dan digunakan untuk mengajukan pengembalian "
"pajak."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/taxes.rst:23
msgid "Taxes on sales and purchases"
msgstr "Pajak atas penjualan dan pembelian"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/taxes.rst:25
msgid ""
"Most sales and purchase documents have a :guilabel:`Taxes` field where taxes "
"can be applied to individual lines. This includes :doc:`invoices "
"<customer_invoices>` and :doc:`vendor bills <vendor_bills>` in the "
"Accounting app, :doc:`sales quotations <../../sales/sales/sales_quotations>` "
"in the Sales app, and :doc:`purchase orders <../../inventory_and_mrp/"
"purchase/manage_deals/rfq>` in the Purchase app."
msgstr ""
"Sebagian besar dokumen penjualan dan pembelian memiliki kolom "
":guilabel:`Taxes` di mana pajak dapat diterapkan pada baris individual. Ini "
"termasuk :doc:`faktur <customer_invoices>` dan :doc:`tagihan vendor "
"<vendor_bills>` di aplikasi Akuntansi, :doc:`penawaran penjualan <../../"
"sales/sales/sales_quotations>` di aplikasi Penjualan, dan :doc:`pesanan "
"pembelian <../../inventory_and_mrp/purchase/manage_deals/rfq>` di aplikasi "
"Pembelian."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/taxes.rst:None
msgid "Adding a 21% tax on an invoice line."
msgstr "Menambahkan pajak 21% pada baris faktur."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/taxes.rst:35
msgid ""
"When adding a product to a sale or purchase line, the taxes :ref:`assigned "
"to the product <taxes/product>` are automatically applied to the line."
msgstr ""
"Saat menambahkan produk ke baris penjualan atau pembelian, pajak yang "
":ref:`ditetapkan ke produk <taxes/product>` secara otomatis diterapkan ke "
"baris tersebut."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/taxes.rst:38
msgid ""
"In the :doc:`Point of Sale <../../sales/point_of_sale>` app, the "
"taxes :ref:`assigned to the products <taxes/product>` are applied directly "
"to the order and cannot be changed except by a :doc:`fiscal position <taxes/"
"fiscal_positions>`."
msgstr ""
"Di aplikasi :doc:`POS <../../sales/point_of_sale>`, pajak yang "
":ref:`ditetapkan ke produk <taxes/product>` diterapkan langsung ke pesanan "
"dan tidak dapat diubah kecuali oleh :doc:`posisi fiskal <taxes/"
"fiscal_positions>`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/taxes.rst:43
msgid "Automatic computation of tax amounts"
msgstr "Perhitungan otomatis jumlah pajak"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/taxes.rst:45
msgid ""
"Applying a tax to a sale or purchase line allows Odoo to automatically "
"compute the tax amount based on the sale or purchase line's subtotal and the "
"tax's configuration. The details of the computation are explained in "
"the :doc:`Tax computation documentation <taxes/tax_computation>`."
msgstr ""
"Menerapkan pajak ke baris penjualan atau pembelian memungkinkan Odoo untuk "
"secara otomatis menghitung jumlah pajak berdasarkan subtotal baris penjualan "
"atau pembelian dan konfigurasi pajak. Detail perhitungan dijelaskan dalam "
":doc:`dokumentasi perhitungan pajak <taxes/tax_computation>`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/taxes.rst:None
msgid "Odoo automatically computes a tax amount for the 21% tax."
msgstr "Odoo secara otomatis menghitung jumlah pajak untuk pajak 21%."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/taxes.rst:53
msgid "Automatic generation of tax journal items"
msgstr "Pembuatan otomatis item jurnal pajak"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/taxes.rst:55
msgid ""
"Upon applying a tax on an :doc:`invoice <customer_invoices>` or :doc:`vendor "
"bill <vendor_bills>`, a tax payable journal item is automatically generated "
"with the tax amount. This keeps track of the tax debit or credit associated "
"with the transaction."
msgstr ""
"Saat menerapkan pajak pada :doc:`faktur <customer_invoices>` atau "
":doc:`tagihan vendor <vendor_bills>`, item jurnal pajak terutang dibuat "
"secara otomatis dengan jumlah pajak. Ini melacak debit atau kredit pajak "
"yang terkait dengan transaksi."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/taxes.rst:59
msgid ""
"Furthermore, the tax amount is added to the amount due on the receivable or "
"payable journal item."
msgstr ""
"Selain itu, jumlah pajak ditambahkan ke jumlah yang harus dibayar pada item "
"jurnal piutang atau utang."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/taxes.rst:61
msgid ""
"Finally, :ref:`Tax Grids <accounting/tax-returns/tax-grids>` are added both "
"to the automatically created tax payable journal item and to the invoice "
"line on which the tax is applied. These tags are used to retrieve the "
"journal items corresponding to the tax's base and tax amount in "
"the :doc:`Tax Return <reporting/tax_returns>` report."
msgstr ""
"Terakhir, :ref:`Kisi Pajak <accounting/tax-returns/tax-grids>` ditambahkan "
"baik ke item jurnal pajak terutang yang dibuat secara otomatis maupun ke "
"baris faktur di mana pajak diterapkan. Tag ini digunakan untuk mengambil "
"item jurnal yang sesuai dengan dasar pajak dan jumlah pajak dalam laporan "
":doc:`Pengembalian Pajak <reporting/tax_returns>`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/taxes.rst:None
msgid ""
"Odoo automatically generates a tax payable journal item for the 21% tax."
msgstr ""
"Odoo secara otomatis membuat item jurnal pajak terutang untuk pajak 21%."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/taxes.rst:70
msgid ""
"If :doc:`Cash Basis <taxes/cash_basis>` is enabled, upon reconciling the "
"invoice or vendor bill with the payment, an additional journal entry is "
"created to represent the creation of the tax debit or credit at that point "
"in time."
msgstr ""
"Jika :doc:`Basis Kas <taxes/cash_basis>` diaktifkan, saat merekonsiliasi "
"faktur atau tagihan vendor dengan pembayaran, entri jurnal tambahan dibuat "
"untuk mewakili pembuatan debit atau kredit pajak pada waktu tersebut."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/taxes.rst:75
msgid "Filing tax returns"
msgstr "Pengajuan pengembalian pajak"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/taxes.rst:77
msgid ""
"The :doc:`Tax Return <reporting/tax_returns>` report aggregates the base and "
"tax amounts from invoices and vendor bills over a given period and presents "
"it in a format tailored to the :doc:`fiscal localization <../"
"fiscal_localizations>`."
msgstr ""
"Laporan :doc:`Pengembalian Pajak <reporting/tax_returns>` mengagregasi "
"jumlah dasar dan pajak dari faktur dan tagihan vendor selama periode "
"tertentu dan menyajikannya dalam format yang disesuaikan dengan "
":doc:`lokalisasi fiskal <../fiscal_localizations>`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/taxes.rst:81
msgid ""
"The amounts presented in the tax return report can be used to complete tax "
"declarations that need to be periodically submitted to the government. In "
"most cases, there is a one-to-one correspondence between the lines of the "
"tax return and the official tax declaration, allowing amounts to simply be "
"copied from one to the other."
msgstr ""
"Jumlah yang disajikan dalam laporan pengembalian pajak dapat digunakan untuk "
"melengkapi deklarasi pajak yang perlu diajukan secara berkala kepada "
"pemerintah. Dalam sebagian besar kasus, ada korespondensi satu-ke-satu "
"antara baris pengembalian pajak dan deklarasi pajak resmi, sehingga jumlah "
"dapat langsung disalin dari satu ke yang lain."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/taxes.rst:None
msgid "The base section of the tax return report for Belgium."
msgstr "Bagian dasar dari laporan pengembalian pajak untuk Belgia."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/taxes.rst:None
msgid "The tax section of the tax return report for Belgium."
msgstr "Bagian pajak dari laporan pengembalian pajak untuk Belgia."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/taxes.rst:95
msgid "Basic tax configuration"
msgstr "Konfigurasi pajak dasar"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/taxes.rst:97
msgid "Follow these basic steps to set up taxes:"
msgstr "Ikuti langkah-langkah dasar berikut untuk mengatur pajak:"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/taxes.rst:99
msgid ""
"Enable any relevant :ref:`company-wide options <taxes/configuration/"
"company>`."
msgstr ""
"Aktifkan semua :ref:`opsi perusahaan <taxes/configuration/company>` yang "
"relevan."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/taxes.rst:100
msgid ""
"Activate any needed :ref:`pre-configured taxes <taxes/list_activation>`."
msgstr ""
"Aktifkan semua :ref:`pajak yang telah dikonfigurasi <taxes/list_activation>` "
"yang diperlukan."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/taxes.rst:101
msgid "Assign taxes on your :ref:`products <taxes/product>`."
msgstr "Tetapkan pajak pada :ref:`produk <taxes/product>` Anda."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/taxes.rst:106
msgid "Company-wide options"
msgstr "Opsi seluruh perusahaan"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/taxes.rst:108
msgid ""
"To access these configuration options, go to :menuselection:`Accounting --> "
"Configuration --> Settings` and scroll down to :guilabel:`Taxes`."
msgstr ""
"Untuk mengakses opsi konfigurasi ini, buka :menuselection:`Akuntansi --> "
"Konfigurasi --> Pengaturan` dan gulir ke bawah ke :guilabel:`Pajak`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/taxes.rst:116
msgid ""
"The default :guilabel:`Sales Tax` and :guilabel:`Purchase Tax` are "
"automatically set on products when creating new products."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Pajak Penjualan` dan :guilabel:`Pajak Pembelian` default secara "
"otomatis ditetapkan pada produk saat membuat produk baru."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/taxes.rst:119
msgid ""
"If :ref:`Accounting Firms <accounting/fiduciaries>` mode is enabled, the "
"default sales tax is automatically set on new invoice lines, and the default "
"purchase tax is automatically set on new vendor bill lines."
msgstr ""
"Jika mode :ref:`Accounting Firms <accounting/fiduciaries>` diaktifkan, pajak "
"penjualan default secara otomatis ditetapkan pada baris invoice baru, dan "
"pajak pembelian default secara otomatis ditetapkan pada baris tagihan vendor "
"baru."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/taxes.rst:123
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Prices` can be changed to :guilabel:`Tax Included` to treat all "
"taxes as :ref:`tax included <taxes/included-in-price>` by default. This "
"would be appropriate if all of a company's pricing is done tax-included. If "
"only some of a company's pricing is tax-included, individual taxes can be "
"set as :guilabel:`Tax Included`."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Harga` dapat diubah menjadi :guilabel:`Termasuk Pajak` untuk "
"memperlakukan semua pajak sebagai :ref:`tax included <taxes/included-in-"
"price>` secara default. Ini akan sesuai jika semua penetapan harga "
"perusahaan dilakukan termasuk pajak. Jika hanya beberapa penetapan harga "
"perusahaan yang termasuk pajak, pajak individual dapat ditetapkan sebagai "
":guilabel:`Termasuk Pajak`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/taxes.rst:129
#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/taxes/eu_distance_selling.rst:3
msgid "EU intra-community distance selling"
msgstr ""

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/taxes.rst:131
msgid ""
"Activate this option if you are based in the EU and sell to consumers in "
"other EU countries to apply local VAT rates."
msgstr ""
"Aktifkan opsi ini jika Anda berbasis di UE dan menjual kepada konsumen di "
"negara UE lainnya untuk menerapkan tarif PPN lokal."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/taxes.rst:135
msgid ":doc:`EU intra-community distance selling<taxes/eu_distance_selling>`"
msgstr ""
":doc:`Penjualan jarak jauh intra-komunitas UE<taxes/eu_distance_selling>`"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/taxes.rst:138
msgid "Cash basis"
msgstr "Basis kas"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/taxes.rst:140
msgid ""
"Activate this option if taxes must be accounted for on a cash rather than "
"accruals basis. Some countries mandate cash basis accounting; in that case, "
"this option will be activated by default by the :doc:`fiscal localization "
"package <../fiscal_localizations>`."
msgstr ""
"Aktifkan opsi ini jika pajak harus dicatat berdasarkan kas daripada akrual. "
"Beberapa negara mewajibkan akuntansi basis kas; dalam kasus tersebut, opsi "
"ini akan diaktifkan secara default oleh :doc:`paket lokalisasi fiskal <../"
"fiscal_localizations>`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/taxes.rst:145
msgid ":doc:`Cash basis <taxes/cash_basis>`"
msgstr ":doc:`Basis kas <taxes/cash_basis>`"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/taxes.rst:150
msgid "Activate pre-configured taxes"
msgstr "Aktifkan pajak yang telah dikonfigurasi sebelumnya"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/taxes.rst:152
msgid ""
"The list of taxes can be accessed by going to :menuselection:`Accounting --> "
"Configuration --> Taxes`."
msgstr ""
"Daftar pajak dapat diakses dengan membuka :menuselection:`Akuntansi --> "
"Konfigurasi --> Pajak`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/taxes.rst:155
msgid ""
"Generally, inactive taxes are created for most sales tax rates by "
"the :doc:`fiscal localization <../fiscal_localizations>` package, but only "
"the main tax rate is active by default. To activate an inactive tax, click "
"the toggle in the :guilabel:`Active` column."
msgstr ""
"Umumnya, pajak tidak aktif dibuat untuk sebagian besar tarif pajak penjualan "
"oleh paket :doc:`lokalisasi fiskal <../fiscal_localizations>`, tetapi hanya "
"tarif pajak utama yang aktif secara default. Untuk mengaktifkan pajak yang "
"tidak aktif, klik toggle di kolom :guilabel:`Aktif`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/taxes.rst:162
msgid "Assign taxes on products"
msgstr "Tetapkan pajak pada produk"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/taxes.rst:164
msgid ""
"To configure the taxes used for each product, go "
"to :menuselection:`Accounting --> Customers --> Products`, select the "
"product to configure, and fill the :guilabel:`Sales Taxes` "
"and :guilabel:`Purchase Taxes` fields. These taxes are automatically applied "
"when adding the product to an invoice, vendor bill, sales order, purchase "
"order, or point of sale order."
msgstr ""
"Untuk mengonfigurasi pajak yang digunakan untuk setiap produk, buka "
":menuselection:`Akuntansi --> Pelanggan --> Produk`, pilih produk yang akan "
"dikonfigurasi, dan isi kolom :guilabel:`Pajak Penjualan` dan "
":guilabel:`Pajak Pembelian`. Pajak ini secara otomatis diterapkan saat "
"menambahkan produk ke invoice, tagihan vendor, sales order, purchase order, "
"atau order POS."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/taxes.rst:170
msgid ""
"Use the :ref:`Default Taxes <taxes/default>` company-wide setting to "
"automatically fill these fields on new products."
msgstr ""
"Gunakan pengaturan :ref:`Default Taxes <taxes/default>` seluruh perusahaan "
"untuk secara otomatis mengisi kolom ini pada produk baru."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/taxes.rst:176
msgid "Advanced tax configuration"
msgstr "Konfigurasi pajak lanjutan"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/taxes.rst:178
msgid "The following aspects of a tax can be customized:"
msgstr "Aspek berikut dari pajak dapat disesuaikan:"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/taxes.rst:180
msgid ""
"How the tax :ref:`appears in the backend <taxes/configuration/back-end>`"
msgstr "Bagaimana pajak :ref:`muncul di backend <taxes/configuration/back-end>`"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/taxes.rst:181
msgid "How the tax :ref:`appears to customers <taxes/configuration/customer>`"
msgstr ""
"Bagaimana pajak :ref:`muncul kepada pelanggan <taxes/configuration/customer>`"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/taxes.rst:182
msgid "The details of the :doc:`tax computation <taxes/tax_computation>`"
msgstr "Detail dari :doc:`perhitungan pajak <taxes/tax_computation>`"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/taxes.rst:183
msgid "How tax payable journal items are :ref:`created <taxes/definition-tab>`"
msgstr ""
"Bagaimana item jurnal pajak terutang :ref:`dibuat <taxes/definition-tab>`"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/taxes.rst:184
msgid ""
"How to configure the tax to :ref:`replace <taxes/tax-mapping>` other taxes "
"according to :doc:`fiscal positions <taxes/fiscal_positions>`."
msgstr ""
"Bagaimana mengonfigurasi pajak untuk :ref:`mengganti <taxes/tax-mapping>` "
"pajak lain sesuai dengan :doc:`posisi fiskal <taxes/fiscal_positions>`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/taxes.rst:187
msgid ""
"To open a tax's configuration, go to :menuselection:`Accounting --> "
"Configuration --> Taxes`, then click the tax name."
msgstr ""
"Untuk membuka konfigurasi pajak, buka :menuselection:`Akuntansi --> "
"Konfigurasi --> Pajak`, kemudian klik nama pajak."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/taxes.rst:193
msgid "Configure backend appearance and availability"
msgstr "Konfigurasikan tampilan dan ketersediaan backend"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/taxes.rst:195
msgid ""
"The following options determine how a tax is displayed to users in the Odoo "
"back-end."
msgstr ""
"Opsi berikut menentukan bagaimana pajak ditampilkan kepada pengguna di "
"backend Odoo."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/taxes.rst:200
#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/australia.rst:158
msgid "Tax name"
msgstr "Nama pajak"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/taxes.rst:202
msgid ""
"The :guilabel:`Tax Name` appears for backend users in the :guilabel:`Taxes` "
"field in :doc:`sales orders <../../sales/sales>`, :doc:`invoices "
"<customer_invoices>`, product forms, etc."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Nama Pajak` muncul untuk pengguna backend di bidang "
":guilabel:`Pajak` dalam :doc:`pesanan penjualan <../../sales/sales>`, "
":doc:`faktur <customer_invoices>`, formulir produk, dll."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/taxes.rst:208
msgid "Tax type"
msgstr "Jenis pajak"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/taxes.rst:210
msgid ""
"The :guilabel:`Tax Type` determines where the tax is available to be "
"selected."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Jenis Pajak` menentukan di mana pajak tersedia untuk dipilih."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/taxes.rst:212
msgid "**Sales**: Customer invoices, product customer taxes, etc."
msgstr "**Penjualan**: Faktur pelanggan, pajak pelanggan produk, dll."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/taxes.rst:213
msgid "**Purchase**: Vendor bills, product vendor taxes, etc."
msgstr "**Pembelian**: Tagihan vendor, pajak vendor produk, dll."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/taxes.rst:214
msgid "**None**"
msgstr "**Tidak ada**"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/taxes.rst:217
msgid ""
"Use :guilabel:`None` for taxes that you want to include in a :ref:`Group of "
"Taxes <taxes/computation>` but that you do not want to list along with other "
"sales or purchase taxes."
msgstr ""
"Gunakan :guilabel:`Tidak Ada` untuk pajak yang ingin Anda sertakan dalam "
":ref:`Grup Pajak <taxes/computation>` tetapi yang tidak ingin Anda cantumkan "
"bersama dengan pajak penjualan atau pembelian lainnya."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/taxes.rst:221
msgid "Tax scope"
msgstr "Cakupan pajak"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/taxes.rst:223
msgid ""
"The :guilabel:`Tax Scope` restricts the use of taxes to a type of product, "
"either **goods** or **services**."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Cakupan Pajak` membatasi penggunaan pajak pada jenis produk "
"tertentu, baik **barang** atau **jasa**."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/taxes.rst:229
msgid ""
"The :guilabel:`Description` can be edited for the purpose of internal "
"documentation."
msgstr ":guilabel:`Deskripsi` dapat diedit untuk tujuan dokumentasi internal."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/taxes.rst:234
msgid "Configure how the tax appears to customers"
msgstr "Konfigurasikan bagaimana pajak muncul kepada pelanggan"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/taxes.rst:239
#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/australia.rst:78
#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/australia.rst:106
#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/new_zealand.rst:81
msgid "Label on invoices"
msgstr "Label pada faktur"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/taxes.rst:241
msgid ""
"The :guilabel:`Label on Invoices` appears on invoice lines in invoice PDFs "
"and on the customer portal."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Label pada Faktur` muncul pada baris faktur dalam PDF faktur dan "
"pada portal pelanggan."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/taxes.rst:None
msgid ""
"The Label on Invoice shows on the invoice line when viewed in the customer "
"portal."
msgstr ""
"Label pada Faktur muncul pada baris faktur ketika dilihat di portal "
"pelanggan."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/taxes.rst:250
msgid "Tax group"
msgstr "Grup pajak"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/taxes.rst:252
msgid ""
"The :guilabel:`Tax Group` is shown in the totals section of the invoice, in "
"invoice PDFs and on the customer portal. Multiple taxes that belong to the "
"same tax group are aggregated together into a single tax amount."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Grup Pajak` ditampilkan di bagian total faktur, dalam PDF faktur "
"dan pada portal pelanggan. Beberapa pajak yang termasuk dalam grup pajak "
"yang sama digabungkan menjadi satu jumlah pajak."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/taxes.rst:None
msgid ""
"The Tax Group shows in the totals section when viewed in the customer portal."
msgstr "Grup Pajak muncul di bagian total ketika dilihat di portal pelanggan."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/taxes.rst:262
msgid "Configure how tax journal items are created"
msgstr "Konfigurasikan bagaimana item jurnal pajak dibuat"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/taxes.rst:264
msgid ""
"The :guilabel:`Distribution for Invoices` and :guilabel:`Distribution for "
"Refunds` sections control the generation of tax payable journal items in "
"invoices and credit notes, respectively. They also determine which :ref:`tax "
"grids <accounting/tax-returns/tax-grids>` are set on invoice lines when this "
"tax is applied."
msgstr ""
"Bagian :guilabel:`Distribusi untuk Faktur` dan :guilabel:`Distribusi untuk "
"Nota Kredit` mengontrol pembuatan item jurnal pajak terutang dalam faktur "
"dan nota kredit. Bagian ini juga menentukan :ref:`grid pajak <accounting/tax-"
"returns/tax-grids>` mana yang ditetapkan pada baris faktur ketika pajak ini "
"diterapkan."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/taxes.rst:269
msgid ""
"Each of these sections should contain one :guilabel:`Base` line, one or "
"more :guilabel:`% of tax` lines amounting to 100% (e.g. one 100% line, or "
"two 50% lines), and optionally, one or more :guilabel:`% of tax` lines "
"amounting to -100.00%."
msgstr ""
"Masing-masing bagian ini harus berisi satu baris :guilabel:`Dasar`, satu "
"atau lebih baris :guilabel:`% dari pajak` yang berjumlah 100% (misalnya satu "
"baris 100%, atau dua baris 50%), dan secara opsional, satu atau lebih baris "
":guilabel:`% dari pajak` yang berjumlah -100,00%."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/taxes.rst:273
msgid ""
"The :guilabel:`Base` line can have one or more :guilabel:`Tax Grids` set, "
"which are added to the invoice line on which the tax is applied."
msgstr ""
"Baris :guilabel:`Dasar` dapat memiliki satu atau lebih :guilabel:`Grid "
"Pajak` yang ditetapkan, yang ditambahkan ke baris faktur di mana pajak "
"diterapkan."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/taxes.rst:276
msgid ""
"The :guilabel:`% of tax` lines control the creation of tax payable journal "
"items. The tax amount is distributed according to the percentages on these "
"lines, and each line is then used as a template to create a tax payable "
"journal item with the same :guilabel:`Account` and :guilabel:`Tax Grids`. If "
"the :guilabel:`Account` is not specified, it defaults to the account of the "
"original invoice line on which the tax is applied."
msgstr ""
"Baris :guilabel:`% dari pajak` mengontrol pembuatan item jurnal pajak "
"terutang. Jumlah pajak didistribusikan sesuai dengan persentase pada baris "
"ini, dan setiap baris kemudian digunakan sebagai templat untuk membuat item "
"jurnal pajak terutang dengan :guilabel:`Akun` dan :guilabel:`Grid Pajak` "
"yang sama. Jika :guilabel:`Akun` tidak ditentukan, secara default "
"menggunakan akun dari baris faktur asli di mana pajak diterapkan."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/taxes.rst:282
msgid "Typical cases include:"
msgstr "Kasus-kasus umum meliputi:"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/taxes.rst:284
msgid ""
"one :guilabel:`100% of tax` line: this is the most common case where the tax "
"amount should appear on a single tax payable journal item."
msgstr ""
"satu baris :guilabel:`100% dari pajak`: ini adalah kasus paling umum di mana "
"jumlah pajak harus muncul pada satu item jurnal pajak terutang."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/taxes.rst:286
msgid ""
"one :guilabel:`100% of tax` and one :guilabel:`-100% of tax` line: this is "
"appropriate if the tax simultaneously generates both a tax debit and a tax "
"credit which cancel each other out (e.g. EU intra-community reverse-charge "
"VAT)."
msgstr ""
"satu baris :guilabel:`100% dari pajak` dan satu baris :guilabel:`-100% dari "
"pajak`: ini sesuai jika pajak secara bersamaan menghasilkan debit pajak dan "
"kredit pajak yang saling meniadakan (misalnya PPN reverse-charge intra-"
"komunitas UE)."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/taxes.rst:289
msgid ""
"one :guilabel:`50% of tax` line that specifies a tax payable account and "
"another :guilabel:`50% of tax` line that does not specify an account: this "
"is appropriate for partially deductible purchase VAT, where part of the tax "
"must be considered an expense rather than a tax credit asset that can offset "
"tax liability."
msgstr ""
"satu baris :guilabel:`50% dari pajak` yang menentukan akun pajak terutang "
"dan baris :guilabel:`50% dari pajak` lainnya yang tidak menentukan akun: ini "
"sesuai untuk PPN pembelian yang dapat dikurangkan sebagian, di mana sebagian "
"pajak harus dianggap sebagai beban daripada aset kredit pajak yang dapat "
"mengimbangi kewajiban pajak."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/taxes.rst:None
msgid "The Distribution for Invoices of a 21% VAT tax."
msgstr "Distribusi untuk Faktur dari pajak PPN 21%."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/taxes.rst:None
msgid "The Distribution for Refunds of a 21% VAT tax."
msgstr "Distribusi untuk Retur dari pajak PPN 21%."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/taxes.rst:303
#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/taxes/avatax.rst:388
#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/taxes/fiscal_positions.rst:35
#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/australia.rst:61
#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/new_zealand.rst:65
msgid "Tax mapping"
msgstr "Pemetaan pajak"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/taxes.rst:305
msgid ""
"Taxes can be combined with :doc:`fiscal positions <taxes/fiscal_positions>` "
"to map taxes to each other so that the correct tax is applied based on the "
"customer's or vendor's location and business type."
msgstr ""
"Pajak dapat dikombinasikan dengan :doc:`posisi fiskal <taxes/"
"fiscal_positions>` untuk memetakan pajak satu sama lain sehingga pajak yang "
"benar diterapkan berdasarkan lokasi dan jenis bisnis pelanggan atau vendor."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/taxes.rst:309
msgid ""
"When configuring a tax, leave the :guilabel:`Fiscal Position` field blank to "
"make the tax immediately available across all fiscal positions, or select "
"specific fiscal positions where this tax should be used to replace other "
"taxes with it. If one or more fiscal positions are selected, use "
"the :guilabel:`Replaces` field to select all of the taxes that this tax "
"should replace for the selected fiscal position(s)."
msgstr ""
"Saat mengonfigurasi pajak, biarkan bidang :guilabel:`Posisi Fiskal` kosong "
"untuk membuat pajak tersedia langsung di semua posisi fiskal, atau pilih "
"posisi fiskal tertentu di mana pajak ini harus digunakan untuk menggantikan "
"pajak lain. Jika satu atau lebih posisi fiskal dipilih, gunakan bidang "
":guilabel:`Menggantikan` untuk memilih semua pajak yang harus digantikan "
"oleh pajak ini untuk posisi fiskal yang dipilih."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/taxes.rst:315
msgid ""
"To replace one tax with multiple other taxes, configure each of the "
"replacement taxes to replace the default product tax."
msgstr ""
"Untuk mengganti satu pajak dengan beberapa pajak lainnya, konfigurasikan "
"setiap pajak pengganti untuk menggantikan pajak produk default."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/taxes.rst:319
msgid ""
"As a sales tax, the :guilabel:`0% Exports` tax applies to quotations, sales "
"orders, and invoices that use the :guilabel:`Foreign Trade` fiscal position. "
"On those records, any time that the :guilabel:`15%` tax would be used, "
"the :guilabel:`0% Exports` tax is used instead."
msgstr ""
"Sebagai pajak penjualan, pajak :guilabel:`0% Ekspor` berlaku untuk penawaran "
"harga, sales order, dan faktur yang menggunakan posisi fiskal "
":guilabel:`Perdagangan Luar Negeri`. Pada catatan tersebut, setiap kali "
"pajak :guilabel:`15%` akan digunakan, pajak :guilabel:`0% Ekspor` digunakan "
"sebagai gantinya."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/taxes.rst:0
msgid "The **0% Exports** tax record"
msgstr "Catatan pajak **0% Ekspor**"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/taxes.rst:327
msgid ""
"Since the first fiscal position in the sequence is considered the company's "
"default, the taxes set on products are expected to be used with that fiscal "
"position, so the :guilabel:`Replaces` field is not displayed on it."
msgstr ""
"Karena posisi fiskal pertama dalam urutan dianggap sebagai default "
"perusahaan, pajak yang ditetapkan pada produk diharapkan digunakan dengan "
"posisi fiskal tersebut, sehingga kolom :guilabel:`Menggantikan` tidak "
"ditampilkan di dalamnya."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/taxes.rst:332
msgid ""
"To more easily view which taxes are replaced, use the :icon:`oi-settings-"
"adjust` :guilabel:`adjust settings` in the taxes list view and display "
"the :guilabel:`Replaces` field."
msgstr ""
"Untuk lebih mudah melihat pajak mana yang digantikan, gunakan :icon:`oi-"
"settings-adjust` :guilabel:`sesuaikan pengaturan` dalam tampilan daftar "
"pajak dan tampilkan kolom :guilabel:`Menggantikan`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/taxes.rst:0
msgid "The **Replaces** field shown in the list view"
msgstr "Kolom **Menggantikan** yang ditampilkan dalam tampilan daftar"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/taxes.rst:339
msgid ""
"Tax mapping only works with :ref:`active <taxes/list_activation>` taxes."
msgstr ""
"Pemetaan pajak hanya berfungsi dengan pajak :ref:`aktif <taxes/"
"list_activation>`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/taxes.rst:342
msgid "Extra taxes"
msgstr "Pajak tambahan"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/taxes.rst:344
msgid ""
"\"Extra taxes\" is a broad term referring to additional taxes beyond the "
"standard or basic taxes imposed by governments. These extra taxes can be "
"**luxury** taxes, **environmental** taxes, **import** or **export duties** "
"taxes, etc."
msgstr ""
"\"Pajak tambahan\" adalah istilah luas yang merujuk pada pajak tambahan di "
"luar pajak standar atau dasar yang dikenakan oleh pemerintah. Pajak tambahan "
"ini dapat berupa pajak **mewah**, pajak **lingkungan**, pajak **impor** atau "
"**ekspor**, dll."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/taxes.rst:349
msgid ""
"The method to compute these taxes varies across different countries. We "
"recommend consulting your country's regulations to understand how to "
"calculate them for your business."
msgstr ""
"Metode penghitungan pajak ini bervariasi di berbagai negara. Kami "
"merekomendasikan untuk berkonsultasi dengan peraturan negara Anda untuk "
"memahami cara menghitungnya untuk bisnis Anda."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/taxes.rst:352
msgid ""
"To compute an extra tax in Odoo, :ref:`create a tax <taxes/configuration>`, "
"enter a tax name, select a :ref:`Tax Computation <taxes/configuration>`, set "
"an :guilabel:`Amount`, and in the :guilabel:`Advanced Options` tab, "
"enable :guilabel:`Affect Base of Subsequent Taxes`. Then, drag and drop the "
"taxes in the :ref:`order they should be computed <taxes/base-subsequent>`."
msgstr ""
"Untuk menghitung pajak tambahan di Odoo, :ref:`buat pajak <taxes/"
"configuration>`, masukkan nama pajak, pilih :ref:`Perhitungan Pajak <taxes/"
"configuration>`, tetapkan :guilabel:`Jumlah`, dan di tab :guilabel:`Opsi "
"Lanjutan`, aktifkan :guilabel:`Mempengaruhi Dasar Pajak Berikutnya`. "
"Kemudian, seret dan lepas pajak dalam :ref:`urutan yang harus dihitung "
"<taxes/base-subsequent>`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/taxes.rst:358
msgid ""
"In Belgium, the formula to compute an environmental tax is: `(product price "
"+ environmental tax) x sales tax`. Therefore, our environmental tax has to "
"come *before* the sales tax in the computation sequence."
msgstr ""
"Di Belgia, rumus untuk menghitung pajak lingkungan adalah: `(harga produk + "
"pajak lingkungan) x pajak penjualan`. Oleh karena itu, pajak lingkungan kita "
"harus datang *sebelum* pajak penjualan dalam urutan penghitungan."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/taxes.rst:361
msgid ""
"In our case, we created a 5% environmental tax (Ecotax) and put it *before* "
"the Belgian base tax of 21%."
msgstr ""
"Dalam kasus kami, kami membuat pajak lingkungan 5% (Ecotax) dan "
"menempatkannya *sebelum* pajak dasar Belgia sebesar 21%."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/taxes.rst:0
msgid "Environmental tax sequence in Belgium."
msgstr "Urutan pajak lingkungan di Belgia."

