msgstr ":doc:`avatax_use`"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/taxes/avatax/avatax_use.rst:3
msgid "AvaTax use"
msgstr "Penggunaan AvaTax"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/taxes/avatax/avatax_use.rst:5
msgid ""
"AvaTax is a tax calculation software that can be integrated with Odoo in the "
"United States and Canada. Once the :doc:`integration setup <../avatax>` is "
"complete, the calculated tax is simple and automatic."
msgstr ""
"AvaTax adalah perangkat lunak penghitungan pajak yang dapat diintegrasikan "
"dengan Odoo di Amerika Serikat dan Kanada. Setelah :doc:`pengaturan "
"integrasi <../avatax>` selesai, penghitungan pajak menjadi sederhana dan "
"otomatis."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/taxes/avatax/avatax_use.rst:12
msgid "Tax calculation"
msgstr "Penghitungan pajak"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/taxes/avatax/avatax_use.rst:14
msgid ""
"Automatically calculate taxes on Odoo quotations and invoices with AvaTax by "
"confirming the documents during the sales flow. Alternatively, calculate the "
"taxes manually by clicking the :guilabel:`Compute Taxes` button, while these "
"documents are in draft stage."
msgstr ""
"Hitung pajak secara otomatis pada penawaran dan faktur Odoo dengan AvaTax "
"dengan mengonfirmasi dokumen selama alur penjualan. Atau, hitung pajak "
"secara manual dengan mengklik tombol :guilabel:`Hitung Pajak`, saat dokumen-"
"dokumen ini masih dalam tahap draf."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/taxes/avatax/avatax_use.rst:19
msgid ""
"Clicking the :guilabel:`Compute Taxes` button recalculates taxes, if any "
"product lines are edited on the invoice."
msgstr ""
"Mengklik tombol :guilabel:`Hitung Pajak` akan menghitung ulang pajak, jika "
"ada baris produk yang diubah pada faktur."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/taxes/avatax/avatax_use.rst:None
msgid "Sales quotation with the confirm and compute taxes button highlighted."
msgstr ""
"Penawaran penjualan dengan tombol konfirmasi dan hitung pajak yang disorot."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/taxes/avatax/avatax_use.rst:26
msgid ""
"The tax calculation is triggered during the following :ref:`automatic "
"trigger <avatax/automatic-triggers>` and :ref:`manual trigger <avatax/manual-"
"triggers>` circumstances."
msgstr ""
"Penghitungan pajak dipicu dalam kondisi :ref:`pemicu otomatis <avatax/"
"automatic-triggers>` dan :ref:`pemicu manual <avatax/manual-triggers>` "
"berikut."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/taxes/avatax/avatax_use.rst:32
msgid "Automatic triggers"
msgstr "Pemicu otomatis"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/taxes/avatax/avatax_use.rst:34
msgid ""
"When the sales rep sends the quote by email with :guilabel:`Send by email` "
"button (pop-up)."
msgstr ""
"Ketika tenaga penjualan mengirim penawaran melalui email dengan tombol "
":guilabel:`Kirim melalui email` (pop-up)."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/taxes/avatax/avatax_use.rst:35
msgid "When the customer views the online quote on the portal."
msgstr "Ketika pelanggan melihat penawaran online di portal."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/taxes/avatax/avatax_use.rst:36
msgid "When a quote is confirmed and becomes a sales order."
msgstr "Ketika penawaran dikonfirmasi dan menjadi Sales Order."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/taxes/avatax/avatax_use.rst:37
msgid "When the customer views the invoice on the portal."
msgstr "Ketika pelanggan melihat faktur di portal."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/taxes/avatax/avatax_use.rst:38
msgid "When a draft invoice is validated."
msgstr "Ketika faktur draf divalidasi."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/taxes/avatax/avatax_use.rst:39
msgid "When the customer views the subscription in the portal."
msgstr "Ketika pelanggan melihat langganan di portal."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/taxes/avatax/avatax_use.rst:40
msgid "When a subscription generates an invoice."
msgstr "Ketika langganan menghasilkan faktur."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/taxes/avatax/avatax_use.rst:41
msgid "When the customer gets to the last screen of the eCommerce checkout."
msgstr "Ketika pelanggan sampai pada layar terakhir checkout eCommerce."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/taxes/avatax/avatax_use.rst:46
msgid "Manual triggers"
msgstr "Pemicu manual"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/taxes/avatax/avatax_use.rst:48
msgid ":guilabel:`Compute Taxes` button at the bottom of the quote."
msgstr "Tombol :guilabel:`Hitung Pajak` di bagian bawah penawaran."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/taxes/avatax/avatax_use.rst:49
msgid ":guilabel:`Compute Taxes` button at the top of the invoice."
msgstr "Tombol :guilabel:`Hitung Pajak` di bagian atas faktur."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/taxes/avatax/avatax_use.rst:51
msgid "Use each of these buttons to manually re-calculate the sales tax."
msgstr ""
"Gunakan masing-masing tombol ini untuk menghitung ulang pajak penjualan "
"secara manual."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/taxes/avatax/avatax_use.rst:54
msgid ""
"Use the :guilabel:`Avalara Partner Code` field that is available on customer "
"records, quotations, and invoices to cross-reference data in Odoo and "
"AvaTax. This field is located under the :menuselection:`Other info` tab of "
"the sales order or quotation in the :guilabel:`Sales` section."
msgstr ""
"Gunakan kolom :guilabel:`Avalara Partner Code` yang tersedia pada catatan "
"pelanggan, penawaran harga, dan faktur untuk referensi silang data di Odoo "
"dan AvaTax. Kolom ini terletak di bawah tab :menuselection:`Other info` dari "
"sales order atau penawaran harga di bagian :guilabel:`Penjualan`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/taxes/avatax/avatax_use.rst:58
msgid ""
"On the customer record, navigate to *Contacts app* and select a contact. "
"Then open the :guilabel:`Sales & Purchase` tab and the :guilabel:`Avalara "
"Partner Code` under the :guilabel:`Sales` section."
msgstr ""
"Pada catatan pelanggan, navigasikan ke *aplikasi Kontak* dan pilih kontak. "
"Kemudian buka tab :guilabel:`Sales & Purchase` dan :guilabel:`Avalara "
"Partner Code` di bawah bagian :guilabel:`Penjualan`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/taxes/avatax/avatax_use.rst:63
msgid ""
"The :guilabel:`Automatic Tax Mapping (AvaTax)` fiscal position is also "
"applied on those Odoo documents, like subscriptions."
msgstr ""
"Posisi fiskal :guilabel:`Automatic Tax Mapping (AvaTax)` juga diterapkan "
"pada dokumen Odoo tersebut, seperti langganan."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/taxes/avatax/avatax_use.rst:67
#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/taxes/avatax/avatax_use.rst:167
msgid ":doc:`../fiscal_positions`"
msgstr ":doc:`../fiscal_positions`"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/taxes/avatax/avatax_use.rst:70
msgid "AvaTax synchronization"
msgstr "Sinkronisasi AvaTax"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/taxes/avatax/avatax_use.rst:72
msgid ""
"Synchronization occurs with AvaTax, when the *invoice* is created in Odoo. "
"This means the sales tax is recorded with Avalara (AvaTax software "
"developer)."
msgstr ""
"Sinkronisasi terjadi dengan AvaTax, ketika *faktur* dibuat di Odoo. Ini "
"berarti pajak penjualan dicatat dengan Avalara (pengembang perangkat lunak "
"AvaTax)."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/taxes/avatax/avatax_use.rst:75
msgid ""
"To do so, navigate to :menuselection:`Sales app --> Orders --> Quotations`. "
"Select a quotation from the list."
msgstr ""
"Untuk melakukannya, navigasikan ke :menuselection:`Sales app --> Orders --> "
"Quotations`. Pilih penawaran harga dari daftar."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/taxes/avatax/avatax_use.rst:78
msgid ""
"After confirming a quotation and validating the delivery, "
"click :guilabel:`Create Invoice`. Indicate whether it is "
"a :guilabel:`Regular invoice`, :guilabel:`Down payment (percentage)`, "
"or :guilabel:`Down payment (fixed amount)`."
msgstr ""
"Setelah mengonfirmasi penawaran harga dan memvalidasi pengiriman, klik "
":guilabel:`Create Invoice`. Tunjukkan apakah itu :guilabel:`Regular "
"invoice`, :guilabel:`Down payment (percentage)`, atau :guilabel:`Down "
"payment (fixed amount)`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/taxes/avatax/avatax_use.rst:82
msgid ""
"Then click :guilabel:`Create and view invoice`. The recorded taxes can be "
"seen in the :guilabel:`Journal Items` tab of the invoice. There will be "
"different taxes depending on the location of the :guilabel:`Delivery "
"Address`."
msgstr ""
"Kemudian klik :guilabel:`Create and view invoice`. Pajak yang dicatat dapat "
"dilihat di tab :guilabel:`Journal Items` dari faktur. Akan ada pajak yang "
"berbeda tergantung pada lokasi :guilabel:`Delivery Address`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/taxes/avatax/avatax_use.rst:None
msgid "Journal items highlighted on a invoice in Odoo."
msgstr "Item jurnal yang disorot pada faktur di Odoo."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/taxes/avatax/avatax_use.rst:90
msgid ""
"Finally, press the :guilabel:`Confirm` button to complete the invoice and "
"synchronize with the AvaTax portal."
msgstr ""
"Terakhir, tekan tombol :guilabel:`Confirm` untuk menyelesaikan faktur dan "
"menyinkronkan dengan portal AvaTax."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/taxes/avatax/avatax_use.rst:94
msgid ""
"An invoice cannot be :guilabel:`Reset to draft` because this causes de-"
"synchronization with the AvaTax Portal. Instead, click :guilabel:`Add credit "
"note` and state: `Sync with AvaTax Portal`. See this "
"documentation: :doc:`../../../accounting/customer_invoices/credit_notes`."
msgstr ""
"Faktur tidak dapat :guilabel:`Reset to draft` karena ini menyebabkan de-"
"sinkronisasi dengan Portal AvaTax. Sebagai gantinya, klik :guilabel:`Add "
"credit note` dan nyatakan: `Sync with AvaTax Portal`. Lihat dokumentasi ini: "
":doc:`../../../accounting/customer_invoices/credit_notes`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/taxes/avatax/avatax_use.rst:99
msgid "Fixed price discounts"
msgstr "Diskon harga tetap"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/taxes/avatax/avatax_use.rst:101
msgid ""
"Add a fixed price discount to a valuable customer, by "
"clicking :guilabel:`Add a line` on the customer's invoice. Add the product "
"discount, and set the :guilabel:`Price` to either a positive or negative "
"value. To recalculate the taxes, click :guilabel:`Compute Taxes`."
msgstr ""
"Tambahkan diskon harga tetap kepada pelanggan berharga, dengan mengklik "
":guilabel:`Add a line` pada faktur pelanggan. Tambahkan diskon produk, dan "
"atur :guilabel:`Price` ke nilai positif atau negatif. Untuk menghitung ulang "
"pajak, klik :guilabel:`Compute Taxes`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/taxes/avatax/avatax_use.rst:106
msgid ""
"Tax calculation can even be done on negative subtotals and credit notes."
msgstr ""
"Perhitungan pajak bahkan dapat dilakukan pada subtotal negatif dan nota "
"kredit."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/taxes/avatax/avatax_use.rst:109
msgid "Logging"
msgstr "Logging"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/taxes/avatax/avatax_use.rst:111
msgid ""
"It is possible to log Avalara/*AvaTax* actions in Odoo for further analysis, "
"or verification of functionality. Logging is accessible through the *AvaTax* "
"settings."
msgstr ""
"Dimungkinkan untuk mencatat log tindakan Avalara/*AvaTax* di Odoo untuk "
"analisis lebih lanjut, atau verifikasi fungsionalitas. Logging dapat diakses "
"melalui pengaturan *AvaTax*."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/taxes/avatax/avatax_use.rst:114
msgid ""
"To start logging *AvaTax* actions, first, navigate to "
"the :menuselection:`Accounting app --> Configuration --> Settings`."
msgstr ""
"Untuk mulai mencatat log tindakan *AvaTax*, pertama, navigasikan ke "
":menuselection:`Accounting app --> Configuration --> Settings`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/taxes/avatax/avatax_use.rst:117
msgid ""
"Then, in the :guilabel:`Taxes` section, under the :guilabel:`AvaTax` "
"settings, click :guilabel:`Start logging for 30 minutes`."
msgstr ""
"Kemudian, di bagian :guilabel:`Taxes`, di bawah pengaturan "
":guilabel:`AvaTax`, klik :guilabel:`Start logging for 30 minutes`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/taxes/avatax/avatax_use.rst:120
msgid ""
"Upon starting the log process, Odoo will log all Avalara/*AvaTax* actions "
"performed in the database."
msgstr ""
"Setelah memulai proses log, Odoo akan mencatat semua tindakan Avalara/"
"*AvaTax* yang dilakukan di database."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/taxes/avatax/avatax_use.rst:122
msgid ""
"To view the logs, click on :guilabel:`Show logs` to the right of "
"the :guilabel:`Start logging for 30 minutes`. This reveals a detailed list "
"of Avalara/*AvaTax* actions. This list is sortable by the following columns:"
msgstr ""
"Untuk melihat log, klik :guilabel:`Show logs` di sebelah kanan "
":guilabel:`Start logging for 30 minutes`. Ini menampilkan daftar terperinci "
"dari tindakan Avalara/*AvaTax*. Daftar ini dapat diurutkan berdasarkan kolom "
"berikut:"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/taxes/avatax/avatax_use.rst:126
msgid ":guilabel:`Created on`: timestamp of the *AvaTax* calculation."
msgstr ":guilabel:`Created on`: timestamp perhitungan *AvaTax*."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/taxes/avatax/avatax_use.rst:127
msgid ":guilabel:`Created by`: numeric value of the user in the database."
msgstr ":guilabel:`Created by`: nilai numerik user di database."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/taxes/avatax/avatax_use.rst:128
msgid ":guilabel:`Database name`: name of the database."
msgstr ":guilabel:`Database name`: nama database."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/taxes/avatax/avatax_use.rst:129
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Type`: two values can be chosen for this "
"field, :guilabel:`Server` or :guilabel:`Client`."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Type`: dua nilai dapat dipilih untuk field ini, "
":guilabel:`Server` atau :guilabel:`Client`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/taxes/avatax/avatax_use.rst:131
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Name`: Avalara service name. In this case, it will be *AvaTax*."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Name`: nama layanan Avalara. Dalam hal ini, akan menjadi *AvaTax*."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/taxes/avatax/avatax_use.rst:132
msgid ":guilabel:`Level`: by default, this will be `INFO`."
msgstr ":guilabel:`Level`: secara default, ini akan menjadi `INFO`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/taxes/avatax/avatax_use.rst:133
msgid ":guilabel:`Path`: indicates the path taken to make the calculation."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Path`: menunjukkan jalur yang diambil untuk melakukan perhitungan."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/taxes/avatax/avatax_use.rst:134
msgid ":guilabel:`Line`: indicates the line the calculation is made on."
msgstr ":guilabel:`Line`: menunjukkan baris di mana perhitungan dilakukan."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/taxes/avatax/avatax_use.rst:135
msgid ":guilabel:`Function`: indicates the calculation taken on the line."
msgstr ":guilabel:`Function`: menunjukkan perhitungan yang diambil pada baris."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/taxes/avatax/avatax_use.rst:None
msgid "Avalara logging page with top row of list highlighted."
msgstr "Halaman logging Avalara dengan baris teratas dari daftar yang disorot."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/taxes/avatax/avatax_use.rst:141
msgid ""
"Click into the log line to reveal another field, called :guilabel:`Message`."
msgstr ""
"Klik ke baris log untuk menampilkan field lain, yang disebut "
":guilabel:`Message`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/taxes/avatax/avatax_use.rst:143
msgid ""
"This field populates a raw transcription of the transaction, which involves "
"the creation (or adjustment) of a sales invoice using the Avalara *AvaTax* "
"API."
msgstr ""
"Field ini mengisi transkripsi mentah dari transaksi, yang melibatkan "
"pembuatan (atau penyesuaian) faktur penjualan menggunakan API Avalara "
"*AvaTax*."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/taxes/avatax/avatax_use.rst:146
msgid ""
"The transaction includes details, such as addresses for shipping from and "
"to, line items describing the products or services, tax codes, tax amounts, "
"and other relevant information."
msgstr ""
"Transaksi mencakup detail seperti alamat pengiriman dari dan ke, item baris "
"yang menjelaskan produk atau layanan, kode pajak, jumlah pajak, dan "
"informasi relevan lainnya."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/taxes/avatax/avatax_use.rst:149
msgid ""
"The :guilabel:`Message` contains the calculated taxes for different "
"jurisdictions and confirms the creation (or adjustment) of the transaction."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Message` berisi pajak yang dihitung untuk berbagai yurisdiksi dan "
"mengonfirmasi pembuatan (atau penyesuaian) transaksi."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/taxes/avatax/avatax_use.rst:153
msgid ""
"Custom fields can be made using Odoo *Studio*. Click the :icon:`fa-ellipsis-"
"v` :guilabel:`(ellipsis)` menu to the far-right of the header row. Then "
"click :icon:`fa-plus` :guilabel:`Add custom field`. This action opens Odoo "
"*Studio*."
msgstr ""
"Field kustom dapat dibuat menggunakan Odoo *Studio*. Klik menu :icon:`fa-"
"ellipsis-v` :guilabel:`(ellipsis)` di ujung kanan baris header. Kemudian "
"klik :icon:`fa-plus` :guilabel:`Add custom field`. Tindakan ini membuka Odoo "
"*Studio*."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/taxes/avatax/avatax_use.rst:158
msgid ""
"Odoo *Studio* requires a *custom* pricing plan. Consult the database's "
"customer success manager for more information on switching plans. Or to see "
"if Odoo *Studio* is included in the database's current pricing plan. See "
"this documentation: :doc:`../../../../studio`."
msgstr ""
"Odoo *Studio* memerlukan paket harga *custom*. Konsultasikan dengan customer "
"success manager database untuk informasi lebih lanjut tentang mengganti "
"paket. Atau untuk melihat apakah Odoo *Studio* termasuk dalam paket harga "
"database saat ini. Lihat dokumentasi ini: :doc:`../../../../studio`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/taxes/avatax/avatax_use.rst:164
msgid ":doc:`avalara_portal`"
msgstr ":doc:`avalara_portal`"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/taxes/cash_basis.rst:3
msgid "Cash basis taxes"
msgstr "Pajak berbasis kas"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/taxes/cash_basis.rst:5
msgid ""
"Cash basis taxes are due when the payment is made, as opposed to standard "
"taxes that are due when the invoice is confirmed. Reporting your income and "
"expenses to the government based on the cash basis method is mandatory in "
"some countries and under some conditions."
msgstr ""
"Pajak berbasis kas jatuh tempo saat pembayaran dilakukan, berbeda dengan "
"pajak standar yang jatuh tempo saat faktur dikonfirmasi. Melaporkan "
"pendapatan dan pengeluaran Anda kepada pemerintah berdasarkan metode "
"berbasis kas adalah wajib di beberapa negara dan dalam kondisi tertentu."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/taxes/cash_basis.rst:10
msgid ""
"You sell a product in the 1st quarter of your fiscal year, and the payment "
"is received in the 2nd quarter. Based on the cash basis method, the tax you "
"must pay is for the 2nd quarter."
msgstr ""
"Anda menjual produk di kuartal pertama tahun fiskal Anda, dan pembayaran "
"diterima di kuartal kedua. Berdasarkan metode berbasis kas, pajak yang harus "
"Anda bayar adalah untuk kuartal kedua."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/taxes/cash_basis.rst:16
msgid ""
"Go to :menuselection:`Accounting --> Configuration --> Settings` and under "
"the :guilabel:`Taxes` section, enable :guilabel:`Cash Basis`."
msgstr ""
"Buka :menuselection:`Accounting --> Configuration --> Settings` dan di bawah "
"bagian :guilabel:`Taxes`, aktifkan :guilabel:`Cash Basis`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/taxes/cash_basis.rst:19
msgid ""
"Then, define the :guilabel:`Tax Cash Basis Journal`. Click on the external "
"link button next to the journal to update its default properties such as "
"the :guilabel:`Journal Name`, :guilabel:`Type` or :guilabel:`Short Code`."
msgstr ""
"Kemudian, tentukan :guilabel:`Jurnal Basis Kas Pajak`. Klik tombol tautan "
"eksternal di samping jurnal untuk memperbarui properti default seperti "
":guilabel:`Nama Jurnal`, :guilabel:`Tipe`, atau :guilabel:`Kode Singkat`."

