msgid "Tax computation"
msgstr "Perhitungan pajak"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/taxes/tax_computation.rst:10
msgid ""
"The :guilabel:`Tax Computation` field determines the relation between the "
"tax amount and the base the tax is based on. The following options are "
"available:"
msgstr ""
"Bidang :guilabel:`Perhitungan Pajak` menentukan hubungan antara jumlah pajak "
"dan dasar pajak. Opsi berikut tersedia:"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/taxes/tax_computation.rst:13
msgid ""
":ref:`Group of Taxes <taxes/computation/group-of-taxes>`: a combination of "
"several other taxes"
msgstr ""
":ref:`Grup Pajak <taxes/computation/group-of-taxes>`: kombinasi dari "
"beberapa pajak lainnya"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/taxes/tax_computation.rst:14
msgid ":ref:`Fixed <taxes/computation/fixed>`: a fixed amount"
msgstr ":ref:`Tetap <taxes/computation/fixed>`: jumlah tetap"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/taxes/tax_computation.rst:15
msgid ""
":ref:`Percentage of Price <taxes/computation/percentage-of-price>`: a "
"percentage of the tax-excluded sales price"
msgstr ""
":ref:`Persentase dari Harga <taxes/computation/percentage-of-price>`: "
"persentase dari harga penjualan tidak termasuk pajak"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/taxes/tax_computation.rst:17
msgid ""
":ref:`Percentage of Price Tax Included <taxes/computation/percentage-of-"
"price-tax-included>`: a percentage of the tax-included total"
msgstr ""
":ref:`Persentase dari Harga Termasuk Pajak <taxes/computation/percentage-of-"
"price-tax-included>`: persentase dari total termasuk pajak"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/taxes/tax_computation.rst:19
msgid ""
":ref:`Custom Formula <taxes/computation/python-code>`: a custom, user-"
"defined formula"
msgstr ""
":ref:`Formula Kustom <taxes/computation/python-code>`: formula khusus yang "
"ditentukan pengguna"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/taxes/tax_computation.rst:24
msgid "Group of taxes"
msgstr "Grup pajak"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/taxes/tax_computation.rst:26
msgid ""
"The tax is a combination of multiple sub-taxes. You can add as many taxes as "
"you want, in the order you want them to be applied."
msgstr ""
"Pajak adalah kombinasi dari beberapa sub-pajak. Anda dapat menambahkan "
"sebanyak mungkin pajak yang Anda inginkan, dalam urutan yang Anda inginkan "
"untuk diterapkan."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/taxes/tax_computation.rst:30
msgid ""
"Make sure the tax sequence is correct, as the display order determines the "
"application order and may affect tax computation, particularly if a "
"tax :ref:`affects the base of subsequent taxes <taxes/base-subsequent>`."
msgstr ""
"Pastikan urutan pajak benar, karena urutan tampilan menentukan urutan "
"penerapan dan dapat mempengaruhi perhitungan pajak, terutama jika pajak "
":ref:`mempengaruhi dasar pajak berikutnya <taxes/base-subsequent>`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/taxes/tax_computation.rst:37
msgid "Fixed"
msgstr "Tetap"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/taxes/tax_computation.rst:39
msgid ""
"The tax has a fixed amount in the default currency. The amount remains the "
"same per unit, regardless of the sales price."
msgstr ""
"Pajak memiliki jumlah tetap dalam mata uang default. Jumlahnya tetap sama "
"per unit, terlepas dari harga penjualan."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/taxes/tax_computation.rst:42
msgid ""
"The computation is :math:`\\text{tax amount} = \\text{fixed tax amount} "
"\\times \\text{quantity}`."
msgstr ""
"Perhitungannya adalah :math:`\\text{tax amount} = \\text{fixed tax amount} "
"\\times \\text{quantity}`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/taxes/tax_computation.rst:45
msgid ""
"A product has a sales price of $1000, and we apply a $10 :guilabel:`Fixed` "
"tax. We then have:"
msgstr ""
"Suatu produk memiliki harga jual $1000, dan kami menerapkan pajak "
":guilabel:`Tetap` sebesar $10. Maka kita memiliki:"

