"If :guilabel:`Included in Price` is :guilabel:`Tax Included`, the "
"computation is :math:`\\text{tax amount} = \\text{sales price} \\times "
"\\frac{\\text{tax rate}}{1 + \\text{tax rate}}`."
msgstr ""
"Jika :guilabel:`Termasuk dalam Harga` diatur ke :guilabel:`Termasuk Pajak`, "
"perhitungannya adalah :math:`\\text{tax amount} = \\text{sales price} \\t"
"imes \\frac{\\text{tax rate}}{1 + \\text{tax rate}}`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/taxes/tax_computation.rst:88
msgid ""
"A product has a sales price of $1000, and we apply a "
"10% :guilabel:`Percentage of Price` tax that is :guilabel:`Tax Included`. We "
"then have:"
msgstr ""
"Suatu produk memiliki harga jual $1000, dan kami menerapkan pajak "
":guilabel:`Persentase dari Harga` sebesar 10% yang :guilabel:`Termasuk "
"Pajak`. Maka kita memiliki:"

