#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/vendor_bills.rst:113
msgid "Bill confirmation"
msgstr "Konfirmasi tagihan"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/vendor_bills.rst:115
msgid ""
"Click :guilabel:`Confirm` when the document is completed. The status changes "
"to :guilabel:`Posted`, and a journal entry is generated based on the vendor "
"bill information. On confirmation, Odoo assigns each vendor bill a unique "
"number from a defined :doc:`sequence <vendor_bills/sequence>`."
msgstr ""
"Klik :guilabel:`Konfirmasi` ketika dokumen selesai. Status berubah menjadi "
":guilabel:`Diposting`, dan entri jurnal dibuat berdasarkan informasi tagihan "
"vendor. Saat konfirmasi, Odoo menetapkan setiap tagihan vendor nomor unik "
"dari :doc:`urutan <vendor_bills/sequence>` yang telah ditentukan."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/vendor_bills.rst:120
msgid ""
