"creation-manual>` maupun :ref:`secara otomatis <accounting/vendor_bills/"
"automatic>`. Saat membuat self-bill, pastikan untuk membuatnya langsung dari "
":ref:`jurnal pembelian self-billing <accounting/vendor_bills/self-billing-"
"config>` di :guilabel:`Accounting Dashboard` atau secara manual atur "
":guilabel:`Journal` dari self-bill ke jurnal pembelian self-billing."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/vendor_bills.rst:165
msgid ""
