#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/vendor_bills.rst:179
msgid ""
"If sending self-bills via :ref:`Peppol <accounting/e-invoicing/peppol>`, "
"first :ref:`configure your Peppol registration <accounting/e-invoicing/"
