"Jika mengirim self-bill via :ref:`Peppol <accounting/e-invoicing/peppol>`, "
"pertama :ref:`konfigurasikan pendaftaran Peppol Anda <accounting/e-invoicing/"
"peppol-registration>`, lalu verifikasi bahwa vendor terdaftar dengan Peppol. "
"Untuk melakukannya, buka :menuselection:`Accounting --> Vendors --> "
"Vendors`, kemudian lakukan :ref:`proses verifikasi kontak <accounting/e-"
"invoicing/contact-verification>`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/vendor_bills.rst:184
msgid ""
"Not every Peppol access point supports self-billing. Check with your "
"suppliers to ensure theirs does."
msgstr ""
"Tidak setiap access point Peppol mendukung self-billing. Periksa dengan "
