":doc:`direkonsiliasi <bank/reconciliation>` dan statusnya diperbarui menjadi "
":guilabel:`Dibayar`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/vendor_bills.rst:215
msgid "Aged payable report"
msgstr "Laporan utang jatuh tempo"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/vendor_bills.rst:217
msgid ""
"For an overview of the open vendor bills and their due dates, go "
"to :menuselection:`Accounting --> Reporting --> Aged payable`."
msgstr ""
"Untuk gambaran umum tentang tagihan vendor yang terbuka dan tanggal jatuh "
