"Dengan aturan penugasan di atas, setiap **Zenith Pro Computer** yang dibeli "
"akan ditetapkan faktor emisi **#1**, kecuali jika dibeli dari **Digital "
"Den**, yang akan ditetapkan faktor emisi **#2**."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/esg.rst:279
msgid "Apply retroactively"
msgstr "Terapkan secara retroaktif"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/esg.rst:281
msgid ""
"Once your emission factors are configured with assignation rules, you can "
"also apply them retroactively to past activity data."
msgstr ""
"Setelah faktor emisi Anda dikonfigurasi dengan aturan penugasan, Anda juga "
"dapat menerapkannya secara retroaktif ke data aktivitas masa lalu."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/esg.rst:284
msgid ""
"To do so, go to :menuselection:`ESG -->  Configuration --> Emission "
"Factors`, select an emission factor, and click :guilabel:`Assign`. Select "
"an :guilabel:`Application Period`, and, if desired, enable "
"the :guilabel:`Replace existing assignations` option."
msgstr ""
"Untuk melakukannya, buka :menuselection:`ESG --> Configuration --> Emission "
"Factors`, pilih faktor emisi, lalu klik :guilabel:`Assign`. Pilih "
":guilabel:`Application Period`, dan, jika diinginkan, aktifkan opsi "
":guilabel:`Replace existing assignations`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/esg.rst:289
msgid ""
"Apply emission factors in bulk by selecting multiple emission factors "
"in :icon:`oi-view-list` list view and clicking :icon:`fa-cog` "
"(:guilabel:`Actions`) :menuselection:`--> Assign Emission Factors`."
msgstr ""
"Terapkan faktor emisi secara massal dengan memilih beberapa faktor emisi "
"dalam tampilan daftar :icon:`oi-view-list` dan klik :icon:`fa-cog` "
"(:guilabel:`Actions`) :menuselection:`--> Assign Emission Factors`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/esg.rst:294
msgid "Sex parity and pay gap"
msgstr "Paritas jenis kelamin dan kesenjangan gaji"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/esg.rst:296
msgid ""
"Sex parity tracks the distribution of sexes across the workforce, such as "
"comparing women and men in technical vs. administrative roles, permanent vs. "
"temporary contracts, different office locations, or management vs. non-"
"management positions."
msgstr ""
"Paritas jenis kelamin melacak distribusi jenis kelamin di seluruh tenaga "
"kerja, seperti membandingkan perempuan dan laki-laki dalam peran teknis vs. "
"administratif, kontrak permanen vs. sementara, lokasi kantor yang berbeda, "
"atau posisi manajemen vs. non-manajemen."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/esg.rst:300
msgid ""
"These insights, based on employee data, are essential for CSRD reporting "
"under ESRS S1 and will also support future VSME standards."
msgstr ""
"Wawasan ini, berdasarkan data karyawan, sangat penting untuk pelaporan CSRD "
"di bawah ESRS S1 dan juga akan mendukung standar VSME di masa mendatang."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/esg.rst:303
msgid ""
"To view a company's sex parity and pay gap measures, set the sex of each "
"employee by opening the :guilabel:`Employees` app and selecting an employee. "
"Under the :guilabel:`Private Information` tab, select the "
"employee's :guilabel:`Gender`."
msgstr ""
"Untuk melihat ukuran paritas jenis kelamin dan kesenjangan gaji perusahaan, "
"tetapkan jenis kelamin setiap karyawan dengan membuka aplikasi "
":guilabel:`Karyawan` dan pilih karyawan. Di bawah tab :guilabel:`Private "
"Information`, pilih :guilabel:`Gender` karyawan."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/esg.rst:307
msgid ""
"The pay gap is calculated using the wages set on the employees' Payroll "
"contracts for the same jobs."
msgstr ""
"Kesenjangan gaji dihitung menggunakan upah yang ditetapkan pada kontrak "
"Payroll karyawan untuk pekerjaan yang sama."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/esg.rst:309
msgid "Pay gap formula"
msgstr "Rumus kesenjangan gaji"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/esg.rst:311
msgid ""
"((`Average male salary` – `Average female salary`) / `Average male salary`) "
"× `100`"
msgstr ""
"((`Rata-rata gaji laki-laki` – `Rata-rata gaji perempuan`) / `Rata-rata gaji "
"laki-laki`) × `100`"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/esg.rst:313
msgid ""
"Access the measures by clicking :menuselection:`ESG --> Measure --> Sex "
"Parity / Pay Gap`."
msgstr ""
"Akses ukuran dengan mengklik :menuselection:`ESG --> Measure --> Sex "
"Parity / Pay Gap`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/esg.rst:316
msgid ""
"Use the different :ref:`Group By <search/group>` options to break down the "
"data by :guilabel:`Leadership Level`, :guilabel:`Department`, :guilabel:`Job "
"Position`, :guilabel:`Contract Type`, or :guilabel:`Country`."
msgstr ""
"Gunakan berbagai opsi :ref:`Group By <search/group>` untuk memecah data "
"berdasarkan :guilabel:`Leadership Level`, :guilabel:`Departemen`, "
":guilabel:`Job Position`, :guilabel:`Contract Type`, atau "
":guilabel:`Country`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/esg.rst:0
msgid "The sex parity graph filtering options"
msgstr "Opsi pemfilteran grafik paritas jenis kelamin"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/esg.rst:324
msgid "Initiatives"
msgstr "Inisiatif-Inisiatif"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/esg.rst:326
msgid ""
"Go to :menuselection:`ESG --> Act --> Initiatives` to access all "
"the :doc:`Project <../services/project>` features, and start taking action "
"on your impact. You can estimate CO₂ savings for each task, track progress, "
"and assign team members with deadlines."
msgstr ""
"Buka :menuselection:`ESG --> Act --> Initiatives` untuk mengakses semua "
"fitur :doc:`Project <../services/project>`, dan mulai mengambil tindakan "
"terhadap dampak Anda. Anda dapat memperkirakan penghematan CO₂ untuk setiap "
"tugas, melacak kemajuan, dan menetapkan anggota tim dengan tenggat waktu."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/esg.rst:331
msgid ""
"Estimated CO₂ reductions do not immediately lower your carbon footprint. The "
"real impact shows only when these reductions are reflected in your "
"operations."
msgstr ""
"Pengurangan CO₂ yang diperkirakan tidak langsung menurunkan jejak karbon "
"Anda. Dampak nyata hanya terlihat ketika pengurangan ini tercermin dalam "
"operasi Anda."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/expenses/approve_expenses.rst:3
msgid "Process expenses"
msgstr "Proses pengeluaran"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/expenses/approve_expenses.rst:5
msgid ""
"Once expenses have been created and submitted, they must be processed by an "
"authorized database user. In Odoo, most users cannot process expenses; only "
"users with the necessary :doc:`access rights <../../general/users/"
"access_rights>` or permissions can. This means that a user **must** have at "
"least *Team Approver* rights for the **Expenses** app. Employees with the "
"necessary rights can review expenses, approve or refuse them, and provide "
"feedback with an integrated :ref:`refuse expense <expenses/refuse-report>` "
"communication tool."
msgstr ""
"Setelah pengeluaran dibuat dan diajukan, pengeluaran tersebut harus diproses "
"oleh user database yang berwenang. Di Odoo, sebagian besar user tidak dapat "
"memproses pengeluaran; hanya user dengan :doc:`hak akses <../../general/"
"users/access_rights>` atau izin yang diperlukan yang dapat melakukannya. Ini "
"berarti bahwa seorang user **harus** memiliki setidaknya hak *Team Approver* "
"untuk aplikasi **Pengeluaran**. Karyawan dengan hak yang diperlukan dapat "
"meninjau pengeluaran, menyetujui atau menolaknya, dan memberikan umpan balik "
"dengan alat komunikasi :ref:`tolak pengeluaran <expenses/refuse-report>` "
"yang terintegrasi."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/expenses/approve_expenses.rst:13
msgid "View expenses"
msgstr "Lihat pengeluaran"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/expenses/approve_expenses.rst:15
msgid ""
"Users who are able to process expenses (typically managers) can view all "
"expenses they have access rights for in the *Expenses to Process* dashboard. "
"To view the dashboard, navigate to :menuselection:`Expenses app --> My "
"Expenses --> Expenses to Process`."
msgstr ""
"User yang dapat memproses pengeluaran (biasanya manajer) dapat melihat semua "
"pengeluaran yang mereka miliki hak aksesnya di dashboard *Pengeluaran untuk "
"Diproses*. Untuk melihat dashboard, navigasi ke :menuselection:`Aplikasi "
"Pengeluaran --> Pengeluaran Saya --> Pengeluaran untuk Diproses`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/expenses/approve_expenses.rst:19
msgid ""
"A list of all expenses with a status of :guilabel:`Submit` appears, while "
"expenses with a status "
"of :guilabel:`Draft`, :guilabel:`Approved`, :guilabel:`Posted`, :guilabel:`In "
"Payment`, :guilabel:`Paid`, or :guilabel:`Refused` are hidden by default. To "
"view expenses with a different status, click the "
"corresponding :guilabel:`Status` button in the side panel."
msgstr ""
"Daftar semua pengeluaran dengan status :guilabel:`Submit` muncul, sementara "
"pengeluaran dengan status :guilabel:`Draft`, :guilabel:`Approved`, "
":guilabel:`Posted`, :guilabel:`In Payment`, :guilabel:`Paid`, atau "
":guilabel:`Refused` disembunyikan secara default. Untuk melihat pengeluaran "
"dengan status berbeda, klik tombol :guilabel:`Status` yang sesuai di panel "
"samping."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/expenses/approve_expenses.rst:None
msgid "Expenses to validate are found on the Expenses to Process dashboard."
msgstr ""
"Pengeluaran yang akan divalidasi ditemukan di dashboard Pengeluaran untuk "
"Diproses."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/expenses/approve_expenses.rst:28
msgid "Approve expenses"
msgstr "Setujui pengeluaran"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/expenses/approve_expenses.rst:30
msgid ""
"Expenses can be approved in two ways: :ref:`individually <expenses/"
"individual>` or :ref:`in bulk <expenses/multiple>`."
msgstr ""
"Pengeluaran dapat disetujui dengan dua cara: :ref:`secara individual "
"<expenses/individual>` atau :ref:`secara massal <expenses/multiple>`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/expenses/approve_expenses.rst:34
msgid "Only reports with a status of :guilabel:`Submitted` can be approved."
msgstr "Hanya laporan dengan status :guilabel:`Submitted` yang dapat disetujui."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/expenses/approve_expenses.rst:39
msgid "Approve individual expenses"
msgstr "Setujui pengeluaran individual"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/expenses/approve_expenses.rst:41
msgid ""
"To approve an individual expense, navigate to :menuselection:`Expenses app --"
"> My Expenses --> Expenses to Process`, and click on an individual expense "
"to view the details."
msgstr ""
"Untuk menyetujui pengeluaran individual, navigasi ke "
":menuselection:`Aplikasi Pengeluaran --> Pengeluaran Saya --> Pengeluaran "
"untuk Diproses`, dan klik pada pengeluaran individual untuk melihat "
"detailnya."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/expenses/approve_expenses.rst:44
msgid ""
"From here, several options are presented: :guilabel:`Post Journal "
"Entries`, :guilabel:`Report in Next "
"Payslip` :guilabel:`Approve`, :guilabel:`Refuse`, :guilabel:`Reset`, :guilabel:`Split "
"Expense`, and :guilabel:`Attach Receipt`. Click :guilabel:`Approve` to "
"approve the expense."
msgstr ""
"Dari sini, beberapa opsi ditampilkan: :guilabel:`Post Journal Entries`, "
":guilabel:`Report in Next Payslip` :guilabel:`Approve`, :guilabel:`Refuse`, "
":guilabel:`Reset`, :guilabel:`Split Expense`, dan :guilabel:`Attach "
"Receipt`. Klik :guilabel:`Approve` untuk menyetujui pengeluaran."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/expenses/approve_expenses.rst:0
msgid "An individual expense report that can be approved or refused."
msgstr "Laporan pengeluaran individual yang dapat disetujui atau ditolak."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/expenses/approve_expenses.rst:54
msgid "Approve multiple expenses"
msgstr "Setujui beberapa pengeluaran"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/expenses/approve_expenses.rst:56
msgid ""
"To approve multiple expenses at once, first navigate "
"to :menuselection:`Expenses app --> My Expenses --> Expenses to Process` to "
"view a list of all expenses waiting to be processed. Next, select the "
"expenses to approve by ticking the checkbox next to each expense being "
"approved, or tick the checkbox next to the :guilabel:`Employee` column title "
"to select all the expenses in the list."
msgstr ""
"Untuk menyetujui beberapa pengeluaran sekaligus, pertama navigasikan ke "
":menuselection:`Aplikasi Pengeluaran --> Pengeluaran Saya --> Pengeluaran "
"yang Harus Diproses` untuk melihat daftar semua pengeluaran yang menunggu "
"untuk diproses. Selanjutnya, pilih pengeluaran yang akan disetujui dengan "
"mencentang kotak centang di sebelah setiap pengeluaran yang disetujui, atau "
"centang kotak centang di sebelah judul kolom :guilabel:`Karyawan` untuk "
"memilih semua pengeluaran dalam daftar."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/expenses/approve_expenses.rst:61
msgid "Next, click the :guilabel:`Approve` button."
msgstr "Selanjutnya, klik tombol :guilabel:`Setujui`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/expenses/approve_expenses.rst:0
msgid "Select multiple expense reports at once."
msgstr "Pilih beberapa laporan pengeluaran sekaligus."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/expenses/approve_expenses.rst:67
msgid ""
"Team managers can view all the expenses for their team members only. While "
"on the :guilabel:`Expenses to Process` page, click the :icon:`fa-caret-"
"down` :guilabel:`(down arrow)` on the right-side of the search bar, then "
"click :guilabel:`My Team` in the :icon:`fa-filter` :guilabel:`Filters` "
"section. This presents all the expenses for only the manager's team."
msgstr ""
"Manajer tim dapat melihat semua pengeluaran untuk anggota tim mereka saja. "
"Saat berada di halaman :guilabel:`Pengeluaran yang Harus Diproses`, klik "
":icon:`fa-caret-down` :guilabel:`(panah bawah)` di sisi kanan bilah "
"pencarian, lalu klik :guilabel:`Tim Saya` di bagian :icon:`fa-filter` "
":guilabel:`Filter`. Ini menampilkan semua pengeluaran hanya untuk tim "
"manajer."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/expenses/approve_expenses.rst:75
msgid "Refuse expenses"
msgstr "Tolak pengeluaran"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/expenses/approve_expenses.rst:77
msgid ""
"Expenses can **only** be refused individually, and **not** from "
"the :guilabel:`Expenses to Process` dashboard. To refuse an individual "
"expense, navigate to :menuselection:`Expenses app --> My expenses --> "
"Expenses to Process`, then click on an individual expense to open the "
"detailed expense record."
msgstr ""
"Pengeluaran **hanya** dapat ditolak secara individual, dan **bukan** dari "
"dashboard :guilabel:`Pengeluaran yang Harus Diproses`. Untuk menolak "
"pengeluaran individual, navigasikan ke :menuselection:`Aplikasi "
"Pengeluaran --> Pengeluaran saya --> Pengeluaran yang Harus Diproses`, lalu "
"klik pada pengeluaran individual untuk membuka catatan pengeluaran yang "
"terperinci."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/expenses/approve_expenses.rst:81
msgid ""
"If more information is needed, such as a missing receipt, communicate any "
"necessary information requests in the *chatter* of the expense record. On "
"the individual expense, click either :guilabel:`Send message` "
"or :guilabel:`Log note` to open a message text box."
msgstr ""
"Jika diperlukan informasi lebih lanjut, seperti tanda terima yang hilang, "
"komunikasikan setiap permintaan informasi yang diperlukan di *chatter* "
"catatan pengeluaran. Pada pengeluaran individual, klik :guilabel:`Kirim "
"pesan` atau :guilabel:`Catat catatan` untuk membuka kotak teks pesan."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/expenses/approve_expenses.rst:85
msgid ""
"Type in a message, tagging the proper people, and post it to the *chatter* "
"by clicking :guilabel:`Send` or :guilabel:`Log`, depending on the method of "
"communication. The message is posted in the chatter, and the tagged people "
"are notified via email."
msgstr ""
"Ketik pesan, tandai orang yang tepat, dan posting ke *chatter* dengan "
"mengklik :guilabel:`Send` atau :guilabel:`Log`, tergantung pada metode "
"komunikasi. Pesan diposting di chatter, dan orang yang ditandai akan "
"diberitahu melalui email."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/expenses/approve_expenses.rst:90
msgid ""
"The only people that can be tagged in a message are *followers* of the "
"specific expense. To see who is a follower, click the :icon:`fa-user-"
"o` :guilabel:`(Show Followers)` icon to display the followers of the expense "
"report. Additional followers can be added by clicking the :icon:`fa-user-"
"o` :guilabel:`(Show Followers)` icon, then clicking :guilabel:`Add "
"Followers`."
msgstr ""
"Satu-satunya orang yang dapat ditandai dalam pesan adalah *pengikut* dari "
"pengeluaran spesifik tersebut. Untuk melihat siapa yang menjadi pengikut, "
"klik ikon :icon:`fa-user-o` :guilabel:`(Tampilkan Pengikut)` untuk "
"menampilkan pengikut laporan pengeluaran. Pengikut tambahan dapat "
"ditambahkan dengan mengklik ikon :icon:`fa-user-o` :guilabel:`(Tampilkan "
"Pengikut)`, lalu mengklik :guilabel:`Tambahkan Pengikut`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/expenses/approve_expenses.rst:0
msgid "Send messages in the chatter."
msgstr "Kirim pesan di chatter."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/expenses/approve_expenses.rst:98
msgid ""
"To refuse an expense, click :guilabel:`Refuse`, and a *Refuse Expense* pop-"
"up window loads. Enter a brief explanation for the refusal in "
"the :guilabel:`Reason` field, then click :guilabel:`Refuse`."
msgstr ""
"Untuk menolak pengeluaran, klik :guilabel:`Tolak`, dan jendela pop-up *Tolak "
"Pengeluaran* akan dimuat. Masukkan penjelasan singkat untuk penolakan di "
"bidang :guilabel:`Alasan`, lalu klik :guilabel:`Tolak`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/expenses/approve_expenses.rst:102
msgid ""
"A reason **must** be entered in the :guilabel:`Reason` field, or the expense "
"cannot be refused."
msgstr ""
"Alasan **harus** dimasukkan di bidang :guilabel:`Alasan`, atau pengeluaran "
"tidak dapat ditolak."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/expenses/approve_expenses.rst:107
msgid ""
"Once the expense is refused, the status changes to :guilabel:`Refused`, and "
"the only buttons that appear are :guilabel:`Add Receipt` "
"and :guilabel:`Reset`."
msgstr ""
"Setelah pengeluaran ditolak, status berubah menjadi :guilabel:`Ditolak`, dan "
"satu-satunya tombol yang muncul adalah :guilabel:`Tambahkan Tanda Terima` "
"dan :guilabel:`Atur Ulang`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/expenses/expense_cards.rst:3
msgid "Expense cards"
msgstr "Kartu pengeluaran"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/expenses/expense_cards.rst:5
msgid ""
"Odoo offers physical and virtual expense cards, allowing for better expense "
"tracking and management. Using expense cards allows for real time expense "
"management, creating expense records as soon as an expense transaction "
"occurs, allowing management greater visibility of expense costs as they are "
"incurred."
msgstr ""
"Odoo menawarkan kartu pengeluaran fisik dan virtual, memungkinkan pelacakan "
"dan pengelolaan pengeluaran yang lebih baik. Menggunakan kartu pengeluaran "
"memungkinkan pengelolaan pengeluaran secara real time, membuat catatan "
"pengeluaran segera setelah transaksi pengeluaran terjadi, memungkinkan "
"manajemen memiliki visibilitas yang lebih besar terhadap biaya pengeluaran "
"saat terjadi."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/expenses/expense_cards.rst:10
msgid ""
"The elimination of the need to :doc:`actively create expense records "
"<log_expenses>` allows for a more streamlined expense workflow, with records "
"automatically created as purchases are made."
msgstr ""
"Penghapusan kebutuhan untuk :doc:`membuat catatan pengeluaran secara aktif "
"<log_expenses>` memungkinkan alur kerja pengeluaran yang lebih efisien, "
"dengan catatan dibuat secara otomatis saat pembelian dilakukan."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/expenses/expense_cards.rst:13
msgid ""
"To use expense cards, first a :ref:`card is configured <expenses/card-"
"configure>`, then it is :ref:`activated <expenses/card-activate>`. Before "
"employees can make purchases with their expense card, a :ref:`Stripe account "
"must be created <expenses/create-stripe>` and configured, then :ref:`funds "
"must be added <expenses/add-funds>` to the company's Stripe account. Once "
"there is money available in the account (this typically takes 2-3 business "
"days for the transfer to Stripe), employees can use their expense cards, and "
"the money is pulled from the company's Stripe account."
msgstr ""
"Untuk menggunakan kartu pengeluaran, pertama :ref:`kartu dikonfigurasi "
"<expenses/card-configure>`, kemudian :ref:`diaktifkan <expenses/card-"
"activate>`. Sebelum karyawan dapat melakukan pembelian dengan kartu "
"pengeluaran mereka, :ref:`akun Stripe harus dibuat <expenses/create-stripe>` "
"dan dikonfigurasi, kemudian :ref:`dana harus ditambahkan <expenses/add-funds>"
"` ke akun Stripe perusahaan. Setelah ada uang tersedia di akun (biasanya "
"memerlukan waktu 2-3 hari kerja untuk transfer ke Stripe), karyawan dapat "
"menggunakan kartu pengeluaran mereka, dan uang ditarik dari akun Stripe "
"perusahaan."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/expenses/expense_cards.rst:21
msgid ""
"To create and use expense cards, both the **Accounting** and **Invoicing** "
"apps **must** be :ref:`installed <general/install>`."
msgstr ""
"Untuk membuat dan menggunakan kartu pengeluaran, aplikasi **Akuntansi** dan "
"**Penagihan** **harus** :ref:`diinstal <general/install>`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/expenses/expense_cards.rst:24
msgid ""
"To access confidential card data (card number and CVV for virtual cards; PIN "
"for physical cards), the employee **must** have a :doc:`user <../../general/"
"users>` profile. These details can **only** be accessed through that profile."
msgstr ""
"Untuk mengakses data kartu rahasia (nomor kartu dan CVV untuk kartu virtual; "
"PIN untuk kartu fisik), karyawan **harus** memiliki profil :doc:`user <../../"
"general/users>`. Rincian ini **hanya** dapat diakses melalui profil tersebut."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/expenses/expense_cards.rst:29
msgid ""
"Expense cards act like pre-paid debit cards, as they can **only** be used "
"with a connected Stripe account, and **only** if funds are added to that "
"account, to be drawn from."
msgstr ""
"Kartu pengeluaran berfungsi seperti kartu debit prabayar, karena hanya "
"**dapat** digunakan dengan akun Stripe yang terhubung, dan **hanya** jika "
"dana ditambahkan ke akun tersebut, untuk ditarik."

