#: ../../content/applications/finance/expenses/expense_cards.rst:52
msgid "Fees"
msgstr "Biaya"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/expenses/expense_cards.rst:54
msgid ""
"Odoo covers **all fees** associated with creating virtual and physical cards."
msgstr ""
"Odoo menanggung **semua biaya** yang terkait dengan pembuatan kartu virtual "
"dan fisik."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/expenses/expense_cards.rst:61
msgid ""
"Two settings must be configured to use expense cards. Navigate "
"to :menuselection:`Expenses app --> Configuration --> Settings`. Tick the "
"box next to :guilabel:`Expense Card`, then click :guilabel:`Save`. "
"The :guilabel:`Settings` page reloads, and two fields now appear beneath "
"the :guilabel:`Expense Card` option."
msgstr ""
"Dua pengaturan harus dikonfigurasi untuk menggunakan kartu pengeluaran. "
"Navigasikan ke :menuselection:`Expenses app --> Configuration --> Settings`. "
"Centang kotak di sebelah :guilabel:`Expense Card`, kemudian klik "
":guilabel:`Save`. Halaman :guilabel:`Settings` dimuat ulang, dan dua bidang "
"sekarang muncul di bawah opsi :guilabel:`Expense Card`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/expenses/expense_cards.rst:66
msgid ""
"A :guilabel:`Journal` field with :guilabel:`Stripe Issuing` appears, "
"populating the field. This is the default journal, and it is **not** "
"recommended to alter this unless instructed by the accounting department."
msgstr ""
"Bidang :guilabel:`Journal` dengan :guilabel:`Stripe Issuing` muncul, mengisi "
"bidang tersebut. Ini adalah jurnal default, dan **tidak** disarankan untuk "
"mengubahnya kecuali diinstruksikan oleh departemen akuntansi."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/expenses/expense_cards.rst:70
msgid ""
"Next, click the text link :guilabel:`terms and conditions` and "
"an :guilabel:`Expense Cards Terms and Conditions` pop-up window loads, with "
"all the details of the agreement. After this has been read, "
"click :guilabel:`Close`, then tick the checkbox next to :guilabel:`I confirm "
"agreeing to the terms and conditions` to accept the terms, then "
"click :guilabel:`Save`."
msgstr ""
"Selanjutnya, klik tautan teks :guilabel:`terms and conditions` dan jendela "
"pop-up :guilabel:`Expense Cards Terms and Conditions` dimuat, dengan semua "
"detail perjanjian. Setelah ini dibaca, klik :guilabel:`Close`, kemudian "
"centang kotak di sebelah :guilabel:`I confirm agreeing to the terms and "
"conditions` untuk menerima persyaratan, kemudian klik :guilabel:`Save`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/expenses/expense_cards.rst:76
msgid "The terms and conditions **must** be agreed to use expense cards."
msgstr ""
"Syarat dan ketentuan **harus** disetujui untuk menggunakan kartu pengeluaran."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/expenses/expense_cards.rst:78
msgid ""
"After agreeing to the terms and conditions, :ref:`create a Stripe connected "
"account <expenses/create-stripe>`."
msgstr ""
"Setelah menyetujui syarat dan ketentuan, :ref:`buat akun terhubung Stripe "
"<expenses/create-stripe>`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/expenses/expense_cards.rst:84
msgid "Create Stripe connected account"
msgstr "Buat akun terhubung Stripe"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/expenses/expense_cards.rst:86
msgid ""
"To create a Stripe connected account, open the **Expenses** app, and ensure "
"the :guilabel:`Expense Card` option is enabled. Next, click :icon:`oi-arrow-"
"right` :guilabel:`Connect` to create a new Stripe Issuing connect account."
msgstr ""
"Untuk membuat akun terhubung Stripe, buka aplikasi **Karyawan**, dan "
"pastikan opsi :guilabel:`Expense Card` diaktifkan. Selanjutnya, klik "
":icon:`oi-arrow-right` :guilabel:`Connect` untuk membuat akun koneksi Stripe "
"Issuing baru."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/expenses/expense_cards.rst:90
msgid ""
"Fill in the KYC questionnaire provided by Stripe. Stripe takes +/-24 hours "
"to approve or refuse account creation requests."
msgstr ""
"Isi kuesioner KYC yang disediakan oleh Stripe. Stripe memerlukan waktu "
"sekitar 24 jam untuk menyetujui atau menolak permintaan pembuatan akun."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/expenses/expense_cards.rst:93
msgid ""
"A green :guilabel:`Verified` tag now appears next to :icon:`oi-arrow-"
"left` :guilabel:`Refresh`, indicating the account is properly configured."
msgstr ""
"Tag hijau :guilabel:`Verified` sekarang muncul di sebelah :icon:`oi-arrow-"
"left` :guilabel:`Refresh`, menunjukkan akun telah dikonfigurasi dengan benar."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/expenses/expense_cards.rst:96
msgid ""
"Once the account is verified, the company must :ref:`add funds <expenses/add-"
"funds>` to their Stripe balance."
msgstr ""
"Setelah akun terverifikasi, perusahaan harus :ref:`menambahkan dana "
"<expenses/add-funds>` ke saldo Stripe mereka."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/expenses/expense_cards.rst:102
msgid "Add funds to Stripe account"
msgstr "Tambahkan dana ke akun Stripe"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/expenses/expense_cards.rst:104
msgid ""
"For employees to use their expense cards, funds must be available in the "
"company's Stripe account, to make purchases against. To add funds to the "
"company's Stripe account, open the **Accounting** app. On "
"the :guilabel:`Stripe Issuing` Kanban card, click :guilabel:`Top-up`, and "
"a :guilabel:`Top-up` pop-up window loads."
msgstr ""
"Agar karyawan dapat menggunakan kartu pengeluaran mereka, dana harus "
"tersedia di akun Stripe perusahaan untuk melakukan pembelian. Untuk "
"menambahkan dana ke akun Stripe perusahaan, buka aplikasi **Akuntansi**. "
"Pada kartu Kanban :guilabel:`Stripe Issuing`, klik :guilabel:`Top-up`, dan "
"jendela pop-up :guilabel:`Top-up` akan muncul."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/expenses/expense_cards.rst:109
msgid ""
"Enter the amount being transferred into the account in "
"the :guilabel:`Amount` field. The :guilabel:`IBAN` and :guilabel:`BIC` "
"fields are populated according to the Stripe configuration and cannot be "
"changed. When configured, click :guilabel:`Topup`, and the transfer is "
"initiated."
msgstr ""
"Masukkan jumlah yang akan ditransfer ke akun di kolom :guilabel:`Amount`. "
"Kolom :guilabel:`IBAN` dan :guilabel:`BIC` diisi sesuai dengan konfigurasi "
"Stripe dan tidak dapat diubah. Setelah dikonfigurasi, klik "
":guilabel:`Topup`, dan transfer akan dimulai."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/expenses/expense_cards.rst:114
msgid ""
"The user wires money to the IBAN shown using a SEPA Credit Transfer (for the "
"EURO Zone). The Stripe issuing partner bank is `Circle Bank`."
msgstr ""
"User mentransfer uang ke IBAN yang ditampilkan menggunakan SEPA Credit "
"Transfer (untuk Zona EURO). Bank mitra penerbit Stripe adalah `Circle Bank`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/expenses/expense_cards.rst:118
msgid ""
"It typically takes 2-3 business days for transfers to be processed. Funds "
"are **not** available until the transfer is complete."
msgstr ""
"Biasanya membutuhkan waktu 2-3 hari kerja untuk pemrosesan transfer. Dana "
"**tidak** tersedia hingga transfer selesai."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/expenses/expense_cards.rst:124
msgid "Configure expense cards"
msgstr "Konfigurasi kartu pengeluaran"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/expenses/expense_cards.rst:126
msgid ""
"To create and configure a new expense card, click :menuselection:`Cards` in "
"the main **Expenses** app menu to view the :guilabel:`Cards` dashboard. "
"Click :guilabel:`New` and a blank :guilabel:`Cards` form loads. Enter the "
"following information on the form:"
msgstr ""
"Untuk membuat dan mengonfigurasi kartu pengeluaran baru, klik "
":menuselection:`Cards` di menu utama aplikasi **Pengeluaran** untuk melihat "
"dashboard :guilabel:`Cards`. Klik :guilabel:`New` dan formulir "
":guilabel:`Cards` kosong akan muncul. Masukkan informasi berikut pada "
"formulir:"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/expenses/expense_cards.rst:130
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Card Name`: The first line on the card form is blank, and "
"displays `Draft`. Enter a name for the card in this field. This does **not** "
"need to be a person's name, it can be something descriptive to explain the "
"use of the card."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Card Name`: Baris pertama pada formulir kartu kosong, dan "
"menampilkan `Draft`. Masukkan nama untuk kartu di kolom ini. Ini **tidak** "
"harus berupa nama seseorang, bisa berupa sesuatu yang deskriptif untuk "
"menjelaskan penggunaan kartu."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/expenses/expense_cards.rst:135
msgid ""
"An employee is going on a week-long business trip to Berlin to visit many "
"clients. The employee needs to pay for meals, transportation, and other "
"business-related expenses. Since this is a short trip, a virtual card is "
"created to capture all the expenses, with the name `Business Trip - Berlin`."
msgstr ""
"Seorang karyawan akan melakukan perjalanan bisnis selama seminggu ke Berlin "
"untuk mengunjungi banyak klien. Karyawan tersebut perlu membayar untuk "
"makanan, transportasi, dan pengeluaran terkait bisnis lainnya. Karena ini "
"adalah perjalanan singkat, kartu virtual dibuat untuk mencatat semua "
"pengeluaran, dengan nama `Business Trip - Berlin`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/expenses/expense_cards.rst:140
msgid ""
"The marketing department pays for many expenses throughout the year, from "
"email marketing services, venue rentals for events, promotional merchandise, "
"etc. Since the expenses do not have an end date, and it is used for an "
"entire department, a physical card is ordered with the name `Marketing`."
msgstr ""
"Departemen pemasaran membayar banyak pengeluaran sepanjang tahun, dari "
"layanan email marketing, sewa venue untuk acara, merchandise promosi, dll. "
"Karena pengeluaran tidak memiliki tanggal berakhir, dan digunakan untuk "
"seluruh departemen, kartu fisik dipesan dengan nama `Marketing`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/expenses/expense_cards.rst:145
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Cardholder`: Select the person using the card from the drop-down "
"menu. Once selected, the person's name populates the :guilabel:`Draft` "
"field, above :guilabel:`Cardholder`."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Cardholder`: Pilih orang yang menggunakan kartu dari menu drop-"
"down. Setelah dipilih, nama orang tersebut akan mengisi kolom "
":guilabel:`Draft`, di atas :guilabel:`Cardholder`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/expenses/expense_cards.rst:147
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Update info`: Next to the cardholder's name, "
"click :guilabel:`Update info` and a :guilabel:`Cardholder Configuration` pop-"
"up window loads. Update the cardholder's name, birthday, phone number, "
"email, and physical address. All the requested information **must** be "
"populated, as it is used to create the expense card with Stripe, and to "
"verify the cardholder's identity, when needed. If any information is missing "
"from this form, the card **cannot** be created, and an error appears when "
"creating or ordering the card."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Update info`: Di samping nama pemegang kartu, klik "
":guilabel:`Update info` dan jendela pop-up :guilabel:`Cardholder "
"Configuration` akan muncul. Perbarui nama pemegang kartu, tanggal lahir, "
"nomor telepon, email, dan alamat fisik. Semua informasi yang diminta "
"**harus** diisi, karena digunakan untuk membuat kartu pengeluaran dengan "
"Stripe, dan untuk memverifikasi identitas pemegang kartu, jika diperlukan. "
"Jika ada informasi yang hilang dari formulir ini, kartu **tidak dapat** "
"dibuat, dan kesalahan akan muncul saat membuat atau memesan kartu."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/expenses/expense_cards.rst:155
msgid ""
"The phone number listed is used for two-factor authentication. The phone "
"number can be changed in the future. When changing the phone number, an "
"alert is sent to the original phone number, notifying them of the change."
msgstr ""
"Nomor telepon yang tercantum digunakan untuk autentikasi dua faktor. Nomor "
"telepon dapat diubah di masa mendatang. Saat mengubah nomor telepon, "
"pemberitahuan akan dikirim ke nomor telepon asli, memberitahukan mereka "
"tentang perubahan tersebut."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/expenses/expense_cards.rst:159
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Type`: Click the radio button next to the desired *type* of "
"expense card. Options are:"
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Type`: Klik tombol radio di samping *jenis* kartu pengeluaran "
"yang diinginkan. Pilihannya adalah:"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/expenses/expense_cards.rst:161
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Physical`: A physical card is printed and mailed out to the "
"employee. If selected, a :guilabel:`Delivery Address` field appears. Using "
"the drop-down menu, select the employee or company address the card is "
"mailed to."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Physical`: Kartu fisik dicetak dan dikirimkan ke karyawan. Jika "
"dipilih, kolom :guilabel:`Delivery Address` akan muncul. Menggunakan menu "
"drop-down, pilih alamat karyawan atau perusahaan tempat kartu dikirimkan."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/expenses/expense_cards.rst:164
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Virtual`: Virtual cards are available instantaneously once the "
"card configuration is completed and the card is activated."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Virtual`: Kartu virtual tersedia secara instan setelah "
"konfigurasi kartu selesai dan kartu diaktifkan."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/expenses/expense_cards.rst:167
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Company`: Select the company the expenses are associated with "
"using the drop-down menu. Each card must be associated with a single "
"company, and are **not** available for use between all companies or branches "
"in the database. Ensure the selected company has its own Stripe Connect "
"account configured, or the expense cards will not work."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Company`: Pilih perusahaan yang terkait dengan pengeluaran "
"menggunakan menu drop-down. Setiap kartu harus dikaitkan dengan satu "
"perusahaan, dan **tidak** tersedia untuk digunakan di semua perusahaan atau "
"cabang dalam database. Pastikan perusahaan yang dipilih memiliki akun Stripe "
"Connect sendiri yang dikonfigurasi, atau kartu pengeluaran tidak akan "
"berfungsi."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/expenses/expense_cards.rst:171
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Stripe Journal`: :guilabel:`Stripe Issuing` populates this field "
"by default, and cannot be modified."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Stripe Journal`: :guilabel:`Stripe Issuing` mengisi kolom ini "
"secara default, dan tidak dapat diubah."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/expenses/expense_cards.rst:174
msgid ""
"Next, configure the following fields in the :guilabel:`Spending Policy` tab "
"of the card form:"
msgstr ""
"Selanjutnya, konfigurasikan kolom berikut di tab :guilabel:`Spending Policy` "
"pada formulir kartu:"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/expenses/expense_cards.rst:176
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Countries`: Using the drop-down menu, select the countries the "
"card is able to be used in. The company's country location populates this "
"field, by default. All other countries the employee may travel to or "
"purchase expensable items from, should be included in this list."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Negara`: Menggunakan menu drop-down, pilih negara tempat kartu "
"dapat digunakan. Lokasi negara perusahaan mengisi bidang ini secara default. "
"Semua negara lain yang mungkin dikunjungi karyawan atau tempat pembelian "
"barang yang dapat diklaim, harus disertakan dalam daftar ini."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/expenses/expense_cards.rst:179
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Categories`: If the expense card is limited to purchase items "
"within a specific *category*, select them using the drop-down menu. If this "
"field is left blank, the card may be used for *any* expense category."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Kategori`: Jika kartu pengeluaran dibatasi untuk membeli barang "
"dalam *kategori* tertentu, pilih menggunakan menu drop-down. Jika bidang ini "
"dibiarkan kosong, kartu dapat digunakan untuk kategori pengeluaran *apa pun*."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/expenses/expense_cards.rst:183
msgid ""
"Odoo is able to categorize transactions based on the :abbr:`MCC (Merchant "
"Category Code)` provided by the card network provider (such as Mastercard). "
"Every merchant has a corresponding :abbr:`MCC (Merchant Category Code)` that "
"identifies their business and product types. When a Stripe-issued card is "
"used, the :abbr:`MCC (Merchant Category Code)` is sent with the transaction, "
"allowing Stripe to approve or block it based on the card's configuration."
msgstr ""
"Odoo dapat mengkategorikan transaksi berdasarkan :abbr:`MCC (Kode Kategori "
"Pedagang)` yang disediakan oleh penyedia jaringan kartu (seperti Mastercard)"
". Setiap pedagang memiliki :abbr:`MCC (Kode Kategori Pedagang)` yang sesuai "
"yang mengidentifikasi bisnis dan jenis produk mereka. Ketika kartu yang "
"diterbitkan Stripe digunakan, :abbr:`MCC (Kode Kategori Pedagang)` dikirim "
"bersama transaksi, memungkinkan Stripe untuk menyetujui atau memblokirnya "
"berdasarkan konfigurasi kartu."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/expenses/expense_cards.rst:190
msgid ""
"A company issues an expense card that is only authorized for airline, train, "
"and taxi travel expenses."
msgstr ""
"Sebuah perusahaan menerbitkan kartu pengeluaran yang hanya diotorisasi untuk "
"pengeluaran perjalanan pesawat, kereta, dan taksi."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/expenses/expense_cards.rst:193
msgid ""
"To configure this, click into the :guilabel:`Category` field, and "
"click :guilabel:`Search more...` at the bottom. In the :guilabel:`Search: "
"Categories` pop-up window, click into the search bar and "
"click :guilabel:`Transportation services` in the :icon:`fa-"
"filter` :guilabel:`Filters` column."
msgstr ""
"Untuk mengonfigurasi ini, klik ke bidang :guilabel:`Kategori`, dan klik "
":guilabel:`Cari lebih banyak...` di bagian bawah. Di jendela pop-up "
":guilabel:`Cari: Kategori`, klik ke bilah pencarian dan klik "
":guilabel:`Layanan transportasi` di kolom :icon:`fa-filter` "
":guilabel:`Filter`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/expenses/expense_cards.rst:198
msgid ""
"Next, tick the checkboxes next to the desired transportation categories. In "
"this example, only :guilabel:`Railroads`, :guilabel:`Passenger "
"Railways`, :guilabel:`Taxicabs Limousines`, and :guilabel:`Airlines Air "
"Carriers` are selected."
msgstr ""
"Selanjutnya, centang kotak centang di samping kategori transportasi yang "
"diinginkan. Dalam contoh ini, hanya :guilabel:`Kereta api`, "
":guilabel:`Kereta api penumpang`, :guilabel:`Taksi limusin`, dan "
":guilabel:`Maskapai penerbangan` yang dipilih."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/expenses/expense_cards.rst:202
msgid ""
"Click :guilabel:`Select` and the selected transportation categories now "
"populate the :guilabel:`Categories` field."
msgstr ""
"Klik :guilabel:`Pilih` dan kategori transportasi yang dipilih sekarang "
"mengisi bidang :guilabel:`Kategori`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/expenses/expense_cards.rst:205
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Limit`: Configure the two spending limits for the card. The first "
"configuration sets the total expense amount allowed during a specific time "
"period. Using the drop-down menu after the word :guilabel:`per`, select the "
"time period the limit applies to. The available options "
"are: :guilabel:`Day`, :guilabel:`Week`, :guilabel:`Month`, :guilabel:`Year`, "
"or :guilabel:`All Time`. Next, enter the maximum amount allowed for the "
"selected time period."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Batas`: Konfigurasikan dua batas pengeluaran untuk kartu. "
"Konfigurasi pertama menetapkan jumlah pengeluaran total yang diizinkan "
"selama periode waktu tertentu. Menggunakan menu drop-down setelah kata "
":guilabel:`per`, pilih periode waktu yang berlaku untuk batas tersebut. Opsi "
"yang tersedia adalah: :guilabel:`Hari`, :guilabel:`Minggu`, "
":guilabel:`Bulan`, :guilabel:`Tahun`, atau :guilabel:`Sepanjang Waktu`. "
"Selanjutnya, masukkan jumlah maksimum yang diizinkan untuk periode waktu "
"yang dipilih."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/expenses/expense_cards.rst:211
msgid ""
"Next, set the *per transaction* limit. Enter the maximum amount that can be "
"charged on the expense card in a single transaction in the field."
msgstr ""
"Selanjutnya, tetapkan batas *per transaksi*. Masukkan jumlah maksimum yang "
"dapat dibebankan pada kartu pengeluaran dalam satu transaksi di bidang "
"tersebut."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/expenses/expense_cards.rst:215
msgid ""
"A company allows employees to purchase airline tickets that are less than "
"$1,000.00 total. Additionally, there is a monthly cap of $3,000.00 for all "
"expenses."
msgstr ""
"Sebuah perusahaan mengizinkan karyawan untuk membeli tiket pesawat yang "
"kurang dari $1.000,00 total. Selain itu, ada batas maksimal bulanan sebesar "
"$3.000,00 untuk semua pengeluaran."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/expenses/expense_cards.rst:218
msgid ""
"The company would configure the limit as follows: `3,000.00` "
"per :guilabel:`Month` and `1,000.00` per transaction."
msgstr ""
"Perusahaan akan mengonfigurasi batas sebagai berikut: `3.000,00` per "
":guilabel:`Bulan` dan `1.000,00` per transaksi."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/expenses/expense_cards.rst:222
msgid ""
"Card limits can be modified at any point. Once modified, they immediately go "
"into effect."
msgstr ""
"Batas kartu dapat dimodifikasi kapan saja. Setelah dimodifikasi, batas "
"tersebut langsung berlaku."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/expenses/expense_cards.rst:225
msgid ""
"All expense cards pull payments from a single Stripe account. It is "
"recommended to set card limits to avoid large charges or transactions that "
"may prematurely deplete the expense Stripe account."
msgstr ""
"Semua kartu pengeluaran menarik pembayaran dari satu akun Stripe. Disarankan "
"untuk menetapkan batas kartu untuk menghindari biaya besar atau transaksi "
"yang mungkin menguras akun Stripe pengeluaran secara prematur."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/expenses/expense_cards.rst:None
msgid "An expense card form filled out for transportation and food only."
msgstr ""
"Formulir kartu pengeluaran yang diisi hanya untuk transportasi dan makanan."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/expenses/expense_cards.rst:235
msgid "Activate expense cards"
msgstr "Aktifkan kartu pengeluaran"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/expenses/expense_cards.rst:237
msgid ""
"Once an expense card is configured, the next step is to activate the cards. "
"First, navigate to :menuselection:`Expenses app --> Cards`, and "
"the :guilabel:`Cards` dashboard loads, displaying all expense cards in a "
"Kanban view."
msgstr ""
"Setelah kartu pengeluaran dikonfigurasi, langkah selanjutnya adalah "
"mengaktifkan kartu. Pertama, navigasikan ke :menuselection:`Aplikasi "
"Pengeluaran --> Kartu`, dan dashboard :guilabel:`Kartu` dimuat, menampilkan "
"semua kartu pengeluaran dalam tampilan Kanban."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/expenses/expense_cards.rst:241
msgid ""
"All cards display their status on a banner in the upper-right corner of each "
"card. Statuses are either:"
msgstr ""
"Semua kartu menampilkan statusnya pada banner di sudut kanan atas setiap "
"kartu. Status bisa:"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/expenses/expense_cards.rst:244
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Draft`: The card form is filled out, but the card has not been "
"requested or activated."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Konsep`: Formulir kartu telah diisi, tetapi kartu belum diminta "
"atau diaktifkan."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/expenses/expense_cards.rst:245
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Pending`: A physical card has been ordered, but not activated."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Tertunda`: Kartu fisik telah dipesan, tetapi belum diaktifkan."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/expenses/expense_cards.rst:246
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Active`: The card is able to be used. This status does **not** "
"display a status banner on the card."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Aktif`: Kartu dapat digunakan. Status ini **tidak** menampilkan "
"banner status pada kartu."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/expenses/expense_cards.rst:248
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Paused`: A card has been put *on hold* and no transactions can be "
"processed with this status."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Ditunda`: Kartu telah *ditahan* dan tidak ada transaksi yang "
"dapat diproses dengan status ini."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/expenses/expense_cards.rst:250
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Blocked`: The physical or virtual card is *cancelled* and cannot "
"be used."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Diblokir`: Kartu fisik atau virtual *dibatalkan* dan tidak dapat "
"digunakan."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/expenses/expense_cards.rst:252
msgid ""
"Click on a card to activate, and the card form loads. Ensure all the fields "
"are :ref:`configured <expenses/card-configure>`, then click "
"either :guilabel:`Order` if requesting a physical card, "
"or :guilabel:`Activate` if creating a virtual card."
msgstr ""
"Klik pada kartu untuk mengaktifkan, dan formulir kartu akan dimuat. Pastikan "
"semua kolom telah :ref:`dikonfigurasi <expenses/card-configure>`, lalu klik "
":guilabel:`Pesan` jika meminta kartu fisik, atau :guilabel:`Aktifkan` jika "
"membuat kartu virtual."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/expenses/expense_cards.rst:257
msgid ""
"Physical cards take 5 to 10 business days to be delivered. Once ordered, "
"delivery information is added to the chatter, and the user who placed the "
"card order receives the information by email."
msgstr ""
"Kartu fisik membutuhkan waktu 5 hingga 10 hari kerja untuk dikirimkan. "
"Setelah dipesan, informasi pengiriman ditambahkan ke chatter, dan user yang "
"memesan kartu menerima informasi tersebut melalui email."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/expenses/expense_cards.rst:260
msgid ""
"If a physical card is requested, the card status changes "
"to :guilabel:`Inactive`, while it is being printed and mailed to the "
"selected address. Once the card arrives, follow the included instructions to "
"activate the card."
msgstr ""
"Jika kartu fisik diminta, status kartu berubah menjadi :guilabel:`Tidak "
"Aktif`, sementara kartu sedang dicetak dan dikirimkan ke alamat yang "
"dipilih. Setelah kartu tiba, ikuti instruksi yang disertakan untuk "
"mengaktifkan kartu."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/expenses/expense_cards.rst:264
msgid ""
"If the card is a virtual card, once :guilabel:`Activate` is clicked, the "
"status changes to :guilabel:`Active` and it is available for use."
msgstr ""
"Jika kartu adalah kartu virtual, setelah :guilabel:`Aktifkan` diklik, status "
"berubah menjadi :guilabel:`Aktif` dan dapat digunakan."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/expenses/expense_cards.rst:267
msgid ""
"Once the status of an expense card is :guilabel:`Active`, the user can use "
"the card to purchase expensable items, as long as the purchases are within "
"the limits set on the card."
msgstr ""
"Setelah status kartu pengeluaran menjadi :guilabel:`Aktif`, user dapat "
"menggunakan kartu untuk membeli item yang dapat ditagih sebagai pengeluaran, "
"selama pembelian berada dalam batas yang ditetapkan pada kartu."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/expenses/expense_cards.rst:271
msgid "Demo expense card"
msgstr "Kartu pengeluaran demo"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/expenses/expense_cards.rst:273
msgid ""
"To test the expense card feature without using a live Stripe "
"account, :ref:`install <general/install>` the `Expense Cards: Demo` module. "
"This replaces production functionalities and allows for the creation of a "
"demo Stripe account, using virtual cards and fake funds to simulate "
"transactions."
msgstr ""
"Untuk menguji fitur kartu pengeluaran tanpa menggunakan akun Stripe aktif, "
":ref:`instal <general/install>` modul `Expense Cards: Demo`. Ini "
"menggantikan fungsionalitas produksi dan memungkinkan pembuatan akun Stripe "
"demo, menggunakan kartu virtual dan dana palsu untuk mensimulasikan "
"transaksi."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/expenses/expense_cards.rst:279
msgid ""
"If a production account is already configured, **do not use** the demo "
"module, as it overwrites the existing setup."
msgstr ""
"Jika akun produksi sudah dikonfigurasi, **jangan gunakan** modul demo, "
"karena akan menimpa pengaturan yang ada."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/expenses/expense_cards.rst:283
msgid "Using expense cards"
msgstr "Menggunakan kartu pengeluaran"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/expenses/expense_cards.rst:285
msgid ""
"Using an expense card is almost identical to using any other credit or debit "
"card. The only difference is if a :ref:`physical card <expenses/physical>` "
"or a :ref:`virtual card <expenses/virtual>` is used."
msgstr ""
"Menggunakan kartu pengeluaran hampir identik dengan menggunakan kartu kredit "
"atau debit lainnya. Satu-satunya perbedaan adalah apakah :ref:`kartu fisik "
"<expenses/physical>` atau :ref:`kartu virtual <expenses/virtual>` yang "
"digunakan."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/expenses/expense_cards.rst:289
msgid ""
"When a charge is made using an expense card, an expense record is "
"automatically created in the **Expenses** app, linked to the specific card. "
"The next step is to attach the corresponding receipt."
msgstr ""
"Ketika biaya dibebankan menggunakan kartu pengeluaran, catatan pengeluaran "
"secara otomatis dibuat di aplikasi **Pengeluaran**, terhubung ke kartu "
"tertentu. Langkah selanjutnya adalah melampirkan tanda terima yang sesuai."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/expenses/expense_cards.rst:293
msgid ""
"It is best proactive to take a photo of a receipt as soon as it is received, "
"to eliminate the risk of losing the receipt and having an expense "
"reimbursement request denied."
msgstr ""
"Sebaiknya langsung mengambil foto tanda terima segera setelah diterima, "
"untuk menghilangkan risiko kehilangan tanda terima dan permintaan "
"penggantian pengeluaran ditolak."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/expenses/expense_cards.rst:296
msgid ""
"Open the expense record by navigating to :menuselection:`Expenses app --> "
"Cards`, and click on the specific card. Next, click the :icon:`fa-"
"usd` :guilabel:`Expenses` smart button, and the :guilabel:`Expenses` "
"dashboard loads for that card. Any expense that does *not* have a receipt "
"attached to the record displays a :icon:`fa-credit-card` :guilabel:`Please "
"upload the receipt.`"
msgstr ""
"Buka catatan pengeluaran dengan menavigasi ke :menuselection:`Expenses "
"app --> Cards`, dan klik pada kartu tertentu. Selanjutnya, klik tombol "
"pintar :icon:`fa-usd` :guilabel:`Pengeluaran`, dan dashboard "
":guilabel:`Pengeluaran` akan dimuat untuk kartu tersebut. Setiap pengeluaran "
"yang *tidak* memiliki tanda terima yang dilampirkan pada catatan menampilkan "
":icon:`fa-credit-card` :guilabel:`Harap unggah tanda terima.`"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/expenses/expense_cards.rst:301
msgid ""
"Click on the desired expense record to open the detailed expense form. Click "
"the :guilabel:`Attach Receipt` button, and a file explorer loads. Navigate "
"to the receipt, and click :guilabel:`Open` to select it and attach it to the "
"expense."
msgstr ""
"Klik pada catatan pengeluaran yang diinginkan untuk membuka formulir "
"pengeluaran terperinci. Klik tombol :guilabel:`Lampirkan Tanda Terima`, dan "
"file explorer akan dimuat. Navigasikan ke tanda terima, dan klik "
":guilabel:`Buka` untuk memilih dan melampirkannya ke pengeluaran."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/expenses/expense_cards.rst:305
msgid ""
"Make any other adjustments to :ref:`the expense record <expenses/"
"manual_expense>`, if necessary. Once the record is correct, "
"click :guilabel:`Submit` to submit the receipt, or :guilabel:`Split`, if the "
"receipt needs to be split between multiple expenses."
msgstr ""
"Lakukan penyesuaian lain pada :ref:`catatan pengeluaran <expenses/"
"manual_expense>`, jika diperlukan. Setelah catatan sudah benar, klik "
":guilabel:`Kirim` untuk mengirimkan tanda terima, atau :guilabel:`Pisahkan`, "
"jika tanda terima perlu dipecah antara beberapa pengeluaran."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/expenses/expense_cards.rst:310
msgid ""
"If a purchase is attempted that either is outside the listed countries, "
"listed categories, or exceeds the transaction limit or total expense limit "
"for the specified time period, the expense is denied and captured in "
"the :guilabel:`Expenses` dashboard for the card, with a status of *Refused*."
msgstr ""
"Jika pembelian dicoba yang berada di luar negara yang terdaftar, kategori "
"yang terdaftar, atau melebihi batas transaksi atau total batas pengeluaran "
"untuk periode waktu yang ditentukan, pengeluaran ditolak dan dicatat dalam "
"dashboard :guilabel:`Pengeluaran` untuk kartu tersebut, dengan status "
"*Ditolak*."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/expenses/expense_cards.rst:315
msgid ""
"To view the details of why the transaction was refused, click on "
"the :icon:`fa-usd` :guilabel:`Expenses` smart button for the card, and click "
"on the refused transaction. The details explaining why the transaction was "
"refused appears in the chatter, authored by *OdooBot*."
msgstr ""
"Untuk melihat detail mengapa transaksi ditolak, klik pada tombol pintar "
":icon:`fa-usd` :guilabel:`Pengeluaran` untuk kartu tersebut, dan klik pada "
"transaksi yang ditolak. Detail yang menjelaskan mengapa transaksi ditolak "
"muncul di chatter, yang dibuat oleh *OdooBot*."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/expenses/expense_cards.rst:322
msgid "Physical card"
msgstr "Kartu fisik"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/expenses/expense_cards.rst:324
msgid ""
"When using a physical card, make charges in the same manner as a regular "
"physical pre-paid debit card."
msgstr ""
"Saat menggunakan kartu fisik, lakukan pembayaran dengan cara yang sama "
"seperti kartu debit pra-bayar fisik biasa."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/expenses/expense_cards.rst:327
msgid ""
"Once the user receives the card, the cardholder must activate the card using "
"the instructions provided with the card. Next, open the **Expenses** app, "
"and click on the physical card, which has a status of :guilabel:`Pending`. "
"Click :guilabel:`Activate`, then when prompted, enter the last four digits "
"of the card, confirm the phone number, accept the terms and conditions, and "
"complete the activation."
msgstr ""
"Setelah user menerima kartu, pemegang kartu harus mengaktifkan kartu "
"menggunakan instruksi yang disediakan bersama kartu. Selanjutnya, buka "
"aplikasi **Pengeluaran**, dan klik pada kartu fisik yang memiliki status "
":guilabel:`Pending`. Klik :guilabel:`Activate`, kemudian saat diminta, "
"masukkan empat digit terakhir kartu, konfirmasi nomor telepon, terima syarat "
"dan ketentuan, lalu selesaikan aktivasi."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/expenses/expense_cards.rst:334
msgid "Card PIN"
msgstr "PIN Kartu"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/expenses/expense_cards.rst:336
msgid ""
"To view the card's PIN, the cardholder **must** have a :doc:`user <../../"
"general/users>` profile. Navigate to :menuselection:`Expenses app --> "
"Cards`, and click on the card to open the card form. Enter the six-digit "
"code sent via SMS to the associated phone number. The card and its PIN "
"appear in a pop-up window. The PIN is displayed below the card and "
"**cannot** be changed."
msgstr ""
"Untuk melihat PIN kartu, pemegang kartu **harus** memiliki profil :doc:`user "
"<../../general/users>`. Navigasi ke :menuselection:`aplikasi Pengeluaran --> "
"Kartu`, dan klik kartu untuk membuka formulir kartu. Masukkan kode enam "
"digit yang dikirim melalui SMS ke nomor telepon terkait. Kartu dan PIN-nya "
"muncul di jendela pop-up. PIN ditampilkan di bawah kartu dan **tidak dapat** "
"diubah."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/expenses/expense_cards.rst:344
msgid "Virtual card"
msgstr "Kartu virtual"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/expenses/expense_cards.rst:346
msgid ""
"If using a virtual card, the cardholder **must** have a :doc:`user <../../"
"general/users>` profile to access the card information required for "
"purchases."
msgstr ""
"Jika menggunakan kartu virtual, pemegang kartu **harus** memiliki profil "
":doc:`user <../../general/users>` untuk mengakses informasi kartu yang "
"diperlukan untuk pembelian."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/expenses/expense_cards.rst:349
msgid ""
"To obtain the card information, navigate to :menuselection:`Expenses app --> "
"Cards` and click on the virtual card being used. Next, click into "
"the :guilabel:`Card Details` tab, and two items appear: the expense card "
"number, with only the last four digits displayed, and the expiration date."
msgstr ""
"Untuk mendapatkan informasi kartu, navigasi ke :menuselection:`Aplikasi "
"Pengeluaran --> Kartu` dan klik pada kartu virtual yang digunakan. "
"Selanjutnya, klik ke tab :guilabel:`Card Details`, dan dua item muncul: "
"nomor kartu pengeluaran dengan hanya empat digit terakhir yang ditampilkan, "
"dan tanggal kedaluwarsa."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/expenses/expense_cards.rst:353
msgid ""
"To view the full details, click :icon:`fa-eye` :guilabel:`View Details`, and "
"a :guilabel:`Two-Factor Authentication` pop-up window loads. Enter the six-"
"digit authentication code that is texted to the cardholder's phone number. "
"The card appears in the pop-up window, with all the information displayed: "
"the card number, expiration date, and security code. When done, close the "
"window by clicking :guilabel:`X`."
msgstr ""
"Untuk melihat detail lengkap, klik :icon:`fa-eye` :guilabel:`View Details`, "
"dan jendela pop-up :guilabel:`Two-Factor Authentication` dimuat. Masukkan "
"kode autentikasi enam digit yang dikirim melalui SMS ke nomor telepon "
"pemegang kartu. Kartu muncul di jendela pop-up, dengan semua informasi "
"ditampilkan: nomor kartu, tanggal kedaluwarsa, dan kode keamanan. Setelah "
"selesai, tutup jendela dengan mengklik :guilabel:`X`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/expenses/expense_cards.rst:360
msgid ""
"Android users can add their virtual expense cards `to a Google wallet "
"<https://support.google.com/wallet/answer/12058983?hl=en>`_."
msgstr ""
"Pengguna Android dapat menambahkan kartu pengeluaran virtual mereka `ke "
"Google wallet <https://support.google.com/wallet/answer/12058983?hl=en>`_."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/expenses/expense_cards.rst:364
msgid "Lost cards"
msgstr "Kartu hilang"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/expenses/expense_cards.rst:366
msgid ""
"When a physical card is lost, or if credentials for a virtual card have been "
"compromised, the cards must be updated in the **Expenses** app so they "
"cannot be used. This is referred to in Odoo as *blocking*."
msgstr ""
"Ketika kartu fisik hilang, atau jika kredensial kartu virtual telah "
"dikompromikan, kartu harus diperbarui di aplikasi **Pengeluaran** agar tidak "
"dapat digunakan. Ini disebut sebagai *pemblokiran* di Odoo."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/expenses/expense_cards.rst:370
msgid ""
"To stop any charges on a card, navigate to :menuselection:`Expenses app --> "
"Cards`, and click on the specific card being deactivated. On the card form, "
"click the :guilabel:`Block` button, and a :guilabel:`Block a Card` pop-up "
"window loads."
msgstr ""
"Untuk menghentikan pembayaran pada kartu, navigasi ke "
":menuselection:`Aplikasi Pengeluaran --> Kartu`, dan klik pada kartu "
"spesifik yang sedang dinonaktifkan. Pada formulir kartu, klik tombol "
":guilabel:`Block`, dan jendela pop-up :guilabel:`Block a Card` dimuat."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/expenses/expense_cards.rst:374
msgid ""
"Click into the field next to :guilabel:`Reason`, and select the reason the "
"card is being blocked. The options are :guilabel:`Lost`, :guilabel:`Stolen`, "
"or :guilabel:`Other`. After making a selection, click :guilabel:`Block`, and "
"the card is unable to be used, and a red :guilabel:`Blocked` banner appears "
"on the card in the :guilabel:`Cards` dashboard view."
msgstr ""
"Klik ke dalam field di sebelah :guilabel:`Reason`, dan pilih alasan kartu "
"diblokir. Opsinya adalah :guilabel:`Lost`, :guilabel:`Stolen`, atau "
":guilabel:`Other`. Setelah membuat pilihan, klik :guilabel:`Block`, dan "
"kartu tidak dapat digunakan, serta banner merah :guilabel:`Blocked` muncul "
"pada kartu di tampilan dashboard :guilabel:`Cards`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/expenses/expense_cards.rst:380
msgid ""
"An employee is given a virtual expense card to use for an upcoming business "
"trip. The employee uses this card to purchase an airline ticket and a hotel "
"room, one month before the scheduled trip."
msgstr ""
"Seorang karyawan diberikan kartu pengeluaran virtual untuk digunakan dalam "
"perjalanan bisnis yang akan datang. Karyawan menggunakan kartu ini untuk "
"membeli tiket pesawat dan kamar hotel, satu bulan sebelum perjalanan yang "
"dijadwalkan."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/expenses/expense_cards.rst:384
msgid ""
"A week before the trip, they receive an email from the airline, explaining "
"there has been a data breach, and customer names, contact information, and "
"purchase details including credit card numbers have been leaked."
msgstr ""
"Seminggu sebelum perjalanan, mereka menerima email dari maskapai "
"penerbangan, menjelaskan bahwa telah terjadi pelanggaran data, dan nama "
"pelanggan, informasi kontak, dan detail pembelian termasuk nomor kartu "
"kredit telah bocor."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/expenses/expense_cards.rst:388
msgid ""
"The employee reaches out to their manager, explaining the situation. The "
"manager opens the virtual expense card, and blocks the card using the "
"reason :guilabel:`Other`. Then the manager issues another virtual card for "
"the employee to use for their business trip."
msgstr ""
"Karyawan menghubungi manajer mereka, menjelaskan situasinya. Manajer membuka "
"kartu pengeluaran virtual, dan memblokir kartu dengan menggunakan alasan "
":guilabel:`Other`. Kemudian manajer menerbitkan kartu virtual lain untuk "
"digunakan karyawan dalam perjalanan bisnis mereka."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/expenses/expense_cards.rst:393
msgid "Temporary card pauses"
msgstr "Jeda kartu sementara"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/expenses/expense_cards.rst:395
msgid ""
"When an employee is out of office for an extended period of time, such as a "
"vacation, or an illness, it is recommended to temporarily deactivate their "
"card to prevent any fraudulent charges. This is referred to in Odoo as "
"*pausing* a card."
msgstr ""
"Ketika seorang karyawan berada di luar kantor untuk waktu yang lama, seperti "
"liburan atau sakit, disarankan untuk menonaktifkan kartu mereka sementara "
"waktu untuk mencegah pembayaran penipuan. Ini disebut sebagai *menjeda* "
"kartu di Odoo."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/expenses/expense_cards.rst:399
msgid ""
"To pause a card, navigate to :menuselection:`Expenses app --> Cards`, and "
"click on the specific card being paused. On the card form, "
"click :guilabel:`Pause`, and the card is unable to be used until it is "
"activated."
msgstr ""
"Untuk menjeda kartu, navigasi ke :menuselection:`Aplikasi Pengeluaran --> "
"Kartu`, dan klik pada kartu spesifik yang dijeda. Pada formulir kartu, klik "
":guilabel:`Pause`, dan kartu tidak dapat digunakan hingga diaktifkan."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/expenses/expense_cards.rst:404
msgid ""
"An employee in the sales department has a physical expense card to use for "
"client meetings. They recently welcomed a new child, and will be out of "
"office on parental leave for three months."
msgstr ""
"Seorang karyawan di departemen penjualan memiliki kartu pengeluaran fisik "
"untuk digunakan dalam pertemuan klien. Mereka baru saja menyambut anak baru, "
"dan akan berada di luar kantor dengan cuti orang tua selama tiga bulan."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/expenses/expense_cards.rst:407
msgid ""
"On the employee's last day, their manager opens the expense card record, and "
"clicks :guilabel:`Pause`. When the employee returns to work, the manager "
"opens the expense card form and clicks :guilabel:`Active` to reactivate the "
"card."
msgstr ""
"Pada hari terakhir karyawan, manajer mereka membuka catatan kartu "
"pengeluaran, dan mengklik :guilabel:`Pause`. Ketika karyawan kembali "
"bekerja, manajer membuka formulir kartu pengeluaran dan mengklik "
":guilabel:`Active` untuk mengaktifkan kembali kartu."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/expenses/expense_categories.rst:3
msgid "Expense categories"
msgstr "Kategori pengeluaran"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/expenses/expense_categories.rst:5
msgid ""
"Odoo **Expenses** streamlines the management of expenses. After an "
"employee :doc:`logs <../expenses/log_expenses>` and :doc:`submits <../"
"expenses/submit_expenses>` their expenses in Odoo, expenses are reviewed by "
"management and accounting teams. Once :doc:`approved <../expenses/"
"approve_expenses>`, payments can be processed and :doc:`disbursed back to "
"the employee <../expenses/reimburse>` for reimbursement."
msgstr ""
"Odoo **Pengeluaran** menyederhanakan pengelolaan pengeluaran. Setelah "
"karyawan :doc:`mencatat <../expenses/log_expenses>` dan :doc:`mengajukan <../"
"expenses/submit_expenses>` pengeluaran mereka di Odoo, pengeluaran ditinjau "
"oleh tim manajemen dan akuntansi. Setelah :doc:`disetujui <../expenses/"
"approve_expenses>`, pembayaran dapat diproses dan :doc:`dikembalikan kepada "
"karyawan <../expenses/reimburse>` untuk penggantian."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/expenses/expense_categories.rst:12
msgid "`Odoo Expenses: product page <https://www.odoo.com/app/expenses>`_"
msgstr "`Odoo Expenses: halaman produk <https://www.odoo.com/app/expenses>`_"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/expenses/expense_categories.rst:15
msgid "View expense categories"
msgstr ""

#: ../../content/applications/finance/expenses/expense_categories.rst:17
msgid ""
"The first step to track expenses is configuring the different types of "
"expenses for the company (managed as *expense categories* in Odoo). Each "
"category can be as specific or generalized as needed. Additionally, expense "
"categories can be configured to repay expenses at either a set price or "
"allow for specific prices to be reported."
msgstr ""

#: ../../content/applications/finance/expenses/expense_categories.rst:22
msgid ""
"To view the default expense categories, navigate to :menuselection:`Expenses "
"app --> Configuration --> Expense Categories`."
msgstr ""

#: ../../content/applications/finance/expenses/expense_categories.rst:25
msgid ""
"The default expense categories allow creating expenses for common expenses, "
"including communication costs, meals, gifts, miles driven, and other travel "
"expenses. For expenses outside these default categories, the general "
"expenses category, :guilabel:`EXP_GEN`, is used. If a company has specific "
"expenses it commonly reimburses, and wants to track them "
"separately, :ref:`new expense categories can be made <expenses/new-"
"category>` or existing expense categories can be modified."
msgstr ""

#: ../../content/applications/finance/expenses/expense_categories.rst:None
msgid "Set expense costs on products."
msgstr "Tetapkan biaya pengeluaran pada produk."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/expenses/expense_categories.rst:37
msgid "Create new expense categories"
msgstr ""

#: ../../content/applications/finance/expenses/expense_categories.rst:39
msgid ""
"Some companies require more expense categories than the **Expenses** app "
"includes. For these situations, new expense categories can be created."
msgstr ""

#: ../../content/applications/finance/expenses/expense_categories.rst:43
msgid ""
"A company that trains car mechanics allows its technicians to purchase $500 "
"worth of tools in a year. In this situation, the company creates a new "
"category called `TOOLS` to track all tool expenses."
msgstr ""

#: ../../content/applications/finance/expenses/expense_categories.rst:47
msgid ""
"To create a new expense category, navigate to :menuselection:`Expenses app --"
"> Configuration --> Expense Categories`. Click :guilabel:`New`, and a new "
"expense category form loads."
msgstr ""

#: ../../content/applications/finance/expenses/expense_categories.rst:51
msgid ""
"Expense *categories* are managed like *products* in Odoo. The expense "
"category form follows the standard product form in Odoo, and the information "
"entered is similar. Expense *products* are referred to as expense "
"*categories* throughout this document since the main menu refers to these "
"as :guilabel:`Expense Categories`."
msgstr ""

#: ../../content/applications/finance/expenses/expense_categories.rst:56
msgid "Enter the following fields on the form:"
msgstr ""

#: ../../content/applications/finance/expenses/expense_categories.rst:58
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Product Name`: Enter a name for the category that is short and "
"informative."
msgstr ""

#: ../../content/applications/finance/expenses/expense_categories.rst:59
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Cost`: If employees can report the actual cost of an expense, and "
"are reimbursed the reported amount, leave the field set to `0.00`. If the "
"expense should **always** be reimbursed for a specific price, enter the "
"amount in this field. If a price is entered, a :guilabel:`per` field appears "
"with :guilabel:`Unit` populated by default. :guilabel:`Unit` covers most "
"expense situations, but if the reimbursement is based on weight, length, "
"volume, etc., choose the corresponding type of unit using the drop-down menu."
msgstr ""

#: ../../content/applications/finance/expenses/expense_categories.rst:67
msgid ""
"Here are some examples for when to set a specific :guilabel:`Cost` on a "
"product vs. leaving the :guilabel:`Cost` at `0.00`:"
msgstr ""
"Berikut adalah beberapa contoh kapan harus menetapkan :guilabel:`Cost` "
"tertentu pada produk versus membiarkan :guilabel:`Cost` pada `0.00`:"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/expenses/expense_categories.rst:70
msgid ""
"**Meals**: If employees are reimbursed for their full meal cost, set "
"the :guilabel:`Cost` to `0.00`. When an employee logs an expense for a meal, "
"they enter the actual amount of the bill and are reimbursed for that amount. "
"An expense for a meal costing $95.23 would equal a reimbursement of $95.23."
msgstr ""

#: ../../content/applications/finance/expenses/expense_categories.rst:74
msgid ""
"**Mileage**: If employees receive a flat rate for each mile they drive, set "
"the :guilabel:`Cost` to `1.00`. When an employee logs an expense for the "
"miles driven, they enter the number of miles driven in "
"the :guilabel:`Quantity` field, and are reimbursed $1.00 per mile they "
"reported. An expense for 100 miles would equal a reimbursement of $100.00."
msgstr ""

#: ../../content/applications/finance/expenses/expense_categories.rst:78
msgid ""
"**Per Diem**: If employees receive a daily flat rate of $125.00 when "
"traveling, set the :guilabel:`Cost` to `125.00`. An expense for three days "
"of per diem costs (meals, incidentals, taxi fare, etc.) would equal a "
"reimbursement of $375.00."
msgstr ""

#: ../../content/applications/finance/expenses/expense_categories.rst:83
msgid ""
"The :guilabel:`Cost` field is always visible on the expense category form, "
"but the :guilabel:`Sales Price` field is *only* visible if "
"the :guilabel:`Sales Price` is selected under the :guilabel:`Re-Invoice "
"Expenses` section. Otherwise, the :guilabel:`Sales Price` field is hidden."
msgstr ""
"Kolom :guilabel:`Cost` selalu terlihat pada formulir kategori pengeluaran, "
"tetapi kolom :guilabel:`Sales Price` *hanya* terlihat jika :guilabel:`Sales "
"Price` dipilih di bagian :guilabel:`Re-Invoice Expenses`. Jika tidak, kolom "
":guilabel:`Sales Price` akan disembunyikan."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/expenses/expense_categories.rst:88
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Reference`: Enter a short reference for the expense, such as "
"`FOOD` or `TRAVEL`. This reference is used when :ref:`emailing expenses "
"<expenses/email_expense>`."
msgstr ""

#: ../../content/applications/finance/expenses/expense_categories.rst:90
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Category`: Using the drop-down menu, select the category the "
"expense falls under. It is recommended to use the default category `All / "
"Expenses`, but another category can be selected if the accounting department "
"requires it."
msgstr ""

#: ../../content/applications/finance/expenses/expense_categories.rst:93
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Company`: If in a multi-company database, select the company the "
"expense category applies to. If the expense category applies to *all* "
"companies, leave this field blank."
msgstr ""

#: ../../content/applications/finance/expenses/expense_categories.rst:95
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Guideline`: Enter some rules or important information for the "
"expense category. This is visible in the :guilabel:`Note` column on "
"the :guilabel:`Expense Category` dashboard."
msgstr ""

#: ../../content/applications/finance/expenses/expense_categories.rst:99
msgid ""
"An expense category for expenses related to working from home may have "
"a :guilabel:`Name` of `WFH`, and the :guilabel:`Guideline` may say "
"`Monitors, Chairs, & Other Home Working Costs`."
msgstr ""

#: ../../content/applications/finance/expenses/expense_categories.rst:102
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Expense Account`: If using the Odoo **Accounting** app, select "
"the :abbr:`CoA (Chart of Accounts)` the expense should be logged on."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Akun Pengeluaran`: Jika menggunakan aplikasi **Akuntansi** Odoo, "
"pilih :abbr:`Bagan Akun (Chart of Accounts)` tempat pengeluaran harus "
"dicatat."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/expenses/expense_categories.rst:106
msgid ""
"Check with the accounting department to determine the correct account to "
"reference in this field as it affects various reports."
msgstr ""
"Periksa dengan departemen akuntansi untuk menentukan akun yang tepat untuk "
"dirujuk di bidang ini karena mempengaruhi berbagai laporan."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/expenses/expense_categories.rst:109
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Purchase Taxes` and :guilabel:`Sales Taxes`: Enter the default "
"taxes that are applied when purchasing or selling this product, if "
"applicable."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Pajak Pembelian` dan :guilabel:`Pajak Penjualan`: Masukkan pajak "
"default yang diterapkan saat membeli atau menjual produk ini, jika berlaku."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/expenses/expense_categories.rst:113
msgid ""
"The :guilabel:`Sales Taxes` field is **only** visible if the **Sales** app "
"is installed, and either the :guilabel:`At cost` or :guilabel:`Sales Price` "
"options are selected in the :ref:`invoicing section <expenses/invoicing>`."
msgstr ""
"Bidang :guilabel:`Pajak Penjualan` **hanya** terlihat jika aplikasi "
"**Penjualan** diinstal, dan salah satu opsi :guilabel:`Sesuai biaya` atau "
":guilabel:`Harga Jual` dipilih di :ref:`bagian penagihan <expenses/invoicing>"
"`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/expenses/expense_categories.rst:118
msgid ""
"It is considered good practice to use a tax that is configured "
"with :ref:`Tax Included in Price <taxes/included-in-price>`. Taxes are "
"automatically configured if these are set."
msgstr ""
"Dianggap sebagai praktik yang baik untuk menggunakan pajak yang "
"dikonfigurasi dengan :ref:`Pajak Termasuk dalam Harga <taxes/included-in-"
"price>`. Pajak secara otomatis dikonfigurasi jika ini diatur."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/expenses/expense_categories.rst:None
msgid "A new expense category for tools."
msgstr "Kategori pengeluaran baru untuk alat."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/expenses/expense_categories.rst:127
msgid "Invoicing section"
msgstr "Bagian Penagihan"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/expenses/expense_categories.rst:129
msgid ""
"If the **Sales** app is installed, an invoicing section is visible. This "
"section allows the expense to be reinvoiced to customers on sales orders."
msgstr ""
"Jika aplikasi **Penjualan** diinstal, bagian penagihan akan terlihat. Bagian "
"ini memungkinkan pengeluaran untuk ditagihkan kembali kepada pelanggan pada "
"pesanan penjualan."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/expenses/expense_categories.rst:132
msgid ""
"If the expense **cannot** be reinvoiced, enable the :guilabel:`No` option. "
"If the expense category **can** be reinvoiced, enable either of these "
"options:"
msgstr ""
"Jika pengeluaran **tidak dapat** ditagihkan kembali, aktifkan opsi "
":guilabel:`Tidak`. Jika kategori pengeluaran **dapat** ditagihkan kembali, "
"aktifkan salah satu dari opsi berikut:"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/expenses/expense_categories.rst:135
msgid ""
":guilabel:`At cost`: Select this option to have the expense item reinvoiced "
"at the price set in the :guilabel:`Cost` field."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Sesuai biaya`: Pilih opsi ini untuk memiliki item pengeluaran "
"ditagihkan kembali pada harga yang ditetapkan di bidang :guilabel:`Biaya`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/expenses/expense_categories.rst:137
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Sales Price`: Select this option to have the expense item "
"reinvoiced at the sales price. When enabled, a :guilabel:`Sales Price` field "
"appears beneath the :guilabel:`Product Name` field. Enter the sales price in "
"the new field."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Harga Jual`: Pilih opsi ini untuk memiliki item pengeluaran "
"ditagihkan kembali pada harga jual. Saat diaktifkan, bidang :guilabel:`Harga "
"Jual` muncul di bawah bidang :guilabel:`Nama Produk`. Masukkan harga jual di "
"bidang baru."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/expenses/expense_categories.rst:142
msgid ""
"A heating and cooling company offers at-home repairs on the furnaces and "
"central air units it sells. Their technicians are sub-contracted, and use "
"their own vans, tools, and parts."
msgstr ""
"Sebuah perusahaan pemanas dan pendingin menawarkan perbaikan di rumah untuk "
"tungku dan unit pendingin sentral yang dijualnya. Teknisi mereka dikontrak, "
"dan menggunakan van, alat, dan suku cadang mereka sendiri."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/expenses/expense_categories.rst:145
msgid ""
"As part of their contracts, technicians are reimbursed for their travel. "
"They receive $1.00 for every mile they drive. Additionally, the customer "
"must pay for the travel as part of their service contract. The customer pays "
"$1.50 for every mile the technician drives to their location."
msgstr ""
"Sebagai bagian dari kontrak mereka, teknisi mendapat penggantian untuk "
"perjalanan mereka. Mereka menerima $1,00 untuk setiap mil yang mereka "
"tempuh. Selain itu, pelanggan harus membayar untuk perjalanan sebagai bagian "
"dari kontrak layanan mereka. Pelanggan membayar $1,50 untuk setiap mil yang "
"ditempuh teknisi ke lokasi mereka."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/expenses/expense_categories.rst:149
msgid ""
"To configure this expense, the :guilabel:`Sales Price` is set to `1.50` and "
"the :guilabel:`Cost` is set to `1.00`."
msgstr ""
"Untuk mengonfigurasi pengeluaran ini, :guilabel:`Harga Jual` diatur ke "
"`1.50` dan :guilabel:`Biaya` diatur ke `1.00`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/expenses/expense_categories.rst:0
msgid "An expense category to reinvoice customers and pay technicians."
msgstr ""
"Kategori pengeluaran untuk menagihkan kembali pelanggan dan membayar teknisi."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/expenses/expenses_analysis.rst:3
msgid "Expenses analysis"
msgstr "Analisis pengeluaran"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/expenses/expenses_analysis.rst:5
msgid ""
"It is important for companies to track expenses so they have an "
"understanding of their expenses and can identify trends. Expense reporting "
"allows for detailed information, such as which expense categories are "
"reimbursed the most, which employees incur the most expenses, and if there "
"are any periods of time that tend to incur more expenses than others."
msgstr ""
"Penting bagi perusahaan untuk melacak pengeluaran sehingga mereka memiliki "
"pemahaman tentang pengeluaran mereka dan dapat mengidentifikasi tren. "
"Pelaporan pengeluaran memungkinkan informasi terperinci, seperti kategori "
"pengeluaran mana yang paling banyak diganti, karyawan mana yang mengeluarkan "
"pengeluaran terbanyak, dan apakah ada periode waktu yang cenderung "
"mengeluarkan lebih banyak pengeluaran daripada yang lain."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/expenses/expenses_analysis.rst:11
msgid "View expense analysis report"
msgstr "Lihat laporan analisis pengeluaran"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/expenses/expenses_analysis.rst:13
msgid ""
"To view the default *Expenses Analysis* report, navigate "
"to :menuselection:`Expenses app --> Reporting --> Expenses Analysis`. "
"The :guilabel:`Expenses Analysis` report displays all expenses for the "
"current year, in a stacked bar chart, grouped by month."
msgstr ""
"Untuk melihat laporan *Analisis Pengeluaran* default, navigasikan ke "
":menuselection:`aplikasi Pengeluaran --> Pelaporan --> Analisis "
"Pengeluaran`. Laporan :guilabel:`Analisis Pengeluaran` menampilkan semua "
"pengeluaran untuk tahun berjalan, dalam bagan batang bertumpuk, "
"dikelompokkan berdasarkan bulan."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/expenses/expenses_analysis.rst:None
msgid "The default stacked bar chart for annual expenses, grouped by month."
msgstr ""
"Bagan batang bertumpuk default untuk pengeluaran tahunan, dikelompokkan "
"berdasarkan bulan."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/expenses/expenses_analysis.rst:21
msgid "View expenses by employee"
msgstr "Lihat pengeluaran berdasarkan karyawan"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/expenses/expenses_analysis.rst:23
msgid ""
"It is possible to view the data so that the total cost of expenses *by "
"employee* is visible. To view the report in this way, navigate "
"to :menuselection:`Expenses app --> Reporting --> Expenses Analysis`. Next, "
"click the :icon:`oi-view-pivot` :guilabel:`(Pivot)` icon to view the data in "
"a pivot table."
msgstr ""
"Dimungkinkan untuk melihat data sehingga total biaya pengeluaran "
"*berdasarkan karyawan* terlihat. Untuk melihat laporan dengan cara ini, "
"navigasikan ke :menuselection:`Aplikasi Pengeluaran --> Pelaporan --> "
"Analisis Pengeluaran`. Selanjutnya, klik ikon :icon:`oi-view-pivot` "
":guilabel:`(Pivot)` untuk melihat data dalam tabel pivot."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/expenses/expenses_analysis.rst:28
msgid ""
"This presents the data with the *employees* populating the rows, and the "
"*total monthly expenses* populate the columns. Next, click :icon:`fa-minus-"
"square-o` :guilabel:`Total` at the top of the monthly columns to hide the "
"individual monthly totals, and present only the *total* amount for the year."
msgstr ""
"Ini menampilkan data dengan *karyawan* mengisi baris, dan *total pengeluaran "
"bulanan* mengisi kolom. Selanjutnya, klik :icon:`fa-minus-square-o` "
":guilabel:`Total` di bagian atas kolom bulanan untuk menyembunyikan total "
"bulanan individual, dan hanya menampilkan jumlah *total* untuk tahun "
"tersebut."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/expenses/expenses_analysis.rst:33
#: ../../content/applications/finance/expenses/expenses_analysis.rst:63
msgid ""
"To present the data in either ascending or descending total, click "
"the :guilabel:`Total In Currency` box, and the information is organized "
"first in ascending order, starting with the smallest amount. "
"Click :guilabel:`Total In Currency` again to reverse the order, and present "
"the highest amount first."
msgstr ""
"Untuk menampilkan data dalam urutan total menaik atau menurun, klik kotak "
":guilabel:`Total In Currency`, dan informasi diatur pertama dalam urutan "
"menaik, dimulai dengan jumlah terkecil. Klik :guilabel:`Total In Currency` "
"lagi untuk membalikkan urutan, dan menampilkan jumlah tertinggi terlebih "
"dahulu."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/expenses/expenses_analysis.rst:39
msgid ""
"In this example it can be determined that :guilabel:`Mike Smith` has the "
"highest amount of expenses, totaling :guilabel:`4,216.44`. This is almost "
"seven times higher than :guilabel:`Ronnie Hart`, who has the second highest "
"expenses, with a total of :guilabel:`644.74`."
msgstr ""
"Dalam contoh ini dapat ditentukan bahwa :guilabel:`Mike Smith` memiliki "
"jumlah pengeluaran tertinggi, dengan total :guilabel:`4,216.44`. Ini hampir "
"tujuh kali lebih tinggi dari :guilabel:`Ronnie Hart`, yang memiliki "
"pengeluaran tertinggi kedua, dengan total :guilabel:`644.74`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/expenses/expenses_analysis.rst:0
msgid ""
"A pivot table with the information shown by employee, in descending order."
msgstr ""
"Tabel pivot dengan informasi yang ditampilkan berdasarkan karyawan, dalam "
"urutan menurun."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/expenses/expenses_analysis.rst:47
msgid "View expenses by category"
msgstr "Lihat pengeluaran berdasarkan kategori"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/expenses/expenses_analysis.rst:49
msgid ""
"It is possible to view the data so that the total cost of expenses *by "
"category* is visible. To view the report in this way, navigate "
"to :menuselection:`Expenses app --> Reporting --> Expenses Analysis`. Next, "
"click the :icon:`oi-view-pivot` :guilabel:`(Pivot)` icon to view the data in "
"a pivot table."
msgstr ""
"Dimungkinkan untuk melihat data sehingga total biaya pengeluaran "
"*berdasarkan kategori* terlihat. Untuk melihat laporan dengan cara ini, "
"navigasikan ke :menuselection:`Aplikasi Pengeluaran --> Pelaporan --> "
"Analisis Pengeluaran`. Selanjutnya, klik ikon :icon:`oi-view-pivot` "
":guilabel:`(Pivot)` untuk melihat data dalam tabel pivot."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/expenses/expenses_analysis.rst:54
msgid ""
"This presents the data with the *employees* populating the rows, and the "
"*total monthly expenses* populate the columns. Next, click :icon:`fa-minus-"
"square-o` :guilabel:`Total` at the top of the employees column. "
"Click :icon:`fa-plus-square` :guilabel:`Total` that appears in place "
"of :icon:`fa-minus-square-o` :guilabel:`Total`, revealing a drop-down menu "
"of options. Click :guilabel:`Category`, and the expense categories now "
"populate the rows."
msgstr ""
"Ini menampilkan data dengan *karyawan* mengisi baris, dan *total pengeluaran "
"bulanan* mengisi kolom. Selanjutnya, klik :icon:`fa-minus-square-o` "
":guilabel:`Total` di bagian atas kolom karyawan. Klik :icon:`fa-plus-square` "
":guilabel:`Total` yang muncul menggantikan :icon:`fa-minus-square-o` "
":guilabel:`Total`, menampilkan menu drop-down pilihan. Klik "
":guilabel:`Category`, dan kategori pengeluaran sekarang mengisi baris."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/expenses/expenses_analysis.rst:60
msgid ""
"Next, click :icon:`fa-minus-square-o` :guilabel:`Total` at the top of the "
"months column to hide the individual months, and only show the annual total "
"for each category."
msgstr ""
"Selanjutnya, klik :icon:`fa-minus-square-o` :guilabel:`Total` di bagian atas "
"kolom bulan untuk menyembunyikan bulan individual, dan hanya menampilkan "
"total tahunan untuk setiap kategori."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/expenses/expenses_analysis.rst:69
msgid ""
"In this example, it can be determined that the company spent the most on "
"travel expenses, with the expense category :guilabel:`[TRANS & ACC] Travel & "
"Accommodation` incurring :guilabel:`2,940.00` of expenses for the year. The "
"company reimbursed mileage the least, with only :guilabel:`229.69` "
"in :guilabel:`[MIL] Mileage` expenses."
msgstr ""
"Dalam contoh ini, dapat ditentukan bahwa perusahaan menghabiskan paling "
"banyak untuk biaya perjalanan, dengan kategori pengeluaran :guilabel:`[TRANS "
"& ACC] Travel & Accommodation` menimbulkan :guilabel:`2,940.00` pengeluaran "
"untuk tahun tersebut. Perusahaan mengganti jarak tempuh paling sedikit, "
"dengan hanya :guilabel:`229.69` dalam pengeluaran :guilabel:`[MIL] Mileage`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/expenses/expenses_analysis.rst:0
msgid ""
"A pivot table with the information shown by catrgory in descending order."
msgstr ""
"Tabel pivot dengan informasi yang ditampilkan berdasarkan kategori dalam "
"urutan menurun."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/expenses/log_expenses.rst:3
msgid "Log expenses"
msgstr "Catat pengeluaran"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/expenses/log_expenses.rst:5
msgid ""
"Before expenses can be reimbursed, each individual expense needs to be "
"logged in the database. Expense records can be created in four different "
"ways: :ref:`manually enter an expense record <expenses/"
"manual_expense>`, :ref:`upload a receipt <expenses/"
"upload_receipt>`, :ref:`drag and drop <expenses/drag_and_drop>` a receipt "
"onto the **Expenses** app dashboard, or :ref:`email a receipt <expenses/"
"email_expense>` to a preconfigured email address."
msgstr ""
"Sebelum pengeluaran dapat diganti, setiap pengeluaran individual perlu "
"dicatat dalam database. Catatan pengeluaran dapat dibuat dengan empat cara "
"berbeda: :ref:`memasukkan catatan pengeluaran secara manual <expenses/"
"manual_expense>`, :ref:`mengunggah tanda terima <expenses/upload_receipt>`, "
":ref:`drag and drop <expenses/drag_and_drop>` tanda terima ke dashboard "
"aplikasi **Pengeluaran**, atau :ref:`mengirim email tanda terima <expenses/"
"email_expense>` ke alamat email yang telah dikonfigurasi sebelumnya."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/expenses/log_expenses.rst:14
msgid "Manually enter expenses"
msgstr "Masukkan pengeluaran secara manual"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/expenses/log_expenses.rst:16
msgid ""
"To record a new expense, open the **Expenses** app, which displays "
"the :guilabel:`My Expenses` page, by default."
msgstr ""
"Untuk mencatat pengeluaran baru, buka aplikasi **Pengeluaran**, yang "
"menampilkan halaman :guilabel:`My Expenses`, secara default."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/expenses/log_expenses.rst:20
msgid ""
"This view can also be accessed at any time by navigating "
"to :menuselection:`Expenses app --> My Expenses --> My Expenses`."
msgstr ""
"Tampilan ini juga dapat diakses kapan saja dengan menavigasi ke "
":menuselection:`Aplikasi Pengeluaran --> My Expenses --> My Expenses`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/expenses/log_expenses.rst:23
msgid ""
"Click the :guilabel:`New` button and fill out the following fields on the "
"blank expense form that loads:"
msgstr ""
"Klik tombol :guilabel:`New` dan isi bidang berikut pada formulir pengeluaran "
"kosong yang dimuat:"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/expenses/log_expenses.rst:26
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Description`: Enter a short description for the expense. This "
"should be concise and informative, such as `Lunch with client` or `Hotel for "
"trade show`."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Description`: Masukkan deskripsi singkat untuk pengeluaran. Ini "
"harus ringkas dan informatif, seperti `Makan siang dengan klien` atau `Hotel "
"untuk pameran dagang`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/expenses/log_expenses.rst:28
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Category`: Using the drop-down menu, select the :doc:`expense "
"category <expense_categories>` that most closely corresponds to the expense."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Category`: Menggunakan menu drop-down, pilih :doc:`kategori "
"pengeluaran <expense_categories>` yang paling sesuai dengan pengeluaran."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/expenses/log_expenses.rst:30
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Total`: Enter the total amount paid for the expense in one of two "
"ways:"
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Total`: Masukkan jumlah total yang dibayarkan untuk pengeluaran "
"dengan salah satu dari dua cara:"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/expenses/log_expenses.rst:32
msgid ""
"If the expense is for a single item/expense, and the category selected was "
"for a single item, enter the cost in the :guilabel:`Total` field "
"(the :guilabel:`Quantity` field is hidden)."
msgstr ""
"Jika pengeluaran untuk satu item/pengeluaran, dan kategori yang dipilih "
"adalah untuk satu item, masukkan biaya di kolom :guilabel:`Total` (kolom "
":guilabel:`Quantity` disembunyikan)."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/expenses/log_expenses.rst:34
msgid ""
"If the expense is for multiples of the same item/expense with a fixed price, "
"the :guilabel:`Unit Price` is displayed. Enter the number of units in "
"the :guilabel:`Quantity` field, and the total cost is automatically updated "
"with the correct total. The total cost appears below "
"the :guilabel:`Quantity`."
msgstr ""
"Jika pengeluaran adalah untuk beberapa item/pengeluaran yang sama dengan "
"harga tetap, :guilabel:`Unit Price` ditampilkan. Masukkan jumlah unit dalam "
"bidang :guilabel:`Quantity`, dan total biaya secara otomatis diperbarui "
"dengan total yang benar. Total biaya muncul di bawah :guilabel:`Quantity`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/expenses/log_expenses.rst:40
msgid ""
"An employee received one dollar for each mile driven for work. "
"The :guilabel:`Category` is :guilabel:`[MIL] Mileage`. The :guilabel:`Unit "
"Price` is automatically populated with `$1.00`, which is the cost *per mile* "
"configured for the expense :guilabel:`Category` :guilabel:`[MIL] Mileage`. "
"The :guilabel:`Quantity` is set to `48`, which is the *number of miles "
"driven*, and the total is calculated to `$48.00`."
msgstr ""
"Seorang karyawan menerima satu dolar untuk setiap mil yang dikendarai untuk "
"pekerjaan. :guilabel:`Category` adalah :guilabel:`[MIL] Mileage`. "
":guilabel:`Unit Price` secara otomatis diisi dengan `$1.00`, yang merupakan "
"biaya *per mil* yang dikonfigurasi untuk :guilabel:`Category` pengeluaran "
":guilabel:`[MIL] Mileage`. :guilabel:`Quantity` diatur ke `48`, yang "
"merupakan *jumlah mil yang dikendarai*, dan totalnya dihitung menjadi "
"`$48.00`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/expenses/log_expenses.rst:46
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Included Taxes`: If taxes were configured on the selected expense "
"category, the tax percentage and amount appear automatically after entering "
"either the :guilabel:`Total` or the :guilabel:`Quantity`."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Pajak yang Disertakan`: Jika pajak dikonfigurasi pada kategori "
"pengeluaran yang dipilih, persentase pajak dan jumlahnya muncul secara "
"otomatis setelah memasukkan :guilabel:`Total` atau :guilabel:`Kuantitas`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/expenses/log_expenses.rst:51
msgid ""
"When a tax is configured on an expense category, the :guilabel:`Included "
"Taxes` value updates in real time, as the :guilabel:`Total` "
"or :guilabel:`Quantity` is updated."
msgstr ""
"Ketika pajak dikonfigurasi pada kategori pengeluaran, nilai "
":guilabel:`Included Taxes` diperbarui secara real time, saat "
":guilabel:`Total` atau :guilabel:`Quantity` diperbarui."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/expenses/log_expenses.rst:54
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Employee`: Using the drop-down menu, select the employee "
"associated with the expense."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Karyawan`: Menggunakan menu drop-down, pilih karyawan yang "
"terkait dengan pengeluaran."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/expenses/log_expenses.rst:55
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Paid By`: Click the radio button to indicate who paid for the "
"expense and should be reimbursed. Select either :guilabel:`Employee (to "
"reimburse)` or :guilabel:`Company`. Depending on the expense category "
"selected, this field may not appear."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Dibayar Oleh`: Klik tombol radio untuk menunjukkan siapa yang "
"membayar pengeluaran dan harus diganti. Pilih :guilabel:`Karyawan (untuk "
"diganti)` atau :guilabel:`Perusahaan`. Tergantung pada kategori pengeluaran "
"yang dipilih, bidang ini mungkin tidak muncul."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/expenses/log_expenses.rst:58
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Expense Date`: Using the calendar popover window that appears "
"when this field is clicked, enter the date the expense was incurred."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Expense Date`: Menggunakan jendela popover kalender yang muncul "
"saat kolom ini diklik, masukkan tanggal pengeluaran terjadi."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/expenses/log_expenses.rst:60
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Account`: If the selected expense :guilabel:`Category` has a "
"specific account linked to it, that account appears in "
"the :guilabel:`Account` field. If no account is specified, the default "
"`600000 Expenses` account populates this field. If a different account is "
"desired, select the account the expense should be logged in."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Akun`: Jika :guilabel:`Kategori` pengeluaran yang dipilih "
"memiliki akun tertentu yang terhubung dengannya, akun tersebut muncul di "
"bidang :guilabel:`Akun`. Jika tidak ada akun yang ditentukan, akun default "
"`600000 Expenses` mengisi bidang ini. Jika akun yang berbeda diinginkan, "
"pilih akun tempat pengeluaran harus dicatat."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/expenses/log_expenses.rst:64
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Customer to Reinvoice`: If the expense should be paid for by a "
"customer and the selected :guilabel:`Category` allows for reinvoicing of "
"expenses, select the :abbr:`SO (Sales Order)` and customer to be invoiced "
"for the expense using the drop-down menu. All sales orders in the drop-down "
"menu list both the :abbr:`SO (Sales Order)`, as well as the company the "
"sales order is written for. After the expense is saved, the customer name "
"disappears, and only the :abbr:`SO (Sales Order)` is visible on the expense."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Pelanggan untuk Ditagih Ulang`: Jika pengeluaran harus dibayar "
"oleh pelanggan dan :guilabel:`Kategori` yang dipilih memungkinkan penagihan "
"ulang pengeluaran, pilih :abbr:`SO (Sales Order)` dan pelanggan yang akan "
"ditagih untuk pengeluaran menggunakan menu drop-down. Semua sales order "
"dalam menu drop-down mencantumkan :abbr:`SO (Sales Order)`, serta perusahaan "
"tempat sales order ditulis. Setelah pengeluaran disimpan, nama pelanggan "
"hilang, dan hanya :abbr:`SO (Sales Order)` yang terlihat pada pengeluaran."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/expenses/log_expenses.rst:72
msgid ""
"A customer wishes to have an on-site meeting for the design and installation "
"of a custom building, and agrees to pay for all expenses associated with the "
"meeting, including travel, hotel, and meals for the traveling employees. All "
"expenses tied to that meeting would indicate the sales order for the custom "
"building (which also references the customer) as the :guilabel:`Customer to "
"Reinvoice`."
msgstr ""
"Seorang pelanggan ingin mengadakan pertemuan di lokasi untuk desain dan "
"instalasi bangunan khusus, dan setuju untuk membayar semua biaya yang "
"terkait dengan pertemuan, termasuk perjalanan, hotel, dan makan untuk "
"karyawan yang bepergian. Semua pengeluaran yang terkait dengan pertemuan "
"tersebut akan menunjukkan sales order untuk bangunan khusus (yang juga "
"mereferensikan pelanggan) sebagai :guilabel:`Pelanggan untuk Ditagih Ulang`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/expenses/log_expenses.rst:78
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Analytic Distribution`: Select the account the expense should be "
"written against from the drop-down menu for "
"either :guilabel:`Projects`, :guilabel:`Departments`, or both. Multiple "
"accounts can be listed for each category, if needed. Adjust the percentage "
"for each analytic account by typing in the percentage value next to each "
"account."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Analytic Distribution`: Pilih akun yang harus ditulisi "
"pengeluaran dari menu drop-down untuk :guilabel:`Projects`, "
":guilabel:`Departments`, atau keduanya. Beberapa akun dapat didaftarkan "
"untuk setiap kategori, jika diperlukan. Sesuaikan persentase untuk setiap "
"akun analitik dengan mengetik nilai persentase di sebelah setiap akun."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/expenses/log_expenses.rst:82
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Company`: If in a multi-company database, select the company the "
"expense should be filed for using the drop-down menu. The current company "
"automatically populates this field."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Perusahaan`: Jika dalam database multi-perusahaan, pilih "
"perusahaan tempat pengeluaran harus diajukan menggunakan menu drop-down. "
"Perusahaan saat ini secara otomatis mengisi bidang ini."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/expenses/log_expenses.rst:84
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Notes...`: If any notes are needed to clarify the expense, enter "
"them in the notes field."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Notes...`: Jika ada catatan yang diperlukan untuk menjelaskan "
"pengeluaran, masukkan di kolom catatan."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/expenses/log_expenses.rst:None
msgid "A filled in expense form for a client lunch."
msgstr "Formulir pengeluaran yang telah diisi untuk makan siang klien."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/expenses/log_expenses.rst:91
msgid "Attach receipts"
msgstr "Lampirkan tanda terima"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/expenses/log_expenses.rst:93
msgid ""
"After the expense record is created, the next step is to attach a receipt. "
"Click the :guilabel:`Attach Receipt` button, and a file explorer appears. "
"Navigate to the receipt to be attached, and click :guilabel:`Open`."
msgstr ""
"Setelah catatan pengeluaran dibuat, langkah selanjutnya adalah melampirkan "
"tanda terima. Klik tombol :guilabel:`Attach Receipt`, dan file explorer akan "
"muncul. Navigasi ke tanda terima yang akan dilampirkan, dan klik "
":guilabel:`Open`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/expenses/log_expenses.rst:97
msgid ""
"The new receipt is recorded in the *chatter*, and the number of receipts "
"appears next to the :icon:`fa-paperclip` :guilabel:`(paperclip)` icon. "
"Multiple receipts can be attached to an individual expense record, as needed."
msgstr ""
"Tanda terima baru dicatat di *chatter*, dan jumlah tanda terima muncul di "
"sebelah ikon :icon:`fa-paperclip` :guilabel:`(paperclip)`. Beberapa tanda "
"terima dapat dilampirkan ke catatan pengeluaran individual, sesuai kebutuhan."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/expenses/log_expenses.rst:104
msgid "Upload expenses"
msgstr "Unggah pengeluaran"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/expenses/log_expenses.rst:106
msgid ""
"It is possible to have expense records created automatically "
"by :ref:`uploading a PDF receipt <expenses/upload>`. To utilize this "
"feature, a setting must be enabled, and :abbr:`IAP (in-app purchases)` "
"credits must be purchased."
msgstr ""
"Dimungkinkan untuk membuat catatan pengeluaran secara otomatis dengan "
":ref:`mengunggah tanda terima PDF <expenses/upload>`. Untuk menggunakan "
"fitur ini, pengaturan harus diaktifkan, dan kredit :abbr:`IAP (in-app "
"purchases)` harus dibeli."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/expenses/log_expenses.rst:113
msgid "Digitalization settings"
msgstr "Pengaturan digitalisasi"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/expenses/log_expenses.rst:115
msgid ""
"To enable receipt scanning, navigate to :menuselection:`Expenses app --> "
"Configuration --> Settings`, and tick the checkbox beside "
"the :guilabel:`Expense Digitization (OCR)` option. Then, "
"click :guilabel:`Save`. When enabled, additional options appear. Click on "
"the corresponding radio button to select one of the following options:"
msgstr ""
"Untuk mengaktifkan pemindaian tanda terima, navigasikan ke "
":menuselection:`aplikasi Pengeluaran --> Konfigurasi --> Pengaturan`, dan "
"centang kotak di samping opsi :guilabel:`Digitalisasi Pengeluaran (OCR)`. "
"Kemudian, klik :guilabel:`Simpan`. Ketika diaktifkan, opsi tambahan akan "
"muncul. Klik tombol radio yang sesuai untuk memilih salah satu opsi berikut:"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/expenses/log_expenses.rst:120
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Do not digitize`: Disables receipt digitization but does *not* "
"uninstall the related digitization module."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Jangan digitalisasi`: Menonaktifkan digitalisasi tanda terima "
"tetapi *tidak* menghapus instalasi modul digitalisasi terkait."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/expenses/log_expenses.rst:122
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Digitize on demand only`: Only digitizes receipts when requested. "
"A :guilabel:`Digitize document` button appears on expense records. When "
"clicked, the receipt is scanned and the expense record is updated."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Digitalisasi hanya sesuai permintaan`: Hanya mendigitalisasi "
"tanda terima saat diminta. Tombol :guilabel:`Digitalisasi dokumen` muncul "
"pada catatan pengeluaran. Saat diklik, tanda terima dipindai dan catatan "
"pengeluaran diperbarui."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/expenses/log_expenses.rst:125
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Digitize automatically`: Automatically digitizes all receipts "
"when they are uploaded."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Digitalisasi secara otomatis`: Secara otomatis mendigitalisasi "
"semua tanda terima saat diunggah."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/expenses/log_expenses.rst:127
msgid ""
"Beneath these options are two additional links. Click the :icon:`fa-arrow-"
"right` :guilabel:`Manage Service & Buy Credits` link to view account details "
"and settings, and purchase credits for receipt digitization. Click "
"the :icon:`fa-arrow-right` :guilabel:`View My Services` link to view a list "
"of all current services, and their remaining credit balances."
msgstr ""
"Di bawah opsi ini terdapat dua tautan tambahan. Klik tautan :icon:`fa-arrow-"
"right` :guilabel:`Kelola Layanan & Beli Kredit` untuk melihat detail dan "
"pengaturan akun, dan membeli kredit untuk digitalisasi tanda terima. Klik "
"tautan :icon:`fa-arrow-right` :guilabel:`Lihat Layanan Saya` untuk melihat "
"daftar semua layanan saat ini, dan saldo kredit yang tersisa."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/expenses/log_expenses.rst:132
msgid ""
"For more information on document digitization and :abbr:`IAPs (in-app "
"purchases)`, refer to the :doc:`In-app purchase (IAP) <../../essentials/"
"in_app_purchase>` documentation."
msgstr ""
"Untuk informasi lebih lanjut tentang digitalisasi dokumen dan :abbr:`IAP "
"(pembelian dalam aplikasi)`, lihat dokumentasi :doc:`Pembelian dalam "
"aplikasi (IAP) <../../essentials/in_app_purchase>`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/expenses/log_expenses.rst:136
msgid ""
"When the :guilabel:`Expense Digitization (OCR)` option is enabled, a "
"necessary module is installed, so receipts can be scanned. Disabling this "
"option uninstalls the module."
msgstr ""
"Ketika opsi :guilabel:`Digitalisasi Pengeluaran (OCR)` diaktifkan, modul "
"yang diperlukan akan diinstal sehingga tanda terima dapat dipindai. "
"Menonaktifkan opsi ini akan menghapus instalasi modul."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/expenses/log_expenses.rst:139
msgid ""
"If, at some point, there is a desire to temporarily stop digitizing "
"receipts, select the :guilabel:`Do not digitize` option. The reason this "
"option is available is so the module is not uninstalled, allowing for "
"digitization to be enabled in the future by selecting one of the other two "
"options."
msgstr ""
"Jika, pada suatu saat, ada keinginan untuk sementara menghentikan "
"digitalisasi tanda terima, pilih opsi :guilabel:`Jangan digitalisasi`. "
"Alasan opsi ini tersedia adalah agar modul tidak dihapus instalasinya, "
"sehingga memungkinkan digitalisasi diaktifkan di masa mendatang dengan "
"memilih salah satu dari dua opsi lainnya."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/expenses/log_expenses.rst:147
msgid "Upload receipts"
msgstr "Unggah tanda terima"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/expenses/log_expenses.rst:149
msgid ""
"Open the :guilabel:`Expenses app`, and from the :guilabel:`My Expenses` "
"dashboard, click :guilabel:`Upload`, and a file explorer appears. Navigate "
"to the desired receipt, select it, then click :guilabel:`Open`."
msgstr ""
"Buka :guilabel:`aplikasi Pengeluaran`, dan dari dashboard "
":guilabel:`Pengeluaran Saya`, klik :guilabel:`Unggah`, maka file explorer "
"akan muncul. Navigasikan ke tanda terima yang diinginkan, pilih, lalu klik "
":guilabel:`Buka`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/expenses/log_expenses.rst:153
msgid ""
"The receipt is scanned, and a new expense record is created. "
"The :guilabel:`Expense Date` field is populated with today's date, along "
"with any other fields based on the scanned data, such as "
"the :guilabel:`Total`."
msgstr ""
"Tanda terima dipindai, dan catatan pengeluaran baru dibuat. Bidang "
":guilabel:`Tanggal Pengeluaran` diisi dengan tanggal hari ini, bersama "
"dengan bidang lainnya berdasarkan data yang dipindai, seperti "
":guilabel:`Total`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/expenses/log_expenses.rst:157
msgid ""
"Click on the new entry to open the individual expense form, and make any "
"changes, if needed. The scanned receipt appears in the *chatter*."
msgstr ""
"Klik entri baru untuk membuka formulir pengeluaran individual, dan lakukan "
"perubahan jika diperlukan. Tanda terima yang dipindai muncul di *chatter*."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/expenses/log_expenses.rst:163
msgid "Drag and drop an expense"
msgstr "Seret dan lepas pengeluaran"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/expenses/log_expenses.rst:165
msgid ""
"If :ref:`digitalization is enabled <expenses/digitalization>`, drag and drop "
"a receipt onto the **Expenses** app dashboard. The receipt is scanned and "
"appears by itself on the :guilabel:`Generate Expenses` dashboard."
msgstr ""
"Jika :ref:`digitalisasi diaktifkan <expenses/digitalization>`, seret dan "
"lepas tanda terima ke dashboard aplikasi **Pengeluaran**. Tanda terima "
"dipindai dan muncul sendiri di dashboard :guilabel:`Generate Expenses`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/expenses/log_expenses.rst:169
msgid ""
"Click on the expense record, and modify the details as needed. After changes "
"are made, return to the :guilabel:`My Expenses` dashboard, and the expense "
"now appears in the list."
msgstr ""
"Klik pada catatan pengeluaran, dan modifikasi detail sesuai kebutuhan. "
"Setelah perubahan dilakukan, kembali ke dashboard :guilabel:`My Expenses`, "
"dan pengeluaran sekarang muncul dalam daftar."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/expenses/log_expenses.rst:175
msgid "Email expenses"
msgstr "Email pengeluaran"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/expenses/log_expenses.rst:177
msgid ""
"Instead of individually creating each expense in the **Expenses** app, "
"expenses can be automatically created by sending an email to an email alias."
msgstr ""
"Alih-alih membuat setiap pengeluaran secara individual di aplikasi "
"**Pengeluaran**, pengeluaran dapat dibuat secara otomatis dengan mengirim "
"email ke alias email."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/expenses/log_expenses.rst:181
msgid ""
"For security purposes, only authenticated employee emails are accepted by "
"Odoo when creating an expense from an email. To confirm an authenticated "
"employee email address, go to the employee card in "
"the :menuselection:`Employees app`, and refer to the :guilabel:`Work Email` "
"field."
msgstr ""
"Untuk tujuan keamanan, hanya email karyawan yang terautentikasi yang "
"diterima oleh Odoo saat membuat pengeluaran dari email. Untuk mengonfirmasi "
"alamat email karyawan yang terautentikasi, buka kartu karyawan di "
":menuselection:`aplikasi Karyawan`, dan lihat field :guilabel:`Email Kerja`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/expenses/log_expenses.rst:0
msgid "Create the domain alias by clicking the link."
msgstr "Buat alias domain dengan mengklik tautan."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/expenses/log_expenses.rst:188
msgid ""
"To do so, an email alias must first be configured. Navigate "
"to :menuselection:`Expenses app --> Configuration --> Settings`. Ensure the "
"checkbox beside :guilabel:`Incoming Emails` is ticked. The default email "
"alias is *expense@(domain).com*. Change the email alias by entering the "
"desired email in the field to the right of :guilabel:`Alias`. Then, "
"click :guilabel:`Save`."
msgstr ""
"Untuk melakukannya, alias email harus dikonfigurasi terlebih dahulu. "
"Navigasikan ke :menuselection:`aplikasi Pengeluaran --> Konfigurasi --> "
"Pengaturan`. Pastikan kotak di samping :guilabel:`Email Masuk` dicentang. "
"Alias email default adalah *expense@(domain).com*. Ubah alias email dengan "
"memasukkan email yang diinginkan di bidang di sebelah kanan "
":guilabel:`Alias`. Kemudian, klik :guilabel:`Simpan`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/expenses/log_expenses.rst:194
msgid ""
"If the domain alias needs to be set up, :icon:`fa-arrow-"
"right` :guilabel:`Setup your domain alias` appears beneath "
"the :guilabel:`Incoming Emails` checkbox, instead of the email address field."
msgstr ""
"Jika alias domain perlu disiapkan, :icon:`fa-arrow-right` :guilabel:`Siapkan "
"alias domain Anda` muncul di bawah kotak centang :guilabel:`Email Masuk`, "
"bukan bidang alamat email."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/expenses/log_expenses.rst:198
msgid ""
"Refer to the :doc:`/applications/websites/website/configuration/"
"domain_names` documentation for setup instructions and more information."
msgstr ""
"Lihat dokumentasi :doc:`/applications/websites/website/configuration/"
"domain_names` untuk instruksi pengaturan dan informasi lebih lanjut."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/expenses/log_expenses.rst:201
msgid ""
"Once the domain alias is configured, the email address field is visible "
"beneath the :guilabel:`Incoming Emails` feature on the :guilabel:`Settings` "
"page in the **Expenses** app."
msgstr ""
"Setelah alias domain dikonfigurasi, bidang alamat email terlihat di bawah "
"fitur :guilabel:`Email Masuk` pada halaman :guilabel:`Pengaturan` di "
"aplikasi **Pengeluaran**."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/expenses/log_expenses.rst:204
msgid ""
"Once the email address has been entered, emails can be sent to that alias to "
"create new expenses, without having to be in the Odoo database."
msgstr ""
"Setelah alamat email dimasukkan, email dapat dikirim ke alias tersebut untuk "
"membuat pengeluaran baru, tanpa harus berada di database Odoo."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/expenses/log_expenses.rst:207
msgid ""
"To submit an expense via email, create a new email, and enter the product's "
"*reference* code (if available) and the amount of the expense as the subject "
"of the email. Next, attach the receipt to the email. Odoo creates the "
"expense by taking the information in the email subject, and combining it "
"with the receipt."
msgstr ""
"Untuk mengirimkan pengeluaran melalui email, buat email baru, dan masukkan "
"kode *referensi* produk (jika tersedia) dan jumlah pengeluaran sebagai "
"subjek email. Selanjutnya, lampirkan tanda terima ke email. Odoo membuat "
"pengeluaran dengan mengambil informasi dalam subjek email, dan "
"menggabungkannya dengan tanda terima."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/expenses/log_expenses.rst:213
msgid ""
"To check an expense category's reference code, go "
"to :menuselection:`Expenses app --> Configuration --> Expense Categories`. "
"Reference codes are listed in the :guilabel:`Reference` column."
msgstr ""
"Untuk memeriksa kode referensi kategori pengeluaran, buka "
":menuselection:`Aplikasi Pengeluaran --> Konfigurasi --> Kategori "
"Pengeluaran`. Kode referensi terdaftar di kolom :guilabel:`Referensi`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/expenses/log_expenses.rst:217
msgid ""
"To add a reference code to an expense category, click on the category to "
"open the expense category form. Enter the reference code in "
"the :guilabel:`Reference` field."
msgstr ""
"Untuk menambahkan kode referensi ke kategori pengeluaran, klik pada kategori "
"untuk membuka formulir kategori pengeluaran. Masukkan kode referensi di "
"bidang :guilabel:`Referensi`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/expenses/log_expenses.rst:0
msgid "Reference categories displayed in the main Expense Categories view."
msgstr ""
"Kategori referensi ditampilkan dalam tampilan Kategori Pengeluaran utama."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/expenses/log_expenses.rst:224
msgid ""
"If submitting an expense, via email, for a $25.00 meal during a work trip, "
"the email subject would be `FOOD $25.00`."
msgstr ""
"Jika mengajukan pengeluaran, melalui email, untuk makanan senilai $25,00 "
"selama perjalanan kerja, subjek email akan menjadi `FOOD $25.00`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/expenses/log_expenses.rst:227
msgid "Explanation:"
msgstr "Penjelasan:"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/expenses/log_expenses.rst:229
msgid "The :guilabel:`Reference` for the expense category `Meals` is `FOOD`"
msgstr ":guilabel:`Referensi` untuk kategori pengeluaran `Meals` adalah `FOOD`"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/expenses/log_expenses.rst:230
msgid "The :guilabel:`Cost` for the expense is `$25.00`"
msgstr ":guilabel:`Biaya` untuk pengeluaran adalah `$25.00`"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/expenses/post_expenses.rst:3
msgid "Post expenses"
msgstr "Post pengeluaran"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/expenses/post_expenses.rst:5
msgid ""
"Once an expense is :doc:`approved <../expenses/approve_expenses>`, the next "
"step is to post the expense to the proper accounting journal."
msgstr ""
"Setelah pengeluaran :doc:`disetujui <../expenses/approve_expenses>`, langkah "
"selanjutnya adalah memposting pengeluaran ke jurnal akuntansi yang sesuai."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/expenses/post_expenses.rst:9
msgid ""
"To post an expense to an accounting journal, the user **must** have the "
"following :doc:`access rights <../../general/users/access_rights>`:"
msgstr ""
"Untuk memposting pengeluaran ke jurnal akuntansi, user **harus** memiliki "
":doc:`hak akses <../../general/users/access_rights>` berikut:"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/expenses/post_expenses.rst:12
msgid "Accounting: *Accountant* or *Adviser*"
msgstr "Akuntansi: *Akuntan* atau *Penasihat*"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/expenses/post_expenses.rst:13
msgid "Expenses: *Manager*"
msgstr "Pengeluaran: *Manajer*"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/expenses/post_expenses.rst:15
msgid ""
"Only expenses with an *Approved* status can be posted to a journal. To view "
"all expenses ready to be posted, navigate to :menuselection:`Expenses app --"
"> My Expenses --> Expenses to Process`. Next, to view **only** approved "
"expenses that need to be posted, adjust the filters on the left side so only "
"the :guilabel:`Approved` checkbox is ticked."
msgstr ""
"Hanya pengeluaran dengan status *Disetujui* yang dapat diposting ke jurnal. "
"Untuk melihat semua pengeluaran yang siap diposting, navigasikan ke "
":menuselection:`Aplikasi Pengeluaran --> Pengeluaran Saya --> Pengeluaran "
"yang Harus Diproses`. Selanjutnya, untuk melihat **hanya** pengeluaran yang "
"disetujui yang perlu diposting, sesuaikan filter di sisi kiri sehingga hanya "
"kotak centang :guilabel:`Disetujui` yang dicentang."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/expenses/post_expenses.rst:20
msgid ""
"Expenses can be posted to accounting journals in two "
"ways: :ref:`individually <expenses/post-individual>` or :ref:`in bulk "
"<expenses/post-multiple>`."
msgstr ""
"Pengeluaran dapat diposting ke jurnal akuntansi dengan dua cara: "
":ref:`secara individual <expenses/post-individual>` atau :ref:`secara massal "
"<expenses/post-multiple>`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/expenses/post_expenses.rst:None
msgid ""
"View reports to post by clicking on expense reports, then reports to post."
msgstr ""
"Lihat laporan untuk diposting dengan mengklik laporan pengeluaran, lalu "
"laporan untuk diposting."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/expenses/post_expenses.rst:27
msgid ""
"The default :guilabel:`Expenses to Process` dashboard displays all expenses "
"with a status of :guilabel:`Submitted`."
msgstr ""
"Dashboard :guilabel:`Pengeluaran yang Harus Diproses` default menampilkan "
"semua pengeluaran dengan status :guilabel:`Diajukan`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/expenses/post_expenses.rst:33
msgid "Post individual expenses"
msgstr "Posting pengeluaran individual"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/expenses/post_expenses.rst:35
msgid ""
"To post an individual expense, navigate to :menuselection:`Expenses app --> "
"My Expenses --> Expenses to Process`, and click on an individual expense, to "
"view the detailed expense form. In this view, several options are "
"presented: :guilabel:`Post Journal Entries`, :guilabel:`Report In Next "
"Payslip`, :guilabel:`Refuse`, :guilabel:`Reset`, :guilabel:`Split Expense`, "
"and :guilabel:`Attach Receipt`."
msgstr ""
"Untuk memposting pengeluaran individual, navigasikan ke "
":menuselection:`Aplikasi Pengeluaran --> Pengeluaran Saya --> Pengeluaran "
"yang Harus Diproses`, dan klik pada pengeluaran individual, untuk melihat "
"formulir pengeluaran yang terperinci. Dalam tampilan ini, beberapa opsi "
"disajikan: :guilabel:`Posting Entri Jurnal`, :guilabel:`Laporkan di Slip "
"Gaji Berikutnya`, :guilabel:`Tolak`, :guilabel:`Atur Ulang`, "
":guilabel:`Pisahkan Pengeluaran`, dan :guilabel:`Lampirkan Tanda Terima`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/expenses/post_expenses.rst:40
msgid ""
"Click :guilabel:`Post Journal Entries` and a *Post expenses* pop-up window "
"loads. The default accounting journal for the expense category populates "
"the :guilabel:`Journal` field, but can be modified if needed. The default "
"journal for all expense categories is *Purchases*. Additionally, the date of "
"the expense populates the :guilabel:`Accounting Date` field, indicating when "
"the expense was incurred."
msgstr ""
"Klik :guilabel:`Posting Entri Jurnal` dan jendela pop-up *Posting "
"pengeluaran* akan dimuat. Jurnal akuntansi default untuk kategori "
"pengeluaran mengisi bidang :guilabel:`Jurnal`, tetapi dapat dimodifikasi "
"jika diperlukan. Jurnal default untuk semua kategori pengeluaran adalah "
"*Pembelian*. Selain itu, tanggal pengeluaran mengisi bidang "
":guilabel:`Tanggal Akuntansi`, yang menunjukkan kapan pengeluaran terjadi."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/expenses/post_expenses.rst:46
msgid ""
"Click the :guilabel:`Post Expenses` button, and the journal entry loads, "
"displaying all the details, and has a status of :guilabel:`Posted`."
msgstr ""
"Klik tombol :guilabel:`Posting Pengeluaran`, dan entri jurnal akan dimuat, "
"menampilkan semua detail, dan memiliki status :guilabel:`Diposting`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/expenses/post_expenses.rst:None
msgid "A single expense report to be approved."
msgstr "Satu laporan pengeluaran untuk disetujui."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/expenses/post_expenses.rst:55
msgid "Post multiple expenses"
msgstr "Posting beberapa pengeluaran"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/expenses/post_expenses.rst:57
msgid ""
"To post multiple expenses at once, navigate to :menuselection:`Expenses app "
"--> My Expenses --> Expenses to Process`, then adjust the filters on the "
"left side so only the :guilabel:`Approved` checkbox is ticked. Next, select "
"the expenses to approve by ticking the checkbox next to each expense being "
"approved."
msgstr ""
"Untuk memposting beberapa pengeluaran sekaligus, navigasi ke "
":menuselection:`Aplikasi Pengeluaran --> Pengeluaran Saya --> Pengeluaran "
"yang Akan Diproses`, lalu sesuaikan filter di sisi kiri sehingga hanya kotak "
"centang :guilabel:`Disetujui` yang dicentang. Selanjutnya, pilih pengeluaran "
"yang akan disetujui dengan mencentang kotak centang di samping setiap "
"pengeluaran yang disetujui."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/expenses/post_expenses.rst:62
msgid ""
"Next, click the :guilabel:`Post Entries` button. A *Post Expenses* pop-up "
"window loads, with the default accounting journal :guilabel:`Purchases` "
"populating the :guilabel:`Journal` field, and the expense date populating "
"the :guilabel:`Accounting date` field. Make any necessary modifications, "
"then click :guilabel:`Post Expenses`."
msgstr ""
"Selanjutnya, klik tombol :guilabel:`Posting Entri`. Jendela pop-up *Posting "
"Pengeluaran* dimuat, dengan jurnal akuntansi default :guilabel:`Pembelian` "
"mengisi bidang :guilabel:`Jurnal`, dan tanggal pengeluaran mengisi bidang "
":guilabel:`Tanggal Akuntansi`. Lakukan modifikasi yang diperlukan, lalu klik "
":guilabel:`Posting Pengeluaran`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/expenses/post_expenses.rst:67
msgid ""
"Once posted, the list changes ot show all the various accounting journal "
"entries created. Click on any entry to view the accounting journal details."
msgstr ""
"Setelah diposting, daftar berubah untuk menampilkan semua berbagai entri "
"jurnal akuntansi yang dibuat. Klik entri mana pun untuk melihat detail "
"jurnal akuntansi."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/expenses/post_expenses.rst:71
msgid ""
"Only expenses with a status of :guilabel:`Approved` can be posted to an "
"accounting journal. If an expense is selected that **cannot** be posted, "
"such as an unapproved expense, or the expense has already been posted to a "
"journal, the :guilabel:`Post Entries` button is **not** visible."
msgstr ""
"Hanya pengeluaran dengan status :guilabel:`Disetujui` yang dapat diposting "
"ke jurnal akuntansi. Jika pengeluaran yang dipilih **tidak dapat** "
"diposting, seperti pengeluaran yang belum disetujui, atau pengeluaran telah "
"diposting ke jurnal, tombol :guilabel:`Posting Entri` **tidak** terlihat."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/expenses/post_expenses.rst:None
msgid ""
"Post multiple reports at a time from the Expense Reports view, with the "
"Approved filter."
msgstr ""
"Posting beberapa laporan sekaligus dari tampilan Laporan Pengeluaran, dengan "
"filter Disetujui."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/expenses/reimburse.rst:3
msgid "Reimburse employees"
msgstr "Reimburse karyawan"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/expenses/reimburse.rst:5
msgid ""
"After an expense is :doc:`posted to an accounting journal <../expenses/"
"post_expenses>`, the next step is to reimburse the employee. Employees can "
"be reimbursed :ref:`directly in their paychecks <expenses/reimburse-"
"payslip>`, or an individual expense can be :ref:`reimbursed via cash, check, "
"or direct deposit <expenses/reimburse-single>`."
msgstr ""
"Setelah pengeluaran :doc:`diposting ke jurnal akuntansi <../expenses/"
"post_expenses>`, langkah selanjutnya adalah mengganti biaya karyawan. "
"Karyawan dapat diganti biayanya :ref:`langsung di slip gaji mereka <expenses/"
"reimburse-payslip>`, atau pengeluaran individual dapat :ref:`diganti "
"biayanya melalui tunai, cek, atau setoran langsung <expenses/reimburse-"
"single>`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/expenses/reimburse.rst:13
msgid "Reimbursement settings"
msgstr "Pengaturan penggantian biaya"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/expenses/reimburse.rst:15
msgid ""
"Reimbursements can be paid via a paycheck, check, cash, or bank transfer "
"(usually referred to as direct deposit). To set up payment options, first "
"configure the various settings by navigating to the :menuselection:`Expenses "
"app --> Configuration --> Settings`."
msgstr ""
"Penggantian biaya dapat dibayarkan melalui slip gaji, cek, tunai, atau "
"transfer bank (biasanya disebut sebagai setoran langsung). Untuk mengatur "
"opsi pembayaran, pertama konfigurasikan berbagai pengaturan dengan "
"menavigasi ke :menuselection:`Aplikasi Pengeluaran --> Konfigurasi --> "
"Pengaturan`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/expenses/reimburse.rst:19
msgid ""
"To reimburse employees for expenses :ref:`in their paychecks <expenses/"
"reimburse-payslip>`, tick the checkbox beside the :guilabel:`Reimburse in "
"Payslip` option in the :guilabel:`Expenses` section."
msgstr ""
"Untuk mereimburse karyawan atas pengeluaran :ref:`di slip gaji mereka "
"<expenses/reimburse-payslip>`, centang kotak di samping opsi "
":guilabel:`Reimburse di Slip Gaji` di bagian :guilabel:`Pengeluaran`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/expenses/reimburse.rst:22
msgid ""
"Next, set how payments are made in the :guilabel:`Accounting` section. Click "
"the drop-down menu under :guilabel:`Payment Methods`, and select the desired "
"payment option. The default options include paying by :guilabel:`Manual "
"Payment (Bank)`, :guilabel:`Batch Deposit (Bank)`, and :guilabel:`Checks "
"(Bank)`. Depending on the installed :doc:`payroll localization <../../hr/"
"payroll/payroll_localizations>`, additional options may appear."
msgstr ""
"Selanjutnya, atur cara pembayaran dilakukan di bagian :guilabel:`Akuntansi`. "
"Klik menu drop-down di bawah :guilabel:`Metode Pembayaran`, dan pilih opsi "
"pembayaran yang diinginkan. Opsi default termasuk membayar dengan "
":guilabel:`Pembayaran Manual (Bank)`, :guilabel:`Setoran Batch (Bank)`, dan "
":guilabel:`Cek (Bank)`. Tergantung pada :doc:`lokalisasi payroll <../../hr/"
"payroll/payroll_localizations>` yang diinstal, opsi tambahan mungkin muncul."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/expenses/reimburse.rst:28
msgid ""
"Leaving this field blank allows for **all** available payment options to be "
"used."
msgstr ""
"Membiarkan bidang ini kosong memungkinkan **semua** opsi pembayaran yang "
"tersedia untuk digunakan."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/expenses/reimburse.rst:30
msgid ""
"When all desired configurations are complete, click :guilabel:`Save` to "
"activate the settings."
msgstr ""
"Ketika semua konfigurasi yang diinginkan selesai, klik :guilabel:`Simpan` "
"untuk mengaktifkan pengaturan."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/expenses/reimburse.rst:35
msgid "Reimburse in payslips"
msgstr "Ganti dalam slip gaji"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/expenses/reimburse.rst:37
msgid ""
"If the  *Reimburse in Payslip* option is activated on the :ref:`settings "
"<expenses/reimburse-settings>` page, payments can be added to the employee's "
"next payslip, instead of issuing separate payments."
msgstr ""
"Jika opsi *Reimburse in Payslip* diaktifkan pada halaman :ref:`pengaturan "
"<expenses/reimburse-settings>`, pembayaran dapat ditambahkan ke slip gaji "
"karyawan berikutnya, alih-alih mengeluarkan pembayaran terpisah."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/expenses/reimburse.rst:42
msgid ""
"Only expenses with a status of :guilabel:`Approved` and :guilabel:`Posted` "
"are able to be reimbursed in a payslip. If an expense with a different "
"status is selected, a warning appears when attempting to repay the expense "
"in a payslip."
msgstr ""
"Hanya pengeluaran dengan status :guilabel:`Disetujui` dan "
":guilabel:`Diposting` yang dapat diganti biayanya di slip gaji. Jika "
"pengeluaran dengan status berbeda dipilih, peringatan muncul saat mencoba "
"mengganti biaya pengeluaran di slip gaji."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/expenses/reimburse.rst:47
msgid ":doc:`Payslips <../../hr/payroll/payslips>`"
msgstr ":doc:`Slip Gaji <../../hr/payroll/payslips>`"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/expenses/reimburse.rst:52
msgid "Reimburse individually"
msgstr "Reimburse secara individual"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/expenses/reimburse.rst:54
msgid ""
"Navigate to :menuselection:`Expenses app --> My Expenses --> Expenses to "
"Process`, and click on an expense with a :guilabel:`Status` "
"of :guilabel:`Approved` or :guilabel:`Posted`."
msgstr ""
"Navigasi ke :menuselection:`Aplikasi Pengeluaran --> Pengeluaran Saya --> "
"Pengeluaran yang Akan Diproses`, dan klik pengeluaran dengan "
":guilabel:`Status` :guilabel:`Disetujui` atau :guilabel:`Diposting`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/expenses/reimburse.rst:57
msgid ""
"On the individual expense, click the :guilabel:`Report in Next Payslip` "
"button. A message is logged in the chatter stating the `Expense (\"Expense "
"Name\") will be added to the next payslip.` The status for the expense "
"remains unchanged, but changes to :guilabel:`Posted` when the journal entry "
"is posted, then :guilabel:`Paid` when the related payslip is processed."
msgstr ""
"Pada pengeluaran individual, klik tombol :guilabel:`Laporkan di Slip Gaji "
"Berikutnya`. Pesan dicatat di chatter yang menyatakan `Pengeluaran (\"Nama "
"Pengeluaran\") akan ditambahkan ke slip gaji berikutnya.` Status untuk "
"pengeluaran tetap tidak berubah, tetapi berubah menjadi "
":guilabel:`Diposting` ketika entri jurnal diposting, kemudian "
":guilabel:`Dibayar` ketika slip gaji terkait diproses."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/expenses/reimburse.rst:62
msgid ""
"If the expense is repaid in another manner before the payslip is processed, "
"the expense can be removed from the payslip by clicking "
"the :guilabel:`Remove from Payslip` button."
msgstr ""
"Jika pengeluaran diganti biayanya dengan cara lain sebelum slip gaji "
"diproses, pengeluaran dapat dihapus dari slip gaji dengan mengklik tombol "
":guilabel:`Hapus dari Slip Gaji`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/expenses/reimburse.rst:None
msgid "The Report in Next Payslip button, visible on an expense."
msgstr "Tombol Laporkan di Slip Gaji Berikutnya, terlihat pada pengeluaran."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/expenses/reimburse.rst:71
msgid "Reimburse in bulk"
msgstr "Reimburse dalam jumlah besar"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/expenses/reimburse.rst:73
msgid ""
"Navigate to :menuselection:`Expenses app --> My Expenses --> Expenses to "
"Process`, and click the checkbox next to all the expenses being reimbursed."
msgstr ""
"Navigasi ke :menuselection:`Aplikasi Pengeluaran --> Pengeluaran Saya --> "
"Pengeluaran yang Akan Diproses`, dan klik kotak centang di samping semua "
"pengeluaran yang akan diganti biayanya."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/expenses/reimburse.rst:77
msgid ""
"To select *all* reimbursable expenses, adjust the side menu so that "
"only :guilabel:`Approved` or :guilabel:`Posted` are checked. Next, click the "
"checkbox next to :guilabel:`Employee` to select all expenses."
msgstr ""
"Untuk memilih *semua* pengeluaran yang dapat diganti biayanya, sesuaikan "
"menu samping sehingga hanya :guilabel:`Disetujui` atau :guilabel:`Diposting` "
"yang dicentang. Selanjutnya, klik kotak centang di samping "
":guilabel:`Karyawan` untuk memilih semua pengeluaran."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/expenses/reimburse.rst:81
msgid ""
"Click the :icon:`fa-gear` :guilabel:`Actions` button, then "
"select :guilabel:`Report in Next Payslip` from the resulting drop-down "
"menu. :guilabel:`Report in Next Payslip` button, and the expenses are all "
"added to the next payslip issued for the corresponding employee."
msgstr ""
"Klik tombol :icon:`fa-gear` :guilabel:`Tindakan`, lalu pilih "
":guilabel:`Laporkan di Slip Gaji Berikutnya` dari menu drop-down yang "
"muncul. Tombol :guilabel:`Laporkan di Slip Gaji Berikutnya`, dan pengeluaran "
"semua ditambahkan ke slip gaji berikutnya yang dikeluarkan untuk karyawan "
"terkait."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/expenses/reimburse.rst:85
msgid ""
"Nothing changes on the :guilabel:`Expenses to Process` dashboard, but a "
"message is logged in the chatter of each individual expense stating the "
"`Expense (\"Expense Name\") will be added to the next payslip.` The status "
"for the individual expenses remains unchanged, but changes "
"to :guilabel:`Posted` when the journal entry is posted, "
"then :guilabel:`Paid` when the related payslip is processed."
msgstr ""
"Tidak ada yang berubah pada dashboard :guilabel:`Pengeluaran yang Akan "
"Diproses`, tetapi pesan dicatat di chatter dari setiap pengeluaran "
"individual yang menyatakan `Pengeluaran (\"Nama Pengeluaran\") akan "
"ditambahkan ke slip gaji berikutnya.` Status untuk pengeluaran individual "
"tetap tidak berubah, tetapi berubah menjadi :guilabel:`Diposting` ketika "
"entri jurnal diposting, kemudian :guilabel:`Dibayar` ketika slip gaji "
"terkait diproses."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/expenses/reimburse.rst:94
msgid "Reimburse expenses via cash, check, or direct deposit"
msgstr "Ganti biaya pengeluaran melalui tunai, cek, atau setoran langsung"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/expenses/reimburse.rst:96
msgid ""
"To reimburse an individual expense, navigate to the :menuselection:`Expenses "
"app --> My Expenses --> Expenses to Process`, and the :guilabel:`Expenses to "
"Process` dashboard appears, displaying all :guilabel:`Submitted` expenses. "
"Adjust the side menu to display only :guilabel:`Posted` expenses."
msgstr ""
"Untuk mengganti biaya pengeluaran individual, navigasi ke "
":menuselection:`Aplikasi Pengeluaran --> Pengeluaran Saya --> Pengeluaran "
"yang Akan Diproses`, dan dashboard :guilabel:`Pengeluaran yang Akan "
"Diproses` muncul, menampilkan semua pengeluaran :guilabel:`Diajukan`. "
"Sesuaikan menu samping untuk menampilkan hanya pengeluaran "
":guilabel:`Diposting`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/expenses/reimburse.rst:101
msgid ""
"Only expenses that have been :doc:`posted to an accounting journal "
"<post_expenses>` (expenses with a status of :guilabel:`Posted`) can be "
"reimbursed."
msgstr ""
"Hanya pengeluaran yang telah :doc:`diposting ke jurnal akuntansi "
"<post_expenses>` (pengeluaran dengan status :guilabel:`Diposting`) yang "
"dapat diganti biayanya."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/expenses/reimburse.rst:104
msgid ""
"Click the expense to pay, then click the :icon:`fa-bars` :guilabel:`Journal "
"Entry` smart button. On the journal entry, click the :guilabel:`Pay` button. "
"In the *Pay* pop-up window, enter the following information in the pop-up "
"window:"
msgstr ""
"Klik pengeluaran yang akan dibayar, lalu klik tombol pintar :icon:`fa-bars` "
":guilabel:`Entri Jurnal`. Pada entri jurnal, klik tombol :guilabel:`Bayar`. "
"Di jendela pop-up *Bayar*, masukkan informasi berikut:"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/expenses/reimburse.rst:108
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Journal`: Select the accounting journal to post the payment using "
"the drop-down menu. The default journal is :guilabel:`Bank`."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Jurnal`: Pilih jurnal akuntansi untuk memposting pembayaran "
"menggunakan menu drop-down. Jurnal default adalah :guilabel:`Bank`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/expenses/reimburse.rst:110
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Payment Method`: Select how the payment is made using the drop-"
"down menu. If :guilabel:`Cash` is selected for the :guilabel:`Journal`, the "
"only option available is :guilabel:`Manual Payment`. If :guilabel:`Bank` is "
"selected for the :guilabel:`Journal`, the default options "
"are :guilabel:`Manual Payment` or :guilabel:`Checks`."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Metode Pembayaran`: Pilih cara pembayaran dilakukan menggunakan "
"menu drop-down. Jika :guilabel:`Tunai` dipilih untuk :guilabel:`Jurnal`, "
"satu-satunya opsi yang tersedia adalah :guilabel:`Pembayaran Manual`. Jika "
":guilabel:`Bank` dipilih untuk :guilabel:`Jurnal`, opsi default adalah "
":guilabel:`Pembayaran Manual` atau :guilabel:`Cek`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/expenses/reimburse.rst:114
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Recipient Bank Account`: This field only appears if "
"the :guilabel:`Journal` is set to :guilabel:`Bank`, and "
"the :guilabel:`Payment Method` is set to :guilabel:`Manual Payment`. The "
"employee's :ref:`bank account <employees/private-info>` populates this "
"field, by default. If the employee has more than one trusted bank account on "
"their employee profile, use the drop-down menu to select the desired bank "
"account."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Rekening Bank Penerima`: Bidang ini hanya muncul jika "
":guilabel:`Jurnal` diatur ke :guilabel:`Bank`, dan :guilabel:`Metode "
"Pembayaran` diatur ke :guilabel:`Pembayaran Manual`. :ref:`Rekening bank "
"<employees/private-info>` karyawan mengisi bidang ini secara default. Jika "
"karyawan memiliki lebih dari satu rekening bank terpercaya di profil "
"karyawan mereka, gunakan menu drop-down untuk memilih rekening bank yang "
"diinginkan."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/expenses/reimburse.rst:119
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Amount`: The total amount being reimbursed populates this field "
"by default."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Jumlah`: Total jumlah yang akan diganti mengisi bidang ini secara "
"default."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/expenses/reimburse.rst:120
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Payment Date`: Enter the date the payment is issued in this "
"field. The current date populates this field by default."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Tanggal Pembayaran`: Masukkan tanggal pembayaran dikeluarkan di "
"bidang ini. Tanggal saat ini mengisi bidang ini secara default."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/expenses/reimburse.rst:122
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Memo`: The text entered in the :guilabel:`Description` field of "
"the expense form populates this field by default."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Memo`: Teks yang dimasukkan di bidang :guilabel:`Deskripsi` pada "
"formulir pengeluaran mengisi bidang ini secara default."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/expenses/reimburse.rst:125
msgid ""
"When the fields of the pop-up window are completed, click "
"the :guilabel:`Create Payment` button to register the payment, and reimburse "
"the employee. A green :guilabel:`Paid` banner now appears on the journal "
"entry."
msgstr ""
"Setelah bidang-bidang di jendela pop-up dilengkapi, klik tombol "
":guilabel:`Buat Pembayaran` untuk mencatat pembayaran dan mengganti biaya "
"karyawan. Spanduk hijau :guilabel:`Dibayar` sekarang muncul pada entri "
"jurnal."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/expenses/reimburse.rst:None
msgid ""
"The Register Payment pop-up window filled out for an individual expense "
"report\n"
"reimbursement."
msgstr ""
"Jendela pop-up Daftarkan Pembayaran yang diisi untuk reimbursement laporan "
"pengeluaran individual."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/expenses/reinvoice_expenses.rst:3
msgid "Reinvoice expenses"
msgstr "Tagih ulang pengeluaran"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/expenses/reinvoice_expenses.rst:5
msgid ""
"If expenses are tracked on customer projects, they can be automatically "
"charged back to the customer. This is done by :ref:`logging an expense "
"<expenses/reinvoice-create>`, referencing the corresponding sales order, and "
"then :ref:`creating an expense report <expenses/reinvoice-expense-report>`."
msgstr ""
"Jika pengeluaran dilacak pada proyek pelanggan, pengeluaran tersebut dapat "
"secara otomatis ditagihkan kembali ke pelanggan. Ini dilakukan dengan "
":ref:`mencatat pengeluaran <expenses/reinvoice-create>`, merujuk sales order "
"yang sesuai, kemudian :ref:`membuat laporan pengeluaran <expenses/reinvoice-"
"expense-report>`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/expenses/reinvoice_expenses.rst:10
msgid ""
"Next, managers :ref:`approve the expense report <expenses/reinvoice-"
"approve>`, then the accounting department :ref:`post the journal entries "
"<expenses/reinvoice-approve>`."
msgstr ""
"Selanjutnya, manajer :ref:`menyetujui laporan pengeluaran <expenses/"
"reinvoice-approve>`, kemudian departemen akuntansi :ref:`memposting entri "
"jurnal <expenses/reinvoice-approve>`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/expenses/reinvoice_expenses.rst:13
msgid ""
"Finally, once the expense report is posted to a journal, the expenses appear "
"on the specified :abbr:`SO (Sales Order)`. When the :abbr:`SO (Sales Order)` "
"is :ref:`invoiced <expenses/reinvoice>`, the customer is charged for the "
"expenses."
msgstr ""
"Akhirnya, setelah laporan pengeluaran diposting ke jurnal, pengeluaran "
"muncul pada :abbr:`SO (Sales Order)` yang ditentukan. Ketika :abbr:`SO "
"(Sales Order)` :ref:`ditagih <expenses/reinvoice>`, pelanggan dikenakan "
"biaya untuk pengeluaran tersebut."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/expenses/reinvoice_expenses.rst:18
msgid ""
"Approving expenses, posting expenses to accounting, and reinvoicing expenses "
"on :abbr:`SOs (Sales Orders)` is **only** possible for users with the "
"appropriate :doc:`access rights <../../general/users/access_rights>`."
msgstr ""
"Menyetujui pengeluaran, memposting pengeluaran ke akuntansi, dan menginvoice "
"ulang pengeluaran pada :abbr:`SO (Sales Order)` **hanya** dimungkinkan untuk "
"pengguna dengan :doc:`hak akses <../../general/users/access_rights>` yang "
"sesuai."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/expenses/reinvoice_expenses.rst:23
msgid ""
"This document provides lower-level instructions for the creation, "
"submission, approval, and posting of expenses. For fully-detailed "
"instructions for any of these steps, refer to the following documentation:"
msgstr ""
"Dokumen ini menyediakan instruksi tingkat rendah untuk pembuatan, pengajuan, "
"persetujuan, dan posting pengeluaran. Untuk instruksi lengkap dari salah "
"satu langkah ini, lihat dokumentasi berikut:"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/expenses/reinvoice_expenses.rst:27
msgid ":doc:`Log expenses <../expenses/log_expenses>`"
msgstr ":doc:`Catat pengeluaran <../expenses/log_expenses>`"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/expenses/reinvoice_expenses.rst:28
msgid ":doc:`Submit expenses <../expenses/submit_expenses>`"
msgstr ":doc:`Ajukan pengeluaran <../expenses/submit_expenses>`"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/expenses/reinvoice_expenses.rst:29
msgid ":doc:`Approve expenses <../expenses/approve_expenses>`"
msgstr ":doc:`Setujui pengeluaran <../expenses/approve_expenses>`"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/expenses/reinvoice_expenses.rst:30
msgid ":doc:`Post expenses <../expenses/post_expenses>`"
msgstr ":doc:`Posting pengeluaran <../expenses/post_expenses>`"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/expenses/reinvoice_expenses.rst:33
#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/india.rst:108
#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/india.rst:267
#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/mexico.rst:1042
msgid "Setup"
msgstr "Setup"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/expenses/reinvoice_expenses.rst:35
msgid ""
"First, specify the invoicing policy for each expense category. Navigate "
"to :menuselection:`Expenses app --> Configuration --> Expense Categories`. "
"Click on an expense category to view the expense category form. Under "
"the :guilabel:`INVOICING` section, click the radio button next to the "
"desired selection for :guilabel:`Re-Invoice costs`:"
msgstr ""
"Pertama, tentukan kebijakan penagihan untuk setiap kategori pengeluaran. "
"Navigasi ke :menuselection:`Aplikasi Pengeluaran --> Konfigurasi --> "
"Kategori Pengeluaran`. Klik pada kategori pengeluaran untuk melihat formulir "
"kategori pengeluaran. Di bawah bagian :guilabel:`PENAGIHAN`, klik tombol "
"radio di sebelah pilihan yang diinginkan untuk :guilabel:`Biaya Tagih Ulang`:"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/expenses/reinvoice_expenses.rst:40
msgid ":guilabel:`No`: The expense category **cannot** be reinvoiced."
msgstr ":guilabel:`Tidak`: Kategori pengeluaran **tidak dapat** ditagih ulang."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/expenses/reinvoice_expenses.rst:41
msgid ""
":guilabel:`At cost`: The expense category invoices expenses at "
"the :guilabel:`Cost` set on the expense category form."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Pada harga pokok`: Kategori pengeluaran menagih pengeluaran pada "
":guilabel:`Harga Pokok` yang ditetapkan pada formulir kategori pengeluaran."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/expenses/reinvoice_expenses.rst:43
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Sales price`: The expense category invoices at "
"the :guilabel:`Sales Price` set on the expense form."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Harga jual`: Kategori pengeluaran menagih pada :guilabel:`Harga "
"Jual` yang ditetapkan pada formulir pengeluaran."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/expenses/reinvoice_expenses.rst:49
msgid "Log an expense"
msgstr "Catat pengeluaran"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/expenses/reinvoice_expenses.rst:51
msgid ""
"First, when :doc:`creating a new expense <../expenses/log_expenses>`, the "
"correct information needs to be entered to reinvoice the expense to a "
"customer. Using the drop-down menu, select the :abbr:`SO (Sales Order)` to "
"add the expense to in the :guilabel:`Customer to Reinvoice` field."
msgstr ""
"Pertama, ketika :doc:`membuat pengeluaran baru <../expenses/log_expenses>`, "
"informasi yang benar perlu dimasukkan untuk menagih ulang pengeluaran ke "
"pelanggan. Menggunakan menu drop-down, pilih :abbr:`SO (Sales Order)` untuk "
"menambahkan pengeluaran pada bidang :guilabel:`Pelanggan untuk Ditagih "
"Ulang`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/expenses/reinvoice_expenses.rst:55
msgid ""
"Next, select the :guilabel:`Analytic Distribution` the expense is posted to. "
"The options available are pulled from the **Projects** app."
msgstr ""
"Selanjutnya, pilih :guilabel:`Distribusi Analitik` tempat pengeluaran "
"diposting. Opsi yang tersedia diambil dari aplikasi **Projects**."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/expenses/reinvoice_expenses.rst:58
msgid ""
"Multiple projects can be selected, if desired. To add "
"another :guilabel:`Analytic Distribution`, click on the line to reveal "
"the :guilabel:`Analytic` pop-over window. Click :guilabel:`Add a line`, then "
"select the desired :guilabel:`Analytic Distribution` from the drop-down menu."
msgstr ""
"Beberapa proyek dapat dipilih, jika diinginkan. Untuk menambahkan "
":guilabel:`Distribusi Analitik` lain, klik pada baris untuk menampilkan "
"jendela pop-over :guilabel:`Analitik`. Klik :guilabel:`Tambahkan baris`, "
"kemudian pilih :guilabel:`Distribusi Analitik` yang diinginkan dari menu "
"drop-down."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/expenses/reinvoice_expenses.rst:None
msgid ""
"An expense entry to reinvoice a project to the customer, for the gallery "
"seating project."
msgstr ""
"Entri pengeluaran untuk menagih ulang project kepada pelanggan, untuk "
"project galeri tempat duduk."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/expenses/reinvoice_expenses.rst:66
msgid ""
"If selecting more than one :guilabel:`Analytic Distribution`, "
"the :guilabel:`Percentage` fields **must** be modified. Both fields are "
"populated with `100%`, by default. Adjust the percentages for all the "
"fields, so the total of all selected accounts equals `100%`."
msgstr ""
"Jika memilih lebih dari satu :guilabel:`Distribusi Analitik`, kolom "
":guilabel:`Persentase` **harus** dimodifikasi. Kedua kolom diisi dengan "
"`100%` secara default. Sesuaikan persentase untuk semua kolom, sehingga "
"total semua akun yang dipilih sama dengan `100%`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/expenses/reinvoice_expenses.rst:71
msgid ""
"A furniture company is building seating for two different locations for one "
"client. The client agrees to pay for all travel expenses for site visits "
"related to these two projects. The furniture company plans one trip to visit "
"*both* locations."
msgstr ""
"Sebuah perusahaan furnitur sedang membangun tempat duduk untuk dua lokasi "
"berbeda untuk satu klien. Klien setuju untuk membayar semua biaya perjalanan "
"untuk kunjungan lokasi terkait dengan dua project ini. Perusahaan furnitur "
"merencanakan satu perjalanan untuk mengunjungi *kedua* lokasi."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/expenses/reinvoice_expenses.rst:75
msgid ""
"When creating the expenses for travel expenses, **both projects** are listed "
"in the :guilabel:`Analytic Distribution` line, for 50% each."
msgstr ""
"Saat membuat pengeluaran untuk biaya perjalanan, **kedua project** tercantum "
"pada baris :guilabel:`Distribusi Analitik`, masing-masing 50%."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/expenses/reinvoice_expenses.rst:81
msgid "Create an expense report"
msgstr "Buat laporan pengeluaran"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/expenses/reinvoice_expenses.rst:83
msgid ""
"After the expenses are created, the expense report must be created and "
"submitted, in the same manner as all other expenses."
msgstr ""
"Setelah pengeluaran dibuat, laporan pengeluaran harus dibuat dan diajukan, "
"dengan cara yang sama seperti semua pengeluaran lainnya."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/expenses/reinvoice_expenses.rst:86
msgid ""
"Once the expense report is submitted, a :icon:`fa-money` :guilabel:`Sales "
"Orders` smart button appears at the top-center of both the expense report, "
"and each individual expense record being reinvoiced."
msgstr ""
"Setelah laporan pengeluaran diajukan, tombol pintar :icon:`fa-money` "
":guilabel:`Sales Order` muncul di bagian tengah atas laporan pengeluaran, "
"dan setiap catatan pengeluaran individual yang diinvoice ulang."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/expenses/reinvoice_expenses.rst:91
msgid ""
"Selecting the proper :abbr:`SO (Sales Order)` in the :guilabel:`Customer to "
"Reinvoice` field is **critical**, since this is how expenses are "
"automatically invoiced after an expense report is approved."
msgstr ""
"Memilih :abbr:`SO (Sales Order)` yang tepat di field :guilabel:`Pelanggan "
"untuk Diinvoice Ulang` sangat **penting**, karena ini adalah cara "
"pengeluaran diinvoice secara otomatis setelah laporan pengeluaran disetujui."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/expenses/reinvoice_expenses.rst:95
msgid ""
"The :guilabel:`Customer to Reinvoice` field can be modified *only* until an "
"expense report is **approved**. After an expense report is approved, "
"the :guilabel:`Customer to Reinvoice` field is no longer able to be modified."
msgstr ""
"Field :guilabel:`Pelanggan untuk Diinvoice Ulang` dapat dimodifikasi *hanya* "
"sampai laporan pengeluaran **disetujui**. Setelah laporan pengeluaran "
"disetujui, field :guilabel:`Pelanggan untuk Diinvoice Ulang` tidak dapat "
"lagi dimodifikasi."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/expenses/reinvoice_expenses.rst:None
msgid "An expense report with a sales order smart button for reinvoicing."
msgstr ""
"Laporan pengeluaran dengan tombol pintar sales order untuk penagihan ulang."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/expenses/reinvoice_expenses.rst:105
msgid "Approve and post expenses"
msgstr "Setujui dan posting pengeluaran"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/expenses/reinvoice_expenses.rst:107
msgid ""
"Before :doc:`approving an expense report <../expenses/approve_expenses>`, "
"ensure the :guilabel:`Analytic Distribution` section is populated for every "
"relevant expense line."
msgstr ""
"Sebelum :doc:`menyetujui laporan pengeluaran <../expenses/approve_expenses>"
"`, pastikan bagian :guilabel:`Distribusi Analitik` terisi untuk setiap baris "
"pengeluaran yang relevan."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/expenses/reinvoice_expenses.rst:110
msgid ""
"If an :guilabel:`Analytic Distribution` entry is missing, assign the correct "
"accounts from the drop-down menu, then click :guilabel:`Approve`."
msgstr ""
"Jika entri :guilabel:`Distribusi Analitik` tidak ada, tetapkan akun yang "
"benar dari menu drop-down, lalu klik :guilabel:`Setujui`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/expenses/reinvoice_expenses.rst:114
msgid ""
"The :guilabel:`Approve` button **only** appears after an expense report has "
"been submitted."
msgstr ""
"Tombol :guilabel:`Setujui` **hanya** muncul setelah laporan pengeluaran "
"diajukan."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/expenses/reinvoice_expenses.rst:116
msgid ""
"The accounting department is typically responsible for :doc:`posting journal "
"entries <../expenses/post_expenses>`. To post expenses to an accounting "
"journal, click :guilabel:`Post Journal Entries`. Once an expense report is "
"approved, it can then be posted."
msgstr ""
"Departemen akuntansi biasanya bertanggung jawab untuk :doc:`memposting entri "
"jurnal <../expenses/post_expenses>`. Untuk memposting pengeluaran ke jurnal "
"akuntansi, klik :guilabel:`Posting Entri Jurnal`. Setelah laporan "
"pengeluaran disetujui, laporan tersebut dapat diposting."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/expenses/reinvoice_expenses.rst:120
msgid ""
"The :abbr:`SO (Sales Order)` is **only** updated *after* the journal entries "
"are posted. Once the journal entries are posted, the expenses now appear on "
"the referenced :abbr:`SO (Sales Order)`."
msgstr ""
":abbr:`SO (Sales Order)` **hanya** diperbarui *setelah* entri jurnal "
"diposting. Setelah entri jurnal diposting, pengeluaran sekarang muncul pada "
":abbr:`SO (Sales Order)` yang direferensikan."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/expenses/reinvoice_expenses.rst:126
msgid "Invoice expenses"
msgstr "Invoice pengeluaran"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/expenses/reinvoice_expenses.rst:128
msgid ""
"After the expense report has been approved, and the journal entries have "
"been posted, the :abbr:`SO (Sales Order)` is updated, and the customer can "
"be invoiced."
msgstr ""
"Setelah laporan pengeluaran disetujui, dan entri jurnal telah diposting, "
":abbr:`SO (Sales Order)` diperbarui, dan pelanggan dapat ditagih."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/expenses/reinvoice_expenses.rst:131
msgid ""
"Navigate to the expense report, and click the :icon:`fa-"
"money` :guilabel:`Sales Orders` smart button to open the :abbr:`SO (Sales "
"Order)`. The expenses to be reinvoiced now appear on the :abbr:`SO (Sales "
"Order)`."
msgstr ""
"Navigasi ke laporan pengeluaran, dan klik tombol pintar :icon:`fa-money` "
":guilabel:`Sales Order` untuk membuka :abbr:`SO (Sales Order)`. Pengeluaran "
"yang akan ditagih ulang sekarang muncul pada :abbr:`SO (Sales Order)`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/expenses/reinvoice_expenses.rst:136
msgid ""
"More than one :abbr:`SO (Sales Order)` can be referenced on an expense "
"report. If more than one :abbr:`SO (Sales Order)` is referenced, clicking "
"the :guilabel:`Sales Orders` smart button opens a list displaying all "
"the :abbr:`SOs (Sales Order)` associated with that expense report. Click on "
"a :abbr:`SO (Sales Order)` to open the individual :abbr:`SO (Sales Order)` "
"details."
msgstr ""
"Lebih dari satu :abbr:`SO (Sales Order)` dapat direferensikan pada laporan "
"pengeluaran. Jika lebih dari satu :abbr:`SO (Sales Order)` direferensikan, "
"klik tombol pintar :guilabel:`Sales Orders` untuk membuka daftar yang "
"menampilkan semua :abbr:`SO (Sales Order)` yang terkait dengan laporan "
"pengeluaran tersebut. Klik pada :abbr:`SO (Sales Order)` untuk membuka "
"detail :abbr:`SO (Sales Order)` individual."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/expenses/reinvoice_expenses.rst:141
msgid ""
"The expenses are listed in the :abbr:`SO (Sales Order)` :guilabel:`Order "
"Lines` tab."
msgstr ""
"Pengeluaran terdaftar di tab :abbr:`SO (Sales Order)` :guilabel:`Baris "
"Pesanan`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/expenses/reinvoice_expenses.rst:143
msgid ""
"Next, click :guilabel:`Create Invoice`, and a :guilabel:`Create invoices` "
"pop-up window appears. Select if the invoice is a :guilabel:`Regular "
"invoice`, a :guilabel:`Down payment (percentage)`, or a :guilabel:`Down "
"payment (fixed amount)`. Then, click :guilabel:`Create Draft`. Doing so "
"creates a draft invoice for the customer. Click :guilabel:`Confirm` to "
"confirm the invoice, and the customer is invoiced for the expenses."
msgstr ""
"Selanjutnya, klik :guilabel:`Buat Invoice`, dan jendela pop-up "
":guilabel:`Buat invoice` akan muncul. Pilih apakah invoice tersebut adalah "
":guilabel:`Invoice reguler`, :guilabel:`Uang muka (persentase)`, atau "
":guilabel:`Uang muka (jumlah tetap)`. Kemudian, klik :guilabel:`Buat Draft`. "
"Dengan melakukan ini akan membuat draft invoice untuk pelanggan. Klik "
":guilabel:`Konfirmasi` untuk mengonfirmasi invoice, dan pelanggan akan "
"ditagih untuk pengeluaran tersebut."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/expenses/reinvoice_expenses.rst:None
msgid "See the expenses listed on the sales order after clicking into it."
msgstr "Lihat pengeluaran yang terdaftar pada sales order setelah mengkliknya."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/expenses/reinvoice_expenses.rst:153
msgid ":doc:`../../sales/sales/invoicing`"
msgstr ":doc:`../../sales/sales/invoicing`"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/expenses/submit_expenses.rst:3
msgid "Submit expenses"
msgstr "Ajukan pengeluaran"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/expenses/submit_expenses.rst:5
msgid ""
"When expenses have been :doc:`logged <log_expenses>` the next step is to "
"submit them for approval, so the expenses can then be reimbursed."
msgstr ""
"Ketika pengeluaran telah :doc:`dicatat <log_expenses>`, langkah selanjutnya "
"adalah mengajukannya untuk disetujui, sehingga pengeluaran kemudian dapat "
"diganti."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/expenses/submit_expenses.rst:11
msgid "My expenses dashboard"
msgstr "Dashboard pengeluaran saya"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/expenses/submit_expenses.rst:13
msgid ""
"Open the **Expenses** app, which displays the :guilabel:`My Expenses` "
"dashboard, by default. Alternatively, navigate to :menuselection:`Expenses "
"app --> My Expenses --> My Expenses`."
msgstr ""
"Buka aplikasi **Pengeluaran**, yang menampilkan dashboard "
":guilabel:`Pengeluaran Saya`, secara default. Atau, navigasi ke "
":menuselection:`aplikasi Pengeluaran --> Pengeluaran Saya --> Pengeluaran "
"Saya`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/expenses/submit_expenses.rst:16
msgid ""
"All expenses are color-coded by status. Any expense with a status "
"of :guilabel:`Draft` (expenses that have been created but not submitted) "
"appears in blue text. For all other statuses "
"(:guilabel:`Submitted`, :guilabel:`Approved`, and :guilabel:`Refused`), the "
"text appears in black."
msgstr ""
"Semua pengeluaran diberi kode warna berdasarkan status. Setiap pengeluaran "
"dengan status :guilabel:`Draft` (pengeluaran yang telah dibuat tetapi belum "
"diajukan) muncul dalam teks biru. Untuk semua status lainnya "
"(:guilabel:`Diajukan`, :guilabel:`Disetujui`, dan :guilabel:`Ditolak`), teks "
"muncul dalam warna hitam."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/expenses/submit_expenses.rst:20
msgid ""
"Above the list of expenses is the total monetary value of all expenses "
"waiting to be submitted, waiting for approval, or waiting for reimbursement. "
"Expenses with a status of :guilabel:`Draft` are used to calculate the amount "
"in the :guilabel:`To Submit` field, expenses with a status "
"of :guilabel:`Submitted` are used to calculate the :guilabel:`Waiting "
"Approval` amount, and expenses with a status of :guilabel:`Approved` are "
"used to calculate the :guilabel:`Waiting Reimbursement` total."
msgstr ""
"Di atas daftar pengeluaran adalah nilai moneter total dari semua pengeluaran "
"yang menunggu untuk diajukan, menunggu persetujuan, atau menunggu "
"penggantian. Pengeluaran dengan status :guilabel:`Draft` digunakan untuk "
"menghitung jumlah di kolom :guilabel:`Untuk Diajukan`, pengeluaran dengan "
"status :guilabel:`Diajukan` digunakan untuk menghitung jumlah "
":guilabel:`Menunggu Persetujuan`, dan pengeluaran dengan status "
":guilabel:`Disetujui` digunakan untuk menghitung total :guilabel:`Menunggu "
"Penggantian`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/expenses/submit_expenses.rst:None
msgid ""
"The top banner above the My Expenses dashboard with all the various totals "
"by status.\\"
msgstr ""
"Spanduk atas di atas dashboard Pengeluaran Saya dengan semua total berbagai "
"berdasarkan status."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/expenses/submit_expenses.rst:31
msgid ""
"While any expense can be selected from the :guilabel:`My Expenses` list, "
"the :guilabel:`Submit` button is *only* visible when expenses with a status "
"of :guilabel:`Draft` are selected. If any other status of expense is "
"selected, the :guilabel:`Submit` button does **not** appear."
msgstr ""
"Meskipun pengeluaran apa pun dapat dipilih dari daftar "
":guilabel:`Pengeluaran Saya`, tombol :guilabel:`Ajukan` *hanya* terlihat "
"ketika pengeluaran dengan status :guilabel:`Draft` dipilih. Jika status "
"pengeluaran lainnya dipilih, tombol :guilabel:`Ajukan` **tidak** muncul."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/expenses/submit_expenses.rst:36
msgid ""
"Another way to select all expenses with a :guilabel:`Draft` status is to "
"click into the search bar and select :guilabel:`To Submit` in the :icon:`fa-"
"filter` :guilabel:`Filters` column, then click the checkbox next "
"to :guilabel:`Employee`."
msgstr ""
"Cara lain untuk memilih semua pengeluaran dengan status :guilabel:`Draft` "
"adalah mengklik bilah pencarian dan memilih :guilabel:`To Submit` di kolom "
":icon:`fa-filter` :guilabel:`Filters`, lalu klik kotak centang di sebelah "
":guilabel:`Karyawan`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/expenses/submit_expenses.rst:41
msgid "Submit expense records"
msgstr "Kirim catatan pengeluaran"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/expenses/submit_expenses.rst:43
msgid ""
"On the :ref:`My Expenses <expenses/my_expenses>` dashboard, select the "
"desired expenses to be submitted on the :guilabel:`My Expenses` dashboard by "
"clicking the checkbox next to each entry."
msgstr ""
"Pada dasbor :ref:`My Expenses <expenses/my_expenses>`, pilih pengeluaran "
"yang diinginkan untuk dikirim pada dasbor :guilabel:`My Expenses` dengan "
"mengklik kotak centang di sebelah setiap entri."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/expenses/submit_expenses.rst:46
msgid ""
"Once the expenses have been selected, click the :guilabel:`Submit` button."
msgstr "Setelah pengeluaran dipilih, klik tombol :guilabel:`Submit`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/expenses/submit_expenses.rst:None
msgid "Selected expenses to submit on the My Expenses dashboard."
msgstr "Pengeluaran yang dipilih untuk dikirim pada dasbor My Expenses."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations.rst:5
msgid "Fiscal localizations"
msgstr "Lokalisasi fiskal"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations.rst:7
msgid ""
"Fiscal localizations are country-specific modules that allows for compliance "
"with a country's fiscal requirements. Most of these modules are related to "
"the **Accounting** app, but they can also be necessary for other apps such "
"as **Point of Sale**, **eCommerce**, etc., depending on a country's fiscal "
"requirements."
msgstr ""
"Lokalisasi fiskal adalah modul khusus negara yang memungkinkan kepatuhan "
"terhadap persyaratan fiskal suatu negara. Sebagian besar modul ini terkait "
"dengan aplikasi **Akuntansi**, tetapi juga dapat diperlukan untuk aplikasi "
"lain seperti **POS**, **eCommerce**, dll., tergantung pada persyaratan "
"fiskal suatu negara."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations.rst:13
msgid ":doc:`../hr/payroll/payroll_localizations` are documented separately."
msgstr ""
":doc:`../hr/payroll/payroll_localizations` didokumentasikan secara terpisah."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations.rst:20
msgid ""
"Odoo should automatically install the fiscal localization's core modules "
"based on the company's country when the related app is installed. The rest "
"can be manually :ref:`installed <general/install>`. Refer to the :ref:`list "
"of countries <fiscal_localizations/countries-list>` to view the currently "
"supported countries and access their specific documentation."
msgstr ""
"Odoo secara otomatis menginstal modul inti lokalisasi fiskal berdasarkan "
"negara perusahaan saat aplikasi terkait diinstal. Sisanya dapat "
":ref:`diinstal <general/install>` secara manual. Lihat :ref:`daftar negara "
"<fiscal_localizations/countries-list>` untuk melihat negara yang saat ini "
"didukung dan mengakses dokumentasi spesifik mereka."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations.rst:26
msgid ""
"Each company in a multi-company environment can use different fiscal "
"localization modules."
msgstr ""
"Setiap perusahaan dalam lingkungan multi-perusahaan dapat menggunakan modul "
"lokalisasi fiskal yang berbeda."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations.rst:28
msgid ""
"Verify the right package of modules is installed by going "
"to :menuselection:`Accounting --> Configuration --> Settings` and checking "
"the :guilabel:`Package` field under the :guilabel:`Fiscal Localization` "
"section. Select another one if necessary."
msgstr ""
"Verifikasi paket modul yang tepat telah diinstal dengan membuka "
":menuselection:`Akuntansi --> Konfigurasi --> Pengaturan` dan memeriksa "
"bidang :guilabel:`Paket` di bawah bagian :guilabel:`Lokalisasi Fiskal`. "
"Pilih yang lain jika diperlukan."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations.rst:33
msgid "Selecting another package is only possible if no entry has been posted."
msgstr ""
"Memilih paket lain hanya dimungkinkan jika tidak ada entri yang telah "
"diposting."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations.rst:35
msgid ""
"These packages require fine-tuning the chart of accounts, activating the "
"taxes to be used, configuring the country-specific statements and "
"certifications, and sometimes more."
msgstr ""
"Paket-paket ini memerlukan penyesuaian bagan akun, mengaktifkan pajak yang "
"akan digunakan, mengkonfigurasi laporan dan sertifikasi khusus negara, dan "
"terkadang lebih banyak lagi."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations.rst:41
msgid "List of countries"
msgstr "Daftar negara"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations.rst:43
msgid ""
"Fiscal localization modules are available for the countries listed below."
msgstr ""
"Modul lokalisasi fiskal tersedia untuk negara-negara yang tercantum di bawah "
"ini."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations.rst:46
msgid ""
"New countries are frequently added to this list and Odoo keeps expanding and "
"improving existing localizations and the related documentation."
msgstr ""
"Negara baru sering ditambahkan ke daftar ini dan Odoo terus memperluas dan "
"meningkatkan lokalisasi yang ada serta dokumentasi terkait."

