#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/argentina.rst:500
msgid ""
"For SME invoices, there are several document types that are classified as "
"**MiPyME**, which are also known as **Electronic Credit Invoice** (or "
"**FCE** in Spanish). This classification develops a mechanism that improves "
"the financing conditions for small and medium-sized businesses, and allows "
"them to increase their productivity, through the early collection of credits "
"and receivables issued to their clients and/or vendors."
msgstr ""
"Untuk faktur UKM, terdapat beberapa jenis dokumen yang diklasifikasikan "
"sebagai **MiPyME**, yang juga dikenal sebagai **Faktur Kredit Elektronik** "
"(atau **FCE** dalam bahasa Spanyol). Klasifikasi ini mengembangkan mekanisme "
"yang meningkatkan kondisi pembiayaan untuk usaha kecil dan menengah, dan "
"memungkinkan mereka untuk meningkatkan produktivitas, melalui pengumpulan "
"awal kredit dan piutang yang diterbitkan kepada klien dan/atau vendor mereka."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/argentina.rst:506
msgid ""
"For these transactions it's important to consider the following requirements:"
msgstr "Untuk transaksi ini penting untuk mempertimbangkan persyaratan berikut:"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/argentina.rst:508
msgid "specific document types (201, 202, 206, etc);"
msgstr "jenis dokumen tertentu (201, 202, 206, dll);"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/argentina.rst:509
msgid "the emitter should be eligible by the AFIP to MiPyME transactions;"
msgstr "penerbit harus memenuhi syarat oleh AFIP untuk transaksi MiPyME;"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/argentina.rst:510
msgid "the amount should be bigger than 100,000 ARS;"
msgstr "jumlahnya harus lebih besar dari 100.000 ARS;"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/argentina.rst:511
msgid ""
"A bank account type CBU must be related to the emisor, otherwise the invoice "
"cannot be validated, having an error message such as the following."
msgstr ""
"Akun bank jenis CBU harus terkait dengan penerbit, jika tidak faktur tidak "
"dapat divalidasi, dengan pesan kesalahan seperti berikut."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/argentina.rst:None
msgid "Bank account relation error."
msgstr "Kesalahan relasi akun bank."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/argentina.rst:518
msgid ""
"To set up the :guilabel:`Transmission Mode`, go to settings and select "
"either :guilabel:`SDC` or :guilabel:`ADC`."
msgstr ""
"Untuk mengatur :guilabel:`Mode Transmisi`, buka pengaturan dan pilih "
":guilabel:`SDC` atau :guilabel:`ADC`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/argentina.rst:None
msgid "Transmission Mode."
msgstr "Mode Transmisi."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/argentina.rst:525
msgid ""
"To change the :guilabel:`Transmission Mode` for a specific invoice, go to "
"the :guilabel:`Other Info` tab and change it before confirming."
msgstr ""
"Untuk mengubah :guilabel:`Mode Transmisi` untuk faktur tertentu, buka tab "
":guilabel:`Info Lain` dan ubah sebelum mengonfirmasi."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/argentina.rst:529
msgid ""
"Changing the :guilabel:`Transmission Mode` will not change the mode selected "
"in :guilabel:`Settings`."
msgstr ""
"Mengubah :guilabel:`Mode Transmisi` tidak akan mengubah mode yang dipilih di "
":guilabel:`Pengaturan`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/argentina.rst:None
msgid "Transmission Mode on Invoice."
msgstr "Mode Transmisi pada Faktur."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/argentina.rst:536
msgid ""
"When creating a :guilabel:`Credit/Debit` note related to a FCE document:"
msgstr "Saat membuat nota :guilabel:`Kredit/Debit` terkait dokumen FCE:"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/argentina.rst:538
msgid ""
"use the :guilabel:`Credit and Debit Note` buttons, so all the information "
"from the invoice is transferred to the new :guilabel:`Credit and Debit Note`;"
msgstr ""
"gunakan tombol :guilabel:`Nota Kredit dan Debit`, sehingga semua informasi "
"dari faktur ditransfer ke :guilabel:`Nota Kredit dan Debit` yang baru;"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/argentina.rst:540
msgid ""
"the document letter should be the same as than the originator document "
"(either A or B);"
msgstr "huruf dokumen harus sama dengan dokumen asli (baik A atau B);"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/argentina.rst:541
msgid ""
"the same currency as the source document must be used. When using a "
"secondary currency there is an exchange difference if the currency rate is "
"different between the emission day and the payment date. It is possible to "
"create a credit/debit note to decrease/increase the amount to pay in ARS."
msgstr ""
"mata uang yang sama dengan dokumen sumber harus digunakan. Saat menggunakan "
"mata uang sekunder terdapat selisih kurs jika nilai tukar berbeda antara "
"tanggal penerbitan dan tanggal pembayaran. Dimungkinkan untuk membuat nota "
"kredit/debit untuk mengurangi/meningkatkan jumlah yang harus dibayar dalam "
"ARS."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/argentina.rst:None
msgid "Credit & debit notes buttons."
msgstr "Tombol nota kredit & debit."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/argentina.rst:549
msgid "When creating a :guilabel:`Credit Note` we can have two scenarios:"
msgstr "Saat membuat :guilabel:`Nota Kredit` kita dapat memiliki dua skenario:"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/argentina.rst:551
msgid ""
"the FCE is rejected so the :guilabel:`Credit Note` should have the "
"field :guilabel:`FCE, is Cancellation?` as *True*; or;"
msgstr ""
"FCE ditolak sehingga :guilabel:`Nota Kredit` harus memiliki field "
":guilabel:`FCE, is Cancellation?` sebagai *True*; atau;"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/argentina.rst:553
msgid ""
"the :guilabel:`Credit Note`, is created to annulate the FCE document, in "
"this case the field :guilabel:`FCE, is Cancellation?` must be *empty* "
"(false)."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Nota Kredit`, dibuat untuk membatalkan dokumen FCE, dalam hal ini "
"field :guilabel:`FCE, is Cancellation?` harus *kosong* (false)."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/argentina.rst:None
msgid "FCE: Es Cancelación?"
msgstr "FCE: Es Cancelación?"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/argentina.rst:563
msgid "Invoice printed report"
msgstr "Laporan tercetak faktur"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/argentina.rst:565
msgid ""
"The :guilabel:`PDF Report` related to electronic invoices that have been "
"validated by the AFIP includes a barcode at the bottom of the format which "
"represents the CAE number. The expiration date is also displayed as it is a "
"legal requirement."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Laporan PDF` terkait faktur elektronik yang telah divalidasi oleh "
"AFIP menyertakan barcode di bagian bawah format yang mewakili nomor CAE. "
"Tanggal kedaluwarsa juga ditampilkan karena merupakan persyaratan hukum."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/argentina.rst:None
msgid "Invoice printed report."
msgstr "Laporan tercetak faktur."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/argentina.rst:574
msgid "Troubleshooting and auditing"
msgstr "Pemecahan masalah dan audit"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/argentina.rst:576
msgid ""
"For auditing and troubleshooting purposes, it is possible to obtain detailed "
"information of an invoice number that has been previously sent to the AFIP. "
"To retrieve this information, activate the :ref:`developer mode <developer-"
"mode>`, then go to the :menuselection:`Accounting` menu and click on the "
"button :guilabel:`Consult Invoice` button in AFIP."
msgstr ""
"Untuk tujuan audit dan pemecahan masalah, dimungkinkan untuk mendapatkan "
"informasi detail dari nomor faktur yang sebelumnya telah dikirim ke AFIP. "
"Untuk mengambil informasi ini, aktifkan :ref:`mode pengembang <developer-"
"mode>`, kemudian buka menu :menuselection:`Akuntansi` dan klik tombol "
":guilabel:`Consult Invoice` di AFIP."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/argentina.rst:None
msgid "Consult invoice in AFIP."
msgstr "Konsultasi faktur di AFIP."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/argentina.rst:None
msgid "Details of invoice consulted in AFIP."
msgstr "Detail faktur yang dikonsultasikan di AFIP."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/argentina.rst:589
msgid ""
"It is also possible to retrieve the last number used in AFIP for a specific "
"document type and POS Number as a reference for any possible issues on the "
"sequence synchronization between Odoo and AFIP."
msgstr ""
"Dimungkinkan juga untuk mengambil nomor terakhir yang digunakan di AFIP "
"untuk jenis dokumen tertentu dan Nomor POS sebagai referensi untuk "
"kemungkinan masalah pada sinkronisasi urutan antara Odoo dan AFIP."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/argentina.rst:None
msgid "Consult the last invoice number."
msgstr "Konsultasi nomor faktur terakhir."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/argentina.rst:600
msgid ""
"Based on the purchase journal selected for the vendor bill, "
"the :guilabel:`Document Type` is now a required field. This value is auto-"
"populated based on the AFIP Responsibility type of Issuer and Customer, but "
"the value can be changed if necessary."
msgstr ""
"Berdasarkan jurnal pembelian yang dipilih untuk tagihan vendor, "
":guilabel:`Jenis Dokumen` sekarang menjadi field wajib. Nilai ini terisi "
"otomatis berdasarkan jenis Tanggung Jawab AFIP dari Penerbit dan Pelanggan, "
"tetapi nilai dapat diubah jika diperlukan."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/argentina.rst:None
msgid "Changing journal and document type."
msgstr "Mengubah jurnal dan jenis dokumen."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/argentina.rst:608
msgid ""
"The :guilabel:`Document Number` field needs to be registered manually and "
"the format will be validated automatically. However, in case the format is "
"invalid, a user error will be displayed indicating the correct format that "
"is expected."
msgstr ""
"Field :guilabel:`Nomor Dokumen` perlu didaftarkan secara manual dan "
"formatnya akan divalidasi secara otomatis. Namun, jika formatnya tidak "
"valid, kesalahan pengguna akan ditampilkan yang menunjukkan format yang "
"benar yang diharapkan."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/argentina.rst:None
msgid "Vendor bill document number."
msgstr "Nomor dokumen tagihan vendor."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/argentina.rst:616
msgid ""
"The vendor bill number is structured in the same way as the customer "
"invoices, excepted that the document sequence is entered by the user using "
"the following format: *Document Prefix - Letter - Document Number*."
msgstr ""
"Nomor tagihan vendor terstruktur dengan cara yang sama seperti faktur "
"pelanggan, kecuali bahwa urutan dokumen dimasukkan oleh pengguna menggunakan "
"format berikut: *Prefix Dokumen - Huruf - Nomor Dokumen*."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/argentina.rst:621
msgid "Validate vendor bill number in AFIP"
msgstr "Validasi nomor tagihan vendor di AFIP"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/argentina.rst:623
msgid ""
"As most companies have internal controls to verify that the vendor bill is "
"related to an AFIP valid document, an automatic validation can be set "
"in :menuselection:`Accounting --> Settings --> Argentinean Localization --> "
"Validate document in the AFIP`, considering the following levels:"
msgstr ""
"Karena sebagian besar perusahaan memiliki kontrol internal untuk "
"memverifikasi bahwa tagihan vendor terkait dengan dokumen AFIP yang valid, "
"validasi otomatis dapat diatur di :menuselection:`Akuntansi --> "
"Pengaturan --> Lokalisasi Argentina --> Validate document in the AFIP`, "
"dengan mempertimbangkan level berikut:"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/argentina.rst:627
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Not available:` the verification is not done (this is the default "
"value);"
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Tidak tersedia:` verifikasi tidak dilakukan (ini adalah nilai "
"default);"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/argentina.rst:628
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Available:` the verification is done. In case the number is not "
"valid, it only displays a warning but still allows the vendor bill to be "
"posted;"
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Tersedia:` verifikasi dilakukan. Jika nomor tidak valid, sistem "
"hanya menampilkan peringatan tetapi tetap mengizinkan tagihan vendor "
"diposting;"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/argentina.rst:630
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Required:` the verification is done, and it does not allow the "
"user to post the vendor bill if the document number is not valid."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Wajib:` verifikasi dilakukan, dan sistem tidak mengizinkan "
"pengguna memposting tagihan vendor jika nomor dokumen tidak valid."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/argentina.rst:None
msgid "Verify Vendor Bills validity in AFIP."
msgstr "Verifikasi validitas Tagihan Vendor di AFIP."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/argentina.rst:638
msgid "Validate vendor bills in Odoo"
msgstr "Validasi tagihan vendor di Odoo"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/argentina.rst:640
msgid ""
"With the vendor validation settings enabled, a new button shows up on the "
"vendor bills inside of Odoo, labeled :guilabel:`Verify on AFIP`, which is "
"located next to the :guilabel:`AFIP Authorization code` field."
msgstr ""
"Dengan pengaturan validasi vendor diaktifkan, tombol baru muncul pada "
"tagihan vendor di dalam Odoo, berlabel :guilabel:`Verify on AFIP`, yang "
"terletak di sebelah field :guilabel:`AFIP Authorization code`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/argentina.rst:None
msgid "Verify on AFIP."
msgstr "Verifikasi di AFIP."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/argentina.rst:648
msgid ""
"In case the vendor bill cannot be validated in AFIP, a value "
"of :guilabel:`Rejected` will be displayed on the dashboard and the details "
"of the invalidation will be added to the chatter."
msgstr ""
"Jika tagihan vendor tidak dapat divalidasi di AFIP, nilai "
":guilabel:`Rejected` akan ditampilkan pada dashboard dan detail pembatalan "
"akan ditambahkan ke chatter."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/argentina.rst:None
msgid "AFIP authorization Rejected."
msgstr "Otorisasi AFIP Ditolak."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/argentina.rst:659
msgid "Untaxed concepts"
msgstr "Konsep tidak kena pajak"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/argentina.rst:661
msgid ""
"There are some transactions that include items that are not a part of the "
"VAT base amount, such as fuel and gasoline invoices."
msgstr ""
"Ada beberapa transaksi yang mencakup item yang bukan bagian dari jumlah "
"dasar PPN, seperti faktur bahan bakar dan bensin."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/argentina.rst:664
msgid ""
"The vendor bill will be registered using one item for each product that is "
"part of the VAT base amount, and an additional item to register the amount "
"of the exempt concept."
msgstr ""
"Tagihan vendor akan didaftarkan menggunakan satu item untuk setiap produk "
"yang merupakan bagian dari jumlah dasar PPN, dan item tambahan untuk "
"mendaftarkan jumlah konsep yang dikecualikan."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/argentina.rst:None
msgid "VAT exempt."
msgstr "Dikecualikan dari PPN."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/argentina.rst:672
msgid "Perception taxes"
msgstr "Pajak persepsi"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/argentina.rst:674
msgid ""
"The vendor bill will be registered using one item for each product that is "
"part of the VAT base amount, and the perception tax can be added in any of "
"the product lines. As a result, there will be one tax group for the VAT and "
"another for the perception. The perception default value is "
"always :guilabel:`0.10`."
msgstr ""
"Tagihan vendor akan didaftarkan menggunakan satu item untuk setiap produk "
"yang merupakan bagian dari jumlah dasar PPN, dan pajak persepsi dapat "
"ditambahkan pada salah satu baris produk. Hasilnya, akan ada satu kelompok "
"pajak untuk PPN dan kelompok lain untuk persepsi. Nilai default persepsi "
"selalu :guilabel:`0.10`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/argentina.rst:679
msgid ""
"To edit the VAT perception and set the correct amount, you should use "
"the :guilabel:`Pencil` icon that is the next to the :guilabel:`Perception` "
"amount. After the VAT perception amount has been set, the invoice can then "
"be validated."
msgstr ""
"Untuk mengedit persepsi PPN dan mengatur jumlah yang benar, Anda harus "
"menggunakan ikon :guilabel:`Pencil` yang berada di sebelah jumlah "
":guilabel:`Perception`. Setelah jumlah persepsi PPN diatur, faktur kemudian "
"dapat divalidasi."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/argentina.rst:None
msgid "Enter the perception amount."
msgstr "Masukkan jumlah persepsi."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/argentina.rst:690
msgid "Withholding management"
msgstr "Manajemen pemotongan"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/argentina.rst:692
msgid ""
"The Argentinean fiscal localization module is already loaded with the "
"necessary withholdings records, which can be seen by navigating "
"to :menuselection:`Accounting app --> Configuration --> Taxes` and removing "
"the default :guilabel:`Sale or Purchase` filter. To verify these records, "
"the **Argentina Payment Withholdings** (`l10n_ar_withholding`) module must "
"be :ref:`installed <general/install>`:"
msgstr ""
"Modul lokalisasi fiskal Argentina sudah dimuat dengan catatan pemotongan "
"yang diperlukan, yang dapat dilihat dengan menavigasi ke "
":menuselection:`Aplikasi Akuntansi --> Konfigurasi --> Pajak` dan menghapus "
"filter default :guilabel:`Sale or Purchase`. Untuk memverifikasi catatan "
"ini, modul **Argentina Payment Withholdings** (`l10n_ar_withholding`) harus "
":ref:`diinstal <general/install>`:"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/argentina.rst:698
msgid ""
"Journal entries are *not* created when payments are posted "
"unless :ref:`outstanding accounts <accounting/journals/outstanding-"
"accounts>` are set up. Thus, for this feature to work properly, it is "
"important to verify that *all* payment methods within the bank journals have "
"an outstanding payment and receipt account set."
msgstr ""
"Entri jurnal *tidak* dibuat saat pembayaran diposting kecuali :ref:`akun "
"outstanding <accounting/journals/outstanding-accounts>` telah disiapkan. "
"Oleh karena itu, agar fitur ini berfungsi dengan baik, penting untuk "
"memverifikasi bahwa *semua* metode pembayaran dalam jurnal bank memiliki "
"akun pembayaran dan penerimaan outstanding yang ditetapkan."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/argentina.rst:None
msgid "An outstanding payment account must be set."
msgstr "Akun pembayaran yang belum diselesaikan harus diatur."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/argentina.rst:706
msgid ""
"This configuration is crucial for the proper accounting of withholding "
"transactions with clients and vendors."
msgstr ""
"Konfigurasi ini sangat penting untuk akuntansi transaksi pemotongan yang "
"tepat dengan klien dan vendor."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/argentina.rst:710
msgid ""
"In Argentina, withholdings represent the cancellation of a specific portion "
"of the total debt owed to a supplier or a reduction in the total payment to "
"be collected from a customer. Therefore, one or multiple withholdings can be "
"recorded for each payment applied to an invoice."
msgstr ""
"Di Argentina, pemotongan (withholding) merupakan pembatalan sebagian "
"tertentu dari total utang yang harus dibayarkan kepada pemasok atau "
"pengurangan dalam total pembayaran yang akan diterima dari pelanggan. Oleh "
"karena itu, satu atau beberapa pemotongan dapat dicatat untuk setiap "
"pembayaran yang diterapkan pada faktur."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/argentina.rst:717
msgid ""
"While Odoo already creates most of the required withholdings inside "
"the :guilabel:`Taxes` menu, in several cases, it is necessary to apply or "
"modify certain configurations to correctly calculate the withholding amount "
"on vendor payments. The following withholding types are available:"
msgstr ""
"Meskipun Odoo sudah membuat sebagian besar pemotongan yang diperlukan di "
"dalam menu :guilabel:`Pajak`, dalam beberapa kasus, perlu menerapkan atau "
"mengubah konfigurasi tertentu untuk menghitung jumlah pemotongan dengan "
"benar pada pembayaran vendor. Jenis pemotongan berikut tersedia:"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/argentina.rst:721
msgid ":ref:`Earnings <l10n_ar/earnings-withholdings>`"
msgstr ":ref:`Penghasilan <l10n_ar/earnings-withholdings>`"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/argentina.rst:722
msgid ":ref:`Earnings Scale <l10n_ar/earnings-scale-withholdings>`"
msgstr ":ref:`Skala Penghasilan <l10n_ar/earnings-scale-withholdings>`"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/argentina.rst:723
msgid ":ref:`IIBB Total Amount <l10n_ar/iib-total-amount-withholdings>`"
msgstr ":ref:`Jumlah Total IIBB <l10n_ar/iib-total-amount-withholdings>`"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/argentina.rst:724
msgid ":ref:`IIBB Non-Taxable <l10n_ar/iib-nontax-withholdings>`"
msgstr ":ref:`IIBB Non-Kena Pajak <l10n_ar/iib-nontax-withholdings>`"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/argentina.rst:729
msgid "Earnings"
msgstr "Penghasilan"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/argentina.rst:731
msgid ""
"For :guilabel:`Earnings` withholdings, Odoo already has a record for each "
"regime group, which is stated under the name of the tax and the AFIP code."
msgstr ""
"Untuk pemotongan :guilabel:`Penghasilan`, Odoo sudah memiliki catatan untuk "
"setiap kelompok rezim, yang dinyatakan di bawah nama pajak dan kode AFIP."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/argentina.rst:734
msgid ""
"Each of these records are ready to be used. As a good practice, the "
"configuration should be double checked to make sure the configuration is "
"updated and well-applied. The fields to validate are:"
msgstr ""
"Setiap catatan ini siap digunakan. Sebagai praktik yang baik, konfigurasi "
"harus diperiksa ulang untuk memastikan konfigurasi telah diperbarui dan "
"diterapkan dengan baik. Field yang perlu divalidasi adalah:"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/argentina.rst:737
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Amount`: This is the percentage of the total payment amount which "
"is withheld."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Jumlah`: Ini adalah persentase dari total jumlah pembayaran yang "
"dipotong."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/argentina.rst:738
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Non-Taxable Amount`: Up to this amount, the withholding does not "
"apply."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Jumlah Non-Kena Pajak`: Hingga jumlah ini, pemotongan tidak "
"berlaku."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/argentina.rst:739
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Minimum Withholding`: If the calculated withholding amount is "
"smaller than this value, the total withholding amount is set to `0.0`."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Pemotongan Minimum`: Jika jumlah pemotongan yang dihitung lebih "
"kecil dari nilai ini, total jumlah pemotongan ditetapkan menjadi `0.0`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/argentina.rst:741
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Withholding Sequence`: This field helps to automate the capture "
"of a withholding number under the payment line. If this field is not set, a "
"number is manually captured while adding a withholding to a payment."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Urutan Pemotongan`: Field ini membantu mengotomatiskan pencatatan "
"nomor pemotongan di bawah baris pembayaran. Jika field ini tidak diatur, "
"nomor dicatat secara manual saat menambahkan pemotongan ke pembayaran."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/argentina.rst:None
msgid "Earnings withholding type."
msgstr "Jenis pemotongan penghasilan."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/argentina.rst:751
msgid "Earnings Scale"
msgstr "Skala Penghasilan"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/argentina.rst:753
msgid ""
"In this particular case, a percentage does not need to be set. Instead, this "
"withholding is calculated based on the value of the :guilabel:`Scale` field."
msgstr ""
"Dalam kasus khusus ini, persentase tidak perlu ditetapkan. Sebaliknya, "
"pemotongan ini dihitung berdasarkan nilai field :guilabel:`Skala`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/argentina.rst:756
msgid ""
"To view, modify, or create new scales, navigate "
"to :menuselection:`Accounting app --> Configuration --> Earnings Scale`. By "
"default, the Argentinian localization is preconfigured with two main scales. "
"However, scales should be created and updated as necessary to suit a "
"business's needs."
msgstr ""
"Untuk melihat, mengubah, atau membuat skala baru, navigasikan ke "
":menuselection:`Aplikasi Akuntansi --> Konfigurasi --> Skala Penghasilan`. "
"Secara default, lokalisasi Argentina telah dikonfigurasi sebelumnya dengan "
"dua skala utama. Namun, skala harus dibuat dan diperbarui sesuai kebutuhan "
"untuk memenuhi kebutuhan bisnis."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/argentina.rst:761
msgid ""
"Earnings scales are cumulative, which means that Odoo keeps track of the "
"different records created for a bill and automatically calculates the proper "
"withholding amount."
msgstr ""
"Skala penghasilan bersifat kumulatif, yang berarti Odoo melacak berbagai "
"catatan yang dibuat untuk tagihan dan secara otomatis menghitung jumlah "
"pemotongan yang tepat."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/argentina.rst:767
msgid "IIBB Total Amount"
msgstr "Jumlah Total IIBB"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/argentina.rst:769
msgid ""
"In this case, the necessary records related to the applicable province need "
"to be created. The withholding amount is calculated based on the "
"percentage :guilabel:`Amount` set on the tax configuration. Since Odoo does "
"not automatically synchronize the percentages applicable to each province, "
"this information needs to be manually updated."
msgstr ""
"Dalam kasus ini, catatan yang diperlukan terkait dengan provinsi yang "
"berlaku perlu dibuat. Jumlah pemotongan dihitung berdasarkan persentase "
":guilabel:`Jumlah` yang ditetapkan pada konfigurasi pajak. Karena Odoo tidak "
"secara otomatis menyinkronkan persentase yang berlaku untuk setiap provinsi, "
"informasi ini perlu diperbarui secara manual."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/argentina.rst:774
msgid ""
"The recommendation, in this case, is to always duplicate and apply the "
"different configurations for each record to safeguard any technical "
"configurations that allow the proper calculation and accounting of the "
"withholding."
msgstr ""
"Rekomendasi dalam kasus ini adalah selalu menduplikasi dan menerapkan "
"konfigurasi yang berbeda untuk setiap catatan untuk melindungi konfigurasi "
"teknis yang memungkinkan penghitungan dan pencatatan pemotongan dengan benar."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/argentina.rst:781
msgid "IIBB Untaxed"
msgstr "IIBB Tidak Kena Pajak"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/argentina.rst:783
msgid ""
"The configuration of non-taxable gross income withholdings is very similar "
"to that of a :ref:`total amount withholding <l10n_ar/iib-total-amount-"
"withholdings>`, so the percentage :guilabel:`Amount` in each of the records "
"needs to be maintained. However, Odoo comes preconfigured with several "
"records that apply to different provinces. The difference, in this case, is "
"that it is not necessary to establish a non-taxable amount or minimum "
"withholding for this record type."
msgstr ""
"Konfigurasi pemotongan pendapatan kotor yang tidak kena pajak sangat mirip "
"dengan :ref:`pemotongan jumlah total <l10n_ar/iib-total-amount-withholdings>"
"`, sehingga persentase :guilabel:`Jumlah` dalam setiap catatan perlu "
"dipelihara. Namun, Odoo hadir dengan beberapa catatan yang telah "
"dikonfigurasi sebelumnya yang berlaku untuk provinsi yang berbeda. "
"Perbedaannya, dalam hal ini, tidak perlu menetapkan jumlah yang tidak kena "
"pajak atau pemotongan minimum untuk jenis catatan ini."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/argentina.rst:790
msgid "Partner withholding assignation"
msgstr "Penugasan pemotongan mitra"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/argentina.rst:792
msgid ""
"Once the proper configuration is set on each possible withholding for "
"partners, the applicable withholdings need to be assigned to each contact. "
"To do this, open the :guilabel:`Contacts` app and select the desired "
"partner. In the :guilabel:`Accounting` tab, find the :guilabel:`Purchase "
"Withholdings` table."
msgstr ""
"Setelah konfigurasi yang tepat diatur pada setiap kemungkinan pemotongan "
"untuk mitra, pemotongan yang berlaku perlu ditugaskan ke setiap kontak. "
"Untuk melakukan ini, buka aplikasi :guilabel:`Kontak` dan pilih mitra yang "
"diinginkan. Di tab :guilabel:`Akuntansi`, temukan tabel "
":guilabel:`Pemotongan Pembelian`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/argentina.rst:797
msgid ""
"By using the additional fields :guilabel:`From Date` and :guilabel:`To "
"Date`, the applicability of multiple withholdings can be automated across "
"different date ranges. The :guilabel:`ref` field allows you to apply an "
"internal control number to each withholding line, which is just for internal "
"reference, so it does not affect any transactions and is not visible on "
"them. These fields are accessible from the :icon:`oi-settings-"
"adjust` :guilabel:`(adjust settings)` menu."
msgstr ""
"Dengan menggunakan bidang tambahan :guilabel:`Dari Tanggal` dan "
":guilabel:`Sampai Tanggal`, penerapan beberapa pemotongan dapat "
"diotomatiskan di berbagai rentang tanggal. Bidang :guilabel:`ref` "
"memungkinkan Anda menerapkan nomor kontrol internal ke setiap baris "
"pemotongan, yang hanya untuk referensi internal, sehingga tidak mempengaruhi "
"transaksi apa pun dan tidak terlihat di dalamnya. Bidang-bidang ini dapat "
"diakses dari menu :icon:`oi-settings-adjust` :guilabel:`(sesuaikan "
"pengaturan)`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/argentina.rst:803
msgid ":guilabel:`From Date`: the start of the withholding date range."
msgstr ":guilabel:`Dari Tanggal`: awal rentang tanggal pemotongan."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/argentina.rst:804
msgid ":guilabel:`To Date`: the end of the withholding date range."
msgstr ":guilabel:`Sampai Tanggal`: akhir rentang tanggal pemotongan."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/argentina.rst:805
msgid ""
":guilabel:`ref`: apply an internal control number to each withholding line "
"that is only visible for internal reference and does not affect any "
"transactions."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`ref`: terapkan nomor kontrol internal ke setiap baris pemotongan "
"yang hanya terlihat untuk referensi internal dan tidak mempengaruhi "
"transaksi apa pun."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/argentina.rst:809
msgid "Automatic withholding calculation and application per payment"
msgstr "Perhitungan dan penerapan pemotongan otomatis per pembayaran"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/argentina.rst:811
msgid ""
"By applying new payments to vendor bills, Odoo automatically applies and "
"calculates the proper withholding into the payment. Based on the record's "
"configuration, it may be necessary to use a reference number for each "
"withholding line."
msgstr ""
"Dengan menerapkan pembayaran baru ke tagihan vendor, Odoo secara otomatis "
"menerapkan dan menghitung pemotongan yang tepat ke dalam pembayaran. "
"Berdasarkan konfigurasi catatan, mungkin perlu menggunakan nomor referensi "
"untuk setiap baris pemotongan."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/argentina.rst:815
msgid ""
"More withholdings can be added, or computed withholdings can be edited if "
"necessary."
msgstr ""
"Lebih banyak pemotongan dapat ditambahkan, atau pemotongan yang dihitung "
"dapat diedit jika diperlukan."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/argentina.rst:None
msgid "Payment with applied withholdings."
msgstr "Pembayaran dengan pemotongan yang diterapkan."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/argentina.rst:821
msgid ""
"The total amount of the debt to be canceled is the total amount of the "
"payment. However, Odoo still captures the net amount (i.e. the amount to be "
"reconciled with the bank), which will be represented as the payment amount "
"after the withholding application."
msgstr ""
"Jumlah total utang yang akan dibatalkan adalah jumlah total pembayaran. "
"Namun, Odoo tetap menangkap jumlah bersih (yaitu jumlah yang akan "
"direkonsiliasi dengan bank), yang akan diwakili sebagai jumlah pembayaran "
"setelah penerapan pemotongan."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/argentina.rst:0
msgid "Payment registered form."
msgstr "Formulir pembayaran terdaftar."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/argentina.rst:829
msgid "Check management"
msgstr "Manajemen cek"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/argentina.rst:831
msgid ""
"To install the *Third Party and Deferred/Electronic Checks Management* "
"module, go to :menuselection:`Apps` and search for the module by its "
"technical name `l10n_latam_check` and click the :guilabel:`Activate` button."
msgstr ""
"Untuk menginstal modul *Manajemen Cek Pihak Ketiga dan Tertunda/Elektronik*, "
"buka :menuselection:`Aplikasi` dan cari modul dengan nama teknisnya "
"`l10n_latam_check` dan klik tombol :guilabel:`Aktifkan`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/argentina.rst:None
msgid "l10n_latam_check module."
msgstr "Modul l10n_latam_check."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/argentina.rst:839
msgid ""
"This module enables the required configuration for journals and payments to:"
msgstr ""
"Modul ini mengaktifkan konfigurasi yang diperlukan untuk jurnal dan "
"pembayaran untuk:"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/argentina.rst:841
msgid "Create, manage, and control your different types of checks"
msgstr "Membuat, mengelola, dan mengontrol berbagai jenis cek Anda"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/argentina.rst:842
msgid "Optimize the management of *own checks* and *third party checks*"
msgstr "Mengoptimalkan manajemen *cek sendiri* dan *cek pihak ketiga*"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/argentina.rst:843
msgid ""
"Have an easy and effective way to manage expiration dates from your own and "
"third party checks"
msgstr ""
"Memiliki cara yang mudah dan efektif untuk mengelola tanggal kedaluwarsa "
"dari cek Anda sendiri dan pihak ketiga"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/argentina.rst:845
msgid ""
"Once all the configurations are made for the Argentinian electronic invoice "
"flow, it is also needed to complete certain configurations for the own "
"checks and the third party checks flows."
msgstr ""
"Setelah semua konfigurasi dibuat untuk alur faktur elektronik Argentina, "
"juga diperlukan untuk melengkapi konfigurasi tertentu untuk alur cek sendiri "
"dan cek pihak ketiga."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/argentina.rst:849
msgid "Own checks"
msgstr "Cek sendiri"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/argentina.rst:851
msgid ""
"Configure the bank journal used to create your own checks by going "
"to :menuselection:`Accounting --> Configuration --> Journals`, selecting the "
"bank journal, and opening the :guilabel:`Outgoing Payments` tab."
msgstr ""
"Konfigurasi jurnal bank yang digunakan untuk membuat cek Anda sendiri dengan "
"membuka :menuselection:`Akuntansi --> Konfigurasi --> Jurnal`, memilih "
"jurnal bank, dan membuka tab :guilabel:`Pembayaran Keluar`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/argentina.rst:855
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Checks` should be available as a :guilabel:`Payment Method`. If "
"not, click :guilabel:`Add a line` and type `Checks` under :guilabel:`Payment "
"Method` to add them"
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Cek` harus tersedia sebagai :guilabel:`Metode Pembayaran`. Jika "
"tidak, klik :guilabel:`Tambah baris` dan ketik `Checks` di bawah "
":guilabel:`Metode Pembayaran` untuk menambahkannya"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/argentina.rst:857
msgid "Enable the :guilabel:`Use electronic and deferred checks` setting."
msgstr "Aktifkan pengaturan :guilabel:`Gunakan cek elektronik dan tertunda`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/argentina.rst:860
msgid ""
"This last configuration **disables** the printing ability but enables to:"
msgstr ""
"Konfigurasi terakhir ini **menonaktifkan** kemampuan pencetakan tetapi "
"memungkinkan untuk:"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/argentina.rst:862
msgid "Enter check numbers manually"
msgstr "Memasukkan nomor cek secara manual"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/argentina.rst:863
msgid "Adds a field to allocate the payment date of the check"
msgstr "Menambahkan bidang untuk mengalokasikan tanggal pembayaran cek"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/argentina.rst:None
msgid "Bank journal configurations."
msgstr "Konfigurasi jurnal bank."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/argentina.rst:870
msgid "Management of own checks"
msgstr "Manajemen cek sendiri"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/argentina.rst:872
msgid ""
"Own checks can be created directly from the vendor bill. For this process, "
"click on the :guilabel:`Register Payment` button."
msgstr ""
"Cek sendiri dapat dibuat langsung dari tagihan vendor. Untuk proses ini, "
"klik tombol :guilabel:`Daftarkan Pembayaran`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/argentina.rst:875
msgid ""
"On the payment registration modal, select the bank journal from which the "
"payment is to be made and set the :guilabel:`Check Cash-In Date`, and "
"the :guilabel:`Amount`."
msgstr ""
"Pada modal pendaftaran pembayaran, pilih jurnal bank dari mana pembayaran "
"akan dilakukan dan atur :guilabel:`Tanggal Pencairan Cek`, dan "
":guilabel:`Jumlah`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/argentina.rst:None
msgid "Payment pop-up window with own check options enabled."
msgstr "Jendela pop-up pembayaran dengan opsi cek sendiri diaktifkan."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/argentina.rst:883
msgid ""
"To manage current checks, the :guilabel:`Check Cash-In Date` field must be "
"left blank or filled in with the current date. To manage deferred checks, "
"the :guilabel:`Check Cash-In Date` must be set in the future."
msgstr ""
"Untuk mengelola cek saat ini, bidang :guilabel:`Tanggal Pencairan Cek` harus "
"dibiarkan kosong atau diisi dengan tanggal saat ini. Untuk mengelola cek "
"tertunda, :guilabel:`Tanggal Pencairan Cek` harus diatur di masa mendatang."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/argentina.rst:887
msgid ""
"To manage your existing own checks, navigate to :menuselection:`Accounting --"
"> Vendors --> Own Checks`. This window shows critical information such as "
"the dates when checks need to be paid, the total quantity of checks, and the "
"total amount paid in checks."
msgstr ""
"Untuk mengelola cek sendiri Anda yang ada, buka "
":menuselection:`Akuntansi --> Vendor --> Cek Sendiri`. Jendela ini "
"menampilkan informasi penting seperti tanggal kapan cek perlu dibayar, "
"jumlah total cek, dan jumlah total yang dibayarkan dalam cek."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/argentina.rst:None
msgid "Own checks menu location."
msgstr "Lokasi menu cek sendiri."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/argentina.rst:895
msgid ""
"It is important to note that the list is pre-filtered by checks that are "
"still *not reconciled* with a bank statement - that were not yet debited "
"from the bank - which can be verified with the :guilabel:`Is Matched with a "
"Bank Statement` field. If you want to see all of your own checks, delete "
"the :guilabel:`No Bank Matching` filter by clicking on the :guilabel:`X` "
"symbol."
msgstr ""
"Penting untuk dicatat bahwa daftar sudah disaring sebelumnya berdasarkan cek "
"yang masih *belum direkonsiliasi* dengan laporan bank - yang belum didebit "
"dari bank - yang dapat diverifikasi dengan bidang :guilabel:`Dicocokkan "
"dengan Laporan Bank`. Jika Anda ingin melihat semua cek sendiri Anda, hapus "
"filter :guilabel:`Tidak Ada Pencocokan Bank` dengan mengklik simbol "
":guilabel:`X`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/argentina.rst:None
msgid "Own checks menu organization and filtering."
msgstr "Organisasi dan pemfilteran menu cek sendiri."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/argentina.rst:905
msgid "Cancel an own check"
msgstr "Batalkan cek sendiri"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/argentina.rst:907
msgid ""
"To cancel an own check created in Odoo, navigate "
"to :menuselection:`Accounting --> Vendors --> Own Checks` and select the "
"check to be cancelled, then click on the :guilabel:`Void Check` button. This "
"will break the reconciliation with the vendor bills and the bank statements "
"and leave the check in a **cancelled** state."
msgstr ""
"Untuk membatalkan cek sendiri yang dibuat di Odoo, buka "
":menuselection:`Akuntansi --> Vendor --> Cek Sendiri` dan pilih cek yang "
"akan dibatalkan, kemudian klik tombol :guilabel:`Batalkan Cek`. Ini akan "
"memutuskan rekonsiliasi dengan tagihan vendor dan laporan bank serta "
"meninggalkan cek dalam status **dibatalkan**."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/argentina.rst:None
msgid "Empty Check button to cancel Own Checks"
msgstr "Tombol Batalkan Cek untuk membatalkan Cek Sendiri"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/argentina.rst:917
msgid "Third party checks"
msgstr "Cek pihak ketiga"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/argentina.rst:919
msgid ""
"In order to register payments using third party checks, two specific "
"journals need to be configured. To do so, navigate "
"to :menuselection:`Accounting --> Configuration --> Journals` and create two "
"new journals:"
msgstr ""
"Untuk mencatat pembayaran menggunakan cek pihak ketiga, dua jurnal khusus "
"perlu dikonfigurasi. Untuk melakukannya, buka :menuselection:`Akuntansi --> "
"Konfigurasi --> Jurnal` dan buat dua jurnal baru:"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/argentina.rst:923
msgid "`Third Party Checks`"
msgstr "`Cek Pihak Ketiga`"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/argentina.rst:924
msgid "`Rejected Third Party Checks`"
msgstr "`Cek Pihak Ketiga yang Ditolak`"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/argentina.rst:927
msgid ""
"You can manually create more journals if you have multiple points of sale "
"and need journals for those."
msgstr ""
"Anda dapat membuat lebih banyak jurnal secara manual jika Anda memiliki "
"beberapa titik penjualan dan memerlukan jurnal untuk itu."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/argentina.rst:930
msgid ""
"To create the *Third Party Checks* journal, click the :guilabel:`New` button "
"and configure the following:"
msgstr ""
"Untuk membuat jurnal *Cek Pihak Ketiga*, klik tombol :guilabel:`Baru` dan "
"konfigurasikan berikut ini:"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/argentina.rst:933
msgid "Type `Third Party Checks` as the :guilabel:`Journal Name`"
msgstr "Ketik `Cek Pihak Ketiga` sebagai :guilabel:`Nama Jurnal`"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/argentina.rst:934
#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/argentina.rst:968
msgid "Select :guilabel:`Cash` as :guilabel:`Type`"
msgstr "Pilih :guilabel:`Kas` sebagai :guilabel:`Tipe`"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/argentina.rst:935
msgid ""
"In the :guilabel:`Journal Entries` tab, set :guilabel:`Cash Account`: to "
"`1.1.1.02.010 Cheques de Terceros`, input a :guilabel:`Short Code` of your "
"choice, and select a :guilabel:`Currency`"
msgstr ""
"Di tab :guilabel:`Entri Jurnal`, atur :guilabel:`Akun Kas` ke `1.1.1.02.010 "
"Cheques de Terceros`, masukkan :guilabel:`Kode Pendek` pilihan Anda, dan "
"pilih :guilabel:`Mata Uang`"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/argentina.rst:None
msgid "Automatically created cash account."
msgstr "Akun kas yang dibuat secara otomatis."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/argentina.rst:942
msgid "The available payment methods are listed in the *payments* tabs:"
msgstr "Metode pembayaran yang tersedia tercantum di tab *pembayaran*:"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/argentina.rst:944
msgid ""
"For new incoming third party checks, go to :menuselection:`Incoming Payments "
"tab --> Add a line` and select :guilabel:`New Third Party Checks`. This "
"method is used to create *new* third party checks."
msgstr ""
"Untuk cek pihak ketiga baru yang masuk, buka :menuselection:`Tab Pembayaran "
"Masuk --> Tambahkan baris` dan pilih :guilabel:`Cek Pihak Ketiga Baru`. "
"Metode ini digunakan untuk membuat cek pihak ketiga *baru*."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/argentina.rst:947
msgid ""
"For incoming and outgoing existing third party checks, go "
"to :menuselection:`Incoming Payments tab --> Add a line` and "
"select :guilabel:`Existing Third Party Checks`. Repeat the same step for "
"the :guilabel:`Outgoing Payments` tab. This method is used to receive and/or "
"pay vendor bills using already *existing* checks, as well as for internal "
"transfers."
msgstr ""
"Untuk cek pihak ketiga yang sudah ada yang masuk dan keluar, buka "
":menuselection:`Tab Pembayaran Masuk --> Tambahkan baris` dan pilih "
":guilabel:`Cek Pihak Ketiga yang Sudah Ada`. Ulangi langkah yang sama untuk "
"tab :guilabel:`Pembayaran Keluar`. Metode ini digunakan untuk menerima dan/"
"atau membayar tagihan vendor menggunakan cek yang sudah *ada*, serta untuk "
"transfer internal."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/argentina.rst:953
msgid ""
"You can delete pre-existing payment methods appearing by default when "
"configuring the third party checks journals."
msgstr ""
"Anda dapat menghapus metode pembayaran yang sudah ada yang muncul secara "
"default saat mengonfigurasi jurnal cek pihak ketiga."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/argentina.rst:None
