msgstr "Metode pembayaran yang dibuat secara otomatis."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/argentina.rst:960
msgid ""
"The *Rejected Third Party Checks* journal also needs to be created and/or "
"configured. This journal is used to manage rejected third party checks and "
"can be utilized to send checks rejected at the moment of collection or when "
"coming from vendors when rejected."
msgstr ""
"Jurnal *Cek Pihak Ketiga yang Ditolak* juga perlu dibuat dan/atau "
"dikonfigurasi. Jurnal ini digunakan untuk mengelola cek pihak ketiga yang "
"ditolak dan dapat digunakan untuk mengirim cek yang ditolak pada saat "
"penagihan atau ketika berasal dari vendor saat ditolak."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/argentina.rst:964
msgid ""
"To create the *Rejected Third Party Checks* journal, click "
"the :guilabel:`New` button and configure the following:"
msgstr ""
"Untuk membuat jurnal *Cek Pihak Ketiga yang Ditolak*, klik tombol "
":guilabel:`Baru` dan konfigurasikan berikut ini:"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/argentina.rst:967
msgid "Type `Rejected Third Party Checks` as the :guilabel:`Journal Name`"
msgstr "Ketik `Cek Pihak Ketiga yang Ditolak` sebagai :guilabel:`Nama Jurnal`"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/argentina.rst:969
msgid ""
"In the :guilabel:`Journal Entries` tab, set :guilabel:`Cash Account`: to "
"`1.1.1.01.002 Rejected Third Party Checks`, input a :guilabel:`Short Code` "
"of your choice, and select a :guilabel:`Currency`"
msgstr ""
"Di tab :guilabel:`Journal Entries`, atur :guilabel:`Cash Account` menjadi "
"`1.1.1.01.002 Rejected Third Party Checks`, masukkan :guilabel:`Short Code` "
"pilihan Anda, dan pilih :guilabel:`Currency`"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/argentina.rst:973
msgid "Use the same payment methods as the *Third Party Checks* journal."
msgstr "Gunakan metode pembayaran yang sama dengan jurnal *Third Party Checks*."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/argentina.rst:976
msgid "New third party checks"
msgstr "Cek pihak ketiga baru"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/argentina.rst:978
msgid ""
"To register a *new* third party check for a customer invoice, click "
"the :guilabel:`Register Payment` button. In the pop-up window, you must "
"select :guilabel:`Third Party Checks` as journal for the payment "
"registration."
msgstr ""
"Untuk mencatat cek pihak ketiga *baru* untuk faktur pelanggan, klik tombol "
":guilabel:`Register Payment`. Di jendela pop-up, Anda harus memilih "
":guilabel:`Third Party Checks` sebagai jurnal untuk pencatatan pembayaran."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/argentina.rst:982
msgid ""
"Select :guilabel:`New Third Party Checks` as :guilabel:`Payment Method`, and "
"fill in the :guilabel:`Check Number`, :guilabel:`Payment Date`, "
"and :guilabel:`Check Bank`. Optionally, you can manually add "
"the :guilabel:`Check Issuer Vat`, but this is automatically filled by the "
"customer's VAT number related to the invoice."
msgstr ""
"Pilih :guilabel:`New Third Party Checks` sebagai :guilabel:`Payment Method`, "
"dan isi :guilabel:`Check Number`, :guilabel:`Payment Date`, dan "
":guilabel:`Check Bank`. Secara opsional, Anda dapat menambahkan "
":guilabel:`Check Issuer Vat` secara manual, tetapi ini akan terisi otomatis "
"dengan nomor PPN pelanggan yang terkait dengan faktur."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/argentina.rst:None
msgid "Payment pop-up window with New Third Party Check options enabled."
msgstr "Jendela pop-up pembayaran dengan opsi New Third Party Check diaktifkan."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/argentina.rst:992
msgid "Existing third party checks"
msgstr "Cek pihak ketiga yang sudah ada"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/argentina.rst:994
msgid ""
"To pay a vendor bill with an *existing* check, click the :guilabel:`Register "
"Payment` button. In the pop-up window, you must select :guilabel:`Third "
"Party Checks` as journal for the payment registration."
msgstr ""
"Untuk membayar tagihan vendor dengan cek yang *sudah ada*, klik tombol "
":guilabel:`Register Payment`. Di jendela pop-up, Anda harus memilih "
":guilabel:`Third Party Checks` sebagai jurnal untuk pencatatan pembayaran."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/argentina.rst:998
msgid ""
"Select :guilabel:`Existing Third Party Checks` as :guilabel:`Payment "
"Method`, and select a check from the :guilabel:`Check` field. The field "
"shows all **available existing checks** to be used as payment for vendor "
"bills."
msgstr ""
"Pilih :guilabel:`Existing Third Party Checks` sebagai :guilabel:`Payment "
"Method`, dan pilih cek dari kolom :guilabel:`Check`. Kolom ini menampilkan "
"semua **cek yang sudah ada dan tersedia** untuk digunakan sebagai pembayaran "
"tagihan vendor."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/argentina.rst:None
msgid "Payment pop-up window with Existing Third Party Check options enabled."
msgstr ""
"Jendela pop-up pembayaran dengan opsi Existing Third Party Check diaktifkan."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/argentina.rst:1006
msgid ""
"When an **existing third party check** is used, you can review the "
"operations related to it. For example, you can see if a third party check "
"made to pay a customer invoice was later used as an existing third party "
"check to pay a vendor bill."
msgstr ""
"Ketika **cek pihak ketiga yang sudah ada** digunakan, Anda dapat meninjau "
"operasi yang terkait dengannya. Misalnya, Anda dapat melihat apakah cek "
"pihak ketiga yang dibuat untuk membayar faktur pelanggan kemudian digunakan "
"sebagai cek pihak ketiga yang sudah ada untuk membayar tagihan vendor."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/argentina.rst:1010
msgid ""
"To do so, either go to :menuselection:`Accounting --> Customers --> Third "
"Party Checks` or :menuselection:`Accounting --> Vendors --> Own Checks` "
"depending on the case, and click on a check. In the :guilabel:`Check Current "
"Journal` field, click on :guilabel:`=> Check Operations` to bring up the "
"check's history and movements."
msgstr ""
"Untuk melakukannya, buka :menuselection:`Accounting --> Customers --> Third "
"Party Checks` atau :menuselection:`Accounting --> Vendors --> Own Checks` "
"tergantung kasusnya, dan klik pada cek. Di kolom :guilabel:`Check Current "
"Journal`, klik :guilabel:`=> Check Operations` untuk menampilkan riwayat dan "
"pergerakan cek."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/argentina.rst:None
msgid "Check Operations menu."
msgstr "Menu Check Operations."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/argentina.rst:1019
msgid ""
"The menu also displays critical information related to these operations, "
"such as:"
msgstr ""
"Menu ini juga menampilkan informasi penting yang terkait dengan operasi ini, "
"seperti:"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/argentina.rst:1021
msgid ""
"The :guilabel:`Payment Type`, allowing to classify whether it is a payment "
"*sent* to a vendor or a payment *received* from a customer"
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Payment Type`, yang memungkinkan untuk mengklasifikasikan apakah "
"itu pembayaran yang *dikirim* ke vendor atau pembayaran yang *diterima* dari "
"pelanggan"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/argentina.rst:1023
msgid "The :guilabel:`Journal` in which the check is currently registered"
msgstr ":guilabel:`Journal` tempat cek saat ini terdaftar"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/argentina.rst:1024
msgid ""
"The **partner** associated with the operation (either customer or vendor)."
msgstr "**Mitra** yang terkait dengan operasi (baik pelanggan atau vendor)."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/argentina.rst:1029
msgid "Ecommerce electronic invoicing"
msgstr "Faktur elektronik eCommerce"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/argentina.rst:1032
msgid ""
":ref:`Install <general/install>` the *Argentinian eCommerce* "
"(`l10n_ar_website_sale`) module to enable the following features and "
