#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/belgium.rst:38
msgid ""
"Default Belgian taxes are created automatically when the :guilabel:`Belgium "
"- Accounting` and the :guilabel:`Belgium - Accounting Reports` modules are "
"installed. Each tax impacts the Belgian :guilabel:`Tax Report`, available by "
"going to :menuselection:`Accounting --> Reporting --> Statements Reports: "
"Tax Report`."
msgstr ""
"Pajak Belgia default dibuat secara otomatis saat modul :guilabel:`Belgia - "
"Akuntansi` dan :guilabel:`Belgia - Laporan Akuntansi` diinstal. Setiap pajak "
"memengaruhi :guilabel:`Laporan Pajak` Belgia, yang tersedia dengan membuka "
":menuselection:`Akuntansi --> Pelaporan --> Laporan Pernyataan: Laporan "
"Pajak`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/belgium.rst:43
msgid ""
"In Belgium, the standard VAT rate is **21%**, but there are lower rates for "
"some categories of goods and services. An intermediate rate of **12%** is "
"applied on social housing and food served in restaurants, while a reduced "
"rate of **6%** applies to most basic goods, such as food, water supply, "
"books, and medicine. A **0%** rate applies to some exceptional goods and "
"services, such as some daily and weekly publications, as well as recycled "
"goods."
msgstr ""
"Di Belgia, tarif PPN standar adalah **21%**, tetapi ada tarif lebih rendah "
"untuk beberapa kategori barang dan jasa. Tarif menengah **12%** diterapkan "
"pada perumahan sosial dan makanan yang disajikan di restoran, sedangkan "
"tarif rendah **6%** berlaku untuk sebagian besar barang pokok, seperti "
"makanan, pasokan air, buku, dan obat-obatan. Tarif **0%** berlaku untuk "
"beberapa barang dan jasa luar biasa, seperti beberapa publikasi harian dan "
"mingguan, serta barang daur ulang."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/belgium.rst:52
msgid "Non-deductible taxes"
msgstr "Pajak tidak dapat dikurangkan"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/belgium.rst:54
msgid ""
"In Belgium, some taxes are not fully deductible, such as taxes on the "
"maintenance of cars. This means a part of these taxes is considered as an "
"expense."
msgstr ""
"Di Belgia, beberapa pajak tidak sepenuhnya dapat dikurangkan, seperti pajak "
"atas pemeliharaan mobil. Ini berarti sebagian dari pajak ini dianggap "
"sebagai beban."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/belgium.rst:57
msgid ""
"In Odoo, you can configure non-deductible taxes by creating tax rules for "
"these taxes and linking them to the corresponding accounts. This way, the "
"system automatically calculates the taxes and allocates them to the "
"appropriate accounts."
msgstr ""
"Di Odoo, Anda dapat mengonfigurasi pajak tidak dapat dikurangkan dengan "
"membuat aturan pajak untuk pajak tersebut dan menghubungkannya ke akun yang "
"sesuai. Dengan cara ini, sistem secara otomatis menghitung pajak dan "
"mengalokasikannya ke akun yang tepat."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/belgium.rst:61
msgid ""
"To configure a new non-deductible tax, go to :menuselection:`Accounting --> "
"Configuration --> Accounting: Taxes`, and click :guilabel:`New`:"
msgstr ""
"Untuk mengonfigurasi pajak tidak dapat dikurangkan baru, buka "
":menuselection:`Akuntansi --> Konfigurasi --> Akuntansi: Pajak`, dan klik "
":guilabel:`Baru`:"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/belgium.rst:64
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Add a line` and select :guilabel:`Base` in the :guilabel:`Based "
"On` column;"
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Tambahkan baris` dan pilih :guilabel:`Dasar` di kolom "
":guilabel:`Berdasarkan`;"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/belgium.rst:65
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Add a line`, then select :guilabel:`on tax` in "
"the :guilabel:`Based on` column and enter the **non-deductible** percentage "
"in the :guilabel:`%` column;"
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Tambahkan baris`, lalu pilih :guilabel:`pada pajak` di kolom "
":guilabel:`Berdasarkan` dan masukkan persentase **tidak dapat dikurangkan** "
"di kolom :guilabel:`%`;"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/belgium.rst:67
msgid ""
"On the :guilabel:`of tax` line, select the :guilabel:`Tax Grid(s)` related "
"to your tax;"
msgstr ""
"Pada baris :guilabel:`of tax`, pilih :guilabel:`Tax Grid(s)` yang terkait "
"dengan pajak Anda;"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/belgium.rst:68
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Add a line` with the **deductible** percentage in "
"the :guilabel:`%` column;"
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Tambahkan baris` dengan persentase **yang dapat dikurangkan** di "
"kolom :guilabel:`%`;"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/belgium.rst:69
msgid "Set :guilabel:`of tax` in :guilabel:`Based On`;"
msgstr "Atur :guilabel:`of tax` di :guilabel:`Based On`;"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/belgium.rst:70
msgid ""
"Select :guilabel:`411000 VAT recoverable` as account, and select the related "
"tax grid."
msgstr ""
"Pilih :guilabel:`411000 VAT recoverable` sebagai akun, dan pilih kisi pajak "
"terkait."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/belgium.rst:72
msgid ""
"Once you have created a non-deductible tax, you can apply it to your "
"transactions by selecting the appropriate tax during the encoding of bills "
"and credit notes. The system automatically calculates the tax amount and "
"allocates it to the corresponding accounts based on the tax rules configured."
msgstr ""
"Setelah Anda membuat pajak yang tidak dapat dikurangkan, Anda dapat "
"menerapkannya pada transaksi Anda dengan memilih pajak yang sesuai saat "
"pengkodean tagihan dan nota kredit. Sistem secara otomatis menghitung jumlah "
"pajak dan mengalokasikannya ke akun yang sesuai berdasarkan aturan pajak "
"yang dikonfigurasi."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/belgium.rst:77
msgid ""
"With the Belgian localization, the **21% car** tax is created by default "
"(50% non-deductible)."
msgstr ""
"Dengan lokalisasi Belgia, pajak **21% car** dibuat secara default (50% tidak "
"dapat dikurangkan)."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/belgium.rst:0
msgid "Example of not-fully deductible tax"
msgstr "Contoh pajak yang tidak sepenuhnya dapat dikurangkan"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/belgium.rst:83
msgid ":doc:`Taxes <../accounting/taxes>`"
msgstr ":doc:`Pajak <../accounting/taxes>`"

