#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/canada.rst:63
msgid ""
"The :doc:`chart of accounts (COA) <../accounting/get_started/"
"chart_of_accounts>` for the Canadian localization, in Odoo, has accounts "
"grouped into seven main categories, with corresponding numeric values that "
"prefix individual journal entries:"
msgstr ""
":doc:`Bagan akun (COA) <../accounting/get_started/chart_of_accounts>` untuk "
"lokalisasi Kanada, di Odoo, memiliki akun yang dikelompokkan ke dalam tujuh "
"kategori utama, dengan nilai numerik yang sesuai sebagai awalan untuk entri "
"jurnal individual:"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/canada.rst:67
#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/united_states.rst:115
msgid ""
"**Receivable**: the balance of money (or credit) due to the business for "
"goods or services delivered or used, but not yet paid for by customers. |AR| "
"is indicated by the journal code labeled (or beginning) with :guilabel:`1`."
msgstr ""
"**Piutang**: saldo uang (atau kredit) yang menjadi hak bisnis untuk barang "
"atau jasa yang telah dikirim atau digunakan, tetapi belum dibayar oleh "
"pelanggan. |AR| ditunjukkan oleh kode jurnal yang diberi label (atau "
"dimulai) dengan :guilabel:`1`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/canada.rst:70
#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/united_states.rst:118
msgid ""
"**Payable**: the business's short-term obligations owed to its creditors or "
"suppliers, which have not yet been paid. |AP| is indicated by the journal "
"code labeled (or beginning) with :guilabel:`2`."
msgstr ""
"**Hutang**: kewajiban jangka pendek bisnis yang terutang kepada kreditor "
"atau pemasoknya, yang belum dibayar. |AP| ditunjukkan oleh kode jurnal yang "
"diberi label (atau dimulai) dengan :guilabel:`2`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/canada.rst:73
msgid ""
"**Equity**: the amount of money that would be returned to a company's "
"shareholders if all of the assets were liquidated and all of the company's "
"debt was paid off in the case of liquidation. Equity is indicated by the "
"journal code labeled (or beginning) with :guilabel:`3` or :guilabel:`9`."
msgstr ""
"**Ekuitas**: jumlah uang yang akan dikembalikan kepada pemegang saham "
"perusahaan jika semua aset dilikuidasi dan semua utang perusahaan dilunasi "
"dalam hal likuidasi. Ekuitas ditunjukkan oleh kode jurnal yang diberi label "
"(atau dimulai) dengan :guilabel:`3` atau :guilabel:`9`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/canada.rst:77
#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/united_states.rst:124
msgid ""
"**Assets**: items listed on the balance sheet that contains economic value "
"or have the ability to generate cash flows in the future, such as a piece of "
"machinery, a financial security, or a patent. Assets are indicated by the "
"journal code labeled (or beginning) with :guilabel:`1`."
msgstr ""
"**Aset**: item yang terdaftar di neraca keuangan yang mengandung nilai "
"ekonomi atau memiliki kemampuan untuk menghasilkan arus kas di masa depan, "
"seperti sebuah mesin, sekuritas keuangan, atau paten. Aset ditunjukkan oleh "
"kode jurnal yang diberi label (atau dimulai) dengan :guilabel:`1`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/canada.rst:80
#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/united_states.rst:127
msgid ""
"**Liability**: refers to a company's financial debts or obligations that "
"arise during the course of business operations. Liabilities are indicated by "
"the journal code labeled (or beginning) with :guilabel:`2`."
msgstr ""
"**Kewajiban**: mengacu pada utang atau kewajiban keuangan perusahaan yang "
"timbul selama operasi bisnis. Kewajiban ditunjukkan oleh kode jurnal yang "
"diberi label (atau dimulai) dengan :guilabel:`2`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/canada.rst:83
#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/united_states.rst:130
msgid ""
"**Income**: synonymous with *net income*, this is the profit a company "
"retains after paying off all relevant expenses from sales revenue earned. "
"Income is indicated by the journal code labeled (or beginning) "
"with :guilabel:`4` or :guilabel:`6`."
msgstr ""
"**Pendapatan**: sinonim dengan *laba bersih*, ini adalah keuntungan yang "
"dipertahankan perusahaan setelah membayar semua biaya relevan dari "
"pendapatan Penjualan yang diperoleh. Pendapatan ditunjukkan oleh kode jurnal "
"yang diberi label (atau dimulai) dengan :guilabel:`4` atau :guilabel:`6`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/canada.rst:86
#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/united_states.rst:133
msgid ""
"**Expenses**: the cost of operations that a company incurs to generate "
"revenue. Expenses are indicated by the journal code labeled (or beginning) "
"with a :guilabel:`6`."
msgstr ""
"**Pengeluaran**: biaya operasi yang dikeluarkan perusahaan untuk "
"menghasilkan pendapatan. Pengeluaran ditunjukkan oleh kode jurnal yang "
"diberi label (atau dimulai) dengan :guilabel:`6`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/canada.rst:90
msgid ""
"Predefined accounts are included in Odoo, as part of the |COA| that's "
"installed with the Canadian localization package. The accounts listed below "
"are preconfigured to perform certain operations within Odoo. It is "
"recommended to **not** delete these accounts; however, if changes are "
"needed, rename the accounts instead."
msgstr ""
"Akun yang telah ditentukan sebelumnya disertakan dalam Odoo, sebagai bagian "
"dari |COA| yang diinstal dengan paket lokalisasi Kanada. Akun yang tercantum "
"di bawah ini telah dikonfigurasi sebelumnya untuk melakukan operasi tertentu "
"dalam Odoo. Disarankan untuk **tidak** menghapus akun ini; namun, jika "
"diperlukan perubahan, ganti nama akunnya."

