msgstr ""
"Klien dari Chili akan dapat memilih apakah mereka memerlukan **faktur** atau "
"**kwitansi** untuk pembelian mereka dengan langkah tambahan yang ditambahkan "
"selama proses checkout."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/chile.rst:None
msgid "Option for EDI Documents for clients."
msgstr "Opsi untuk Dokumen EDI bagi klien."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/chile.rst:1023
msgid ""
"If the customer selects the :guilabel:`Electronic Invoice` option, fiscal "
"fields are required to be filled out, including the :guilabel:`Activity "
"Description`, the :guilabel:`Identification Number` and their :guilabel:`DTE "
"Email`."
msgstr ""
"Jika pelanggan memilih opsi :guilabel:`Electronic Invoice`, kolom fiskal "
"wajib diisi, termasuk :guilabel:`Activity Description`, "
":guilabel:`Identification Number` dan :guilabel:`DTE Email` mereka."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/chile.rst:None
msgid "Fiscal fields required for an Invoice to be requested."
msgstr "Kolom fiskal yang diperlukan untuk Invoice yang diminta."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/chile.rst:1030
msgid ""
"If the client selects the :guilabel:`Electronic Receipts` option, they will "
"be directed to the next step, and the electronic document will be generated "
"for the *Consumidor Final Anónimo* contact."
msgstr ""
"Jika klien memilih opsi :guilabel:`Electronic Receipts`, mereka akan "
"diarahkan ke langkah berikutnya, dan dokumen elektronik akan dibuat untuk "
"kontak *Consumidor Final Anónimo*."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/chile.rst:1033
msgid ""
"Clients from countries other than Chile, will have their electronic receipts "
