#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/colombia.rst:19
msgid ""
"Have a valid digital signature certificate `approved by the ONAC <https://"
"onac.org.co/directorio-de-acreditados/>`_."
msgstr ""
"Memiliki sertifikat tanda tangan digital yang valid `disetujui oleh ONAC "
