#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/colombia.rst:302
msgid ""
"Ensure that :guilabel:`[CO] Bank of the Republic` is selected as "
"the :guilabel:`Service`."
msgstr ""
"Pastikan :guilabel:`[CO] Bank of the Republic` dipilih sebagai "
":guilabel:`Layanan`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/colombia.rst:303
msgid ""
"Select an :guilabel:`Interval` for how frequently the currency rate should "
"be automatically updated."
msgstr ""
"Pilih :guilabel:`Interval` untuk seberapa sering nilai tukar mata uang harus "
"diperbarui secara otomatis."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/colombia.rst:307
msgid "Main workflows"
msgstr "Alur kerja utama"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/colombia.rst:314
msgid ""
"The following is a breakdown of the main workflow for electronic invoices "
"with the Colombian localization:"
msgstr ""
"Berikut adalah rincian alur kerja utama untuk faktur elektronik dengan "
"lokalisasi Kolombia:"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/colombia.rst:317
msgid "The user creates an invoice."
msgstr "User membuat faktur."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/colombia.rst:318
msgid "Odoo generates the legal XML file."
msgstr "Odoo menghasilkan file XML legal."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/colombia.rst:319
msgid ""
"Odoo generates the CUFE (Invoice Electronic Code) with the electronic "
"signature."
msgstr ""
"Odoo menghasilkan CUFE (Invoice Electronic Code) dengan tanda tangan "
"elektronik."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/colombia.rst:320
msgid "Odoo sends a notification to DIAN."
msgstr "Odoo mengirimkan notifikasi ke DIAN."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/colombia.rst:321
msgid "|DIAN| validates the invoice."
msgstr "|DIAN| memvalidasi faktur."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/colombia.rst:322
msgid "|DIAN| accepts or rejects the invoice."
msgstr "|DIAN| menerima atau menolak faktur."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/colombia.rst:323
msgid "Odoo generates the PDF invoice with a QR code."
msgstr "Odoo menghasilkan faktur PDF dengan kode QR."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/colombia.rst:324
msgid ""
"Odoo compresses the attached document (containing the sent XML file and the "
"DIAN validation response) and the fiscal valid PDF into a :file:`.zip` file."
msgstr ""
"Odoo mengompresi dokumen terlampir (berisi file XML yang dikirim dan respons "
"validasi DIAN) dan PDF yang valid secara fiskal menjadi file :file:`.zip`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/colombia.rst:326
msgid ""
"The user sends the invoice (:file:`.zip` file) via Odoo to the acquirer."
msgstr "User mengirimkan faktur (file :file:`.zip`) melalui Odoo ke penerima."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/colombia.rst:334
msgid ""
"The functional workflow taking place before an invoice validation does "
"**not** alter the main changes introduced with the electronic invoice."
msgstr ""
"Alur kerja fungsional yang terjadi sebelum validasi faktur **tidak** "
"mengubah perubahan utama yang diperkenalkan dengan faktur elektronik."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/colombia.rst:337
msgid ""
"Electronic invoices are generated and sent to both the |DIAN| and the "
"customer. These documents can be created from the sales order or manually "
"generated. To create a new invoice, go to :menuselection:`Accounting --> "
"Costumers --> Invoices`, and select :guilabel:`Create`. On the invoice form, "
"configure the following fields:"
msgstr ""
"Faktur elektronik dibuat dan dikirim ke |DIAN| dan pelanggan. Dokumen-"
"dokumen ini dapat dibuat dari sales order atau dibuat secara manual. Untuk "
"membuat faktur baru, buka :menuselection:`Akuntansi --> Pelanggan --> "
"Faktur`, dan pilih :guilabel:`Buat`. Pada formulir faktur, konfigurasikan "
"kolom-kolom berikut:"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/colombia.rst:342
msgid ":guilabel:`Customer`: customer's information."
msgstr ":guilabel:`Pelanggan`: informasi pelanggan."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/colombia.rst:343
msgid ":guilabel:`Journal`: journal used for electronic invoices."
msgstr ":guilabel:`Jurnal`: jurnal yang digunakan untuk faktur elektronik."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/colombia.rst:344
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Electronic Invoice Type`: Select the type of document. By "
"default, :guilabel:`Factura de Venta` is selected."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Jenis Faktur Elektronik`: Pilih jenis dokumen. Secara default, "
":guilabel:`Factura de Venta` dipilih."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/colombia.rst:346
msgid ":guilabel:`Invoice Lines`: Specify the products with the correct taxes."
msgstr ":guilabel:`Baris Faktur`: Tentukan produk dengan pajak yang benar."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/colombia.rst:349
msgid ""
"When creating the first invoice related to an electronic invoicing journal, "
"it is required to manually change the *sequence* of the invoice to the |"
"DIAN| format: `Prefix + Sequence`."
msgstr ""
"Saat membuat faktur pertama yang terkait dengan jurnal penagihan elektronik, "
"diperlukan untuk mengubah *urutan* faktur secara manual ke format |DIAN|: "
"`Prefix + Sequence`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/colombia.rst:352
msgid "For example, format the sequence from `SETP/2024/00001` to `SETP1`."
msgstr "Misalnya, format urutan dari `SETP/2024/00001` menjadi `SETP1`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/colombia.rst:354
#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/guatemala.rst:227
msgid "When done, click :guilabel:`Confirm`."
msgstr "Setelah selesai, klik :guilabel:`Konfirmasi`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/colombia.rst:359
msgid "Electronic invoice sending"
msgstr "Pengiriman faktur elektronik"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/colombia.rst:361
msgid ""
"After the :ref:`invoice confirmation <localization/colombia/invoice-"
"creation>`, click :guilabel:`Send`. In the wizard that appears, make sure to "
