"Setelah :ref:`konfirmasi faktur <localization/colombia/invoice-creation>`, "
"klik :guilabel:`Kirim`. Di wizard yang muncul, pastikan untuk mengaktifkan "
"kotak centang :guilabel:`DIAN` dan :guilabel:`Email` untuk mengirim XML ke "
"layanan web |DIAN| dan faktur yang divalidasi ke email fiskal klien, lalu "
"klik :guilabel:`Kirim`. Kemudian:"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/colombia.rst:366
#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/guatemala.rst:244
msgid "The XML document is created."
msgstr "Dokumen XML dibuat."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/colombia.rst:367
msgid "The CUFE is generated."
msgstr "CUFE dihasilkan."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/colombia.rst:368
msgid "The XML is processed synchronously by the |DIAN|."
msgstr "XML diproses secara sinkron oleh |DIAN|."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/colombia.rst:369
msgid ""
"If accepted, the file is displayed in the chatter and the email to the "
"client with the corresponding :file:`.zip` file."
msgstr ""
"Jika diterima, file ditampilkan di chatter dan email kepada klien dengan "
"file :file:`.zip` yang sesuai."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/colombia.rst:None
#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/guatemala.rst:None
msgid "EDI documents available in the chatter."
msgstr "Dokumen EDI tersedia di chatter."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/colombia.rst:375
msgid "The :guilabel:`DIAN` tab then displays the following:"
msgstr "Tab :guilabel:`DIAN` kemudian menampilkan hal berikut:"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/colombia.rst:377
msgid ":guilabel:`Signed Date`: timestamp recorded of the XML creation."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Tanggal Ditandatangani`: stempel waktu yang dicatat dari "
"pembuatan XML."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/colombia.rst:378
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Status`: Status result obtained in the |DIAN| response. If the "
"invoice was rejected, the error messages can be seen here."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Status`: Hasil status yang diperoleh dalam respons |DIAN|. Jika "
"faktur ditolak, pesan kesalahan dapat dilihat di sini."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/colombia.rst:380
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Testing Environment`: To know if the document sent was delivered "
"to the |DIAN| testing environment."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Lingkungan Pengujian`: Untuk mengetahui apakah dokumen yang "
"dikirim telah dikirimkan ke lingkungan pengujian |DIAN|."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/colombia.rst:382
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Certification Process`: To know if the document was sent as part "
"of the certification process with the |DIAN|."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Proses Sertifikasi`: Untuk mengetahui apakah dokumen dikirim "
"sebagai bagian dari proses sertifikasi dengan |DIAN|."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/colombia.rst:384
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Download`: To download the sent XML file, even if the |DIAN| "
"result was rejected."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Unduh`: Untuk mengunduh file XML yang dikirim, meskipun hasil "
