"Modul inti lokalisasi diinstal secara otomatis bersama lokalisasi. Sisanya "
"dapat :ref:`diinstal secara manual <general/install>`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/croatia.rst:40
msgid ""
":doc:`Documentation on e-invoicing’s legality and compliance in Croatia <../"
"accounting/customer_invoices/electronic_invoicing/croatia>`"
msgstr ""
":doc:`Dokumentasi tentang legalitas dan kepatuhan e-invoicing di Kroasia <../"
"accounting/customer_invoices/electronic_invoicing/croatia>`"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/croatia.rst:48
msgid ""
"Odoo can connect to the national eRačun platform via the third-party "
"provider `mojeRačun <https://moj-eracun.hr>`_ to send and receive e-invoices."
msgstr ""
"Odoo dapat terhubung ke platform eRačun nasional melalui penyedia pihak "
"ketiga `mojeRačun <https://moj-eracun.hr>`_ untuk mengirim dan menerima e-"
"invoice."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/croatia.rst:52
msgid ""
"The :guilabel:`Croatia - e-invoicing` (`l10n_hr_edi`) module must "
"be :ref:`installed <general/install>` to configure e-invoicing via mojeRačun."
msgstr ""
"Modul :guilabel:`Kroasia - e-invoicing` (`l10n_hr_edi`) harus :ref:`diinstal "
"<general/install>` untuk mengonfigurasi e-invoicing melalui mojeRačun."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/croatia.rst:56
msgid ""
"To use this integration, an account and `invoice package <https://portal.moj-"
"eracun.hr/podrska/cjenik/>`_ from mojeRačun are needed. The rest of this "
"documentation assumes that one has already been obtained."
msgstr ""
"Untuk menggunakan integrasi ini, diperlukan akun dan `paket faktur <https://"
"portal.moj-eracun.hr/podrska/cjenik/>`_ dari mojeRačun. Sisa dokumentasi ini "
"mengasumsikan bahwa akun tersebut sudah diperoleh."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/croatia.rst:65
msgid "Follow these steps to set up e-invoicing via mojeRačun in Odoo."
msgstr ""
"Ikuti langkah-langkah berikut untuk mengatur e-invoicing melalui mojeRačun "
"di Odoo."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/croatia.rst:70
msgid "Company configuration"
msgstr "Konfigurasi perusahaan"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/croatia.rst:72
msgid ""
"Go to :menuselection:`Accounting --> Configuration --> Settings` and scroll "
"down to :guilabel:`MojEracun E-invoicing`. Fill the :guilabel:`Username` "
"field with the numeric username and the :guilabel:`Password` field with the "
"password provided by mojeRačun."
msgstr ""
"Buka :menuselection:`Akuntansi --> Konfigurasi --> Pengaturan` dan gulir ke "
"bawah ke :guilabel:`MojEracun E-invoicing`. Isi kolom :guilabel:`Username` "
"dengan nama pengguna numerik dan kolom :guilabel:`Password` dengan kata "
"sandi yang diberikan oleh mojeRačun."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/croatia.rst:77
msgid ""
"Alternatively, the :guilabel:`Username` can be set to the e-mail address "
"used to register on mojeRačun."
msgstr ""
"Sebagai alternatif, :guilabel:`Username` dapat diatur ke alamat email yang "
"digunakan untuk mendaftar di mojeRačun."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/croatia.rst:80
msgid ""
"Ensure that the :guilabel:`Company ID (OIB or GIN)` and :guilabel:`Company "
"Business Unit (PJ)` fields are correctly filled in, matching the data used "
"to register on mojeRačun."
msgstr ""
"Pastikan kolom :guilabel:`Company ID (OIB or GIN)` dan :guilabel:`Company "
"Business Unit (PJ)` diisi dengan benar, sesuai dengan data yang digunakan "
"untuk mendaftar di mojeRačun."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/croatia.rst:83
msgid ""
"The :guilabel:`Business Software (ERP) ID` should be set to `Saodoo-001`."
msgstr ":guilabel:`Business Software (ERP) ID` harus diatur ke `Saodoo-001`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/croatia.rst:85
msgid ""
"Optionally, specify the :guilabel:`Incoming E-Invoices Journal` where "
"invoices received via |MER| should be created. If left unset, the default "
"purchase journal will be used."
msgstr ""
"Secara opsional, tentukan :guilabel:`Incoming E-Invoices Journal` tempat "
"faktur yang diterima melalui |MER| harus dibuat. Jika tidak diatur, jurnal "
"pembelian default akan digunakan."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/croatia.rst:88
msgid ""
"Set the :guilabel:`MojEracun Operating Mode` to :guilabel:`Production` to "
"send and receive invoices on the production network."
msgstr ""
"Atur :guilabel:`Mode Operasi MojEracun` ke :guilabel:`Production` untuk "
"mengirim dan menerima faktur di jaringan produksi."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/croatia.rst:92
msgid ""
"Using the :guilabel:`Test` mode connects to a MER demo server that requires "
"separate credentials and is not relevant for most end users."
msgstr ""
"Menggunakan mode :guilabel:`Test` terhubung ke server demo MER yang "
"memerlukan kredensial terpisah dan tidak relevan untuk sebagian besar "
"pengguna akhir."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/croatia.rst:95
msgid ""
"Then click :guilabel:`Activate` to activate the connection with mojeRačun."
msgstr ""
"Kemudian klik :guilabel:`Activate` untuk mengaktifkan koneksi dengan "
"mojeRačun."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/croatia.rst:100
msgid "Journal configuration"
msgstr "Konfigurasi jurnal"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/croatia.rst:102
msgid ""
"Go to :menuselection:`Accounting --> Configuration --> Journals` and click "
"the :guilabel:`Sales` journal to open its configuration."
msgstr ""
"Buka :menuselection:`Akuntansi --> Konfigurasi --> Jurnal` dan klik jurnal "
":guilabel:`Penjualan` untuk membuka konfigurasinya."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/croatia.rst:105
msgid ""
"In the :guilabel:`Fiscalization (HR)` section, complete "
"the :guilabel:`Business premises label`, :guilabel:`Issuing device "
"label`, :guilabel:`Business premises label (refund approval)`, "
"and :guilabel:`Issuing device label (refund approval)` fields."
msgstr ""
"Di bagian :guilabel:`Fiscalization (HR)`, lengkapi kolom :guilabel:`Business "
"premises label`, :guilabel:`Issuing device label`, :guilabel:`Business "
"premises label (refund approval)`, dan :guilabel:`Issuing device label "
"(refund approval)`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/croatia.rst:109
msgid ""
"The :guilabel:`Business premises label` and :guilabel:`Issuing device label` "
"are used to generate invoice names. The :guilabel:`Business premises label "
"(refund approval)` and :guilabel:`Issuing device label (refund approval)` "
"fields are used to generate credit note names."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Business premises label` dan :guilabel:`Issuing device label` "
"digunakan untuk menghasilkan nama faktur. Kolom :guilabel:`Business premises "
"label (refund approval)` dan :guilabel:`Issuing device label (refund "
"approval)` digunakan untuk menghasilkan nama nota kredit."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/croatia.rst:116
msgid "Sending an e-invoice"
msgstr "Mengirim e-faktur"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/croatia.rst:118
msgid ""
"To send an e-invoice, follow the :ref:`standard e-invoicing <accounting/e-"
"invoicing/generation>` workflow. Be sure to select :guilabel:`by MojEracun` "
"when sending the e-invoice."
msgstr ""
"Untuk mengirim e-faktur, ikuti alur kerja :ref:`e-invoicing standar "
"<accounting/e-invoicing/generation>`. Pastikan untuk memilih :guilabel:`by "
"MojEracun` saat mengirim e-faktur."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/croatia.rst:121
msgid "The following invoice fields must be set before sending to mojeRačun:"
msgstr "Kolom faktur berikut harus diatur sebelum mengirim ke mojeRačun:"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/croatia.rst:123
msgid ""
"**Invoice sequence:** Ensure the invoice sequence is in the format `{Journal "
"code}-{Year}-{Sequence}/{Business premises label}/{Issuing device label}`. "
"If the journal is configured :ref:`as instructed above <localizations/"
"croatia/configuration/journal>`, Odoo automatically formats invoice names to "
"fit this format."
msgstr ""
"**Urutan faktur:** Pastikan urutan faktur dalam format `{Kode jurnal}-"
"{Tahun}-{Urutan}/{Business premises label}/{Issuing device label}`. Jika "
"jurnal dikonfigurasi :ref:`seperti yang diinstruksikan di atas "
"<localizations/croatia/configuration/journal>`, Odoo secara otomatis "
"memformat nama faktur agar sesuai dengan format ini."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/croatia.rst:127
msgid ""
":guilabel:`KPD category`: Set the :guilabel:`KPD category` on every invoice "
"line."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Kategori KPD`: Atur :guilabel:`Kategori KPD` pada setiap baris "
"faktur."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/croatia.rst:130
msgid ""
"The |KPD category| can also be set on the product record, which will then "
"automatically apply it on invoice lines when the product is used. To do so, "
"go to :menuselection:`Accounting -> Customers -> Products`, click the "
"product, and set the :guilabel:`KPD category`."
msgstr ""
"|KPD category| juga dapat diatur pada catatan produk, yang kemudian akan "
"secara otomatis diterapkan pada baris faktur saat produk digunakan. Untuk "
"melakukannya, buka :menuselection:`Akuntansi -> Pelanggan -> Produk`, klik "
"produk, dan atur :guilabel:`Kategori KPD`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/croatia.rst:134
msgid "In the :guilabel:`Croatia: Fiscalization 2.0` tab of invoices:"
msgstr "Di tab :guilabel:`Croatia: Fiscalization 2.0` pada faktur:"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/croatia.rst:136
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Business process type`: Set the :guilabel:`Business Process Type` "
"as appropriate. If :guilabel:`P99: Customer-defined process` is selected, "
"complete the :guilabel:`Custom Process Name` field."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Jenis proses bisnis`: Atur :guilabel:`Business Process Type` "
"sesuai kebutuhan. Jika :guilabel:`P99: Customer-defined process` dipilih, "
"lengkapi kolom :guilabel:`Custom Process Name`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/croatia.rst:139
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Fiscal user` and :guilabel:`Operator OIB`: The Croatian "
"government expects the user who sends the invoice to be identified via their "
"personal |OIB| number. The fiscal user defaults to the user who confirms the "
"invoice and is identified under :guilabel:`Fiscal User`."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Fiscal user` dan :guilabel:`Operator OIB`: Pemerintah Kroasia "
"mengharapkan pengguna yang mengirim faktur diidentifikasi melalui nomor "
"|OIB| pribadi mereka. Fiscal user default adalah pengguna yang mengonfirmasi "
"faktur dan diidentifikasi di bawah :guilabel:`Fiscal User`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/croatia.rst:143
msgid ""
"The user's |OIB| can be set on the user's contact record. To do so, follow "
"these steps:"
msgstr ""
"|OIB| pengguna dapat diatur pada catatan kontak pengguna. Untuk "
"melakukannya, ikuti langkah-langkah berikut:"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/croatia.rst:145
msgid ""
"Go to :menuselection:`Settings --> Users & Companies --> Users` and click "
"the user in the list view."
msgstr ""
"Buka :menuselection:`Pengaturan --> User & Perusahaan --> User` dan klik "
"pengguna di tampilan daftar."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/croatia.rst:147
msgid ""
"In the user's form, click the :guilabel:`Contact` smart button to access the "
"user's :guilabel:`Contact` form."
msgstr ""
"Di formulir pengguna, klik tombol pintar :guilabel:`Contact` untuk mengakses "
"formulir :guilabel:`Contact` pengguna."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/croatia.rst:149
msgid ""
"In the :guilabel:`Sales & Purchase` tab, set the :guilabel:`Personal OIB` in "
"the :guilabel:`Misc` section."
msgstr ""
"Di tab :guilabel:`Penjualan & Pembelian`, atur :guilabel:`Personal OIB` di "
"bagian :guilabel:`Misc`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/croatia.rst:152
msgid "Once an invoice has been sent:"
msgstr "Setelah faktur dikirim:"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/croatia.rst:154
msgid ""
"**Invoice fiscalization information:** The :guilabel:`Fiscalization "
"status`, :guilabel:`Fiscalization request ID`, :guilabel:`Payment amount "
"already reported to Tax Authority`, and :guilabel:`MojeRačun document "
"ElectronicId` can be viewed in the :guilabel:`Croatia: Fiscalization 2.0` "
"tab."
msgstr ""
"**Informasi fiskalisasi faktur:** :guilabel:`Status fiskalisasi`, "
":guilabel:`ID permintaan fiskalisasi`, :guilabel:`Jumlah pembayaran yang "
"sudah dilaporkan ke Otoritas Pajak`, dan :guilabel:`ElectronicId dokumen "
"MojeRačun` dapat dilihat di tab :guilabel:`Kroasia: Fiskalisasi 2.0`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/croatia.rst:158
msgid ""
"**Fetching status updates:** Odoo periodically checks for any updates to the "
"invoice's status (e.g., rejection by |MER|, the eRačun system, or the "
"recipient). To manually check for updates, go to "
"the :menuselection:`Accounting` dashboard, and in the :guilabel:`Customer "
"Invoices` (sales) journal, click the :guilabel:`MER: Fetch status` button."
msgstr ""
"**Mengambil pembaruan status:** Odoo secara berkala memeriksa pembaruan "
"status faktur (misalnya, penolakan oleh |MER|, sistem eRačun, atau penerima)"
". Untuk memeriksa pembaruan secara manual, buka dashboard "
":menuselection:`Akuntansi`, dan di jurnal :guilabel:`Faktur Pelanggan` "
"(penjualan), klik tombol :guilabel:`MER: Ambil status`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/croatia.rst:162
msgid ""
"**Reporting a payment:** The Croatian government expects to be notified once "
"payment has been received for an invoice. To send this notification, click "
"the :guilabel:`MER: Report payments` button on the invoice form view, which "
"appears if the invoice has unreported payments."
msgstr ""
"**Melaporkan pembayaran:** Pemerintah Kroasia mengharapkan untuk diberitahu "
"setelah pembayaran diterima untuk suatu faktur. Untuk mengirim notifikasi "
"ini, klik tombol :guilabel:`MER: Laporkan pembayaran` pada tampilan formulir "
"faktur, yang muncul jika faktur memiliki pembayaran yang belum dilaporkan."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/croatia.rst:167
msgid ""
"To report multiple payment notifications at once, select multiple invoices "
"from the invoice list view and click the :guilabel:`MER: Report payments` "
"button."
msgstr ""
"Untuk melaporkan beberapa notifikasi pembayaran sekaligus, pilih beberapa "
"faktur dari tampilan daftar faktur dan klik tombol :guilabel:`MER: Laporkan "
"pembayaran`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/croatia.rst:173
msgid "Receiving e-invoices"
msgstr "Menerima faktur elektronik"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/croatia.rst:175
msgid ""
"Odoo periodically checks for new invoices received via mojeRačun. New "
"invoices received via mojeRačun appear in the :guilabel:`Incoming E-Invoices "
"Journal` specified in the :ref:`settings <localizations/croatia/"
"configuration/company>`."
msgstr ""
"Odoo secara berkala memeriksa faktur baru yang diterima melalui mojeRačun. "
"Faktur baru yang diterima melalui mojeRačun muncul di :guilabel:`Jurnal "
"Faktur Elektronik Masuk` yang ditentukan di :ref:`pengaturan <localizations/"
"croatia/configuration/company>`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/croatia.rst:180
msgid "Rejecting an invoice"
msgstr "Menolak faktur"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/croatia.rst:182
msgid ""
"To reject an incoming invoice, click the :guilabel:`MER: Reject eRacun` "
"button on the invoice form view. This notifies the eRačun system and the "
"sender that the invoice is rejected."
msgstr ""
"Untuk menolak faktur masuk, klik tombol :guilabel:`MER: Tolak eRacun` pada "
"tampilan formulir faktur. Ini memberi tahu sistem eRačun dan pengirim bahwa "
"faktur ditolak."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/denmark.rst:3
msgid "Denmark"
msgstr "Denmark"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/denmark.rst:6
msgid ""
"Compliance with Danish bookkeeping requirements: data retention and integrity"
msgstr ""
"Kepatuhan terhadap persyaratan pembukuan Denmark: retensi dan integritas data"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/denmark.rst:8
msgid ""
"This page outlines how Odoo complies with the Danish Bookkeeping Act, "
"specifically regarding the storage and integrity of financial transactions "
"and receipts. Odoo recognizes the importance of adhering to Danish "
"regulations and has implemented robust measures to ensure clients' data is "
"secure and compliant."
msgstr ""
"Halaman ini menjelaskan bagaimana Odoo mematuhi Undang-Undang Pembukuan "
"Denmark, khususnya terkait penyimpanan dan integritas transaksi keuangan dan "
"tanda terima. Odoo menyadari pentingnya mematuhi peraturan Denmark dan telah "
"menerapkan langkah-langkah yang kuat untuk memastikan data klien aman dan "
"sesuai ketentuan."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/denmark.rst:14
msgid ""
"Odoo’s registration as a digital bookkeeping system has been confirmed by "
"the Danish Business Authority under registration numbers `fob585505` and "
"`fob441967`. Customers must meet certain conditions to benefit from it, as "
"outlined below."
msgstr ""
"Pendaftaran Odoo sebagai sistem pembukuan digital telah dikonfirmasi oleh "
"Otoritas Bisnis Denmark dengan nomor registrasi `fob585505` dan `fob441967`. "
"Pelanggan harus memenuhi kondisi tertentu untuk mendapatkan manfaatnya, "
"sebagaimana diuraikan di bawah ini."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/denmark.rst:20
msgid "Key requirements of the Danish Bookkeeping Act"
msgstr "Persyaratan utama Undang-Undang Pembukuan Denmark"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/denmark.rst:22
msgid ""
"The Danish Bookkeeping Act (DBA) outlines the `requirements for digital "
"bookkeping systems <https://danishbusinessauthority.dk/requirements-digital-"
"bookkeeping-systems>`_:"
msgstr ""
"Undang-Undang Pembukuan Denmark (DBA) menguraikan `persyaratan untuk sistem "
"pembukuan digital <https://danishbusinessauthority.dk/requirements-digital-"
"bookkeeping-systems>`_:"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/denmark.rst:25
msgid ""
"**Retain transactional data and receipts:** Store all recorded transactions "
"and receipts covered by § 3 for a minimum of five years from the end of the "
"financial year to which they pertain."
msgstr ""
"**Simpan data transaksi dan tanda terima:** Simpan semua transaksi yang "
"dicatat dan tanda terima yang tercakup dalam § 3 selama minimal lima tahun "
"sejak akhir tahun keuangan yang terkait."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/denmark.rst:28
msgid ""
"**Ensure data integrity:** Prevent the customer from changing, backdating, "
"or deleting recorded transactions."
msgstr ""
"**Pastikan integritas data:** Cegah pelanggan mengubah, memundurkan tanggal, "
"atau menghapus transaksi yang telah dicatat."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/denmark.rst:30
msgid ""
"**Maintain data accessibility:** Store all recorded transactions in a "
"structured and machine-readable format for the required five-year period, "
"regardless of customer relationship status, bankruptcy, or dissolution."
msgstr ""
"**Pertahankan aksesibilitas data:** Simpan semua transaksi yang dicatat "
"dalam format terstruktur dan dapat dibaca mesin selama periode lima tahun "
"yang diperlukan, terlepas dari status hubungan pelanggan, kebangkrutan, atau "
"pembubaran."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/denmark.rst:33
msgid ""
"**Provide decryption capabilities:** Ensure that encrypted bookkeeping data "
"and receipts can be decrypted into a structured and readable format."
msgstr ""
"**Sediakan kemampuan dekripsi:** Pastikan data pembukuan dan tanda terima "
"terenkripsi dapat didekripsi ke dalam format terstruktur dan dapat dibaca."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/denmark.rst:37
msgid "Odoo Compliance"
msgstr "Kepatuhan Odoo"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/denmark.rst:39
msgid ""
"Odoo's registration as digital standard bookkeeping systems with the Danish "
"Business Authority confirms that Odoo meets the applicable criteria for "
"digital bookkeeping systems in Denmark, in accordance with the requirements "
"of the :abbr:`DBA (Danish Bookkeeping Act)`."
msgstr ""
"Pendaftaran Odoo sebagai sistem pembukuan standar digital dengan Otoritas "
"Bisnis Denmark mengonfirmasi bahwa Odoo memenuhi kriteria yang berlaku untuk "
"sistem pembukuan digital di Denmark, sesuai dengan persyaratan :abbr:`DBA "
"(Undang-Undang Pembukuan Denmark)`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/denmark.rst:43
msgid ""
"However, to benefit from all the required guarantees for digital bookkeeping "
"systems in Denmark, customers must meet a few conditions."
msgstr ""
"Namun, untuk mendapatkan semua jaminan yang diperlukan untuk sistem "
"pembukuan digital di Denmark, pelanggan harus memenuhi beberapa kondisi."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/denmark.rst:47
msgid "Conditions for full DBA compliance"
msgstr "Kondisi untuk kepatuhan DBA penuh"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/denmark.rst:49
msgid ""
"The customer uses Odoo Accounting on the Odoo SaaS platform (Odoo Online);"
msgstr ""
"Pelanggan menggunakan Odoo Akuntansi pada platform Odoo SaaS (Odoo Online);"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/denmark.rst:50
msgid ""
"The customer has an active Odoo subscription (e.g., Standard or Custom "
"Plan), or their database is managed by an officially registered `Odoo "
"Accounting Firm <https://www.odoo.com/accounting-firms>`_;"
msgstr ""
"Pelanggan memiliki langganan Odoo aktif (misalnya, Paket Standard atau "
"Custom), atau database mereka dikelola oleh `Firma Akuntansi Odoo <https://"
"www.odoo.com/accounting-firms>`_ yang terdaftar secara resmi;"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/denmark.rst:52
msgid ""
"The customer refrains from customizations or actions intended to undermine "
"the system’s immutability, traceability, or security controls."
msgstr ""
"Pelanggan menghindari kustomisasi atau tindakan yang dimaksudkan untuk "
"merusak ketidakberubahan sistem, kemampuan pelacakan, atau kontrol keamanan."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/denmark.rst:56
msgid ""
"Customers using Odoo products outside these conditions are responsible for "
"ensuring their own compliance with the DBA."
msgstr ""
"Pelanggan yang menggunakan produk Odoo di luar kondisi ini bertanggung jawab "
"untuk memastikan kepatuhan mereka sendiri terhadap DBA."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/denmark.rst:59
msgid ""
"When the above conditions are met, the requirements of the DBA are fulfilled "
"through features and processes described in the following sections."
msgstr ""
"Ketika kondisi di atas terpenuhi, persyaratan DBA dipenuhi melalui fitur dan "
"proses yang dijelaskan dalam bagian berikut."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/denmark.rst:63
msgid "Immutable transaction records"
msgstr "Catatan transaksi yang tidak dapat diubah"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/denmark.rst:65
msgid ""
"Once transactions are recorded, they cannot be deleted through the user "
"interface."
msgstr ""
"Setelah transaksi dicatat, transaksi tersebut tidak dapat dihapus melalui "
"antarmuka pengguna."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/denmark.rst:66
msgid "All modifications are logged, providing a complete audit trail."
msgstr "Semua modifikasi dicatat, menyediakan jejak audit yang lengkap."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/denmark.rst:67
msgid ""
"While historically dated entries can be made, Odoo records the creation date "
"and time of the entry."
msgstr ""
"Meskipun entri bertanggal historis dapat dibuat, Odoo mencatat tanggal dan "
"waktu pembuatan entri."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/denmark.rst:70
msgid "Secure document storage"
msgstr "Penyimpanan dokumen aman"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/denmark.rst:72
msgid ""
"Receipts and digital vouchers are stored as attachments and integrated into "
"the database, ensuring they are included in backups."
msgstr ""
"Tanda terima dan voucher digital disimpan sebagai lampiran dan "
"diintegrasikan ke dalam database, memastikan bahwa mereka disertakan dalam "
"cadangan."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/denmark.rst:74
msgid "Posted documents cannot be deleted."
msgstr "Dokumen yang telah diposting tidak dapat dihapus."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/denmark.rst:75
msgid ""
"We fully support the storage of mandatory digital vouchers as defined by "
"Danish regulations."
msgstr ""
"Kami sepenuhnya mendukung penyimpanan voucher digital wajib sebagaimana "
"ditentukan oleh peraturan Denmark."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/denmark.rst:78
msgid "Continuous data availability"
msgstr "Ketersediaan data berkelanjutan"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/denmark.rst:80
msgid ""
"Clients with active subscriptions can access all transactions and digital "
"vouchers through Odoo."
msgstr ""
"Klien dengan Langganan aktif dapat mengakses semua transaksi dan voucher "
"digital melalui Odoo."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/denmark.rst:81
msgid ""
"Regardless of customer relations, bankruptcy, or dissolution, Odoo can "
"provide access to transaction and digital voucher details to former clients "
"for six years (see :ref:`localizations/denmark/data-lifecycle`)."
msgstr ""
"Terlepas dari hubungan pelanggan, kebangkrutan, atau pembubaran, Odoo dapat "
"menyediakan akses ke detail transaksi dan voucher digital kepada klien lama "
"selama enam tahun (lihat :ref:`localizations/denmark/data-lifecycle`)."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/denmark.rst:85
msgid "Automated data export and secure storage"
msgstr "Ekspor data otomatis dan penyimpanan aman"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/denmark.rst:87
msgid ""
"Odoo Accounting implements no automatic deletion or archival of recorded "
"transactions, so if a customer has been recording transactions for six "
"years, the six years of history are preserved in the Odoo Accounting "
"database."
msgstr ""
"Odoo Akuntansi tidak menerapkan penghapusan atau pengarsipan otomatis "
"terhadap transaksi yang tercatat, sehingga jika pelanggan telah mencatat "
"transaksi selama enam tahun, riwayat enam tahun tersebut akan tersimpan "
"dalam database Odoo Akuntansi."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/denmark.rst:89
msgid ""
"As described in the `Odoo Cloud Hosting SLA <https://www.odoo.com/cloud-"
"sla>`_ and `Odoo Privacy Policy <https://www.odoo.com/privacy>`_, the Odoo "
"Cloud relies on immutable daily snapshot backups, which cannot be "
"individually altered or deleted, even at the customer's request, ensuring "
"their integrity."
msgstr ""
"Sebagaimana dijelaskan dalam `Odoo Cloud Hosting SLA <https://www.odoo.com/"
"cloud-sla>`_ dan `Odoo Privacy Policy <https://www.odoo.com/privacy>`_, Odoo "
"Cloud mengandalkan cadangan snapshot harian yang tidak dapat diubah, yang "
"tidak dapat diubah atau dihapus secara individual, bahkan atas permintaan "
"pelanggan, sehingga menjamin integritasnya."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/denmark.rst:92
msgid ""
"All documents and receipts stored in a database backup are available as a "
"standard ZIP archive accompanying the SQL dump."
msgstr ""
"Semua dokumen dan tanda terima yang disimpan dalam cadangan database "
"tersedia sebagai arsip ZIP standar yang menyertai dump SQL."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/denmark.rst:98
msgid "Data lifecycle management"
msgstr "Manajemen siklus hidup data"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/denmark.rst:100
msgid ""
"Odoo database backups are available in standard SQL dump formats at all "
"times and include all recorded transactions."
msgstr ""
"Cadangan database Odoo tersedia dalam format dump SQL standar setiap saat "
"dan mencakup semua transaksi yang tercatat."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/denmark.rst:102
msgid ""
"The `Odoo Cloud Hosting SLA <https://www.odoo.com/cloud-sla>`_ guarantees "
"three months of backup history to all active customers. As a special "
"guarantee for Danish customers subject to the DBA and meeting the conditions "
"highlighted above the last Odoo Cloud backup retention gets increased to six "
"years as soon as they decide to terminate their Odoo Cloud subscription, in "
"order to comply with the requirements of Annex 1, 4 of Executive Order 97."
msgstr ""
"`Odoo Cloud Hosting SLA <https://www.odoo.com/cloud-sla>`_ menjamin riwayat "
"cadangan tiga bulan untuk semua pelanggan aktif. Sebagai jaminan khusus bagi "
"pelanggan Denmark yang tunduk pada DBA dan memenuhi kondisi yang disorot di "
"atas, retensi cadangan Odoo Cloud terakhir akan ditingkatkan menjadi enam "
"tahun segera setelah mereka memutuskan untuk mengakhiri Langganan Odoo Cloud "
"mereka, untuk mematuhi persyaratan Lampiran 1, 4 dari Perintah Eksekutif 97."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/denmark.rst:108
msgid "Decryption"
msgstr "Dekripsi"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/denmark.rst:110
msgid ""
"Odoo Accounting customer data on the Odoo Cloud is always stored in "
"encrypted form (encryption at rest at storage level). When backups are "
"retrieved, they are automatically decrypted and provided in decrypted form "
"in standard formats for the user: SQL dumps + ZIP archive of all attached "
"documents (file store)."
msgstr ""
"Data pelanggan Odoo Akuntansi di Odoo Cloud selalu disimpan dalam bentuk "
"terenkripsi (enkripsi saat penyimpanan di tingkat penyimpanan). Ketika "
"cadangan diambil, mereka secara otomatis didekripsi dan disediakan dalam "
"bentuk terdekripsi dalam format standar untuk user: dump SQL + arsip ZIP "
"dari semua dokumen terlampir (penyimpanan file)."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/ecuador.rst:3
msgid "Ecuador"
msgstr "Ekuador"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/ecuador.rst:5
msgid ""
"With the Ecuadorian localization, electronic documents can be generated "
"using XML, fiscal folio, electronic signature, and direct connection to tax "
"authority SRI."
msgstr ""
"Dengan lokalisasi Ekuador, dokumen elektronik dapat dibuat menggunakan XML, "
"folio fiskal, tanda tangan elektronik, dan koneksi langsung ke otoritas "
"pajak SRI."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/ecuador.rst:8
msgid ""
"The supported documents are invoices, credit notes, debit notes, purchase "
"liquidations, and withholdings."
msgstr ""
"Dokumen yang didukung adalah faktur, nota kredit, nota debit, likuidasi "
"Pembelian, dan pemotongan pajak."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/ecuador.rst:11
msgid ""
"The localization also includes automation to easily predict the withholding "
"tax to be applied to each purchase invoice."
msgstr ""
"Lokalisasi ini juga mencakup otomatisasi untuk dengan mudah memprediksi "
"pajak pemotongan yang akan diterapkan pada setiap faktur Pembelian."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/ecuador.rst:15
msgid ""
"`App Tour - Localización de Ecuador <https://www.youtube.com/watch?"
"v=BQOXVSDeeK8>`_"
msgstr ""
"`App Tour - Localización de Ecuador <https://www.youtube.com/"
"watch?v=BQOXVSDeeK8>`_"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/ecuador.rst:16
msgid ""
"`Smart Tutorial - Localización de Ecuador <https://www.odoo.com/slides/smart-"
"tutorial-localizacion-de-ecuador-170>`_"
msgstr ""
"`Smart Tutorial - Localización de Ecuador <https://www.odoo.com/slides/smart-"
"tutorial-localizacion-de-ecuador-170>`_"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/ecuador.rst:18
msgid ""
":doc:`Documentation on e-invoicing's legality and compliance in Ecuador <../"
"accounting/customer_invoices/electronic_invoicing/ecuador>`"
msgstr ""
":doc:`Dokumentasi tentang legalitas dan kepatuhan e-invoicing di Ekuador <../"
"accounting/customer_invoices/electronic_invoicing/ecuador>`"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/ecuador.rst:22
msgid ""
"**SRI**: *Servicio de Rentas Internas*, the government organization that "
"enforces the payment of taxes in Ecuador."
msgstr ""
"**SRI**: *Servicio de Rentas Internas*, organisasi pemerintah yang mengawasi "
"pembayaran pajak di Ekuador."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/ecuador.rst:24
msgid ""
"**SRI certificate**: Document or digital credential issued by the *SRI* that "
"is crucial for compliance with Ecuadorian tax laws."
msgstr ""
"**Sertifikat SRI**: Dokumen atau kredensial digital yang dikeluarkan oleh "
"*SRI* yang sangat penting untuk kepatuhan terhadap undang-undang perpajakan "
"Ekuador."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/ecuador.rst:26
msgid ""
"**EDI**: *Electronic Data Interchange*, which refers to the electronic "
"transmission of documents."
msgstr ""
"**EDI**: *Electronic Data Interchange*, yang mengacu pada transmisi dokumen "
"secara elektronik."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/ecuador.rst:28
msgid ""
"**RIMPE**: *Regimen Simplificado para Emprendedores y Negocios*, the type of "
"taxpayer qualified for SRI."
msgstr ""
"**RIMPE**: *Regimen Simplificado para Emprendedores y Negocios*, jenis wajib "
"pajak yang memenuhi syarat untuk SRI."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/ecuador.rst:36
msgid ""
":doc:`Install </applications/general/apps_modules>` the following modules to "
"get all the features of the Ecuadorian localization:"
msgstr ""
":doc:`Instal </applications/general/apps_modules>` modul-modul berikut untuk "
"mendapatkan semua fitur lokalisasi Ekuador:"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/ecuador.rst:46
msgid ":guilabel:`Ecuadorian - Accounting`"
msgstr ":guilabel:`Ekuador - Akuntansi`"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/ecuador.rst:47
msgid "`l10n_ec`"
msgstr "`l10n_ec`"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/ecuador.rst:48
msgid ""
"The default :doc:`fiscal localization package <../fiscal_localizations>` "
"adds accounting characteristics for the Ecuadorian localization, which "
"represent the minimum configuration required for a company to operate in "
"Ecuador according to the guidelines set by the :abbr:`SRI (servicio de "
"rentas internas)`. The module's installation automatically loads: a chart of "
"accounts, taxes, document types, and tax support types. Additionally, the "
"generation of forms 103 and 104 is automatic."
msgstr ""
"Paket :doc:`lokalisasi fiskal <../fiscal_localizations>` default menambahkan "
"karakteristik akuntansi untuk lokalisasi Ekuador, yang merupakan konfigurasi "
"minimum yang diperlukan bagi perusahaan untuk beroperasi di Ekuador sesuai "
"dengan pedoman yang ditetapkan oleh :abbr:`SRI (servicio de rentas internas)"
"`. Instalasi modul secara otomatis memuat: bagan akun, pajak, jenis dokumen, "
"dan jenis dukungan pajak. Selain itu, pembuatan formulir 103 dan 104 "
"dilakukan secara otomatis."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/ecuador.rst:54
msgid ":guilabel:`Ecuadorian Accounting EDI`"
msgstr ":guilabel:`Akuntansi EDI Ekuador`"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/ecuador.rst:55
msgid "`l10n_ec_edi`"
msgstr "`l10n_ec_edi`"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/ecuador.rst:56
msgid ""
"Includes all the technical and functional requirements to generate and "
"validate :doc:`Electronics Documents <../accounting/customer_invoices/"
"electronic_invoicing>` based on the technical documentation published by the "
"SRI. The authorized documents are: Invoices, Credit Notes, Debit Notes, "
"Withholdings, and Purchase liquidations."
msgstr ""
"Mencakup semua persyaratan teknis dan fungsional untuk menghasilkan dan "
"memvalidasi :doc:`Dokumen Elektronik <../accounting/customer_invoices/"
"electronic_invoicing>` berdasarkan dokumentasi teknis yang dipublikasikan "
"oleh SRI. Dokumen yang diotorisasi adalah: Faktur, Nota Kredit, Nota Debit, "
"Pemotongan, dan likuidasi Pembelian."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/ecuador.rst:60
msgid ":guilabel:`Ecuadorian Accounting Reports`"
msgstr ":guilabel:`Laporan Akuntansi Ekuador`"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/ecuador.rst:61
msgid "`l10n_ec_reports`"
msgstr "`l10n_ec_reports`"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/ecuador.rst:62
msgid ""
"Includes all the technical and functional requirements to generate forms 103 "
"and 104."
msgstr ""
"Mencakup semua persyaratan teknis dan fungsional untuk menghasilkan formulir "
"103 dan 104."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/ecuador.rst:63
