"kredensial API. Anda memerlukan kode ini untuk :ref:`mengonfigurasi aplikasi "
"Odoo Accounting <egypt/e-invoicing-configuration>`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/egypt.rst:49
msgid ""
"Access your company profile on the ETA portal by clicking on :guilabel:`View "
"Taxpayer Profile`."
msgstr ""
"Akses profil perusahaan Anda di portal ETA dengan mengklik :guilabel:`View "
"Taxpayer Profile`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/egypt.rst:None
msgid "Clicking on \"View Taxpayer Profile\" on an ETA invoicing portal"
