#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/france.rst:157
msgid "FEC - Fichier des Écritures Comptables"
msgstr "FEC - Fichier des Écritures Comptables"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/france.rst:159
msgid ""
"An FEC :dfn:`Fichier des Écritures Comptables` audit file contains all the "
"accounting data and entries recorded in all the accounting journals for a "
"financial year. The entries in the file must be arranged in chronological "
"order. Since January 2014, every French company is required to produce and "
"transmit this file upon request by the tax authorities for audit purposes."
msgstr ""
"File audit FEC :dfn:`Fichier des Écritures Comptables` berisi semua data dan "
"entri akuntansi yang dicatat dalam semua jurnal akuntansi untuk tahun "
"keuangan. Entri dalam file harus disusun secara kronologis. Sejak Januari "
"2014, setiap perusahaan Prancis diwajibkan untuk membuat dan mengirimkan "
"file ini atas permintaan otoritas pajak untuk tujuan audit."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/france.rst:167
msgid "FEC Import"
msgstr "Impor FEC"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/france.rst:169
msgid ""
":doc:`Install </applications/general/apps_modules>` the :guilabel:`France - "
"FEC Import` (`l10n_fr_fec_import`) module to import FEC files from other "
"software."
msgstr ""
":doc:`Pasang </applications/general/apps_modules>` modul :guilabel:`France - "
"FEC Import` (`l10n_fr_fec_import`) untuk mengimpor file FEC dari perangkat "
"lunak lain."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/france.rst:172
msgid ""
"To enable this feature, go to :menuselection:`Accounting --> Configuration --"
"> Settings`. In the :guilabel:`Accounting Import` section, click :icon:`oi-"
"arrow-right` :guilabel:`Import` and :guilabel:`Import FEC`. Then, in "
"the :guilabel:`FEC Import` window, upload the FEC file and "
"click :guilabel:`Import`."
msgstr ""
"Untuk mengaktifkan fitur ini, buka :menuselection:`Akuntansi --> "
"Konfigurasi --> Pengaturan`. Di bagian :guilabel:`Impor Akuntansi`, klik "
":icon:`oi-arrow-right` :guilabel:`Impor` dan :guilabel:`Impor FEC`. "
"Kemudian, di jendela :guilabel:`Impor FEC`, unggah file FEC dan klik "
":guilabel:`Impor`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/france.rst:178
msgid ""
"Importing FEC files from different years requires no particular actions or "
"computations. However, if multiple files contain RAN :dfn:`Reports à "
"Nouveaux` with the starting balance for the year, these entries are "
"automatically marked as unnecessary in Odoo and may need to be deleted."
msgstr ""
"Mengimpor file FEC dari tahun yang berbeda tidak memerlukan tindakan atau "
"perhitungan khusus. Namun, jika beberapa file berisi RAN :dfn:`Reports à "
"Nouveaux` dengan saldo awal untuk tahun tersebut, entri ini secara otomatis "
"ditandai sebagai tidak diperlukan di Odoo dan mungkin perlu dihapus."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/france.rst:185
msgid "File formats"
msgstr "Format file"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/france.rst:188
msgid "FEC files must be in CSV format, as XML format is not supported."
msgstr "File FEC harus dalam format CSV, karena format XML tidak didukung."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/france.rst:189
msgid ""
"The FEC CSV file is a plain text file structured as a data table. The first "
"line serves as the header, defining the list of fields for each entry, and "
"each following line represents a single accounting entry without any "
"specific order."
msgstr ""
"File CSV FEC adalah file teks biasa yang terstruktur sebagai tabel data. "
"Baris pertama berfungsi sebagai header, mendefinisikan daftar kolom untuk "
"setiap entri, dan setiap baris berikutnya mewakili satu entri akuntansi "
"tanpa urutan tertentu."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/france.rst:193
msgid "FEC files must comply with the following technical specifications:"
msgstr "File FEC harus mematuhi spesifikasi teknis berikut:"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/france.rst:195
msgid "**Encoding**: UTF-8, UTF-8-SIG and iso8859_15."
msgstr "**Encoding**: UTF-8, UTF-8-SIG dan iso8859_15."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/france.rst:196
msgid "**Separator**: any of these: `;` or `|` or `,` or `TAB`."
msgstr "**Separator**: salah satu dari: `;` atau `|` atau `,` atau `TAB`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/france.rst:197
msgid ""
"**Line terminators**: both CR+LF (`\\\\r\\\\n`) and LF (`\\\\n`) character "
"groups are supported."
msgstr ""
"**Line terminators**: kedua grup karakter CR+LF (`\\\\r\\\\n`) dan LF (`\\\\"
"n`) didukung."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/france.rst:198
msgid "**Date format**: `%Y%m%d`"
msgstr "**Format tanggal**: `%Y%m%d`"

