#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/france.rst:268
msgid "Implementation details"
msgstr "Detail implementasi"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/france.rst:270
msgid ""
"The following accounting entities are imported from the FEC files: "
"**Accounts, Journals, Partners**, and **Moves**. The module automatically "
"determines the encoding, line terminator, and separator used in the file. "
"Next, a check is performed to ensure that each line has the correct number "
"of fields matching the header. If the check is successful, the entire file "
"is read, stored in memory, and scanned. Accounting entities are then "
"imported one type at a time in the following order."
msgstr ""
"Entitas akuntansi berikut diimpor dari file FEC: **Akun, Jurnal, Mitra**, "
"dan **Perpindahan**. Modul secara otomatis menentukan encoding, pembatas "
"baris, dan pemisah yang digunakan dalam file. Selanjutnya, pemeriksaan "
"dilakukan untuk memastikan bahwa setiap baris memiliki jumlah bidang yang "
"benar sesuai dengan header. Jika pemeriksaan berhasil, seluruh file dibaca, "
"disimpan dalam memori, dan dipindai. Entitas akuntansi kemudian diimpor satu "
"jenis pada satu waktu dalam urutan berikut."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/france.rst:279
msgid "Accounts"
msgstr "Akun"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/france.rst:281
msgid ""
"Each accounting entry is associated with an account identified by "
"the :guilabel:`CompteNum` field."
msgstr ""
"Setiap entri akuntansi dikaitkan dengan akun yang diidentifikasi oleh bidang "
":guilabel:`CompteNum`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/france.rst:286
msgid "Code matching"
msgstr "Pencocokan kode"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/france.rst:288
msgid ""
"If an account with the same code already exists, the existing one is used "
"rather than creating a new one. In Odoo, account numbers follow the default "
"digit length of the fiscal localization. Since the FEC module is tied to the "
"French localization, the default account length is 6 digits. This means that "
"trailing zeros in account codes are removed, and the comparison between the "
"account codes in the FEC file and those already in Odoo is made based only "
"on the first six digits of the codes."
msgstr ""
"Jika akun dengan kode yang sama sudah ada, akun yang ada digunakan daripada "
"membuat yang baru. Di Odoo, nomor akun mengikuti panjang digit default dari "
"lokalisasi fiskal. Karena modul FEC terikat pada lokalisasi Prancis, panjang "
"akun default adalah 6 digit. Ini berarti bahwa nol di belakang dalam kode "
"akun dihapus, dan perbandingan antara kode akun dalam file FEC dan yang "
"sudah ada di Odoo dibuat hanya berdasarkan enam digit pertama dari kode."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/france.rst:296
msgid ""
"The account code `65800000` in the file is matched with an existing `658000` "
"account in Odoo, and the existing account is used instead of creating a new "
"one."
msgstr ""
"Kode akun `65800000` dalam file dicocokkan dengan akun `658000` yang ada di "
"Odoo, dan akun yang ada digunakan sebagai pengganti pembuatan yang baru."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/france.rst:302
msgid "Reconcilable flag"
msgstr "Tanda dapat direkonsiliasi"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/france.rst:304
msgid ""
"An account is technically flagged as *reconcilable* if the first line in "
"which it appears has the :guilabel:`EcritureLet` field filled out, "
"indicating that the accounting entry will be reconciled with another one."
msgstr ""
"Sebuah akun secara teknis ditandai sebagai *dapat direkonsiliasi* jika baris "
"pertama di mana akun tersebut muncul memiliki bidang :guilabel:`EcritureLet` "
"yang terisi, yang menunjukkan bahwa entri akuntansi akan direkonsiliasi "
"dengan yang lain."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/france.rst:309
msgid ""
"The field can be left empty on the line, but the entry must still be "
"reconciled with an unrecorded payment. The account is flagged as "
"reconcilable once the import of the move lines requires it."
msgstr ""
"Bidang dapat dibiarkan kosong pada baris, tetapi entri masih harus "
"direkonsiliasi dengan pembayaran yang tidak tercatat. Akun ditandai sebagai "
"dapat direkonsiliasi setelah impor baris perpindahan memerlukannya."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/france.rst:316
msgid "Account type and templates matching"
msgstr "Pencocokan jenis dan templat akun"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/france.rst:318
msgid ""
"Since the account **type** is not specified in the FEC format, **new** "
"accounts are created with the default type :guilabel:`Current Assets`. After "
"the import process, they are matched against the installed Chart of Account "
"templates. The *reconcile* flag is also determined this way."
msgstr ""
"Karena **jenis** akun tidak ditentukan dalam format FEC, akun **baru** "
"dibuat dengan jenis default :guilabel:`Aset Lancar`. Setelah proses impor, "
"akun tersebut dicocokkan dengan templat Bagan Akun yang terpasang. Flag "
"*rekonsiliasi* juga ditentukan dengan cara ini."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/france.rst:322
msgid ""
"The matching is performed by comparing the left-most digits, starting with "
"all digits, followed by 3 digits, and then 2 digits."
msgstr ""
"Pencocokan dilakukan dengan membandingkan digit paling kiri, dimulai dengan "
"semua digit, diikuti oleh 3 digit, dan kemudian 2 digit."

