msgid "Company registration and fiscal year information"
msgstr "Informasi pendaftaran perusahaan dan tahun fiskal"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/france.rst:527
msgid ""
"To register the company on Teledec, go to :guilabel:`Vos entreprises` (Your "
"companies) and click :guilabel:`Enregistrer votre entreprise` (Register your "
"company). Make sure to fill in the following company information in "
"the :guilabel:`Coordonnées de l'entreprise` (Company's details) "
