"partial :guilabel:`Amount` to be received; the :guilabel:`Amount to receive` "
"field updates automatically."
msgstr ""
"Di bidang :guilabel:`Jumlah`, masukkan total atau sebagian "
":guilabel:`Jumlah` yang akan diterima; bidang :guilabel:`Jumlah yang akan "
"diterima` akan diperbarui secara otomatis."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/france.rst:638
msgid ""
"A yellow banner appears if the amount does not match the amount that needs "
"to be received. If proceeding without matching the VAT amount, the "
"difference will be carried over to the next period."
msgstr ""
"Spanduk kuning muncul jika jumlahnya tidak sesuai dengan jumlah yang perlu "
"diterima. Jika melanjutkan tanpa mencocokkan jumlah PPN, selisihnya akan "
"dibawa ke periode berikutnya."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/france.rst:642
msgid ""
"Click :guilabel:`Send VAT Report` to submit the tax return (VAT report) "
"to :abbr:`DGFIP (Direction Générale des Finances Publiques)`."
msgstr ""
"Klik :guilabel:`Kirim Laporan PPN` untuk mengirimkan SPT (laporan PPN) ke "
":abbr:`DGFIP (Direction Générale des Finances Publiques)`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/france.rst:645
msgid ""
"The :guilabel:`Submit` action step turns orange, and a submission message "
"appears in the chatter, then turns green when :abbr:`DGFIP (Direction "
"Générale des Finances Publiques)` confirms reception."
msgstr ""
"Langkah tindakan :guilabel:`Kirim` berubah menjadi oranye, dan pesan "
"pengiriman muncul di chatter, kemudian berubah menjadi hijau ketika "
":abbr:`DGFIP (Direction Générale des Finances Publiques)` mengonfirmasi "
"penerimaan."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/france.rst:649
msgid ""
"To access the tax report XML file, go to :menuselection:`Accounting --> "
"Reporting --> EDI Exports`."
msgstr ""
"Untuk mengakses file XML laporan pajak, buka :menuselection:`Akuntansi --> "
"Pelaporan --> Ekspor EDI`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/france.rst:660
msgid "VAT anti-fraud certification"
msgstr "Sertifikasi anti-penipuan PPN"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/france.rst:662
msgid ""
"Since January 2018, new anti-fraud legislation has been in effect in France "
"and its overseas territories (DOM-TOM). This legislation establishes "
"specific requirements for the integrity, security, storage, and archiving of "
"sales data. Odoo complies with these legal requirements by providing a "
"module and a downloadable certificate of conformity."
msgstr ""
"Sejak Januari 2018, undang-undang anti-penipuan baru telah berlaku di "
"Prancis dan wilayah seberang lautnya (DOM-TOM). Undang-undang ini menetapkan "
"persyaratan khusus untuk integritas, keamanan, penyimpanan, dan pengarsipan "
"data penjualan. Odoo mematuhi persyaratan hukum ini dengan menyediakan modul "
"dan sertifikat kesesuaian yang dapat diunduh."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/france.rst:667
msgid ""
"Anti-fraud cash register software, such as Odoo (CGI art. 286, I. 3° bis), "
"is required for companies taxable in France or DOM-TOM, where some customers "
"are private individuals (B2C). This rule applies to all company sizes, but "
"auto-entrepreneurs exempt from VAT are unaffected."
msgstr ""
"Perangkat lunak kasir anti-penipuan, seperti Odoo (CGI art. 286, I. 3° bis), "
"diperlukan untuk perusahaan yang dikenakan pajak di Prancis atau DOM-TOM, di "
"mana beberapa pelanggan adalah individu pribadi (B2C). Aturan ini berlaku "
"untuk semua ukuran perusahaan, tetapi auto-entrepreneur yang dikecualikan "
"dari PPN tidak terpengaruh."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/france.rst:672
msgid ""
"`Frequently Asked Questions <https://www.economie.gouv.fr/files/files/"
"directions_services/dgfip/controle_fiscal/actualites_reponses/"
"logiciels_de_caisse.pdf>`_"
msgstr ""
"`Pertanyaan yang Sering Diajukan <https://www.economie.gouv.fr/files/files/"
"directions_services/dgfip/controle_fiscal/actualites_reponses/"
"logiciels_de_caisse.pdf>`_"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/france.rst:674
msgid ""
"`Official Statement <http://bofip.impots.gouv.fr/bofip/10691-PGP.html?"
"identifiant=BOI-TVA-DECLA-30-10-30-20160803>`_"
msgstr ""
"<http://bofip.impots.gouv.fr/bofip/10691-PGP.html?identifiant=BOI-TVA-DECLA-"
"30-10-30-20160803>`Pernyataan Resmi`_"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/france.rst:676
msgid ""
"`Item 88 of Finance Law 2016 <https://www.legifrance.gouv.fr/"
"affichTexteArticle.do?"
"idArticle=JORFARTI000031732968&categorieLien=id&cidTexte=JORFTEXT000031732865>`_"
msgstr ""
"`Item 88 Undang-Undang Keuangan 2016 <https://www.legifrance.gouv.fr/"
"affichTexteArticle.do?idArticle=JORFARTI000031732968&categorieLien=id&cidTexte=JORFTEXT000031732865>"
"`_"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/france.rst:682
msgid "Odoo certification"
msgstr "Sertifikasi Odoo"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/france.rst:684
msgid ""
"The tax administration requires all companies to provide a certificate of "
"conformity confirming that their software complies with anti-fraud "
"legislation. In case of non-compliance, a €7,500 fine may be imposed."
msgstr ""
"Administrasi pajak mengharuskan semua perusahaan untuk menyediakan "
"sertifikat kesesuaian yang mengonfirmasi bahwa perangkat lunak mereka "
"mematuhi undang-undang anti-penipuan. Dalam kasus ketidakpatuhan, denda €"
"7.500 dapat dikenakan."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/france.rst:689
msgid ""
"This `certificate <https://www.odoo.com/my/contract/french-certification/>`_ "
"is granted by Odoo SA to Odoo Enterprise users with a subscription number."
msgstr ""
"Sertifikat `ini <https://www.odoo.com/my/contract/french-certification/>`_ "
"diberikan oleh Odoo SA kepada pengguna Odoo Enterprise dengan nomor "
"langganan."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/france.rst:692
msgid "To get the certification, follow these steps:"
msgstr "Untuk mendapatkan sertifikasi, ikuti langkah-langkah berikut:"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/france.rst:694
msgid ""
":doc:`Install </applications/general/apps_modules>` the :guilabel:`France - "
"VAT Anti-Fraud Certification for Point of Sale (CGI 286 I-3 bis)` "
"(`l10n_fr_pos_cert`) module."
msgstr ""
":doc:`Instal </applications/general/apps_modules>` modul :guilabel:`France - "
"VAT Anti-Fraud Certification for Point of Sale (CGI 286 I-3 bis)` "
"(`l10n_fr_pos_cert`)."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/france.rst:696
msgid ""
"Set the :guilabel:`Country` field on the :doc:`company record </applications/"
"general/companies>` to encrypt entries for the inalterability check."
msgstr ""
"Atur bidang :guilabel:`Country` pada :doc:`catatan perusahaan </applications/"
"general/companies>` untuk mengenkripsi entri untuk pemeriksaan "
"ketidakterubahan."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/france.rst:698
msgid ""
"Download the mandatory `certificate of conformity <https://www.odoo.com/my/"
"contract/french-certification/>`_ delivered by Odoo SA."
msgstr ""
"Unduh `sertifikat kesesuaian wajib <https://www.odoo.com/my/contract/french-"
"certification/>`_ yang dikeluarkan oleh Odoo SA."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/france.rst:704
msgid "Anti-fraud features"
msgstr "Fitur anti-penipuan"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/france.rst:706
msgid "The anti-fraud module introduces the following features:"
msgstr "Modul anti-penipuan memperkenalkan fitur-fitur berikut:"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/france.rst:708
msgid ":ref:`Inalterability <localizations/france/pos-inalterability>`"
msgstr ":ref:`Ketidakterubahan <localizations/france/pos-inalterability>`"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/france.rst:709
msgid ":ref:`Security <localizations/france/pos-security>`"
msgstr ":ref:`Keamanan <localizations/france/pos-security>`"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/france.rst:710
msgid ":ref:`Storage <localizations/france/pos-storage>`"
msgstr ":ref:`Penyimpanan <localizations/france/pos-storage>`"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/france.rst:715
msgid "Inalterability"
msgstr "Ketidakterubahan"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/france.rst:717
msgid ""
"All methods to cancel or modify key data in POS orders, invoices, and "
"journal entries are deactivated for companies located in France or any DOM-"
"TOM."
msgstr ""
"Semua metode untuk membatalkan atau mengubah data kunci dalam pesanan POS, "
"faktur, dan entri jurnal dinonaktifkan untuk perusahaan yang berlokasi di "
"Prancis atau DOM-TOM mana pun."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/france.rst:721
msgid ""
"In a multi-company environment, only the documents of such companies are "
"impacted."
msgstr ""
"Dalam lingkungan multi-perusahaan, hanya dokumen dari perusahaan tersebut "
"yang terpengaruh."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/france.rst:726
msgid "Security"
msgstr "Keamanan"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/france.rst:728
msgid ""
"To ensure inalterability, every order or journal entry is encrypted upon "
"validation. This number (or hash) is calculated from the document's key data "
"and the hash of the precedent documents. The module introduces an interface "
"to test the data's inalterability. The test will fail if any information is "
"modified on a document after its validation. The algorithm recomputes all "
"the hashes and compares them against the initial ones. In case of failure, "
"the system points out the first corrupted document recorded in the system."
msgstr ""
"Untuk memastikan ketidakterubahan, setiap pesanan atau entri jurnal "
"dienkripsi saat validasi. Nomor ini (atau hash) dihitung dari data kunci "
"dokumen dan hash dari dokumen sebelumnya. Modul ini memperkenalkan antarmuka "
"untuk menguji ketidakterubahan data. Pengujian akan gagal jika informasi apa "
"pun diubah pada dokumen setelah validasinya. Algoritme menghitung ulang "
"semua hash dan membandingkannya dengan yang awal. Jika terjadi kegagalan, "
"sistem menunjukkan dokumen rusak pertama yang tercatat dalam sistem."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/france.rst:735
msgid ""
"Only users with :doc:`administrator </applications/general/users/"
"access_rights>` access rights can initiate the inalterability check:"
msgstr ""
"Hanya pengguna dengan hak akses :doc:`administrator </applications/general/"
"users/access_rights>` yang dapat memulai pemeriksaan ketidakterubahan:"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/france.rst:738
msgid ""
"For POS orders, go to :menuselection:`Point of Sales --> Reporting --> POS "
"Inalterability Check`;"
msgstr ""
"Untuk pesanan POS, buka :menuselection:`Point of Sales --> Reporting --> POS "
"Inalterability Check`;"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/france.rst:739
msgid ""
"For journal entries, go to :menuselection:`Invoicing/Accounting --> "
"Configuration --> Settings`. In the :guilabel:`Reporting` section, "
"click :guilabel:`Download the Data Inalterability Check Report`."
msgstr ""
"Untuk entri jurnal, buka :menuselection:`Invoicing/Accounting --> "
"Configuration --> Settings`. Di bagian :guilabel:`Reporting`, klik "
":guilabel:`Download the Data Inalterability Check Report`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/france.rst:746
msgid "Storage"
msgstr "Storage"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/france.rst:748
msgid ""
"The system also processes automatic sales closings daily, monthly, and "
"annually. Such closings compute the sales total for the period and the "
"cumulative grand totals from the very first sales entry recorded in the "
"system."
msgstr ""
"Sistem juga memproses penutupan penjualan otomatis secara harian, bulanan, "
"dan tahunan. Penutupan seperti itu menghitung total penjualan untuk periode "
"tersebut dan total kumulatif keseluruhan dari entri penjualan pertama yang "
"tercatat dalam sistem."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/france.rst:752
msgid ""
"To access closings, either go to :menuselection:`Point of Sales --> "
"Reporting --> Sales Closings` or :menuselection:`Invoicing/Accounting --> "
"Reporting --> Sales Closings`."
msgstr ""
"Untuk mengakses penutupan, buka :menuselection:`Point of Sales --> "
"Reporting --> Sales Closings` atau :menuselection:`Penagihan/Akuntansi --> "
"Reporting --> Sales Closings`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/france.rst:756
msgid ""
"Closings compute the totals for journal entries of sales journals (Journal "
"Type = Sales)."
msgstr ""
"Penutupan menghitung total untuk entri jurnal dari jurnal penjualan (Jenis "
"Jurnal = Penjualan)."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/france.rst:757
msgid ""
"For multi-companies environments, such closings are performed by company."
msgstr ""
"Untuk lingkungan multi-perusahaan, penutupan tersebut dilakukan per "
"perusahaan."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/france.rst:758
msgid ""
"POS orders are posted as journal entries at the closing of the POS register. "
"Closing the POS register can be done at any time. To prompt users to do it "
"daily, the module prevents them from resuming a session that was opened more "
"than 24 hours ago. Such a session must be closed before selling again."
msgstr ""
"Pesanan POS diposting sebagai entri jurnal saat penutupan register POS. "
"Penutupan register POS dapat dilakukan kapan saja. Untuk mengingatkan "
"pengguna melakukannya setiap hari, modul ini mencegah mereka melanjutkan "
"sesi yang dibuka lebih dari 24 jam yang lalu. Sesi tersebut harus ditutup "
"sebelum menjual lagi."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/france.rst:762
msgid ""
"A period’s total is computed from all the journal entries posted after the "
"previous closing of the same type, regardless of their posting date. "
"Recording a new sales transaction for a period already closed will be "
"counted in the very next closing."
msgstr ""
"Total periode dihitung dari semua entri jurnal yang diposting setelah "
"penutupan sebelumnya dengan jenis yang sama, terlepas dari tanggal "
"postingnya. Pencatatan transaksi penjualan baru untuk periode yang sudah "
"ditutup akan dihitung dalam penutupan berikutnya."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/france.rst:767
msgid ""
"For test & audit purposes, closings can be manually generated "
"in :ref:`developer mode <developer-mode>`. To do so, go "
"to :menuselection:`Settings --> Technical --> Scheduled Actions`. In the "
"scheduled actions list view, open the desired :guilabel:`Sale Closing` "
"action and click :guilabel:`Run manually`."
msgstr ""
"Untuk keperluan pengujian & audit, penutupan dapat dibuat secara manual "
"dalam :ref:`mode pengembang <developer-mode>`. Untuk melakukannya, buka "
":menuselection:`Settings --> Technical --> Scheduled Actions`. Dalam "
"tampilan daftar tindakan terjadwal, buka tindakan :guilabel:`Sale Closing` "
"yang diinginkan dan klik :guilabel:`Run manually`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/france.rst:775
msgid "Responsibilities"
msgstr "Tanggung Jawab"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/france.rst:777
msgid ""
"Uninstalling this module will reset the security hashes. This means the "
"system will no longer guarantee the integrity of the past data."
msgstr ""
"Mencopot modul ini akan mereset hash keamanan. Ini berarti sistem tidak akan "
"lagi menjamin integritas data masa lalu."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/france.rst:780
msgid ""
"Users are responsible for their Odoo system and must operate it carefully. "
"Modifying source code responsible for ensuring data integrity is not allowed."
msgstr ""
"Pengguna bertanggung jawab atas sistem Odoo mereka dan harus "
"mengoperasikannya dengan hati-hati. Memodifikasi kode sumber yang "
"bertanggung jawab untuk memastikan integritas data tidak diizinkan."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/france.rst:783
msgid ""
"Odoo is not responsible for any issues with this module's functionality if "
"caused by uncertified third-party applications."
msgstr ""
"Odoo tidak bertanggung jawab atas masalah apa pun dengan fungsi modul ini "
"jika disebabkan oleh aplikasi pihak ketiga yang tidak bersertifikat."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/germany.rst:11
msgid ""
"Both SKR03 and SKR04 charts of accounts are supported in Odoo. When you "
"create a new Odoo Online database, SKR03 is installed by default."
msgstr ""
"Baik bagan akun SKR03 maupun SKR04 didukung di Odoo. Saat Anda membuat "
"database Odoo Online baru, SKR03 dipasang secara default."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/germany.rst:14
msgid ""
"Verify which is installed by going to :menuselection:`Accounting --> "
"Configuration --> Settings` and checking the :guilabel:`Package` field under "
"the :guilabel:`Fiscal Localization` section."
msgstr ""
"Verifikasi mana yang terpasang dengan membuka :menuselection:`Akuntansi --> "
"Configuration --> Settings` dan memeriksa kolom :guilabel:`Package` di bawah "
"bagian :guilabel:`Fiscal Localization`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/germany.rst:18
msgid ""
"Selecting another package is only possible if you have not created an "
"accounting entry. If one was posted, a new company or database must be set "
"up to select another package. In addition, all journal entries will need to "
"be created again."
msgstr ""
"Memilih paket lain hanya mungkin jika Anda belum membuat entri akuntansi. "
"Jika ada yang diposting, perusahaan atau database baru harus dibuat untuk "
"memilih paket lain. Selain itu, semua entri jurnal perlu dibuat lagi."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/germany.rst:25
msgid "The following German-specific reports available on Odoo Enterprise:"
msgstr "Laporan khusus Jerman berikut tersedia di Odoo Enterprise:"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/germany.rst:29
msgid "Tax Report (Umsatzsteuervoranmeldung)"
msgstr "Laporan Pajak (Umsatzsteuervoranmeldung)"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/germany.rst:30
msgid "EC Sales List"
msgstr "Daftar Sales EC"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/germany.rst:34
msgid "Exporting entries from Odoo to DATEV"
msgstr "Mengekspor entri dari Odoo ke DATEV"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/germany.rst:36
msgid ""
"Provided that one of the German :ref:`fiscal localization packages "
"<fiscal_localizations/packages>` is installed, you can export your "
"accounting entries from Odoo to DATEV from the general ledger."
msgstr ""
"Dengan ketentuan bahwa salah satu :ref:`paket lokalisasi fiskal "
"<fiscal_localizations/packages>` Jerman terpasang, Anda dapat mengekspor "
"entri akuntansi Anda dari Odoo ke DATEV dari buku besar."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/germany.rst:40
msgid ""
"Two types of exports are needed: first the DATEV ATCH export, then the DATEV "
"DATA export."
msgstr ""
"Dua jenis ekspor diperlukan: pertama ekspor DATEV ATCH, kemudian ekspor "
"DATEV DATA."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/germany.rst:43
msgid ""
"Both are needed at different stages to transfer the data correctly to DATEV, "
"as DATEV works with two interfaces, one for clients (DUO - DATEV Unternehmen "
"Online) and one for tax advisors (DATEV Rechnungswesen)."
msgstr ""
"Keduanya diperlukan pada tahap yang berbeda untuk mentransfer data dengan "
"benar ke DATEV, karena DATEV bekerja dengan dua antarmuka, satu untuk klien "
"(DUO - DATEV Unternehmen Online) dan satu untuk penasihat pajak (DATEV "
"Rechnungswesen)."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/germany.rst:48
msgid "1. DATEV ATCH"
msgstr "1. DATEV ATCH"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/germany.rst:50
msgid ""
"Go to :menuselection:`Accounting --> Reporting --> General Ledger`, click "
"the :icon:`fa-cog` (:guilabel:`Actions`) button, and select :guilabel:`Datev "
"ATCH (zip)`."
msgstr ""
"Buka :menuselection:`Akuntansi --> Reporting --> Buku Besar`, klik tombol "
":icon:`fa-cog` (:guilabel:`Actions`), dan pilih :guilabel:`Datev ATCH (zip)`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/germany.rst:None
msgid "General ledger's actions menu with DATEV exports"
msgstr "Menu tindakan Buku Besar dengan ekspor DATEV"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/germany.rst:56
msgid ""
"Upload the downloaded ZIP file via the `DATEV Belegtransfer software "
"<https://www.datev.de/web/de/berufsgruppenuebergreifend/mydatev/cloud-"
"anwendungen/datev-upload-online>`_."
msgstr ""
"Unggah file ZIP yang diunduh melalui `perangkat lunak DATEV Belegtransfer "
"<https://www.datev.de/web/de/berufsgruppenuebergreifend/mydatev/cloud-"
"anwendungen/datev-upload-online>`_."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/germany.rst:59
msgid ""
"If you do not have the DATEV Belegtransfer software `installed <https://"
"apps.datev.de/myupdates/download/products/ddc1adec-4b1e-4581-"
"b5b0-504fe0d68fd2>`_ on your computer, ask your tax advisor to help you with "
"this."
msgstr ""
"Jika Anda tidak memiliki perangkat lunak DATEV Belegtransfer yang `terinstal "
"<https://apps.datev.de/myupdates/download/products/ddc1adec-4b1e-4581-b5b0-"
"504fe0d68fd2>`_ di komputer Anda, mintalah bantuan penasihat pajak Anda "
"untuk ini."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/germany.rst:63
msgid ""
"The DATEV ATCH ZIP file includes the files (reports) linked to an Odoo "
"invoice or bill. For customer invoices, the file must have been generated by "
"using the :guilabel:`Send` button. For vendor bills, the file must have been "
"received via an email alias or uploaded by using the :guilabel:`Upload` "
"button."
msgstr ""
"File ZIP DATEV ATCH mencakup file (laporan) yang terhubung ke faktur atau "
"tagihan Odoo. Untuk faktur pelanggan, file harus dibuat menggunakan tombol "
":guilabel:`Kirim`. Untuk tagihan vendor, file harus diterima melalui alias "
"email atau diunggah menggunakan tombol :guilabel:`Unggah`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/germany.rst:68
#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/germany.rst:90
msgid "DATEV ATCH ZIP file"
msgstr "File ZIP DATEV ATCH"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/germany.rst:70
msgid "The ZIP file contains two types of files:"
msgstr "File ZIP berisi dua jenis file:"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/germany.rst:72
msgid ""
"the individual invoice/bill files (PDF, JPEG, etc.) for the selected period "
"on the general ledger, and"
msgstr ""
"file faktur/tagihan individual (PDF, JPEG, dll.) untuk periode yang dipilih "
"pada Buku Besar, dan"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/germany.rst:74
msgid ""
"a :file:`document.xml` file used to generate a unique ID (GUID) for each "
"file."
msgstr ""
"file :file:`document.xml` yang digunakan untuk membuat ID unik (GUID) untuk "
"setiap file."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/germany.rst:76
msgid ""
"These unique IDs are essential as they allow DATEV to automatically link the "
"files to the individual journal items, which will be imported with the DATEV "
"DATA file in the next step."
msgstr ""
"ID unik ini penting karena memungkinkan DATEV untuk secara otomatis "
"menghubungkan file ke item jurnal individual, yang akan diimpor dengan file "
"DATEV DATA pada langkah berikutnya."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/germany.rst:80
msgid "2. DATEV DATA"
msgstr "2. DATEV DATA"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/germany.rst:82
msgid ""
"Go to :menuselection:`Accounting --> Reporting --> General Ledger`, click "
"the :icon:`fa-cog` (:guilabel:`Actions`) button, and select :guilabel:`Datev "
"DATA (zip)`."
msgstr ""
"Buka :menuselection:`Akuntansi --> Pelaporan --> Buku Besar`, klik tombol "
":icon:`fa-cog` (:guilabel:`Tindakan`), dan pilih :guilabel:`Datev DATA (zip)"
"`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/germany.rst:85
msgid ""
"Transfer the downloaded ZIP file to your tax advisor. They should import the "
"ZIP file into DATEV Rechnungswesen."
msgstr ""
"Transfer file ZIP yang diunduh ke penasihat pajak Anda. Mereka harus "
"mengimpor file ZIP ke DATEV Rechnungswesen."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/germany.rst:88
msgid "Check with your tax advisor how often they need these files."
msgstr ""
"Periksa dengan penasihat pajak Anda seberapa sering mereka memerlukan file-"
"file ini."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/germany.rst:92
msgid "The ZIP file contains three CSV files:"
msgstr "File ZIP berisi tiga file CSV:"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/germany.rst:94
msgid ""
"the :file:`EXTF_customer_accounts.csv` file containing all information "
"related to your customers,"
msgstr ""
"file :file:`EXTF_customer_accounts.csv` yang berisi semua informasi terkait "
"pelanggan Anda,"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/germany.rst:96
msgid ""
"the :file:`EXTF_vendor_accounts.csv` file containing all information related "
"to your vendors, and"
msgstr ""
"file :file:`EXTF_vendor_accounts.csv` yang berisi semua informasi terkait "
"vendor Anda, dan"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/germany.rst:98
msgid ""
"the :file:`EXTF_accounting_entries.csv` containing all journal items for the "
"period defined on the general ledger, as well as the unique IDs (GUID) so "
"that the journal items can be linked to the files inside the DATEV ATCH ZIP "
"file."
msgstr ""
"file :file:`EXTF_accounting_entries.csv` yang berisi semua item jurnal untuk "
"periode yang ditentukan pada Buku Besar, serta ID unik (GUID) sehingga item "
"jurnal dapat dihubungkan ke file di dalam file ZIP DATEV ATCH."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/germany.rst:105
msgid "GoBD compliance"
msgstr "Kepatuhan GoBD"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/germany.rst:107
msgid ""
"**GoBD** stands for *Grundsätze zur ordnungsmäßigen Führung und Aufbewahrung "
"von Büchern, Aufzeichnungen und Unterlagen in elektronischer Form sowie zum "
"Datenzugriff*. In short, it is a guideline for the proper management and "
"storage of books, records, and documents in electronic form, as well as for "
"data access, that is relevant for the German tax authority, tax declaration, "
"and balance sheet."
msgstr ""
"**GoBD** adalah singkatan dari *Grundsätze zur ordnungsmäßigen Führung und "
"Aufbewahrung von Büchern, Aufzeichnungen und Unterlagen in elektronischer "
"Form sowie zum Datenzugriff*. Singkatnya, ini adalah pedoman untuk "
"pengelolaan dan penyimpanan buku, catatan, dan dokumen yang tepat dalam "
"bentuk elektronik, serta untuk akses data, yang relevan untuk otoritas pajak "
"Jerman, deklarasi pajak, dan neraca keuangan."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/germany.rst:113
msgid ""
"These principles have been written and published by the Federal Ministry of "
"Finance (BMF) in November 2014. Since January 2015, **they have become the "
"norm** and have replaced previously accepted practices linked to computer-"
"based accounting. Several changes have been made by the BMF in 2019 and "
"January 2020 to specify some of the content due to the development of "
"digital solutions (cloud hosting, paperless companies, etc.)."
msgstr ""
"Prinsip-prinsip ini telah ditulis dan diterbitkan oleh Kementerian Keuangan "
"Federal (BMF) pada November 2014. Sejak Januari 2015, **prinsip-prinsip ini "
"telah menjadi norma** dan telah menggantikan praktik-praktik yang sebelumnya "
"diterima terkait dengan akuntansi berbasis komputer. Beberapa perubahan "
"telah dilakukan oleh BMF pada tahun 2019 dan Januari 2020 untuk menentukan "
"beberapa konten karena perkembangan solusi digital (hosting cloud, "
"perusahaan tanpa kertas, dll.)."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/germany.rst:120
msgid "Odoo is certified **GoBD-compliant**."
msgstr "Odoo bersertifikat **patuh terhadap GoBD**."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/germany.rst:123
msgid "Understanding GoBD in relation to accounting software"
msgstr "Memahami GoBD dalam kaitannya dengan perangkat lunak akuntansi"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/germany.rst:125
msgid ""
"The **GoBD is binding for companies that have to present accounts**, which "
"includes SMEs, freelancers, and entrepreneurs, to the financial authorities. "
"As such, **the taxpayer himself is the sole responsible** for the complete "
"and exhaustive keeping of fiscal-relevant data (above-mentioned financial "
"and related data)."
msgstr ""
"**GoBD mengikat bagi perusahaan yang harus menyajikan laporan keuangan**, "
"yang mencakup UKM, pekerja lepas, dan pengusaha, kepada otoritas keuangan. "
"Dengan demikian, **wajib pajak sendiri adalah satu-satunya pihak yang "
"bertanggung jawab** atas penyimpanan data yang relevan secara fiskal (data "
"keuangan dan data terkait yang disebutkan di atas) secara lengkap dan "
"menyeluruh."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/germany.rst:130
msgid ""
"Apart from software requirements, the user is required to ensure internal "
"control systems (*in accordance with sec. 146 of the Fiscal Code*):"
msgstr ""
"Selain persyaratan perangkat lunak, user diharuskan untuk memastikan sistem "
"kontrol internal (*sesuai dengan pasal 146 Kode Fiskal*):"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/germany.rst:133
msgid "access rights control;"
msgstr "kontrol hak akses;"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/germany.rst:134
msgid "segregation of duties, functional separating;"
msgstr "pemisahan tugas, pemisahan fungsional;"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/germany.rst:135
msgid "entry controls (error notifications, plausibility checks);"
msgstr "kontrol masukan (notifikasi kesalahan, pemeriksaan kewajaran);"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/germany.rst:136
msgid "reconciliation checks at data entry;"
msgstr "pemeriksaan rekonsiliasi pada saat entri data;"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/germany.rst:137
msgid "processing controls; and"
msgstr "kontrol pemrosesan; dan"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/germany.rst:138
msgid ""
"measures to prevent intentional or unintentional manipulation of software, "
"data, or documents."
msgstr ""
"langkah-langkah untuk mencegah manipulasi yang disengaja atau tidak "
"disengaja terhadap perangkat lunak, data, atau dokumen."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/germany.rst:140
msgid ""
"The user must distribute tasks within their organization to the relevant "
"positions (*control*) and verify that the tasks are properly and completely "
"performed (*supervision*). The result of these controls must be recorded "
"(*documentation*), and should errors be found during these controls, "
"appropriate measures to correct the situation should be put into place "
"(*prevention*)."
msgstr ""
"User harus mendistribusikan tugas dalam organisasi mereka ke posisi yang "
"relevan (*kontrol*) dan memverifikasi bahwa tugas-tugas tersebut dilakukan "
"dengan benar dan lengkap (*pengawasan*). Hasil dari kontrol ini harus "
"dicatat (*dokumentasi*), dan jika ditemukan kesalahan selama kontrol ini, "
"langkah-langkah yang tepat untuk memperbaiki situasi harus diterapkan "
"(*pencegahan*)."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/germany.rst:146
msgid "Data security"
msgstr "Keamanan data"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/germany.rst:148
msgid ""
"The taxpayer must **secure the system against any data loss** due to "
"deletion, removal, or theft of any data. If the entries are not sufficiently "
"secured, the bookkeeping will be regarded as not in accordance with the GoBD "
"guidelines."
msgstr ""
"Wajib pajak harus **mengamankan sistem terhadap kehilangan data** akibat "
"penghapusan, pemindahan, atau pencurian data apa pun. Jika entri tidak "
"diamankan dengan memadai, pembukuan akan dianggap tidak sesuai dengan "
"pedoman GoBD."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/germany.rst:152
msgid ""
"Once bookings have been finally posted, they can no longer be changed or "
"deleted via the application."
msgstr ""
"Setelah pembukuan diposting secara final, pembukuan tersebut tidak dapat "
"lagi diubah atau dihapus melalui aplikasi."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/germany.rst:155
msgid ""
"If Odoo is used in the cloud, regular backups are part of the Odoo Online "
"service. In addition, regular backups can be downloaded and backed up on "
"external systems."
msgstr ""
"Jika Odoo digunakan di cloud, cadangan rutin merupakan bagian dari layanan "
"Odoo Online. Selain itu, cadangan rutin dapat diunduh dan dicadangkan pada "
"sistem eksternal."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/germany.rst:159
msgid ""
"`Odoo Cloud Hosting - Service Level Agreement <https://www.odoo.com/cloud-"
"sla>`_"
msgstr ""
"`Odoo Cloud Hosting - Service Level Agreement <https://www.odoo.com/cloud-"
"sla>`_"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/germany.rst:161
msgid ""
"If the server is operated locally, the user is responsible for creating the "
"necessary backup infrastructure."
msgstr ""
"Jika server dioperasikan secara lokal, user bertanggung jawab untuk membuat "
"infrastruktur cadangan yang diperlukan."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/germany.rst:165
msgid ""
"In some cases, data has to be kept for ten years or more, so always have "
"backups saved. It is even more important if you decide to change software "
"provider."
msgstr ""
"Dalam beberapa kasus, data harus disimpan selama sepuluh tahun atau lebih, "
"jadi selalu simpan cadangan. Hal ini bahkan lebih penting jika Anda "
"memutuskan untuk mengganti penyedia perangkat lunak."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/germany.rst:169
msgid "Responsibility of the software editor"
msgstr "Tanggung jawab editor perangkat lunak"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/germany.rst:171
msgid ""
"Considering GoBD applies only to the taxpayer, **the software editor can by "
"no means be held responsible for the accurate and compliant documentation of "
"their users' financial transactional data**. It can merely provide the "
"necessary tools for the user to respect the software-related guidelines "
"described in the GoBD."
msgstr ""
"Mengingat GoBD hanya berlaku bagi wajib pajak, **editor perangkat lunak "
"tidak dapat dengan cara apa pun dimintai pertanggungjawaban atas dokumentasi "
"data transaksi keuangan user mereka yang akurat dan sesuai**. Mereka hanya "
"dapat menyediakan alat yang diperlukan bagi user untuk mematuhi pedoman "
"terkait perangkat lunak yang dijelaskan dalam GoBD."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/germany.rst:177
msgid "Ensuring compliance through Odoo"
msgstr "Memastikan kepatuhan melalui Odoo"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/germany.rst:179
msgid ""
"The keywords, when it comes to GoBD are: **traceable, verifiable, true, "
"clear, and continuous**. In short, you need to have audit-proof archiving in "
"place, and Odoo provides you with the means to achieve all of these "
"objectives:"
msgstr ""
"Kata kunci dalam hal GoBD adalah: **dapat dilacak, dapat diverifikasi, "
"benar, jelas, dan berkelanjutan**. Singkatnya, Anda perlu memiliki "
"pengarsipan yang tahan audit, dan Odoo memberi Anda sarana untuk mencapai "
"semua tujuan ini:"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/germany.rst:0
msgid "**Traceability and verifiability**"
msgstr "**Ketertelusuran dan keterverifikasian**"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/germany.rst:0
msgid ""
"Each record in Odoo is stamped with the creator of the document, the "
"creation date, the modification date, and who modified it. In addition, "
"relevant fields are tracked. Thus, it can be seen which value was changed by "
"whom in the chatter of the relevant object."
msgstr ""
"Setiap rekaman di Odoo diberi cap dengan pembuat dokumen, tanggal pembuatan, "
"tanggal modifikasi, dan siapa yang memodifikasinya. Selain itu, bidang yang "
"relevan dilacak. Dengan demikian, dapat dilihat nilai mana yang diubah oleh "
"siapa dalam chatter objek yang relevan."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/germany.rst:0
msgid "**Completeness**"
msgstr "**Kelengkapan**"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/germany.rst:0
msgid ""
"All financial data must be recorded in the system, and there can be no gaps. "
"Odoo ensures that there is no gap in the numbering of the financial "
"transactions. It is the responsibility of the user to encode all financial "
"data in the system. As most financial data in Odoo is generated "
"automatically, it remains the responsibility of the user to encode all "
"vendor bills and miscellaneous operations completely."
msgstr ""
"Semua data keuangan harus dicatat dalam sistem, dan tidak boleh ada celah. "
"Odoo memastikan bahwa tidak ada celah dalam penomoran transaksi keuangan. "
"Tanggung jawab pengguna adalah untuk mengenkode semua data keuangan dalam "
"sistem. Karena sebagian besar data keuangan di Odoo dihasilkan secara "
"otomatis, tetap menjadi tanggung jawab pengguna untuk mengenkode semua "
"tagihan vendor dan operasi lain-lain secara lengkap."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/germany.rst:0
msgid "**Accuracy**"
msgstr "**Akurasi**"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/germany.rst:0
msgid ""
"Odoo ensures that, with the correct configuration, the correct accounts are "
"used. In addition, the control mechanisms between purchase orders and sales "
"orders and their respective invoices reflect the reality of the business. It "
"is the responsibility of the user to scan and attach the paper-based vendor "
"bill to the respective record in Odoo. *Odoo Documents helps you automate "
"this task*."
msgstr ""
"Odoo memastikan bahwa, dengan konfigurasi yang benar, akun yang tepat "
"digunakan. Selain itu, mekanisme kontrol antara pesanan pembelian dan "
"pesanan penjualan serta faktur masing-masing mencerminkan realitas bisnis. "
"Tanggung jawab pengguna adalah untuk memindai dan melampirkan tagihan vendor "
"berbasis kertas ke rekaman masing-masing di Odoo. *Odoo Dokumen membantu "
"Anda mengotomatiskan tugas ini*."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/germany.rst:0
msgid "**Timely booking and record-keeping**"
msgstr "**Pembukuan dan pencatatan tepat waktu**"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/germany.rst:0
msgid ""
"As most financial data in Odoo is generated by the transactional objects "
"(for example, the invoice is booked at confirmation), Odoo ensures out-of-"
"the-box timely record-keeping. It is the responsibility of the user to "
"encode all incoming vendor bills in a timely manner, as well as the "
"miscellaneous operations."
msgstr ""
"Karena sebagian besar data keuangan di Odoo dihasilkan oleh objek "
"transaksional (misalnya, faktur dibukukan saat konfirmasi), Odoo memastikan "
"pencatatan tepat waktu secara otomatis. Tanggung jawab pengguna adalah untuk "
"mengenkode semua tagihan vendor masuk secara tepat waktu, serta operasi lain-"
"lain."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/germany.rst:0
msgid "**Order**"
msgstr "**Urutan**"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/germany.rst:0
msgid ""
"Financial data stored in Odoo is, per definition, ordered and can be "
"reordered according to most fields present in the model. A specific ordering "
"is not enforced by the GoBD, but the system must ensure that a given "
"financial transaction can be quickly found by a third-party expert. Odoo "
"ensures this out-of-the-box."
msgstr ""
"Data keuangan yang disimpan di Odoo, per definisi, diurutkan dan dapat "
"diurutkan ulang sesuai sebagian besar bidang yang ada dalam model. "
"Pengurutan spesifik tidak diberlakukan oleh GoBD, tetapi sistem harus "
"memastikan bahwa transaksi keuangan tertentu dapat ditemukan dengan cepat "
"oleh ahli pihak ketiga. Odoo memastikan hal ini secara otomatis."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/germany.rst:0
msgid "**Inalterability**"
msgstr "**Ketidakterubahan**"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/germany.rst:0
msgid ""
"With the German Odoo localization, Odoo is in standard configured in such a "
"way that the inalterability clause can be adhered to without any further "
"customization."
msgstr ""
"Dengan lokalisasi Odoo Jerman, Odoo dikonfigurasi secara standar sedemikian "
"rupa sehingga klausul ketidakterubahan dapat dipatuhi tanpa kustomisasi "
"lebih lanjut."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/germany.rst:214
msgid "GoBD export"
msgstr "Ekspor GoBD"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/germany.rst:216
msgid ""
"In the case of fiscal control, the fiscal authority can request three levels "
"of access to the accounting system (Z1, Z2, Z3). These levels vary from "
"direct access to the interface to the handover of the financial data on a "
"storage device."
msgstr ""
"Dalam hal kontrol fiskal, otoritas fiskal dapat meminta tiga tingkat akses "
"ke sistem akuntansi (Z1, Z2, Z3). Tingkat-tingkat ini bervariasi dari akses "
"langsung ke antarmuka hingga penyerahan data keuangan pada perangkat "
"penyimpanan."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/germany.rst:220
msgid ""
"In the case of a handover of financial data to a storage device, the GoBD "
"does **not** enforce the format. It can be, for example, in XLS, CSV, XML, "
"Lotus 123, SAP-format, AS/400-format, or else. Odoo supports the CSV and XLS "
"export of financial data out of the box. The GoBD **recommends** the export "
"in a specific XML-based GoBD format (see \"Ergänzende Informationen zur "
"Datenträgerüberlassung\" §3), but it is not binding."
msgstr ""
"Dalam hal penyerahan data keuangan ke perangkat penyimpanan, GoBD **tidak** "
"memberlakukan format. Dapat berupa, misalnya, dalam format XLS, CSV, XML, "
"Lotus 123, format SAP, format AS/400, atau lainnya. Odoo mendukung ekspor "
"data keuangan dalam format CSV dan XLS secara otomatis. GoBD "
"**merekomendasikan** ekspor dalam format GoBD berbasis XML tertentu (lihat "
"\"Ergänzende Informationen zur Datenträgerüberlassung\" §3), tetapi tidak "
"mengikat."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/germany.rst:227
msgid "Non-compliance"
msgstr "Ketidakpatuhan"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/germany.rst:229
msgid ""
"In the event of an infringement, you can expect a fine and a court order "
"demanding the implementation of specific measures."
msgstr ""
"Jika terjadi pelanggaran, Anda dapat dikenakan denda dan perintah pengadilan "
"yang menuntut implementasi tindakan tertentu."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/germany.rst:238
msgid "Technical security system"
msgstr "Sistem keamanan teknis"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/germany.rst:240
msgid ""
"The **Kassensicherungsverordnung** (The Act on Protection against "
"Manipulation of Digital Records) requires that electronic record-keeping "
"systems - including the :doc:`point of sale </applications/sales/"
"point_of_sale>` systems - must be equipped with a **technical security "
"system** (also called **TSS** or **TSE**)."
msgstr ""
"**Kassensicherungsverordnung** (Undang-Undang Perlindungan terhadap "
"Manipulasi Catatan Digital) mensyaratkan bahwa sistem pencatatan "
"elektronik - termasuk sistem :doc:`point of sale </applications/sales/"
"point_of_sale>` - harus dilengkapi dengan **sistem keamanan teknis** (juga "
"disebut **TSS** atau **TSE**)."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/germany.rst:245
msgid ""
"Odoo offers a service that is compliant with the help of `fiskaly <https://"
"fiskaly.com>`_, a *cloud-based solution*."
msgstr ""
"Odoo menawarkan layanan yang sesuai dengan bantuan `fiskaly <https://"
"fiskaly.com>`_, sebuah *solusi berbasis cloud*."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/germany.rst:249
msgid ""
"Since this solution is cloud-based, a working internet connection is "
"required."
msgstr ""
"Karena solusi ini berbasis cloud, diperlukan koneksi internet yang berfungsi."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/germany.rst:252
msgid ""
"The only VAT rates allowed are given by fiskaly. You can check these rates "
"by consulting `fiskaly DSFinV-K API: VAT Definition <https://"
"developer.fiskaly.com/api/dsfinvk/v0/#tag/VAT-Definition>`_."
msgstr ""
"Satu-satunya tarif PPN yang diizinkan diberikan oleh fiskaly. Anda dapat "
"memeriksa tarif ini dengan membaca `fiskaly DSFinV-K API: VAT Definition "
"<https://developer.fiskaly.com/api/dsfinvk/v0/#tag/VAT-Definition>`_."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/germany.rst:259
msgid ""
":ref:`Install <general/install>` the **Germany - Certification for Point of "
"Sale** (`l10n_de_pos_cert`) and **Germany - Certification for Point of Sale "
"of type restaurant** (`l10n_de_pos_res_cert`) modules."
msgstr ""
":ref:`Instal <general/install>` modul **Germany - Certification for Point of "
"Sale** (`l10n_de_pos_cert`) dan **Germany - Certification for Point of Sale "
"of type restaurant** (`l10n_de_pos_res_cert`)."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/germany.rst:264
msgid ""
"If these modules are not listed, :ref:`update the app list <general/"
"install>`."
msgstr ""
"Jika modul ini tidak terdaftar, :ref:`perbarui daftar aplikasi <general/"
"install>`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/germany.rst:267
msgid "Company registration at the financial authority"
msgstr "Pendaftaran perusahaan di otoritas keuangan"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/germany.rst:269
msgid ""
"To register your company, open the :guilabel:`Settings` app, "
"click :guilabel:`Update Info` under the :guilabel:`Companies` section, and "
"fill in the following fields:"
msgstr ""
"Untuk mendaftarkan perusahaan Anda, buka aplikasi :guilabel:`Settings`, klik "
":guilabel:`Update Info` di bawah bagian :guilabel:`Companies`, dan isi kolom "
"berikut:"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/germany.rst:273
msgid ":guilabel:`Address`"
msgstr ":guilabel:`Alamat`"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/germany.rst:274
msgid ":guilabel:`VAT`"
msgstr ":guilabel:`VAT`"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/germany.rst:275
msgid ""
":guilabel:`St.-Nr.` (Steuernummer) this number is assigned by the tax office "
"to every taxable natural or legal person (e.g., `2893081508152`)."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`St.-Nr.` (Steuernummer) nomor ini diberikan oleh kantor pajak "
"kepada setiap orang perseorangan atau badan hukum yang dikenakan pajak "
"(misalnya, `2893081508152`)."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/germany.rst:277
msgid ""
":guilabel:`W-IdNr.` (Wirtschafts-Identifikationsnummer) this number is used "
"as a permanent identification number for economically active persons."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`W-IdNr.` (Wirtschafts-Identifikationsnummer) nomor ini digunakan "
"sebagai nomor identifikasi permanen untuk orang yang aktif secara ekonomi."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/germany.rst:280
msgid ""
"You can then **register your company through fiskaly** by opening "
"the :guilabel:`Fiskaly` tab and clicking the :guilabel:`Fiskaly "
"Registration` button."
msgstr ""
"Anda kemudian dapat **mendaftarkan perusahaan Anda melalui fiskaly** dengan "
"membuka tab :guilabel:`Fiskaly` dan mengklik tombol :guilabel:`Fiskaly "
"Registration`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/germany.rst:284
msgid ""
"If you do not see the :guilabel:`Fiskaly Registration` button, make sure "
"that you *saved* your company details and are not in *editing mode* anymore."
msgstr ""
"Jika Anda tidak melihat tombol :guilabel:`Fiskaly Registration`, pastikan "
"Anda telah *menyimpan* detail perusahaan Anda dan tidak lagi dalam *mode "
"edit*."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/germany.rst:287
msgid "Once the registration has been finalized, new fields appear:"
msgstr "Setelah pendaftaran selesai, kolom baru akan muncul:"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/germany.rst:289
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Fiskaly Organization ID` refers to the ID of your company on "
"fiskaly's side."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Fiskaly Organization ID` merujuk pada ID perusahaan Anda di sisi "
"fiskaly."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/germany.rst:290
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Fiskaly API Key` and :guilabel:`Fiskaly API Secret` are the "
"credentials the system uses to access the services offered by fiskaly."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Fiskaly API Key` dan :guilabel:`Fiskaly API Secret` adalah "
"kredensial yang digunakan sistem untuk mengakses layanan yang ditawarkan "
"oleh fiskaly."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/germany.rst:None
msgid "Fiskaly registration tab"
msgstr "Tab pendaftaran Fiskaly"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/germany.rst:297
msgid ""
"It is possible to request new credentials if there is any issue with the "
"current ones by clicking the :guilabel:`New keys` button."
msgstr ""
"Dimungkinkan untuk meminta kredensial baru jika ada masalah dengan "
"kredensial saat ini dengan mengklik tombol :guilabel:`New keys`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/germany.rst:301
msgid "Create a technical security system and link it to a POS"
msgstr "Membuat sistem keamanan teknis dan menghubungkannya ke POS"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/germany.rst:303
msgid ""
"To use a point of sale in Germany, first create a :abbr:`TSS (Technical "
"Security System)` by going to :menuselection:`Point of Sale --> "
"Configuration --> Point of Sale`, selecting the :guilabel:`Point of Sale` to "
"edit, then checking the :guilabel:`Create TSS` box under "
"the :guilabel:`Fiskaly API` section."
msgstr ""
"Untuk menggunakan point of sale di Jerman, pertama buat :abbr:`TSS "
"(Technical Security System)` dengan membuka :menuselection:`Point of "
"Sale --> Configuration --> Point of Sale`, pilih :guilabel:`Point of Sale` "
"yang akan diedit, kemudian centang kotak :guilabel:`Create TSS` di bawah "
"bagian :guilabel:`Fiskaly API`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/germany.rst:308
msgid "Once the creation of the TSS is successful, you can find the:"
msgstr "Setelah pembuatan TSS berhasil, Anda dapat menemukan:"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/germany.rst:310
msgid ""
":guilabel:`TSS ID`, which refers to the ID of your TSS on fiskaly's side, and"
msgstr ":guilabel:`TSS ID`, yang merujuk pada ID TSS Anda di sisi fiskaly, dan"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/germany.rst:311
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Fiskaly Client ID`, which refers to your POS on fiskaly's side."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`ID Klien Fiskaly`, yang merujuk pada POS Anda di sisi fiskaly."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/germany.rst:None
msgid "Fiskaly API section"
msgstr "Bagian API Fiskaly"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/germany.rst:317
msgid "DSFinV-K export"
msgstr "Ekspor DSFinV-K"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/germany.rst:319
msgid ""
"Whenever you close the POS register, the details of the orders are sent to "
"the :abbr:`DSFinV-K (Digitale Schnittstelle der Finanzverwaltung für "
"Kassensysteme)` service of fiskaly."
msgstr ""
"Setiap kali Anda menutup register POS, detail pesanan dikirim ke layanan "
":abbr:`DSFinV-K (Digitale Schnittstelle der Finanzverwaltung für "
"Kassensysteme)` fiskaly."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/germany.rst:322
msgid ""
"In case of an audit, you can export the data sent to DSFinV-K by going "
"to :menuselection:`Point of Sale --> Orders --> DSFinV-K Exports --> New`."
msgstr ""
"Jika terjadi audit, Anda dapat mengekspor data yang dikirim ke DSFinV-K "
"dengan membuka :menuselection:`POS --> Pesanan --> Ekspor DSFinV-K --> Baru`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/germany.rst:None
msgid "Menu to export DSFinV-K"
msgstr "Menu untuk mengekspor DSFinV-K"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/germany.rst:328
msgid "These fields are mandatory:"
msgstr "Kolom berikut wajib diisi:"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/germany.rst:330
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Start Datetime`: export data with dates larger than or equal to "
"the given start date"
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Tanggal Waktu Mulai`: ekspor data dengan tanggal lebih besar dari "
"atau sama dengan tanggal mulai yang diberikan"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/germany.rst:331
msgid ""
":guilabel:`End Datetime`: export data with dates smaller than or equal to "
"the given end date"
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Tanggal Waktu Akhir`: ekspor data dengan tanggal lebih kecil dari "
"atau sama dengan tanggal akhir yang diberikan"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/germany.rst:333
msgid ""
"Leave the :guilabel:`Point of Sale` field blank to export the data of all "
"your points of sale; specify one if you want to export data for this "
"specific POS only."
msgstr ""
"Biarkan kolom :guilabel:`POS` kosong untuk mengekspor data semua POS Anda; "
"tentukan satu POS jika Anda ingin mengekspor data untuk POS tertentu saja."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/germany.rst:None
msgid "Exporting DSFinV-K"
msgstr "Mengekspor DSFinV-K"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/germany.rst:339
msgid ""
"When an export is successfully triggered and is being processed, "
"the :guilabel:`State` field should mention :guilabel:`Pending`. "
