msgstr ""
"Setelah Anda mengaktifkan :ref:`akses API <india/gstr_api>` di portal GST, "
":ref:`aktifkan <india/indian-configuration>` :guilabel:`Fitur E-Filing & "
"Pencocokan GST` untuk mulai menggunakan Layanan GST. Kemudian, di bagian "
":guilabel:`Terdaftar di Bawah GST`, isi :guilabel:`Nama Pengguna GST` yang "
"diperlukan."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/india.rst:0
msgid "Please enter your GST portal Username as Username"
msgstr "Silakan masukkan Nama Pengguna portal GST Anda sebagai Nama Pengguna"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/india.rst:455
msgid "File-in GST Return"
msgstr "Pengajuan Pengembalian GST"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/india.rst:457
msgid ""
"To file a GST return, make sure the :ref:`GST E-Filing & Matching Feature "
"<india/indian-configuration>` is enabled. Then, go to the Accounting "
"dashboard and click :guilabel:`Tax Returns` on the :guilabel:`Tax Returns` "
"journal. In the :guilabel:`Accounting Periods` window, fill in the following "
"fields."
msgstr ""
"Untuk mengajukan pengembalian GST, pastikan :ref:`Fitur E-Filing & "
"Pencocokan GST <india/indian-configuration>` diaktifkan. Kemudian, buka "
"dashboard Akuntansi dan klik :guilabel:`Pengembalian Pajak` pada jurnal "
":guilabel:`Pengembalian Pajak`. Di jendela :guilabel:`Periode Akuntansi`, "
"isi kolom berikut."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/india.rst:462
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Opening Date`: Starting date from which tax return periods are "
"created."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Tanggal Pembukaan`: Tanggal awal dari periode pengembalian pajak "
"dibuat."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/india.rst:463
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Fiscal Year End`: End date of the fiscal year "
"(e.g., :guilabel:`31 March`)."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Akhir Tahun Fiskal`: Tanggal akhir tahun fiskal (misalnya, "
":guilabel:`31 Maret`)."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/india.rst:464
msgid ""
":guilabel:`GSTIN Periodicity`: Frequency of return filing "
"(e.g., :guilabel:`Monthly`)."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Periodisitas GSTIN`: Frekuensi pengajuan pengembalian (misalnya, "
":guilabel:`Bulanan`)."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/india.rst:467
msgid ""
"Alternatively, go to :menuselection:`Accounting --> Reporting --> Tax "
"Report`, click :icon:`fa-book` :guilabel:`Report:` and "
"select :guilabel:`GSTR-1 (IN)`. Then, click :guilabel:`Returns` to file the "
"return."
msgstr ""
"Sebagai alternatif, buka :menuselection:`Akuntansi --> Pelaporan --> Laporan "
"Pajak`, klik :icon:`fa-book` :guilabel:`Laporan:` dan pilih :guilabel:`GSTR-"
"1 (IN)`. Kemudian, klik :guilabel:`Pengembalian` untuk mengajukan "
"pengembalian."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/india.rst:472
msgid ""
"To reconcile vendor bills with GST portal data, go "
"to :menuselection:`Accounting --> Reporting --> Tax Report`, click :icon:`fa-"
"book` :guilabel:`Report:` and select :guilabel:`GSTR-2B`, and "
"click :guilabel:`Reconcile`."
msgstr ""
"Untuk merekonsiliasi tagihan vendor dengan data portal GST, buka "
":menuselection:`Akuntansi --> Pelaporan --> Laporan Pajak`, klik :icon:`fa-"
"book` :guilabel:`Laporan:` dan pilih :guilabel:`GSTR-2B`, dan klik "
":guilabel:`Rekonsiliasi`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/india.rst:479
msgid "Filing GSTR-1 tax return"
msgstr "Pengajuan pengembalian pajak GSTR-1"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/india.rst:481
msgid "To file a GSTR-1 tax return, follow these steps:"
msgstr ""
"Untuk mengajukan pengembalian pajak GSTR-1, ikuti langkah-langkah berikut:"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/india.rst:483
msgid ""
"Click the suitable :guilabel:`GSTR-1` report for the desired period to open "
"the filing view."
msgstr ""
"Klik laporan :guilabel:`GSTR-1` yang sesuai untuk periode yang diinginkan "
"untuk membuka tampilan pengajuan."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/india.rst:0
msgid "GSTR-1 filing view"
msgstr "Tampilan pengajuan GSTR-1"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/india.rst:489
msgid ""
"It is recommended to file the return **five days before the filing date** to "
"avoid any penalties."
msgstr ""
"Disarankan untuk mengajukan pengembalian **lima hari sebelum tanggal "
"pengajuan** untuk menghindari penalti."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/india.rst:492
msgid ""
"Odoo automatically performs validation checks before submission to ensure "
"compliance with GST portal requirements that must be addressed before filing."
msgstr ""
"Odoo secara otomatis melakukan pemeriksaan validasi sebelum pengajuan untuk "
"memastikan kepatuhan terhadap persyaratan portal GST yang harus ditangani "
"sebelum pengajuan."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/india.rst:496
msgid "The following types of validation issues can be raised:"
msgstr "Jenis masalah validasi berikut dapat muncul:"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/india.rst:498
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Apply Appropriate Tax`: :guilabel:`IGST` is not applicable for "
"intra-state transactions."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Terapkan Pajak yang Sesuai`: :guilabel:`IGST` tidak berlaku untuk "
"transaksi intra-negara bagian."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/india.rst:500
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Wrong CGST/SGST on Inter-State Transactions`: :guilabel:`CGST/"
"SGST` cannot be applied on inter-state transactions."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`CGST/SGST Salah pada Transaksi Antar-Negara Bagian`: "
":guilabel:`CGST/SGST` tidak dapat diterapkan pada transaksi antar-negara "
"bagian."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/india.rst:502
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Fiscal Year Reversed Move`: Credit Notes for invoices issued in a "
"given financial year should not be included in GSTR-1 after **November "
"30th**; remove tax from these lines."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Pembalikan Pergerakan Tahun Fiskal`: Nota Kredit untuk faktur "
"yang diterbitkan dalam tahun keuangan tertentu tidak boleh dimasukkan dalam "
"GSTR-1 setelah **30 November**; hapus pajak dari baris ini."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/india.rst:504
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Invalid HSN Codes`: - For products (non-services), HSN codes must "
"not begin with `99`. - For services, HSN codes must begin with `99`."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Kode HSN Tidak Valid`: - Untuk produk (bukan layanan), kode HSN "
"tidak boleh dimulai dengan `99`. - Untuk layanan, kode HSN harus dimulai "
"dengan `99`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/india.rst:507
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Missing HSN Codes`: Some product lines do not have HSN codes for "
"journal items."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Kode HSN Hilang`: Beberapa baris produk tidak memiliki kode HSN "
"untuk item jurnal."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/india.rst:509
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Invalid UQC Codes`: The Unit Quantity Code (UQC) must comply with "
"Indian GST standards."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Kode UQC Tidak Valid`: Kode Unit Kuantitas (UQC) harus mematuhi "
"standar GST India."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/india.rst:511
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Missing Document Summary`: Document summary lines are mandatory "
"for GSTR-1. This check is always marked as :guilabel:`Anomaly` initially. "
"After reviewing the summary by clicking the relevant check, it changes "
"to :guilabel:`Reviewed`."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Ringkasan Dokumen Hilang`: Baris ringkasan dokumen wajib untuk "
"GSTR-1. Pemeriksaan ini selalu ditandai sebagai :guilabel:`Anomali` pada "
"awalnya. Setelah meninjau ringkasan dengan mengklik pemeriksaan yang "
"relevan, statusnya berubah menjadi :guilabel:`Ditinjau`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/india.rst:514
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Missing E-Invoice`: Some invoices are not linked to an e-invoice."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`E-Invoice Hilang`: Beberapa faktur tidak terhubung dengan e-"
"invoice."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/india.rst:515
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Unlinked Unregistered Credit Notes`: Credit Notes have been "
"issued without referencing an invoice."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Nota Kredit Tidak Terdaftar yang Tidak Tertaut`: Nota Kredit "
"telah diterbitkan tanpa merujuk pada faktur."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/india.rst:518
msgid "Validation checks have four stages:"
msgstr ""

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/india.rst:520
msgid ":guilabel:`To Review`: Check requires review."
msgstr ""

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/india.rst:521
msgid ":guilabel:`Reviewed`: Check has been reviewed."
msgstr ""

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/india.rst:522
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Supervised`: Check is supervised, and a supervisor is assigned."
msgstr ""

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/india.rst:523
msgid ":guilabel:`Anomaly`: Check has failed."
msgstr ""

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/india.rst:525
msgid ""
"Click on any individual check to view and resolve the corresponding issue."
msgstr ""

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/india.rst:528
msgid ""
"A tax return can only be validated when all checks are in "
"the :guilabel:`Reviewed` or :guilabel:`Supervised` stage."
msgstr ""

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/india.rst:531
msgid ""
"After reviewing the checks, click :guilabel:`Validate`. "
"The :guilabel:`Review` stage appears in green then."
msgstr ""

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/india.rst:534
msgid "Click :guilabel:`GSTR-1 (IN)` to review the report."
msgstr ""

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/india.rst:536
msgid ""
"Click :guilabel:`Submit`, and click :guilabel:`Push Data` in "
"the :guilabel:`Submission Instructions` window to send the report to the GST "
"portal."
msgstr ""

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/india.rst:539
msgid ""
"During this step, GST portal credentials must be verified. As the data is "
"being sent, the :guilabel:`Send` stage in the progress bar appears orange. "
"Once the GST portal confirms receipt, the stage turns green. If an error "
"occurs, the :guilabel:`Send` stage changes to red."
msgstr ""

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/india.rst:544
msgid ""
"Click the :icon:`fa-ellipsis-v` :guilabel:`(ellipsis)` icon on the "
"relevant :guilabel:`GSTR-1` line to display additional options:"
msgstr ""

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/india.rst:547
msgid ":guilabel:`Generate XLSX`: Download the GSTR-1 report as an XLSX file."
msgstr ""

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/india.rst:548
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Reset`: Clear the current state and revert the return to the "
"initial stage."
msgstr ""

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/india.rst:550
msgid ""
"Click :guilabel:`Check Status` to retrieve the current status from the GST "
"portal. Once the confirmation is received, the :guilabel:`Review` stage in "
"the progress bar turns green. Then, click :guilabel:`Mark as Filed` to "
"finalize and submit the return as filed."
msgstr ""

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/india.rst:555
msgid ""
"Once a return is marked as **Filed**, it cannot be reset or filed again."
msgstr ""

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/india.rst:560
msgid "Receive GSTR-2B tax reconciliation"
msgstr ""

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/india.rst:562
msgid ""
"Select the relevant :guilabel:`GSTR-2B` report for the desired period that "
"needs to be reconciled."
msgstr ""

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/india.rst:565
msgid ""
"In the validation checks view, click :guilabel:`Fetch E-Invoice` to retrieve "
"vendor e-invoice data for the reconciliation period. The check is initially "
"marked as :guilabel:`Anomaly` and changes to :guilabel:`Reviewed` after "
"fetching. Then, click :guilabel:`Validate` to confirm and mark "
"the :guilabel:`Review` stage as green."
msgstr ""

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/india.rst:571
msgid ""
"The :guilabel:`Fetch E-Invoice` check only turns green if the e-invoice data "
"is fetched **two days after the end of the last month's reconciliation "
"period**."
msgstr ""

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/india.rst:574
msgid ""
"Click :guilabel:`Fetch GSTR-2B` to retrieve all invoices from the GST "
"portal. Once the data is fetched, the :guilabel:`Fetch` stage in the "
"progress bar turns green. To view the raw report data, "
"click :guilabel:`GSTR-2B (IN)`."
msgstr ""
"Klik :guilabel:`Fetch GSTR-2B` untuk mengambil semua faktur dari portal GST. "
"Setelah data diambil, tahap :guilabel:`Fetch` pada bilah kemajuan berubah "
"menjadi hijau. Untuk melihat data laporan mentah, klik :guilabel:`GSTR-2B "
"(IN)`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/india.rst:578
msgid ""
"The fetched invoices are automatically matched with the E-invoices. "
"Click :guilabel:`View Bills` to see detailed matching results."
msgstr ""
"Faktur yang diambil secara otomatis dicocokkan dengan E-invoice. Klik "
":guilabel:`View Bills` untuk melihat hasil pencocokan secara rinci."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/india.rst:582
msgid "The :guilabel:`Match` stage indicates the reconciliation status:"
msgstr "Tahap :guilabel:`Match` menunjukkan status rekonsiliasi:"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/india.rst:584
msgid "Orange: Partially matched (some bills require correction)."
msgstr "Oranye: Sebagian cocok (beberapa tagihan memerlukan koreksi)."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/india.rst:585
msgid "Green: Fully matched (all bills reconciled)."
msgstr "Hijau: Sepenuhnya cocok (semua tagihan direkonsiliasi)."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/india.rst:587
msgid ""
"In case of mismatches, correct the affected bills, then click the :icon:`fa-"
"ellipsis-v` :guilabel:`(ellipsis)` icon to access additional options:"
msgstr ""
"Jika terjadi ketidakcocokan, perbaiki tagihan yang terpengaruh, lalu klik "
"ikon :icon:`fa-ellipsis-v` :guilabel:`(elipsis)` untuk mengakses opsi "
"tambahan:"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/india.rst:590
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Re-Match`: Re-run the matching process after making corrections."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Re-Match`: Jalankan ulang proses pencocokan setelah melakukan "
"koreksi."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/india.rst:591
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Reset`: Reset the reconciliation to the :guilabel:`Match` stage."
msgstr ":guilabel:`Reset`: Atur ulang rekonsiliasi ke tahap :guilabel:`Match`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/india.rst:593
msgid ""
"After all bills are fully matched, click the :icon:`fa-ellipsis-"
"v` :guilabel:`(ellipsis)` icon and select :guilabel:`Mark as Complete`. "
"The :guilabel:`Complete` stage in the progress bar turns green, finalizing "
"the bill reconciliation."
msgstr ""
"Setelah semua tagihan sepenuhnya cocok, klik ikon :icon:`fa-ellipsis-v` "
":guilabel:`(elipsis)` dan pilih :guilabel:`Mark as Complete`. Tahap "
":guilabel:`Complete` pada bilah kemajuan berubah menjadi hijau, "
"menyelesaikan rekonsiliasi tagihan."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/india.rst:601
#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/malaysia.rst:111
msgid "Tax reports"
msgstr "Laporan pajak"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/india.rst:606
msgid "GSTR-1 report"
msgstr "Laporan GSTR-1"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/india.rst:608
msgid ""
"The :guilabel:`GSTR-1` report is divided into sections. It displays "
"the :guilabel:`Base` amount, :abbr:`CGST (Central Goods and Services "
"Tax)`, :abbr:`SGST (State Goods and Service Tax)`, :abbr:`IGST (Integrated "
"Goods and Services Tax)`, and :guilabel:`CESS` for each section."
msgstr ""
"Laporan :guilabel:`GSTR-1` dibagi menjadi beberapa bagian. Laporan ini "
"menampilkan jumlah :guilabel:`Dasar`, :abbr:`CGST (Pajak Barang dan Jasa "
"Pusat)`, :abbr:`SGST (Pajak Barang dan Jasa Negara Bagian)`, :abbr:`IGST "
"(Pajak Barang dan Jasa Terintegrasi)`, dan :guilabel:`CESS` untuk setiap "
"bagian."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/india.rst:0
msgid "GSTR-1 Report"
msgstr "Laporan GSTR-1"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/india.rst:618
msgid "GSTR-2B report"
msgstr "Laporan GSTR-2B"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/india.rst:620
msgid ""
"The :guilabel:`GSTR-2` report is divided into sections. It displays "
"the :guilabel:`Base` amount, :abbr:`CGST (Central Goods and Services "
"Tax)`, :abbr:`SGST (State Goods and Service Tax)`, :abbr:`IGST (Integrated "
"Goods and Services Tax)`, and :guilabel:`CESS` for each section."
msgstr ""
"Laporan :guilabel:`GSTR-2` dibagi menjadi beberapa bagian. Ini menampilkan "
"jumlah :guilabel:`Base`, :abbr:`CGST (Central Goods and Services Tax)`, "
":abbr:`SGST (State Goods and Service Tax)`, :abbr:`IGST (Integrated Goods "
"and Services Tax)`, dan :guilabel:`CESS` untuk setiap bagian."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/india.rst:0
msgid "GSTR-2B Report"
msgstr "Laporan GSTR-2B"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/india.rst:630
msgid "GSTR-3B report"
msgstr "Laporan GSTR-3B"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/india.rst:632
msgid "The :guilabel:`GSTR-3B` report contains different sections:"
msgstr "Laporan :guilabel:`GSTR-3B` berisi berbagai bagian:"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/india.rst:634
msgid "Details of inward and outward supply subject to a **reverse charge**;"
msgstr "Rincian pasokan masuk dan keluar yang dikenakan **biaya balik**;"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/india.rst:635
msgid "Eligible :abbr:`ITC (Income Tax Credit)`;"
msgstr ":abbr:`ITC (Kredit Pajak Penghasilan)` yang memenuhi syarat;"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/india.rst:636
msgid "Values of **exempt**, **Nil-rated**, and **non-GST** inward supply;"
msgstr ""
"Nilai pasokan masuk yang **dikecualikan**, **bertarif Nol**, dan **non-GST**;"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/india.rst:637
msgid "Details of inter-state supplies made to **unregistered** persons."
msgstr ""
"Rincian pasokan antar negara bagian yang dilakukan kepada orang yang **tidak "
"terdaftar**."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/india.rst:0
msgid "GSTR-3B Report"
msgstr "Laporan GSTR-3B"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/india.rst:643
msgid "Profit and Loss (IN) report"
msgstr "Laporan Laba Rugi (IN)"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/india.rst:645
msgid ""
"This is a :guilabel:`Profit and Loss` report that displays the balances for "
"**Opening Stock** and **Closing Stock**. It helps users using Continental "
"accounting to accurately determine the cost of goods (i.e :guilabel:`Opening "
"Stock` + purchases during the period - :guilabel:`Closing Stock`)."
msgstr ""
"Ini adalah laporan :guilabel:`Laba Rugi` yang menampilkan saldo untuk **Stok "
"Pembukaan** dan **Stok Penutupan**. Laporan ini membantu pengguna yang "
"menggunakan akuntansi Kontinental untuk menentukan biaya barang secara "
"akurat (yaitu :guilabel:`Stok Pembukaan` + pembelian selama periode - "
":guilabel:`Stok Penutupan`)."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/india.rst:0
msgid "Profit and Loss report"
msgstr "Laporan Laba Rugi"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/india.rst:655
msgid "TDS/TCS threshold alert"
msgstr "Peringatan ambang batas TDS/TCS"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/india.rst:657
msgid ""
":abbr:`TDS (tax deducted at source)` and :abbr:`TCS (tax collected at "
"source)` are tax provisions under Indian law, triggered when transaction "
"amounts exceed specified thresholds. This alert notifies users when the "
"value of invoices or bills surpasses these limits, prompting the application "
"of the appropriate TDS/TCS."
msgstr ""
":abbr:`TDS (pajak dipotong di sumber)` dan :abbr:`TCS (pajak dipungut di "
"sumber)` adalah ketentuan pajak berdasarkan hukum India, yang dipicu ketika "
"jumlah transaksi melebihi ambang batas yang ditentukan. Peringatan ini "
"memberi tahu pengguna ketika nilai faktur atau tagihan melampaui batas ini, "
"sehingga memicu penerapan TDS/TCS yang sesuai."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/india.rst:662
msgid ""
"To configure Odoo to advise you on when to apply TDS/TCS, set "
"the :guilabel:`TDS/TCS section` field on the corresponding account in the "
"chart of accounts. Odoo will display a banner suggesting the TDS/TCS section "
"under which tax might be applicable when recording an invoice or bill."
msgstr ""
"Untuk mengonfigurasi Odoo agar memberi tahu Anda kapan harus menerapkan TDS/"
"TCS, atur bidang :guilabel:`Bagian TDS/TCS` pada akun yang sesuai di bagan "
"akun. Odoo akan menampilkan banner yang menyarankan bagian TDS/TCS di mana "
"pajak mungkin berlaku saat mencatat faktur atau tagihan."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/india.rst:669
msgid "Navigate to :menuselection:`Accounting --> Configuration --> Settings`"
msgstr ""
"Navigasikan ke :menuselection:`Akuntansi --> Konfigurasi --> Pengaturan`"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/india.rst:670
msgid ""
"In the :guilabel:`Indian Integration` section, enable the :guilabel:`TDS` "
"or :guilabel:`TCS` feature as required."
msgstr ""
