#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/india.rst:685
msgid "Applying TCS/TDS on invoices and bills"
msgstr "Menerapkan TCS/TDS pada faktur dan tagihan"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/india.rst:687
msgid ""
"Based on the account used on the customer invoice or vendor bill, Odoo "
"checks the TCS/TDS threshold limit. If the limit specified in "
"the :guilabel:`TCS/TDS Section` of the account is exceeded, Odoo displays an "
"alert that suggests applying the appropriate TCS/TDS. The alert will "
"disappear once the TCS/TDS is applied."
msgstr ""
"Berdasarkan akun yang digunakan pada faktur pelanggan atau tagihan vendor, "
"Odoo memeriksa batas ambang TCS/TDS. Jika batas yang ditentukan dalam "
":guilabel:`Bagian TCS/TDS` dari akun terlampaui, Odoo menampilkan peringatan "
"yang menyarankan untuk menerapkan TCS/TDS yang sesuai. Peringatan akan "
"hilang setelah TCS/TDS diterapkan."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/india.rst:None
msgid "TCS advice"
msgstr "Saran TCS"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/india.rst:695
msgid ""
