#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/italy.rst:110
msgid ""
"If you need to use a different kind of exoneration, go "
"to :menuselection:`Accounting --> Configuration --> Taxes`, select a similar "
"tax, then click on the cog icon and select :guilabel:`Duplicate`. In "
"the :guilabel:`Advanced Options` tab, add the :guilabel:`Exoneration` "
"and :guilabel:`Law Reference`. To confirm click :guilabel:`Save`."
msgstr ""
"Jika Anda perlu menggunakan jenis pembebasan yang berbeda, buka "
":menuselection:`Akuntansi --> Konfigurasi --> Pajak`, pilih pajak serupa, "
"lalu klik ikon roda gigi dan pilih :guilabel:`Duplikasi`. Di tab "
":guilabel:`Opsi Lanjutan`, tambahkan :guilabel:`Pembebasan` dan "
":guilabel:`Referensi Hukum`. Untuk mengonfirmasi, klik :guilabel:`Simpan`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/italy.rst:116
msgid ""
"**Rename** your taxes in the :guilabel:`Name` field according to "
"their :guilabel:`Exoneration` to differentiate them easily."
msgstr ""
"**Ubah nama** pajak Anda di kolom :guilabel:`Nama` sesuai dengan "
":guilabel:`Pembebasan` mereka untuk membedakannya dengan mudah."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/italy.rst:122
msgid "Reverse charge"
msgstr "Reverse charge"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/italy.rst:124
msgid ""
"The **reverse charge** mechanism is a VAT rule that shifts the liability to "
"pay VAT from the supplier to the customer. The customers pay the VAT "
"*themselves* to the |AdE| instead. There are different types:"
msgstr ""
"Mekanisme **reverse charge** adalah aturan PPN yang mengalihkan kewajiban "
"membayar PPN dari pemasok ke pelanggan. Pelanggan membayar PPN *sendiri* ke "
"|AdE| sebagai gantinya. Ada beberapa jenis:"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/italy.rst:0
msgid ":guilabel:`Internal Reverse Charge` (for domestic sales)"
msgstr ":guilabel:`Reverse Charge Internal` (untuk penjualan domestik)"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/italy.rst:0
msgid ""
"The VAT responsibility is shifted to the buyer for certain categories of "
"products and services."
msgstr ""
"Tanggung jawab PPN dialihkan kepada pembeli untuk kategori produk dan "
"layanan tertentu."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/italy.rst:0
msgid ":guilabel:`External Reverse Charge` (for intra-EU sales)"
msgstr ":guilabel:`Reverse Charge Eksternal` (untuk penjualan intra-EU)"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/italy.rst:0
msgid ""
"VAT is due in the country of the delivery or in the country where the "
"service is performed. When the buyer is itself an Italian business, then the "
"EU offers a mechanism that allows the seller to transfer his responsibility "
"to the buyer."
msgstr ""
"PPN jatuh tempo di negara pengiriman atau di negara tempat layanan "
"dilakukan. Ketika pembeli itu sendiri adalah bisnis Italia, maka EU "
"menawarkan mekanisme yang memungkinkan penjual untuk mengalihkan tanggung "
"jawabnya kepada pembeli."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/italy.rst:138
#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/italy.rst:553
#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/spain.rst:146
msgid "Invoices"
msgstr "Faktur"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/italy.rst:140
msgid ""
"**Reverse-charged** customer invoices show no VAT amount, but the |AdE| "
"requires the seller to specify the :guilabel:`Tax Exemption` reason and "
"the :guilabel:`Law Reference` that enable the reverse-charge mechanism. Odoo "
"provides a set of special 0% taxes that can be assigned to each reverse-"
"charged invoice lines, representing the most commonly used configurations."
msgstr ""
"Faktur pelanggan **reverse-charged** tidak menampilkan jumlah PPN, tetapi "
"|AdE| mengharuskan penjual untuk menentukan alasan :guilabel:`Tax Exemption` "
"dan :guilabel:`Law Reference` yang memungkinkan mekanisme reverse-charge. "
"Odoo menyediakan serangkaian pajak khusus 0% yang dapat ditetapkan untuk "
"setiap baris faktur reverse-charged, mewakili konfigurasi yang paling umum "
"digunakan."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/italy.rst:150
msgid ""
"Italian companies subject to **reverse charge** must send bill details to "
"the |AdE|."
msgstr ""
"Perusahaan Italia yang dikenakan **reverse charge** harus mengirimkan "
"rincian tagihan ke |AdE|."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/italy.rst:153
msgid ""
"Self-reported VAT XML files must be issued and sent to the |AdE| for "
"**reverse charged** bills."
msgstr ""
"File XML PPN yang dilaporkan sendiri harus diterbitkan dan dikirim ke |AdE| "
"untuk tagihan **reverse charged**."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/italy.rst:155
msgid ""
"When creating a vendor bill, **reverse charge** taxes are available to be "
"added in the :guilabel:`Taxes` field. You can check which taxes are "
"available by going to :menuselection:`Accounting --> Configuration --> "
"Taxes`, you can see that the 10% Goods and 22% Services taxes are activated, "
"among others. Due to the automated configuration of the Italian fiscal "
"position, these are automatically activated in the tax list."
msgstr ""
"Saat membuat tagihan vendor, pajak **reverse charge** tersedia untuk "
"ditambahkan di kolom :guilabel:`Pajak`. Anda dapat memeriksa pajak mana yang "
"tersedia dengan membuka :menuselection:`Akuntansi --> Konfigurasi --> "
"Pajak`, Anda dapat melihat bahwa pajak Barang 10% dan Layanan 22% "
"diaktifkan, di antara yang lainnya. Karena konfigurasi otomatis posisi "
"fiskal Italia, pajak ini secara otomatis diaktifkan dalam daftar pajak."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/italy.rst:166
msgid ""
"The Italian localization has a specific :ref:`tax grid <accounting/tax-"
"returns/tax-grids>` section for **reverse charge** taxes. These tax grids "
"are identifiable by the :guilabel:`VJ` tag, and can be found by going "
"to :menuselection:`Accounting --> Reporting --> Tax Return`."
msgstr ""
"Lokalisasi Italia memiliki bagian :ref:`tax grid <accounting/tax-returns/tax-"
"grids>` khusus untuk pajak **reverse charge**. Tax grid ini dapat "
"diidentifikasi dengan tag :guilabel:`VJ`, dan dapat ditemukan dengan membuka "
":menuselection:`Accounting --> Reporting --> Tax Return`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/italy.rst:None
msgid "Reverse charge tax grid from the VJ section of the Tax Declaration"
msgstr "Grid pajak reverse charge dari bagian VJ Deklarasi Pajak"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/italy.rst:179
msgid ""
"Make sure all the Italian-specific e-invoicing :ref:`modules <localizations/"
"italy/modules>` are :ref:`installed <general/install>`."
msgstr ""
"Pastikan semua :ref:`modul <localizations/italy/modules>` e-invoicing khusus "
"Italia sudah :ref:`diinstal <general/install>`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/italy.rst:182
msgid ""
"The |SdI| is the :doc:`electronic invoicing <../accounting/customer_invoices/"
"electronic_invoicing>` system used in Italy. It enables the sending and "
"receiving of electronic invoices to and from customers. The documents must "
"be in an XML :abbr:`EDI (Electronic Data Interchange)` format called "
"**FatturaPA** and formally validated by the system before being delivered."
msgstr ""
"|SdI| adalah sistem :doc:`electronic invoicing <../accounting/"
"customer_invoices/electronic_invoicing>` yang digunakan di Italia. Sistem "
"ini memungkinkan pengiriman dan penerimaan faktur elektronik ke dan dari "
"pelanggan. Dokumen harus dalam format :abbr:`EDI (Electronic Data "
"Interchange)` XML yang disebut **FatturaPA** dan divalidasi secara formal "
"oleh sistem sebelum dikirimkan."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/italy.rst:187
msgid ""
"To be able to receive invoices and notifications, the |SdI| service must be "
"notified that the user's files need to be sent to Odoo and processed on "
"their behalf. To do so, you must set up Odoo's :guilabel:`Destination Code` "
"on the |AdE| portal."
msgstr ""
"Untuk dapat menerima faktur dan notifikasi, layanan |SdI| harus diberitahu "
"bahwa file user perlu dikirim ke Odoo dan diproses atas nama mereka. Untuk "
"melakukannya, Anda harus menyiapkan :guilabel:`Destination Code` Odoo di "
"portal |AdE|."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/italy.rst:191
msgid ""
"Go to the `Italian authorities portal <https://"
"ivaservizi.agenziaentrate.gov.it/portale>`_ and authenticate."
msgstr ""
"Buka `portal otoritas Italia <https://ivaservizi.agenziaentrate.gov.it/"
"portale>`_ dan lakukan autentikasi."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/italy.rst:193
msgid "Go to the :guilabel:`Fatture e Corrispettivi` section."
msgstr "Buka bagian :guilabel:`Fatture e Corrispettivi`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/italy.rst:194
msgid ""
"Set the user as Legal Party for the VAT number you wish to configure the "
"electronic address."
msgstr ""
"Tetapkan user sebagai Pihak Legal untuk nomor PPN yang ingin Anda "
"konfigurasikan alamat elektroniknya."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/italy.rst:195
msgid ""
"In :menuselection:`Servizi Disponibili --> Fatturazione Elettronica --> "
"Registrazione dell’indirizzo telematico dove ricevere tutte le fatture "
"elettroniche`, insert Odoo's :guilabel:`Destination Code` `K95IV18`, and "
"confirm."
msgstr ""
"Di :menuselection:`Servizi Disponibili --> Fatturazione Elettronica --> "
"Registrazione dell'indirizzo telematico dove ricevere tutte le fatture "
"elettroniche`, masukkan :guilabel:`Kode Tujuan` Odoo `K95IV18`, dan "
"konfirmasi."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/italy.rst:202
msgid "Demo and production modes"
msgstr "Mode demo dan produksi"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/italy.rst:205
msgid ""
"Demo mode is enabled by default and remains active until the "
"option :guilabel:`By checking this box, I authorize Odoo to send and receive "
"my invoices through the Sistema di Interscambio (SDI)` is enabled in "
"the :guilabel:`Fattura Electronica (FatturaPA)` section. Once this option is "
"activated, production mode is enabled and cannot be disabled."
msgstr ""
"Mode demo diaktifkan secara default dan tetap aktif hingga opsi "
":guilabel:`By checking this box, I authorize Odoo to send and receive my "
"invoices through the Sistema di Interscambio (SDI)` diaktifkan di bagian "
":guilabel:`Fattura Electronica (FatturaPA)`. Setelah opsi ini diaktifkan, "
"mode produksi diaktifkan dan tidak dapat dinonaktifkan."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/italy.rst:209
msgid ""
"Demo mode simulates an environment in which invoices are sent to the "
"government. In this mode, invoices must be *manually* downloaded as XML "
"files and uploaded to the |AdE|'s website."
msgstr ""
"Mode demo mensimulasikan lingkungan di mana faktur dikirim ke pemerintah. "
"Dalam mode ini, faktur harus diunduh *secara manual* sebagai file XML dan "
"diunggah ke situs web |AdE|."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/italy.rst:212
msgid ""
"Since files are transmitted through Odoo's server before being sent to the |"
"SdI| or received by your database, authorization is required for Odoo to "
"process them. To activate production mode and enable transmission to the |"
"SdI|, follow these steps:"
msgstr ""
"Karena file ditransmisikan melalui server Odoo sebelum dikirim ke |SdI| atau "
"diterima oleh database Anda, diperlukan otorisasi agar Odoo dapat "
"memprosesnya. Untuk mengaktifkan mode produksi dan mengaktifkan transmisi ke "
"|SdI|, ikuti langkah-langkah berikut:"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/italy.rst:216
msgid ""
"Make sure the :guilabel:`Codice Fiscale` field is completed in "
"the :ref:`Company information <localizations/italy/company>`."
msgstr ""
"Pastikan field :guilabel:`Codice Fiscale` telah diisi di :ref:`Company "
"information <localizations/italy/company>`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/italy.rst:218
msgid ""
"Go to :menuselection:`Accounting --> Configuration --> Settings` and scroll "
"to the :guilabel:`Italian Electronic Invoicing` section."
msgstr ""
"Buka :menuselection:`Accounting --> Configuration --> Settings` dan gulir ke "
"bagian :guilabel:`Italian Electronic Invoicing`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/italy.rst:220
msgid ""
"In the :guilabel:`Fattura Electronica (FatturaPA)` section, enable the "
"option :guilabel:`By checking this box, I authorize Odoo to send and receive "
"my invoices through the Sistema di Interscambio (SDI)`."
msgstr ""
"Di bagian :guilabel:`Fattura Electronica (FatturaPA)`, aktifkan opsi "
":guilabel:`By checking this box, I authorize Odoo to send and receive my "
"invoices through the Sistema di Interscambio (SDI)`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/italy.rst:228
#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/italy.rst:643
msgid "Process"
msgstr "Proses :"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/italy.rst:230
msgid ""
"The submission of invoices to the |SdI| for Italy is an electronic process "
"used for the mandatory transmission of tax documents in XML format between "
"companies and the |AdE| to reduce errors and verify the correctness of "
"operations."
msgstr ""
"Pengajuan faktur ke |SdI| untuk Italia adalah proses elektronik yang "
"digunakan untuk transmisi wajib dokumen pajak dalam format XML antara "
"perusahaan dan |AdE| untuk mengurangi kesalahan dan memverifikasi kebenaran "
"operasi."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/italy.rst:235
msgid ""
"You can check the current status of an invoice by the :guilabel:`SdI State` "
"field. The XML file is attached to the invoice."
msgstr ""
"Anda dapat memeriksa status faktur saat ini di kolom :guilabel:`Status SdI`. "
"File XML dilampirkan pada faktur."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/italy.rst:None
msgid "EDI system architecture"
msgstr "Arsitektur sistem EDI"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/italy.rst:244
msgid "XML documents creation"
msgstr "Pembuatan dokumen XML"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/italy.rst:246
msgid ""
"Odoo generates the required XML files as attachments to invoices in the "
"`FatturaPA` format required by the :abbr:`AdE (Agenzia delle Entrate)`. Once "
"the invoices needed are selected, click the :guilabel:`Send` button."
msgstr ""
"Odoo menghasilkan file XML yang diperlukan sebagai lampiran pada faktur "
"dalam format `FatturaPA` yang diperlukan oleh :abbr:`AdE (Agenzia delle "
"Entrate)`. Setelah faktur yang diperlukan dipilih, klik tombol "
":guilabel:`Kirim`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/italy.rst:250
msgid ""
"When the pop-up window opens there is a selection of actions that can be "
"taken. :guilabel:`Generate XML File` generates the attachments."
msgstr ""
"Ketika jendela pop-up terbuka, ada pilihan tindakan yang dapat diambil. "
":guilabel:`Hasilkan File XML` menghasilkan lampiran."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/italy.rst:253
msgid ""
"The XML file as well as the PDF once can be found attached to the invoice."
msgstr "File XML serta PDF dapat ditemukan dilampirkan pada faktur."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/italy.rst:None
msgid "EDI Attachments"
msgstr "Lampiran EDI"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/italy.rst:258
msgid "After choosing the desired actions, click :guilabel:`Send`."
msgstr "Setelah memilih tindakan yang diinginkan, klik :guilabel:`Kirim`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/italy.rst:263
msgid "Submission to SDI"
msgstr "Pengiriman ke SDI"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/italy.rst:265
msgid ""
"The :guilabel:`Send to Tax Agency` option in the :guilabel:`Send and Print` "
"dialog sends the attachment to the :guilabel:`Proxy Server`, which gathers "
"all requests and then forwards them via a WebServices channel to the |SdI|. "
"Check the sending status of the invoice through the :guilabel:`Check "
"Sending` button at the top of the invoice's view."
msgstr ""
"Opsi :guilabel:`Kirim ke Badan Pajak` dalam dialog :guilabel:`Kirim dan "
"Cetak` mengirimkan lampiran ke :guilabel:`Server Proxy`, yang mengumpulkan "
"semua permintaan dan kemudian meneruskannya melalui saluran WebServices ke "
"|SdI|. Periksa status pengiriman faktur melalui tombol :guilabel:`Periksa "
"Pengiriman` di bagian atas tampilan faktur."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/italy.rst:273
msgid "Processing by SDI"
msgstr "Pemrosesan oleh SDI"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/italy.rst:275
msgid ""
"The |SdI| receives the document and verifies for any errors. At this stage, "
"the invoice is in the :guilabel:`SdI Processing` state, as shown on the "
"invoice. The invoice also gets assigned a :guilabel:`FatturaPA Transaction` "
"number that is shown in the :guilabel:`Electronic Invoicing` tab. The checks "
"may take variable time, ranging from a few seconds up to a day, depending on "
"the queue of invoices sent throughout Italy."
msgstr ""
"|SdI| menerima dokumen dan memverifikasi kesalahan apa pun. Pada tahap ini, "
"faktur berada dalam status :guilabel:`Pemrosesan SdI`, seperti yang "
"ditampilkan pada faktur. Faktur juga mendapatkan nomor :guilabel:`Transaksi "
"FatturaPA` yang ditampilkan di tab :guilabel:`Faktur Elektronik`. "
"Pemeriksaan dapat memakan waktu yang bervariasi, mulai dari beberapa detik "
"hingga satu hari, tergantung pada antrean faktur yang dikirim di seluruh "
"Italia."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/italy.rst:None
msgid "Check Sending button and Sdi Processing state"
msgstr "Periksa tombol Kirim dan status Pemrosesan SdI"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/italy.rst:287
msgid "Acceptance"
msgstr "Penerimaan"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/italy.rst:289
msgid ""
"If the document is valid, it is recorded and considered fiscally valid by "
"the |AdE|, which will proceed with archiving in :guilabel:`Substitute "
"Storage (Conservazione Sostitutiva)` if explicitly requested on the Agency's "
"portal."
msgstr ""
"Jika dokumen valid, dokumen tersebut dicatat dan dianggap sah secara fiskal "
"oleh |AdE|, yang akan melanjutkan dengan pengarsipan dalam "
":guilabel:`Penyimpanan Pengganti (Conservazione Sostitutiva)` jika secara "
"eksplisit diminta di portal Badan."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/italy.rst:294
msgid ""
"Odoo does not offer the `Conservazione Sostitutiva <https://www.agid.gov.it/"
"index.php/it/piattaforme/conservazione>`_ requirements. Other providers and |"
"AdE| supply free and certified storage to meet the specifications requested "
"by law."
msgstr ""
"Odoo tidak menawarkan persyaratan `Conservazione Sostitutiva <https://"
"www.agid.gov.it/index.php/it/piattaforme/conservazione>`_. Penyedia lain dan "
"|AdE| menyediakan penyimpanan gratis dan tersertifikasi untuk memenuhi "
"spesifikasi yang diminta oleh hukum."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/italy.rst:299
msgid ""
"The |SdI| :guilabel:`Destination Code` attempts to forward the invoice to "
"the customer at the provided address, whether it is a `PEC` email address or "
"a |SdI| :guilabel:`Destination Code` for their ERP's WebServices channels. A "
"maximum of 6 attempts are made every 12 hours, so even if unsuccessful, this "
"process can take up to three days. The invoice status is :guilabel:`Accepted "
"by SDI, Forwarding to Partner`."
msgstr ""
"|SdI| :guilabel:`Kode Tujuan` mencoba meneruskan faktur ke pelanggan di "
"alamat yang diberikan, baik itu alamat email `PEC` atau |SdI| "
":guilabel:`Kode Tujuan` untuk saluran WebServices ERP mereka. Maksimal 6 "
"percobaan dilakukan setiap 12 jam, jadi meskipun tidak berhasil, proses ini "
"dapat memakan waktu hingga tiga hari. Status faktur adalah "
":guilabel:`Diterima oleh SDI, Meneruskan ke Mitra`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/italy.rst:308
msgid "Possible rejection"
msgstr "Kemungkinan penolakan"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/italy.rst:310
msgid ""
"The |SdI| may find inaccuracies in the compilation, possibly even formal "
"ones. In this case, the invoice is in the :guilabel:`SDI Rejected` state. "
"The |SdI|'s observations are inserted at the top of the Invoice tab. To "
"resolve the issue, it is sufficient to delete the attachments of the "
"invoice, return the invoice to :guilabel:`Draft`, and fix the errors. Once "
"the invoice is ready, it can be resent."
msgstr ""
"|SdI| mungkin menemukan ketidakakuratan dalam kompilasi, bahkan mungkin yang "
"bersifat formal. Dalam hal ini, faktur berada dalam status "
":guilabel:`Ditolak SDI`. Pengamatan |SdI| dimasukkan di bagian atas tab "
"Faktur. Untuk mengatasi masalah ini, cukup hapus lampiran faktur, kembalikan "
"faktur ke :guilabel:`Draf`, dan perbaiki kesalahan. Setelah faktur siap, "
"faktur dapat dikirim ulang."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/italy.rst:317
msgid ""
"To regenerate the XML, both the XML attachment and the PDF report must be "
"deleted, so that they are then regenerated together. This ensures that both "
"always contain the same data."
msgstr ""
"Untuk membuat ulang XML, lampiran XML dan laporan PDF harus dihapus, "
"sehingga keduanya kemudian dibuat ulang bersama-sama. Ini memastikan bahwa "
"keduanya selalu berisi data yang sama."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/italy.rst:None
msgid "EDI Rejected State"
msgstr "Status Ditolak EDI"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/italy.rst:326
msgid "Forwarding completed"
msgstr "Penerusan selesai"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/italy.rst:328
msgid ""
"The invoice has been delivered to the customer; however, you can still send "
"a copy to the customer in PDF via email or post. Its status "
"is :guilabel:`Accepted by SDI, Delivered to Partner`."
msgstr ""
"Faktur telah dikirim ke pelanggan; namun, Anda masih dapat mengirim salinan "
"ke pelanggan dalam format PDF melalui email atau pos. Statusnya adalah "
":guilabel:`Diterima oleh SDI, Dikirim ke Mitra`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/italy.rst:331
msgid ""
"If the |SdI| cannot contact your customer, they may not be registered on the "
"|AdE| portal. In this case, just make sure to send the invoice in PDF via "
"email or by mail. The invoice is then in the :guilabel:`Accepted by SDI, "
"Partner Delivery Failed` state."
msgstr ""
"Jika |SdI| tidak dapat menghubungi pelanggan Anda, mereka mungkin tidak "
"terdaftar di portal |AdE|. Dalam hal ini, pastikan untuk mengirim faktur "
"dalam format PDF melalui email atau surat. Faktur kemudian berada dalam "
"status :guilabel:`Diterima oleh SDI, Pengiriman Mitra Gagal`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/italy.rst:338
msgid "Tax integration"
msgstr "Integrasi pajak"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/italy.rst:340
msgid ""
"When you receive a vendor bill, either from |SdI|, from paper or from an "
"imported XML file, the Tax Agency might request that you send some tax "
"information integration back to the |SdI|. It happens when a transaction "
"that was tax exempt becomes taxable for any reason."
msgstr ""
"Ketika Anda menerima tagihan vendor, baik dari |SdI|, dari kertas atau dari "
"file XML yang diimpor, Badan Pajak mungkin meminta Anda untuk mengirim "
"kembali integrasi informasi pajak ke |SdI|. Ini terjadi ketika transaksi "
"yang dibebaskan dari pajak menjadi kena pajak karena alasan apa pun."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/italy.rst:345
msgid "Here is a non-exhaustive list:"
msgstr "Berikut adalah daftar yang tidak lengkap:"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/italy.rst:0
msgid ":ref:`localizations/italy/reverse-charge`"
msgstr ":ref:`localizations/italy/reverse-charge`"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/italy.rst:0
msgid ""
"As a buyer, you have to pay taxes on what you buy and integrate tax "
"information. :guilabel:`Reverse Charge` taxes."
msgstr ""
"Sebagai pembeli, Anda harus membayar pajak atas apa yang Anda beli dan "
"mengintegrasikan informasi pajak. Pajak :guilabel:`Reverse Charge`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/italy.rst:0
msgid ":ref:`localizations/italy/split-payment`"
msgstr ":ref:`localizations/italy/split-payment`"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/italy.rst:0
msgid ""
"As a |PA| business buyer, you have to pay taxes and integrate tax "
"information. Be sure that you replace the :guilabel:`0% Sale Taxes` on the "
"vendor bill you received with the correct :guilabel:`Split Payment` taxes."
msgstr ""
"Sebagai pembeli bisnis |PA|, Anda harus membayar pajak dan mengintegrasikan "
"informasi pajak. Pastikan Anda mengganti :guilabel:`Pajak Penjualan 0%` pada "
"tagihan vendor yang Anda terima dengan pajak :guilabel:`Pembayaran Terpisah` "
"yang benar."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/italy.rst:0
msgid ":guilabel:`Self Consumption`"
msgstr ":guilabel:`Self Consumption`"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/italy.rst:0
msgid ""
"When, as a business owner, you use an asset that you bought for business for "
"personal reasons instead, you have to pay those taxes you originally "
"deducted as a business cost for it."
msgstr ""
"Ketika, sebagai pemilik bisnis, Anda menggunakan aset yang Anda beli untuk "
"bisnis untuk keperluan pribadi, Anda harus membayar pajak yang awalnya Anda "
"deduksi sebagai biaya bisnis untuk aset tersebut."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/italy.rst:358
msgid ""
"Odoo may detect that your vendor bill can be interpreted as a document of a "
"type that needs tax integration, as detailed in the :ref:`localizations/"
"italy/document-types` section."
msgstr ""
"Odoo dapat mendeteksi bahwa tagihan vendor Anda dapat ditafsirkan sebagai "
"dokumen jenis yang memerlukan integrasi pajak, seperti dijelaskan dalam "
"bagian :ref:`localizations/italy/document-types`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/italy.rst:362
msgid ""
"Be sure that you replace the :guilabel:`0% Sale Taxes` on the vendor bill "
"you received with the ones you're supposed to pay to the |AdE|. A button "
"then appears on the top of the single vendor bill form to send them."
msgstr ""
"Pastikan Anda mengganti :guilabel:`Pajak Penjualan 0%` pada tagihan vendor "
"yang Anda terima dengan yang seharusnya Anda bayar ke |AdE|. Tombol kemudian "
"muncul di bagian atas formulir tagihan vendor tunggal untuk mengirimnya."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/italy.rst:366
msgid ""
"When clicking on the :guilabel:`Send Tax Integration` button, an XML file of "
"the appropriate :guilabel:`Document Type` is generated, attached to the "
"bill, and sent as for invoices."
msgstr ""
"Ketika mengklik tombol :guilabel:`Send Tax Integration`, file XML dengan "
":guilabel:`Document Type` yang sesuai akan dihasilkan, dilampirkan ke "
"tagihan, dan dikirim seperti untuk faktur."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/italy.rst:0
msgid "EDI Send Tax Integration button"
msgstr "Tombol EDI Send Tax Integration"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/italy.rst:377
msgid ""
"The |SdI| requires businesses to send customer invoices and other documents "
"through the :abbr:`EDI (Electronic Data Interchange)`."
msgstr ""
"|SdI| mengharuskan bisnis untuk mengirim faktur pelanggan dan dokumen lain "
"melalui :abbr:`EDI (Electronic Data Interchange)`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/italy.rst:380
msgid ""
"The following :guilabel:`Document Type` codes all technically identify "
"different business use cases."
msgstr ""
"Kode :guilabel:`Document Type` berikut secara teknis mengidentifikasi kasus "
"penggunaan bisnis yang berbeda."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/italy.rst:385
msgid "TD01 - invoices"
msgstr "TD01 - faktur"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/italy.rst:387
msgid ""
"This represents the standard **domestic** scenario for all invoices "
"exchanged through the |SdI|. Any invoice that doesn't fall into one of the "
"specific special cases is categorized as a regular invoice, identified by "
"the :guilabel:`Document Type` `TD01`."
msgstr ""
"Ini merupakan skenario **domestik** standar untuk semua faktur yang "
"dipertukarkan melalui |SdI|. Setiap faktur yang tidak termasuk dalam salah "
"satu kasus khusus tertentu dikategorikan sebagai faktur reguler, "
"diidentifikasi oleh :guilabel:`Jenis Dokumen` `TD01`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/italy.rst:394
msgid "TD02 - down payments"
msgstr "TD02 - uang muka"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/italy.rst:396
msgid ""
"**Down payment** invoices are imported/exported with a "
"different :guilabel:`Document Type` code `TDO2` than regular invoices. Upon "
"import of the invoice, a regular vendor bill is created."
msgstr ""
"Faktur **uang muka** diimpor/diekspor dengan kode :guilabel:`Document Type` "
"`TDO2` yang berbeda dari faktur biasa. Saat mengimpor faktur, tagihan vendor "
"biasa akan dibuat."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/italy.rst:399
msgid ""
"Odoo exports transactions as `TD02` if the following conditions are met:"
msgstr ""
"Odoo mengekspor transaksi sebagai `TD02` jika kondisi berikut terpenuhi:"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/italy.rst:401
#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/italy.rst:541
msgid "It is an invoice."
msgstr "Ini adalah faktur."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/italy.rst:402
msgid "All invoice lines are related to down payment sales order lines."
msgstr "Semua baris faktur terkait dengan baris sales order uang muka."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/italy.rst:407
msgid "TD04 - credit notes"
msgstr "TD04 - nota kredit"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/italy.rst:409
msgid ""
"It is the standard scenario for all **credit notes** issued to **domestic** "
"clients, when we need to formally acknowledge that the seller is reducing or "
"cancelling a previously issued invoice, for example, in case of overbilling, "
"incorrect items, or overpayment. Just like invoices, they must be sent to "
"the |SdI|, their :guilabel:`Document Type` `TD04`"
msgstr ""
"Ini adalah skenario standar untuk semua **nota kredit** yang diterbitkan "
"kepada klien **domestik**, ketika kita perlu mengakui secara formal bahwa "
"penjual mengurangi atau membatalkan faktur yang diterbitkan sebelumnya, "
"misalnya, dalam kasus penagihan berlebih, item yang salah, atau pembayaran "
"berlebih. Sama seperti faktur, nota kredit harus dikirim ke |SdI|, "
":guilabel:`Jenis Dokumen` mereka adalah `TD04`"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/italy.rst:417
msgid "TD07, TD08, TD09 - simplified invoicing"
msgstr "TD07, TD08, TD09 - penagihan sederhana"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/italy.rst:419
msgid ""
"Simplified invoices (`TD07`), credit notes (`TD08`), and debit notes "
"(`TD09`) can be used to certify domestic transactions under 400 EUR (VAT "
"included). Its status is the same as that of a regular invoice, but with "
"fewer information requirements."
msgstr ""
"Faktur sederhana (`TD07`), nota kredit (`TD08`), dan nota debit (`TD09`) "
"dapat digunakan untuk mengesahkan transaksi domestik di bawah 400 EUR "
"(termasuk PPN). Statusnya sama dengan faktur biasa, tetapi dengan "
"persyaratan informasi yang lebih sedikit."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/italy.rst:423
msgid "For a simplified invoice to be established, it must include:"
msgstr "Agar faktur sederhana dapat dibuat, faktur harus mencakup:"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/italy.rst:425
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Customer Invoice` reference: **unique** numbering sequence with "
"**no gaps**."
msgstr ""
"Referensi :guilabel:`Faktur Pelanggan`: urutan penomoran **unik** **tanpa "
"celah**."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/italy.rst:426
msgid ":guilabel:`Invoice Date`: issue **date** of the invoice."
msgstr ":guilabel:`Tanggal Faktur`: **tanggal** penerbitan faktur."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/italy.rst:427
msgid ""
":ref:`Company Info <general/companies/company>`: the **seller**'s full "
"credentials (VAT/TIN number, name, full address)."
msgstr ""
":ref:`Info Perusahaan <general/companies/company>`: kredensial lengkap "
"**penjual** (nomor VAT/TIN, nama, alamat lengkap)."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/italy.rst:429
msgid ":guilabel:`VAT`: the **buyer**'s VAT/TIN number (on the partner form)."
msgstr ":guilabel:`VAT`: nomor VAT/TIN **pembeli** (pada formulir mitra)."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/italy.rst:430
msgid ":guilabel:`Total`: the total **amount** (VAT included) of the invoice."
msgstr ":guilabel:`Total`: **jumlah** total (termasuk PPN) dari faktur."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/italy.rst:432
msgid ""
"In the :abbr:`EDI (Electronic Data Interchange)`, Odoo exports invoices as "
"simplified if:"
msgstr ""
"Dalam :abbr:`EDI (Electronic Data Interchange)`, Odoo mengekspor faktur "
"sebagai sederhana jika:"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/italy.rst:434
msgid "It is a domestic transaction (i.e., the partner is from Italy)."
msgstr "Ini adalah transaksi domestik (yaitu, mitra berasal dari Italia)."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/italy.rst:435
msgid ""
"Your company's **required fields** (:guilabel:`VAT Number` "
"or :guilabel:`Codice Fiscale`, :guilabel:`Fiscal Regime`, and full "
"**address**) are provided."
msgstr ""
"Bidang **wajib** perusahaan Anda (:guilabel:`Nomor VAT` atau "
":guilabel:`Codice Fiscale`, :guilabel:`Rezim Fiskal`, dan **alamat** "
"lengkap) telah disediakan."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/italy.rst:437
msgid ""
"The partner's address is not fully specified (i.e., it misses the City or "
"the ZipCode)."
msgstr ""
"Alamat mitra tidak sepenuhnya ditentukan (yaitu, tidak ada Kota atau Kode "
"Pos)."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/italy.rst:438
msgid "The total amount of VAT included is **less** than **400 EUR**."
msgstr "Jumlah total PPN yang termasuk **kurang** dari **400 EUR**."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/italy.rst:441
msgid ""
"The 400 EUR threshold was defined in `the decree of the 10th of May 2019 in "
"the Gazzetta Ufficiale <https://www.gazzettaufficiale.it/eli/id/"
"2019/05/24/19A03271/sg>`_. We advise you to check the current official value."
msgstr ""
"Ambang batas 400 EUR ditetapkan dalam `keputusan 10 Mei 2019 di Gazzetta "
"Ufficiale <https://www.gazzettaufficiale.it/eli/id/2019/05/24/19A03271/sg>"
"`_. Kami menyarankan Anda untuk memeriksa nilai resmi saat ini."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/italy.rst:448
msgid "TD16 - internal reverse charge"
msgstr "TD16 - reverse charge internal"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/italy.rst:450
msgid ""
"Internal **reverse charge** transactions (see :ref:`localizations/italy/tax-"
"exemption` and :ref:`localizations/italy/reverse-charge`) are exported as "
"`TD16` if the following conditions are met:"
msgstr ""
"Transaksi **reverse charge** internal (lihat :ref:`localizations/italy/tax-"
"exemption` dan :ref:`localizations/italy/reverse-charge`) diekspor sebagai "
"`TD16` jika kondisi berikut terpenuhi:"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/italy.rst:454
#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/italy.rst:473
#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/italy.rst:489
#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/italy.rst:510
#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/italy.rst:576
msgid "It is a vendor bill."
msgstr "Ini adalah tagihan vendor."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/italy.rst:455
msgid ""
"It has at least **one tax** on the invoice lines that targets one of "
"these :ref:`tax grids <localizations/italy/grids>`: `VJ6`, `VJ7`, `VJ8`, "
"`VJ12`, `VJ13`, `VJ14`, `VJ15`, `VJ16`, `VJ17`"
msgstr ""
"Memiliki setidaknya **satu pajak** pada baris faktur yang menargetkan salah "
"satu :ref:`kisi pajak <localizations/italy/grids>` berikut: `VJ6`, `VJ7`, "
"`VJ8`, `VJ12`, `VJ13`, `VJ14`, `VJ15`, `VJ16`, `VJ17`"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/italy.rst:461
msgid "TD17 - buying services from abroad"
msgstr "TD17 - pembelian layanan dari luar negeri"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/italy.rst:463
msgid ""
"When buying **services** from **EU** and **non-EU** countries, the foreign "
"*seller* invoices a service with a **VAT-excluded** price, as it is not "
"taxable in Italy. The VAT is paid by the *buyer* in Italy."
msgstr ""
"Ketika membeli **layanan** dari negara-negara **UE** dan **non-UE**, "
"*penjual* asing menagih layanan dengan harga **tidak termasuk PPN**, karena "
"tidak kena pajak di Italia. PPN dibayar oleh *pembeli* di Italia."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/italy.rst:467
msgid ""
"Within the EU: the *buyer* integrates the invoice received with the **VAT "
"information** due in Italy (i.e., **vendor bill tax integration**)."
msgstr ""
"Dalam UE: *pembeli* mengintegrasikan faktur yang diterima dengan **informasi "
"VAT** yang harus dibayar di Italia (yaitu, **integrasi pajak tagihan "
"vendor**)."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/italy.rst:469
msgid ""
"Non-EU: the *buyer* sends themselves an invoice (i.e., **self-billing**)."
msgstr ""
"Non-UE: *pembeli* mengirim faktur kepada diri mereka sendiri (yaitu, **self-"
"billing**)."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/italy.rst:471
