msgstr "menerima kode QR dari JoFotara pada PDF faktur"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/jordan.rst:191
msgid ""
"Multiple invoices can be :ref:`sent at once <accounting/invoice/sending>` to "
"JoFotara."
msgstr ""
"Beberapa faktur dapat :ref:`dikirim sekaligus <accounting/invoice/sending>` "
