#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/luxembourg.rst:219
msgid "Completing the declaration"
msgstr "Melengkapi deklarasi"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/luxembourg.rst:221
msgid ""
"The annual declaration contains five sections labelled I to V, seven "
"appendices labelled A to G, and an additional Appendix to Operational "
"Expenditures."
msgstr ""
"Deklarasi tahunan berisi lima bagian yang diberi label I hingga V, tujuh "
"lampiran yang diberi label A hingga G, dan Lampiran tambahan untuk "
"Pengeluaran Operasional."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/luxembourg.rst:224
msgid ""
"Sections I, III, and Appendix A can be pre-populated automatically based on "
"the :ref:`account tag configuration <luxembourg/account-tag-configuration>`. "
"After configuring the account tags, :ref:`set the tax lock date <accounting/"
"tax-returns/lock-date>` to the end of the fiscal year. This will trigger the "
"pre-computation of those values."
msgstr ""
"Bagian I, III, dan Lampiran A dapat diisi secara otomatis berdasarkan "
":ref:`konfigurasi tag akun <luxembourg/account-tag-configuration>`. Setelah "
"mengonfigurasi tag akun, :ref:`atur tanggal kunci pajak <accounting/tax-"
"returns/lock-date>` ke akhir tahun fiskal. Ini akan memicu pra-komputasi "
"nilai-nilai tersebut."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/luxembourg.rst:None
msgid ""
"Odoo Accounting populates a Luxembourgish annual VAT declaration based on "
"account tags."
msgstr ""
"Odoo Akuntansi mengisi deklarasi PPN tahunan Luksemburg berdasarkan tag akun."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/luxembourg.rst:232
msgid ""
"Alternatively, the year's total VAT debit and credit can be manually "
"distributed among the various report lines in sections I and III. You can "
"use the :icon:`fa-pencil` (:guilabel:`Edit`) icon to manually enter the "
"value for each report line."
msgstr ""
"Atau, total debit dan kredit PPN tahun ini dapat didistribusikan secara "
"manual di antara berbagai baris laporan di bagian I dan III. Anda dapat "
"menggunakan ikon :icon:`fa-pencil` (:guilabel:`Edit`) untuk memasukkan nilai "
"secara manual untuk setiap baris laporan."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/luxembourg.rst:236
msgid "Sections II and IV are automatically computed."
msgstr "Bagian II dan IV dihitung secara otomatis."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/luxembourg.rst:238
msgid ""
"You then need to manually complete appendices B through G, as well as the "
"Appendix to Operational Expenditures, with any additional information to be "
"reported."
msgstr ""
"Anda kemudian perlu melengkapi lampiran B hingga G secara manual, serta "
"Lampiran Pengeluaran Operasional, dengan informasi tambahan yang perlu "
"dilaporkan."

