msgstr ""
"Untuk mendaftar, buka :menuselection:`Akuntansi --> Konfigurasi --> "
"Pengaturan`, dan di bagian :guilabel:`Malaysian Electronic Invoicing`, klik "
":guilabel:`Register`. Setelah registrasi selesai, **:ROB** dapat dihapus "
"dari :guilabel:`Tax ID`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/malaysia.rst:232
msgid ""
"Additionally, remember to log into `MyTax account <https://"
"mytax.hasil.gov.my/>`_ and set the :guilabel:`Type of Role` "
"as :guilabel:`Business Owner`."
msgstr ""
"Selain itu, ingat untuk masuk ke `akun MyTax <https://mytax.hasil.gov.my/>`_ "
"dan atur :guilabel:`Type of Role` sebagai :guilabel:`Business Owner`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/malaysia.rst:240
msgid "Access the contact's form and fill in the following fields:"
msgstr "Akses formulir kontak dan isi field berikut:"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/malaysia.rst:245
msgid ":guilabel:`Tax ID`"
msgstr ":guilabel:`Tax ID`"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/malaysia.rst:246
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Identification`: the :guilabel:`ID Type` and the "
"corresponding :guilabel:`Identification number` of the contact registered on "
"MyTax."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Identification`: :guilabel:`ID Type` dan "
":guilabel:`Identification number` kontak yang sesuai yang terdaftar di MyTax."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/malaysia.rst:250
msgid ""
"For specific use cases—such as transactions with buyers without a :abbr:`TIN "
"(tax identification number)` or foreign customers—refer to the list of "
"general TINs provided in the **Appendix** of the `e-Invoice Specific "
"Guideline <https://www.hasil.gov.my/en/e-invoice/reference-for-the-"
"implementation-of-e-invoice/guidelines/>`_."
msgstr ""
"Untuk kasus penggunaan tertentu—seperti transaksi dengan pembeli tanpa "
":abbr:`TIN (tax identification number)` atau pelanggan asing—lihat daftar "
"TIN umum yang disediakan dalam **Lampiran** dari `e-Invoice Specific "
"Guideline <https://www.hasil.gov.my/en/e-invoice/reference-for-the-"
"implementation-of-e-invoice/guidelines/>`_."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/malaysia.rst:260
msgid ""
"All products to be included in e-invoices require a Malaysian classification "
"code. To add it, access the :guilabel:`Product` form and in "
"the :guilabel:`General Information` tab, fill in the :guilabel:`Malaysian "
"classification code` field."
msgstr ""
"Semua produk yang akan disertakan dalam e-invoice memerlukan kode "
"klasifikasi Malaysia. Untuk menambahkannya, akses formulir "
":guilabel:`Product` dan di tab :guilabel:`General Information`, isi field "
":guilabel:`Malaysian classification code`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/malaysia.rst:265
msgid "Malaysian tax type"
msgstr "Jenis pajak Malaysia"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/malaysia.rst:267
msgid ""
"To configure a tax's :guilabel:`Malaysian Tax Type` field, go "
"to :menuselection:`Accounting --> Configuration --> Accounting --> Taxes` "
"and open the relevant tax in the :guilabel:`Taxes` list view."
msgstr ""
"Untuk mengonfigurasi field :guilabel:`Malaysian Tax Type` pajak, buka "
":menuselection:`Akuntansi --> Konfigurasi --> Akuntansi --> Pajak` dan buka "
"pajak yang relevan di tampilan daftar :guilabel:`Taxes`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/malaysia.rst:271
msgid ""
"When an invoice or bill includes a tax with the :guilabel:`Malaysian Tax "
"Type` set to **Tax Exempt**, a :guilabel:`Tax Exemption Reason` must be "
"specified in the :guilabel:`MyInvois` tab before the document is sent."
msgstr ""
"Ketika invoice atau tagihan mencakup pajak dengan :guilabel:`Malaysian Tax "
"Type` yang diatur ke **Tax Exempt**, :guilabel:`Tax Exemption Reason` harus "
"ditentukan di tab :guilabel:`MyInvois` sebelum dokumen dikirim."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/malaysia.rst:None
msgid "MyInvois tax exemption reason"
msgstr "Alasan pembebasan pajak MyInvois"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/malaysia.rst:286
msgid "Send invoices to MyInvois"
msgstr "Kirim invoice ke MyInvois"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/malaysia.rst:288
msgid ""
"Invoices can be sent to MyInvois once they have been confirmed. To do so, "
"click :guilabel:`Send to MyInvois`."
msgstr ""
"Invoice dapat dikirim ke MyInvois setelah dikonfirmasi. Untuk melakukannya, "
"klik :guilabel:`Send to MyInvois`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/malaysia.rst:292
msgid ""
"For invoices in foreign currencies, the exchange rate applied to the invoice "
"is sent to :guilabel:`MyInvois`."
msgstr ""
"Untuk invoice dalam mata uang asing, kurs yang diterapkan pada invoice "
"dikirim ke :guilabel:`MyInvois`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/malaysia.rst:296
msgid "Send bills to MyInvois"
msgstr "Kirim tagihan ke MyInvois"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/malaysia.rst:298
msgid ""
"Sending a bill to MyInvois is necessary when issuing an e-Invoice on behalf "
"of a supplier. Once a bill is confirmed, click :guilabel:`Send To MyInvois`."
msgstr ""
"Mengirim tagihan ke MyInvois diperlukan saat menerbitkan e-Invoice atas nama "
"pemasok. Setelah tagihan dikonfirmasi, klik :guilabel:`Send To MyInvois`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/malaysia.rst:302
msgid ""
"In `MyInvois <https://preprod.myinvois.hasil.gov.my/content>`_, these vendor "
"bills are categorized as :guilabel:`Self-billed Invoice`."
msgstr ""
"Di `MyInvois <https://preprod.myinvois.hasil.gov.my/content>`_, tagihan "
"vendor ini dikategorikan sebagai :guilabel:`Self-billed Invoice`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/malaysia.rst:305
msgid ""
"If a :guilabel:`Bill Reference` field is empty, Odoo's vendor bill number is "
"used as the MyInvois number. If a reference is entered in "
"the :guilabel:`Bill Reference` field, that reference is used instead."
msgstr ""
"Jika kolom :guilabel:`Bill Reference` kosong, nomor tagihan vendor Odoo "
"digunakan sebagai nomor MyInvois. Jika referensi dimasukkan di kolom "
":guilabel:`Bill Reference`, referensi tersebut digunakan sebagai gantinya."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/malaysia.rst:312
msgid "MyInvois status"
msgstr "Status MyInvois"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/malaysia.rst:314
msgid ""
"The current MyInvois status of an invoice or bill is shown in "
"the :guilabel:`MyInvois State` field within the :guilabel:`MyInvois` tab."
msgstr ""
"Status MyInvois saat ini dari faktur atau tagihan ditampilkan di kolom "
":guilabel:`MyInvois State` dalam tab :guilabel:`MyInvois`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/malaysia.rst:317
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Validation in Progress`: the validation is being processed by "
"MyInvois. A blue :guilabel:`Processing` banner is also displayed."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Validation in Progress`: validasi sedang diproses oleh MyInvois. "
"Banner :guilabel:`Processing` berwarna biru juga ditampilkan."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/malaysia.rst:319
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Valid`: it is validated by MyInvois. The :guilabel:`Submission "
"UID`, :guilabel:`MyInvois` and :guilabel:`Validation Time` are automatically "
"updated with information from MyInvois."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Valid`: divalidasi oleh MyInvois. :guilabel:`Submission UID`, "
":guilabel:`MyInvois` dan :guilabel:`Validation Time` secara otomatis "
"diperbarui dengan informasi dari MyInvois."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/malaysia.rst:324
msgid ""
"Odoo automatically checks and updates the status every hour. To update it "
"manually at any time, click :guilabel:`Update MyInvois Status`."
msgstr ""
"Odoo secara otomatis memeriksa dan memperbarui status setiap jam. Untuk "
"memperbaruinya secara manual kapan saja, klik :guilabel:`Perbarui Status "
"MyInvois`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/malaysia.rst:332
msgid ""
"Sent invoices can be canceled within 72 hours from :guilabel:`Validation "
"time`. In this case, open the invoice and click :guilabel:`Request Cancel`. "
"In the :guilabel:`Cancel document` window, include the "
"cancellation :guilabel:`Reason`, then click :guilabel:`Update Invoice`. "
"The :guilabel:`MyInvois State` is updated to :guilabel:`cancelled`."
msgstr ""
"Faktur yang dikirim dapat dibatalkan dalam 72 jam dari :guilabel:`Validation "
"time`. Dalam hal ini, buka faktur dan klik :guilabel:`Request Cancel`. Di "
"jendela :guilabel:`Cancel document`, sertakan :guilabel:`Reason` pembatalan, "
"lalu klik :guilabel:`Update Invoice`. :guilabel:`MyInvois State` diperbarui "
"menjadi :guilabel:`cancelled`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/malaysia.rst:338
msgid "Send credit notes to MyInvois"
msgstr "Kirim nota kredit ke MyInvois"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/malaysia.rst:340
msgid ""
"Before sending a credit note, the original invoice must be successfully "
"submitted to MyInvois. Otherwise, the credit note's :guilabel:`MyInvois "
"State` is updated to :guilabel:`Invalid`."
msgstr ""
"Sebelum mengirim nota kredit, faktur asli harus berhasil dikirimkan ke "
"MyInvois. Jika tidak, :guilabel:`MyInvois State` nota kredit diperbarui "
"menjadi :guilabel:`Invalid`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/malaysia.rst:343
msgid ""
"While Odoo uses a single :guilabel:`credit note` document, MyInvois "
"categorizes these into two types: :guilabel:`credit note` "
"and :guilabel:`refund note`, depending on how they are reconciled."
msgstr ""
"Meskipun Odoo menggunakan satu dokumen :guilabel:`credit note`, MyInvois "
"mengkategorikan ini menjadi dua jenis: :guilabel:`credit note` dan "
":guilabel:`refund note`, tergantung bagaimana mereka direkonsiliasi."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/malaysia.rst:346
msgid ""
":guilabel:`MyInvois Credit Note`: This is created when an Odoo credit note "
"is reconciled with the original invoice."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`MyInvois Credit Note`: Ini dibuat ketika nota kredit Odoo "
"direkonsiliasi dengan faktur asli."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/malaysia.rst:348
msgid ""
":guilabel:`MyInvois Refund Note`: This is created when an Odoo credit note "
"is reconciled with a full payment instead of the original invoice."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`MyInvois Refund Note`: Ini dibuat ketika nota kredit Odoo "
"direkonsiliasi dengan pembayaran penuh, bukan dengan faktur asli."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/malaysia.rst:352
msgid ""
"If a credit note is reconciled with only a partial payment before being "
"sent, it is still categorized as a :guilabel:`credit note` in MyInvois."
msgstr ""
"Jika nota kredit direkonsiliasi hanya dengan pembayaran parsial sebelum "
"dikirim, nota kredit tersebut tetap dikategorikan sebagai :guilabel:`credit "
"note` di MyInvois."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/malaysia.rst:358
msgid ""
"To issue both a credit note and a refund note for the same original invoice:"
msgstr ""
"Untuk menerbitkan nota kredit dan nota pengembalian dana untuk faktur asli "
"yang sama:"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/malaysia.rst:357
msgid "Create two separate credit notes in Odoo from the original invoice."
msgstr "Buat dua nota kredit terpisah di Odoo dari faktur asli."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/malaysia.rst:358
msgid ""
"For a MyInvois :guilabel:`Refund Note`: Register a payment before sending it."
msgstr ""
"Untuk :guilabel:`Refund Note` MyInvois: Daftarkan pembayaran sebelum "
"mengirimnya."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/malaysia.rst:359
msgid ""
"For a MyInvois :guilabel:`Credit Note`: Do not register a payment before "
"sending it."
msgstr ""
"Untuk :guilabel:`Credit Note` MyInvois: Jangan daftarkan pembayaran sebelum "
"mengirimnya."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/malaysia.rst:362
msgid ""
"The same logic applies to credit notes created from bills: if reconciled "
"with a full payment, the credit note becomes a :guilabel:`Self-billed Refund "
"Note`; otherwise, it becomes a :guilabel:`Self-billed Credit Note`."
msgstr ""
"Logika yang sama berlaku untuk nota kredit yang dibuat dari tagihan: jika "
"direkonsiliasi dengan pembayaran penuh, nota kredit menjadi :guilabel:`Self-"
"billed Refund Note`; jika tidak, menjadi :guilabel:`Self-billed Credit Note`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/malaysia.rst:367
msgid "Send debit notes to MyInvois"
msgstr "Kirim nota debit ke MyInvois"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/malaysia.rst:369
msgid ""
":ref:`Issue a debit note from an existing bill or invoice <accounting/"
"credit_notes/issue-debit-note>` and click :guilabel:`Send To MyInvois`. In "
"MyInvois, it appears then as a :guilabel:`Debit Note` if issued from an "
"invoice or a :guilabel:`Self-billed Debit Note` from a vendor bill."
msgstr ""
":ref:`Terbitkan nota debit dari tagihan atau faktur yang ada <accounting/"
"credit_notes/issue-debit-note>` dan klik :guilabel:`Kirim Ke MyInvois`. Di "
"MyInvois, dokumen tersebut kemudian muncul sebagai :guilabel:`Nota Debit` "
"jika diterbitkan dari faktur atau :guilabel:`Nota Debit Self-billed` dari "
"tagihan vendor."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/malaysia.rst:376
msgid "POS workflow"
msgstr "Alur kerja POS"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/malaysia.rst:378
msgid ""
"Two workflows are available to issue e-invoices in :doc:`Point of Sale "
"<../../sales/point_of_sale>`:"
msgstr ""
"Dua alur kerja tersedia untuk menerbitkan e-invoice di :doc:`Point of Sale "
"<../../sales/point_of_sale>`:"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/malaysia.rst:380
msgid ""
":ref:`Individual e-invoice <malaysia/myinvois/pos_workflow/submit>`: Issue "
"an e-invoice immediately for a specific order using the customer's details."
msgstr ""
":ref:`E-invoice individual <malaysia/myinvois/pos_workflow/submit>`: "
"Terbitkan e-invoice segera untuk pesanan tertentu menggunakan detail "
"pelanggan."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/malaysia.rst:382
msgid ""
":ref:`Consolidated e-invoice <malaysia/myinvois/pos_workflow/consolidated>`: "
"Create orders as usual, then aggregate them periodically into a single "
"consolidated e-invoice."
msgstr ""
":ref:`E-invoice terkonsolidasi <malaysia/myinvois/pos_workflow/consolidated>"
"`: Buat pesanan seperti biasa, kemudian gabungkan secara berkala menjadi "
"satu e-invoice terkonsolidasi."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/malaysia.rst:388
msgid "Individual e-invoice"
msgstr "E-invoice individual"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/malaysia.rst:390
msgid ""
"To issue an individual e-invoice and send it to MyInvois, :doc:`create an "
"invoice </applications/sales/point_of_sale/use/pos_invoices>`, and ensure "
"the selected customer has a valid :abbr:`TIN (tax identification number)` or "
"**Identification Number**."
msgstr ""
"Untuk menerbitkan e-invoice individual dan mengirimkannya ke MyInvois, "
":doc:`buat invoice </applications/sales/point_of_sale/use/pos_invoices>`, "
"dan pastikan pelanggan yang dipilih memiliki :abbr:`TIN (tax identification "
"number)` atau **Identification Number** yang valid."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/malaysia.rst:395
msgid ""
"If the QR code does not appear on the invoice, the MyInvois validation is "
"still in progress. Odoo automatically retrieves the status in the "
"background. Simply reopen the invoice later to retrieve the validated "
"version with the QR code."
msgstr ""
"Jika kode QR tidak muncul pada invoice, validasi MyInvois masih dalam "
"proses. Odoo secara otomatis mengambil status di latar belakang. Cukup buka "
"kembali invoice nanti untuk mengambil versi yang sudah divalidasi dengan "
"kode QR."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/malaysia.rst:402
msgid "Consolidated e-invoice"
msgstr "E-invoice terkonsolidasi"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/malaysia.rst:404
msgid ""
"Orders that are not e-invoiced individually can be aggregated into a "
"consolidated e-invoice."
msgstr ""
"Pesanan yang tidak difaktur elektronik secara individual dapat digabungkan "
"ke dalam e-faktur konsolidasi."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/malaysia.rst:406
msgid ""
"Navigate to :menuselection:`Point of Sale --> Orders --> Consolidated "
"Invoice`."
msgstr "Navigasi ke :menuselection:`POS --> Pesanan --> Faktur Konsolidasi`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/malaysia.rst:407
msgid ""
"Click :guilabel:`Consolidate Orders` and set the :guilabel:`Date From` "
"and :guilabel:`Date To`."
msgstr ""
"Klik :guilabel:`Konsolidasikan Pesanan` dan atur :guilabel:`Tanggal Dari` "
"dan :guilabel:`Tanggal Sampai`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/malaysia.rst:408
msgid "Click :guilabel:`Submit to MyInvois`."
msgstr "Klik :guilabel:`Kirim ke MyInvois`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/malaysia.rst:410
msgid ""
"Odoo automatically fetches all eligible POS orders within that timeframe "
"that have not been individually :ref:`invoiced <malaysia/myinvois/"
"pos_workflow/submit>` nor :ref:`refunded <malaysia/myinvois/pos_workflow/"
"refund>`."
msgstr ""
"Odoo secara otomatis mengambil semua pesanan POS yang memenuhi syarat dalam "
"jangka waktu tersebut yang belum :ref:`difakturkan <malaysia/myinvois/"
"pos_workflow/submit>` maupun :ref:`dikembalikan <malaysia/myinvois/"
"pos_workflow/refund>` secara individual."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/malaysia.rst:415
msgid ""
"Orders belonging to an :ref:`open POS register <pos/use/open-register>` are "
"not included in the consolidation. :ref:`Close the register <pos/use/"
"register-close>` to include them."
msgstr ""
"Pesanan yang termasuk dalam :ref:`register POS terbuka <pos/use/open-"
"register>` tidak disertakan dalam konsolidasi. :ref:`Tutup register <pos/use/"
"register-close>` untuk menyertakannya."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/malaysia.rst:418
msgid ""
"To submit the consolidation, click :guilabel:`Submit to MyInvois` on the "
"form view. For multiple records, click :guilabel:`Consolidated Invoices` to "
"go back to the list view, and select the relevant consolidated invoices. "
"Then, click :guilabel:`Submit to MyInvois`. Consolidated e-invoices are "
"issued to the pre-configured :guilabel:`General Public` contact."
msgstr ""
"Untuk mengirimkan konsolidasi, klik :guilabel:`Kirim ke MyInvois` pada "
"tampilan formulir. Untuk beberapa catatan, klik :guilabel:`Faktur "
"Konsolidasi` untuk kembali ke tampilan daftar, dan pilih faktur konsolidasi "
"yang relevan. Kemudian, klik :guilabel:`Kirim ke MyInvois`. E-faktur "
"konsolidasi diterbitkan kepada kontak :guilabel:`Masyarakat Umum` yang telah "
"dikonfigurasi sebelumnya."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/malaysia.rst:426
#: ../../content/applications/finance/payment_providers.rst:403
msgid "Refunds"
msgstr "Pengembalian"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/malaysia.rst:428
msgid "To refund a customer, :ref:`process a return <pos/use/refund>`."
msgstr ""
"Untuk mengembalikan dana pelanggan, :ref:`proses pengembalian <pos/use/"
"refund>`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/malaysia.rst:430
msgid ""
"Refunds for orders e-invoiced individually or via consolidation must be "
"issued as e-invoices (Refund Notes). To do so, click :guilabel:`Invoice` "
"before processing the refund."
msgstr ""
"Pengembalian dana untuk pesanan yang difaktur elektronik secara individual "
"atau melalui konsolidasi harus diterbitkan sebagai e-faktur (Nota Kredit). "
"Untuk melakukannya, klik :guilabel:`Faktur` sebelum memproses pengembalian "
"dana."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/malaysia.rst:434
msgid "Access invoices via QR code"
msgstr "Akses faktur melalui kode QR"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/malaysia.rst:436
msgid ""
"When a document is successfully submitted to MyInvois, a QR code is added to "
"its PDF version. Scanning this code links directly to the validated document "
"in MyInvois."
msgstr ""
"Ketika dokumen berhasil dikirim ke MyInvois, kode QR ditambahkan ke versi "
"PDF-nya. Memindai kode ini mengarah langsung ke dokumen yang telah "
"divalidasi di MyInvois."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/malaysia.rst:439
msgid "To download the PDF from an invoice or bill:"
msgstr "Untuk mengunduh PDF dari faktur atau tagihan:"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/malaysia.rst:441
msgid "Click the :icon:`fa-cog` :guilabel:`(gear)` icon"
msgstr "Klik ikon :icon:`fa-cog` :guilabel:`(roda gigi)`"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/malaysia.rst:442
msgid "Select :guilabel:`Download`"
msgstr "Pilih :guilabel:`Download`"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/malaysia.rst:443
msgid "Choose either :guilabel:`PDF` or :guilabel:`PDF without Payment`"
msgstr "Pilih :guilabel:`PDF` atau :guilabel:`PDF tanpa Pembayaran`"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/malaysia.rst:None
msgid "MyInvois QR code"
msgstr "Kode QR MyInvois"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/malaysia.rst:451
#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/singapore.rst:60
#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/united_kingdom.rst:248
msgid "Employment Hero payroll"
msgstr "Payroll Employment Hero"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/malaysia.rst:453
#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/singapore.rst:62
#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/united_kingdom.rst:250
msgid ""
"If your business is already up and running with :doc:`Employment Hero <../../"
"hr/payroll/payroll_localizations/employment_hero>`, you can use our "
"connector as an alternative payroll solution."
msgstr ""
"Jika bisnis Anda sudah berjalan dengan :doc:`Employment Hero <../../hr/"
"payroll/payroll_localizations/employment_hero>`, Anda dapat menggunakan "
"konektor kami sebagai solusi payroll alternatif."

