#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/mexico.rst:450
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Usage`, :guilabel:`Payment Policy` and :guilabel:`Payment Method` "
"can be previously set on a sale order and/or can be set on the contact for "
"every invoice."
msgstr ""

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/mexico.rst:453
msgid ""
"The payment policy is a selectable field on the invoice and can be manually "
"set to the required policy, however if no policy is selected, Odoo will "
"compute an automatic policy based on the following general rules:"
msgstr ""

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/mexico.rst:457
msgid ""
"The value will be set to |PUE| if the due date in which the payment is "
"expected is within the current month, in case the date is outside the "
"current month, the policy will be set to |PPD| instead."
msgstr ""

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/mexico.rst:462
msgid ""
"If the payment policy is not selected and |PPD| policy is expected, either "
"select an invoice :guilabel:`Due Date` on a different month than the current "
"one, or choose :guilabel:`Payment terms` that imply changing the due month "
"(i.e., :guilabel:`30 Days`, or :guilabel:`15 Days`, as long as they fall on "
"the next month)."
msgstr ""

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/mexico.rst:467
msgid ""
"After clicking :guilabel:`Confirm` in the customer invoice, click "
"the :guilabel:`Send` button to process the invoice with the government. Make "
"sure that the :guilabel:`CFDI` checkbox is marked."
msgstr ""
"Setelah mengklik :guilabel:`Konfirmasi` di faktur pelanggan, klik tombol "
":guilabel:`Kirim` untuk memproses faktur dengan pemerintah. Pastikan bahwa "
"kotak centang :guilabel:`CFDI` dicentang."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/mexico.rst:None
msgid "CFDI Checkbox"
msgstr ""

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/mexico.rst:473
msgid ""
"After receiving the signed document back from the government, "
"the :guilabel:`Fiscal Folio` field appears on the document, and the XML file "
"appears both in the |CFDI| tab and attached in the chatter."
msgstr ""

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/mexico.rst:477
msgid ""
"If an email address is configured on the customer contact record, marking "
"the :guilabel:`by Email` and :guilabel:`CFDI` checkboxes sends both the XML "
"and PDF files together."
msgstr ""

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/mexico.rst:480
msgid "To download the PDF file locally, click the :guilabel:`Print` button."
msgstr ""

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/mexico.rst:483
msgid ""
"When clicking :guilabel:`Update SAT`, the :guilabel:`SAT status` field on "
"the invoice will confirm if the XML file is **Validated** in the |SAT|."
msgstr ""

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/mexico.rst:486
msgid ""
"On a testing environment, the message :guilabel:`Not Found` will always come "
"up."
msgstr ""

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/mexico.rst:489
msgid ""
"If the partner does not contain the :guilabel:`Country` or :guilabel:`Zip` "
"the invoicing is assumed as a |CFDI| to public and the invoicing will be "
"addressed to the generic customer. If however, these fields are left empty "
"and the user unticks the :guilabel:`CFDI to public` checkbox, a pop-up will "
"appear blocking the operation."
msgstr ""
"Jika mitra tidak memiliki :guilabel:`Negara` atau :guilabel:`Kode Pos`, "
"penagihan diasumsikan sebagai |CFDI| untuk publik dan penagihan akan "
"ditujukan kepada pelanggan umum. Namun, jika kolom-kolom ini dibiarkan "
"kosong dan pengguna menghapus centang pada kotak :guilabel:`CFDI untuk "
"publik`, pop-up akan muncul memblokir operasi."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/mexico.rst:499
msgid ""
"While an invoice is a document type \"I\" (Ingreso), a credit note is a "
"document type \"E\" (Egreso)."
msgstr ""
"Sementara faktur adalah tipe dokumen \"I\" (Ingreso), nota kredit adalah "
"tipe dokumen \"E\" (Egreso)."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/mexico.rst:501
msgid ""
"An addition to the :doc:`standard flow for credit notes <../accounting/"
"customer_invoices/credit_notes>` is that, as a requirement of the |SAT|, "
"there has to be a relation between a credit note and an invoice through the "
"fiscal folio."
msgstr ""
"Sebagai tambahan untuk :doc:`alur standar untuk nota kredit <../accounting/"
"customer_invoices/credit_notes>` adalah bahwa, sebagai persyaratan dari "
"|SAT|, harus ada hubungan antara nota kredit dan faktur melalui folio fiskal."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/mexico.rst:505
msgid ""
"Because of this requirement, the field :guilabel:`CFDI Origin` adds this "
"relation with a `01|`, followed by the fiscal folio of the "
"original :abbr:`UUID (universally unique identifier)`."
msgstr ""
"Karena persyaratan ini, kolom :guilabel:`CFDI Origin` menambahkan hubungan "
"ini dengan `01|`, diikuti oleh folio fiskal dari :abbr:`UUID (universally "
"unique identifier)` asli."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/mexico.rst:509
msgid ""
"For the :guilabel:`CFDI Origin` field to be automatically added, use "
"the :guilabel:`Add Credit Note` button from the invoice, instead of creating "
"it manually."
msgstr ""
"Agar kolom :guilabel:`Asal CFDI` ditambahkan secara otomatis, gunakan tombol "
":guilabel:`Tambahkan Nota Kredit` dari faktur, bukan membuatnya secara "
"manual."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/mexico.rst:512
msgid ""
"Generally credit notes reverse the main sales account defined in the "
"journal, but it is also possible to globally assign an account to all credit "
"notes. To do so, go to :menuselection:`Accounting --> Configuration --> "
"Settings` and set the :guilabel:`Credit notes` account under "
"the :guilabel:`Default Accounts` section."
msgstr ""
"Umumnya nota kredit membalik akun penjualan utama yang ditentukan dalam "
"jurnal, tetapi juga dimungkinkan untuk menetapkan akun secara global ke "
"semua nota kredit. Untuk melakukannya, buka :menuselection:`Accounting --> "
"Configuration --> Settings` dan atur akun :guilabel:`Credit notes` di bawah "
"bagian :guilabel:`Default Accounts`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/mexico.rst:518
msgid ""
"On the default configuration, the credit notes account is set "
"as :guilabel:`402.01.01 Returns, discounts or bonuses over sales and/or "
"services at the general rate`."
msgstr ""
"Pada konfigurasi default, akun nota kredit diatur sebagai "
":guilabel:`402.01.01 Returns, discounts or bonuses over sales and/or "
"services at the general rate`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/mexico.rst:526
msgid ""
"Vendor bills have to have a fiscal folio for reports and payments to work "
"correctly, if the vendor bill was created by the purchase app or added "
"manually, just add the XML file of the invoice on the chatter **As a log "
"note** and the fiscal folio will be updated accordingly, keep in mind that "
"the bill **Must be in draft state** for the update to happen."
msgstr ""
"Tagihan vendor harus memiliki folio fiskal agar laporan dan pembayaran "
"berfungsi dengan benar. Jika tagihan vendor dibuat oleh aplikasi pembelian "
"atau ditambahkan secara manual, cukup tambahkan file XML faktur pada chatter "
"**Sebagai catatan log** dan folio fiskal akan diperbarui dengan tepat. Perlu "
"diingat bahwa tagihan **Harus dalam status draf** agar pembaruan terjadi."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/mexico.rst:532
msgid ""
"When clicking :guilabel:`Update SAT`, the :guilabel:`SAT status` field on "
"the invoice will confirm if the XML file is **Validated** by the |SAT|, this "
"is also true for vendor bills."
msgstr ""
"Saat mengklik :guilabel:`Update SAT`, kolom :guilabel:`SAT status` pada "
"faktur akan mengonfirmasi apakah file XML **Validated** oleh |SAT|, ini juga "
"berlaku untuk tagihan vendor."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/mexico.rst:536
msgid ":doc:`../accounting/vendor_bills`"
msgstr ":doc:`../accounting/vendor_bills`"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/mexico.rst:543
msgid ""
"The module :guilabel:`EDI for Mexico (Advanced Features)` "
"(`l10n_mx_edi_extended`) must be installed on the database to complete "
"the :guilabel:`Address Issued` field on the sales journal. This ensures that "
"all invoices from that sales journal, as well as :ref:`global invoices <l10n/"
"mx/global-invoice>`, use the correct zipcode when generating the CFDI."
msgstr ""
"Modul :guilabel:`EDI for Mexico (Advanced Features)` "
"(`l10n_mx_edi_extended`) harus diinstal pada database untuk melengkapi field "
":guilabel:`Address Issued` pada jurnal penjualan. Hal ini memastikan bahwa "
"semua faktur dari jurnal penjualan tersebut, serta :ref:`faktur global <l10n/"
"mx/global-invoice>`, menggunakan kode pos yang benar saat menghasilkan CFDI."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/mexico.rst:548
msgid ""
"To invoice within a company under different time zones with the same user, a "
"system parameter must be created to ensure the correct time zone is applied "
"when invoicing, as the user's time zone is used by default."
msgstr ""
"Untuk membuat faktur dalam sebuah perusahaan di zona waktu yang berbeda "
"dengan user yang sama, parameter sistem harus dibuat untuk memastikan zona "
"waktu yang benar diterapkan saat membuat faktur, karena zona waktu user "
"digunakan secara default."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/mexico.rst:552
msgid ""
"To do so, enable :doc:`developer mode <../../general/developer_mode>` and go "
"to :menuselection:`Settings --> Technical --> System Parameters`. "
"Click :guilabel:`New` to create a new parameter with the key "
"`l10n_mx_edi_tz_XX` where `XX` is the ID of the journal, and set the desired "
"time zone as the value, for example, “America/Tijuana”."
msgstr ""
"Untuk melakukannya, aktifkan :doc:`mode pengembang <../../general/"
"developer_mode>` dan buka :menuselection:`Settings --> Technical --> System "
"Parameters`. Klik :guilabel:`New` untuk membuat parameter baru dengan kunci "
"`l10n_mx_edi_tz_XX` di mana `XX` adalah ID jurnal, dan atur zona waktu yang "
"diinginkan sebagai nilai, misalnya, \"America/Tijuana\"."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/mexico.rst:565
msgid "Payment policy"
msgstr "Kebijakan pembayaran"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/mexico.rst:567
msgid ""
"One addition of the Mexican localization is the :guilabel:`Payment Policy` "
"field. `According to the SAT documentation <https://www.sat.gob.mx/consultas/"
"92764/comprobante-de-recepcion-de-pagos>`_, there are two types of payments:"
msgstr ""
"Salah satu penambahan dari lokalisasi Meksiko adalah kolom "
":guilabel:`Kebijakan Pembayaran`. `Menurut dokumentasi SAT<https://"
"www.sat.gob.mx/consultas/92764/comprobante-de-recepcion-de-pagos>`_, ada dua "
"jenis pembayaran:"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/mexico.rst:571
msgid ""
":guilabel:`PUE` (Pago en una Sola Exhibición/Payment in a Single Exhibition)"
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`PUE` (Pago en una Sola Exhibición/Pembayaran dalam Satu Kali)"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/mexico.rst:572
msgid ""
":guilabel:`PPD` (Pago en Parcialidades o Diferido/Payment in Installements "
"or Deferred)"
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`PPD` (Pago en Parcialidades o Diferido/Pembayaran Dicicil atau "
"Ditangguhkan)"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/mexico.rst:575
msgid ""
"Payment Complements are only generated if the policy of the invoice is set "
"to |PPD|, please note that it is a requirement to set the :guilabel:`Payment "
"Method` to something different than **99 - Por definir**."
msgstr ""
"Komplemen Pembayaran hanya dibuat jika kebijakan faktur diatur ke |PPD|. "
"Perlu diperhatikan bahwa merupakan persyaratan untuk mengatur "
":guilabel:`Metode Pembayaran` menjadi sesuatu yang berbeda dari **99 - Por "
"definir**."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/mexico.rst:None
msgid "Example of an invoice with the PUE requirements."
msgstr "Contoh faktur dengan persyaratan PUE."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/mexico.rst:582
msgid ""
"If the invoice has a due date outside the current month, it will default to |"
"PPD|."
msgstr ""
"Jika faktur memiliki tanggal jatuh tempo di luar bulan berjalan, secara "
"default akan menjadi |PPD|."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/mexico.rst:None
msgid "Example of an invoice with the PPD requirements."
msgstr "Contoh faktur dengan persyaratan PPD."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/mexico.rst:590
msgid "Payment flow"
msgstr "Alur pembayaran"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/mexico.rst:592
msgid ""
"In both cases, the payment process in Odoo :doc:`is the same <../accounting/"
"payments>`, the main difference being payments related to |PPD| invoices, by "
"law, need to be sent to the government as a document type \"P\" (Pago)."
msgstr ""
"Dalam kedua kasus, proses pembayaran di Odoo :doc:`adalah sama <../"
"accounting/payments>`, perbedaan utamanya adalah pembayaran terkait faktur "
"|PPD|, menurut hukum, perlu dikirim ke pemerintah sebagai tipe dokumen \"P\" "
"(Pago)."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/mexico.rst:596
msgid ""
"If a payment is related to a |PUE| invoice, it can be registered through the "
"payment popup, and be associated with the corresponding invoice. To do so, "
"navigate to :menuselection:`Accounting --> Customers --> Invoices`, and "
"select an invoice. Then, click the :guilabel:`Pay` button to open the "
"payment popup, set the :guilabel:`Payment Way` and any other fields, and "
"click :guilabel:`Create Payment`."
msgstr ""
"Jika pembayaran terkait dengan faktur |PUE|, dapat didaftarkan melalui popup "
"pembayaran, dan dikaitkan dengan faktur yang sesuai. Untuk melakukannya, "
"navigasi ke :menuselection:`Akuntansi --> Pelanggan --> Faktur`, dan pilih "
"faktur. Kemudian, klik tombol :guilabel:`Bayar` untuk membuka popup "
"pembayaran, atur :guilabel:`Cara Pembayaran` dan kolom lainnya, lalu klik "
":guilabel:`Buat Pembayaran`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/mexico.rst:603
msgid ":doc:`../accounting/payments`"
msgstr ":doc:`../accounting/payments`"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/mexico.rst:604
msgid ":doc:`../accounting/bank/reconciliation`"
msgstr ":doc:`../accounting/bank/reconciliation`"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/mexico.rst:606
msgid ""
"While this process is the same for PPD invoices, the addition of creating "
"an :doc:`electronic document <../accounting/customer_invoices/"
"electronic_invoicing>` means some additional requirements are needed to "
"correctly send the document to the |SAT|."
msgstr ""
"Meskipun proses ini sama untuk faktur PPD, penambahan pembuatan "
":doc:`dokumen elektronik <../accounting/customer_invoices/"
"electronic_invoicing>` berarti beberapa persyaratan tambahan diperlukan "
"untuk mengirim dokumen dengan benar ke |SAT|."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/mexico.rst:610
msgid ""
"From a legal perspective, PPD invoices **must** include the "
"specific :guilabel:`Payment Way` that the payment was received. Because of "
"this, the :guilabel:`Payment Way` field **cannot** be set as :guilabel:`To "
"Define`, thus the field will become invisible when selecting it."
msgstr ""
"Dari perspektif hukum, faktur PPD **harus** mencantumkan :guilabel:`Cara "
"Pembayaran` spesifik yang digunakan untuk menerima pembayaran. Karena itu, "
"kolom :guilabel:`Cara Pembayaran` **tidak dapat** diatur sebagai "
":guilabel:`Untuk Didefinisikan`, sehingga kolom akan menjadi tidak terlihat "
"saat memilihnya."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/mexico.rst:615
msgid ""
"If a bank account number is required, add it in the :guilabel:`Accounting` "
"tab of a customer's contact record."
msgstr ""
"Jika nomor rekening bank diperlukan, tambahkan di tab :guilabel:`Akuntansi` "
"pada catatan kontak pelanggan."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/mexico.rst:617
msgid ""
"The exact configurations are in the `Anexo 20 of the SAT <http://"
"omawww.sat.gob.mx/tramitesyservicios/Paginas/anexo_20.htm>`_. Usually, "
"the :guilabel:`Bank Account` needs to be 10 or 18 digits for transfers, 16 "
"for credit or debit cards."
msgstr ""
"Konfigurasi yang tepat ada di `Anexo 20 of the SAT <http://omawww.sat.gob.mx/"
"tramitesyservicios/Paginas/anexo_20.htm>`_. Biasanya, :guilabel:`Akun Bank` "
"harus terdiri dari 10 atau 18 digit untuk transfer, 16 untuk kartu kredit "
"atau debit."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/mexico.rst:622
msgid ""
"If a fully-reconciled payment is related to an invoice with "
"a :guilabel:`Fiscal Folio`, the :guilabel:`Update Payments` appears. Click "
"the :guilabel:`Update Payments` button to send the **payment complement** "
"XML file to the government automatically and display it in the |CFDI| tab in "
"both the invoice and the payment."
msgstr ""
"Jika pembayaran yang telah direkonsiliasi penuh terkait dengan faktur yang "
"memiliki :guilabel:`Fiscal Folio`, maka :guilabel:`Update Payments` akan "
"muncul. Klik tombol :guilabel:`Update Payments` untuk mengirim file XML "
"**komplemen pembayaran** ke pemerintah secara otomatis dan menampilkannya di "
"tab |CFDI| baik di faktur maupun pembayaran."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/mexico.rst:628
msgid ""
"While it is a bad fiscal practice, the |PUE| payments can also be sent to "
"the government, however it is required to click :guilabel:`Force CFDI` in "
"the :guilabel:`CFDI` tab for this."
msgstr ""
"Meskipun ini merupakan praktik fiskal yang buruk, pembayaran |PUE| juga "
"dapat dikirim ke pemerintah, namun diperlukan untuk mengklik "
":guilabel:`Force CFDI` di tab :guilabel:`CFDI` untuk hal ini."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/mexico.rst:631
msgid ""
"Similar to an invoice or credit note, the PDF and XML can be sent to the "
"final customer. To do so, click the :icon:`fa-cog` :guilabel:`(gear)` icon "
"to open the actions drop-down menu and select :guilabel:`Send receipt by "
"email` from the payment view."
msgstr ""
"Mirip dengan faktur atau nota kredit, PDF dan XML dapat dikirim ke pelanggan "
"akhir. Untuk melakukannya, klik ikon :icon:`fa-cog` :guilabel:`(roda gigi)` "
"untuk membuka menu drop-down tindakan dan pilih :guilabel:`Send receipt by "
"email` dari tampilan pembayaran."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/mexico.rst:635
msgid ""
"Regardless of whether the payment was created with or without "
"reconciliation, it is possible to download the payment PDF from "
"the :guilabel:`CFDI` tab on the invoice by clicking the :guilabel:`print` "
"button."
msgstr ""
"Terlepas dari apakah pembayaran dibuat dengan atau tanpa rekonsiliasi, "
"dimungkinkan untuk mengunduh PDF pembayaran dari tab :guilabel:`CFDI` pada "
"faktur dengan mengklik tombol :guilabel:`cetak`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/mexico.rst:None
msgid "Example of the print button on the CFDI tab."
msgstr "Contoh tombol cetak pada tab CFDI."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/mexico.rst:645
msgid "Invoice cancellations"
msgstr "Pembatalan faktur"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/mexico.rst:647
msgid ""
"It is possible to cancel the EDI documents sent to the |SAT|. According to "
"the `Reforma Fiscal 2022 <https://www.sat.gob.mx/consultas/91447/nuevo-"
"esquema-de-cancelacion>`_, since January 1st, 2022, there are two "
"requirements for this:"
msgstr ""
"Dimungkinkan untuk membatalkan dokumen EDI yang dikirim ke |SAT|. Menurut "
"`Reforma Fiscal 2022 <https://www.sat.gob.mx/consultas/91447/nuevo-esquema-"
"de-cancelacion>`_, sejak 1 Januari 2022, ada dua persyaratan untuk hal ini:"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/mexico.rst:651
msgid "All cancellation requests require a *cancellation reason*."
msgstr "Semua permintaan pembatalan memerlukan *alasan pembatalan*."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/mexico.rst:652
msgid ""
"After 24 hours from the invoice creation, the client must be asked to "
"approve the cancellation. If there is no response within 72 hours, the "
"cancellation is processed automatically."
msgstr ""
"Setelah 24 jam dari pembuatan faktur, klien harus diminta untuk menyetujui "
"pembatalan. Jika tidak ada respons dalam 72 jam, pembatalan diproses secara "
"otomatis."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/mexico.rst:655
msgid ""
"Invoice cancellations are updated automatically on Odoo but can take some "
"time, to check the status of the cancellation just press "
"the :guilabel:`Update SAT` button."
msgstr ""
"Pembatalan faktur diperbarui secara otomatis di Odoo tetapi dapat memakan "
"waktu, untuk memeriksa status pembatalan cukup tekan tombol "
":guilabel:`Update SAT`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/mexico.rst:658
msgid "Invoice cancellations can be made for one of the following reasons:"
msgstr "Pembatalan faktur dapat dilakukan karena salah satu alasan berikut:"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/mexico.rst:660
msgid "01 - Invoice issued with errors (with related document)"
msgstr "01 - Faktur diterbitkan dengan kesalahan (dengan dokumen terkait)"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/mexico.rst:661
msgid "02 - Invoice issued with errors (no replacement)"
msgstr "02 - Faktur diterbitkan dengan kesalahan (tanpa penggantian)"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/mexico.rst:662
msgid "03 - The operation was not carried out"
msgstr "03 - Operasi tidak dilakukan"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/mexico.rst:663
msgid "04 - Nominative operation related to the global invoice"
msgstr "04 - Operasi nominatif terkait dengan faktur global"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/mexico.rst:665
msgid ""
"To initiate a cancellation, go to :menuselection:`Accounting --> Customers --"
"> Invoices`, select the posted invoice to cancel, and "
"click :guilabel:`Request Cancel`. Then, refer to the :ref:`l10n/mx/01-"
"invoice-cancellation` or :ref:`l10n/mx/02-03-04-invoice-cancellation` "
"sections, depending on the cancellation reason."
msgstr ""
"Untuk memulai pembatalan, buka :menuselection:`Akuntansi --> Pelanggan --> "
"Faktur`, pilih faktur yang diposting untuk dibatalkan, dan klik "
":guilabel:`Request Cancel`. Kemudian, lihat bagian :ref:`l10n/mx/01-invoice-"
"cancellation` atau :ref:`l10n/mx/02-03-04-invoice-cancellation`, tergantung "
"pada alasan pembatalan."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/mexico.rst:671
msgid ""
"Alternatively, request a cancellation from the :guilabel:`CFDI` tab by "
"clicking :guilabel:`Cancel` on the line item."
msgstr ""
"Alternatifnya, minta pembatalan dari tab :guilabel:`CFDI` dengan mengklik "
":guilabel:`Cancel` pada item baris."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/mexico.rst:675
msgid ""
"If a cancellation is requested on a locked period, the CFDI will be "
"cancelled but not the accounting entry."
msgstr ""
"Jika pembatalan diminta pada periode yang terkunci, CFDI akan dibatalkan "
"tetapi bukan entri akuntansinya."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/mexico.rst:677
msgid ""
"If the client rejects the cancellation, the invoice cancellation line item "
"is removed from the :guilabel:`CFDI` tab."
msgstr ""
"Jika klien menolak pembatalan, item baris pembatalan faktur dihapus dari tab "
":guilabel:`CFDI`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/mexico.rst:683
msgid "Cancellation reason 01"
msgstr "Alasan pembatalan 01"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/mexico.rst:685
msgid ""
"In the :guilabel:`Request CFDI Cancellation` pop-up window, "
"select :guilabel:`01 - Invoice issued with errors (with related document)` "
"from the :guilabel:`Reason` field and click :guilabel:`Create Replacement "
"Invoice` to create a new draft invoice. This new draft invoice replaces the "
"previous invoice, along with the related |CFDI|."
msgstr ""
"Di jendela pop-up :guilabel:`Request CFDI Cancellation`, pilih "
":guilabel:`01 - Invoice issued with errors (with related document)` dari "
"kolom :guilabel:`Reason` dan klik :guilabel:`Create Replacement Invoice` "
"untuk membuat faktur draft baru. Faktur draft baru ini menggantikan faktur "
"sebelumnya, beserta |CFDI| yang terkait."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/mexico.rst:689
msgid ":guilabel:`Confirm` the draft and :guilabel:`Send` the invoice."
msgstr ":guilabel:`Konfirmasi` draft dan :guilabel:`Kirim` faktur."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/mexico.rst:690
msgid ""
"Return to the initial invoice (i.e., the invoice from which you first "
"requested the cancellation). Notice the :guilabel:`Substituted By` field "
"appears with a reference to the new replacement invoice."
msgstr ""
"Kembali ke faktur awal (yaitu, faktur yang dari sana Anda pertama kali "
"meminta pembatalan). Perhatikan bahwa kolom :guilabel:`Substituted By` "
"muncul dengan referensi ke faktur pengganti yang baru."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/mexico.rst:693
msgid ""
"Click :guilabel:`Request Cancel`. In the :guilabel:`Request CFDI "
"Cancellation` pop-up window, the :guilabel:`01 - Invoice issued with errors "
"(with related document)` option is automatically selected in "
"the :guilabel:`Reason` field."
msgstr ""
"Klik :guilabel:`Request Cancel`. Di jendela pop-up :guilabel:`Request CFDI "
"Cancellation`, opsi :guilabel:`01 - Invoice issued with errors (with related "
"document)` secara otomatis dipilih di kolom :guilabel:`Reason`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/mexico.rst:696
msgid "Click :guilabel:`Confirm`."
msgstr "Klik :guilabel:`Confirm`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/mexico.rst:698
msgid ""
"The invoice cancellation is then generated with a reason line item in "
"the :guilabel:`CFDI` tab."
msgstr ""
"Pembatalan faktur kemudian dibuat dengan item baris alasan di tab "
":guilabel:`CFDI`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/mexico.rst:None
msgid "Canceled invoice line item in the CFDI tab."
msgstr "Item baris faktur yang dibatalkan di tab CFDI."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/mexico.rst:704
msgid ""
"When using the :guilabel:`01 - Invoice issued with errors (with related "
"document)` cancellation reason, the `04|` prefix appears in "
"the :guilabel:`Fiscal Folio` field. This is an internal prefix used by Odoo "
"to complete the cancellation and **does not** mean that the cancellation "
"reason was :guilabel:`04 - Nominative operation related to the global "
"invoice`."
msgstr ""
"Saat menggunakan alasan pembatalan :guilabel:`01 - Invoice issued with "
"errors (with related document)`, awalan `04|` muncul di kolom "
":guilabel:`Fiscal Folio`. Ini adalah awalan internal yang digunakan oleh "
"Odoo untuk menyelesaikan pembatalan dan **tidak** berarti bahwa alasan "
"pembatalan adalah :guilabel:`04 - Nominative operation related to the global "
"invoice`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/mexico.rst:712
msgid "Cancellation reasons 02, 03, and 04"
msgstr "Alasan pembatalan 02, 03, dan 04"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/mexico.rst:714
msgid ""
"In the :guilabel:`Request CFDI Cancellation` pop-up window, select the "
"desired cancellation :guilabel:`Reason` and :guilabel:`Confirm` the "
"cancellation."
msgstr ""
"Di jendela pop-up :guilabel:`Request CFDI Cancellation`, pilih "
":guilabel:`Reason` pembatalan yang diinginkan dan :guilabel:`Confirm` "
"pembatalan tersebut."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/mexico.rst:717
msgid ""
"Upon doing so, the invoice cancellation is generated with a reason line item "
"in the :guilabel:`CFDI` tab."
msgstr ""
"Setelah melakukan hal tersebut, pembatalan faktur dibuat dengan item baris "
"alasan di tab :guilabel:`CFDI`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/mexico.rst:721
msgid ""
"If the :guilabel:`SAT Status` goes back to **Validated** it could be due to "
"one of these three reasons:"
msgstr ""
"Jika :guilabel:`SAT Status` kembali ke **Validated** hal ini dapat "
"disebabkan oleh salah satu dari tiga alasan berikut:"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/mexico.rst:724
msgid ""
"The invoice is labeled as *No Cancelable* in the `SAT Website <https://"
"www.sat.gob.mx/home>`_. due to the fact that it has a valid related "
"document: Either another invoice linked with the :guilabel:`CFDI Origin` "
"field or a Payment Complement. If so, you need to cancel any other related "
"document first."
msgstr ""
"Faktur diberi label sebagai *No Cancelable* di `SAT Website <https://"
"www.sat.gob.mx/home>`_ karena fakta bahwa faktur memiliki dokumen terkait "
"yang valid: Baik faktur lain yang ditautkan dengan kolom :guilabel:`CFDI "
"Origin` atau Komplemen Pembayaran. Jika demikian, Anda perlu membatalkan "
"dokumen terkait lainnya terlebih dahulu."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/mexico.rst:728
msgid ""
"The cancellation request is still being processed by the |SAT|. If so, wait "
"a few minutes and try again."
msgstr ""
"Permintaan pembatalan masih diproses oleh |SAT|. Jika demikian, tunggu "
"beberapa menit dan coba lagi."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/mexico.rst:730
msgid ""
"The final customer needs to reject or accept the cancellation request in "
"their `Buzón Tributario <http://omawww.sat.gob.mx/BuzonTributario/Paginas/"
"servicios_disponibles.html>`_. This can take up to 72 hours and, in case "
"that the cancellation requests gets rejected, you will need to repeat the "
"process again."
msgstr ""
"Pelanggan akhir perlu menolak atau menerima permintaan pembatalan di `Buzón "
"Tributario <http://omawww.sat.gob.mx/BuzonTributario/Paginas/"
"servicios_disponibles.html>`_ mereka. Ini dapat memakan waktu hingga 72 jam "
"dan, jika permintaan pembatalan ditolak, Anda perlu mengulangi proses "
"tersebut lagi."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/mexico.rst:736
msgid ""
"`Tool to validate Mexican Electronic Documents (CFDI) status <https://"
"verificacfdi.facturaelectronica.sat.gob.mx/>`_"
msgstr ""
"`Tool to validate Mexican Electronic Documents (CFDI) status <https://"
"verificacfdi.facturaelectronica.sat.gob.mx/>`_"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/mexico.rst:739
msgid ""
"For the cancellation reasons **02**, **03** and **04**, "
"the :guilabel:`Create Replacement Invoice` button is replaced by "
"a :guilabel:`Confirm` button that requests the cancellation immediately."
msgstr ""
"Untuk alasan pembatalan **02**, **03** dan **04**, tombol :guilabel:`Create "
"Replacement Invoice` diganti dengan tombol :guilabel:`Confirm` yang meminta "
"pembatalan segera."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/mexico.rst:742
msgid ""
"Both the current :guilabel:`State` and :guilabel:`Cancellation Reason` can "
"be found in the :guilabel:`CFDI` tab."
msgstr ""
"Baik :guilabel:`State` saat ini maupun :guilabel:`Cancellation Reason` dapat "
"ditemukan di tab :guilabel:`CFDI`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/mexico.rst:None
msgid "Old invoice with CFDI Origin."
msgstr "Faktur lama dengan CFDI Origin."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/mexico.rst:751
msgid "Payment cancellations"
msgstr "Pembatalan pembayaran"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/mexico.rst:753
msgid ""
"To cancel :ref:`payment complements <l10n/mx/payment-flow>`, go to "
"the :guilabel:`CFDI` tab of the related invoice and click :guilabel:`Cancel` "
"on the line of the payment complement."
msgstr ""
"Untuk membatalkan :ref:`payment complements <l10n/mx/payment-flow>`, buka "
"tab :guilabel:`CFDI` dari faktur terkait dan klik :guilabel:`Cancel` pada "
"baris payment complement."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/mexico.rst:756
msgid ""
"Like with invoices, go to the payment and click :guilabel:`Update SAT` in "
"order to change the :guilabel:`SAT Status` and :guilabel:`Status` "
"to :guilabel:`Cancelled`."
msgstr ""
"Seperti halnya pada faktur, buka pembayaran dan klik :guilabel:`Update SAT` "
"untuk mengubah :guilabel:`SAT Status` dan :guilabel:`Status` menjadi "
":guilabel:`Cancelled`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/mexico.rst:760
msgid ""
"Just like invoices, when creating a new payment complement, it is possible "
"to add the relation of the original document, by adding a `04|` plus the "
"fiscal folio in the :guilabel:`CFDI Origin` field."
msgstr ""
"Sama seperti faktur, saat membuat pelengkap pembayaran baru, dimungkinkan "
"untuk menambahkan relasi dokumen asli dengan menambahkan `04|` ditambah "
"folio fiskal di bidang :guilabel:`CFDI Origin`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/mexico.rst:764
msgid ""
"This action cancels the invoice and marks the :guilabel:`Reason` "
"as :guilabel:`01 - Invoice issued with errors (with related document)`."
msgstr ""
"Tindakan ini membatalkan faktur dan menandai :guilabel:`Reason` sebagai "
":guilabel:`01 - Invoice issued with errors (with related document)`."

