#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/mexico.rst:813
msgid ""
"The :guilabel:`Main Currency` in Mexico is MXN. While this is mandatory for "
"all Mexican companies, it is possible to send and receive invoices (and "
"payments) in different currencies. To enable the use of :doc:`multicurrency "
"<../accounting/get_started/multi_currency>`, navigate to "
"the :menuselection:`Accounting --> Configuration --> Currencies`, and "
"set :guilabel:`[MX] Bank of Mexico` as the :guilabel:`Service` in "
"the :guilabel:`Automatic Currency Rates` section. Then, set "
"the :guilabel:`Interval` field to the frequency you wish to update the "
"exchange rates."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Main Currency` di Meksiko adalah MXN. Meskipun ini wajib untuk "
"semua perusahaan Meksiko, dimungkinkan untuk mengirim dan menerima faktur "
"(dan pembayaran) dalam mata uang yang berbeda. Untuk mengaktifkan penggunaan "
":doc:`multicurrency <../accounting/get_started/multi_currency>`, navigasikan "
"ke :menuselection:`Accounting --> Configuration --> Currencies`, dan atur "
":guilabel:`[MX] Bank of Mexico` sebagai :guilabel:`Service` di bagian "
":guilabel:`Automatic Currency Rates`. Kemudian, atur bidang "
":guilabel:`Interval` ke frekuensi yang Anda inginkan untuk memperbarui nilai "
"tukar."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/mexico.rst:820
msgid ""
"This way, the XML file of the document will have the correct exchange rate, "
"and the total amount, in both the foreign currency and in MXN."
msgstr ""
"Dengan cara ini, file XML dari dokumen akan memiliki kurs yang benar, dan "
"jumlah total, baik dalam mata uang asing maupun dalam MXN."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/mexico.rst:823
msgid ""
"It is highly recommended to use separate :doc:`bank accounts for each "
"currency <../accounting/bank/foreign_currency>`."
msgstr ""
"Sangat disarankan untuk menggunakan :doc:`rekening bank terpisah untuk "
"setiap mata uang <../accounting/bank/foreign_currency>`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/mexico.rst:827
msgid ""
"The only currencies that automatically update their exchange rate daily are: "
"USD, EUR, GBP, JPY and CNY."
msgstr ""
"Satu-satunya mata uang yang secara otomatis memperbarui kurs mereka setiap "
"hari adalah: USD, EUR, GBP, JPY dan CNY."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/mexico.rst:835
msgid ""
"By law, electronic documents sent to the government cannot have negative "
"lines, as this can trigger errors. Therefore, when using :doc:`Gift Cards "
"<../../sales/sales/products_prices/ewallets_giftcards>` or :doc:`Loyalty "
"Programs <../../sales/sales/products_prices/loyalty_discount>`, the "
"subsequent negative lines will be translated in the XML as if they were "
"regular :doc:`Discounts <../../sales/sales/products_prices/prices/pricing/>`."
msgstr ""
"Menurut hukum, dokumen elektronik yang dikirim ke pemerintah tidak boleh "
"memiliki baris negatif, karena ini dapat memicu kesalahan. Oleh karena itu, "
"saat menggunakan :doc:`Kartu Hadiah <../../sales/sales/products_prices/"
"ewallets_giftcards>` atau :doc:`Program Loyalitas <../../sales/sales/"
"products_prices/loyalty_discount>`, baris negatif berikutnya akan "
"diterjemahkan dalam XML seolah-olah mereka adalah :doc:`Diskon <../../sales/"
"sales/products_prices/prices/pricing/>` biasa."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/mexico.rst:842
msgid ""
"In order to set this up, navigate to :menuselection:`Sales --> Products --> "
"Products` and create a product `Discounts`, make sure that it has a "
"valid :guilabel:`Tax` (usually :guilabel:`IVA` at `16%`)."
msgstr ""
"Untuk menyiapkan ini, navigasikan ke :menuselection:`Penjualan --> "
"Produk --> Produk` dan buat produk `Discounts`, pastikan bahwa produk "
"tersebut memiliki :guilabel:`Pajak` yang valid (biasanya :guilabel:`IVA` "
"pada `16%`)."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/mexico.rst:846
msgid ""
"After this, create and sign the invoice via |CFDI|, and add the `Discounts` "
"product at the bottom. In the XML, Odoo will distribute the discount between "
"the lines evenly, while any math differences will be added in a rounding "
"product."
msgstr ""
"Setelah ini, buat dan tandatangani faktur melalui |CFDI|, dan tambahkan "
"produk `Discounts` di bagian bawah. Dalam XML, Odoo akan mendistribusikan "
"diskon di antara baris secara merata, sementara perbedaan matematis apa pun "
"akan ditambahkan dalam produk pembulatan."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/mexico.rst:851
msgid ""
"A `Discount` and `UNSPSC Product Category` for each product variant related "
"to :guilabel:`Gift Cards` or :guilabel:`Loyalty Programs` have to be created."
msgstr ""
"Sebuah `Discount` dan `UNSPSC Product Category` untuk setiap varian produk "
"yang terkait dengan :guilabel:`Kartu Hadiah` atau :guilabel:`Program "
"Loyalitas` harus dibuat."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/mexico.rst:857
msgid "Down payments"
msgstr "Uang muka"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/mexico.rst:859
msgid ""
"A common practice in Mexico is the usage of :doc:`down payments <../../sales/"
"sales/invoicing/down_payment>`. It's usage primarily consists of cases where "
"you receive a payment for a good or service where either the product or the "
"price (or both) has not been fully determined."
msgstr ""
"Praktik umum di Meksiko adalah penggunaan :doc:`down payments <../../sales/"
"sales/invoicing/down_payment>`. Penggunaannya terutama terdiri dari kasus di "
"mana Anda menerima pembayaran untuk barang atau layanan di mana produk atau "
"harga (atau keduanya) belum sepenuhnya ditentukan."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/mexico.rst:864
msgid ""
"The |SAT| allows two different ways to handle this process: both of them "
"involve linking all invoices to each other with the :guilabel:`CFDI Origin` "
"field."
msgstr ""
"|SAT| memungkinkan dua cara berbeda untuk menangani proses ini: keduanya "
"melibatkan menautkan semua faktur satu sama lain dengan kolom "
":guilabel:`CFDI Origin`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/mexico.rst:868
msgid "For this process, the :doc:`Sales <../../sales>` app must be installed."
msgstr ""
"Untuk proses ini, aplikasi :doc:`Penjualan <../../sales>` harus diinstal."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/mexico.rst:871
msgid ""
"`The official documentation for registration of down payments in Mexico "
"<http://http://omawww.sat.gob.mx/tramitesyservicios/Paginas/documentos/"
"GuiaAnexo311221.pdf>`_."
msgstr ""
"`Dokumentasi resmi untuk pendaftaran uang muka di Meksiko <http://http://"
"omawww.sat.gob.mx/tramitesyservicios/Paginas/documentos/GuiaAnexo311221.pdf>"
"`_."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/mexico.rst:877
msgid ""
"First, navigate to :menuselection:`Sales --> Products --> Products` to "
"create a product `Anticipo` and configure it. The :guilabel:`Product Type` "
"must be :guilabel:`Service`, and use the :guilabel:`UNSPSC "
"Category` :guilabel:`84111506 Servicios de facturación`."
msgstr ""
"Pertama, navigasikan ke :menuselection:`Penjualan --> Produk --> Produk` "
"untuk membuat produk `Anticipo` dan konfigurasikan. :guilabel:`Jenis Produk` "
"harus :guilabel:`Layanan`, dan gunakan :guilabel:`Kategori UNSPSC` "
":guilabel:`84111506 Servicios de facturación`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/mexico.rst:881
msgid ""
"Then, go to :menuselection:`Sales --> Settings --> Invoicing --> Down "
"Payments`, and add the *Anticipo* product as the default."
msgstr ""
"Kemudian, buka :menuselection:`Penjualan --> Pengaturan --> Penagihan --> "
"Uang Muka`, dan tambahkan produk *Anticipo* sebagai default."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/mexico.rst:887
msgid "Method A"
msgstr "Metode A"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/mexico.rst:889
msgid ""
"This method consists of creating a down payment invoice, creating a invoice "
"for the total amount, and finally, creating a credit note for the total of "
"the down payment."
msgstr ""
"Metode ini terdiri dari membuat faktur uang muka, membuat faktur untuk "
"jumlah total, dan akhirnya, membuat nota kredit untuk total uang muka."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/mexico.rst:892
msgid ""
"First, create a sales order with the total amount, and create a down payment "
"from it (either using a percentage or fixed amount). Then, sign the document "
"via CFDI, and register the payment."
msgstr ""
"Pertama, buat sales order dengan jumlah total, dan buat uang muka dari situ "
"(baik menggunakan persentase atau jumlah tetap). Kemudian, tanda tangani "
"dokumen melalui CFDI, dan daftarkan pembayaran."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/mexico.rst:895
msgid ""
"When the time comes for the customer to get the final invoice, create it "
"again from the same sales order. In the :guilabel:`Create Invoice` popup, "
"select :guilabel:`Regular Invoice`. Make sure to delete the line that "
"contains the product *Anticipo*."
msgstr ""
"Ketika saatnya tiba bagi pelanggan untuk mendapatkan faktur akhir, buat lagi "
"dari sales order yang sama. Dalam popup :guilabel:`Buat Faktur`, pilih "
":guilabel:`Faktur Reguler`. Pastikan untuk menghapus baris yang berisi "
"produk *Anticipo*."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/mexico.rst:900
msgid ""
"When using down payments with the Mexican localization, make sure that "
"the :guilabel:`Invoicing Policy` of the products are :guilabel:`Ordered "
"quantities`. Otherwise a customer credit note will be created."
msgstr ""
"Saat menggunakan uang muka dengan lokalisasi Meksiko, pastikan bahwa "
":guilabel:`Kebijakan Penagihan` dari produk adalah :guilabel:`Jumlah yang "
"dipesan`. Jika tidak, nota kredit pelanggan akan dibuat."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/mexico.rst:904
msgid ""
"Then, copy the :guilabel:`Fiscal Folio` from the down payment invoice, and "
"paste it into the :guilabel:`CDFI Origin` of the final invoice, adding the "
"prefix `07|` before the value and sign the document via |CFDI|."
msgstr ""
"Kemudian, salin :guilabel:`Folio Fiskal` dari faktur uang muka, dan "
"tempelkan ke :guilabel:`Asal CDFI` dari faktur akhir, tambahkan awalan `07|` "
"sebelum nilai dan tanda tangani dokumen melalui |CFDI|."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/mexico.rst:908
msgid ""
"Finally, create a credit note for the first invoice. Copy "
"the :guilabel:`Fiscal Folio` from the final invoice, and paste it in "
"the :guilabel:`CFDI Origin` of the credit note, adding the prefix `07|`. "
"Then, sign the document via |CFDI|."
msgstr ""
"Akhirnya, buat nota kredit untuk faktur pertama. Salin :guilabel:`Folio "
"Fiskal` dari faktur akhir, dan tempelkan di :guilabel:`Asal CFDI` dari nota "
"kredit, tambahkan awalan `07|`. Kemudian, tanda tangani dokumen melalui "
"|CFDI|."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/mexico.rst:912
msgid ""
"With this, all electronic documents are linked to each other. The final step "
"is to fully pay the new invoice. At the bottom of the new invoice, you can "
"find the credit note in the :guilabel:`Outstanding credits` - add it as "
"payment. Finally, register the remaining amount with the :guilabel:`Pay` "
"popup."
msgstr ""
"Dengan ini, semua dokumen elektronik terhubung satu sama lain. Langkah "
"terakhir adalah membayar penuh faktur baru. Di bagian bawah faktur baru, "
"Anda dapat menemukan nota kredit di :guilabel:`Kredit yang beredar` - "
"tambahkan sebagai pembayaran. Akhirnya, daftarkan jumlah sisa dengan popup "
":guilabel:`Bayar`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/mexico.rst:917
msgid ""
"In the sales order, all three documents should appear as \"In Payment\"."
msgstr ""
"Dalam sales order, ketiga dokumen harus muncul sebagai \"Dalam Pembayaran\"."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/mexico.rst:920
msgid "Method B"
msgstr "Metode B"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/mexico.rst:922
msgid ""
"Another, simpler way to fulfill |SAT| requirements involves creating only "
"the down payment invoice, and a second invoice for the remnant. This method "
"involves the fact that negative lines are treated as discounts."
msgstr ""
"Cara lain yang lebih sederhana untuk memenuhi persyaratan |SAT| melibatkan "
"pembuatan hanya faktur uang muka, dan faktur kedua untuk sisanya. Metode ini "
"melibatkan fakta bahwa baris negatif diperlakukan sebagai diskon."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/mexico.rst:926
msgid ""
"For this, follow the same process as :ref:`Method A <l10n-mx/down-payment-"
"method-a>`, up until the creation of the final invoice. Do not delete the "
"line that contains the *Anticipo* and instead rename the other "
"products :guilabel:`Description` to include the text `CFDI por remanente de "
"un anticipo`. Don't forget to add the :guilabel:`Fiscal Folio` of the down "
"payment invoice in the :guilabel:`CDFI Origin` of the final invoice, adding "
"the prefix `07|`."
msgstr ""
"Untuk ini, ikuti proses yang sama seperti :ref:`Metode A <l10n-mx/down-"
"payment-method-a>`, hingga pembuatan faktur akhir. Jangan hapus baris yang "
"berisi *Anticipo* dan sebagai gantinya ubah nama produk lain "
":guilabel:`Deskripsi` untuk menyertakan teks `CFDI por remanente de un "
"anticipo`. Jangan lupa untuk menambahkan :guilabel:`Fiscal Folio` dari "
"faktur uang muka di :guilabel:`CDFI Origin` dari faktur akhir, dengan "
"menambahkan awalan `07|`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/mexico.rst:932
msgid "Finally, sign the final invoice via |CFDI|."
msgstr "Terakhir, tanda tangani faktur akhir melalui |CFDI|."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/mexico.rst:937
msgid "Addendas and complements"
msgstr "Addenda dan komplemen"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/mexico.rst:939
msgid ""
"Addendas and complements can be included in the XML. To add one, go "
"to :menuselection:`Accounting --> Configuration --> Addendas & Complementos "
"(MX)` and :guilabel:`New` to enter the code to be injected. Additional "
"fields beyond standard Odoo may be required."
msgstr ""
"Addenda dan komplemen dapat disertakan dalam XML. Untuk menambahkannya, buka "
":menuselection:`Akuntansi --> Konfigurasi --> Addendas & Complementos (MX)` "
"dan :guilabel:`Baru` untuk memasukkan kode yang akan diinjeksi. Bidang "
"tambahan di luar Odoo standar mungkin diperlukan."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/mexico.rst:944
msgid ""
"This section might require technical knowledge and may risk adding technical "
"debt; it is recommended to ask your account manager for the best technical "
"advice."
msgstr ""
"Bagian ini mungkin memerlukan pengetahuan teknis dan dapat berisiko "
"menambahkan utang teknis; disarankan untuk meminta manajer akun Anda untuk "
"saran teknis terbaik."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/mexico.rst:947
msgid ""
"Once the desired nodes are created, they can be selected on each contact to "
"make them appear on every invoice addressed to that contact. By default, all "
"the selected nodes will be added automatically on every invoice."
msgstr ""
"Setelah node yang diinginkan dibuat, node tersebut dapat dipilih pada setiap "
"kontak untuk membuatnya muncul di setiap faktur yang ditujukan kepada kontak "
"tersebut. Secara default, semua node yang dipilih akan ditambahkan secara "
"otomatis pada setiap faktur."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/mexico.rst:951
msgid ""
"It is also possible to just select the nodes as needed on every invoice by "
"selecting the :guilabel:`Other info` tab and then selecting the desired "
"nodes from :guilabel:`Addendas & Complementos`"
msgstr ""
"Dimungkinkan juga untuk hanya memilih node sesuai kebutuhan pada setiap "
"faktur dengan memilih tab :guilabel:`Info lain` dan kemudian memilih node "
"yang diinginkan dari :guilabel:`Addendas & Complementos`"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/mexico.rst:956
msgid "It is possible to add more than one per contact or per invoice."
msgstr ""
"Dimungkinkan untuk menambahkan lebih dari satu per kontak atau per faktur."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/mexico.rst:961
msgid "XML reader"
msgstr "Pembaca XML"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/mexico.rst:963
msgid ""
"In certain occasions, such as when you are creating invoices in another "
"software or in the |SAT| directly, you would want to upload the invoices in "
"Odoo. The XML Reader allows you to retrieve the data from an XML file. To do "
"this, navigate to :menuselection:`Accounting --> Customers --> Invoices` "
"and, in the list view, click the :guilabel:`Upload` button to select any "
"number of XML files, and draft invoices will be automatically created. This "
"can work also by dragging the files from your computer and dropping them in "
"the view."
msgstr ""
"Dalam situasi tertentu, seperti saat Anda membuat faktur di perangkat lunak "
"lain atau di |SAT| secara langsung, Anda mungkin ingin mengunggah faktur di "
"Odoo. Pembaca XML memungkinkan Anda mengambil data dari file XML. Untuk "
"melakukan ini, buka :menuselection:`Akuntansi --> Pelanggan --> Faktur` dan, "
"dalam tampilan daftar, klik tombol :guilabel:`Unggah` untuk memilih sejumlah "
"file XML, dan faktur draft akan dibuat secara otomatis. Ini juga dapat "
"dilakukan dengan menyeret file dari komputer Anda dan meletakkannya di "
"tampilan."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/mexico.rst:970
msgid ""
"The draft invoices will retrieve the :guilabel:`Customer information` (if it "
"doesn't exist, new ones will be created), the :guilabel:`Product Lines` "
"(only if products with the same name already exist) and will calculate all "
"taxes and additional fields exclusive to the Mexican Localization. The "
"import information will appear in the chatter."
msgstr ""
"Faktur draft akan mengambil :guilabel:`Informasi Pelanggan` (jika tidak ada, "
"yang baru akan dibuat), :guilabel:`Baris Produk` (hanya jika produk dengan "
"nama yang sama sudah ada) dan akan menghitung semua pajak dan bidang "
"tambahan yang eksklusif untuk Lokalisasi Meksiko. Informasi impor akan "
"muncul di chatter."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/mexico.rst:976
msgid ""
"Depending on where the invoice was created, XML files could have different "
"values from the total calculated in Odoo. **Always** double-check any "
"document uploaded this way."
msgstr ""
"Tergantung di mana faktur dibuat, file XML dapat memiliki nilai berbeda dari "
"total yang dihitung di Odoo. **Selalu** periksa ulang dokumen apa pun yang "
"diunggah dengan cara ini."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/mexico.rst:979
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Customer Invoices` created this way will be able to create "
"**payment complements** and to be canceled at any time. If you use "
"the :guilabel:`Print` button, the PDF document will have all the "
"corresponding information."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Faktur Pelanggan` yang dibuat dengan cara ini akan dapat membuat "
"**komplemen pembayaran** dan dibatalkan kapan saja. Jika Anda menggunakan "
"tombol :guilabel:`Cetak`, dokumen PDF akan memiliki semua informasi yang "
"sesuai."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/mexico.rst:983
msgid "This can be done for :guilabel:`Vendor Bills` too."
msgstr "Ini dapat dilakukan untuk :guilabel:`Tagihan Vendor` juga."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/mexico.rst:986
msgid ""
"To retrieve the :guilabel:`Fiscal Folio`, drag and drop XML files as a log "
"note in the chatter for previously created draft invoices."
msgstr ""
"Untuk mengambil :guilabel:`Fiscal Folio`, seret dan lepas file XML sebagai "
"catatan log di chatter untuk faktur draft yang telah dibuat sebelumnya."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/mexico.rst:992
#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/mexico.rst:1533
msgid "CFDI to public"
msgstr "CFDI untuk publik"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/mexico.rst:994
msgid ""
"The Mexican government requires that any goods or services that are sold "
"must be backed up by an invoice. If the customer does not require an invoice "
"or has no |RFC|, a *CFDI to Public* has to be created also known as a "
"\"nominative\" invoice."
msgstr ""
"Pemerintah Meksiko mewajibkan bahwa setiap barang atau jasa yang dijual "
"harus didukung oleh faktur. Jika pelanggan tidak memerlukan faktur atau "
"tidak memiliki |RFC|, *CFDI untuk Publik* harus dibuat yang juga dikenal "
"sebagai faktur \"nominatif\"."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/mexico.rst:998
msgid "A contact must be created and it must have a particular name."
msgstr "Kontak harus dibuat dan harus memiliki nama tertentu."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/mexico.rst:1000
msgid ""
"If  the :guilabel:`CFDI to Public` checkbox in either a sales order or an "
"invoice is checked, the final XML will override the data in the invoice "
"contact and will add the following characteristics:"
msgstr ""
"Jika kotak centang :guilabel:`CFDI untuk Publik` di sales order atau faktur "
"dicentang, XML akhir akan menimpa data dalam kontak faktur dan akan "
"menambahkan karakteristik berikut:"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/mexico.rst:1003
msgid ""
"|RFC|: **XAXX010101000** if it is a national customer or **XEXX010101000** "
"if it is a foreign customer"
msgstr ""
"|RFC|: **XAXX010101000** jika pelanggan nasional atau **XEXX010101000** jika "
"pelanggan asing"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/mexico.rst:1005
msgid ":guilabel:`ZIP` code: The same code of the company"
msgstr "Kode :guilabel:`ZIP`: Kode yang sama dengan perusahaan"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/mexico.rst:1006
msgid ":guilabel:`Usage`: S01 - Without Fiscal Effects"
msgstr ":guilabel:`Penggunaan`: S01 - Tanpa Efek Fiskal"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/mexico.rst:None
msgid "CFDI to Public Checkbox"
msgstr "Kotak Centang CFDI ke Publik"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/mexico.rst:1011
msgid ""
"If the final customer doesn't share any details, create a "
"generic :guilabel:`Customer`. The name cannot be `PUBLICO EN GENERAL` or an "
"error will be triggered (it can be, for example, `CLIENTE FINAL`)."
msgstr ""
"Jika pelanggan akhir tidak memberikan rincian apa pun, buat "
":guilabel:`Pelanggan` umum. Nama tidak boleh `PUBLICO EN GENERAL` atau akan "
"memicu kesalahan (dapat berupa, misalnya, `CLIENTE FINAL`)."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/mexico.rst:1016
msgid ""
"By default sending the invoice is not allowed if the partner does not have "
"either the *Country* or *Zip code* set, however this is not required if "
"the :guilabel:`CFDI to public` checkbox is active."
msgstr ""
"Secara default pengiriman faktur tidak diizinkan jika mitra tidak memiliki "
"*Negara* atau *Kode pos* yang ditetapkan, namun ini tidak diperlukan jika "
"kotak centang :guilabel:`CFDI ke publik` aktif."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/mexico.rst:1021
msgid ""
"`Regla 2.7.1.21 Expedición de comprobantes en operaciones con el público en "
"general <https://www.sat.gob.mx/articulo/90959/regla-2.7.1.21>`_."
msgstr ""
"`Regla 2.7.1.21 Expedición de comprobantes en operaciones con el público en "
"general <https://www.sat.gob.mx/articulo/90959/regla-2.7.1.21>`_."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/mexico.rst:1027
#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/mexico.rst:1465
msgid "Global invoice"
msgstr "Faktur Global"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/mexico.rst:1029
msgid ""
"If by the end of a certain period of time (that can vary from daily to "
"bimonthly, depending of your company's legal needs and preferences) and the "
"customer still has sales that weren't marked as regular invoices or "
"individual *CFDI to Public* invoices, the |SAT| allows for the creation of a "
"single invoice that can contain all operations, known as a *global invoice*."
msgstr ""
"Jika pada akhir periode waktu tertentu (yang dapat bervariasi dari harian "
"hingga dua bulanan, tergantung pada kebutuhan hukum dan preferensi "
"perusahaan Anda) dan pelanggan masih memiliki penjualan yang tidak ditandai "
"sebagai faktur reguler atau faktur *CFDI ke Publik* individual, |SAT| "
"mengizinkan pembuatan satu faktur yang dapat berisi semua operasi, yang "
"dikenal sebagai *faktur global*."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/mexico.rst:1035
msgid ""
"For this process, the :doc:`Sales <../../sales/sales>` app must be installed."
msgstr ""
"Untuk proses ini, aplikasi :doc:`Penjualan <../../sales/sales>` harus "
"diinstal."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/mexico.rst:1038
msgid ""
"`Guía de llenado del CFDI global <http://omawww.sat.gob.mx/"
"tramitesyservicios/Paginas/documentos/GuiallenadoCFDIglobal311221.pdf>`_"
msgstr ""
"`Guía de llenado del CFDI global <http://omawww.sat.gob.mx/"
"tramitesyservicios/Paginas/documentos/GuiallenadoCFDIglobal311221.pdf>`_"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/mexico.rst:1044
msgid ""
"The :guilabel:`Global Invoice Serie` is specific to each branch or company "
"and is used to define the sequence of global invoices. To configure it, go "
"to :menuselection:`Accounting --> Configuration --> Settings`, and navigate "
"to the :guilabel:`MX Electronic invoicing` section. The :guilabel:`Global "
"Invoice Serie` field can be found within the :guilabel:`Service Tax "
"Administration (SAT)` section."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Global Invoice Serie` khusus untuk setiap cabang atau perusahaan "
"dan digunakan untuk menentukan urutan faktur global. Untuk "
"mengonfigurasinya, buka :menuselection:`Akuntansi --> Configuration --> "
"Settings`, dan arahkan ke bagian :guilabel:`MX Electronic invoicing`. Field "
":guilabel:`Global Invoice Serie` dapat ditemukan dalam bagian "
":guilabel:`Service Tax Administration (SAT)`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/mexico.rst:None
msgid "Accounting setting with an MX company."
msgstr "Pengaturan Akuntansi dengan perusahaan MX."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/mexico.rst:1053
msgid "The default sequence for every company/branch is `GINV/`"
msgstr "Urutan default untuk setiap perusahaan/cabang adalah `GINV/`"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/mexico.rst:1056
msgid "Sales flow"
msgstr "Alur penjualan"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/mexico.rst:1058
msgid ""
"First, create a dedicated journal in :menuselection:`Accounting --> "
"Configuration --> Journals` to maintain a separate sequence that is used for "
"global invoices, which function as orders when they are created."
msgstr ""
"Pertama, buat jurnal khusus di :menuselection:`Akuntansi --> "
"Configuration --> Journals` untuk mempertahankan urutan terpisah yang "
"digunakan untuk faktur global, yang berfungsi sebagai pesanan saat dibuat."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/mexico.rst:1062
msgid ""
"Then, make sure that all the sales orders that need to be signed have the "
"following configurations:"
msgstr ""
"Kemudian, pastikan bahwa semua pesanan penjualan yang perlu ditandatangani "
"memiliki konfigurasi berikut:"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/mexico.rst:1064
msgid ":guilabel:`CFDI to Public` checkbox enabled"
msgstr "Kotak centang :guilabel:`CFDI ke Publik` diaktifkan"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/mexico.rst:1065
msgid ":guilabel:`Invoice Status` marked as :guilabel:`To Invoice`"
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Status Faktur` ditandai sebagai :guilabel:`Untuk Difakturkan`"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/mexico.rst:1067
msgid ""
"After this, go to :menuselection:`Sales --> To Invoice --> Orders to "
"Invoice`, select all relevant sales orders and press :guilabel:`Create "
"Invoices`. Make sure to disable the :guilabel:`Consolidated Billing` "
"checkbox and click :guilabel:`Create Draft Invoice`."
msgstr ""
"Setelah ini, buka :menuselection:`Penjualan --> Untuk Difakturkan --> "
"Pesanan untuk Difakturkan`, pilih semua pesanan penjualan yang relevan dan "
"tekan :guilabel:`Buat Faktur`. Pastikan untuk menonaktifkan kotak centang "
":guilabel:`Penagihan Terkonsolidasi` dan klik :guilabel:`Buat Faktur Draf`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/mexico.rst:1071
msgid ""
"Odoo will redirect to a list of invoices. Select all of them and in "
"the :icon:`fa-gear` :guilabel:`Actions` drop-down menu "
"select :guilabel:`Post entries`. Select all posted invoices again and go "
"back to the  :icon:`fa-gear` :guilabel:`Actions` drop-down menu to "
"select :guilabel:`Create Global Invoice`."
msgstr ""
"Odoo akan mengarahkan ke daftar faktur. Pilih semuanya dan di menu drop-down "
":icon:`fa-gear` :guilabel:`Tindakan` pilih :guilabel:`Posting entri`. Pilih "
"semua faktur yang telah diposting lagi dan kembali ke menu drop-down "
":icon:`fa-gear` :guilabel:`Tindakan` untuk memilih :guilabel:`Buat Faktur "
"Global`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/mexico.rst:1076
msgid ""
"In the wizard, select the :guilabel:`Periodicity` indicated by a "
"professional accountant and press :guilabel:`Create`. All invoices should be "
"signed under the same XML file, with the same :guilabel:`Fiscal Folio`."
msgstr ""
"Dalam wizard, pilih :guilabel:`Periodisitas` yang ditunjukkan oleh akuntan "
"profesional dan tekan :guilabel:`Buat`. Semua faktur harus ditandatangani di "
"bawah file XML yang sama, dengan :guilabel:`Folio Fiskal` yang sama."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/mexico.rst:1081
msgid ""
"Click :guilabel:`Show` in the :guilabel:`CFDI` tab to display a list with "
"all related invoices."
msgstr ""
"Klik :guilabel:`Tampilkan` di tab :guilabel:`CFDI` untuk menampilkan daftar "
"dengan semua faktur terkait."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/mexico.rst:1082
msgid ""
"Click :guilabel:`Cancel` in the :guilabel:`CFDI` tab to cancel the global "
"invoice in both the |SAT| and Odoo."
msgstr ""
"Klik :guilabel:`Batalkan` di tab :guilabel:`CFDI` untuk membatalkan faktur "
"global di |SAT| dan Odoo."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/mexico.rst:1086
msgid ""
"Global invoices created this way won't have a **PDF** in them as their "
"information is already within Odoo and is not to be seen by a customer."
msgstr ""
"Faktur global yang dibuat dengan cara ini tidak akan memiliki **PDF** di "
"dalamnya karena informasinya sudah ada di dalam Odoo dan tidak untuk dilihat "
"oleh pelanggan."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/mexico.rst:1092
msgid "Electronic accounting (reporting)"
msgstr "Akuntansi elektronik (pelaporan)"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/mexico.rst:1094
msgid ""
"For Mexico, `Electronic Accounting <https://www.sat.gob.mx/aplicacion/42150/"
"envia-tu-contabilidad-electronica>`_ refers to the obligation to keep "
"accounting records and entries through electronic means, and to enter "
"accounting information on a monthly basis, through the |SAT| website."
msgstr ""
"Untuk Meksiko, `Akuntansi Elektronik <https://www.sat.gob.mx/aplicacion/"
"42150/envia-tu-contabilidad-electronica>`_ mengacu pada kewajiban untuk "
"menyimpan catatan dan entri akuntansi melalui media elektronik, dan "
"memasukkan informasi akuntansi setiap bulan melalui website |SAT|."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/mexico.rst:1099
msgid "It consists of three main XML files:"
msgstr "Ini terdiri dari tiga file XML utama:"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/mexico.rst:1101
msgid "The updated list of the chart of accounts that is currently in use"
msgstr "Daftar terbaru dari bagan akun yang saat ini digunakan"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/mexico.rst:1102
msgid ""
"A monthly trial balance, plus a closing entry report, also known as: *Trial "
"Balance Month 13*"
msgstr ""
"Neraca saldo bulanan, ditambah laporan entri penutup, juga dikenal sebagai: "
"*Neraca Saldo Bulan 13*"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/mexico.rst:1103
msgid ""
"An export of the journal entries in the general ledger (optional except in "
"the case of a compulsory audit)"
msgstr ""
"Ekspor entri jurnal dalam buku besar (opsional kecuali dalam kasus audit "
"wajib)"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/mexico.rst:1106
msgid ""
"The resulting XML files follow the requirements of the `Anexo Técnico de "
"Contabilidad Electrónica 1.3 <https://www.gob.mx/cms/uploads/attachment/file/"
"151135/Anexo24_05012015.pdf>`_."
msgstr ""
"File XML yang dihasilkan mengikuti persyaratan dari `Anexo Técnico de "
"Contabilidad Electrónica 1.3 <https://www.gob.mx/cms/uploads/attachment/file/"
"151135/Anexo24_05012015.pdf>`_."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/mexico.rst:1109
msgid ""
"In addition to this, it is possible to generate the `DIOT <https://"
"www.sat.gob.mx/declaracion/74295/presenta-tu-declaracion-informativa-de-"
"operaciones-con- terceros-(diot)->`_: a report of vendors' journal entries "
"that involve IVA taxes that can be exported in a TXT file."
msgstr ""
"Selain itu, dimungkinkan untuk menghasilkan `DIOT <https://www.sat.gob.mx/"
"declaracion/74295/presenta-tu-declaracion-informativa-de-operaciones-con- "
"terceros-(diot)->`_: laporan entri jurnal vendor yang melibatkan pajak IVA "
"yang dapat diekspor dalam file TXT."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/mexico.rst:1115
msgid "In order to use these reports, the following modules must be installed:"
msgstr "Untuk menggunakan laporan ini, modul berikut harus diinstal:"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/mexico.rst:1117
msgid ":guilabel:`Odoo Mexican Localization Reports` `l10n_mx_reports`"
msgstr ":guilabel:`Odoo Mexican Localization Reports` `l10n_mx_reports`"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/mexico.rst:1118
msgid ":guilabel:`Mexico - Month 13 Trial Balance` `l10n_mx_reports_closing`"
msgstr ":guilabel:`Mexico - Month 13 Trial Balance` `l10n_mx_reports_closing`"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/mexico.rst:1119
msgid ":guilabel:`Odoo Mexican XML Polizas Export` `l10n_mx_xml_polizas`"
msgstr ":guilabel:`Odoo Mexican XML Polizas Export` `l10n_mx_xml_polizas`"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/mexico.rst:1121
msgid ""
"The *chart of accounts* and the *Trial Balance Month 13* reports can be "
"found in :menuselection:`Accounting --> Reporting --> Trial Balance`. The "
"*DIOT* report can be found in :menuselection:`Accounting --> Reporting --> "
"Tax Report`."
msgstr ""
"Laporan *bagan akun* dan *Neraca Saldo Bulan 13* dapat ditemukan di "
":menuselection:`Akuntansi --> Pelaporan --> Neraca Saldo`. Laporan *DIOT* "
"dapat ditemukan di :menuselection:`Akuntansi --> Pelaporan --> Laporan "
"Pajak`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/mexico.rst:1126
msgid ""
"The specific characteristics and obligations of the reports that you send "
"might change according to your fiscal regime. Always contact your accountant "
"before sending any documents to the government."
msgstr ""
"Karakteristik dan kewajiban spesifik dari laporan yang Anda kirim mungkin "
"berubah sesuai dengan rezim fiskal Anda. Selalu hubungi akuntan Anda sebelum "
"mengirim dokumen apa pun ke pemerintah."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/mexico.rst:1135
msgid ""
"The :doc:`chart of accounts <../accounting/get_started/chart_of_accounts>` "
"in Mexico follows a specific pattern based on |SAT|'s' `Código agrupador de "
"cuentas <http://omawww.sat.gob.mx/fichas_tematicas/buzon_tributario/"
"Documents/codigo_agrupador.pdf>`_."
msgstr ""
":doc:`Bagan akun <../accounting/get_started/chart_of_accounts>` di Meksiko "
"mengikuti pola spesifik berdasarkan `Código agrupador de cuentas <http://"
"omawww.sat.gob.mx/fichas_tematicas/buzon_tributario/Documents/"
"codigo_agrupador.pdf>`_ dari |SAT|."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/mexico.rst:1139
msgid ""
"It is possible to create any account, as long as it respects |SAT|'s "
"encoding group: the pattern is `NNN.YY.ZZ` or `NNN.YY.ZZZ`."
msgstr ""
"Dimungkinkan untuk membuat akun apa pun, selama mengikuti kelompok "
"pengkodean |SAT|: polanya adalah `NNN.YY.ZZ` atau `NNN.YY.ZZZ`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/mexico.rst:1143
msgid "Some examples are `102.01.99` or `401.01.001`."
msgstr "Beberapa contohnya adalah `102.01.99` atau `401.01.001`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/mexico.rst:1145
msgid ""
"When a new account is created in :menuselection:`Accounting --> "
"Configuration --> Chart of Accounts`, with the |SAT| encoding group pattern, "
"the correct grouping code appears in :guilabel:`Tags`, and the account "
"appears in the *COA* report."
msgstr ""
"Ketika akun baru dibuat di :menuselection:`Akuntansi --> Konfigurasi --> "
"Bagan Akun`, dengan pola kelompok pengkodean |SAT|, kode pengelompokan yang "
"benar muncul di :guilabel:`Tag`, dan akun tersebut muncul dalam laporan "
"*COA*."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/mexico.rst:1149
msgid ""
"Once all accounts are created, make sure the correct :guilabel:`Tags` are "
"added as these mark the nature of the account."
msgstr ""
"Setelah semua akun dibuat, pastikan :guilabel:`Tag` yang benar ditambahkan "
"karena ini menandai sifat akun."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/mexico.rst:1153
msgid ""
"It is not advised use any pattern that ends a section with a 0 (such as "
"`100.01.01`, `301.00.003` or `604.77.00`). This triggers errors in the "
"report. By default Odoo will mark the accounts as yellow if the numbering "
"will cause issue later on, this is to prevent reports from providing "
"inaccurate data."
msgstr ""
"Tidak disarankan menggunakan pola apa pun yang mengakhiri bagian dengan 0 "
"(seperti `100.01.01`, `301.00.003` atau `604.77.00`). Ini memicu kesalahan "
"dalam laporan. Secara default Odoo akan menandai akun sebagai kuning jika "
"penomoran akan menyebabkan masalah di kemudian hari, ini untuk mencegah "
"laporan memberikan data yang tidak akurat."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/mexico.rst:1158
msgid ""
"Once everything is set up, go to :menuselection:`Accounting --> Reporting --"
"> Trial Balance`, and click the :guilabel:`COA SAT (XML)` button to generate "
"an XML file containing all of the accounts. This XML file is ready to upload "
"to the |SAT| website."
msgstr ""
"Setelah semuanya diatur, buka :menuselection:`Akuntansi --> Pelaporan --> "
"Neraca Saldo`, dan klik tombol :guilabel:`COA SAT (XML)` untuk menghasilkan "
"file XML yang berisi semua akun. File XML ini siap diunggah ke website |SAT|."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/mexico.rst:1167
msgid ""
"The trial balance reports the initial balance, credit, and total balance of "
"your accounts, provided that you added their correct :ref:`encoding group "
"<l10n_mx/chart-of-accounts>`."
msgstr ""
"Laporan neraca saldo menampilkan saldo awal, kredit, dan saldo total akun "
"Anda, asalkan Anda telah menambahkan :ref:`grup pengkodean <l10n_mx/chart-of-"
"accounts>` yang benar."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/mexico.rst:1170
msgid ""
"To generate an XML file of the trial balance, go "
"to :menuselection:`Accounting --> Reporting --> Trial Balance`, select the "
"date, and click the :icon:`fa-cog` :guilabel:`(action menu)`, then "
"select :guilabel:`SAT (XML)`."
msgstr ""
"Untuk menghasilkan file XML neraca saldo, buka :menuselection:`Akuntansi --> "
"Pelaporan --> Neraca Saldo`, pilih tanggal, lalu klik :icon:`fa-cog` "
":guilabel:`(menu tindakan)`, kemudian pilih :guilabel:`SAT (XML)`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/mexico.rst:None
msgid "Trial balance report."
msgstr "Laporan neraca saldo."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/mexico.rst:1178
msgid "Odoo does not generate the *Balanza de Comprobación Complementaria*."
msgstr "Odoo tidak menghasilkan *Balanza de Comprobación Complementaria*."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/mexico.rst:1183
msgid "Month 13"
msgstr "Bulan 13"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/mexico.rst:1185
msgid ""
"An additional report is the *Month 13*: a closing balance sheet that shows "
"any adjustments or movements made in the accounting to close the year."
msgstr ""
"Laporan tambahan adalah *Bulan 13*: neraca penutupan yang menampilkan "
"penyesuaian atau pergerakan yang dibuat dalam akuntansi untuk menutup tahun."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/mexico.rst:1188
msgid ""
"To generate this XML document, navigate to :menuselection:`Accounting --> "
"Accounting --> Journal Entries`, and create a new document. Here, add all "
"amounts to modify, and balance the debit and/or credit of each one."
msgstr ""
"Untuk menghasilkan dokumen XML ini, navigasikan ke "
":menuselection:`Akuntansi --> Akuntansi --> Entri Jurnal`, dan buat dokumen "
"baru. Di sini, tambahkan semua jumlah yang akan dimodifikasi, dan "
"seimbangkan debit dan/atau kredit masing-masing."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/mexico.rst:1192
msgid ""
"After this is done, go to the :guilabel:`Other Info` tab and check "
"the :guilabel:`Month 13 Closing` field. If needed, go "
"to :menuselection:`Accounting --> Reporting --> Trial Balance` and select "
"the date :guilabel:`Month 13`, where it is possible to see the the total "
"amount of the year, plus all the additions of the journal entry. To generate "
"the XML file, click the :icon:`fa-cog` :guilabel:`(action menu)`, then "
"select :guilabel:`SAT (XML)`."
msgstr ""
"Setelah selesai, buka tab :guilabel:`Info Lain` dan centang kolom "
":guilabel:`Penutupan Bulan 13`. Jika diperlukan, buka "
":menuselection:`Akuntansi --> Pelaporan --> Neraca Saldo` dan pilih tanggal "
":guilabel:`Bulan 13`, di mana dimungkinkan untuk melihat total jumlah tahun "
"tersebut, ditambah semua penambahan dari entri jurnal. Untuk menghasilkan "
"file XML, klik :icon:`fa-cog` :guilabel:`(menu tindakan)`, kemudian pilih "
":guilabel:`SAT (XML)`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/mexico.rst:1203
msgid ""
"By law, all transactions in Mexico must be recorded digitally. Since Odoo "
"automatically creates all the underlying journal entries of all invoices and "
"payments, simply exporting the general ledger complies with |SAT|'s audits "
"and/or tax refunds."
msgstr ""
"Menurut hukum, semua transaksi di Meksiko harus dicatat secara digital. "
"Karena Odoo secara otomatis membuat semua entri jurnal yang mendasari semua "
"faktur dan pembayaran, cukup mengekspor buku besar untuk mematuhi audit dan/"
"atau pengembalian pajak |SAT|."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/mexico.rst:1208
msgid ""
"The report can be filtered by period or by journal, depending on the need."
msgstr ""
"Laporan dapat difilter berdasarkan periode atau berdasarkan jurnal, "
"tergantung kebutuhan."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/mexico.rst:1210
msgid ""
"To create the XML, go to :menuselection:`Accounting --> Reporting --> "
"General Ledger`, click :icon:`fa-cog` :guilabel:`(action menu)`, then "
"click :guilabel:`XML (Polizas)`. Then, select among four :guilabel:`Export` "
"types:"
msgstr ""
"Untuk membuat XML, buka :menuselection:`Akuntansi --> Pelaporan --> Buku "
"Besar`, klik :icon:`fa-cog` :guilabel:`(menu tindakan)`, lalu klik "
":guilabel:`XML (Polizas)`. Kemudian, pilih di antara empat tipe "
":guilabel:`Ekspor`:"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/mexico.rst:1214
msgid ":guilabel:`Tax audit`"
msgstr ":guilabel:`Audit pajak`"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/mexico.rst:1215
msgid ":guilabel:`Audit certification`"
msgstr ":guilabel:`Sertifikasi audit`"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/mexico.rst:1216
msgid ":guilabel:`Return of goods`"
msgstr ":guilabel:`Pengembalian barang`"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/mexico.rst:1217
msgid ":guilabel:`Compensation`"
msgstr ":guilabel:`Kompensasi`"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/mexico.rst:1219
msgid ""
"For :guilabel:`Tax audit` or :guilabel:`Audit certification`, add "
"the :guilabel:`Order Number` provided by the |SAT|. For :guilabel:`Return of "
"goods` or :guilabel:`Compensation`, add the :guilabel:`Process Number`, also "
"provided by the |SAT|."
msgstr ""
"Untuk :guilabel:`Audit pajak` atau :guilabel:`Sertifikasi audit`, tambahkan "
":guilabel:`Nomor Pesanan` yang disediakan oleh |SAT|. Untuk "
":guilabel:`Pengembalian barang` atau :guilabel:`Kompensasi`, tambahkan "
":guilabel:`Nomor Proses`, yang juga disediakan oleh |SAT|."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/mexico.rst:1224
msgid ""
"To see this report without sending it, use `ABC6987654/99` for "
"the :guilabel:`Order Number` or `AB123451234512` for the :guilabel:`Process "
"Number`."
msgstr ""
"Untuk melihat laporan ini tanpa mengirimkannya, gunakan `ABC6987654/99` "
"untuk :guilabel:`Nomor Pesanan` atau `AB123451234512` untuk :guilabel:`Nomor "
"Proses`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/mexico.rst:1230
msgid "DIOT report"
msgstr "Laporan DIOT"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/mexico.rst:1232
msgid ""
"The DIOT (Declaración Informativa de Operaciones con Terceros / *Informative "
"Declaration of Operations with Third Parties*) is an additional obligation "
"with the |SAT|, where the current status of creditable and non-creditable "
"payments, withholdings, import taxes, and refunds of VAT from your vendor "
"bills are provided to the |SAT|."
msgstr ""
"DIOT (Declaración Informativa de Operaciones con Terceros / *Deklarasi "
"Informatif Operasi dengan Pihak Ketiga*) adalah kewajiban tambahan dengan "
"|SAT|, di mana status terkini pembayaran yang dapat dikreditkan dan tidak "
"dapat dikreditkan, pemotongan, pajak impor, dan pengembalian PPN dari "
"tagihan vendor Anda diberikan kepada |SAT|."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/mexico.rst:1238
msgid "Since July 2025 the new 2025 version of the report is available."
msgstr "Sejak Juli 2025, versi laporan 2025 yang baru telah tersedia."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/mexico.rst:1240
msgid ""
"Unlike other reports, the |DIOT| is uploaded to a website provided by the |"
"SAT| that contains the A-29 form. In Odoo, you can download the records of "
"your transactions as a TXT file that can be uploaded to the form, avoiding "
"direct capture of this data."
msgstr ""
"Tidak seperti laporan lainnya, |DIOT| diunggah ke website yang disediakan "
"oleh |SAT| yang berisi formulir A-29. Di Odoo, Anda dapat mengunduh catatan "
"transaksi Anda sebagai file TXT yang dapat diunggah ke formulir, menghindari "
"pemasukan data secara langsung."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/mexico.rst:1244
msgid ""
"The transactions file contains the total amount of the payments registered "
"in vendor bills, broken down into the corresponding types of IVA. "
"The :guilabel:`VAT`, :guilabel:`Country` and :guilabel:`Type of operation` "
"fields are mandatory for all vendors."
msgstr ""
"File transaksi berisi jumlah total pembayaran yang tercatat dalam tagihan "
"vendor, dirinci ke dalam jenis-jenis IVA yang sesuai. Field :guilabel:`VAT`, "
":guilabel:`Country`, dan :guilabel:`Type of operation` wajib diisi untuk "
"semua vendor."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/mexico.rst:1248
msgid ""
"To download the |DIOT| report as a TXT file, go "
"to :menuselection:`Accounting --> Reports --> Tax Return`. Select the "
"desired month, click :icon:`fa-cog` :guilabel:`(action menu)`, and "
"select :guilabel:`DIOT (TXT)`."
msgstr ""
"Untuk mengunduh laporan |DIOT| sebagai file TXT, buka "
":menuselection:`Akuntansi --> Reports --> Tax Return`. Pilih bulan yang "
"diinginkan, klik :icon:`fa-cog` :guilabel:`(menu aksi)`, dan pilih "
":guilabel:`DIOT (TXT)`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/mexico.rst:1252
msgid ""
"In case new taxes are created on the database, there are two types of tags, "
"the tags containing **tax** must go into the tax distribution and the ones "
"with the base name go on the base of the tax. All lines of a VAT tax "
"**must** containing at least one tax grid."
msgstr ""
"Jika pajak baru dibuat pada database, ada dua jenis tag, tag yang berisi "
"**tax** harus masuk ke dalam distribusi pajak dan yang dengan nama base "
"masuk pada dasar pajak. Semua baris pajak PPN **harus** berisi setidaknya "
"satu grid pajak."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/mexico.rst:None
msgid "DIOT (TXT) download button."
msgstr "Tombol unduh DIOT (TXT)."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/mexico.rst:1260
msgid ""
"It is required to fill in the :guilabel:`Type of Operation` field in "
"the :guilabel:`Accounting` tab of each vendor to prevent validation errors. "
"Make sure that foreign customers have their :guilabel:`Country` set."
msgstr ""
"Field :guilabel:`Type of Operation` pada tab :guilabel:`Akuntansi` setiap "
"vendor wajib diisi untuk mencegah kesalahan validasi. Pastikan bahwa "
"pelanggan asing memiliki :guilabel:`Country` yang telah diatur."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/mexico.rst:None
msgid "DIOT information on a vendor contact."
msgstr "Informasi DIOT pada kontak vendor."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/mexico.rst:1267
msgid ""
"Selecting :guilabel:`87 - Global Operations` will cause the final TXT file "
"to merge all vendors that are part of the global operations under one "
"generic VAT: *XAXX010101000*."
msgstr ""
"Memilih :guilabel:`87 - Global Operations` akan menyebabkan file TXT akhir "
"menggabungkan semua vendor yang merupakan bagian dari operasi global di "
"bawah satu VAT generik: *XAXX010101000*."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/mexico.rst:1273
msgid "External trade"
msgstr "Perdagangan luar negeri"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/mexico.rst:1275
msgid ""
"The external trade is a complement to a regular invoice that adds certain "
"values in both the XML and PDF, to invoices with a foreign customer "
"according to `SAT regulations <http://omawww.sat.gob.mx/tramitesyservicios/"
"Paginas/complemento_comercio_exterior.htm>`_, such as:"
msgstr ""
"Perdagangan luar negeri adalah pelengkap faktur reguler yang menambahkan "
"nilai tertentu baik dalam XML maupun PDF, untuk faktur dengan pelanggan luar "
"negeri sesuai dengan `peraturan SAT <http://omawww.sat.gob.mx/"
"tramitesyservicios/Paginas/complemento_comercio_exterior.htm>`_, seperti:"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/mexico.rst:1279
msgid "The specific address of the receiver and the sender"
msgstr "Alamat spesifik penerima dan pengirim"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/mexico.rst:1280
msgid ""
"The addition of a :guilabel:`Tariff Fraction` that identifies the type of "
"product"
msgstr ""
"Penambahan :guilabel:`Tariff Fraction` yang mengidentifikasi jenis produk"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/mexico.rst:1281
msgid ""
"The correct :doc:`../accounting/customer_invoices/incoterms` (International "
"Commercial Terms)"
msgstr ""
":doc:`../accounting/customer_invoices/incoterms` yang benar (International "
"Commercial Terms)"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/mexico.rst:1282
msgid ""
"And more, such as the *certificate of origin* and *special units of measure*"
msgstr "Dan lainnya, seperti *sertifikat asal* dan *satuan ukuran khusus*"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/mexico.rst:1284
msgid ""
"This allows the correct identification of exporters and importers, in "
"addition to expanding the description of the merchandise sold."
msgstr ""
"Hal ini memungkinkan identifikasi yang benar terhadap eksportir dan "
"importir, selain memperluas deskripsi barang dagangan yang dijual."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/mexico.rst:1287
msgid ""
"Since January 1, 2018, external trade is a requirement for taxpayers who "
"carry export operations of type A1. While the current CFDI is 4.0, the "
"external trade is currently on version 2.0."
msgstr ""
"Sejak 1 Januari 2018, perdagangan luar negeri adalah persyaratan bagi wajib "
"pajak yang melakukan operasi ekspor tipe A1. Meskipun CFDI saat ini adalah "
"4.0, perdagangan luar negeri saat ini menggunakan versi 2.0."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/mexico.rst:1291
msgid ""
"In order to use this feature, the :guilabel:`EDI for Mexico (Advanced "
"Features)` `l10n_mx_edi_extended` module must be installed."
msgstr ""
"Untuk menggunakan fitur ini, modul :guilabel:`EDI for Mexico (Advanced "
"Features)` `l10n_mx_edi_extended` harus diinstal."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/mexico.rst:1295
msgid ""
"Before installing, make sure your business needs to use this feature. "
"Consult your accountant first, if needed, before installing any modules."
msgstr ""
"Sebelum menginstal, pastikan bisnis Anda perlu menggunakan fitur ini. "
"Konsultasikan dengan akuntan Anda terlebih dahulu, jika diperlukan, sebelum "
"menginstal modul apa pun."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/mexico.rst:1298
msgid ""
"The :guilabel:`CFDI to public` checkbox must be ticked when creating foreign "
"invoices."
msgstr ""
"Checkbox :guilabel:`CFDI to public` harus dicentang saat membuat faktur luar "
"negeri."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/mexico.rst:1306
msgid ""
"To configure your company contact for external trade, navigate "
"to :menuselection:`Accounting --> Customers --> Customers`, remove the "
"default :guilabel:`Customer Invoices` filter, and select "
"your :guilabel:`Company` name. While the CFDI 4.0 requirements require "
"adding a valid :guilabel:`ZIP` code in the company contact record, the "
"external trade complement adds the requirement that the :guilabel:`City` and "
"the :guilabel:`State` must also be valid. All three fields must coincide "
"with the `Official SAT Catalog for Carta Porte <http://omawww.sat.gob.mx/"
"tramitesyservicios/Paginas/catalogos_emision_cfdi_complemento_ce.htm>`_, or "
"it will produce an error."
msgstr ""
"Untuk mengonfigurasi kontak perusahaan Anda untuk perdagangan luar negeri, "
"buka :menuselection:`Akuntansi --> Customers --> Customers`, hapus filter "
"default :guilabel:`Customer Invoices`, dan pilih nama :guilabel:`Company` "
"Anda. Sementara persyaratan CFDI 4.0 mengharuskan menambahkan kode "
":guilabel:`ZIP` yang valid dalam catatan kontak perusahaan, pelengkap "
"perdagangan luar negeri menambahkan persyaratan bahwa :guilabel:`City` dan "
":guilabel:`State` juga harus valid. Ketiga field tersebut harus sesuai "
"dengan `Katalog Resmi SAT untuk Carta Porte <http://omawww.sat.gob.mx/"
"tramitesyservicios/Paginas/catalogos_emision_cfdi_complemento_ce.htm>`_, "
"atau akan menghasilkan kesalahan."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/mexico.rst:1316
msgid ""
"Add the :guilabel:`City` and :guilabel:`State` in the company's *contact "
"record*, not in the company record itself."
msgstr ""
"Tambahkan :guilabel:`City` dan :guilabel:`State` di *catatan kontak* "
"perusahaan, bukan di catatan perusahaan itu sendiri."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/mexico.rst:1319
msgid ""
"On the contact record, the optional fields :guilabel:`Locality` "
"and :guilabel:`Colony Code` can also be filled. These two fields also have "
"to coincide with the data in the |SAT|."
msgstr ""
"Pada catatan kontak, kolom opsional :guilabel:`Locality` dan "
":guilabel:`Colony Code` juga dapat diisi. Kedua kolom ini juga harus sesuai "
"dengan data di |SAT|."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/mexico.rst:1322
msgid ""
"To configure the contact data for a foreign receiving client, navigate "
"to :menuselection:`Accounting --> Customers --> Customers`, and select the "
"foreign client's contact. The contact must have the following fields "
"completed to avoid errors:"
msgstr ""
"Untuk mengonfigurasi data kontak klien penerima asing, navigasikan ke "
":menuselection:`Akuntansi --> Pelanggan --> Pelanggan`, dan pilih kontak "
"klien asing tersebut. Kontak harus memiliki kolom berikut yang telah "
"dilengkapi untuk menghindari kesalahan:"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/mexico.rst:1326
msgid ""
"The entire company :guilabel:`Address`, including a valid :guilabel:`ZIP` "
"code and the foreign :guilabel:`Country`."
msgstr ""
"Seluruh :guilabel:`Address` perusahaan, termasuk kode :guilabel:`ZIP` yang "
"valid dan :guilabel:`Country` asing."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/mexico.rst:1328
msgid ""
"The foreign :guilabel:`RFC` (tax identification number), in the correct "
"format (for example: Colombia `123456789-1`)"
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`RFC` asing (nomor identifikasi pajak), dalam format yang benar "
"(misalnya: Kolombia `123456789-1`)"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/mexico.rst:1330
msgid ""
"In the :guilabel:`Sales & Purchase` tab, to activate the :guilabel:`Needs "
"external trade?` checkbox."
msgstr ""
"Di tab :guilabel:`Sales & Purchase`, untuk mengaktifkan kotak centang "
":guilabel:`Needs external trade?`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/mexico.rst:1334
msgid ""
"In the resulting XML and PDF files, the :guilabel:`VAT` is automatically "
"replaced by the generic VAT for abroad transactions: `XEXX010101000`."
msgstr ""
"Dalam file XML dan PDF yang dihasilkan, :guilabel:`VAT` secara otomatis "
"diganti dengan PPN generik untuk transaksi luar negeri: `XEXX010101000`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/mexico.rst:1340
msgid ""
"All products involved with external trade have four additional fields that "
"are required, two of which are exclusive to external trade."
msgstr ""
"Semua produk yang terlibat dengan perdagangan eksternal memiliki empat kolom "
"tambahan yang diperlukan, dua di antaranya eksklusif untuk perdagangan "
"eksternal."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/mexico.rst:1343
msgid ""
"The :guilabel:`Reference` of the product must be set in "
"the :guilabel:`General Information` tab."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Reference` produk harus diatur di tab :guilabel:`General "
"Information`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/mexico.rst:1344
msgid ""
"The :guilabel:`Weight` of the product in the :guilabel:`Inventory` tab must "
"be more than `0`."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Weight` produk di tab :guilabel:`Inventaris` harus lebih dari `0`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/mexico.rst:1345
msgid ""
"The `correct  <https://www.ventanillaunica.gob.mx/vucem/"
"Clasificador.html>`_ :guilabel:`Tariff Fraction` of the product must be set "
"in the :guilabel:`Accounting` tab for external trade."
msgstr ""
"`<https://www.ventanillaunica.gob.mx/vucem/Clasificador.html> "
":guilabel:`Tariff Fraction` yang benar` dari produk harus diatur di tab "
":guilabel:`Akuntansi` untuk perdagangan eksternal."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/mexico.rst:1347
msgid ""
"The :guilabel:`UMT Aduana` in the :guilabel:`Accounting` tab must be set and "
"correspond to the :guilabel:`Tariff Fraction` for external trade."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`UMT Aduana` di tab :guilabel:`Akuntansi` harus diatur dan sesuai "
"dengan :guilabel:`Tariff Fraction` untuk perdagangan eksternal."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/mexico.rst:None
msgid "Required external trade product fields."
msgstr "Kolom produk perdagangan eksternal yang diperlukan."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/mexico.rst:1354
msgid ""
"If the UoM code of the :guilabel:`Tariff Fraction` is `01`, the "
"correct :guilabel:`UMT Aduana` is `kg`."
msgstr ""
"Jika kode UoM dari :guilabel:`Tariff Fraction` adalah `01`, :guilabel:`UMT "
"Aduana` yang benar adalah `kg`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/mexico.rst:1356
msgid ""
"If the UoM code of the :guilabel:`Tariff Fraction` is `06`, the "
"correct :guilabel:`UMT Aduana` is `Units`."
msgstr ""
"Jika kode UoM dari :guilabel:`Tariff Fraction` adalah `06`, :guilabel:`UMT "
"Aduana` yang benar adalah `Units`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/mexico.rst:1362
msgid ""
"Before creating an invoice, it is important to take into account that "
"external trade invoices require converting product prices into a foreign "
"currency such as USD. Therefore, :doc:`multicurrency <../accounting/"
"get_started/multi_currency>` **must** be enabled with the foreign currency "
"activated in the :guilabel:`Currencies` section. The "
"correct :guilabel:`Service` to run is :guilabel:`[MX] Bank of Mexico`. To "
"convert product prices, create a :doc:`pricelist <../../sales/sales/"
"products_prices/prices/pricing>` in the foreign currency."
msgstr ""
"Sebelum membuat faktur, penting untuk mempertimbangkan bahwa faktur "
"perdagangan eksternal memerlukan konversi harga produk ke dalam mata uang "
"asing seperti USD. Oleh karena itu, :doc:`multimata uang <../accounting/"
"get_started/multi_currency>` **harus** diaktifkan dengan mata uang asing "
"diaktifkan di bagian :guilabel:`Currencies`. :guilabel:`Service` yang benar "
"untuk dijalankan adalah :guilabel:`[MX] Bank of Mexico`. Untuk mengonversi "
"harga produk, buat :doc:`daftar harga <../../sales/sales/products_prices/"
"prices/pricing>` dalam mata uang asing."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/mexico.rst:1369
msgid ""
"Then, with the correct exchange rate set up in :menuselection:`Accounting --"
"> Settings --> Currency`, set the :guilabel:`Incoterm` and the "
"optional :guilabel:`Certificate Source` fields in the "
"invoice's :guilabel:`Other Info` tab."
msgstr ""
"Kemudian, dengan nilai tukar yang benar diatur di "
":menuselection:`Akuntansi --> Pengaturan --> Mata Uang`, atur kolom "
":guilabel:`Incoterm` dan kolom opsional :guilabel:`Certificate Source` di "
"tab :guilabel:`Other Info` faktur."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/mexico.rst:1374
msgid ""
"While not mandatory, the information will be more complete "
"if :guilabel:`CFDI to public` is also active."
msgstr ""
"Meskipun tidak wajib, informasi akan lebih lengkap jika :guilabel:`CFDI to "
"public` juga aktif."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/mexico.rst:1377
msgid ""
"Finally, confirm the invoice with the same process as a regular invoice, and "
"click the :guilabel:`Send` button to sign it via CFDI."
msgstr ""
"Terakhir, konfirmasikan faktur dengan proses yang sama seperti faktur biasa, "
"dan klik tombol :guilabel:`Send` untuk menandatanganinya melalui CFDI."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/mexico.rst:1385
msgid ""
"The :doc:`Point of sale <../../sales/point_of_sale>` adaptation of the "
"Mexican Localization enables the creation of invoices that comply with the |"
"SAT| requirements directly from the **POS register**, with the added benefit "
"of creating receipt tickets that allow *self-invoicing* in a special portal "
"and creating global invoices."
msgstr ""
"Adaptasi :doc:`POS <../../sales/point_of_sale>` dari Lokalisasi Meksiko "
"memungkinkan pembuatan faktur yang sesuai dengan persyaratan |SAT| langsung "
"dari **register POS**, dengan keuntungan tambahan berupa pembuatan tiket "
"kwitansi yang memungkinkan *faktur mandiri* di portal khusus dan pembuatan "
"faktur global."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/mexico.rst:1393
msgid "Point of sale flow"
msgstr "Alur POS"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/mexico.rst:1395
msgid ""
"On top of the standard :ref:`Point of Sale configuration <pos/use/"
"settings>`, the Mexican localization requires each payment method to be "
"configured with a correct :guilabel:`Payment Way` as well as a :guilabel:`Re-"
"invoicing account` to handle the accounting for invoices with the invoicing "
"portal."
msgstr ""
"Selain :ref:`konfigurasi Point of Sale <pos/use/settings>` standar, "
"lokalisasi Meksiko mengharuskan setiap metode pembayaran dikonfigurasi "
"dengan :guilabel:`Cara Pembayaran` yang benar serta :guilabel:`Akun re-"
"invoicing` untuk menangani akuntansi faktur dengan portal penagihan."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/mexico.rst:1401
msgid ""
"By default, Odoo creates pre-configured payment methods for cash, credit "
"card, and debit card and assigns the :guilabel:`402.04.01 Re-invoicing` "
"account as default for re-invoicing."
msgstr ""
"Secara default, Odoo membuat metode pembayaran yang telah dikonfigurasi "
"sebelumnya untuk tunai, kartu kredit, dan kartu debit serta menetapkan akun "
":guilabel:`402.04.01 Re-invoicing` sebagai default untuk penagihan ulang."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/mexico.rst:1404
msgid ""
"While selling on the **Point of Sale**, click the :guilabel:`Customer` "
"button to either create or select a customer. Here it is possible to review "
"customer invoicing information (such as the |RFC| or :guilabel:`Fiscal "
"Regime`) and even modify it directly inside the session."
msgstr ""
"Saat menjual di **POS**, klik tombol :guilabel:`Customer` untuk membuat atau "
"memilih pelanggan. Di sini dimungkinkan untuk meninjau informasi penagihan "
"pelanggan (seperti |RFC| atau :guilabel:`Fiscal Regime`) dan bahkan "
"memodifikasinya secara langsung di dalam sesi."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/mexico.rst:1408
msgid ""
"After selecting a customer, tick the :icon:`fa-file-text-"
"o` :guilabel:`Invoice` checkbox. This opens a menu to select "
"the :guilabel:`Usage` and to define if it is an invoice to the public. Click "
"confirm, select the payment method, and then click validate to complete the "
"order. The PDF is then downloaded and it is possible to send the invoice via "
"mail to the final customer alongside the receipt."
msgstr ""
"Setelah memilih pelanggan, centang kotak :icon:`fa-file-text-o` "
":guilabel:`Invoice`. Ini akan membuka menu untuk memilih :guilabel:`Usage` "
"dan menentukan apakah ini adalah faktur untuk publik. Klik konfirmasi, pilih "
"metode pembayaran, lalu klik validasi untuk menyelesaikan pesanan. PDF "
"kemudian akan diunduh dan dimungkinkan untuk mengirim faktur melalui email "
"ke pelanggan akhir bersama dengan tanda terima."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/mexico.rst:1415
msgid ""
"To create invoices from orders, go to the :guilabel:`Orders` menu, select "
"the order, click :guilabel:`Load Order`, and tick the :icon:`fa-file-text-"
"o` :guilabel:`Invoice` checkbox. This opens the same menu for "
"the :guilabel:`Usage` and :guilabel:`CFDI to Public`."
msgstr ""
"Untuk membuat faktur dari pesanan, buka menu :guilabel:`Orders`, pilih "
"pesanan, klik :guilabel:`Load Order`, dan centang kotak :icon:`fa-file-text-"
"o` :guilabel:`Invoice`. Ini akan membuka menu yang sama untuk "
":guilabel:`Usage` dan :guilabel:`CFDI to Public`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/mexico.rst:None
msgid "Invoice Configuration for Point of Sale."
msgstr "Konfigurasi Faktur untuk POS."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/mexico.rst:1422
msgid ""
"To sign a credit note automatically, tick the :icon:`fa-file-text-"
"o` :guilabel:`Invoice` checkbox when processing a :ref:`refund <pos/use/"
"refund>`."
msgstr ""
"Untuk menandatangani nota kredit secara otomatis, centang kotak :icon:`fa-"
"file-text-o` :guilabel:`Faktur` saat memproses :ref:`pengembalian dana <pos/"
"use/refund>`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/mexico.rst:1426
msgid ""
"Credit notes for returned products will contain the relation "
"type :guilabel:`03 - Devolución de mercancía sobre facturas o traslados "
"previos`."
msgstr ""
"Nota kredit untuk produk yang dikembalikan akan berisi jenis relasi "
":guilabel:`03 - Devolución de mercancía sobre facturas o traslados previos`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/mexico.rst:1430
msgid ""
"In the Mexican localization, positive and negative lines in a **POS** "
"session cannot be mixed."
msgstr ""
"Dalam lokalisasi Meksiko, baris positif dan negatif dalam sesi **POS** tidak "
"dapat dicampur."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/mexico.rst:1432
msgid ""
"If a |SAT| validation error occurs customer will get a :doc:`Pro-Forma "
"invoice <../../sales/sales/invoicing/proforma>` instead."
msgstr ""
"Jika terjadi kesalahan validasi |SAT|, pelanggan akan mendapatkan "
":doc:`Faktur Pro-Forma <../../sales/sales/invoicing/proforma>` sebagai "
"gantinya."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/mexico.rst:1438
msgid "Self-invoicing portal"
msgstr "Portal faktur mandiri"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/mexico.rst:1440
msgid ""
"If the final customer is not sure if they want to have their invoice "
"generated at the exact moment of the sale, it is possible to give them the "
"option of creating a receipt with either a QR code or a URL. To do so, "
"follow these steps:"
msgstr ""
"Jika pelanggan akhir tidak yakin apakah mereka ingin faktur mereka dibuat "
"pada saat penjualan, dimungkinkan untuk memberi mereka opsi membuat tanda "
"terima dengan kode QR atau URL. Untuk melakukannya, ikuti langkah-langkah "
"berikut:"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/mexico.rst:1444
msgid "Go to :menuselection:`Point of Sale --> Configuration`."
msgstr "Buka :menuselection:`Point of Sale --> Configuration`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/mexico.rst:1445
msgid "Select the :guilabel:`Point of Sale`."
msgstr "Pilih :guilabel:`Point of Sale`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/mexico.rst:1446
msgid "Scroll to the :guilabel:`Bills & Receipts` section."
msgstr "Gulir ke bagian :guilabel:`Bills & Receipts`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/mexico.rst:1447
msgid "Enable :guilabel:`Self-service invoicing`."
msgstr "Aktifkan :guilabel:`Self-service invoicing`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/mexico.rst:1448
msgid ""
"Set the :guilabel:`Print` field to :guilabel:`QR code`, :guilabel:`URL`, "
"or :guilabel:`QR code + URL`."
msgstr ""
"Atur bidang :guilabel:`Print` ke :guilabel:`QR code`, :guilabel:`URL`, atau "
":guilabel:`QR code + URL`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/mexico.rst:1451
msgid ""
"Customers who scan this QR code or follow the URL will access to a menu "
"where they can add their fiscal information, including the *Usage* and "
"*Fiscal Regime* once they enter the five digit code that is also provided on "
"the receipt."
msgstr ""
"Pelanggan yang memindai kode QR ini atau mengikuti URL akan mengakses menu "
"di mana mereka dapat menambahkan informasi fiskal mereka, termasuk *Usage* "
"dan *Fiscal Regime* setelah mereka memasukkan kode lima digit yang juga "
"disediakan pada tanda terima."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/mexico.rst:1455
msgid ""
"On the journal entries of the session, the previously selected **Re-"
"invoicing account** will be used to handle reversals of the sales entries "
"when invoices are requested as well as be used as a sales account for the "
"new invoices."
msgstr ""
"Pada entri jurnal sesi, **Re-invoicing account** yang dipilih sebelumnya "
"akan digunakan untuk menangani pembalikan entri penjualan saat faktur "
"diminta serta digunakan sebagai akun penjualan untuk faktur baru."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/mexico.rst:1460
msgid ":doc:`../../sales/point_of_sale/use/pos_invoices`"
msgstr ":doc:`../../sales/point_of_sale/use/pos_invoices`"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/mexico.rst:1467
msgid ""
"As with regular sales orders, global invoices can also be created from the "
"POS register."
msgstr ""
"Seperti pesanan penjualan biasa, faktur global juga dapat dibuat dari "
"register POS."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/mexico.rst:1469
msgid ""
"For this, make sure not to select a customer or the invoice option in the "
"payment menu and go to :menuselection:`Point of Sale --> Orders --> Orders`. "
"There, select all the orders to invoice, click :icon:`fa-"
"cog` :guilabel:`Actions` and select :guilabel:`Create Global Invoice`."
msgstr ""
"Untuk ini, pastikan untuk tidak memilih pelanggan atau opsi faktur di menu "
"pembayaran dan buka :menuselection:`Point of Sale --> Orders --> Orders`. Di "
"sana, pilih semua pesanan yang akan difaktur, klik :icon:`fa-cog` "
":guilabel:`Actions` dan pilih :guilabel:`Create Global Invoice`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/mexico.rst:1473
msgid ""
"Like with sales orders, choose the correct :guilabel:`Periodicity` and "
"press :guilabel:`Create`."
msgstr ""
"Seperti pesanan penjualan, pilih :guilabel:`Periodicity` yang benar dan "
"tekan :guilabel:`Create`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/mexico.rst:1475
msgid ""
"This attaches an XML file to each of the selected orders. The XML files can "
"be downloaded by going to the :guilabel:`CFDI` tab. If needed, it is "
"possible to cancel the invoice from the same tab."
msgstr ""
"Ini melampirkan file XML ke setiap pesanan yang dipilih. File XML dapat "
"diunduh dengan membuka tab :guilabel:`CFDI`. Jika diperlukan, dimungkinkan "
"untuk membatalkan faktur dari tab yang sama."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/mexico.rst:1478
msgid ""
"If eventually any of the orders that are part of the global invoice need to "
"be addressed to a customer, it is still possible to send an invoice by "
"opening the POS register, clicking the :icon:`fa-bars` :guilabel:`(drop-down "
"menu)`, then click :guilabel:`Orders`. Change the :guilabel:`All active "
"orders` filter to :guilabel:`Paid`, select the order, and click "
"the :icon:`fa-file-text-o` :guilabel:`Invoice` button."
msgstr ""
"Jika pada akhirnya salah satu pesanan yang merupakan bagian dari faktur "
"global perlu ditujukan kepada pelanggan, masih dimungkinkan untuk mengirim "
"faktur dengan membuka register POS, mengklik :icon:`fa-bars` :guilabel:`"
"(menu drop-down)`, kemudian klik :guilabel:`Pesanan`. Ubah filter "
":guilabel:`Semua pesanan aktif` menjadi :guilabel:`Dibayar`, pilih pesanan, "
"dan klik tombol :icon:`fa-file-text-o` :guilabel:`Faktur`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/mexico.rst:1485
msgid ""
"Global invoices, just as regular invoices, can only be grouped by physical "
"address. That is determined by the address set on the POS invoice journal, "
"so when attempting to invoice two addresses a warning will come up to warn "
"the user of the error."
msgstr ""
"Faktur global, sama seperti faktur reguler, hanya dapat dikelompokkan "
"berdasarkan alamat fisik. Hal itu ditentukan oleh alamat yang ditetapkan "
"pada jurnal faktur POS, jadi saat mencoba memfakturkan dua alamat, "
"peringatan akan muncul untuk memperingatkan user tentang kesalahan tersebut."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/mexico.rst:1494
msgid ""
"The eCommerce adaptation of the Mexican Localization provides and extra step "
"to create invoices that comply with the |SAT| requirements "
"on :doc:`eCommerce  <../../websites/ecommerce>` by retrieving the customer "
"data after the **Checkout** and even allowing for the signature of "
"**automatic invoices** after the payment is processed, as well as sending "
"customers the files via email and granting them access to retrieve their PDF "
"file from their own customer portal."
msgstr ""
"Adaptasi eCommerce dari Lokalisasi Meksiko menyediakan langkah tambahan "
"untuk membuat faktur yang sesuai dengan persyaratan |SAT| pada "
":doc:`eCommerce  <../../websites/ecommerce>` dengan mengambil data pelanggan "
"setelah **Checkout** dan bahkan memungkinkan penandatanganan **faktur "
"otomatis** setelah pembayaran diproses, serta mengirimkan file kepada "
"pelanggan melalui email dan memberi mereka akses untuk mengambil file PDF "
"mereka dari portal pelanggan mereka sendiri."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/mexico.rst:1503
msgid "eCommerce flow"
msgstr "Alur eCommerce"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/mexico.rst:1505
msgid ""
"During the regular checkout process, a new :guilabel:`Invoicing Info` step "
"appears, where it is possible to request an invoice or not. "
"If :guilabel:`No` is selected, a **CFDI to Public** is created,. "
"If :guilabel:`Yes` is selected, the :guilabel:`RFC`, :guilabel:`Fiscal "
"Regime`, and :guilabel:`Usage` are required in order to get all information "
"in the sales order, where its status will change to :guilabel:`To Invoice`."
msgstr ""
"Selama proses checkout reguler, langkah :guilabel:`Informasi Penagihan` baru "
"muncul, di mana dimungkinkan untuk meminta faktur atau tidak. Jika "
":guilabel:`Tidak` dipilih, **CFDI untuk Publik** dibuat. Jika :guilabel:`Ya` "
"dipilih, :guilabel:`RFC`, :guilabel:`Rezim Fiskal`, dan "
":guilabel:`Penggunaan` diperlukan untuk mendapatkan semua informasi di sales "
"order, di mana statusnya akan berubah menjadi :guilabel:`Untuk Difaktur`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/mexico.rst:1511
msgid ""
"Additionally the customer can decide whether or not to request :ref:`IEPS "
"Breakdown <l10n/mx/ieps-breakdown>`."
msgstr ""
"Selain itu, pelanggan dapat memutuskan apakah akan meminta :ref:`Rincian "
"IEPS <l10n/mx/ieps-breakdown>` atau tidak."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/mexico.rst:1515
msgid ""
"Make sure to add a :guilabel:`UNSPSC code` to the :ref:`shipping product "
"<ecommerce/checkout/delivery>`."
msgstr ""
"Pastikan untuk menambahkan :guilabel:`kode UNSPSC` ke :ref:`produk "
"pengiriman <ecommerce/checkout/delivery>`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/mexico.rst:1518
msgid ""
"If the :guilabel:`Automatic Invoicing` is enabled "
"in :menuselection:`Settings --> Website --> Invoicing`, the electronic "
"document will be signed automatically."
msgstr ""
"Jika :guilabel:`Penagihan Otomatis` diaktifkan di "
":menuselection:`Pengaturan --> Website --> Penagihan`, dokumen elektronik "
"akan ditandatangani secara otomatis."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/mexico.rst:1526
msgid ""
"The **Sales** app contains fields that make invoicing easier, while the "
"fields themselves do not change the sales behavior, they are directly copied "
"when creating an invoice."
msgstr ""
"Aplikasi **Penjualan** berisi kolom yang membuat penagihan lebih mudah, "
"meskipun kolom itu sendiri tidak mengubah perilaku penjualan, kolom tersebut "
"langsung disalin saat membuat faktur."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/mexico.rst:1529
msgid "The copied fields are:"
msgstr "Kolom yang disalin adalah:"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/mexico.rst:1531
msgid "Payment Way"
msgstr "Cara Pembayaran"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/mexico.rst:1536
msgid ""
"Additionally, it is possible to get a preview of the invoice for validation "
"purposes with the customer by installing the :doc:`pro-forma module <../../"
"sales/sales/invoicing/proforma>`. This module adds the mentioned fields to "
"the sale order as well as:"
msgstr ""
"Selain itu, dimungkinkan untuk mendapatkan pratinjau faktur untuk tujuan "
"validasi dengan pelanggan dengan menginstal :doc:`modul pro-forma <../../"
"sales/sales/invoicing/proforma>`. Modul ini menambahkan kolom yang "
"disebutkan ke sales order serta:"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/mexico.rst:1540
msgid "Product code"
msgstr "Kode produk"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/mexico.rst:1541
msgid "Unit code"
msgstr "Kode unit"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/mexico.rst:1542
msgid "Fiscal regime"
msgstr "Rezim fiskal"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/mexico.rst:1547
msgid "Subscriptions"
msgstr "Langganan"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/mexico.rst:1549
msgid ""
"While handling subscriptions, all the sales fields are used to create the "
"recurrent invoices. These are automatically signed and sent via email with "
"the PDF and XML attached with no additional manual actions required."
msgstr ""
"Saat menangani langganan, semua kolom penjualan digunakan untuk membuat "
"faktur berulang. Faktur ini secara otomatis ditandatangani dan dikirim "
"melalui email dengan PDF dan XML terlampir tanpa tindakan manual tambahan "
"yang diperlukan."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/mexico.rst:1554
msgid ""
"All invoices generated by the subscription app will always be automatically "
"signed with no exceptions."
msgstr ""
"Semua faktur yang dihasilkan oleh aplikasi langganan akan selalu "
"ditandatangani secara otomatis tanpa pengecualian."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/mexico.rst:1560
msgid "Inventory"
msgstr "Stok Persediaan"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/mexico.rst:1565
msgid "Customs numbers"
msgstr "Nomor pabean"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/mexico.rst:1567
msgid ""
"A *customs declaration* (Pedimento Aduanero) is a fiscal document that "
"certifies that all contributions to the fiscal entity (the |SAT|) have been "
"paid for, including the import/export of goods."
msgstr ""
"*Deklarasi pabean* (Pedimento Aduanero) adalah dokumen fiskal yang "
"menyatakan bahwa semua kontribusi kepada entitas fiskal (|SAT|) telah "
"dibayar, termasuk impor/ekspor barang."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/mexico.rst:1571
msgid ""
"According to the `Annex 20 <http://omawww.sat.gob.mx/tramitesyservicios/"
"Paginas/anexo_20.htm>`_ of CFDI 4.0, in documents where the invoiced goods "
"come from a first-hand import operation, the :guilabel:`Customs Number` "
"field needs to be added to all lines of products involved with the "
"operation, as does the date of the document."
msgstr ""
"Menurut `Annex 20 <http://omawww.sat.gob.mx/tramitesyservicios/Paginas/"
"anexo_20.htm>`_ dari CFDI 4.0, dalam dokumen di mana barang yang ditagih "
"berasal dari operasi impor langsung, kolom :guilabel:`Customs Number` perlu "
"ditambahkan ke semua baris produk yang terlibat dengan operasi tersebut, "
"begitu pula tanggal dokumen."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/mexico.rst:1577
msgid ""
"To do so, the :guilabel:`Odoo Mexico Localization for Stock/Landing` "
"`l10n_mx_edi_landing` module must be installed, in addition to "
"the :doc:`Inventory <../../inventory_and_mrp/inventory>`, :doc:`Purchase "
"<../../inventory_and_mrp/purchase>`, and :doc:`Sales <../../sales/sales>` "
"apps."
msgstr ""
"Untuk melakukannya, modul :guilabel:`Lokalisasi Meksiko Odoo untuk Stock/"
"Landing` `l10n_mx_edi_landing` harus diinstal, selain aplikasi "
":doc:`Inventaris <../../inventory_and_mrp/inventory>`, :doc:`Pembelian <../"
"../inventory_and_mrp/purchase>`, dan :doc:`Penjualan <../../sales/sales>`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/mexico.rst:1582
msgid ""
"Do not confuse this feature with external trade. The customs numbers are "
"directly related to importing goods, while the external trade complement is "
"related to exporting. Consult your accountant first if this feature is "
"needed before doing any modifications."
msgstr ""
"Jangan bingungkan fitur ini dengan perdagangan luar negeri. Nomor pabean "
"terkait langsung dengan impor barang, sedangkan komplemen perdagangan luar "
"negeri terkait dengan ekspor. Konsultasikan dengan akuntan Anda terlebih "
"dahulu jika fitur ini diperlukan sebelum melakukan modifikasi apa pun."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/mexico.rst:1589
msgid ""
"In order to track the correct customs number for a specific invoice, Odoo "
"uses :doc:`landed costs <../../inventory_and_mrp/inventory/"
"inventory_valuation/landed_costs>`. Go to :menuselection:`Inventory --> "
"Configuration --> Settings`, and in the :guilabel:`Valuation` section, make "
"sure that :guilabel:`Landed Costs` is activated."
msgstr ""
"Untuk melacak nomor bea cukai yang benar untuk faktur tertentu, Odoo "
"menggunakan :doc:`landed costs <../../inventory_and_mrp/inventory/"
"inventory_valuation/landed_costs>`. Buka :menuselection:`Inventory --> "
"Configuration --> Settings`, dan di bagian :guilabel:`Valuation`, pastikan "
"bahwa :guilabel:`Landed Costs` diaktifkan."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/mexico.rst:1595
msgid ""
"It is recommended to add a :guilabel:`Default Journal` to automatically fill "
"the mandatory :guilabel:`Journal` field on landed costs even though landed "
"costs that only add customs numbers without adding :guilabel:`Additional "
"Costs` do not create journal entries."
msgstr ""
"Disarankan untuk menambahkan :guilabel:`Default Journal` untuk secara "
"otomatis mengisi kolom :guilabel:`Journal` yang wajib pada biaya landed cost "
"meskipun biaya landed cost yang hanya menambahkan nomor pabean tanpa "
"menambahkan :guilabel:`Additional Costs` tidak membuat entri jurnal."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/mexico.rst:1599
msgid ""
"Configure the **goods-type** products that hold the customs numbers. To do "
"so, create the products and complete these three requirements:"
msgstr ""
"Konfigurasikan produk **goods-type** yang menyimpan nomor pabean. Untuk "
"melakukannya, buat produk dan lengkapi tiga persyaratan berikut:"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/mexico.rst:1602
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Tracking` **must** be set to either :guilabel:`By Lots` "
"or :guilabel:`By Unique Serial Number` but **not** :guilabel:`By Quantity`."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Tracking` **harus** diatur ke :guilabel:`By Lots` atau "
":guilabel:`By Unique Serial Number` tetapi **tidak** :guilabel:`By Quantity`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/mexico.rst:1604
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Invoicing Policy` **must** be set to :guilabel:`Delivered "
"quantities`."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Invoicing Policy` **harus** diatur ke :guilabel:`Delivered "
"quantities`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/mexico.rst:1605
msgid ""
":doc:`Valuation by lots/serial numbers <../../inventory_and_mrp/inventory/"
"inventory_valuation/valuation_by_lots>` **must** be enabled."
msgstr ""
":doc:`Valuation by lots/serial numbers <../../inventory_and_mrp/inventory/"
"inventory_valuation/valuation_by_lots>` **harus** diaktifkan."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/mexico.rst:1608
msgid ""
"This will make the field :guilabel:`Customs invoicing` available on "
"the :guilabel:`Accounting` tab. Enable the field to use customs numbers with "
"this product."
msgstr ""
"Ini akan membuat kolom :guilabel:`Customs invoicing` tersedia pada tab "
":guilabel:`Akuntansi`. Aktifkan kolom tersebut untuk menggunakan nomor bea "
"cukai dengan produk ini."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/mexico.rst:1611
msgid ""
"It is important to make sure the product has a :guilabel:`Product Category` "
"and has the following configuration:"
msgstr ""
"Penting untuk memastikan produk memiliki :guilabel:`Product Category` dan "
"memiliki konfigurasi berikut:"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/mexico.rst:1614
msgid ":guilabel:`Costing Method`: Either :guilabel:`FIFO` or :guilabel:`AVCO`"
msgstr ":guilabel:`Metode Biaya`: Baik :guilabel:`FIFO` atau :guilabel:`AVCO`"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/mexico.rst:1615
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Inventory Valuation`: Either :guilabel:`Periodic` "
"or :guilabel:`Perpetual`"
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Inventory Valuation`: Baik :guilabel:`Periodic` atau "
":guilabel:`Perpetual`"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/mexico.rst:1618
msgid ""
"The feature works regardless of whether the :doc:`inventory valuation <../../"
"inventory_and_mrp/inventory/inventory_valuation/cheat_sheet>` is set to "
"either :guilabel:`Periodic (at closing)` or :guilabel:`Perpetual (at "
"invoicing)`."
msgstr ""
"Fitur ini berfungsi terlepas dari apakah :doc:`inventory valuation <../../"
"inventory_and_mrp/inventory/inventory_valuation/cheat_sheet>` diatur ke "
":guilabel:`Periodic (at closing)` atau :guilabel:`Perpetual (at invoicing)`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/mexico.rst:None
msgid "Storable products general configuration."
msgstr "Konfigurasi umum produk yang dapat disimpan."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/mexico.rst:None
msgid "Storable product category configuration."
msgstr "Konfigurasi kategori produk yang dapat disimpan."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/mexico.rst:1629
msgid "Purchase and sales flow"
msgstr "Alur pembelian dan penjualan"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/mexico.rst:1631
msgid ""
"After configuring the product, follow the standard :doc:`purchase flow "
"<../../inventory_and_mrp/purchase>`."
msgstr ""
"Setelah mengkonfigurasi produk, ikuti :doc:`alur pembelian <../../"
"inventory_and_mrp/purchase>` standar."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/mexico.rst:1634
msgid ""
"Create a purchase order from :menuselection:`Purchase --> Orders --> "
"Purchase Order`. Then, confirm the order to display a :guilabel:`Receipt` "
"smart button. Click the :guilabel:`Receipt` smart button "
"and :guilabel:`Validate` the receipt."
msgstr ""
"Buat pesanan pembelian dari :menuselection:`Pembelian --> Pesanan --> "
"Pesanan Pembelian`. Kemudian, konfirmasi pesanan untuk menampilkan tombol "
"pintar :guilabel:`Penerimaan`. Klik tombol pintar :guilabel:`Penerimaan` dan "
":guilabel:`Validasi` penerimaan."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/mexico.rst:1638
msgid ""
"Go to :menuselection:`Inventory --> Operations --> Landed Costs`, and create "
"a new record. In the :guilabel:`Transfer`, add the receipt that was just "
"validated, and add the :guilabel:`Customs number`."
msgstr ""
"Buka :menuselection:`Inventaris --> Operations --> Landed Costs`, dan buat "
"catatan baru. Di :guilabel:`Transfer`, tambahkan penerimaan yang baru saja "
"divalidasi, dan tambahkan :guilabel:`Customs number`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/mexico.rst:1643
msgid ""
"While it is possible to add costs related to the customs number at this "
"stage of the process, it is highly recommended to create a landed cost from "
"a vendor bill from your customs agent. Learn more about :doc:`Landed Costs "
"here <../../inventory_and_mrp/inventory/inventory_valuation/landed_costs>`."
msgstr ""
"Meskipun memungkinkan untuk menambahkan biaya terkait nomor bea cukai pada "
"tahap proses ini, sangat disarankan untuk membuat landed cost dari tagihan "
"vendor dari agen bea cukai Anda. Pelajari lebih lanjut tentang :doc:`Landed "
"Costs di sini <../../inventory_and_mrp/inventory/inventory_valuation/"
"landed_costs>`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/mexico.rst:1649
msgid ""
"The :guilabel:`Customs number` field is not editable once it is set, and "
"cannot be repeated, however it is possible to fix the number on the lot or "
"serial number later by selecting a different landed cost."
msgstr ""
"Kolom :guilabel:`Customs number` tidak dapat diedit setelah ditetapkan, dan "
"tidak dapat diulang, namun dimungkinkan untuk memperbaiki nomor pada lot "
"atau nomor seri nanti dengan memilih landed cost yang berbeda."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/mexico.rst:None
msgid "Customs number on a landed costs Inventory record."
msgstr "Nomor bea cukai pada catatan Inventaris landed costs."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/mexico.rst:1656
msgid ""
"The customs number assigned to a specific lot or serial number can be found "
"on the its registry on :menuselection:`Inventory --> Products --> Lots/"
"Serial Numbers`. The :guilabel:`L10N Mx Edi Landed Cost` field can be edited "
"at any time to fix any mistakes that could have occurred when registering "
"the landed cost. Editing the :guilabel:`L10N Mx Edi Landed Cost` field "
"automatically updates the :guilabel:`Customs number` and the name of the lot "
"or serial number."
msgstr ""
"Nomor bea cukai yang ditetapkan untuk lot atau nomor seri tertentu dapat "
"ditemukan pada registrinya di :menuselection:`Inventaris --> Products --> "
"Lots/Serial Numbers`. Kolom :guilabel:`L10N Mx Edi Landed Cost` dapat diedit "
"kapan saja untuk memperbaiki kesalahan yang mungkin terjadi saat "
"mendaftarkan landed cost. Mengedit kolom :guilabel:`L10N Mx Edi Landed Cost` "
"secara otomatis memperbarui :guilabel:`Customs number` dan nama lot atau "
"nomor seri."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/mexico.rst:1662
msgid ""
"Next, create a sales order and confirm it. Click the :guilabel:`Delivery` "
"smart button that appears, and carefully review the assigned lots/serial "
"numbers to make sure they are the desired values, after "
"that :guilabel:`Validate` the delivery order."
msgstr ""
"Selanjutnya, buat sales order dan konfirmasi. Klik tombol pintar "
":guilabel:`Pengiriman` yang muncul, dan periksa dengan cermat lot/nomor seri "
"yang ditetapkan untuk memastikan nilainya sesuai yang diinginkan, setelah "
"itu :guilabel:`Validasi` surat jalan."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/mexico.rst:1666
msgid ""
"Finally, :ref:`create an invoice from the sales order <accounting/inv-"
"process/so>`, and confirm it. The invoice lines are created according to the "
"distribution of the delivery order, in cases where more than one customs "
"number were selected, Odoo will split the invoice lines by quantity and "
"customs numbers."
msgstr ""
"Terakhir, :ref:`buat invoice dari sales order <accounting/inv-process/so>`, "
"dan konfirmasi. Baris invoice dibuat sesuai dengan distribusi surat jalan, "
"dalam kasus di mana lebih dari satu nomor bea cukai dipilih, Odoo akan "
"memisahkan baris invoice berdasarkan kuantitas dan nomor bea cukai."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/mexico.rst:None
msgid "Customs number on confirmed sales order product."
msgstr "Nomor bea cukai pada produk Sales Order yang dikonfirmasi."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/mexico.rst:1679
msgid ""
"A `Carta Porte <https://www.sat.gob.mx/portal/public/tramites/complemento-"
"carta-porte>`_ is a bill of lading: a document that states the type, "
"quantity, and destination of goods being carried."
msgstr ""
"`Carta Porte <https://www.sat.gob.mx/portal/public/tramites/complemento-"
"carta-porte>`_ adalah surat jalan: dokumen yang menyatakan jenis, kuantitas, "
"dan tujuan barang yang dibawa."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/mexico.rst:1682
msgid ""
"On July 17th, 2024, version 3.1 of this |CFDI| was implemented for all "
"transportation providers, intermediaries, and owners of goods. Odoo is able "
"to generate a document type \"T\" (Traslado), which, unlike other documents, "
"is created in a delivery order instead of an invoice or payment."
msgstr ""
"Pada 17 Juli 2024, versi 3.1 dari |CFDI| ini diterapkan untuk semua penyedia "
"transportasi, perantara, dan pemilik barang. Odoo dapat menghasilkan dokumen "
"tipe \"T\" (Traslado), yang berbeda dari dokumen lainnya, dibuat dalam surat "
"jalan dan bukan di faktur atau pembayaran."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/mexico.rst:1686
msgid ""
"Odoo can create XML and PDF files with (or without) ground transport, and "
"can process materials that are treated as *Dangerous Hazards*."
msgstr ""
"Odoo dapat membuat file XML dan PDF dengan (atau tanpa) transportasi darat, "
"dan dapat memproses material yang diperlakukan sebagai *Bahaya Berbahaya*."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/mexico.rst:1689
msgid ""
"In order to print the PDF, the delivery order must be signed by the "
"government and then it can be printed using the :guilabel:`Print Carta "
"Porte` button on the delivery order."
msgstr ""
"Untuk mencetak PDF, surat jalan harus ditandatangani oleh pemerintah dan "
"kemudian dapat dicetak menggunakan tombol :guilabel:`Print Carta Porte` pada "
"surat jalan."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/mexico.rst:1693
msgid ""
"The PDF file contains a QR code to verify the CCP code for the authorities."
msgstr ""
"File PDF berisi kode QR untuk memverifikasi kode CCP untuk pihak berwenang."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/mexico.rst:1695
msgid ""
"In order to transport goods between warehouses, the logistic route must "
"contain a **Delivery** type of operation."
msgstr ""
"Untuk mengangkut barang antar gudang, rute logistik harus berisi operasi "
"tipe **Pengiriman**."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/mexico.rst:1699
msgid ""
":doc:`Inter-warehouse replenishment <../../inventory_and_mrp/inventory/"
"warehouses_storage/replenishment/resupply_warehouses>`"
msgstr ""
":doc:`Pengisian ulang antar-gudang <../../inventory_and_mrp/inventory/"
"warehouses_storage/replenishment/resupply_warehouses>`"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/mexico.rst:1703
msgid ""
"In order to use this feature, the :guilabel:`Mexico - Electronic Delivery "
"Guide` `l10n_mx_edi_stock` module must be installed."
msgstr ""
"Untuk menggunakan fitur ini, modul :guilabel:`Mexico - Electronic Delivery "
"Guide` `l10n_mx_edi_stock` harus diinstal."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/mexico.rst:1706
msgid ""
"Additionally, it is necessary to have the :doc:`Inventory <../../"
"inventory_and_mrp/inventory>` and :doc:`Sales <../../sales/sales>` apps "
"installed."
msgstr ""
"Selain itu, aplikasi :doc:`Inventaris <../../inventory_and_mrp/inventory>` "
"dan :doc:`Penjualan <../../sales/sales>` harus diinstal."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/mexico.rst:1710
msgid ""
"Odoo does not support Carta Porte type document type \"I\" (Ingreso), air, "
"train or marine transport."
msgstr ""
"Odoo tidak mendukung dokumen Carta Porte tipe \"I\" (Ingreso), transportasi "
"udara, kereta api, atau laut."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/mexico.rst:1713
msgid ""
"Consult your accountant first if this feature is needed before doing any "
"modifications."
msgstr ""
"Konsultasikan dengan akuntan Anda terlebih dahulu jika fitur ini diperlukan "
"sebelum melakukan modifikasi apapun."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/mexico.rst:1718
msgid ""
"Odoo manages two different types of CFDI type \"T\". Both can be created "
"from either :doc:`incoming shipments or delivery orders <../../"
"inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/daily_operations>`."
msgstr ""
"Odoo mengelola dua tipe CFDI tipe \"T\" yang berbeda. Keduanya dapat dibuat "
"dari :doc:`pengiriman masuk atau surat jalan <../../inventory_and_mrp/"
"inventory/shipping_receiving/daily_operations>`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/mexico.rst:1722
msgid ""
":guilabel:`No Federal Highways` is used when the :guilabel:`Distance to "
"Destination` is `less than 30 km <http://omawww.sat.gob.mx/cartaporte/"
"Paginas/documentos/PreguntasFrecuentes_Autotransporte.pdf>`_."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`No Federal Highways` digunakan ketika :guilabel:`Distance to "
"Destination` `kurang dari 30 km <http://omawww.sat.gob.mx/cartaporte/Paginas/"
"documentos/PreguntasFrecuentes_Autotransporte.pdf>`_."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/mexico.rst:1725
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Federal Transport` is used when the :guilabel:`Distance to "
"Destination` exceeds 30 km."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Federal Transport` digunakan ketika :guilabel:`Distance to "
"Destination` melebihi 30 km."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/mexico.rst:1727
msgid ""
"For No Federal Highways, no other configuration is required beyond the "
"standard requirements of regular invoicing (the |RFC| of the customer, the "
"UNSPSC code, etc.)."
msgstr ""
"Untuk Tanpa Jalan Raya Federal, tidak ada konfigurasi lain yang diperlukan "
"selain persyaratan standar penagihan reguler (|RFC| pelanggan, kode UNSPSC, "
"dll.)."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/mexico.rst:1730
msgid ""
"For *Federal Transport*, several configurations have to be added to "
"contacts, vehicle setups, and products. Those configurations are then "
"included in the XML and PDF files."
msgstr ""
"Untuk *Federal Transport*, beberapa konfigurasi harus ditambahkan ke kontak, "
"pengaturan kendaraan, dan produk. Konfigurasi tersebut kemudian disertakan "
"dalam file XML dan PDF."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/mexico.rst:1734
msgid "Contacts and vehicles"
msgstr "Kontak dan kendaraan"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/mexico.rst:1736
msgid ""
"Like the external trade feature, the :guilabel:`Address` in both the company "
"and the final customer must be complete. The :guilabel:`ZIP` "
"code, :guilabel:`City`, and :guilabel:`State` must coincide with the "
"`Official SAT Catalog for Carta Porte <http://omawww.sat.gob.mx/"
"tramitesyservicios/Paginas/catalogos_emision_cfdi_complemento_ce.htm>`_."
msgstr ""
"Seperti fitur perdagangan eksternal, :guilabel:`Address` baik pada "
"perusahaan maupun pelanggan akhir harus lengkap. Kode :guilabel:`ZIP`, "
":guilabel:`City`, dan :guilabel:`State` harus sesuai dengan `Katalog SAT "
"Resmi untuk Carta Porte <http://omawww.sat.gob.mx/tramitesyservicios/Paginas/"
"catalogos_emision_cfdi_complemento_ce.htm>`_."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/mexico.rst:1742
msgid "The :guilabel:`Locality` field is optional for both addresses."
msgstr "Kolom :guilabel:`Locality` bersifat opsional untuk kedua alamat."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/mexico.rst:1745
msgid ""
"The origin address used for the delivery guide is set "
"in :menuselection:`Inventory --> Configuration --> Warehouses`. While this "
"is set as the company address by default, you can change it to your correct "
"warehouse address."
msgstr ""
"Alamat asal yang digunakan untuk panduan pengiriman diatur di "
":menuselection:`Inventory --> Configuration --> Warehouses`. Meskipun ini "
"diatur sebagai alamat perusahaan secara default, Anda dapat mengubahnya ke "
"alamat gudang yang benar."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/mexico.rst:1749
msgid ""
"This feature requires the use of :doc:`Fleet <../../hr/fleet/new_vehicle>` "
"to manage vehicles. The vehicle setup is managed directly on the vehicle, "
"and all the required fields are only visible after checking "
"the :guilabel:`L10N Mx Is Freight Vehicle` field."
msgstr ""
"Fitur ini memerlukan penggunaan :doc:`Armada <../../hr/fleet/new_vehicle>` "
"untuk mengelola kendaraan. Pengaturan kendaraan dikelola langsung pada "
"kendaraan, dan semua kolom yang diperlukan hanya terlihat setelah mencentang "
"kolom :guilabel:`L10N Mx Is Freight Vehicle`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/mexico.rst:1753
msgid ""
"Checking the :guilabel:`L10N Mx Is Freight Vehicle` field displays "
"the :guilabel:`MX Parameters` tab where the mandatory fields are required to "
"create a correct delivery guide. Additionally the vehicle **must** contain "
"a :guilabel:`License Plate`, a :guilabel:`Model Year`, and "
"a :guilabel:`Driver`."
msgstr ""
"Mencentang kolom :guilabel:`L10N Mx Is Freight Vehicle` menampilkan tab "
":guilabel:`MX Parameters` di mana kolom wajib diperlukan untuk membuat "
"panduan pengiriman yang benar. Selain itu kendaraan **harus** berisi "
":guilabel:`License Plate`, :guilabel:`Model Year`, dan :guilabel:`Driver`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/mexico.rst:1758
msgid ""
"The :guilabel:`Vehicle Plate Number` and :guilabel:`Number Plate` fields "
"must contain between 5 and 7 characters."
msgstr ""
"Kolom :guilabel:`Vehicle Plate Number` dan :guilabel:`Number Plate` harus "
"berisi antara 5 dan 7 karakter."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/mexico.rst:1761
msgid ""
"The main driver of the vehicle is set directly on the :guilabel:`Driver` "
"field, and it is possible to add more vehicle operators in "
"the :guilabel:`Intermediaries` section. The only mandatory fields for driver "
"contacts are the :guilabel:`VAT` and :guilabel:`Operator License`."
msgstr ""
"Pengemudi utama kendaraan ditetapkan langsung pada kolom :guilabel:`Driver`, "
"dan dimungkinkan untuk menambahkan lebih banyak operator kendaraan di bagian "
":guilabel:`Intermediaries`. Satu-satunya kolom wajib untuk kontak pengemudi "
"adalah :guilabel:`VAT` dan :guilabel:`Operator License`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/mexico.rst:None
msgid "Delivery guide vehicle configuration."
msgstr "Konfigurasi kendaraan panduan pengiriman."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/mexico.rst:1769
msgid ""
"If the vehicle is rented or more intermediaries are required, it is possible "
"to add them in the :guilabel:`Intermediaries` field."
msgstr ""
"Jika kendaraan disewa atau lebih banyak perantara diperlukan, dimungkinkan "
"untuk menambahkannya di kolom :guilabel:`Intermediaries`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/mexico.rst:1775
msgid ""
"Similar to regular invoicing, all products must have a :guilabel:`UNSPSC "
"category`. In addition to this, there are two extra configurations for "
"products involved in delivery guides:"
msgstr ""
"Mirip dengan penagihan reguler, semua produk harus memiliki "
":guilabel:`kategori UNSPSC`. Selain itu, ada dua konfigurasi tambahan untuk "
"produk yang terlibat dalam panduan pengiriman:"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/mexico.rst:1778
msgid ""
"The :guilabel:`Product Type` must be set as :guilabel:`Storable Product` for "
"stock movements to be created."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Jenis Produk` harus diatur sebagai :guilabel:`Produk yang Dapat "
"Disimpan` agar pergerakan stok dapat dibuat."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/mexico.rst:1780
msgid ""
"In the :guilabel:`Inventory` tab, the :guilabel:`Weight` field must be more "
"than `0`."
msgstr ""
"Di tab :guilabel:`Inventaris`, kolom :guilabel:`Weight` harus lebih dari `0`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/mexico.rst:1783
msgid ""
"Creating a delivery guide of a product with the :guilabel:`Weight` set to "
"`0` will trigger an error. As the :guilabel:`Weight` is immediately stored "
"in the delivery order, it is then necessary to return the products and "
"recreate the delivery order (and delivery guide) with the correct values."
msgstr ""
"Membuat panduan pengiriman dari produk dengan :guilabel:`Weight` yang diatur "
"ke `0` akan memicu error. Karena :guilabel:`Weight` segera disimpan dalam "
"order pengiriman, maka perlu mengembalikan produk dan membuat ulang order "
"pengiriman (dan panduan pengiriman) dengan nilai yang benar."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/mexico.rst:1789
msgid "Sales and inventory flow"
msgstr "Alur penjualan dan inventaris"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/mexico.rst:1791
msgid ""
"To create a delivery guide, first create and confirm a sales order "
"from :menuselection:`Sales --> Sales Order`. Click the :guilabel:`Delivery` "
"smart button that is generated, and :guilabel:`Validate` the transfer."
msgstr ""
"Untuk membuat panduan pengiriman, pertama buat dan konfirmasi sales order "
"dari :menuselection:`Penjualan --> Sales Order`. Klik tombol pintar "
":guilabel:`Delivery` yang dihasilkan, dan :guilabel:`Validate` transfer "
"tersebut."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/mexico.rst:1795
msgid ""
"After the status is set to :guilabel:`Done`, you can edit the transfer, and "
"select the :guilabel:`Transport Type` in the :guilabel:`Additional Info` tab."
msgstr ""
"Setelah status diatur ke :guilabel:`Selesai`, Anda dapat mengedit transfer, "
"dan memilih :guilabel:`Jenis Transportasi` di tab :guilabel:`Info Tambahan`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/mexico.rst:1798
msgid ""
"If using the :guilabel:`No Federal Highways` :guilabel:`Transport Type`, "
"save the transfer, and then click :guilabel:`Generate Delivery Guide`. The "
"resulting XML can be found in the chatter."
msgstr ""
"Jika menggunakan :guilabel:`Jenis Transportasi` :guilabel:`Tanpa Jalan Tol "
"Federal`, simpan transfer, lalu klik :guilabel:`Buat Panduan Pengiriman`. "
"XML yang dihasilkan dapat ditemukan di chatter."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/mexico.rst:1802
msgid ""
"Other than the :guilabel:`UNSPSC` on all products, delivery guides that "
"use :guilabel:`No Federal Highways` do not require any special configuration "
"to be sent to the government, as they are a type \"T\" CFDI with no delivery "
"guide complement."
msgstr ""
"Selain :guilabel:`UNSPSC` pada semua produk, panduan pengiriman yang "
"menggunakan :guilabel:`No Federal Highways` tidak memerlukan konfigurasi "
"khusus untuk dikirim ke pemerintah, karena merupakan CFDI tipe \"T\" tanpa "
"komplemen panduan pengiriman."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/mexico.rst:1806
msgid ""
"If using the :guilabel:`Federal Transport` :guilabel:`Transport Type`, "
"the :guilabel:`Vehicle Setup` is displayed to be selected. "
"The :guilabel:`Gross vehicle weight` is taken from the :guilabel:`Vehicle "
"setup` configuration where it is possible to add additional :guilabel:`Extra "
"weight` to account for the drivers and luggage."
msgstr ""
"Jika menggunakan :guilabel:`Federal Transport` :guilabel:`Transport Type`, "
":guilabel:`Vehicle Setup` akan ditampilkan untuk dipilih. :guilabel:`Gross "
"vehicle weight` diambil dari konfigurasi :guilabel:`Vehicle setup` di mana "
"dimungkinkan untuk menambahkan :guilabel:`Extra weight` tambahan untuk "
"memperhitungkan pengemudi dan bagasi."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/mexico.rst:1812
msgid ""
"Odoo will calculate the :guilabel:`Gross vehicle weight` with the following "
"formula:"
msgstr ""
"Odoo akan menghitung :guilabel:`Gross vehicle weight` dengan rumus berikut:"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/mexico.rst:1814
msgid ""
"Gross vehicle weight = Vehicle weight + (Weight + Extra Weight) / 1000\n"
"\n"
msgstr ""
"Gross vehicle weight = Vehicle weight + (Weight + Extra Weight) / 1000\n"
"\n"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/mexico.rst:1817
msgid ""
"Every delivery requires a value in :guilabel:`Distance to Destination (KM)` "
"greater than `0`. Finally, enter the :guilabel:`Delivery Date` and "
"click :guilabel:`Generate Delivery Guide`."
msgstr ""
"Setiap pengiriman memerlukan nilai di :guilabel:`Distance to Destination (KM)"
"` lebih besar dari `0`. Terakhir, masukkan :guilabel:`Delivery Date` dan "
"klik :guilabel:`Generate Delivery Guide`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/mexico.rst:1821
msgid ""
"By default the :guilabel:`Scheduled Date` is filled and represents the time "
"at which the shipment leaves the warehouse and the :guilabel:`Delivery Date` "
"is the time that the shipment is expected to arrive at its destination. "
"These values are declared in both the XML and PDF."
msgstr ""
"Secara default :guilabel:`Scheduled Date` terisi dan mewakili waktu saat "
"pengiriman meninggalkan gudang dan :guilabel:`Delivery Date` adalah waktu "
"pengiriman diharapkan tiba di tujuan. Nilai-nilai ini dideklarasikan di XML "
"dan PDF."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/mexico.rst:1826
msgid "Dangerous hazards"
msgstr "Bahaya berbahaya"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/mexico.rst:1828
msgid ""
"Certain values in the :guilabel:`UNSPSC Category` are considered in the "
"`official SAT catalog <http://omawww.sat.gob.mx/tramitesyservicios/Paginas/"
"complemento_carta_porte.htm>`_ as *dangerous hazards*. These categories need "
"additional considerations when creating a delivery guide "
"with :guilabel:`Federal Transport`."
msgstr ""
"Nilai tertentu dalam :guilabel:`Kategori UNSPSC` dianggap dalam katalog "
"resmi SAT<http://omawww.sat.gob.mx/tramitesyservicios/Paginas/"
"complemento_carta_porte.htm> sebagai *bahaya berbahaya*. Kategori ini "
"memerlukan pertimbangan tambahan saat membuat panduan pengiriman dengan "
":guilabel:`Transportasi Federal`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/mexico.rst:1833
msgid ""
"First, select the product from :menuselection:`Inventory --> Products --> "
"Products`. Then, in the :guilabel:`Accounting` tab, fill "
"the :guilabel:`Hazardous Material Designation Code` and :guilabel:`Hazardous "
"Packaging` fields with the correct code from the |SAT| catalog."
msgstr ""
"Pertama, pilih produk dari :menuselection:`Inventaris --> Produk --> "
"Produk`. Kemudian, di tab :guilabel:`Akuntansi`, isi kolom :guilabel:`Kode "
"Penetapan Bahan Berbahaya` dan :guilabel:`Kemasan Berbahaya` dengan kode "
"yang benar dari katalog |SAT|."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/mexico.rst:None
msgid "Delivery guide hazardous material product required fields."
msgstr "Kolom wajib produk bahan berbahaya panduan pengiriman."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/mexico.rst:1841
msgid ""
"There exists the possibility that a :guilabel:`UNSPSC Category` may or may "
"not be a dangerous hazard (for example *01010101*). If it is not dangerous, "
"enter `0` in the :guilabel:`Hazardous Material Designation Code` field."
msgstr ""
"Ada kemungkinan bahwa :guilabel:`Kategori UNSPSC` mungkin merupakan atau "
"bukan bahaya berbahaya (misalnya *01010101*). Jika tidak berbahaya, masukkan "
"`0` di kolom :guilabel:`Kode Penetapan Bahan Berbahaya`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/mexico.rst:1845
msgid ""
"In :guilabel:`MX Parameters`, complete the :guilabel:`Environment Insurer` "
"and :guilabel:`Environment Insurance Policy` as well. After this, continue "
"with the regular process to create a delivery guide."
msgstr ""
"Di :guilabel:`MX Parameters`, lengkapi :guilabel:`Environment Insurer` dan "
":guilabel:`Environment Insurance Policy` juga. Setelah ini, lanjutkan dengan "
"proses reguler untuk membuat panduan pengiriman."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/mexico.rst:1850
msgid "Imports and Exports"
msgstr "Impor dan Ekspor"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/mexico.rst:1852
msgid ""
"If your Carta Porte is for international operations (for exports), some "
"additional fields need to be taken into account."
msgstr ""
"Jika Carta Porte Anda untuk operasi internasional (untuk ekspor), beberapa "
"kolom tambahan perlu diperhatikan."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/mexico.rst:1855
msgid ""
"First, make sure that all relevant :guilabel:`Products` have the following "
"configuration:"
msgstr ""
"Pertama, pastikan bahwa semua :guilabel:`Produk` yang relevan memiliki "
"konfigurasi berikut:"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/mexico.rst:1857
msgid ""
":guilabel:`UNSPSC Category` cannot be :guilabel:`01010101 Does not exist in "
"the catalog`."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Kategori UNSPSC` tidak boleh :guilabel:`01010101 Tidak ada dalam "
"katalog`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/mexico.rst:1858
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Tariff Fraction` and :guilabel:`UMT Aduana` must be set, similar "
"to the :ref:`external trade <l10n/mx/external-trade>` flow."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Fraksi Tarif` dan :guilabel:`UMT Aduana` harus diatur, mirip "
"dengan alur :ref:`perdagangan eksternal <l10n/mx/external-trade>`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/mexico.rst:1860
msgid ":guilabel:`Material Type` must be set."
msgstr ":guilabel:`Jenis Material` harus diatur."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/mexico.rst:1862
msgid ""
"Then, when creating a :guilabel:`Delivery Guide` from a delivery or receipt, "
"fill the following fields:"
msgstr ""
"Kemudian, saat membuat :guilabel:`Panduan Pengiriman` dari pengiriman atau "
"penerimaan, isi kolom berikut:"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/mexico.rst:1865
msgid ":guilabel:`Customs Regimes`"
msgstr ":guilabel:`Rezim Bea Cukai`"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/mexico.rst:1866
msgid ":guilabel:`Customs Document Type`"
msgstr ":guilabel:`Jenis Dokumen Bea Cukai`"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/mexico.rst:1867
msgid ":guilabel:`Customs Document Identification`"
msgstr ":guilabel:`Identifikasi Dokumen Bea Cukai`"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/mexico.rst:1869
msgid ""
"Then, when creating a :guilabel:`Delivery Guide` for a receipt where "
"the :guilabel:`Customs Document Type` is :guilabel:`Customs number`, two new "
"fields appear: :guilabel:`Customs Number` and :guilabel:`Importer`."
msgstr ""
"Kemudian, saat membuat :guilabel:`Delivery Guide` untuk penerimaan di mana "
":guilabel:`Customs Document Type` adalah :guilabel:`Customs number`, dua "
"field baru muncul: :guilabel:`Customs Number` dan :guilabel:`Importer`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/mexico.rst:1874
msgid ""
"The field :guilabel:`Customs Number` should follow the pattern `xx xx xxxx "
"xxxxxxx`. For example, `15 48 3009 0001235` with **Two** spaces between text."
msgstr ""
"Field :guilabel:`Customs Number` harus mengikuti pola `xx xx xxxx xxxxxxx`. "
"Misalnya, `15 48 3009 0001235` dengan **Dua** spasi di antara teks."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/netherlands.rst:6
msgid ""
":doc:`Documentation on e-invoicing’s legality and compliance in the "
"Netherlands <../accounting/customer_invoices/electronic_invoicing/"
"netherlands>`"
msgstr ""
":doc:`Dokumentasi tentang legalitas dan kepatuhan e-invoicing di Belanda <../"
"accounting/customer_invoices/electronic_invoicing/netherlands>`"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/netherlands.rst:10
msgid "XAF Export"
msgstr "Ekspor XAF"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/netherlands.rst:12
msgid ""
"With the Dutch accounting localization installed, you will be able to export "
"all your accounting entries in XAF format. For this, you have to go "
"in :menuselection:`Accounting --> Reporting --> General Ledger`, you define "
"the entries you want to export using the filters (period, journals, ...) and "
"then you click on the button **EXPORT (XAF)**."
msgstr ""
"Dengan lokalisasi akuntansi Belanda terpasang, Anda dapat mengekspor semua "
"entri akuntansi Anda dalam format XAF. Untuk ini, Anda harus masuk ke "
":menuselection:`Akuntansi --> Pelaporan --> Buku Besar`, tentukan entri yang "
"ingin Anda ekspor menggunakan filter (periode, jurnal, ...) lalu klik tombol "
"**EKSPOR (XAF)**."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/netherlands.rst:19
msgid "Dutch Accounting Reports"
msgstr "Laporan Akuntansi Belanda"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/netherlands.rst:21
msgid ""
"If you install the Dutch accounting localization, you will have access to "
"some reports that are specific to the Netherlands such as :"
msgstr ""
"Jika Anda memasang lokalisasi akuntansi Belanda, Anda akan memiliki akses ke "
"beberapa laporan yang khusus untuk Belanda seperti:"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/netherlands.rst:25
msgid "Tax Report (Aangifte omzetbelasting)"
msgstr "Laporan Pajak (Aangifte omzetbelasting)"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/netherlands.rst:26
msgid "Intrastat Report (ICP)"
msgstr "Laporan Intrastat (ICP)"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/new_zealand.rst:3
msgid "New Zealand"
msgstr "New Zealand"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/new_zealand.rst:10
msgid ""
"The following modules related to the New Zealand localization are available:"
msgstr "Modul berikut yang terkait dengan lokalisasi Selandia Baru tersedia:"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/new_zealand.rst:19
msgid ":guilabel:`New Zealand - Accounting`"
msgstr ":guilabel:`Selandia Baru - Akuntansi`"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/new_zealand.rst:20
msgid "`l10n_nz`"
msgstr "`l10n_nz`"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/new_zealand.rst:21
msgid ""
"Installed by default when the accounting fiscal localization package is set "
"to New Zealand. This module also installs the remittance advice report "
"module."
msgstr ""
"Terpasang secara default ketika paket lokalisasi fiskal akuntansi diatur ke "
"Selandia Baru. Modul ini juga memasang modul laporan saran pengiriman uang."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/new_zealand.rst:23
msgid ":guilabel:`Employment Hero NZ Payroll`"
msgstr ":guilabel:`Employment Hero NZ Payroll`"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/new_zealand.rst:25
msgid ""
"This module synchronizes all pay runs from Employment Hero with Odoo's "
"journal entries."
msgstr ""
"Modul ini menyinkronkan semua penggajian dari Employment Hero dengan entri "
"jurnal Odoo."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/new_zealand.rst:26
msgid ":guilabel:`EFT Batch Payment`"
