#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/new_zealand.rst:118
msgid ""
"The **Goods and Services Tax (GST) report** is a critical tax reporting "
"requirement for businesses registered for GST. The GST return is used to "
"report and remit GST to the **Inland Revenue Department (IRD)**."
msgstr ""
"**Laporan Pajak Barang dan Jasa (GST)** adalah persyaratan pelaporan pajak "
"penting bagi bisnis yang terdaftar untuk GST. Pengembalian GST digunakan "
"untuk melaporkan dan menyetor GST ke **Departemen Pendapatan Dalam Negeri "
"(IRD)**."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/new_zealand.rst:None
msgid "GST Report."
msgstr "Laporan GST."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/new_zealand.rst:125
msgid ""
"The base and tax amounts are collected from the **GST**, which is pre-"
"configured in Odoo to align with GST Return requirements (Boxes 1-15). The "
"**GST** can also be manually configured for special use cases, such as "
"specific GST treatments (e.g., zero-rating for exported agricultural goods). "
"Once the **GST** setup for each account is complete, Odoo automatically "
"categorizes journal items into the appropriate boxes. This ensures the "
"**GST** return is accurate and fully reflects the business's financial "
"activities."
msgstr ""
"Jumlah dasar dan pajak dikumpulkan dari **GST**, yang telah dikonfigurasi "
"sebelumnya di Odoo agar selaras dengan persyaratan Pengembalian GST (Kotak 1-"
"15). **GST** juga dapat dikonfigurasi secara manual untuk kasus penggunaan "
"khusus, seperti perlakuan GST tertentu (misalnya, tarif nol untuk barang "
"pertanian yang diekspor). Setelah pengaturan **GST** untuk setiap akun "
"selesai, Odoo secara otomatis mengkategorikan item jurnal ke dalam kotak "
"yang sesuai. Hal ini memastikan pengembalian **GST** akurat dan sepenuhnya "
"mencerminkan aktivitas keuangan bisnis."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/new_zealand.rst:138
msgid "Closing the GST report"
msgstr "Menutup laporan GST"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/new_zealand.rst:140
msgid ""
"The :ref:`tax return periodicity <accounting/tax-returns/periodicity>` must "
"be set up before submitting the :ref:`tax return <accounting/tax-returns/"
"report>` (**GST report**) to the **IRD**."
msgstr ""
":ref:`Periodisitas pengembalian pajak <accounting/tax-returns/periodicity>` "
"harus diatur sebelum mengirimkan :ref:`tax return <accounting/tax-returns/"
"report>` (**laporan GST**) ke **IRD**."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/new_zealand.rst:144
msgid ""
":doc:`Year-end closing documentation <../../../applications/finance/"
"accounting/reporting/year_end>`"
msgstr ""
":doc:`Dokumentasi penutupan akhir tahun <../../../applications/finance/"
"accounting/reporting/year_end>`"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/new_zealand.rst:147
msgid ""
"Before closing the entry for the first time, enable the :doc:`developer mode "
"<../../../applications/general/developer_mode>` and go "
"to :menuselection:`Accounting --> Configuration --> Tax Groups` to set the "
"default **GST payable account** and **GST receivable account**."
msgstr ""
"Sebelum menutup entri untuk pertama kalinya, aktifkan :doc:`mode pengembang "
"<../../../applications/general/developer_mode>` dan buka "
":menuselection:`Accounting --> Configuration --> Tax Groups` untuk mengatur "
"**akun hutang GST** dan **akun piutang GST** default."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/new_zealand.rst:152
msgid ""
"Once the **GST payable** and **GST receivable** accounts are set up, the "
"**Tax Return** report generates an accurate journal closing entry "
"automatically, balancing the GST balance with the GST clearing account."
msgstr ""
"Setelah akun **hutang GST** dan **piutang GST** diatur, laporan **Tax "
"Return** menghasilkan entri penutupan jurnal yang akurat secara otomatis, "
"menyeimbangkan saldo GST dengan akun kliring GST."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/new_zealand.rst:156
msgid ""
"The balance between **GST receivable** and **payable** is set against the "
"tax clearing account defined on the tax group. The amount to be paid to or "
"received from **IRD** can then be reconciled with a bank transaction."
msgstr ""
"Saldo antara **piutang GST** dan **hutang** diatur terhadap akun kliring "
"pajak yang ditentukan pada grup pajak. Jumlah yang harus dibayarkan kepada "
"atau diterima dari **IRD** kemudian dapat direkonsiliasi dengan transaksi "
"bank."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/new_zealand.rst:161
msgid ""
"The **GST** report is not submitted directly to the **IRD**. Instead, Odoo "
"automatically calculates the required values for each section, providing "
"options to audit and review the data for a clearer understanding of its "
"history. Businesses can then submit these values to the `IRD portal <https://"
"myir.ird.govt.nz/_/>`_."
msgstr ""
"Laporan **GST** tidak dikirimkan langsung ke **IRD**. Sebaliknya, Odoo "
"secara otomatis menghitung nilai yang diperlukan untuk setiap bagian, "
"menyediakan opsi untuk mengaudit dan meninjau data untuk pemahaman yang "
"lebih jelas tentang riwayatnya. Bisnis kemudian dapat mengirimkan nilai-"
"nilai ini ke `portal IRD <https://myir.ird.govt.nz/_/>`_."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/new_zealand.rst:171
msgid ""
