#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/peru.rst:599
msgid ""
"When creating invoices that is subject to Detractions, take into account the "
"next considerations:"
msgstr ""
"Saat membuat faktur yang dikenakan Pengurangan, pertimbangkan hal-hal "
"berikut:"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/peru.rst:601
msgid ""
"All the products included in the invoice must have these fields configured:"
msgstr ""
"Semua produk yang disertakan dalam faktur harus dikonfigurasi dengan bidang-"
"bidang berikut:"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/peru.rst:0
msgid "Detraction fields on products."
msgstr "Bidang Pengurangan pada produk."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/peru.rst:606
msgid "Operation type in your invoice must be ``1001``"
msgstr "Jenis operasi pada faktur Anda harus ``1001``"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/peru.rst:0
msgid "Detraction code on invoices."
msgstr "Kode Pengurangan pada faktur."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/peru.rst:612
msgid "Credit Notes"
msgstr "Catatan Kredit"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/peru.rst:614
msgid ""
"When a correction or refund is needed over a validated invoice, a credit "
"note must be generated, for this just click on the button “Add Credit Note”, "
"a part of the Peruvian localization you need to prove a Credit Reason "
"selecting one of the options in the list."
msgstr ""
"Ketika diperlukan koreksi atau pengembalian dana atas faktur yang telah "
"divalidasi, nota kredit harus dibuat. Untuk ini, cukup klik tombol "
"\"Tambahkan Nota Kredit\". Sebagai bagian dari lokalisasi Peru, Anda perlu "
"membuktikan Alasan Kredit dengan memilih salah satu opsi dalam daftar."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/peru.rst:None
msgid "Add Credit Note from invoice."
msgstr "Tambahkan Nota Kredit dari faktur."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/peru.rst:622
msgid ""
"When creating your first credit Note, select the Credit Method: Partial "
"Refund, this allows you to define the credit note sequence."
msgstr ""
"Saat membuat Nota Kredit pertama Anda, pilih Metode Kredit: Pengembalian "
"Dana Parsial. Ini memungkinkan Anda menentukan urutan nota kredit."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/peru.rst:625
msgid "By default the Credit Note is set in the document type:"
msgstr "Secara default, Nota Kredit diatur dalam jenis dokumen:"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/peru.rst:None
msgid "Credit Note document type."
msgstr "Jenis dokumen Nota Kredit."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/peru.rst:630
msgid ""
"To finish the workflow please follow the instructions on :doc:`our page "
"about Credit Notes <../accounting/customer_invoices/credit_notes>`."
msgstr ""
"Untuk menyelesaikan alur kerja, silakan ikuti instruksi di :doc:`halaman "
"kami tentang Nota Kredit <../accounting/customer_invoices/credit_notes>`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/peru.rst:634
msgid ""
"The EDI workflow for the Credit notes works in the same way as the invoices."
msgstr ""
"Alur kerja EDI untuk nota kredit bekerja dengan cara yang sama seperti "
"faktur."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/peru.rst:637
msgid "Debit Notes"
msgstr "Nota-Nota Debit"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/peru.rst:639
msgid ""
"As part of the Peruvian localization, besides creating credit notes from an "
"existing document you can also create debit Notes. For this just use the "
"button “Add Debit Note”."
msgstr ""
"Sebagai bagian dari lokalisasi Peru, selain membuat nota kredit dari dokumen "
"yang ada, Anda juga dapat membuat Nota Debit. Untuk ini, cukup gunakan "
"tombol \"Tambahkan Nota Debit\"."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/peru.rst:642
msgid "By default the Debit Note is set in the document type."
msgstr "Secara default, Nota Debit diatur dalam jenis dokumen."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/peru.rst:647
msgid "Electronic delivery guide 2.0"
msgstr "Panduan pengiriman elektronik 2.0"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/peru.rst:649
msgid ""
"The *Guía de Remisión Electrónica* (GRE) is an electronic document generated "
"by the shipper to support the transportation or transfer of goods from one "
"place to another, such as a warehouse or establishment. In Odoo, there are "
"several configuration steps needed before you can successfully use this "
"feature."
msgstr ""
"*Guía de Remisión Electrónica* (GRE) adalah dokumen elektronik yang dibuat "
"oleh pengirim untuk mendukung transportasi atau transfer barang dari satu "
"tempat ke tempat lain, seperti gudang atau tempat usaha. Di Odoo, ada "
"beberapa langkah konfigurasi yang diperlukan sebelum Anda dapat menggunakan "
"fitur ini dengan sukses."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/peru.rst:654
msgid ""
"The use of the *guía de remisión electrónica* electronic document is "
"mandatory and required by |SUNAT| for taxpayers who need to transfer their "
"products, except those under the *Single Simplified Regime* (régimen único "
"simplificado or RUS)."
msgstr ""
"Penggunaan dokumen elektronik *guía de remisión electrónica* bersifat wajib "
"dan diwajibkan oleh |SUNAT| untuk wajib pajak yang perlu mentransfer produk "
"mereka, kecuali mereka yang berada di bawah *Rezim Sederhana Tunggal* "
"(régimen único simplificado atau RUS)."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/peru.rst:659
msgid "Delivery guide types"
msgstr "Jenis panduan pengiriman"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/peru.rst:662
msgid "Sender"
msgstr "Pengirim"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/peru.rst:664
msgid ""
"The *Sender* delivery guide type is issued when a sale is made, a service is "
"rendered (including processing), goods are assigned for use, or goods are "
"transferred between premises of the same company and others."
msgstr ""
"Jenis panduan pengiriman *Pengirim* diterbitkan ketika penjualan dilakukan, "
"layanan diberikan (termasuk pemrosesan), barang ditugaskan untuk digunakan, "
"atau barang ditransfer antara tempat usaha perusahaan yang sama dan lainnya."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/peru.rst:668
msgid ""
"This delivery guide is issued by the owner of the goods (i.e., the sender) "
"at the beginning of the shipment. The sender delivery guide is supported in "
"Odoo."
msgstr ""
"Panduan pengiriman ini diterbitkan oleh pemilik barang (yaitu, pengirim) "
"pada awal pengiriman. Panduan pengiriman pengirim didukung di Odoo."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/peru.rst:672
msgid "`SUNAT guía de remisión <https://www.gob.pe/7899-guia-de-remision>`_"
msgstr "`SUNAT guía de remisión <https://www.gob.pe/7899-guia-de-remision>`_"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/peru.rst:675
#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/peru.rst:804
msgid "Carrier"
msgstr "Pembawa"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/peru.rst:677
msgid ""
"The *Carrier* delivery guide type justifies the transportation service the "
"driver (or carrier) performs."
msgstr ""
"Jenis panduan pengiriman *Carrier* membenarkan layanan transportasi yang "
"dilakukan oleh pengemudi (atau pengangkut)."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/peru.rst:680
msgid ""
"This delivery guide is issued by the carrier and must be issued to each "
"shipper when the shipment goes through public transport."
msgstr ""
"Panduan pengiriman ini diterbitkan oleh pengangkut dan harus diterbitkan "
"untuk setiap pengirim ketika pengiriman melalui transportasi umum."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/peru.rst:684
msgid "The carrier delivery guide is **not** supported in Odoo."
msgstr "Panduan pengiriman pengangkut **tidak** didukung di Odoo."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/peru.rst:687
msgid ""
"`SUNAT guía de remisión transportista <https://tefacturo.pe/blog/sunat/guia-"
"de-remision-electronica/guia-de-remision-transportista/>`_"
msgstr ""
"`SUNAT guía de remisión transportista <https://tefacturo.pe/blog/sunat/guia-"
"de-remision-electronica/guia-de-remision-transportista/>`_"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/peru.rst:691
msgid "Transportation types"
msgstr "Jenis transportasi"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/peru.rst:694
msgid "Private"
msgstr "Pribadi"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/peru.rst:696
msgid ""
"The *Private* transportation type option is used when the owner transfers "
"goods using their own vehicles. In this case, a sender's delivery guide must "
"be issued."
msgstr ""
"Opsi jenis transportasi *Private* digunakan ketika pemilik mentransfer "
"barang menggunakan kendaraan mereka sendiri. Dalam hal ini, panduan "
"pengiriman pengirim harus diterbitkan."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/peru.rst:700
msgid "Public"
msgstr "Umum"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/peru.rst:702
msgid ""
"The *Public* transportation type option is used when an external carrier "
"moves the goods. In this case, two delivery guides must be issued: the "
"sender's delivery guide and the carrier's delivery guide."
msgstr ""
"Opsi jenis transportasi *Public* digunakan ketika pengangkut eksternal "
"memindahkan barang. Dalam hal ini, dua panduan pengiriman harus diterbitkan: "
"panduan pengiriman pengirim dan panduan pengiriman pengangkut."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/peru.rst:707
msgid "Direct submission to SUNAT"
msgstr "Pengiriman langsung ke SUNAT"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/peru.rst:709
msgid ""
"The creation of the |GRE| delivery guide in Odoo **must** be sent directly "
"to the |SUNAT|, regardless of the electronic document provider: IAP, "
"Digiflow, or |SUNAT|."
msgstr ""
"Pembuatan panduan pengiriman |GRE| di Odoo **harus** dikirim langsung ke "
"|SUNAT|, terlepas dari penyedia dokumen elektronik: IAP, Digiflow, atau "
"|SUNAT|."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/peru.rst:713
#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/united_states.rst:518
msgid "Required information"
msgstr "Informasi yang diperlukan"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/peru.rst:715
msgid ""
"Version 2.0 of the electronic delivery guide requires additional information "
"on the general configuration, vehicles, contacts, and products. In the "
"general configuration, it is necessary to add new credentials that you can "
"retrieve from the |SUNAT| portal."
msgstr ""
"Versi 2.0 dari panduan pengiriman elektronik memerlukan informasi tambahan "
"tentang konfigurasi umum, kendaraan, kontak, dan produk. Dalam konfigurasi "
"umum, perlu menambahkan kredensial baru yang dapat Anda ambil dari portal "
"|SUNAT|."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/peru.rst:720
msgid "Cancellations"
msgstr "Pembatalan"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/peru.rst:722
msgid ""
"**Both** the sender and the carrier can cancel the electronic waybill as "
"long as the following conditions are met:"
msgstr ""
"**Baik** pengirim maupun pengangkut dapat membatalkan surat jalan elektronik "
"selama kondisi berikut terpenuhi:"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/peru.rst:725
msgid "The shipment has not been initiated."
msgstr "Pengiriman belum dimulai."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/peru.rst:726
msgid ""
"If the shipment has been initiated, the receiver **must** be changed before "
"reaching the final destination."
msgstr ""
"Jika pengiriman telah dimulai, penerima **harus** diubah sebelum mencapai "
"tujuan akhir."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/peru.rst:730
msgid ""
"The |SUNAT| no longer uses the term \"Anula\", but now uses the term \"Dar "
"de baja\" for cancellations."
msgstr ""
"|SUNAT| tidak lagi menggunakan istilah \"Anula\", tetapi sekarang "
"menggunakan istilah \"Dar de baja\" untuk pembatalan."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/peru.rst:734
#: ../../content/applications/finance/payment_providers/paypal.rst:56
msgid "Testing"
msgstr "Pengujian"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/peru.rst:736
msgid ""
"The |SUNAT| does not support a test environment. This means that any "
"delivery guides that were generated by mistake **will** be sent to the |"
"SUNAT|."
msgstr ""
"|SUNAT| tidak mendukung lingkungan pengujian. Ini berarti bahwa setiap "
"panduan pengiriman yang dibuat karena kesalahan **akan** dikirim ke |SUNAT|."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/peru.rst:739
msgid ""
"If, by mistake, the waybill was created in this environment, it is necessary "
"to delete it from the |SUNAT| portal."
msgstr ""
"Jika, karena kesalahan, surat jalan dibuat di lingkungan ini, maka perlu "
"menghapusnya dari portal |SUNAT|."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/peru.rst:746
msgid ""
"Electronic sender's |GRE| is currently the only supported type of waybill in "
"Odoo."
msgstr ""
"Pengirim elektronik |GRE| saat ini adalah satu-satunya jenis surat jalan "
"yang didukung di Odoo."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/peru.rst:747
msgid ""
"The delivery guide is dependent on the Odoo *Inventory* app, "
"the :guilabel:`l10n_pe_edi` and :guilabel:`l10n_pe` modules."
msgstr ""
"Panduan pengiriman bergantung pada aplikasi *Inventaris* Odoo, modul "
":guilabel:`l10n_pe_edi` dan :guilabel:`l10n_pe`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/peru.rst:749
msgid ""
"A second user **must** be added for the creation of electronic documents."
msgstr "User kedua **harus** ditambahkan untuk pembuatan dokumen elektronik."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/peru.rst:751
msgid ""
"After following the steps to configure the :ref:`electronic invoicing <peru-"
"accounting-settings>` and the :ref:`master data <peru-"
"master_data>`, :ref:`install <general/install>` the :guilabel:`Peruvian - "
"Electronic Delivery Note 2.0` module (`l10n_pe_edi_stock_20`)."
msgstr ""
"Setelah mengikuti langkah-langkah untuk mengonfigurasi :ref:`penagihan "
"elektronik <peru-accounting-settings>` dan :ref:`data master <peru-"
"master_data>`, :ref:`instal <general/install>` modul :guilabel:`Peruvian - "
"Electronic Delivery Note 2.0` (`l10n_pe_edi_stock_20`)."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/peru.rst:755
msgid ""
"Next, you need to retrieve the *client ID* and *client secret* from |SUNAT|. "
"To do so, follow the `manual de servicios web plataforma nueva GRE <https://"
"cpe.sunat.gob.pe/sites/default/files/inline-files/"
"Manual_Servicios_GRE%20%281%29.pdf>`_."
msgstr ""
"Selanjutnya, Anda perlu mengambil *ID klien* dan *rahasia klien* dari "
"|SUNAT|. Untuk melakukannya, ikuti `manual de servicios web plataforma nueva "
"GRE <https://cpe.sunat.gob.pe/sites/default/files/inline-files/"
"Manual_Servicios_GRE%20%281%29.pdf>`_."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/peru.rst:760
msgid ""
"In the |SUNAT| portal, it is important to have the correct access rights "
"enabled, as they may differ from the user set for electronic invoicing."
msgstr ""
"Di portal |SUNAT|, penting untuk mengaktifkan hak akses yang benar, karena "
"mungkin berbeda dari user yang diatur untuk penagihan elektronik."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/peru.rst:763
msgid ""
"These credentials should be used to configure the delivery guide general "
"settings from :menuselection:`Inventory --> Configuration --> Settings`, and "
"scroll down to the :guilabel:`Peru Delivery Guide` section."
msgstr ""
"Kredensial ini harus digunakan untuk mengonfigurasi pengaturan umum panduan "
"pengiriman dari :menuselection:`Inventaris --> Configuration --> Settings`, "
"dan gulir ke bawah ke bagian :guilabel:`Peru Delivery Guide`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/peru.rst:767
msgid "Configure the following :guilabel:`Sunat Delivery Guide API` fields:"
msgstr "Konfigurasikan kolom :guilabel:`Sunat Delivery Guide API` berikut:"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/peru.rst:769
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Guide Client ID`: the unique API *client ID* generated in the |"
"SUNAT| portal"
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Guide Client ID`: *ID klien* API unik yang dihasilkan di portal "
"|SUNAT|"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/peru.rst:770
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Guide Client Secret`: the unique API *client secret* generated in "
"the |SUNAT| portal"
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Guide Client Secret`: *rahasia klien* API unik yang dihasilkan di "
"portal |SUNAT|"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/peru.rst:771
msgid ":guilabel:`Guide SOL User`: the RUC Number + SOL username"
msgstr ":guilabel:`Guide SOL User`: Nomor RUC + nama pengguna SOL"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/peru.rst:772
msgid ":guilabel:`Guide SOL Password`: the SOL user password"
msgstr ":guilabel:`Guide SOL Password`: kata sandi pengguna SOL"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/peru.rst:None
msgid "Example for the SUNAT Delivery Guide API section configuration."
msgstr "Contoh konfigurasi bagian SUNAT Delivery Guide API."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/peru.rst:778
msgid ""
"It is required to follow the format `RUC + UsuarioSol` (e.g., "
"`20557912879SOLUSER`) for the :guilabel:`Guide SOL User` field, depending on "
"the user selected when generating the |GRE| API credentials in the |SUNAT| "
"portal."
msgstr ""
"Diharuskan untuk mengikuti format `RUC + UsuarioSol` (misalnya, "
"`20557912879SOLUSER`) untuk kolom :guilabel:`Guide SOL User`, tergantung "
"pada user yang dipilih saat menghasilkan kredensial API |GRE| di portal "
"|SUNAT|."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/peru.rst:783
msgid "Operator"
msgstr "Operator"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/peru.rst:785
msgid ""
"The *operator* is the vehicle's driver in cases where the delivery guide is "
"through *private* transport."
msgstr ""
"*Operator* adalah pengemudi kendaraan dalam kasus di mana panduan pengiriman "
"melalui transportasi *pribadi*."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/peru.rst:788
msgid ""
"To create a new operator, navigate to :menuselection:`Contacts --> Create` "
"and fill out the contact information."
msgstr ""
"Untuk membuat operator baru, navigasikan ke :menuselection:`Kontak --> "
"Create` dan isi informasi kontak."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/peru.rst:791
msgid ""
"First, select :guilabel:`Individual` as the :guilabel:`Company Type`. Then, "
"add the :guilabel:`Operator License` in the :guilabel:`Accounting` tab of "
"the contact form."
msgstr ""
"Pertama, pilih :guilabel:`Individual` sebagai :guilabel:`Company Type`. "
"Kemudian, tambahkan :guilabel:`Operator License` di tab "
":guilabel:`Akuntansi` dari formulir kontak."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/peru.rst:794
msgid "For the customer address, make sure the following fields are complete:"
msgstr "Untuk alamat pelanggan, pastikan kolom berikut sudah lengkap:"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/peru.rst:796
#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/peru.rst:817
msgid ":guilabel:`District`"
msgstr ":guilabel:`District`"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/peru.rst:797
#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/peru.rst:818
msgid ":guilabel:`Tax ID` (:guilabel:`DNI`/:guilabel:`RUC`)"
msgstr ":guilabel:`Tax ID` (:guilabel:`DNI`/:guilabel:`RUC`)"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/peru.rst:798
#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/peru.rst:819
msgid ":guilabel:`Tax ID Number`"
msgstr ":guilabel:`Nomor ID Pajak`"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/peru.rst:None
msgid "Individual type operator configurations in the Contact form."
msgstr "Konfigurasi operator tipe individu dalam formulir Kontak."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/peru.rst:806
msgid ""
"The *carrier* is used when the delivery guide is through *public* transport."
msgstr ""
"*Pengangkut* digunakan ketika panduan pengiriman melalui transportasi "
"*publik*."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/peru.rst:808
msgid ""
"To create a new carrier, navigate to :menuselection:`Contacts --> Create` "
"and fill out the contact information."
msgstr ""
"Untuk membuat pengangkut baru, navigasi ke :menuselection:`Kontak --> Buat` "
"dan isi informasi kontak."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/peru.rst:811
msgid ""
"First, select :guilabel:`Company` as the :guilabel:`Company Type`. Then, add "
"the :guilabel:`MTC Registration Number`, :guilabel:`Authorization Issuing "
"Entity`, and the :guilabel:`Authorization Number`."
msgstr ""
"Pertama, pilih :guilabel:`Perusahaan` sebagai :guilabel:`Tipe Perusahaan`. "
"Kemudian, tambahkan :guilabel:`Nomor Registrasi MTC`, :guilabel:`Entitas "
"Penerbit Otorisasi`, dan :guilabel:`Nomor Otorisasi`."

