"\"Hace falta el campo\" \"Peso\"\" en el producto`"
msgstr ""
"`2325 - GrossWeightMeasure - El dato no cumple con el formato establecido "
"\"Hace falta el campo\" \"Peso\"\" en el producto`"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/peru.rst:891
msgid ""
"This error occurs when the weight on the product is set as `0.00`. To fix "
"this, you need to cancel the waybill and recreate it. Make sure that you fix "
"the weight on the product before creating the new waybill, or it will result "
"in the same error."
msgstr ""
"Kesalahan ini terjadi ketika berat pada produk diatur sebagai `0.00`. Untuk "
"memperbaikinya, Anda perlu membatalkan surat jalan dan membuatnya kembali. "
"Pastikan Anda memperbaiki berat pada produk sebelum membuat surat jalan "
"baru, atau akan menghasilkan kesalahan yang sama."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/peru.rst:894
msgid ""
"`JSONDecodeError: Expecting value: line 1 column 1 (char 0) when creating a "
"Delivery Guide`"
msgstr ""
"`JSONDecodeError: Expecting value: line 1 column 1 (char 0) when creating a "
"Delivery Guide`"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/peru.rst:896
msgid ""
"This error is typically generated due to SOL user issues. Verify the user's "
"connection with the |SUNAT|; the SOL user must be established with the "
"company RUT + user ID. For example `2012188549JOHNSMITH`."
msgstr ""
"Kesalahan ini biasanya dihasilkan karena masalah user SOL. Verifikasi "
"koneksi user dengan |SUNAT|; user SOL harus dibuat dengan RUT perusahaan + "
"ID user. Misalnya `2012188549JOHNSMITH`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/peru.rst:899
msgid ""
"`El número de documento relacionado al traslado de mercancía no cumple con "
"el formato establecido: error: documento relacionado`"
msgstr ""
"`El número de documento relacionado al traslado de mercancía no cumple con "
"el formato establecido: error: documento relacionado`"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/peru.rst:902
msgid ""
"The *Related Document Type* and *Related Document Number* fields only apply "
"to invoices and receipts."
msgstr ""
"Kolom *Jenis Dokumen Terkait* dan *Nomor Dokumen Terkait* hanya berlaku "
"untuk faktur dan tanda terima."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/peru.rst:904
msgid "`400 Client error: Bad Request for URL`"
msgstr "`400 Client error: Bad Request for URL`"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/peru.rst:906
msgid ""
"This error is not solvable from Odoo; it is advised you reach out to the |"
"SUNAT| and verify the user. It may be necessary to create a new user."
msgstr ""
"Kesalahan ini tidak dapat diselesaikan dari Odoo; disarankan Anda "
"menghubungi |SUNAT| dan memverifikasi user. Mungkin perlu membuat user baru."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/peru.rst:909
msgid ""
"`Invalid content was found starting with element 'cac:BuyerCustomerParty'`"
msgstr ""
"`Invalid content was found starting with element 'cac:BuyerCustomerParty'`"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/peru.rst:911
msgid ""
"This error occurs when the transfer reason is set as *other*. Please select "
"another option. Following to the official documentation of the |SUNAT|'s "
"waybill guide, the transfer reasons *03 (sale with shipment to third party)* "
"or *12 (others)* does not work in Odoo, since you should not have an empty "
"or blank customer."
msgstr ""
"Kesalahan ini terjadi ketika alasan transfer diatur sebagai *lainnya*. "
"Silakan pilih opsi lain. Mengikuti dokumentasi resmi dari panduan surat "
"jalan |SUNAT|, alasan transfer *03 (penjualan dengan pengiriman ke pihak "
"ketiga)* atau *12 (lainnya)* tidak berfungsi di Odoo, karena Anda tidak "
"boleh memiliki pelanggan yang kosong atau blank."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/peru.rst:915
msgid "`Duda cliente: consumo de créditos IAP al usar GRE 2.0`"
msgstr "Pertanyaan klien: konsumsi kredit IAP saat menggunakan GRE 2.0`"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/peru.rst:917
msgid ""
"For live clients using IAP, no credit is consumed (in theory) because it "
"does not go through the OSE, i.e., these documents are directly sent to the |"
"SUNAT|."
msgstr ""
"Untuk klien live yang menggunakan IAP, tidak ada kredit yang dikonsumsi "
"(secara teori) karena tidak melalui OSE, yaitu, dokumen-dokumen ini langsung "
"dikirim ke |SUNAT|."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/peru.rst:919
msgid "`Errores con formato credenciales GRE 2.0 (traceback error)`"
msgstr "`Kesalahan dengan format kredensial GRE 2.0 (traceback error)`"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/peru.rst:921
msgid ""
"Odoo currently throws an error with a traceback instead of a message that "
"the credentials are not correctly configured in the database. If this occurs "
"on your database, please verify your credentials."
msgstr ""
"Odoo saat ini menampilkan kesalahan dengan traceback alih-alih pesan bahwa "
"kredensial tidak dikonfigurasi dengan benar di database. Jika ini terjadi "
"pada database Anda, harap verifikasi kredensial Anda."

