#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/peru.rst:972
msgid ""
"Once the :ref:`configurations <peru-ecommerce-configuration>` are all set, "
"fiscal input fields will be available during the checkout process for signed-"
"in customers."
msgstr ""
"Setelah semua :ref:`konfigurasi <peru-ecommerce-configuration>` diatur, "
"field input fiskal akan tersedia selama proses checkout untuk pelanggan yang "
"telah masuk."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/peru.rst:975
msgid ""
"When customers enter their fiscal data at checkout and complete a successful "
"purchase, the invoice is generated with the corresponding |EDI| elements. "
"The document type (Boleta/Factura) is selected based on their tax ID (RUC/"
"DNI). The invoice must then :ref:`be sent to the OSE and the SUNAT <peru-"
"electronic-invoice-status>`. By default, all published invoices are sent "
"once a day through a scheduled action, but you can also send each invoice "
"manually if needed."
msgstr ""
"Ketika pelanggan memasukkan data fiskal mereka saat checkout dan "
"menyelesaikan pembelian dengan sukses, faktur dibuat dengan elemen |EDI| "
"yang sesuai. Jenis dokumen (Boleta/Factura) dipilih berdasarkan ID pajak "
"mereka (RUC/DNI). Faktur kemudian harus :ref:`dikirim ke OSE dan SUNAT <peru-"
"electronic-invoice-status>`. Secara default, semua faktur yang "
"dipublikasikan dikirim sekali sehari melalui tindakan terjadwal, tetapi Anda "
"juga dapat mengirim setiap faktur secara manual jika diperlukan."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/peru.rst:981
msgid ""
"Once the invoice is validated with |SUNAT|, customers can download the .zip "
"file with the CDR, XML, and PDF files directly from the customer portal by "
"clicking the :guilabel:`Download` button."
msgstr ""
"Setelah faktur divalidasi dengan |SUNAT|, pelanggan dapat mengunduh file "
".zip dengan file CDR, XML, dan PDF langsung dari portal pelanggan dengan "
"mengklik tombol :guilabel:`Download`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/peru.rst:990
msgid "Permanent inventory reports: |PLE| 12.1 and |PLE| 13.1"
msgstr "Laporan inventaris permanen: |PLE| 12.1 dan |PLE| 13.1"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/peru.rst:992
msgid ""
"Odoo can produce two permanent inventory reports as `.txt` files for "
"Peruvian accounting: |PLE| 12.1 and |PLE| 13.1. All inventory transactions "
"made need to be reported."
msgstr ""
"Odoo dapat menghasilkan dua laporan inventaris permanen sebagai file `.txt` "
"untuk akuntansi Peru: |PLE| 12.1 dan |PLE| 13.1. Semua transaksi inventaris "
"yang dilakukan perlu dilaporkan."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/peru.rst:995
msgid ""
"|PLE| 12.1 **only tracks inventory in physical units**, focusing on the "
"inflow and outflow of goods for effective management and planning."
msgstr ""
"|PLE| 12.1 **hanya melacak inventaris dalam unit fisik**, berfokus pada arus "
"masuk dan keluar barang untuk manajemen dan perencanaan yang efektif."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/peru.rst:998
msgid ""
"|PLE| 13.1 tracks **both physical quantities and monetary values of "
"inventory**, providing a comprehensive view for tax and management purposes."
msgstr ""
"|PLE| 13.1 melacak **baik kuantitas fisik maupun nilai moneter inventaris**, "
"memberikan tampilan komprehensif untuk tujuan pajak dan manajemen."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/peru.rst:1001
msgid ""
"Both reports must be maintained semi-annually (January-June and July-"
"December), with monthly transaction details reported within these periods. "
"The submission deadlines are October 1st for the first semester and April "
"1st for the second semester, in accordance with the *Resolución de "
"Superintendencia N° 169-2015*."
msgstr ""
"Kedua laporan harus dipelihara secara semesteran (Januari-Juni dan Juli-"
"Desember), dengan rincian transaksi bulanan dilaporkan dalam periode ini. "
"Tenggat waktu pengajuan adalah 1 Oktober untuk semester pertama dan 1 April "
"untuk semester kedua, sesuai dengan *Resolución de Superintendencia N° 169-"
"2015*."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/peru.rst:1009
msgid ""
"Before generating the |PLE| 12.1 or |PLE| 13.1 reports, make sure "
"the :guilabel:`Peru - Stock Reports` (`l10n_pe_reports_stock`) module is "
"installed, then update the fields for:"
msgstr ""
"Sebelum menghasilkan laporan |PLE| 12.1 atau |PLE| 13.1, pastikan modul "
":guilabel:`Peru - Stock Reports` (`l10n_pe_reports_stock`) terinstal, "
"kemudian perbarui kolom untuk:"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/peru.rst:1012
msgid ":ref:`Products <peru/reports-ple-products>`"
msgstr ":ref:`Produk <peru/reports-ple-products>`"

