#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/peru.rst:1023
msgid ""
"**Type of existence**: For all products needing |PLE| reporting, go to the "
"product record's :guilabel:`Accounting` tab and select the :guilabel:`Type "
"of Existence` according to |SUNAT|'s table 5 for inventory reporting."
msgstr ""
"**Jenis keberadaan**: Untuk semua produk yang memerlukan pelaporan |PLE|, "
"buka tab :guilabel:`Akuntansi` pada catatan produk dan pilih :guilabel:`Type "
"of Existence` sesuai dengan tabel 5 |SUNAT| untuk pelaporan inventaris."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/peru.rst:1027
msgid ""
"**Automatic inventory valuation**: For storable goods (:dfn:`products with "
"tracked inventory`), use :doc:`automatic inventory valuation <../../"
"inventory_and_mrp/inventory/inventory_valuation/cheat_sheet>`. Once "
"automatic inventory valuation is enabled, this valuation method can be "
"enabled for a product's product category."
msgstr ""
"**Penilaian inventaris otomatis**: Untuk barang yang dapat disimpan "
"(:dfn:`produk dengan inventaris yang dilacak`), gunakan :doc:`automatic "
"inventory valuation <../../inventory_and_mrp/inventory/inventory_valuation/"
"cheat_sheet>`. Setelah penilaian inventaris otomatis diaktifkan, metode "
"penilaian ini dapat diaktifkan untuk kategori produk dari suatu produk."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/peru.rst:1032
msgid ""
"**Costing method:** Storable goods must use a :doc:`costing method <../../"
"inventory_and_mrp/inventory/inventory_valuation/cheat_sheet>` **other** "
"than :guilabel:`Standard Price`, as the journal entries generated from stock "
"moves are used to populate the |PLE| reports."
msgstr ""
"**Metode biaya:** Barang yang dapat disimpan harus menggunakan :doc:`costing "
"method <../../inventory_and_mrp/inventory/inventory_valuation/cheat_sheet>` "
"**selain** :guilabel:`Standard Price`, karena entri jurnal yang dihasilkan "
"dari perpindahan stok digunakan untuk mengisi laporan |PLE|."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/peru.rst:1040
msgid "Warehouses"
msgstr "Gudang"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/peru.rst:1042
msgid ""
"When :doc:`setting up a warehouse <../../inventory_and_mrp/inventory/"
"warehouses_storage/inventory_management/warehouses>`, the :guilabel:`Annex "
"Establishment Code` field must be filled. This code acts as a unique ID for "
"each warehouse and should only be a numeric combination, containing between "
"4 to 7 digits."
msgstr ""
"Saat :doc:`menyiapkan gudang <../../inventory_and_mrp/inventory/"
"warehouses_storage/inventory_management/warehouses>`, kolom :guilabel:`Annex "
"Establishment Code` harus diisi. Kode ini bertindak sebagai ID unik untuk "
"setiap gudang dan hanya boleh berupa kombinasi angka, berisi antara 4 hingga "
"7 digit."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/peru.rst:1050
msgid "Inventory transfers"
msgstr "Transfer inventaris"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/peru.rst:1052
msgid ""
"Transferring inventory is a key process captured in the |PLE| 12.1 and |PLE| "
"13.1 reports. :doc:`Inventory transfers <../../inventory_and_mrp/inventory/"
"shipping_receiving/daily_operations>` include both incoming and outgoing "
"shipments."
msgstr ""
"Transfer inventaris adalah proses kunci yang tercatat dalam laporan |PLE| "
"12.1 dan |PLE| 13.1. :doc:`Transfer inventaris <../../inventory_and_mrp/"
"inventory/shipping_receiving/daily_operations>` mencakup pengiriman masuk "
"dan keluar."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/peru.rst:1056
msgid ""
"When validating an inventory transfer (either on a warehouse receipt or "
"delivery order), select the :guilabel:`Type of Operation (PE)` performed "
"according to |SUNAT|'s table 12 for permanent inventory reporting."
msgstr ""
"Saat memvalidasi transfer inventaris (baik pada penerimaan gudang atau surat "
"jalan), pilih :guilabel:`Type of Operation (PE)` yang dilakukan sesuai "
"dengan tabel 12 |SUNAT| untuk pelaporan inventaris permanen."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/peru.rst:1061
msgid "Generate a .txt file for permanent inventory Kardex reports"
msgstr "Hasilkan file .txt untuk laporan Kardex inventaris permanen"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/peru.rst:1063
msgid ""
"|PLE| 12.1 and 13.1 come as two separate books. The books need to be "
"downloaded in `.txt` file format from Odoo, and then they should be "
"submitted to the |SUNAT| |PLE| software."
msgstr ""
"|PLE| 12.1 dan 13.1 hadir sebagai dua buku terpisah. Buku-buku tersebut "
"perlu diunduh dalam format file `.txt` dari Odoo, dan kemudian harus "
"dikirimkan ke perangkat lunak |SUNAT| |PLE|."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/peru.rst:1066
msgid ""
"On the :ref:`Inventory Valuation Report <inventory/product_management/"
"valuation-report>`, click the :guilabel:`PLE Reports` button. Then, select "
"the :guilabel:`Period` and choose a report to export: either "
"the :guilabel:`PLE 12.1` or :guilabel:`PLE 13.1`. Odoo generates a `.txt` "
"file for the chosen report."
msgstr ""
"Di :ref:`Inventory Valuation Report <inventory/product_management/valuation-"
"report>`, klik tombol :guilabel:`PLE Reports`. Kemudian, pilih "
":guilabel:`Period` dan pilih laporan untuk diekspor: baik :guilabel:`PLE "
"12.1` atau :guilabel:`PLE 13.1`. Odoo menghasilkan file `.txt` untuk laporan "
"yang dipilih."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/peru.rst:None
msgid "Export Buttons selection"
msgstr "Pilihan Tombol Ekspor"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/peru.rst:1075
msgid ""
"Only a download of the report in `.txt` format is available. There is no "
"preview or visualization available within Odoo."
msgstr ""
"Hanya unduhan laporan dalam format `.txt` yang tersedia. Tidak ada pratinjau "
"atau visualisasi yang tersedia di dalam Odoo."

