#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/philippines.rst:72
msgid ""
"Default taxes are pre-configured and mapped to the relevant reports. To "
"create a new tax, it is recommended to **duplicate** an existing one to "
"preserve this configuration. To do so, select the tax, click :icon:`fa-"
"cog` :guilabel:`Actions`, and select :guilabel:`Duplicate`."
msgstr ""
"Pajak default telah dikonfigurasi sebelumnya dan dipetakan ke laporan yang "
"relevan. Untuk membuat pajak baru, disarankan untuk **menduplikasi** yang "
"sudah ada guna mempertahankan konfigurasi ini. Untuk melakukannya, pilih "
"pajak, klik :icon:`fa-cog` :guilabel:`Tindakan`, dan pilih "
":guilabel:`Duplikasi`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/philippines.rst:79
msgid "ATC codes"
msgstr "Kode ATC"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/philippines.rst:81
msgid ""
"ATC codes are essential for generating :ref:`BIR 2307 <localizations/"
"philippines/reports/bir2307>`, :ref:`localizations/philippines/reports/"
"sawt_qap` reports. These codes ensure compliance with regulatory "
"requirements."
msgstr ""
"Kode ATC sangat penting untuk menghasilkan laporan :ref:`BIR 2307 "
"<localizations/philippines/reports/bir2307>`, :ref:`localizations/"
"philippines/reports/sawt_qap`. Kode ini memastikan kepatuhan terhadap "
"persyaratan regulasi."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/philippines.rst:85
msgid ""
"To configure a withholding tax, go to :menuselection:`Accounting --> "
"Configuration --> Taxes`, select the tax, and fill in "
"the :guilabel:`Philippines ATC` (Alphanumeric Tax Code) field under "
"the :guilabel:`Philippines` tab."
msgstr ""
"Untuk mengonfigurasi pajak pemotongan, buka :menuselection:`Akuntansi --> "
"Konfigurasi --> Pajak`, pilih pajak, dan isi kolom :guilabel:`ATC Filipina` "
"(Kode Pajak Alfanumerik) di bawah tab :guilabel:`Filipina`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/philippines.rst:97
msgid "2550Q"
msgstr "2550Q"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/philippines.rst:99
msgid ""
"The **BIR Form 2550Q** summarizes sales, purchases, output VAT, input VAT, "
"and the resulting VAT payable or refundable for the period."
msgstr ""
"**Formulir BIR 2550Q** merangkum penjualan, pembelian, PPN keluaran, PPN "
"masukan, dan PPN yang harus dibayar atau dapat dikembalikan untuk periode "
"tersebut."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/philippines.rst:102
msgid ""
"To access it, navigate to :menuselection:`Accounting --> Reporting --> Tax "
"Report`, click :icon:`fa-book` :guilabel:`Report`, and "
"select :guilabel:`2550Q (PH)`."
msgstr ""
"Untuk mengaksesnya, buka :menuselection:`Akuntansi --> Pelaporan --> Laporan "
"Pajak`, klik :icon:`fa-book` :guilabel:`Laporan`, dan pilih :guilabel:`2550Q "
"(PH)`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/philippines.rst:108
msgid "SAWT and QAP"
msgstr "SAWT dan QAP"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/philippines.rst:110
msgid ""
"To access these reports, navigate to :menuselection:`Accounting --> "
"Reporting --> Tax Report`, click :icon:`fa-book` :guilabel:`Report`, and "
"select :guilabel:`SAWT & QAP (PH)`."
msgstr ""
"Untuk mengakses laporan ini, buka :menuselection:`Akuntansi --> "
"Pelaporan --> Laporan Pajak`, klik :icon:`fa-book` :guilabel:`Laporan`, dan "
"pilih :guilabel:`SAWT & QAP (PH)`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/philippines.rst:113
msgid ""
"**Summary of Alphalist of Withholding Taxes (SAWT)**: Displays all customer "
"invoices that have sales withholding taxes applied. This export is used as a "
"supporting document for forms **1701Q**, **1701**, **1702Q**, and **1702**."
msgstr ""
"**Ringkasan Alphalist Pajak Pemotongan (SAWT)**: Menampilkan semua faktur "
"pelanggan yang telah menerapkan pajak pemotongan penjualan. Ekspor ini "
"digunakan sebagai dokumen pendukung untuk formulir **1701Q**, **1701**, "
"**1702Q**, dan **1702**."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/philippines.rst:116
msgid ""
"**Quarterly Alphalist of Payees (QAP)**: Includes all vendor bills that have "
"purchase withholding taxes applied. This export is used as a supporting "
"document for forms **1601EQ** and **1604E**."
msgstr ""
"**Alphalist Penerima Pembayaran Triwulanan (QAP)**: Mencakup semua tagihan "
"vendor yang telah menerapkan pajak pemotongan pembelian. Ekspor ini "
"digunakan sebagai dokumen pendukung untuk formulir **1601EQ** dan **1604E**."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/philippines.rst:121
msgid ""
"The generated file is based on the specific **period** selected in the "
"calendar report filter. For example, while the **1601EQ** is a quarterly "
"report, `.DAT` files are submitted monthly. Make sure to filter "
"by :guilabel:`Month` and select the appropriate month before exporting."
msgstr ""
"File yang dihasilkan berdasarkan **periode** tertentu yang dipilih dalam "
"filter laporan kalender. Misalnya, meskipun **1601EQ** adalah laporan "
"triwulanan, file `.DAT` dikirimkan secara bulanan. Pastikan untuk memfilter "
"berdasarkan :guilabel:`Bulan` dan pilih bulan yang sesuai sebelum mengekspor."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/philippines.rst:125
msgid ""
"Both SAWT and QAP reports can be exported in `.DAT` format, which is "
"compatible with the BIR :abbr:`Alpha (Alphalist Data Entry and Validation)` "
"module. To do so, follow these steps:"
msgstr ""
"Laporan SAWT dan QAP dapat diekspor dalam format `.DAT`, yang kompatibel "
"dengan modul :abbr:`Alpha (Entri dan Validasi Data Alphalist)` BIR. Untuk "
"melakukannya, ikuti langkah-langkah berikut:"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/philippines.rst:128
#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/philippines.rst:159
msgid "Make sure to filter by the appropriate month."
msgstr "Pastikan untuk memfilter berdasarkan bulan yang sesuai."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/philippines.rst:129
msgid ""
"On the report page, click the :icon:`fa-cog` :guilabel:`(gear)` icon and "
"select :guilabel:`Export SAWT & QAP`."
msgstr ""
"Pada halaman laporan, klik ikon :icon:`fa-cog` :guilabel:`(roda gigi)` dan "
"pilih :guilabel:`Export SAWT & QAP`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/philippines.rst:131
msgid ""
"In the :guilabel:`DAT Export Options` window, choose the "
"relevant :guilabel:`Attachment For (e.g., 1601EQ)` and "
"click :guilabel:`Export`."
msgstr ""
"Pada jendela :guilabel:`DAT Export Options`, pilih :guilabel:`Attachment For "
"(misalnya, 1601EQ)` yang relevan dan klik :guilabel:`Export`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/philippines.rst:137
msgid "SLSP"
msgstr "SLSP"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/philippines.rst:139
msgid ""
"The **SLSP (Summary lists of sales and purchases)** is an electronic "
"schedule required from VAT‑registered taxpayers listing sales and purchase "
"transactions."
msgstr ""
"**SLSP (Summary lists of sales and purchases)** adalah jadwal elektronik "
"yang diwajibkan dari wajib pajak terdaftar PPN yang mencantumkan transaksi "
"penjualan dan pembelian."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/philippines.rst:142
msgid ""
"To access it, navigate to :menuselection:`Accounting --> Reporting --> "
"Summary Lists of Sales and Purchases`."
msgstr ""
"Untuk mengaksesnya, navigasi ke :menuselection:`Akuntansi --> Pelaporan --> "
"Summary Lists of Sales and Purchases`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/philippines.rst:145
msgid ""
"**Summary List of Sales (SLS)**: Detailed sales per customer with amounts "
"and output VAT."
msgstr ""
"**Summary List of Sales (SLS)**: Penjualan terperinci per pelanggan dengan "
"jumlah dan PPN keluaran."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/philippines.rst:146
msgid ""
"**Summary List of Purchases (SLP)**: Detailed purchases per supplier with "
"amounts and input VAT."
msgstr ""
"**Summary List of Purchases (SLP)**: Pembelian terperinci per pemasok dengan "
"jumlah dan PPN masukan."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/philippines.rst:149
msgid ""
"The :guilabel:`Summary List of Purchases` report excludes imports by "
"default. To include import transactions, click :icon:`fa-"
"sliders` :guilabel:`Posted Entries` and select :guilabel:`Including "
