"berdasarkan :guilabel:`Month` dan pilih bulan yang sesuai sebelum mengekspor."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/philippines.rst:156
msgid ""
"SLS and SLP reports can be exported in `.DAT` format, which is compatible "
"with the :abbr:`ReLiEf (Reconciliation of Listings for Enforcement)` module. "
