"disesuaikan dengan standar Arab Saudi."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/saudi_arabia.rst:55
msgid ""
"The Saudi Arabian localization package provides the following key features "
"to ensure compliance with local fiscal and accounting regulations:"
msgstr ""
"Paket lokalisasi Arab Saudi menyediakan fitur-fitur utama berikut untuk "
"memastikan kepatuhan terhadap peraturan fiskal dan akuntansi lokal:"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/saudi_arabia.rst:58
msgid ""
":doc:`../accounting/get_started/chart_of_accounts`: a predefined structure "
"aligned with Saudi Arabian regulations"
msgstr ""
":doc:`../accounting/get_started/chart_of_accounts`: struktur yang telah "
"dikonfigurasi sebelumnya sesuai dengan peraturan Arab Saudi"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/saudi_arabia.rst:60
msgid ""
":ref:`localizations/saudi-arabia/taxes`: preconfigured tax rates, including "
"standard 15% VAT, zero-rated, and exempt options"
msgstr ""
":ref:`localizations/saudi-arabia/taxes`: tarif pajak yang telah "
"dikonfigurasi sebelumnya, termasuk PPN standar 15%, opsi tarif nol, dan "
"bebas pajak"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/saudi_arabia.rst:64
msgid ""
":ref:`Withholding taxes <localizations/saudi-arabia/withholding-taxes>`: "
"predefined withholding tax rules for applicable service categories"
msgstr ""
":ref:`Pajak pemotongan <localizations/saudi-arabia/withholding-taxes>`: "
"aturan pajak pemotongan yang telah dikonfigurasi sebelumnya untuk kategori "
"layanan yang berlaku"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/saudi_arabia.rst:66
msgid ":ref:`localizations/saudi-arabia/tax-reporting`: automated tax reports"
msgstr ":ref:`localizations/saudi-arabia/tax-reporting`: laporan pajak otomatis"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/saudi_arabia.rst:67
msgid ""
":ref:`E-invoicing (ZATCA) <localizations/saudi-arabia/zatca>`: integration "
