msgstr ""
":ref:`E-invoicing (ZATCA) <localizations/saudi-arabia/zatca>`: integrasi "
"untuk faktur elektronik sesuai dengan persyaratan pemerintah Arab Saudi"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/saudi_arabia.rst:75
msgid ""
"The Saudi Arabian localization includes preconfigured sales, purchase, and "
"withholding :doc:`taxes <../accounting/taxes>`:"
msgstr ""
"Lokalisasi Arab Saudi mencakup :doc:`pajak <../accounting/taxes>` Penjualan, "
"Pembelian, dan pemotongan yang telah dikonfigurasi sebelumnya:"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/saudi_arabia.rst:0
msgid ""
"Standard VAT (15%): The prevailing rate applied to the majority of goods and "
"services supplied within the Kingdom."
msgstr ""
"PPN standar (15%): Tarif yang berlaku diterapkan pada sebagian besar barang "
"dan jasa yang dipasok di dalam Kerajaan."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/saudi_arabia.rst:0
msgid ""
"The supplier charges 15% VAT on the sale (Output VAT) and is generally "
"entitled to deduct the VAT paid on its business purchases (Input VAT)."
msgstr ""
"Pemasok mengenakan PPN 15% pada penjualan (PPN Keluaran) dan umumnya berhak "
"mengurangi PPN yang dibayar pada pembelian bisnisnya (PPN Masukan)."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/saudi_arabia.rst:84
#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/united_arab_emirates.rst:87
msgid ""
"Most commercial sales, retail goods, telecommunication services, non-exempt "
"private education, and non-exempt private healthcare."
msgstr ""
"Sebagian besar penjualan komersial, barang ritel, layanan telekomunikasi, "
"pendidikan swasta yang tidak dikecualikan, dan layanan kesehatan swasta yang "
"tidak dikecualikan."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/saudi_arabia.rst:0
msgid ""
"Zero-rated VAT (0%): These are taxable supplies where the rate of tax "
"applied is 0%."
msgstr ""
"PPN tarif nol (0%): Ini adalah pasokan kena pajak di mana tarif pajak yang "
"diterapkan adalah 0%."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/saudi_arabia.rst:0
msgid ""
"The supplier charges no VAT on the sale, but, critically, is fully entitled "
"to recover the input VAT paid on costs related to making those supplies."
msgstr ""
"Pemasok tidak mengenakan PPN pada penjualan, tetapi, yang penting, "
"sepenuhnya berhak untuk memulihkan PPN masukan yang dibayar atas biaya yang "
"terkait dengan pembuatan pasokan tersebut."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/saudi_arabia.rst:92
msgid ""
"Exports: Supplies of goods and services to a non-:abbr:`GCC (Gulf "
"Cooperation Council)` resident or for consumption outside the Kingdom."
msgstr ""
"Ekspor: Pasokan barang dan jasa kepada penduduk non-:abbr:`GCC (Dewan Kerja "
"Sama Teluk)` atau untuk konsumsi di luar Kerajaan."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/saudi_arabia.rst:94
msgid ""
"International transport: Services for the international transport of "
"passengers and goods, and related services."
msgstr ""
"Transportasi internasional: Layanan untuk transportasi internasional "
"penumpang dan barang, serta layanan terkait."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/saudi_arabia.rst:96
msgid ""
"Specific goods: Supplies of qualifying medicines and qualifying medical "
"equipment, as specified by ZATCA/Ministry of Health."
msgstr ""
"Barang tertentu: Pasokan obat-obatan yang memenuhi syarat dan peralatan "
"medis yang memenuhi syarat, sebagaimana ditentukan oleh ZATCA/Kementerian "
"Kesehatan."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/saudi_arabia.rst:98
msgid ""
"Residential property: First supply of a new residential building/property to "
"a Saudi citizen, up to a value of SAR 1,000,000 (subject to specific "
"conditions)."
msgstr ""
"Properti residensial: Pasokan pertama bangunan/properti residensial baru "
"kepada warga negara Saudi, hingga nilai SAR 1.000.000 (tunduk pada ketentuan "
"tertentu)."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/saudi_arabia.rst:100
msgid ""
"Investment metals: Qualifying gold, silver, and platinum of 99% purity or "
"higher (supplied for investment)."
msgstr ""
"Logam investasi: Emas, perak, dan platina yang memenuhi syarat dengan "
"kemurnian 99% atau lebih tinggi (dipasok untuk investasi)."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/saudi_arabia.rst:0
msgid ""
"Exempt transactions: These transactions fall outside the scope of VAT, "
"meaning they are not subject to the tax."
msgstr ""
"Transaksi bebas pajak: Transaksi ini berada di luar cakupan PPN, yang "
"berarti tidak dikenakan pajak."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/saudi_arabia.rst:0
msgid ""
"The supplier does not charge any VAT on the sale and is not entitled to "
"recover the input VAT paid on costs related to making these supplies "
"(resulting in an unrecoverable cost)."
msgstr ""
"Pemasok tidak membebankan PPN apa pun atas penjualan dan tidak berhak "
"memulihkan PPN masukan yang dibayarkan atas biaya terkait dengan penyediaan "
"pasokan ini (mengakibatkan biaya yang tidak dapat dipulihkan)."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/saudi_arabia.rst:109
msgid ""
"Financial services: interest on loans, provision of credit, operations of "
"current/deposit/savings accounts, issuance or transfer of money or "
"securities, and life insurance."
msgstr ""
"Layanan keuangan: bunga pinjaman, penyediaan kredit, operasi rekening giro/"
"deposito/tabungan, penerbitan atau transfer uang atau surat berharga, dan "
"asuransi jiwa."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/saudi_arabia.rst:112
msgid "Real estate: bare rental (leasing) of residential property."
msgstr "Real estat: sewa kosong (leasing) properti residensial."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/saudi_arabia.rst:0
msgid ""
"Import VAT: VAT is levied on goods brought into the Kingdom from a "
"non-:abbr:`GCC (Gulf Cooperation Council)` country."
msgstr ""
"PPN Impor: PPN dikenakan atas barang yang dibawa ke Kerajaan dari negara non-"
":abbr:`GCC (Gulf Cooperation Council)`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/saudi_arabia.rst:0
msgid ""
"VAT is typically calculated at the standard rate (15%) and is paid to the "
"Customs Authority at the point of importation."
msgstr ""
"PPN biasanya dihitung dengan tarif standar (15%) dan dibayarkan kepada "
"Otoritas Bea Cukai pada saat impor."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/saudi_arabia.rst:120
msgid ""
"When assigning :doc:`discounts <../../sales/sales/products_prices/prices/"
"discounts>` to invoices, assign a 15% tax on the line containing a global "
"discount to comply with ZATCA rules."
msgstr ""
"Saat menetapkan :doc:`diskon <../../sales/sales/products_prices/prices/"
"discounts>` ke faktur, tetapkan pajak 15% pada baris yang berisi diskon "
"global untuk mematuhi aturan ZATCA."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/saudi_arabia.rst:124
#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/united_arab_emirates.rst:128
msgid "Reverse charge mechanism (RCM)"
msgstr "Mekanisme reverse charge (RCM)"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/saudi_arabia.rst:126
msgid ""
"Description: Mechanism that shifts the responsibility for accounting for VAT "
"from the non-resident supplier to the resident recipient of the goods or "
"services."
msgstr ""
"Deskripsi: Mekanisme yang mengalihkan tanggung jawab untuk menghitung PPN "
"dari pemasok non-residen ke penerima barang atau jasa yang merupakan residen."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/saudi_arabia.rst:128
msgid ""
"Mechanism: The VAT-registered recipient must calculate and account for the "
"VAT (as both output VAT and input VAT) in their :ref:`VAT return <accounting/"
"tax-returns/vat-report>`. This typically results in a net zero effect on the "
"VAT return, provided the input tax is fully deductible."
msgstr ""
"Mekanisme: Penerima yang terdaftar PPN harus menghitung dan mencatat PPN "
"(baik sebagai PPN keluaran maupun PPN masukan) dalam :ref:`pengembalian PPN "
"<accounting/tax-returns/vat-report>` mereka. Ini biasanya menghasilkan efek "
"nol bersih pada pengembalian PPN, asalkan pajak masukan sepenuhnya dapat "
"dikurangkan."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/saudi_arabia.rst:131
msgid ""
"Application: Primarily used for B2B supplies of services from a non-resident "
"supplier to a VAT-registered business in Saudi Arabia."
msgstr ""
"Penerapan: Terutama digunakan untuk pasokan B2B layanan dari pemasok non-"
"residen kepada bisnis terdaftar PPN di Arab Saudi."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/saudi_arabia.rst:139
msgid ""
"There are two available methods for calculating withholding tax: gross and "
"deducted."
msgstr ""
"Ada dua metode yang tersedia untuk menghitung pajak pemotongan: bruto dan "
"dipotong."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/saudi_arabia.rst:141
msgid ""
"Gross withholding: This is the primary configuration, where the withholding "
"amount is calculated in addition to the bill total. For example, if the "
"total bill is entered as 115 SAR, the system calculates the base plus "
"Withholding Tax (WHT) without reducing the payment amount."
msgstr ""
"Pemotongan bruto: Ini adalah konfigurasi utama, di mana jumlah pemotongan "
"dihitung sebagai tambahan dari total tagihan. Misalnya, jika total tagihan "
"dimasukkan sebagai 115 SAR, sistem menghitung dasar ditambah Pajak "
"Pemotongan (WHT) tanpa mengurangi jumlah pembayaran."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/saudi_arabia.rst:144
msgid ""
"Deducted withholding: It reduces the payable amount by the withholding "
"amount directly, meaning the total payment reflects the deduction upfront. "
"This affects how the accounting entries and payable lines are booked."
msgstr ""
"Pemotongan yang dipotong: Ini mengurangi jumlah yang harus dibayar dengan "
"jumlah pemotongan secara langsung, yang berarti total pembayaran "
"mencerminkan pengurangan di awal. Ini memengaruhi bagaimana entri akuntansi "
"dan baris yang harus dibayar dicatat."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/saudi_arabia.rst:149
msgid ""
"Deducted withholding taxes are not enabled by default. To activate it, go to "
"Accounting --> Configuration --> Taxes and enable the relevant withholding "
"tax."
msgstr ""
"Pajak pemotongan yang dipotong tidak diaktifkan secara default. Untuk "
"mengaktifkannya, buka Akuntansi --> Konfigurasi --> Pajak dan aktifkan pajak "
"pemotongan yang relevan."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/saudi_arabia.rst:152
msgid ""
"The following Withholding Tax (WHT) configurations are preloaded and "
"available for use:"
msgstr ""
"Konfigurasi Pajak Pemotongan (WHT) berikut telah dimuat sebelumnya dan "
"tersedia untuk digunakan:"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/saudi_arabia.rst:154
msgid ""
"5% Withholding Tax: Applied on payments for rent, dividends, technical and "
"consulting services, air and maritime freight, as well as interest, "
"insurance, and reinsurance premiums."
msgstr ""
"Pajak Pemotongan 5%: Diterapkan pada pembayaran untuk sewa, dividen, layanan "
"teknis dan konsultasi, pengangkutan udara dan laut, serta bunga, asuransi, "
"dan premi reasuransi."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/saudi_arabia.rst:156
msgid ""
"15% Withholding Tax: Applies to royalties and other general service payments "
"made to non-residents."
msgstr ""
"Pajak Pemotongan 15%: Berlaku untuk royalti dan pembayaran layanan umum "
"lainnya yang dilakukan kepada non-residen."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/saudi_arabia.rst:158
msgid ""
"20% Withholding Tax: Reserved for management fees and specific high-value "
"service payments."
msgstr ""
"Pajak Pemotongan 20%: Dicadangkan untuk biaya manajemen dan pembayaran "
"layanan bernilai tinggi tertentu."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/saudi_arabia.rst:165
msgid ""
"The :ref:`VAT and Withholding Return <accounting/tax-returns/vat-report>` "
"provide a detailed breakdown of taxable, zero-rated, exempt, and withholding "
"transactions. Like other financial reports, the :guilabel:`VAT` "
"and :guilabel:`Withholding Return` can be filtered by period, compared "
"against other periods, and exported in Excel and PDF formats, ensuring "
"compliance with Saudi Arabia tax laws."
msgstr ""
":ref:`Pengembalian PPN dan Pemotongan <accounting/tax-returns/vat-report>` "
"menyediakan rincian terperinci transaksi kena pajak, tarif nol, bebas pajak, "
"dan pemotongan. Seperti laporan keuangan lainnya, :guilabel:`PPN` dan "
":guilabel:`Pengembalian Pemotongan` dapat difilter berdasarkan periode, "
"dibandingkan dengan periode lain, dan diekspor dalam format Excel dan PDF, "
"memastikan kepatuhan terhadap undang-undang pajak Arab Saudi."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/saudi_arabia.rst:176
msgid ""
"To ensure proper integration with :ref:`ZATCA <localizations/saudi-arabia/"
"zatca>`, the following fields are required on the :ref:`company record "
"<general/companies/company>`:"
msgstr ""
"Untuk memastikan integrasi yang tepat dengan :ref:`ZATCA <localizations/"
"saudi-arabia/zatca>`, kolom-kolom berikut diperlukan pada :ref:`catatan "
"perusahaan <general/companies/company>`:"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/saudi_arabia.rst:179
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Company Name`, limited to a maximum of 63 characters to comply "
"with ZATCA requirements."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Nama Perusahaan`, dibatasi maksimum 63 karakter untuk mematuhi "
"persyaratan ZATCA."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/saudi_arabia.rst:181
msgid ""
"All relevant :guilabel:`Address` fields, including "
"the :guilabel:`District`, :guilabel:`Building Number`, and :guilabel:`Plot "
"Identification`"
msgstr ""
"Semua kolom :guilabel:`Alamat` yang relevan, termasuk :guilabel:`Distrik`, "
":guilabel:`Nomor Bangunan`, dan :guilabel:`Identifikasi Plot`"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/saudi_arabia.rst:183
msgid ":guilabel:`Identification Scheme`"
msgstr ":guilabel:`Skema Identifikasi`"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/saudi_arabia.rst:185
msgid ":guilabel:`Tax Identification Number`"
msgstr ":guilabel:`Nomor Identifikasi Pajak`"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/saudi_arabia.rst:186
