msgstr ""
"Untuk :guilabel:`Tax Invoices`: Buka :menuselection:`Accounting --> "
"Configuration --> Settings`, di bagian :guilabel:`Customer Invoices`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/saudi_arabia.rst:242
#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/united_arab_emirates.rst:255
msgid ""
"For Point of Sale receipts: Go to :menuselection:`Point of Sale --> "
"Configuration --> Settings`, and navigate to the :guilabel:`Bills & "
"Receipts` section."
msgstr ""
"Untuk struk POS: Buka :menuselection:`POS --> Konfigurasi --> Pengaturan`, "
"dan navigasi ke bagian :guilabel:`Tagihan & Struk`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/saudi_arabia.rst:245
#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/united_arab_emirates.rst:258
msgid ""
"Then, enable the :guilabel:`Gulf Cooperation Council Format` option, "
"and :guilabel:`Save`."
msgstr ""
"Kemudian, aktifkan opsi :guilabel:`Format Dewan Kerja Sama Teluk`, dan "
":guilabel:`Simpan`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/saudi_arabia.rst:250
msgid "Electronic invoicing with ZATCA"
msgstr "Faktur elektronik dengan ZATCA"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/saudi_arabia.rst:252
msgid ""
"The ZATCA e-invoicing system is designed to streamline and digitize the "
"invoicing process for businesses operating in Saudi Arabia."
msgstr ""
"Sistem e-invoicing ZATCA dirancang untuk menyederhanakan dan mendigitalkan "
"proses penagihan bagi bisnis yang beroperasi di Arab Saudi."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/saudi_arabia.rst:255
msgid ""
"ZATCA Phase 2 employs a clearance e-invoicing model for Business-to-Business "
"(B2B) transactions. Conversely, for Business-to-Consumer (B2C) transactions, "
"Odoo generates a QR code and subsequently reports these transactions to the "
"Fatoora reporting endpoint."
msgstr ""
"Fase 2 ZATCA menggunakan model e-invoicing clearance untuk transaksi "
"Business-to-Business (B2B). Sebaliknya, untuk transaksi Business-to-Consumer "
"(B2C), Odoo menghasilkan kode QR dan selanjutnya melaporkan transaksi ini ke "
"endpoint pelaporan Fatoora."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/saudi_arabia.rst:259
msgid ""
"In a B2B scenario, a :guilabel:`Tax Invoice` is issued, whereas in a B2C "
"scenario, a :guilabel:`Simplified Tax Invoice` is generated."
msgstr ""
"Dalam skenario B2B, :guilabel:`Faktur Pajak` diterbitkan, sedangkan dalam "
"skenario B2C, :guilabel:`Faktur Pajak Sederhana` dihasilkan."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/saudi_arabia.rst:263
msgid ""
"`ZATCA e-invoicing page <https://zatca.gov.sa/en/E-Invoicing/Pages/"
