msgstr "Periksa sertifikat autentikasi dan kunci rahasia."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/saudi_arabia.rst:424
msgid "Correct the credentials and resubmit."
msgstr "Perbaiki kredensial dan kirim ulang."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/saudi_arabia.rst:425
msgid ":guilabel:`413 – Payload Too Large (Invoice Not Received)`"
msgstr ":guilabel:`413 – Muatan Terlalu Besar (Faktur Tidak Diterima)`"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/saudi_arabia.rst:426
msgid "Reduce the invoice payload size and resend."
msgstr "Kurangi ukuran muatan faktur dan kirim ulang."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/saudi_arabia.rst:427
msgid ":guilabel:`429 – Too Many Requests (Invoice Not Received)`"
msgstr ":guilabel:`429 – Too Many Requests (Faktur Tidak Diterima)`"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/saudi_arabia.rst:428
#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/saudi_arabia.rst:430
#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/saudi_arabia.rst:432
#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/saudi_arabia.rst:434
msgid "Resend the invoice."
msgstr "Kirim ulang faktur."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/saudi_arabia.rst:429
msgid ":guilabel:`500 – Internal Server Error (Invoice Not Received)`"
msgstr ":guilabel:`500 – Internal Server Error (Faktur Tidak Diterima)`"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/saudi_arabia.rst:431
msgid ":guilabel:`503 – Service Unavailable (Invoice Not Received)`"
msgstr ":guilabel:`503 – Service Unavailable (Faktur Tidak Diterima)`"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/saudi_arabia.rst:433
msgid ":guilabel:`504 – Request Timed Out (Invoice Not Received)`"
msgstr ":guilabel:`504 – Request Timed Out (Faktur Tidak Diterima)`"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/saudi_arabia.rst:436
msgid ""
"The color of the message displayed in the chatter after an invoice is "
"confirmed and submitted indicates the following information:"
msgstr ""
"Warna pesan yang ditampilkan di chatter setelah faktur dikonfirmasi dan "
"dikirimkan menunjukkan informasi berikut:"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/saudi_arabia.rst:439
msgid ""
"Green: invoice successfully accepted - The invoice is fully compliant and "
"has been successfully validated by ZATCA."
msgstr ""
"Hijau: faktur berhasil diterima - Faktur sepenuhnya sesuai dan telah "
"berhasil divalidasi oleh ZATCA."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/saudi_arabia.rst:441
msgid ""
"Yellow: invoice accepted with warnings - The invoice is legally valid but "
"was accepted with a warning. The issue should be reviewed and corrected for "
"future submissions."
msgstr ""
"Kuning: faktur diterima dengan peringatan - Faktur sah secara hukum tetapi "
"diterima dengan peringatan. Masalah harus ditinjau dan diperbaiki untuk "
"pengiriman di masa mendatang."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/saudi_arabia.rst:443
msgid ""
"Red: invoice was rejected - The invoice was not accepted by ZATCA and is not "
"legally valid. It must be corrected and resubmitted."
msgstr ""
"Merah: faktur ditolak - Faktur tidak diterima oleh ZATCA dan tidak sah "
"secara hukum. Faktur harus diperbaiki dan dikirim ulang."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/saudi_arabia.rst:446
msgid ""
"If the invoice is rejected, an error message is displayed in the invoice’s "
"chatter. Correct the underlying issue described in the message description "
"in the invoice or company settings. Then, to resubmit the invoice, "
"click :guilabel:`Retry`."
msgstr ""
"Jika faktur ditolak, pesan kesalahan ditampilkan di chatter faktur. Perbaiki "
"masalah yang mendasari yang dijelaskan dalam deskripsi pesan di faktur atau "
"pengaturan perusahaan. Kemudian, untuk mengirim ulang faktur, klik "
":guilabel:`Coba Lagi`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/saudi_arabia.rst:451
msgid ""
"Invoices rejected by ZATCA remain in a :guilabel:`Rejected` state and are "
"not considered legally valid."
msgstr ""
"Faktur yang ditolak oleh ZATCA tetap dalam status :guilabel:`Ditolak` dan "
"tidak dianggap sah secara hukum."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/saudi_arabia.rst:453
msgid ""
"In case of any incidents, technical errors, or emergency matters that "
"prevent the generation of e-invoices/e-receipts, notify `ZATCA <https://"
"zatca.gov.sa/en/E-Invoicing/FailureNotifications/Pages/"
"VerifyTaxpayer.aspx>`_. Once the issue has been resolved, contact ZATCA "
"again using the same communication channel. For specific failure scenarios, "
"refer to the steps outlined in `ZATCA's guidelines (page 45) <https://"
"zatca.gov.sa/en/E-Invoicing/Introduction/Guidelines/Documents/E-"
"Invoicing_Detailed__Guideline.pdf>`_."
msgstr ""
"Jika terjadi insiden, kesalahan teknis, atau masalah darurat yang mencegah "
"pembuatan e-faktur/e-resi, beritahu `ZATCA <https://zatca.gov.sa/en/E-"
"Invoicing/FailureNotifications/Pages/VerifyTaxpayer.aspx>`_. Setelah masalah "
"teratasi, hubungi ZATCA lagi menggunakan saluran komunikasi yang sama. Untuk "
"skenario kegagalan tertentu, lihat langkah-langkah yang diuraikan dalam "
"`pedoman ZATCA (halaman 45) <https://zatca.gov.sa/en/E-Invoicing/"
"Introduction/Guidelines/Documents/E-Invoicing_Detailed__Guideline.pdf>`_."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/saudi_arabia.rst:462
msgid "QR code verification"
msgstr "Verifikasi kode QR"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/saudi_arabia.rst:464
msgid ""
"To verify the QR Code on the invoice, scan it using the official `ZATCA app "
"<https://zatca.gov.sa/en/AboutUs/ZATCAApps/Pages/default.aspx>`_."
msgstr ""
"Untuk memverifikasi Kode QR pada faktur, pindai menggunakan `aplikasi resmi "
"ZATCA <https://zatca.gov.sa/en/AboutUs/ZATCAApps/Pages/default.aspx>`_."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/saudi_arabia.rst:467
msgid ""
"Once in the app, click :guilabel:`Services`. In the :guilabel:`E-Invoice "
"Validation` section, click :guilabel:`Start Service`. Then, begin scanning "
"the invoices' QR codes."
msgstr ""
"Setelah berada di aplikasi, klik :guilabel:`Services`. Di bagian "
":guilabel:`E-Invoice Validation`, klik :guilabel:`Start Service`. Kemudian, "
"mulai pindai kode QR faktur."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/saudi_arabia.rst:471
msgid ""
"The QR verification output does not display a currency symbol. The invoice "
"amount is always shown as a plain numeric value, irrespective of the "
"currency used."
msgstr ""
"Output verifikasi QR tidak menampilkan simbol mata uang. Jumlah faktur "
"selalu ditampilkan sebagai nilai numerik biasa, terlepas dari mata uang yang "
"digunakan."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/saudi_arabia.rst:473
msgid ""
"An invoice with a related contact (e.g., Invoicing Address) is sent to the "
"clearance API (B2B)."
msgstr ""
"Faktur dengan kontak terkait (misalnya, Alamat Penagihan) dikirim ke API "
"clearance (B2B)."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/saudi_arabia.rst:481
msgid ""
"To create a :ref:`credit <accounting/credit_notes/issue-credit-note>` "
"or :ref:`debit <accounting/credit_notes/issue-debit-note>` note, include a "
"ZATCA-approved reason from the :guilabel:`ZATCA Reason` field in "
"the :guilabel:`Credit`/:guilabel:`Debit` window, as required by ZATCA "
"regulations:"
msgstr ""
"Untuk membuat nota :ref:`kredit <accounting/credit_notes/issue-credit-note>` "
"atau :ref:`debit <accounting/credit_notes/issue-debit-note>`, sertakan "
"alasan yang disetujui ZATCA dari bidang :guilabel:`ZATCA Reason` di jendela "
":guilabel:`Credit`/:guilabel:`Debit`, sebagaimana dipersyaratkan oleh "
"peraturan ZATCA:"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/saudi_arabia.rst:486
msgid ""
"Cancellation or suspension of the supplies after their occurrence, either "
"wholly or partially."
msgstr ""
"Pembatalan atau penghentian pasokan setelah terjadinya, baik seluruhnya "
"maupun sebagian."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/saudi_arabia.rst:487
msgid ""
"Essential change or amendment in the supply that results in a change to the "
"VAT due."
msgstr ""
"Perubahan atau amandemen esensial dalam penyediaan yang mengakibatkan "
"perubahan PPN yang terutang."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/saudi_arabia.rst:488
msgid ""
"Amendment of the supply value that was pre-agreed between the supplier and "
"the consumer."
msgstr ""
"Amandemen nilai penyediaan yang telah disepakati sebelumnya antara pemasok "
"dan konsumen."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/saudi_arabia.rst:489
msgid "Goods or services refund."
msgstr "Pengembalian barang atau jasa."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/saudi_arabia.rst:490
msgid "Change in the seller’s or buyer’s information."
msgstr "Perubahan informasi penjual atau pembeli."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/saudi_arabia.rst:493
msgid ""
"The :guilabel:`ZATCA Reason` field is also available in the credit/debit "
"note :guilabel:`Other Info` tab."
msgstr ""
"Bidang :guilabel:`ZATCA Reason` juga tersedia di tab :guilabel:`Other Info` "
"nota kredit/debit."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/saudi_arabia.rst:497
msgid ""
"Whenever the credit/debit note is unrelated/independent, fill in the "
"sequential number of the original invoice(s) that the credit/debit note is "
"related to in the :guilabel:`Customer Reference` field."
msgstr ""
"Setiap kali nota kredit/debit tidak terkait/independen, isi nomor urut "
"faktur asli yang terkait dengan nota kredit/debit tersebut di bidang "
":guilabel:`Customer Reference`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/saudi_arabia.rst:504
msgid "Down payments (advance payments)"
msgstr "Uang muka (pembayaran di muka)"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/saudi_arabia.rst:506
msgid ""
"Handle :doc:`down payments (advance payments) <../../sales/sales/invoicing/"
"invoicing_policy>` in compliance with `ZATCA’s guidelines <https://"
"zatca.gov.sa/en/E-Invoicing/Introduction/Guidelines/Documents/E-"
"Invoicing_Detailed__Guideline.pdf>`_."
msgstr ""
"Tangani :doc:`uang muka (pembayaran di muka) <../../sales/sales/invoicing/"
"invoicing_policy>` sesuai dengan `pedoman ZATCA<https://zatca.gov.sa/en/E-"
"Invoicing/Introduction/Guidelines/Documents/E-"
"Invoicing_Detailed__Guideline.pdf>`_."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/saudi_arabia.rst:513
msgid "Retention"
msgstr "Retensi"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/saudi_arabia.rst:515
msgid ""
"Retention is an amount temporarily held by the customer, defined by the "
"commercial contract, to ensure the quality and completion of the work. It is "
"usually a percentage of the invoice value (e.g., 5-10%) and serves as "
"security against future defects; it is ultimately paid back to the "
"contractor once the warranty period expires."
msgstr ""
"Retensi adalah jumlah yang sementara ditahan oleh pelanggan, yang ditentukan "
"oleh kontrak komersial, untuk memastikan kualitas dan penyelesaian "
"pekerjaan. Biasanya berupa persentase dari nilai faktur (misalnya, 5-10%) "
"dan berfungsi sebagai jaminan terhadap cacat di masa mendatang; pada "
"akhirnya dibayarkan kembali kepada kontraktor setelah masa garansi berakhir."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/saudi_arabia.rst:520
msgid ""
"For ZATCA, the commonly applied rule is that VAT is calculated based on the "
"full invoice amount, even if the customer withholds a portion as retention. "
"ZATCA advises taxpayers to first determine the tax position, specifically "
"whether the retention amount reduces the taxable amount or not. Tax position "
"depends on contractual terms."
msgstr ""
"Untuk ZATCA, aturan yang umumnya diterapkan adalah PPN dihitung berdasarkan "
"jumlah faktur penuh, meskipun pelanggan menahan sebagian sebagai retensi. "
"ZATCA menyarankan wajib pajak untuk terlebih dahulu menentukan posisi pajak, "
"khususnya apakah jumlah retensi mengurangi jumlah kena pajak atau tidak. "
"Posisi pajak bergantung pada ketentuan kontrak."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/saudi_arabia.rst:525
msgid ""
"The Odoo retention workflow ensures, through tax position, that the "
"retention amount does not reduce the taxable amount."
msgstr ""
"Alur kerja retensi Odoo memastikan, melalui posisi pajak, bahwa jumlah "
"retensi tidak mengurangi jumlah kena pajak."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/saudi_arabia.rst:529
msgid ""
"Any negative tax (e.g., -20%) configured with the :guilabel:`Is Retention` "
"checkbox enabled has no impact on the UBL 2.1. It only applies when this "
"retention tax is used in conjunction with a generic tax (e.g., 15%) on the "
"invoice line and represents a percentage of that invoice line. For example, "
"if a taxpayer wants to retain 20% of the invoiced goods, both the 15% tax "
"and the -20% retention tax would be applied to the invoice line."
msgstr ""
"Setiap pajak negatif (misalnya, -20%) yang dikonfigurasi dengan kotak "
"centang :guilabel:`Is Retention` yang diaktifkan tidak berdampak pada UBL "
"2.1. Ini hanya berlaku ketika pajak retensi ini digunakan bersama dengan "
"pajak umum (misalnya, 15%) pada baris faktur dan mewakili persentase dari "
"baris faktur tersebut. Misalnya, jika wajib pajak ingin menahan 20% dari "
"barang yang ditagih, baik pajak 15% maupun pajak retensi -20% akan "
"diterapkan pada baris faktur."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/saudi_arabia.rst:535
msgid ""
"Within this same tax position, retention can also be applied at the invoice "
"level as an separate negative invoice line using a 0% (Not Subject to VAT) "
"tax rate."
msgstr ""
"Dalam posisi pajak yang sama ini, retensi juga dapat diterapkan di tingkat "
"faktur sebagai baris faktur negatif terpisah menggunakan tarif pajak 0% "
"(Tidak Dikenakan PPN)."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/saudi_arabia.rst:539
msgid ""
"Adding either a negative tax with :guilabel:`Is Retention` enabled and a "
"generic tax on the invoice line, or a separate negative invoice line with a "
"0% (:guilabel:`Not Subject to VAT`) tax rate at the invoice level, usually "
"indicates that VAT has been paid on the full taxable amount. Therefore, the "
"final invoice for releasing the retention amount does not qualify as "
"a :guilabel:`Tax Invoice` and should not be submitted to ZATCA."
msgstr ""
"Menambahkan pajak negatif dengan :guilabel:`Is Retention` diaktifkan dan "
"pajak umum pada baris faktur, atau baris faktur negatif terpisah dengan "
"tarif pajak 0% (:guilabel:`Not Subject to VAT`) pada tingkat faktur, "
"biasanya menunjukkan bahwa PPN telah dibayar atas jumlah kena pajak penuh. "
"Oleh karena itu, faktur akhir untuk melepaskan jumlah retensi tidak memenuhi "
"syarat sebagai :guilabel:`Tax Invoice` dan tidak boleh dikirimkan ke ZATCA."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/saudi_arabia.rst:544
msgid ""
"The 0% (Not Subject to VAT) tax is already preconfigured according to ZATCA "
"rules; do not modify it."
msgstr ""
"Pajak 0% (Tidak Dikenakan PPN) sudah dikonfigurasi sebelumnya sesuai dengan "
"aturan ZATCA; jangan memodifikasinya."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/saudi_arabia.rst:548
msgid ""
"When creating a new retention tax, create a :guilabel:`Retention` tax group "
"and assign it to this newly created retention tax to comply with ZATCA rules."
msgstr ""
"Saat membuat pajak retensi baru, buat grup pajak :guilabel:`Retention` dan "
"tetapkan ke pajak retensi yang baru dibuat ini untuk mematuhi aturan ZATCA."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/saudi_arabia.rst:550
msgid ""
"To add the :guilabel:`Retention Amount` as a note on the invoice line, "
"click :guilabel:`Add a note` to comply with ZATCA rules. For example - "
"Retention Amount: `[retention amount] SAR`"
msgstr ""
"Untuk menambahkan :guilabel:`Retention Amount` sebagai catatan pada baris "
"faktur, klik :guilabel:`Add a note` untuk mematuhi aturan ZATCA. Misalnya - "
"Retention Amount: `[jumlah retensi] SAR`"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/saudi_arabia.rst:556
msgid "Generated documents"
msgstr "Dokumen yang dihasilkan"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/saudi_arabia.rst:558
msgid ""
"Once an invoice is submitted, a UBL 2.1 XML file is generated and sent to "
"ZATCA API endpoints. For auditability, this XML file is stored in the "
"chatter. To display it, click the :icon:`fa-"
"paperclip` :guilabel:`(attachments)` icon."
msgstr ""
"Setelah faktur dikirimkan, file XML UBL 2.1 dihasilkan dan dikirim ke "
"endpoint API ZATCA. Untuk kemampuan audit, file XML ini disimpan di chatter. "
"Untuk menampilkannya, klik ikon :icon:`fa-paperclip` :guilabel:`(lampiran)`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/saudi_arabia.rst:562
msgid ""
"Additionally, the invoice PDF generated when using :guilabel:`Send` is "
"displayed in the chatter. Both the XML and PDF files are permanently "
"attached to the invoice and cannot be deleted to ensure compliance with "
"ZATCA regulations."
msgstr ""
"Selain itu, PDF faktur yang dihasilkan saat menggunakan :guilabel:`Send` "
"ditampilkan di chatter. Baik file XML maupun PDF dilampirkan secara permanen "
"ke faktur dan tidak dapat dihapus untuk memastikan kepatuhan terhadap "
"peraturan ZATCA."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/saudi_arabia.rst:567
msgid ""
"Successfully ZATCA-submitted invoices can only be reset to draft "
"in :ref:`Sandbox <localizations/saudi-arabia/sandbox>` or :ref:`Simulation "
"(Pre-Production) <localizations/saudi-arabia/simulation>` modes."
msgstr ""
"Faktur yang berhasil dikirim ke ZATCA hanya dapat dikembalikan ke draf dalam "
"mode :ref:`Sandbox <localizations/saudi-arabia/sandbox>` atau :ref:`Simulasi "
"(Pra-Produksi) <localizations/saudi-arabia/simulation>`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/saudi_arabia.rst:572
msgid ""
"To automatically generate a PDF/A-3 with the embedded UBL 2.1, "
"click :guilabel:`Send`."
msgstr ""
"Untuk secara otomatis menghasilkan PDF/A-3 dengan UBL 2.1 yang tertanam, "
"klik :guilabel:`Kirim`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/saudi_arabia.rst:582
msgid "ZATCA integration configuration"
msgstr "Konfigurasi integrasi ZATCA"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/saudi_arabia.rst:585
msgid ""
"Make sure the :guilabel:`Saudi Arabia - E-invoicing (Simplified) "
"(l10n_sa_edi_pos)` module is :ref:`installed <general/install>`."
msgstr ""
"Pastikan modul :guilabel:`Arab Saudi - E-invoicing (Simplified) "
"(l10n_sa_edi_pos)` telah :ref:`diinstal <general/install>`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/saudi_arabia.rst:588
msgid ""
"PoS orders must be properly reported in compliance with ZATCA Phase 2. To do "
"so, follow these steps:"
msgstr ""
"Pesanan POS harus dilaporkan dengan benar sesuai dengan ZATCA Fase 2. Untuk "
"melakukannya, ikuti langkah-langkah berikut:"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/saudi_arabia.rst:590
msgid ""
"Onboard the :guilabel:`Invoices` default journal in the :ref:`PoS settings "
"<pos/use/settings>`:"
msgstr ""
"Lakukan onboarding jurnal default :guilabel:`Faktur` di :ref:`pengaturan PoS "
"<pos/use/settings>`:"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/saudi_arabia.rst:592
msgid ""
"Go to :menuselection:`Point of Sale --> Configuration --> Settings`. In the "
"yellow banner, select the relevant :guilabel:`Point of Sale`, then navigate "
"to the :guilabel:`Accounting` section."
msgstr ""
"Buka :menuselection:`POS --> Configuration --> Settings`. Pada banner "
"kuning, pilih :guilabel:`Point of Sale` yang relevan, kemudian arahkan ke "
"bagian :guilabel:`Akuntansi`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/saudi_arabia.rst:595
msgid ""
"In the :guilabel:`Default Journals` section, find the :guilabel:`Invoices` "
"field and click the :icon:`oi-arrow-right` :guilabel:`(right arrow)` to open "
"the default :guilabel:`Sales` journal."
msgstr ""
"Di bagian :guilabel:`Default Journals`, temukan field :guilabel:`Invoices` "
"dan klik :icon:`oi-arrow-right` :guilabel:`(panah kanan)` untuk membuka "
"jurnal :guilabel:`Penjualan` default."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/saudi_arabia.rst:601
msgid ""
":ref:`Assign a customer <pos/use/customers>` to the order before finalizing "
"the transaction."
msgstr ""
":ref:`Tetapkan pelanggan <pos/use/customers>` ke pesanan sebelum "
"menyelesaikan transaksi."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/saudi_arabia.rst:603
msgid ""
"These steps ensure that each receipt is processed as a compliant e-invoice "
"and reported to the ZATCA portal in real time. Once the receipt is "
"generated, the Phase 2 QR code automatically appears on both the printed "
"receipt and the PDF."
msgstr ""
"Langkah-langkah ini memastikan bahwa setiap struk diproses sebagai e-invoice "
"yang sesuai dan dilaporkan ke portal ZATCA secara real time. Setelah struk "
"dihasilkan, kode QR Fase 2 secara otomatis muncul pada struk cetak dan PDF."

