#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/spain.rst:105
msgid "Veri*Factu"
msgstr "Veri*Factu"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/spain.rst:108
msgid ""
"Producers of Veri*Factu billing systems must self-certify their compliance "
"with the regulations. :download:`Download Odoo's \"declaración "
"responsable\"<spain/declaracion_responsable.pdf>`"
msgstr ""
"Produsen sistem penagihan Veri*Factu harus menyatakan sendiri kepatuhan "
"mereka terhadap peraturan. :download:`Unduh \"declaración responsable\" "
"Odoo<spain/declaracion_responsable.pdf>`"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/spain.rst:111
msgid ""
"**Veri*Factu** is an e-Invoicing system used by the Spanish Tax Agency. It "
"is mandatory for most taxpayers in Spain, except for those who use the SII "
"system or are under a regional tax regime (i.e., TicketBai)."
msgstr ""
"**Veri*Factu** adalah sistem e-Invoicing yang digunakan oleh Badan Pajak "
"Spanyol. Sistem ini wajib bagi sebagian besar wajib pajak di Spanyol, "
"kecuali bagi mereka yang menggunakan sistem SII atau berada di bawah rezim "
"pajak regional (misalnya, TicketBai)."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/spain.rst:115
msgid ""
"Odoo allows :ref:`invoices <localizations/spain/veri-factu-invoices>` and "
"Point of Sale :ref:`orders <localizations/spain/veri-factu-orders>` to be "
"automatically sent to the tax authorities."
msgstr ""
"Odoo memungkinkan :ref:`faktur <localizations/spain/veri-factu-invoices>` "
"dan :ref:`pesanan <localizations/spain/veri-factu-orders>` Point of Sale "
"untuk dikirim secara otomatis ke otoritas pajak."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/spain.rst:123
msgid "To enable **Veri\\*Factu**, follow these steps:"
msgstr "Untuk mengaktifkan **Veri\\*Factu**, ikuti langkah-langkah berikut:"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/spain.rst:125
msgid ""
"Open the Settings app to make sure your company's :guilabel:`Country` "
"and :guilabel:`Tax ID` are correctly set in the :ref:`Companies <general/"
"companies/company>` section."
msgstr ""
"Buka aplikasi Pengaturan untuk memastikan :guilabel:`Negara` dan "
":guilabel:`ID Pajak` perusahaan Anda telah diatur dengan benar di bagian "
":ref:`Perusahaan <general/companies/company>`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/spain.rst:127
msgid ""
":ref:`Install <general/install>` the :guilabel:`Spain - Veri*Factu "
"(l10n_es_edi_verifactu)` module."
msgstr ""
":ref:`Instal <general/install>` modul :guilabel:`Spain - Veri*Factu "
"(l10n_es_edi_verifactu)`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/spain.rst:129
msgid ""
"Go to :menuselection:`Accounting --> Configuration --> Settings`, scroll to "
"the :guilabel:`Veri\\*Factu` section, check the :guilabel:`Enable "
"Veri*Factu` option, and click :icon:`oi-arrow-right` :guilabel:`Manage "
"certificates` to add a certificate."
msgstr ""
"Buka :menuselection:`Akuntansi --> Konfigurasi --> Pengaturan`, gulir ke "
"bagian :guilabel:`Veri\\*Factu`, centang opsi :guilabel:`Enable Veri*Factu`, "
"dan klik :icon:`oi-arrow-right` :guilabel:`Kelola sertifikat` untuk "
"menambahkan sertifikat."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/spain.rst:132
msgid ""
"In the :guilabel:`Certificates for Veri\\*Factu` list view, "
"click :guilabel:`New`."
msgstr ""
"Di tampilan daftar :guilabel:`Certificates for Veri\\*Factu`, klik "
":guilabel:`Baru`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/spain.rst:133
msgid ""
"Click :guilabel:`Upload your file`, then select a certificate file and enter "
"the :guilabel:`Password` needed to open the certificate (if there is one)."
msgstr ""
"Klik :guilabel:`Upload your file`, lalu pilih file sertifikat dan masukkan "
":guilabel:`Kata Sandi` yang diperlukan untuk membuka sertifikat (jika ada)."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/spain.rst:137
msgid "At least one certificate has to be uploaded."
msgstr "Setidaknya satu sertifikat harus diunggah."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/spain.rst:138
msgid ""
"By default Veri*Factu is in testing mode. The data is sent to test servers "
"and is not considered official. When official data can be sent to the "
"production servers, go to the :guilabel:`Veri\\*Factu` section in "
"the :guilabel:`Settings` and disable :guilabel:`Test Environment`."
msgstr ""
"Secara default, Veri*Factu berada dalam mode pengujian. Data dikirim ke "
"server uji dan tidak dianggap resmi. Ketika data resmi dapat dikirim ke "
"server produksi, buka bagian :guilabel:`Veri\\*Factu` di "
":guilabel:`Pengaturan` dan nonaktifkan :guilabel:`Test Environment`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/spain.rst:148
msgid ""
"Once an :doc:`invoice <../../finance/accounting/customer_invoices>` is "
"confirmed, it can be :ref:`sent <accounting/invoice/sending>`. In "
"the :guilabel:`Send` window, the Veri*Factu option is available if "
"Veri*Factu has been enabled."
msgstr ""
"Setelah :doc:`faktur <../../finance/accounting/customer_invoices>` "
"dikonfirmasi, faktur dapat :ref:`dikirim <accounting/invoice/sending>`. Di "
"jendela :guilabel:`Kirim`, opsi Veri*Factu tersedia jika Veri*Factu telah "
"diaktifkan."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/spain.rst:152
msgid ""
"Click :guilabel:`Send` to generate a JSON file containing the invoice "
"details. This file is stored as a Veri*Factu document. In "
"the :guilabel:`Veri*Factu` tab, all corresponding documents are listed by "
"their creation date and current status."
msgstr ""
"Klik :guilabel:`Kirim` untuk menghasilkan file JSON yang berisi detail "
"faktur. File ini disimpan sebagai dokumen Veri*Factu. Di tab "
":guilabel:`Veri*Factu`, semua dokumen terkait tercantum berdasarkan tanggal "
"pembuatan dan status saat ini."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/spain.rst:157
#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/spain.rst:182
msgid ""
"To download a JSON file, click on its document in the :guilabel:`Veri*Factu` "
"tab. Then, in the :guilabel:`Open: Veri*Factu Documents` window, click the "
"link in the :guilabel:`JSON` field."
msgstr ""
"Untuk mengunduh file JSON, klik dokumennya di tab :guilabel:`Veri*Factu`. "
"Kemudian, di jendela :guilabel:`Open: Veri*Factu Documents`, klik tautan di "
"bidang :guilabel:`JSON`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/spain.rst:161
#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/spain.rst:186
msgid ""
"The document should be sent to the :abbr:`AEAT (Agencia Estatal de "
"Administración Tributaria)` immediately. However, it may be delayed due to "
"mandatory waiting periods between submissions required by the :abbr:`AEAT "
"(Agencia Estatal de Administración Tributaria)`. In such cases, the document "
"is automatically sent the next time a scheduled action runs."
msgstr ""
"Dokumen harus dikirim ke :abbr:`AEAT (Agencia Estatal de Administración "
"Tributaria)` segera. Namun, pengiriman mungkin tertunda karena periode "
"tunggu wajib antara pengajuan yang diwajibkan oleh :abbr:`AEAT (Agencia "
"Estatal de Administración Tributaria)`. Dalam kasus seperti itu, dokumen "
"secara otomatis dikirim saat tindakan terjadwal berikutnya berjalan."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/spain.rst:165
msgid ""
"A Veri\\*Factu **QR code** appears on the invoice PDF. Scan this code to "
"verify that the invoice has been received and recognized by the :abbr:`AEAT "
"(Agencia Estatal de Administración Tributaria)`."
msgstr ""
"**Kode QR** Veri\\*Factu muncul di PDF faktur. Pindai kode ini untuk "
"memverifikasi bahwa faktur telah diterima dan diakui oleh :abbr:`AEAT "
"(Agencia Estatal de Administración Tributaria)`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/spain.rst:172
msgid "Point of sale orders"
msgstr "Pesanan point of sale"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/spain.rst:174
msgid ""
"Once an order has been :ref:`paid <pos/use/sell>`, a JSON file containing "
"the order details is generated. This file is stored as a Veri*Factu document."
msgstr ""
"Setelah pesanan :ref:`dibayar <pos/use/sell>`, file JSON yang berisi detail "
"pesanan dihasilkan. File ini disimpan sebagai dokumen Veri*Factu."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/spain.rst:177
msgid ""
"Go to :menuselection:`Point of Sale --> Orders --> Orders`. In "
"the :guilabel:`Orders` list view, select the relevant order. In "
"the :guilabel:`Veri*Factu` tab, all the corresponding documents are listed "
"by their creation date and current status."
msgstr ""
"Buka :menuselection:`POS --> Pesanan --> Pesanan`. Di tampilan daftar "
":guilabel:`Pesanan`, pilih pesanan yang relevan. Di tab "
":guilabel:`Veri*Factu`, semua dokumen terkait didaftarkan berdasarkan "
"tanggal pembuatan dan status saat ini."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/spain.rst:191
msgid ""
"If an invoice is generated for an order during the payment process, the "
"Veri*Factu document is :ref:`created and sent for the invoice <localizations/"
"spain/veri-factu-invoices>` instead."
msgstr ""
"Jika faktur dibuat untuk pesanan selama proses pembayaran, dokumen "
"Veri*Factu :ref:`dibuat dan dikirim untuk faktur tersebut <localizations/"
"spain/veri-factu-invoices>`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/spain.rst:195
msgid ""
"A Veri\\*Factu **QR code** appears on the order receipt, even if an invoice "
"is created for the order. Scan this code to verify that the invoice has been "
"received and recognized by the :abbr:`AEAT (Agencia Estatal de "
"Administración Tributaria)`"
msgstr ""
"**Kode QR** Veri\\*Factu muncul pada struk pesanan, meskipun faktur dibuat "
"untuk pesanan tersebut. Pindai kode ini untuk memverifikasi bahwa faktur "
"telah diterima dan diakui oleh :abbr:`AEAT (Agencia Estatal de "
"Administración Tributaria)`"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/spain.rst:200
msgid "TicketBAI"
msgstr "TicketBAI"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/spain.rst:202
msgid ""
"`Ticket BAI <https://www.gipuzkoa.eus/es/web/ogasuna/ticketbai>`_ or "
"**TBAI** is an e-Invoicing system used by the Basque government and its "
"three provincial councils (Álava, Biscay, and Gipuzkoa)."
msgstr ""
"`Ticket BAI <https://www.gipuzkoa.eus/es/web/ogasuna/ticketbai>`_ atau "
"**TBAI** adalah sistem e-Invoicing yang digunakan oleh pemerintah Basque dan "
"tiga dewan provinsinya (Álava, Biscay, dan Gipuzkoa)."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/spain.rst:206
msgid ""
"Odoo supports the **TicketBAI (TBAI)** electronic invoicing format for all "
"three regions of the **Basque Country**. To enable **TicketBAI**, set your "
"company's :guilabel:`Country` and :guilabel:`Tax ID` "
"under :menuselection:`Settings --> General Settings` in "
"the :guilabel:`Companies` section."
msgstr ""
"Odoo mendukung format faktur elektronik **TicketBAI (TBAI)** untuk ketiga "
"wilayah **Negara Basque**. Untuk mengaktifkan **TicketBAI**, atur "
":guilabel:`Negara` dan :guilabel:`ID Pajak` perusahaan Anda di "
":menuselection:`Pengaturan --> Pengaturan Umum` pada bagian "
":guilabel:`Perusahaan`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/spain.rst:211
msgid ""
"Then, :ref:`install <general/install>` the module :guilabel:`Spain "
"-TicketBAI (l10n_es_edi_TBAI)`, go to :menuselection:`Accounting --> "
"Configuration --> Settings`, and select a **region** in the :guilabel:`Spain "
"Localization` section's :guilabel:`Tax Agency for TBAI` field."
msgstr ""
"Kemudian, :ref:`instal <general/install>` modul :guilabel:`Spain -TicketBAI "
"(l10n_es_edi_TBAI)`, buka :menuselection:`Akuntansi --> Konfigurasi --> "
"Pengaturan`, dan pilih **wilayah** di kolom :guilabel:`Tax Agency for TBAI` "
"pada bagian :guilabel:`Spain Localization`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/spain.rst:215
msgid ""
"Once a region is selected, click :guilabel:`Manage certificates (SII/"
"TicketBAI)`, then click :guilabel:`New`, upload the certificate, and enter "
"the password provided by the tax agency."
msgstr ""
"Setelah wilayah dipilih, klik :guilabel:`Manage certificates (SII/TicketBAI)"
"`, kemudian klik :guilabel:`Baru`, unggah sertifikat, dan masukkan kata "
"sandi yang diberikan oleh otoritas pajak."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/spain.rst:219
msgid ""
"If you are testing certificates, enable :guilabel:`Test Mode` in "
"the :guilabel:`Spain Localization` section, which can be found "
"under :guilabel:`Accounting` in the **Settings** app."
msgstr ""
"Jika Anda menguji sertifikat, aktifkan :guilabel:`Test Mode` di bagian "
":guilabel:`Spain Localization`, yang dapat ditemukan di bawah "
":guilabel:`Akuntansi` di aplikasi **Pengaturan**."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/spain.rst:224
#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/spain.rst:268
msgid "Use case"
msgstr "Kasus penggunaan"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/spain.rst:226
msgid ""
"Once an invoice has been :doc:`created <../../finance/accounting/"
"customer_invoices>` and confirmed, a TicketBAI **banner** appears at the top."
msgstr ""
"Setelah faktur :doc:`dibuat <../../finance/accounting/customer_invoices>` "
"dan dikonfirmasi, **banner** TicketBAI muncul di bagian atas."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/spain.rst:None
msgid "TicketBAI banner at the top of the invoice once sent."
msgstr "Banner TicketBAI di bagian atas faktur setelah dikirim."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/spain.rst:232
msgid ""
"Odoo sends invoices through TicketBAI automatically every **24 hours**. "
"However, you can click :guilabel:`Process now` to send the invoice "
"immediately."
msgstr ""
"Odoo mengirim faktur melalui TicketBAI secara otomatis setiap **24 jam**. "
"Namun, Anda dapat mengklik :guilabel:`Process now` untuk mengirim faktur "
"segera."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/spain.rst:235
msgid ""
"When the invoice is **sent**, the status of the field :guilabel:`Electronic "
"Invoice` changes to :guilabel:`Sent`, and the XML file can be found in the "
"**chatter**. Under the :guilabel:`EDI Documents` tab, you can see the "
"traceability of other generated documents related to the invoice (e.g., if "
"the invoice should also be sent through the **SII**, it will appear here)."
msgstr ""
"Ketika faktur **dikirim**, status kolom :guilabel:`Electronic Invoice` "
"berubah menjadi :guilabel:`Sent`, dan file XML dapat ditemukan di "
"**chatter**. Di bawah tab :guilabel:`EDI Documents`, Anda dapat melihat "
"ketertelusuran dokumen lain yang dihasilkan terkait dengan faktur (misalnya, "
"jika faktur juga harus dikirim melalui **SII**, itu akan muncul di sini)."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/spain.rst:241
msgid "The TBAI **QR code** is displayed on the invoice PDF."
msgstr "**Kode QR** TBAI ditampilkan pada PDF faktur."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/spain.rst:0
msgid "QR code of the TicketBAI on the invoice."
msgstr "Kode QR TicketBAI pada faktur."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/spain.rst:247
msgid "FACe"
msgstr "FACe"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/spain.rst:249
msgid ""
"`FACe <https://face.gob.es/en>`_ is the e-Invoicing platform used by the "
"public administrations in Spain to send electronic invoices."
msgstr ""
"`FACe <https://face.gob.es/en>`_ adalah platform e-Invoicing yang digunakan "
"oleh administrasi publik di Spanyol untuk mengirim faktur elektronik."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/spain.rst:252
msgid ""
"Before configuring the :abbr:`FACe (General Entrance for Electronic "
"Invoices)` system, :ref:`install <general/install>` the :guilabel:`Spain - "
"Facturae EDI (l10n_es_edi_facturae)` module and other **Facturae EDI**-"
"related modules."
msgstr ""
"Sebelum mengonfigurasi sistem :abbr:`FACe (General Entrance for Electronic "
"Invoices)`, :ref:`instal <general/install>` modul :guilabel:`Spain - "
"Facturae EDI (l10n_es_edi_facturae)` dan modul terkait **Facturae EDI** "
"lainnya."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/spain.rst:256
msgid "To configure FACe, follow these steps:"
msgstr "Untuk mengonfigurasi FACe, ikuti langkah-langkah berikut:"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/spain.rst:258
msgid "Go to :menuselection:`Accounting --> Configuration --> Certificates`."
msgstr "Buka :menuselection:`Akuntansi --> Konfigurasi --> Sertifikat`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/spain.rst:259
msgid "Click :guilabel:`New` to create a new certificate."
msgstr "Klik :guilabel:`Baru` untuk membuat sertifikat baru."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/spain.rst:260
msgid ""
"Complete the fields, including uploading the file of "
"the :guilabel:`Certificate` provided by the tax agency and the "
"provided :guilabel:`Certificate Password`."
msgstr ""
"Lengkapi kolom-kolom yang ada, termasuk mengunggah file "
":guilabel:`Sertifikat` yang disediakan oleh lembaga pajak dan "
":guilabel:`Kata Sandi Sertifikat` yang diberikan."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/spain.rst:264
msgid ""
"If using the Invoicing app instead of Accounting, go "
"to :menuselection:`Invoicing --> Configuration --> Certificates`."
msgstr ""
"Jika menggunakan aplikasi Penagihan, bukan Akuntansi, buka "
":menuselection:`Penagihan --> Konfigurasi --> Sertifikat`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/spain.rst:270
msgid ""
"Once you have :doc:`created <../../finance/accounting/customer_invoices>` an "
"invoice and confirmed it, click :guilabel:`Send`. Make "
"sure :guilabel:`Generate Facturae edi file` is enabled, and "
"click :guilabel:`Send` again. Once the invoice is sent, the generated XML "
"file is available in the **chatter**."
msgstr ""
"Setelah Anda :doc:`membuat <../../finance/accounting/customer_invoices>` "
"invoice dan mengonfirmasinya, klik :guilabel:`Kirim`. Pastikan "
":guilabel:`Generate Facturae edi file` diaktifkan, dan klik "
":guilabel:`Kirim` lagi. Setelah invoice dikirim, file XML yang dihasilkan "
"tersedia di **chatter**."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/spain.rst:276
msgid ""
"The file is **NOT** automatically sent. You have to send it yourself "
"manually."
msgstr ""
"File **TIDAK** dikirim secara otomatis. Anda harus mengirimnya sendiri "
"secara manual."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/spain.rst:279
msgid ""
"You can send **FACe** XML files in batch through `the governmental portal "
"<https://www.facturae.gob.es/formato/Paginas/descarga-aplicacion-"
"escritorio.aspx>`_."
msgstr ""
"Anda dapat mengirim file XML **FACe** secara batch melalui `portal "
"pemerintah <https://www.facturae.gob.es/formato/Paginas/descarga-aplicacion-"
"escritorio.aspx>`_."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/spain.rst:282
msgid "Administrative centers"
msgstr "Pusat administratif"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/spain.rst:284
msgid ""
"In order for **FACe** to work with **administrative centers**, the invoice "
"*must* include specific data about the centers."
msgstr ""
"Agar **FACe** dapat bekerja dengan **pusat administratif**, faktur *harus* "
"menyertakan data spesifik tentang pusat tersebut."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/spain.rst:287
msgid ""
"To add **administrative centers**, create a new **contact** to add to the "
"**partner** company. Select :guilabel:`FACe Center` as the **type**, assign "
"one or more **role(s)** to that contact, and :guilabel:`Save`. The **three** "
"roles usually required are:"
msgstr ""
"Untuk menambahkan **pusat administratif**, buat **kontak** baru untuk "
"ditambahkan ke perusahaan **mitra**. Pilih :guilabel:`Pusat FACe` sebagai "
"**tipe**, tetapkan satu atau beberapa **peran** ke kontak tersebut, dan "
":guilabel:`Simpan`. **Tiga** peran yang biasanya diperlukan adalah:"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/spain.rst:291
msgid "Órgano gestor: :guilabel:`Receptor` (Receiver);"
msgstr "Órgano gestor: :guilabel:`Penerima` (Receiver);"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/spain.rst:292
msgid "Unidad tramitadora: :guilabel:`Pagador` (Payer);"
msgstr "Unidad tramitadora: :guilabel:`Pembayar` (Payer);"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/spain.rst:293
msgid "Oficina contable: :guilabel:`Fiscal` (Fiscal)."
msgstr "Oficina contable: :guilabel:`Fiskal` (Fiscal)."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/spain.rst:None
msgid "Administrative center contact form for public entities."
msgstr "Formulir kontak pusat administratif untuk entitas publik."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/spain.rst:299
msgid ""
"If administrative centers need different :guilabel:`Codes` per role, you "
"*must* create different centers for each role."
msgstr ""
"Jika pusat administratif memerlukan :guilabel:`Kode` yang berbeda per peran, "
"Anda *harus* membuat pusat yang berbeda untuk setiap peran."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/spain.rst:301
msgid ""
"When an electronic invoice is created using a partner with **administrative "
"centers**, *all* administrative centers are included in the invoice."
msgstr ""
"Ketika faktur elektronik dibuat menggunakan mitra dengan **pusat "
"administratif**, *semua* pusat administratif disertakan dalam faktur."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/spain.rst:303
msgid ""
"You can add one contact with multiple roles or multiple contacts with a "
"different role each."
msgstr ""
"Anda dapat menambahkan satu kontak dengan beberapa peran atau beberapa "
"kontak dengan peran yang berbeda."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/switzerland.rst:3
msgid "Switzerland"
msgstr "Switzerland"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/switzerland.rst:6
msgid "ISR (In-payment Slip with Reference number)"
msgstr "ISR (Slip Pembayaran dengan Nomor Referensi)"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/switzerland.rst:8
msgid ""
"The ISRs are payment slips used in Switzerland. You can print them directly "
"from Odoo. On the customer invoices, there is a new button called *Print "
"ISR*."
msgstr ""
"ISR adalah slip pembayaran yang digunakan di Swiss. Anda dapat mencetaknya "
"langsung dari Odoo. Pada faktur pelanggan, terdapat tombol baru bernama "
"*Cetak ISR*."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/switzerland.rst:16
msgid ""
"The button *Print ISR* only appears there is well a bank account defined on "
"the invoice. You can use CH6309000000250097798 as bank account number and "
"010391391 as CHF ISR reference."
msgstr ""
"Tombol *Cetak ISR* hanya muncul jika ada rekening bank yang ditentukan pada "
"faktur. Anda dapat menggunakan CH6309000000250097798 sebagai nomor rekening "
"bank dan 010391391 sebagai referensi ISR CHF."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/switzerland.rst:23
msgid "Then you open a pdf with the ISR."
msgstr "Kemudian Anda akan membuka pdf dengan ISR."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/switzerland.rst:28
msgid ""
"There exists two layouts for ISR: one with, and one without the bank "
"coordinates. To choose which one to use, there is an option to print the "
"bank information on the ISR. To activate it, go "
"in :menuselection:`Accounting --> Configuration --> Settings --> Customer "
"Invoices` and enable **Print bank on ISR**:"
msgstr ""
"Terdapat dua tata letak untuk ISR: satu dengan, dan satu tanpa koordinat "
"bank. Untuk memilih mana yang akan digunakan, ada opsi untuk mencetak "
"informasi bank pada ISR. Untuk mengaktifkannya, buka "
":menuselection:`Akuntansi --> Konfigurasi --> Pengaturan --> Faktur "
"Pelanggan` dan aktifkan **Cetak bank pada ISR**:"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/switzerland.rst:38
msgid "ISR reference on invoices"
msgstr "Referensi ISR pada faktur"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/switzerland.rst:40
msgid ""
"To ease the reconciliation process, you can add your ISR reference as "
"**Payment Reference** on your invoices."
msgstr ""
"Untuk mempermudah proses rekonsiliasi, Anda dapat menambahkan referensi ISR "
"Anda sebagai **Referensi Pembayaran** pada faktur Anda."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/switzerland.rst:43
msgid ""
"To do so, you need to configure the Journal you usually use to issue "
"invoices. Go to :menuselection:`Accounting --> Configuration --> Journals`, "
"open the Journal you want to modify (By default, the Journal is named "
"*Customer Invoices*), click en *Edit*, and open the *Advanced Settings* tab. "
"In the **Communication Standard** field, select *Switzerland*, and click on "
"*Save*."
msgstr ""
"Untuk melakukannya, Anda perlu mengkonfigurasi Jurnal yang biasanya Anda "
"gunakan untuk menerbitkan faktur. Buka :menuselection:`Akuntansi --> "
"Konfigurasi --> Jurnal`, buka Jurnal yang ingin Anda ubah (Secara default, "
"Jurnal diberi nama *Faktur Pelanggan*), klik *Edit*, dan buka tab "
"*Pengaturan Lanjutan*. Di bidang **Standar Komunikasi**, pilih "
"*Switzerland*, dan klik *Simpan*."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/switzerland.rst:None
msgid ""
"Configure your Journal to display your ISR as payment reference on your "
"invoices in Odoo"
msgstr ""
"Konfigurasikan Jurnal Anda untuk menampilkan ISR Anda sebagai referensi "
"pembayaran pada faktur Anda di Odoo"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/switzerland.rst:53
msgid "Currency Rate Live Update"
msgstr "Pembaruan Langsung Kurs Mata Uang"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/switzerland.rst:55
msgid ""
"You can update automatically your currencies rates based on the Federal Tax "
"Administration from Switzerland. For this, go in :menuselection:`Accounting "
"--> Settings`, activate the multi-currencies setting and choose the service "
"you want."
msgstr ""
"Anda dapat memperbarui kurs mata uang Anda secara otomatis berdasarkan "
"Federal Tax Administration dari Swiss. Untuk ini, buka "
":menuselection:`Akuntansi --> Pengaturan`, aktifkan pengaturan multi-mata "
"uang dan pilih layanan yang Anda inginkan."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/switzerland.rst:64
msgid "Updated VAT for January 2018"
msgstr "PPN yang Diperbarui untuk Januari 2018"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/switzerland.rst:66
msgid ""
"Starting from the 1st January 2018, new reduced VAT rates will be applied in "
"Switzerland. The normal 8.0% rate will switch to 7.7% and the specific rate "
"for the hotel sector will switch from 3.8% to 3.7%."
msgstr ""
"Mulai 1 Januari 2018, tarif PPN yang dikurangi baru akan diterapkan di "
"Swiss. Tarif normal 8,0% akan berubah menjadi 7,7% dan tarif khusus untuk "
"sektor hotel akan berubah dari 3,8% menjadi 3,7%."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/switzerland.rst:71
msgid ""
"How to update your taxes in Odoo Enterprise (Odoo Online or On-premise)?"
msgstr ""
"Bagaimana cara memperbarui pajak Anda di Odoo Enterprise (Odoo Online atau "
"On-premise)?"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/switzerland.rst:73
msgid ""
"If you have the V11.1 version, all the work is already been done, you don't "
"have to do anything."
msgstr ""
"Jika Anda memiliki versi V11.1, semua pekerjaan sudah selesai, Anda tidak "
"perlu melakukan apa pun."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/switzerland.rst:76
msgid ""
"If you have started on an earlier version, you first have to update the "
"module \"Switzerland - Accounting Reports\". For this, you go "
"in :menuselection:`Apps --> remove the filter \"Apps\" --> search for "
"\"Switzerland - Accounting Reports\" --> open the module --> click on "
"\"upgrade\"`."
msgstr ""
"Jika Anda memulai pada versi sebelumnya, Anda harus memperbarui modul "
"\"Switzerland - Accounting Reports\" terlebih dahulu. Untuk ini, buka "
":menuselection:`Aplikasi --> hapus filter \"Aplikasi\" --> cari "
"\"Switzerland - Accounting Reports\" --> buka modul --> klik \"tingkatkan\"`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/switzerland.rst:83
msgid ""
"Once it has been done, you can work on creating new taxes for the updated "
"rates."
msgstr ""
"Setelah selesai, Anda dapat membuat pajak baru untuk tarif yang diperbarui."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/switzerland.rst:87
msgid ""
"**Do not suppress or modify the existing taxes** (8.0% and 3.8%). You want "
"to keep them since you may have to use both rates for a short period of "
"time. Instead, remember to archive them once you have encoded all your 2017 "
"transactions."
msgstr ""
"**Jangan hapus atau ubah pajak yang ada** (8,0% dan 3,8%). Anda ingin "
"menyimpannya karena Anda mungkin harus menggunakan kedua tarif untuk jangka "
"waktu singkat. Sebaliknya, ingatlah untuk mengarsipkannya setelah Anda "
"mengkodekan semua transaksi 2017 Anda."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/switzerland.rst:92
msgid "The creation of such taxes should be done in the following manner:"
msgstr "Pembuatan pajak tersebut harus dilakukan dengan cara berikut:"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/switzerland.rst:94
msgid ""
"**Purchase taxes**: copy the origin tax, change its name, label on invoice, "
"rate and tax group (effective from v10 only)"
msgstr ""
"**Pajak pembelian**: salin pajak asli, ubah nama, label pada faktur, tarif, "
"dan grup pajaknya (berlaku dari v10 saja)"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/switzerland.rst:97
msgid ""
"**Sale taxes**: copy the origin tax, change its name, label on invoice, rate "
"and tax group (effective from v10 only). Since the vat report now shows the "
"details for old and new rates, you should also set the tags accordingly to"
msgstr ""
"**Pajak penjualan**: salin pajak asli, ubah nama, label pada faktur, tarif, "
"dan grup pajaknya (berlaku dari v10 saja). Karena laporan PPN sekarang "
"menampilkan detail untuk tarif lama dan baru, Anda juga harus mengatur tag "
"yang sesuai dengan"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/switzerland.rst:102
msgid ""
"For 7.7% taxes: Switzerland VAT Form: grid 302 base, Switzerland VAT Form: "
"grid 302 tax"
msgstr ""
"Untuk pajak 7,7%: Switzerland VAT Form: grid 302 base, Switzerland VAT Form: "
"grid 302 tax"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/switzerland.rst:105
msgid ""
"For 3.7% taxes: Switzerland VAT Form: grid 342 base, Switzerland VAT Form: "
"grid 342 tax"
msgstr ""
"Untuk pajak 3,7%: Switzerland VAT Form: grid 342 base, Switzerland VAT Form: "
"grid 342 tax"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/switzerland.rst:108
msgid ""
"You'll find below, as examples, the correct configuration for all taxes "
"included in Odoo by default"
msgstr ""
