#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/turkiye.rst:368
msgid ""
"The e-Dispatch is an electronic document that replaces traditional paper "
"delivery notes, allowing businesses to digitally issue, transmit, and track "
"shipment details for goods in transit. In Odoo, users can generate e-"
"Dispatch documents as XML and upload them through the Nilvera integration, "
"ensuring compliant and traceable delivery operations."
msgstr ""
"E-Dispatch adalah dokumen elektronik yang menggantikan surat jalan "
"tradisional berbasis kertas, memungkinkan bisnis untuk menerbitkan, "
"mengirimkan, dan melacak detail pengiriman barang dalam perjalanan secara "
"digital. Di Odoo, pengguna dapat menghasilkan dokumen e-Dispatch sebagai XML "
"dan mengunggahnya melalui integrasi Nilvera, memastikan operasi pengiriman "
"yang patuh dan dapat dilacak."

