":ref:`Bagan Akun <localizations/uae/coa>`: struktur yang telah ditentukan "
"sebelumnya dan selaras dengan standar akuntansi UEA"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/united_arab_emirates.rst:51
msgid ""
":ref:`Taxes <localizations/uae/taxes>`: preconfigured tax groups and "
"templates based on UAE VAT rules"
msgstr ""
":ref:`Pajak <localizations/uae/taxes>`: grup pajak dan templat yang telah "
"dikonfigurasi sebelumnya berdasarkan aturan PPN UAE"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/united_arab_emirates.rst:53
msgid ""
":doc:`../accounting/taxes/fiscal_positions`: automated tax adjustments to "
"handle local and cross-border transactions"
msgstr ""
":doc:`../accounting/taxes/fiscal_positions`: penyesuaian pajak otomatis "
"untuk menangani transaksi lokal dan lintas batas"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/united_arab_emirates.rst:55
msgid ""
":ref:`VAT return <localizations/uae/tax-return>`: structured according to "
"the UAE VAT return format, as issued by the :abbr:`FTA (Federal Tax "
