msgstr "Akun pendapatan yang dikecualikan"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/united_arab_emirates.rst:182
msgid ""
"Exempt income generally refers to revenue that is not subject to corporate "
"tax under UAE rules. Examples may include:"
msgstr ""
"Pendapatan yang dikecualikan umumnya mengacu pada pendapatan yang tidak "
"dikenakan pajak perusahaan berdasarkan peraturan UEA. Contohnya mungkin "
