msgid "Invoice types"
msgstr "Jenis faktur"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/united_arab_emirates.rst:265
msgid "The type of invoice to be issued depends on the following criteria:"
msgstr "Jenis faktur yang akan diterbitkan tergantung pada kriteria berikut:"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/united_arab_emirates.rst:267
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Tax Invoices (B2B)`: A :guilabel:`Tax Invoice`, used for business-"
"to-business transactions, contains all the details required for VAT "
"recovery, including the supplier and customer legal names, "
"addresses, :abbr:`TRN (Tax Registration Number)` numbers (where applicable), "
"itemized VAT amounts, and total amounts. This is the standard document "
"required when a customer intends to reclaim VAT."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Faktur Pajak (B2B)`: :guilabel:`Faktur Pajak`, yang digunakan "
"untuk transaksi business-to-business, berisi semua detail yang diperlukan "
"untuk pemulihan PPN, termasuk nama hukum pemasok dan pelanggan, alamat, "
"nomor :abbr:`TRN (Nomor Registrasi Pajak)` (jika berlaku), jumlah PPN yang "
"dirinci, dan jumlah total. Ini adalah dokumen standar yang diperlukan ketika "
"pelanggan bermaksud mengklaim kembali PPN."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/united_arab_emirates.rst:272
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Simplified Tax Invoices (B2C)`: A :guilabel:`Simplified Tax "
"Invoice` is primarily used for business-to-consumer (B2C) transactions, "
"where the customer is not expected to reclaim VAT. It contains reduced "
"customer information (customer :abbr:`TRN (Tax Registration Number)` is not "
"required), focusing instead on supplier details, VAT charged, and the total "
"amount payable."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Faktur Pajak Sederhana (B2C)`: :guilabel:`Faktur Pajak Sederhana` "
"terutama digunakan untuk transaksi business-to-consumer (B2C), di mana "
"pelanggan tidak diharapkan untuk mengklaim kembali PPN. Ini berisi informasi "
"pelanggan yang dikurangi (:abbr:`TRN (Nomor Registrasi Pajak)` pelanggan "
"tidak diperlukan), fokus pada detail pemasok, PPN yang dikenakan, dan jumlah "
"total yang harus dibayar."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/united_arab_emirates.rst:278
msgid ""
"A :guilabel:`Simplified Tax Invoice` is still a legally valid tax invoice "
"under VAT law."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Faktur Pajak Sederhana` masih merupakan faktur pajak yang sah "
"secara hukum berdasarkan undang-undang PPN."

