#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/united_kingdom.rst:390
msgid ""
"In the :guilabel:`Information correct declaration` section, confirm the "
"information is true and complete by checking the box. Then, enter "
"the :guilabel:`Password` used in the :guilabel:`HMRC Credentials` section "
"during :ref:`contractor setup <localization/united-kingdom/cis-contractor-"
"setup>`."
msgstr ""
