"tersebut benar dan lengkap dengan mencentang kotak. Kemudian, masukkan "
":guilabel:`Kata Sandi` yang digunakan di bagian :guilabel:`Kredensial HMRC` "
"selama :ref:`penyiapan kontraktor <localization/united-kingdom/cis-"
"contractor-setup>`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/united_kingdom.rst:394
msgid ""
"Click :guilabel:`Send` to prompt Odoo to request |HMRC| to initiate the "
"transaction."
msgstr ""
"Klik :guilabel:`Kirim` untuk meminta Odoo meminta |HMRC| memulai transaksi."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/united_kingdom.rst:396
msgid ""
"When |HMRC| replies to a transaction, Odoo automatically notifies the user "
"who submitted it by email. The email informs them that the response is "
"available in the company's chatter with an attached XML document for "
"download. Both the electronic and paper versions of the |HMRC| receipt "
"should be retained. If an error is detected, a new submission is required to "
"comply with |HMRC| requirements."
msgstr ""
"Ketika |HMRC| membalas transaksi, Odoo secara otomatis memberi tahu user "
"yang mengirimkannya melalui email. Email tersebut memberitahu mereka bahwa "
"respons tersedia di chatter perusahaan dengan dokumen XML terlampir untuk "
"diunduh. Versi elektronik dan kertas dari tanda terima |HMRC| harus "
"disimpan. Jika kesalahan terdeteksi, pengiriman baru diperlukan untuk "
"mematuhi persyaratan |HMRC|."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/united_kingdom.rst:403
msgid ""
"Transactions are updated daily. To manually update the |HMRC| request, click "
"the :icon:`fa-cog` :guilabel:`(gear)` icon and select :guilabel:`Refresh "
"HMRC request`."
msgstr ""
"Transaksi diperbarui setiap hari. Untuk memperbarui permintaan |HMRC| secara "
"manual, klik ikon :icon:`fa-cog` :guilabel:`(roda gigi)` dan pilih "
":guilabel:`Refresh HMRC request`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/united_kingdom.rst:405
msgid ""
"|CIS| invoices are included in the :guilabel:`CIS Deduction (GB)` report but "
"are not sent to |HMRC|."
msgstr ""
"Faktur |CIS| disertakan dalam laporan :guilabel:`CIS Deduction (GB)` tetapi "
"tidak dikirim ke |HMRC|."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/united_states.rst:16
msgid ""
"The Odoo fiscal localization package for the United States follows the "
"Generally Acceptable Accounting Principles (GAAP) accounting standards and "
"rules used to prepare financial statements, as outlined by the Financial "
"Accounting Standards Board (FASB) and adopted by the Securities and Exchange "
"Commission (SEC)."
msgstr ""
"Paket lokalisasi fiskal Odoo untuk Amerika Serikat mengikuti standar dan "
"aturan akuntansi Generally Acceptable Accounting Principles (GAAP) yang "
"digunakan untuk menyiapkan laporan keuangan, sebagaimana diuraikan oleh "
"Financial Accounting Standards Board (FASB) dan diadopsi oleh Securities and "
"Exchange Commission (SEC)."

