"Dari dashboard :guilabel:`Bagan Akun`, buat akun baru dengan mengklik tombol "
":guilabel:`Baru` di pojok kiri atas dashboard dan :ref:`mengisi formulir "
"yang sesuai <chart-of-account/create>`. Cari dan urutkan akun yang ada "
"dengan menggunakan :guilabel:`Filter` dan kriteria :guilabel:`Kelompokkan "
"Berdasarkan` tertentu, yang tersedia di menu drop-down pencarian."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/united_states.rst:189
msgid ""
"To filter accounts by category, click the :icon:`fa-caret-"
"down` :guilabel:`(dropdown)` icon to access the drop-down menu and look "
"under the :guilabel:`Filters` column for individual selections. Clicking on "
"a specific category will only show accounts that match that particular "
"filter."
msgstr ""
"Untuk memfilter akun berdasarkan kategori, klik ikon :icon:`fa-caret-down` "
":guilabel:`(dropdown)` untuk mengakses menu drop-down dan lihat di bawah "
"kolom :guilabel:`Filters` untuk pilihan individual. Mengklik kategori "
"tertentu hanya akan menampilkan akun yang cocok dengan filter tersebut."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/united_states.rst:193
msgid ""
"To view all the available account types, remove all of the filters in the "
"search bar, and then click the :icon:`fa-caret-down` :guilabel:`(dropdown)` "
"icon to access the drop-down menu. From there, select :guilabel:`Account "
"Type` under the :guilabel:`Group By` column heading to list all of the "
"account types in the table."
msgstr ""
"Untuk melihat semua tipe akun yang tersedia, hapus semua filter di bilah "
"pencarian, lalu klik ikon :icon:`fa-caret-down` :guilabel:`(dropdown)` untuk "
"mengakses menu drop-down. Dari sana, pilih :guilabel:`Account Type` di bawah "
"judul kolom :guilabel:`Group By` untuk membuat daftar semua tipe akun dalam "
"tabel."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/united_states.rst:None
msgid "Chart of Accounts grouped by Account Type."
msgstr "Bagan Akun dikelompokkan berdasarkan Tipe Akun."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/united_states.rst:201
msgid ""
"Besides structure, there are other key differences in the chart of accounts "
"in the United States, compared to other countries:"
msgstr ""
"Selain struktur, ada perbedaan utama lainnya dalam bagan akun di Amerika "
"Serikat, dibandingkan dengan negara lain:"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/united_states.rst:204
msgid ""
"**Specificity**: US |GAAP| often requires more detailed accounts compared to "
"some other countries. This can include separate accounts for various types "
"of revenue, expenses, and assets, providing more granular information in "
"financial reports."
msgstr ""
"**Kekhususan**: |GAAP| AS sering memerlukan akun yang lebih detail "
"dibandingkan dengan beberapa negara lain. Ini dapat mencakup akun terpisah "
"untuk berbagai jenis pendapatan, pengeluaran, dan aset, memberikan informasi "
"yang lebih rinci dalam laporan keuangan."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/united_states.rst:207
msgid ""
"**Regulatory Requirements**: In the United States, there are specific "
"regulatory requirements set by bodies such as the |SEC| for publicly traded "
"companies. These requirements may influence the structure and content of the "
"|COA| to ensure compliance with reporting standards."
msgstr ""
"**Persyaratan Regulasi**: Di Amerika Serikat, ada persyaratan regulasi "
"khusus yang ditetapkan oleh badan seperti |SEC| untuk perusahaan yang "
"diperdagangkan secara publik. Persyaratan ini dapat memengaruhi struktur dan "
"konten |COA| untuk memastikan kepatuhan terhadap standar pelaporan."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/united_states.rst:210
msgid ""
"**Industry Practices**: Certain industries in the United States may have "
"unique accounting requirements or specialized |COA| structures. For example, "
"financial institutions often have specific accounts related to loans, "
"investments, and interest income."
msgstr ""
"**Praktik Industri**: Industri tertentu di Amerika Serikat mungkin memiliki "
"persyaratan akuntansi unik atau struktur |COA| khusus. Misalnya, lembaga "
"keuangan sering memiliki akun khusus yang berkaitan dengan pinjaman, "
"investasi, dan pendapatan bunga."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/united_states.rst:213
msgid ""
"**Tax Considerations**: The |COA| may also reflect tax considerations, such "
"as accounts for deductible expenses, deferred tax assets, and liabilities, "
"to ensure compliance with tax laws and facilitate tax reporting."
msgstr ""
"**Pertimbangan Pajak**: |COA| juga dapat mencerminkan pertimbangan pajak, "
"seperti akun untuk pengeluaran yang dapat dikurangkan, aset pajak tangguhan, "
"dan kewajiban, untuk memastikan kepatuhan terhadap undang-undang pajak dan "
"memfasilitasi pelaporan pajak."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/united_states.rst:217
msgid ""
"These differences, ultimately, should be reflected in the |COA| structure "
"itself, with the addition of new accounts, as needed, in order to meet the "
"demands of US accounting reporting requirements."
msgstr ""
"Perbedaan ini, pada akhirnya, harus tercermin dalam struktur |COA| itu "
"sendiri, dengan penambahan akun baru, sesuai kebutuhan, untuk memenuhi "
"tuntutan persyaratan pelaporan akuntansi AS."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/united_states.rst:221
msgid ":ref:`Create a new account <chart-of-account/create>`"
msgstr ""

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/united_states.rst:229
msgid ""
"In the United States, tax rates and what is considered taxable vary by "
"jurisdiction. Default *sales* and *purchase* taxes are created automatically "
"when the Odoo **Accounting** app is installed. To manage existing or "
"configure additional taxes, navigate to :menuselection:`Accounting --> "
"Configuration --> Taxes`."
msgstr ""
"Di Amerika Serikat, tarif pajak dan apa yang dianggap kena pajak bervariasi "
"menurut yurisdiksi. Pajak *penjualan* dan *pembelian* default dibuat secara "
"otomatis saat aplikasi **Akuntansi** Odoo diinstal. Untuk mengelola pajak "
"yang ada atau mengonfigurasi pajak tambahan, navigasikan ke "
":menuselection:`Akuntansi --> Konfigurasi --> Pajak`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/united_states.rst:239
msgid ""
"**Avalara AvaTax** is a cloud-based tax calculation and compliance software "
"that integrates with Odoo for several localizations. Integrating AvaTax with "
"Odoo provides real-time and region-specific tax calculations when items are "
"sold, purchased, and invoiced in the database."
msgstr ""

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/united_states.rst:244
msgid ""
"AvaTax is available for integration with databases/companies that have "
"locations in the United States and Canada. Reference the :ref:`accounting/"
"avatax/fiscal_country` documentation for more information."
msgstr ""

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/united_states.rst:255
msgid ""
"`US Tax Compliance: AvaTax elearning video <https://www.odoo.com/slides/"
"slide/us-tax-compliance-avatax-2858?fullscreen=1>`_"
msgstr ""

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/united_states.rst:265
msgid ""
"A number of :doc:`report selections <../accounting/reporting>` are readily "
"available for the US localization, under the :menuselection:`Accounting app "
"--> Reporting` drop-down menu:"
msgstr ""

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/united_states.rst:268
msgid ""
":ref:`Balance Sheet <accounting/reporting/balance-sheet>`: A \"snapshot\" of "
"a company's financial position at a specific point in time, which contains "
"an overview of a company's assets, liabilities, and equity."
msgstr ""
":ref:`Neraca Keuangan <accounting/reporting/balance-sheet>`: \"Snapshot\" "
"dari posisi keuangan perusahaan pada titik waktu tertentu, yang berisi "
"gambaran umum aset, liabilitas, dan ekuitas perusahaan."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/united_states.rst:271
msgid ""
":ref:`Profit and Loss (P&L) <l10n_us/profit-loss-statement>`: Provides a "
"summary of a company's revenues, expenses, and profits/losses over a given "
"period of time. Also known as a *P&L statement* or *income statement*."
msgstr ""
":ref:`Laba Rugi (P&L) <l10n_us/profit-loss-statement>`: Menyediakan "
"ringkasan pendapatan, pengeluaran, dan laba/rugi perusahaan selama periode "
"waktu tertentu. Juga dikenal sebagai *laporan P&L* atau *laporan laba rugi*."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/united_states.rst:274
msgid ""
":ref:`Cash Flow Statement <l10n_us/cash-flow-statement>`: Shows how much "
"cash and cash equivalents a company has received and spent in a given period."
msgstr ""
":ref:`Laporan Arus Kas <l10n_us/cash-flow-statement>`: Menunjukkan berapa "
"banyak kas dan setara kas yang telah diterima dan dibelanjakan perusahaan "
"dalam periode tertentu."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/united_states.rst:276
msgid ""
":ref:`Executive Summary <accounting/reporting/executive-summary>`: An "
"overview report that covers the key performance indicators of a company's "
"financial position, such as revenue, profit, and debt."
msgstr ""
":ref:`Ringkasan Eksekutif <accounting/reporting/executive-summary>`: Laporan "
"gambaran umum yang mencakup indikator kinerja utama dari posisi keuangan "
"perusahaan, seperti pendapatan, laba, dan utang."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/united_states.rst:279
msgid ""
":ref:`Tax Report <accounting/reporting/tax-report>`: An official form filed "
"for a tax authority that reports income, expenses, and other pertinent tax "
"information. Tax reports allow taxpayers to calculate their tax liability, "
"schedule tax payments, or request refunds for the overpayment of taxes. In "
"Odoo, the tax report can be made monthly, every two months, quarterly, every "
"4 months, semi-annually, and annually."
msgstr ""
":ref:`Laporan Pajak <accounting/reporting/tax-report>`: Formulir resmi yang "
"diajukan untuk otoritas pajak yang melaporkan pendapatan, pengeluaran, dan "
"informasi pajak terkait lainnya. Laporan pajak memungkinkan wajib pajak "
"menghitung kewajiban pajak mereka, menjadwalkan pembayaran pajak, atau "
"meminta pengembalian dana untuk pembayaran pajak berlebih. Di Odoo, laporan "
"pajak dapat dibuat bulanan, setiap dua bulan, triwulanan, setiap 4 bulan, "
"semesteran, dan tahunan."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/united_states.rst:284
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Check Register`: A report that displays cash transactions "
"(regardless of the journal) with their running balance after the "
"transaction. Only visible with the *US - Accounting Reports* "
"(`l10n_us_reports`) module installed."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Register Cek`: Laporan yang menampilkan transaksi kas (terlepas "
"dari jurnal) dengan saldo berjalan mereka setelah transaksi. Hanya terlihat "
"dengan modul *US - Accounting Reports* (`l10n_us_reports`) terinstal."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/united_states.rst:287
msgid ""
":ref:`1099 Report <l10n_us/1099-report>`: A CSV download of payments made to "
"non-employees in a period to file electronically in a third-party service. "
"Only visible with the *1099 Reporting* (`l10n_us_1099`) module installed."
msgstr ""
":ref:`Laporan 1099 <l10n_us/1099-report>`: Unduhan CSV pembayaran yang "
"dilakukan kepada non-karyawan dalam periode untuk diajukan secara elektronik "
"di layanan pihak ketiga. Hanya terlihat dengan modul *1099 Reporting* "
"(`l10n_us_1099`) terinstal."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/united_states.rst:293
msgid ""
"Depending on the type of report, certain filters are available at the top of "
"the dashboard:"
msgstr ""

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/united_states.rst:295
msgid ""
"A *date* filter, indicated by a :icon:`fa-calendar` :guilabel:`(calendar)` "
"icon that precedes a date in *MM/DD/YYYY* format. Use this to select a "
"specific date or date range for the report."
msgstr ""
"Filter *tanggal*, ditunjukkan oleh ikon :icon:`fa-calendar` :guilabel:`"
"(kalender)` yang mendahului tanggal dalam format *MM/DD/YYYY*. Gunakan ini "
"untuk memilih tanggal atau rentang tanggal tertentu untuk laporan."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/united_states.rst:297
msgid ""
"A :icon:`fa-bar-chart` :guilabel:`Comparison` filter, to compare reporting "
"periods against each other"
msgstr ""
"Filter :icon:`fa-bar-chart` :guilabel:`Perbandingan`, untuk membandingkan "
"periode pelaporan satu sama lain"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/united_states.rst:299
msgid ""
"A *journal* filter, as indicated by a :icon:`fa-book` :guilabel:`(book)` "
"icon and the default setting of :guilabel:`All Journals`. Use this filter to "
"specify which journals should be included in the report."
msgstr ""
"Filter *jurnal*, seperti yang ditunjukkan oleh ikon :icon:`fa-book` "
":guilabel:`(buku)` dan pengaturan default :guilabel:`Semua Jurnal`. Gunakan "
"filter ini untuk menentukan jurnal mana yang harus disertakan dalam laporan."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/united_states.rst:302
msgid ""
"An *entries type* filter, as indicated by a :icon:`fa-"
"filter` :guilabel:`(filter)` icon, with the default setting "
"of :guilabel:`Posted Entries Only, Accrual Basis`. Use this filter to "
"determine which type of journal entries should be included in the report "
"(e.g. posted or draft), along with the type of accounting method (e.g. "
"accrual or cash basis)."
msgstr ""
"Filter *jenis entri*, seperti yang ditunjukkan oleh ikon :icon:`fa-filter` "
":guilabel:`(filter)`, dengan pengaturan default :guilabel:`Hanya Entri "
"Terposting, Basis Akrual`. Gunakan filter ini untuk menentukan jenis entri "
"jurnal mana yang harus disertakan dalam laporan (misalnya terposting atau "
"draf), bersama dengan jenis metode akuntansi (misalnya basis akrual atau kas)"
"."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/united_states.rst:307
msgid ""
"There are view options in this filter, as well, one that "
"will :guilabel:`Hide lines at 0` for more relevant viewing, along with "
"a :guilabel:`Split Horizontally` option to keep the report above the "
"screen's fold, removing the need to scroll."
msgstr ""

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/united_states.rst:0
msgid ""
"Accounting method filter menu for reports, covering accrual vs. cash basis "
"methods."
msgstr ""

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/united_states.rst:314
msgid ""
"A *decimal* filter, that by default, includes figures with cents, as "
"indicated by the :guilabel:`In .$` setting. Use the other options in the "
"drop-down menu to change figures in the report to whole numbers "
"(:guilabel:`In $`), thousands (:guilabel:`In K$`), or millions "
"(:guilabel:`In M$`) formats."
msgstr ""
"Filter *desimal*, yang secara default menyertakan angka dengan sen, seperti "
"yang ditunjukkan oleh pengaturan :guilabel:`Dalam .$`. Gunakan opsi lain "
"dalam menu drop-down untuk mengubah angka dalam laporan menjadi format angka "
"bulat (:guilabel:`Dalam $`), ribuan (:guilabel:`Dalam K$`), atau jutaan "
"(:guilabel:`Dalam M$`)."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/united_states.rst:318
msgid ""
"A report *customization* filter, indicated by the :icon:`fa-"
"cogs` :guilabel:`(gears)` icon. Use this filter to customize the current "
"report's sections and line items, or build new reports, as desired."
msgstr ""
"Filter *kustomisasi* laporan, ditunjukkan oleh ikon :icon:`fa-cogs` "
":guilabel:`(roda gigi)`. Gunakan filter ini untuk menyesuaikan bagian dan "
"item baris laporan saat ini, atau membuat laporan baru sesuai kebutuhan."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/united_states.rst:331
msgid ""
"The 1099 report, available by :ref:`installing <general/install>` the *1099 "
"Reporting* (`l10n_us_1099`) module, includes payments that are made to non-"
"employees across a given reporting period. Use the available CSV download "
"from the report in Odoo to file 1099 payments electronically via a third-"
"party service."
msgstr ""

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/united_states.rst:336
msgid ""
"To generate a 1099 report, navigate to :menuselection:`Accounting app --> "
"Reporting --> Management: 1099 Report` to open a :guilabel:`1099 Report` "
"wizard."
msgstr ""

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/united_states.rst:339
msgid ""
"First, enter the date range of the transactions to report in "
"the :guilabel:`Start Date` and :guilabel:`End Date` fields."
msgstr ""

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/united_states.rst:342
msgid ""
"Then, edit the journal items that appear on the wizard. Click :guilabel:`Add "
"a line` to add any items that are missing. Be sure to remove any items that "
"should not be included in the report by clicking :icon:`fa-"
"times` :guilabel:`(delete)` on the row."
msgstr ""

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/united_states.rst:346
msgid ""
"Finally, once all necessary items are included in the 1099 report, click on "
"the :guilabel:`Generate` button. Doing so downloads a CSV file that groups "
"transactions by the partner that received the payments."
msgstr ""

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/united_states.rst:355
msgid ""
"Navigate to the *Cash Flow Statement* (CFS) dashboard by going "
"to :menuselection:`Accounting app --> Reporting --> Statement Reports: Cash "
"Flow Statement`. From here, |CFS| reports can be generated using the "
"various :ref:`filters <l10n_us/report-filters>` that are available at the "
"top of the dashboard."
msgstr ""

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/united_states.rst:360
msgid ""
"Odoo uses the *direct* cash flow method to compile cash flow statements, "
"which measures actual cash inflows and outflows from the company's "
"operations, such as when cash is received from customers or when cash "
"payments are made to suppliers."
msgstr ""

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/united_states.rst:364
msgid ""
"By default, an account labeled with any of the three "
"default :guilabel:`Tags` on the :guilabel:`Chart of Accounts` dashboard is "
"included in the report, which includes: :guilabel:`Operating "
"Activities`, :guilabel:`Financing Activities`, and :guilabel:`Investing & "
"Extraordinary Activities`."
msgstr ""
"Secara default, akun yang diberi label dengan salah satu dari tiga "
":guilabel:`Tag` default pada dashboard :guilabel:`Bagan Akun` disertakan "
"dalam laporan, yang meliputi: :guilabel:`Aktivitas Operasional`, "
":guilabel:`Aktivitas Pendanaan`, dan :guilabel:`Aktivitas Investasi & Luar "
"Biasa`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/united_states.rst:None
msgid ""
"Examples of tagged accounts that are included in the Cash Flow Statement in "
"Odoo."
msgstr ""

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/united_states.rst:372
msgid "Additionally, the cash flow statement in Odoo:"
msgstr ""

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/united_states.rst:374
msgid ""
"is limited to the *Bank* and *Cash* journals to reflect money coming in or "
"out; and"
msgstr ""

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/united_states.rst:375
msgid ""
"also contains *Expenses* accounts, to show the counterpart transactions "
"versus *Bank* or *Cash* journal entries, while excluding |AR| and |AP| "
"activity."
msgstr ""

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/united_states.rst:379
msgid ""
"Create a vendor bill for $100, as an operating expense (not |AP|). Doing so "
"will **not** reflect a transaction on the cash flow statement. However, "
"register a corresponding payment for $100, and the transaction **will** "
"reflect on the cash flow statement as :guilabel:`Cash paid for operating "
"activities`."
msgstr ""

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/united_states.rst:0
msgid ""
"Example of a bill registered as an operating expense as part of a cash flow "
"statement."
msgstr ""
"Contoh tagihan yang didaftarkan sebagai biaya operasional sebagai bagian "
"dari laporan arus kas."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/united_states.rst:390
msgid "Profit & loss statement"
msgstr "Laporan laba rugi"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/united_states.rst:392
msgid ""
"To view the |P&L| statement, navigate to :menuselection:`Accounting --> "
"Reporting --> Profit and Loss`. To conform with |GAAP| standards and "
"facilitate migration from other US accounting software, the labels of the "
"generic |P&L| statement are modified for the US localization. The structure "
"and formulas in this :doc:`custom report <../accounting/reporting/"
"customize>` are identical to the generic report."
msgstr ""
"Untuk melihat laporan |P&L|, buka :menuselection:`Akuntansi --> "
"Pelaporan --> Laba Rugi`. Untuk mematuhi standar |GAAP| dan memfasilitasi "
"migrasi dari perangkat lunak akuntansi AS lainnya, label laporan |P&L| "
"generik dimodifikasi untuk lokalisasi AS. Struktur dan rumus dalam "
":doc:`laporan kustom <../accounting/reporting/customize>` ini identik dengan "
"laporan generik."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/united_states.rst:398
msgid ""
"To view the labels used in the report, enter :ref:`developer mode <developer-"
"mode>`, navigate to the |P&L| statement, and click the :icon:`fa-"
"cogs` :guilabel:`(cogs)` smart button. The US |P&L| statement line items "
"correspond to the generic |P&L| statement line items as follows:"
msgstr ""
"Untuk melihat label yang digunakan dalam laporan, aktifkan :ref:`mode "
"pengembang <developer-mode>`, buka laporan |P&L|, dan klik tombol pintar "
":icon:`fa-cogs` :guilabel:`(roda gigi)`. Item baris laporan |P&L| AS sesuai "
"dengan item baris laporan |P&L| generik sebagai berikut:"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/united_states.rst:406
msgid "Generic P&L Statement"
msgstr "Laporan L/R Generik"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/united_states.rst:407
