#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/united_states.rst:432
msgid ""
"*Net Other Income* is calculated by subtracting *Other Expense* from *Other "
"Income*."
msgstr ""
"*Pendapatan Lain-Lain Bersih* dihitung dengan mengurangkan *Beban Lain-Lain* "
"dari *Pendapatan Lain-Lain*."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/united_states.rst:434
msgid ""
"European accounting frameworks include appropriation of profit in the "
"generic |P&L| statement. Under |GAAP| accounting standards, the |P&L| "
"statement summarizes performance only. As a result, the US report does not "
"include *Allocations and Withdrawals*."
msgstr ""
"Kerangka kerja akuntansi Eropa mencakup apropriasi laba dalam laporan |P&L| "
"umum. Berdasarkan standar akuntansi |GAAP|, laporan |P&L| hanya merangkum "
"kinerja. Hasilnya, laporan AS tidak mencakup *Alokasi dan Penarikan*."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/united_states.rst:454
msgid ""
"Using checks is still a common payment practice in the US. Be sure the *US "
"Checks Layout* (`l10n_us_check_printing`) module for the US localization "
"is :ref:`installed <general/install>`."
msgstr ""
"Penggunaan cek masih merupakan praktik pembayaran yang umum di AS. Pastikan "
"modul *US Checks Layout* (`l10n_us_check_printing`) untuk lokalisasi AS "
"sudah :ref:`terpasang <general/install>`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/united_states.rst:461
msgid ""
"Select a pre-printed or blank :guilabel:`Check Layout` from the drop-down "
"menu:"
msgstr ""
"Pilih :guilabel:`Tata Letak Cek` yang sudah dicetak atau kosong dari menu "
"drop-down:"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/united_states.rst:463
msgid ":guilabel:`Print Check (Top) - US`"
msgstr ":guilabel:`Cetak Cek (Atas) - AS`"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/united_states.rst:464
msgid ":guilabel:`Print Check (Middle) - US`"
msgstr ":guilabel:`Cetak Cek (Tengah) - AS`"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/united_states.rst:465
msgid ":guilabel:`Print Check (Bottom) - US`"
msgstr ":guilabel:`Cetak Cek (Bawah) - AS`"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/united_states.rst:466
msgid ":guilabel:`Print Blank Check (Top) - US`"
msgstr ":guilabel:`Cetak Cek Kosong (Atas) - AS`"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/united_states.rst:467
msgid ":guilabel:`Print Blank Check (Middle) - US`"
msgstr ":guilabel:`Cetak Cek Kosong (Tengah) - AS`"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/united_states.rst:468
msgid ":guilabel:`Print Blank Check (Bottom) - US`"
msgstr ":guilabel:`Cetak Cek Kosong (Bawah) - AS`"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/united_states.rst:472
msgid ""
"Optionally set a :guilabel:`Check Top Margin` and :guilabel:`Check Left "
"Margin`, if required."
msgstr ""
"Secara opsional, atur :guilabel:`Margin Atas Cek` dan :guilabel:`Margin Kiri "
"Cek`, jika diperlukan."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/united_states.rst:477
msgid ""
"Pre-printed check formats (non-blank checks) require pre-printed paper from "
"a third-party vendor. `Pre-printed checks from checkdepot.net <https://"
"checkdepot.net/collections/odoo-checks>`_ are recommended."
msgstr ""
"Format cek yang sudah dicetak (cek non-kosong) memerlukan kertas yang sudah "
"dicetak dari vendor pihak ketiga. `Cek yang sudah dicetak dari "
"checkdepot.net <https://checkdepot.net/collections/odoo-checks>`_ "
"direkomendasikan."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/united_states.rst:483
msgid ""
"Use one of the blank check formats to print the information of the check ad-"
"hoc when needed. This requires the use of both :abbr:`MICR (Magnetic Ink "
"Character Recognition)` ink or toner complying with the standards for check "
"printing, as well as `check quality paper <https://checkdepot.net/"
"collections/blank-check-paper/products/top-format-blank-check-paper-"
"cdt164>`_. Other information, such as the company name, bank account, and "
"check number, is printed when creating the blank check."
msgstr ""
"Gunakan salah satu format cek kosong untuk mencetak informasi cek secara ad-"
"hoc bila diperlukan. Ini memerlukan penggunaan tinta atau toner :abbr:`MICR "
"(Magnetic Ink Character Recognition)` yang mematuhi standar untuk pencetakan "
"cek, serta `kertas berkualitas cek <https://checkdepot.net/collections/blank-"
"check-paper/products/top-format-blank-check-paper-cdt164>`_. Informasi lain, "
"seperti nama perusahaan, rekening bank, dan nomor cek, dicetak saat membuat "
"cek kosong."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/united_states.rst:498
msgid ""
"The **Payroll** app is responsible for calculating an employee's pay, taking "
"into account all work, vacation, and sick time, benefits, and deductions. "
"The **Payroll** app pulls information from the **Attendances**, "
"**Timesheets**, **Time Off**, **Employees** and **Expenses** apps, to "
"calculate the worked hours and compensation for each employee."
msgstr ""
"Aplikasi **Payroll** bertanggung jawab untuk menghitung gaji karyawan, "
"dengan memperhitungkan semua waktu kerja, liburan, dan sakit, tunjangan, dan "
"potongan. Aplikasi **Payroll** mengambil informasi dari aplikasi "
"**Absensi**, **Tabel Waktu**, **Cuti**, **Karyawan**, dan **Pengeluaran**, "
"untuk menghitung jam kerja dan kompensasi untuk setiap karyawan."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/united_states.rst:503
msgid ""
"When using an external payroll provider, such as *ADP*, it is necessary to "
"export the various payroll-related data, such as work entries, repayment of "
"expenses, taxes, commissions, and any other relevant data, so the data can "
"be uploaded into the payroll provider, who then issues the actual paychecks "
"or directly deposits the funds into an employee's bank account."
msgstr ""
"Saat menggunakan penyedia payroll eksternal, seperti *ADP*, perlu mengekspor "
"berbagai data terkait payroll, seperti entri kerja, penggantian pengeluaran, "
"pajak, komisi, dan data relevan lainnya, sehingga data tersebut dapat "
"diunggah ke penyedia payroll, yang kemudian mengeluarkan cek gaji aktual "
"atau langsung menyetorkan dana ke rekening bank karyawan."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/united_states.rst:508
msgid ""
"In order to export the payroll data, the work entries must first be "
"validated and correct. Refer to the :doc:`work entries <../../hr/payroll/"
"work_entries>` documentation for more information regarding validating work "
"entries."
msgstr ""
"Untuk mengekspor data payroll, entri kerja harus terlebih dahulu divalidasi "
"dan benar. Lihat dokumentasi :doc:`entri kerja <../../hr/payroll/"
"work_entries>` untuk informasi lebih lanjut mengenai validasi entri kerja."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/united_states.rst:512
msgid ""
"Once work entries are validated, the information can be :ref:`exported to "
"ADP <l10n_us/adp>`."
msgstr ""
"Setelah entri kerja divalidasi, informasi dapat :ref:`diekspor ke ADP "
"<l10n_us/adp>`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/united_states.rst:514
msgid ""
"After payments have been issued to employees, payslips can be processed into "
"batches, validated, and posted to the corresponding accounting journals to "
"keep all financial records in Odoo current."
msgstr ""
"Setelah pembayaran diterbitkan kepada karyawan, slip gaji dapat diproses "
"menjadi batch, divalidasi, dan diposting ke jurnal akuntansi yang sesuai "
"untuk menjaga semua catatan keuangan di Odoo tetap terkini."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/united_states.rst:520
msgid ""
"It is important to have the **Employees** app installed, and all employee "
"information populated. Several fields in both the :ref:`employee records "
"<l10n_us/payroll-employee-records>`, as well as in an :ref:`employee "
"contracts <l10n_us/payroll-employee-contracts>`, are necessary to properly "
"process the employee's pay. Ensure the following fields are filled out in "
"their respective places."
msgstr ""
"Penting untuk menginstal aplikasi **Karyawan**, dan semua informasi karyawan "
"terisi. Beberapa bidang dalam :ref:`catatan karyawan <l10n_us/payroll-"
"employee-records>`, serta dalam :ref:`kontrak karyawan <l10n_us/payroll-"
"employee-contracts>`, diperlukan untuk memproses gaji karyawan dengan benar. "
"Pastikan bidang berikut diisi di tempat yang sesuai."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/united_states.rst:528
msgid "Employee records"
msgstr "Catatan karyawan"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/united_states.rst:530
msgid ""
"In each employee record, there is various information the **Payroll** app "
"requires to properly process payslips, including various banking, tax, and "
"work information."
msgstr ""
"Di setiap catatan karyawan, ada berbagai informasi yang diperlukan aplikasi "
"**Payroll** untuk memproses slip gaji dengan benar, termasuk berbagai "
"informasi perbankan, pajak, dan pekerjaan."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/united_states.rst:533
msgid ""
"Navigate to the :menuselection:`Employees app` and select an employee record "
"to view the sections of the employee form that directly affect *Payroll*:"
msgstr ""
"Navigasi ke :menuselection:`aplikasi Karyawan` dan pilih catatan karyawan "
"untuk melihat bagian dari formulir karyawan yang secara langsung "
"mempengaruhi *Payroll*:"

