msgstr ":doc:`Dokumentasi Karyawan <../../hr/employees/new_employee>`"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/united_states.rst:602
msgid "Export work entries to ADP"
msgstr "Ekspor entri kerja ke ADP"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/united_states.rst:607
msgid ""
"In order to create a report that can be uploaded to ADP, there are some "
"initial configuration steps that must be completed first."
msgstr ""
"Untuk membuat laporan yang dapat diunggah ke ADP, ada beberapa langkah "
"konfigurasi awal yang harus diselesaikan terlebih dahulu."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/united_states.rst:610
msgid ""
"First, ensure the *United States - Payroll - Export to ADP* "
"(`l10n_us_hr_payroll_adp`) module is :ref:`installed <general/install>`."
msgstr ""
"Pertama, pastikan modul *United States - Payroll - Export to ADP* "
"(`l10n_us_hr_payroll_adp`) sudah :ref:`terpasang <general/install>`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/united_states.rst:613
msgid ""
"Then, the company **must** have an *ADP Code* entered in the company "
"settings. To do so, navigate to :menuselection:`Payroll app --> "
"Configuration --> Settings`. Enter the :guilabel:`ADP Code` in "
"the :guilabel:`US Localization` section."
msgstr ""
"Kemudian, perusahaan **harus** memiliki *ADP Code* yang dimasukkan dalam "
"pengaturan perusahaan. Untuk melakukannya, navigasi ke "
":menuselection:`Aplikasi Payroll --> Konfigurasi --> Pengaturan`. Masukkan "
":guilabel:`ADP Code` di bagian :guilabel:`US Localization`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/united_states.rst:617
msgid ""
"Next, work entry types **must** have the correct ADP code listed in the "
"*External Code* field for each work entry type that is being referenced."
msgstr ""
"Selanjutnya, tipe entri kerja **harus** memiliki kode ADP yang benar yang "
"tercantum di kolom *External Code* untuk setiap tipe entri kerja yang "
"dirujuk."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/united_states.rst:620
msgid ""
"Lastly, every employee **must** have an *ADP Code* entered on their employee "
"form. To do so, navigate to :menuselection:`Employees app`, select an "
"employee record, and open the :guilabel:`HR Settings` tab. Enter "
"the :guilabel:`ADP Code` in the :guilabel:`ADP Information` section."
msgstr ""
"Terakhir, setiap karyawan **harus** memiliki *ADP Code* yang dimasukkan pada "
"formulir karyawan mereka. Untuk melakukannya, navigasi ke "
":menuselection:`Aplikasi Karyawan`, pilih catatan karyawan, dan buka tab "
":guilabel:`HR Settings`. Masukkan :guilabel:`ADP Code` di bagian "
":guilabel:`ADP Information`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/united_states.rst:624
msgid ""
"The :guilabel:`ADP Code` code is how ADP identifies that particular "
"employee, and is typically a six-digit number."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`ADP Code` adalah cara ADP mengidentifikasi karyawan tertentu, dan "
"biasanya berupa nomor enam digit."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/united_states.rst:628
msgid ":ref:`payroll/new-work-entry`"
msgstr ":ref:`payroll/new-work-entry`"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/united_states.rst:629
msgid ":doc:`../../hr/employees/new_employee`"
msgstr ":doc:`../../hr/employees/new_employee`"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/united_states.rst:632
msgid "Export data"
msgstr "Ekspor data"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/united_states.rst:634
msgid ""
"Once :doc:`work entries <../../hr/payroll/work_entries>` have been verified, "
"the information can be exported to a CSV file, which can then be uploaded "
"into ADP."
msgstr ""
"Setelah :doc:`entri kerja <../../hr/payroll/work_entries>` diverifikasi, "
"informasi dapat diekspor ke file CSV, yang kemudian dapat diunggah ke ADP."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/united_states.rst:637
msgid ""
"To export the data, navigate to :menuselection:`Payroll app --> Reporting --"
"> United States: ADP Export`, then click :guilabel:`New`. Next, enter "
"the :guilabel:`Start Date` and :guilabel:`End Date` for the work entries "
"using the calendar pop-over."
msgstr ""
"Untuk mengekspor data, navigasi ke :menuselection:`Aplikasi Payroll --> "
"Pelaporan --> United States: ADP Export`, lalu klik :guilabel:`New`. "
"Selanjutnya, masukkan :guilabel:`Start Date` dan :guilabel:`End Date` untuk "
"entri kerja menggunakan pop-over kalender."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/united_states.rst:641
msgid ""
"Then, enter a :guilabel:`Batch ID` in the corresponding field. The "
"recommendation for this field is to enter the date in a `YY-MM-DD` format, "
"followed by any other characters to distinguish that specific batch, such as "
"a department name, or any other defining characteristics for the batch."
msgstr ""
"Kemudian, masukkan :guilabel:`Batch ID` di kolom yang sesuai. Rekomendasi "
"untuk kolom ini adalah memasukkan tanggal dalam format `YY-MM-DD`, diikuti "
"dengan karakter lain untuk membedakan batch tertentu, seperti nama "
"departemen, atau karakteristik lain yang mendefinisikan batch tersebut."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/united_states.rst:645
msgid ""
"Enter a :guilabel:`Batch Description` in the corresponding field. This "
"should be short and descriptive, but distinct from the :guilabel:`Batch "
"Name`."
msgstr ""
"Masukkan :guilabel:`Batch Description` di kolom yang sesuai. Ini harus "
"singkat dan deskriptif, tetapi berbeda dari :guilabel:`Batch Name`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/united_states.rst:648
msgid ""
"Ensure the correct company populates the :guilabel:`Company` field. Change "
"the selected company with the drop-down menu, if needed."
msgstr ""
"Pastikan perusahaan yang benar mengisi kolom :guilabel:`Company`. Ubah "
"perusahaan yang dipilih dengan menu drop-down, jika diperlukan."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/united_states.rst:651
msgid ""
"Lastly, add the employee's work entry information to the list. "
"Click :guilabel:`Add a line` and an :guilabel:`Add: Employee` pop-up window "
"loads. The list can be :doc:`filtered <../../essentials/search>` to find the "
"employees to add to the list."
msgstr ""
"Terakhir, tambahkan informasi entri kerja karyawan ke daftar. Klik "
":guilabel:`Tambahkan baris` dan jendela pop-up :guilabel:`Tambahkan: "
"Karyawan` dimuat. Daftar dapat :doc:`difilter <../../essentials/search>` "
"untuk menemukan karyawan yang akan ditambahkan ke daftar."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/united_states.rst:656
msgid ""
"Process the data export in multiple groups instead of in one large group "
"that contains all employees. This helps to meaningfully differentiate the "
"batches and makes processing more tenable, overall. The most common ways to "
"group employees is by department, or by wage type (hourly or salaried)."
msgstr ""
"Proses ekspor data dalam beberapa kelompok alih-alih dalam satu kelompok "
"besar yang berisi semua karyawan. Ini membantu membedakan batch secara "
"bermakna dan membuat pemrosesan lebih mudah dikelola secara keseluruhan. "
"Cara paling umum untuk mengelompokkan karyawan adalah berdasarkan "
"departemen, atau berdasarkan jenis upah (per jam atau gaji)."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/united_states.rst:661
msgid ""
"Select the employees to add to the list by ticking the box to the left of "
"their name. Once all desired employees have been selected, click "
"the :guilabel:`Select` button in the lower-left corner, and the employees "
"appear in the list."
msgstr ""
"Pilih karyawan untuk ditambahkan ke daftar dengan mencentang kotak di "
"sebelah kiri nama mereka. Setelah semua karyawan yang diinginkan dipilih, "
"klik tombol :guilabel:`Select` di sudut kiri bawah, dan karyawan akan muncul "
"dalam daftar."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/united_states.rst:665
msgid ""
"To create the CSV file, click the :guilabel:`Generate` button in the top-"
"left corner."
msgstr ""
"Untuk membuat file CSV, klik tombol :guilabel:`Generate` di sudut kiri atas."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/united_states.rst:670
msgid "ACH - electronic transfers"
msgstr "ACH - transfer elektronik"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/united_states.rst:672
msgid ""
"Automated Clearing House (ACH) payments are a modern way to transfer funds "
"electronically between bank accounts, replacing traditional paper-based "
"methods. |ACH| payments are commonly used for direct deposits, bill "
"payments, and business transactions."
msgstr ""
"Automated Clearing House (ACH) adalah cara modern untuk mentransfer dana "
"secara elektronik antar rekening bank, menggantikan metode tradisional "
"berbasis kertas. Pembayaran |ACH| umumnya digunakan untuk setoran langsung, "
"pembayaran tagihan, dan transaksi bisnis."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/united_states.rst:677
msgid "Receive ACH payments: payment provider integration"
msgstr "Terima pembayaran ACH: integrasi penyedia pembayaran"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/united_states.rst:679
msgid ""
"|ACH| payments are supported by *Authorize.net* and *Stripe* payment "
"integrations in Odoo."
msgstr ""
"Pembayaran |ACH| didukung oleh integrasi pembayaran *Authorize.net* dan "
"*Stripe* di Odoo."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/united_states.rst:682
msgid ""
":ref:`Setting up Authorize.net for ACH payments (Odoo) <authorize/"
"ach_payments>`"
msgstr ""
":ref:`Mengatur Authorize.net untuk pembayaran ACH (Odoo) <authorize/"
"ach_payments>`"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/united_states.rst:683
msgid ""
"`Authorize.net's ACH payment processing for small businesses documentation "
"<https://www.authorize.net/resources/blog/2021/ach-payments-for-small-"
"businesses.html>`_"
msgstr ""
"`Dokumentasi pemrosesan pembayaran ACH Authorize.net untuk bisnis kecil "
"<https://www.authorize.net/resources/blog/2021/ach-payments-for-small-"
"businesses.html>`_"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/united_states.rst:685
msgid ""
":doc:`Setting up Stripe for ACH payments (Odoo) <../payment_providers/"
"stripe>`"
msgstr ""
":doc:`Mengatur Stripe untuk pembayaran ACH (Odoo) <../payment_providers/"
"stripe>`"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/united_states.rst:686
msgid ""
"`Stripe's ACH Direct Debit documentation <https://docs.stripe.com/payments/"
"ach-debit>`_"
msgstr ""
"`Dokumentasi ACH Direct Debit Stripe <https://docs.stripe.com/payments/ach-"
"debit>`_"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/united_states.rst:691
msgid "Send payments: NACHA files"
msgstr "Kirim pembayaran: file NACHA"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/united_states.rst:693
msgid ""
"Odoo can generate a National Automated Clearing House Association (NACHA) "
"compatible |ACH| file to send to a company's bank. For each individual "
"*Bank* journal that the company wishes to pay vendors with, a |NACHA| "
"configuration section needs to be filled out on the Odoo database."
msgstr ""
"Odoo dapat menghasilkan file |ACH| yang kompatibel dengan National Automated "
"Clearing House Association (NACHA) untuk dikirim ke bank perusahaan. Untuk "
"setiap jurnal *Bank* individual yang ingin digunakan perusahaan untuk "
"membayar vendor, bagian konfigurasi |NACHA| perlu diisi di database Odoo."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/united_states.rst:700
msgid ""
"First, navigate to the :menuselection:`Accounting app --> Configuration --> "
"Journals`. Open the bank journal and click into the :guilabel:`Outgoing "
"Payments` tab."
msgstr ""
"Pertama, navigasi ke :menuselection:`Aplikasi Akuntansi --> Konfigurasi --> "
"Jurnal`. Buka jurnal bank dan klik ke tab :guilabel:`Pembayaran Keluar`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/united_states.rst:None
msgid ""
"NACHA (National Automated Clearing House Association) configuration settings "
"on Odoo."
msgstr ""
"Pengaturan konfigurasi NACHA (National Automated Clearing House Association) "
"di Odoo."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/united_states.rst:707
msgid ""
"The following |NACHA| configuration information is normally provided by the "
"company's financial institution once they have been approved to send "
"payments via their account."
msgstr ""
"Informasi konfigurasi |NACHA| berikut biasanya disediakan oleh lembaga "
"keuangan perusahaan setelah mereka disetujui untuk mengirim pembayaran "
"melalui akun mereka."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/united_states.rst:710
msgid ""
"Under the section labeled, :guilabel:`NACHA configuration` are the fields "
"required to generate a |NACHA| compatible |ACH| file to send to a company's "
"bank. First, enter the routing number of the financial institution in the "
"field labeled, :guilabel:`Immediate Destination`. This information is widely "
"available on the Internet and generally varies by bank location. This number "
"is usually provided during the initial account setup."
msgstr ""
"Di bawah bagian berlabel :guilabel:`Konfigurasi NACHA` adalah field yang "
"diperlukan untuk menghasilkan file |ACH| yang kompatibel dengan |NACHA| "
"untuk dikirim ke bank perusahaan. Pertama, masukkan nomor routing lembaga "
"keuangan di field berlabel :guilabel:`Tujuan Langsung`. Informasi ini "
"tersedia secara luas di Internet dan umumnya bervariasi berdasarkan lokasi "
"bank. Nomor ini biasanya disediakan selama pengaturan akun awal."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/united_states.rst:716
msgid ""
"Next, enter the registered name of the financial institution in the field "
"called, :guilabel:`Destination`. This information is provided by the bank or "
"credit union."
msgstr ""
"Selanjutnya, masukkan nama terdaftar lembaga keuangan di bidang yang "
"disebut, :guilabel:`Tujuan`. Informasi ini disediakan oleh bank atau credit "
"union."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/united_states.rst:719
msgid ""
"Following the :guilabel:`Destination` field is the :guilabel:`Immediate "
"Origin` field. Enter the 9-digit company ID or Employer Identification "
"Number (EIN) into this field. This information is provided by the financial "
"institution."
msgstr ""
"Setelah field :guilabel:`Tujuan` adalah field :guilabel:`Asal Langsung`. "
"Masukkan ID perusahaan 9 digit atau Employer Identification Number (EIN) ke "
"dalam field ini. Informasi ini disediakan oleh lembaga keuangan."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/united_states.rst:723
msgid ""
"Next, enter the :guilabel:`Company Identification` number, which is a 10-"
"digit number made from combining the 9-digit company ID or Employer "
"Identification Number (EIN), along with an additional number at the start of "
"the sequence. This number is often a `1`. Check with the financial "
"institution should this first number differ to verify that it is correct, as "
"this number is provided for |ACH| approved accounts."
msgstr ""
"Selanjutnya, masukkan nomor :guilabel:`Identifikasi Perusahaan`, yang "
"merupakan nomor 10 digit yang dibuat dari menggabungkan ID perusahaan 9 "
"digit atau Employer Identification Number (EIN), bersama dengan nomor "
"tambahan di awal urutan. Nomor ini sering kali adalah `1`. Periksa dengan "
"lembaga keuangan jika nomor pertama ini berbeda untuk memverifikasi bahwa "
"itu benar, karena nomor ini disediakan untuk akun yang disetujui |ACH|."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/united_states.rst:729
msgid ""
"Enter the :guilabel:`Originating DFI Identification` number next, which "
"should contain an assigned 8-digit number from the financial institution."
msgstr ""
"Masukkan nomor :guilabel:`Identifikasi DFI Asal` selanjutnya, yang harus "
"berisi nomor 8 digit yang ditetapkan dari lembaga keuangan."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/united_states.rst:733
msgid ""
"Enter the numerical values in this section *exactly* as the company's "
"financial institution (e.g. bank or credit union) has provided them, "
"otherwise risk failing a successful |NACHA| configuration in Odoo."
msgstr ""
"Masukkan nilai numerik di bagian ini *persis* seperti yang telah disediakan "
"oleh lembaga keuangan perusahaan (misalnya bank atau credit union), jika "
"tidak berisiko gagal dalam konfigurasi |NACHA| yang berhasil di Odoo."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/united_states.rst:None
msgid ""
"NACHA settings with the standard entry class code drop-down menu highlighted."
msgstr ""
"Pengaturan NACHA dengan menu drop-down kode kelas entri standar yang disorot."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/united_states.rst:740
msgid ""
"Two options are available for the next field: :guilabel:`Standard Entry "
"Class Code`. Select the drop-down menu to the right of the field and pick "
"either :guilabel:`Corporate Credit or Debit (CCD)` or :guilabel:`Prearranged "
"Payment and Deposit (PPD)`. Again, this information is provided by the "
"financial institution. By default :guilabel:`Corporate Credit or Debit "
"(CCD)` is selected."
msgstr ""
"Dua opsi tersedia untuk bidang berikutnya: :guilabel:`Kode Kelas Entri "
"Standar`. Pilih menu drop-down di sebelah kanan bidang dan pilih "
":guilabel:`Kredit atau Debit Perusahaan (CCD)` atau :guilabel:`Pembayaran "
"dan Setoran yang Telah Diatur (PPD)`. Sekali lagi, informasi ini disediakan "
"oleh lembaga keuangan. Secara default :guilabel:`Kredit atau Debit "
"Perusahaan (CCD)` dipilih."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/united_states.rst:745
msgid ""
"Finally, the last option is for :guilabel:`Generated Balanced Files`. Tick "
"the checkbox to the right of the field to enable :guilabel:`Generated "
"Balanced Files`. Consult the company's accountant or financial adviser to "
"make an informed decision for this field."
msgstr ""
"Terakhir, opsi terakhir adalah untuk :guilabel:`File Seimbang yang "
"Dihasilkan`. Centang kotak centang di sebelah kanan bidang untuk "
"mengaktifkan :guilabel:`File Seimbang yang Dihasilkan`. Konsultasikan dengan "
"akuntan atau penasihat keuangan perusahaan untuk membuat keputusan yang "
"tepat untuk bidang ini."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/united_states.rst:749
msgid ""
"Manually save the configuration by clicking the :icon:`fa-cloud-"
"upload` :guilabel:`(cloud upload)` icon, or navigate away from this screen "
"to auto-save. The configuration is now complete."
msgstr ""
"Simpan konfigurasi secara manual dengan mengklik ikon :icon:`fa-cloud-"
"upload` :guilabel:`(unggah cloud)`, atau navigasi keluar dari layar ini "
"untuk menyimpan secara otomatis. Konfigurasi sekarang selesai."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/united_states.rst:755
msgid "Create batch payment"
msgstr "Buat pembayaran batch"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/united_states.rst:757
msgid "Now, record each payment in Odoo using the |NACHA| payment method."
msgstr ""
"Sekarang, catat setiap pembayaran di Odoo menggunakan metode pembayaran "
"|NACHA|."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/united_states.rst:760
msgid ""
":ref:`Register Payments in Odoo <accounting/payments/from-invoice-bill>`"
msgstr ""
":ref:`Daftarkan Pembayaran di Odoo <accounting/payments/from-invoice-bill>`"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/united_states.rst:763
msgid ""
"Be aware of the cut-off time for same-day payments. Either the file needs to "
"have a future date associated with each payment or the file needs to be sent "
"prior to the cut-off, if the dates included in it match today's date. "
"Consult the financial institution for the exact cut-off time for their "
"processing of same-day payments."
msgstr ""
"Perhatikan waktu batas untuk pembayaran di hari yang sama. File harus "
"memiliki tanggal masa depan yang terkait dengan setiap pembayaran atau file "
"harus dikirim sebelum waktu batas, jika tanggal yang termasuk di dalamnya "
"sesuai dengan tanggal hari ini. Konsultasikan dengan lembaga keuangan untuk "
"waktu batas yang tepat untuk pemrosesan pembayaran di hari yang sama mereka."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/united_states.rst:768
msgid ""
"Once all the payments to be included in the |NACHA| |ACH| file have been "
"made, a batch payment needs to be made from the :icon:`fa-"
"cog` :guilabel:`Action` menu."
msgstr ""
"Setelah semua pembayaran yang akan disertakan dalam file |NACHA| |ACH| telah "
"dibuat, batch pembayaran perlu dibuat dari menu :icon:`fa-cog` "
":guilabel:`Tindakan`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/united_states.rst:771
msgid ""
"To create the batch payments, access the payments page, by navigating "
"to :menuselection:`Accounting --> Vendors --> Payments`. Select all the "
"payments that should be included in the |NACHA| |ACH| file, by ticking the "
"checkboxes to the far-left of the rows."
msgstr ""
"Untuk membuat batch pembayaran, akses halaman pembayaran dengan menavigasi "
"ke :menuselection:`Akuntansi --> Vendor --> Pembayaran`. Pilih semua "
"pembayaran yang harus disertakan dalam file |NACHA| |ACH|, dengan mencentang "
"kotak centang di paling kiri baris."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/united_states.rst:None
msgid ""
"On the payments screen, the action menu is highlighted with create a batch "
"payment\n"
"selected."
msgstr ""
"Pada layar pembayaran, menu tindakan disorot dengan buat batch pembayaran\n"
"dipilih."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/united_states.rst:780
msgid ""
"All payments in the batch **must** share the same |NACHA| payment method."
msgstr ""
"Semua pembayaran dalam batch **harus** memiliki metode pembayaran |NACHA| "
"yang sama."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/united_states.rst:782
msgid ""
"Next, navigate to the batched payment (:menuselection:`Accounting --> "
"Vendors --> Batch Payments`). Click into the payment recently created and "
"then click into the :guilabel:`Exported File` tab. The generated file is "
"listed with the :guilabel:`Generation Date`. Click the :icon:`fa-"
"download` :guilabel:`(download)` button to download the file."
msgstr ""
"Selanjutnya, navigasikan ke pembayaran batch (:menuselection:`Akuntansi --> "
"Vendor --> Pembayaran Batch`). Klik ke dalam pembayaran yang baru dibuat "
"lalu klik ke dalam tab :guilabel:`File yang Diekspor`. File yang dihasilkan "
"terdaftar dengan :guilabel:`Tanggal Pembuatan`. Klik tombol :icon:`fa-"
"download` :guilabel:`(unduh)` untuk mengunduh file."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/united_states.rst:None
msgid ""
"The exported file tab highlighted in the batch payment with the download "
"circled."
msgstr ""
"Tab file yang diekspor disorot dalam batch pembayaran dengan unduhan "
"dilingkari."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/united_states.rst:790
msgid ""
"If any adjustments need to be made, click the :guilabel:`Re-generate Export "
"File` button to recreate a new |NACHA| |ACH| file."
msgstr ""
"Jika ada penyesuaian yang perlu dilakukan, klik tombol :guilabel:`Buat Ulang "
"File Ekspor` untuk membuat ulang file |NACHA| |ACH| baru."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/united_states.rst:795
msgid ":doc:`Europe's direct debiting <../accounting/payments/batch_sdd>`"
msgstr ":doc:`Debit langsung Eropa <../accounting/payments/batch_sdd>`"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/united_states.rst:800
msgid "Pay by direct deposit"
msgstr "Bayar dengan setoran langsung"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/united_states.rst:802
msgid ""
"Direct deposit is an electronic fund transfer primarily used in the United "
"States, in which money is sent directly to a bank account without the use of "
"a physical check or manual deposit. Odoo offers direct deposit through an "
"international money transfer service called `Wise.com <https://wise.com/>`_."
msgstr ""
"Setoran langsung adalah transfer dana elektronik yang terutama digunakan di "
"Amerika Serikat, di mana uang dikirim langsung ke rekening bank tanpa "
"menggunakan cek fisik atau setoran manual. Odoo menawarkan setoran langsung "
"melalui layanan transfer uang internasional yang disebut `Wise.com <https://"
"wise.com/>`_."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/united_states.rst:807
msgid ""
"Wise provides an |API|, invoicing tools, and business accounts. Businesses "
"can send and receive payments using Wise's cross-border payment technology "
"without building everything from scratch."
msgstr ""
"Wise menyediakan |API|, alat penagihan, dan akun bisnis. Bisnis dapat "
"mengirim dan menerima pembayaran menggunakan teknologi pembayaran lintas "
"batas Wise tanpa harus membangun semuanya dari awal."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/united_states.rst:810
msgid "This feature can be used to pay vendor bills."
msgstr "Fitur ini dapat digunakan untuk membayar tagihan vendor."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/united_states.rst:816
msgid "Wise configuration"
msgstr "Konfigurasi Wise"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/united_states.rst:818
msgid ""
"Wise configuration involves three main steps: creating a Wise account, "
"linking a bank account to the Wise account, and generating |API| tokens from "
"the Wise account. These steps are detailed below:"
msgstr ""
"Konfigurasi Wise melibatkan tiga langkah utama: membuat akun Wise, "
"menghubungkan rekening bank ke akun Wise, dan menghasilkan token |API| dari "
"akun Wise. Langkah-langkah ini dijelaskan secara rinci di bawah ini:"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/united_states.rst:821
msgid ""
"Navigate to `Wise.com <https://wise.com/>`_ and click :guilabel:`Sign-Up` to "
"create an account."
msgstr ""
"Navigasi ke `Wise.com <https://wise.com/>`_ dan klik :guilabel:`Sign-Up` "
"untuk membuat akun."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/united_states.rst:822
msgid ""
"Select :guilabel:`Business Account` and finish providing company and "
"personal user details to complete the sign-up process."
msgstr ""
"Pilih :guilabel:`Business Account` dan selesaikan pengisian detail "
"perusahaan dan pengguna pribadi untuk menyelesaikan proses pendaftaran."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/united_states.rst:825
msgid ""
"Wise may require additional verification documents depending on the business "
"type and country. This process can take 1–3 business days."
msgstr ""
"Wise mungkin memerlukan dokumen verifikasi tambahan tergantung pada jenis "
"bisnis dan negara. Proses ini dapat memakan waktu 1–3 hari kerja."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/united_states.rst:828
msgid ""
"Navigate to the account settings by clicking the :guilabel:`Company Name` in "
"the top-right corner of the dashboard."
msgstr ""
"Navigasi ke pengaturan akun dengan mengklik :guilabel:`Company Name` di "
"sudut kanan atas dashboard."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/united_states.rst:830
msgid ""
"Select :menuselection:`Payment Methods --> Connected bank accounts` and "
