msgstr ""
"Pilih :menuselection:`Payment Methods --> Connected bank accounts` dan klik "
":guilabel:`Connect Your Bank Account`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/united_states.rst:832
msgid ""
"Search for the bank and add the bank account information. This bank account "
