msgstr ""
"Cari bank dan tambahkan informasi rekening bank. Rekening bank ini juga akan "
"dikonfigurasi di Odoo."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/united_states.rst:835
msgid ""
"Go to the account settings by clicking the :guilabel:`Company Name` in the "
"top-right corner of the dashboard."
msgstr ""
"Buka pengaturan akun dengan mengklik :guilabel:`Company Name` di sudut kanan "
"atas dashboard."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/united_states.rst:837
msgid ""
"Select :menuselection:`Integration and Tools --> API Tokens` and "
"click :guilabel:`Add new token`."
msgstr ""
"Pilih :menuselection:`Integration and Tools --> API Tokens` dan klik "
":guilabel:`Add new token`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/united_states.rst:838
msgid ""
"Add a description and select :guilabel:`Full Access`, then "
"click :guilabel:`Create Token`."
msgstr ""
"Tambahkan deskripsi dan pilih :guilabel:`Full Access`, kemudian klik "
":guilabel:`Create Token`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/united_states.rst:839
msgid ""
