#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/united_states.rst:954
msgid "ISO 20022"
msgstr "ISO 20022"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/united_states.rst:956
msgid ""
"ISO 20022 is a global standard for sending financial information between "
"banks and payment systems using XML files. It can be thought of as a "
"universal language for money messages."
msgstr ""
"ISO 20022 adalah standar global untuk mengirim informasi keuangan antara "
"bank dan sistem pembayaran menggunakan file XML. Ini dapat dianggap sebagai "
"bahasa universal untuk pesan uang."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/united_states.rst:959
msgid ""
"This standard helps banks all over the world talk to each other in the same "
"way, or *language*, so information is transferred correctly, making sending "
"and receiving money faster, clearer, and safer."
msgstr ""
"Standar ini membantu bank di seluruh dunia berkomunikasi satu sama lain "
"dengan cara yang sama, atau *bahasa*, sehingga informasi ditransfer dengan "
"benar, membuat pengiriman dan penerimaan uang lebih cepat, lebih jelas, dan "
"lebih aman."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/united_states.rst:962
msgid ""
"In Odoo, ISO 20022 files are generated from :ref:`batch payments <l10n_us/"
"batch-payment>`."
msgstr ""
"Di Odoo, file ISO 20022 dihasilkan dari :ref:`pembayaran batch <l10n_us/"
"batch-payment>`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/united_states.rst:965
msgid "Configurations"
msgstr "Konfigurasi-Konfigurasi"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/united_states.rst:967
msgid ""
"Before creating ISO 20022 records, several configurations must be made, "
"including :ref:`general settings <l10n_us/settings>`, contact information "
"for the :ref:`company <l10n_us/contact-info-company>`, and contact and "
"banking information for all :ref:`recipients <l10n_us/contact-info-"
"recipient>`."
msgstr ""
"Sebelum membuat catatan ISO 20022, beberapa konfigurasi harus dibuat, "
"termasuk :ref:`pengaturan umum <l10n_us/settings>`, informasi kontak untuk "
":ref:`perusahaan <l10n_us/contact-info-company>`, dan informasi kontak dan "
"perbankan untuk semua :ref:`penerima <l10n_us/contact-info-recipient>`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/united_states.rst:975
msgid "Settings"
msgstr "Pengaturan"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/united_states.rst:977
msgid ""
"First, navigate to :menuselection:`Acounting app --> Configuration --> "
"Settings`, scroll to the :guilabel:`Customer Payment` section, and enable "
"the :guilabel:`Batch Payments` option."
msgstr ""
"Pertama, navigasikan ke :menuselection:`Aplikasi Akuntansi --> "
"Konfigurasi --> Pengaturan`, gulir ke bagian :guilabel:`Pembayaran "
"Pelanggan`, dan aktifkan opsi :guilabel:`Pembayaran Batch`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/united_states.rst:980
msgid ""
"Then scroll to the :guilabel:`Vendor Payments` section and enable "
"the :guilabel:`SEPA Credit Transfer / ISO20022` option. Once Enabled, three "
"fields appear: :guilabel:`Your Company`, :guilabel:`Name Identification`, "
"and :guilabel:`Issuer`. Enter the information for these fields. The "
"information entered is required by the bank to identify the account, and is "
"added to the XML file."
msgstr ""
"Kemudian gulir ke bagian :guilabel:`Pembayaran Vendor` dan aktifkan opsi "
":guilabel:`Transfer Kredit SEPA / ISO20022`. Setelah diaktifkan, tiga bidang "
"muncul: :guilabel:`Perusahaan Anda`, :guilabel:`Identifikasi Nama`, dan "
":guilabel:`Penerbit`. Masukkan informasi untuk bidang ini. Informasi yang "
"dimasukkan diperlukan oleh bank untuk mengidentifikasi akun, dan ditambahkan "
"ke file XML."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/united_states.rst:985
msgid "Click :guilabel:`Save` after making changes."
msgstr "Klik :guilabel:`Simpan` setelah melakukan perubahan."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/united_states.rst:None
msgid ""
"The settings configured for the ISO 20022 in the Accounting app settings "
"page."
msgstr ""
"Pengaturan yang dikonfigurasi untuk ISO 20022 di halaman pengaturan aplikasi "
"Akuntansi."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/united_states.rst:991
msgid ""
"The :guilabel:`Name Identification` and :guilabel:`Issuer` information are "
"typically provided by the bank."
msgstr ""
"Informasi :guilabel:`Identifikasi Nama` dan :guilabel:`Penerbit` biasanya "
"disediakan oleh bank."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/united_states.rst:999
msgid ""
"Ensure the company's address information is correct, as the XML files "
"generated include the company address. Navigate to "
"the :menuselection:`Settings app --> Users & Companies --> Companies`, and "
"click on the desired company to open the company form. Ensure "
"the :guilabel:`Address` fields are fully configured in "
"the :guilabel:`General Information` tab."
msgstr ""
"Pastikan informasi alamat perusahaan sudah benar, karena file XML yang "
"dihasilkan mencakup alamat perusahaan. Buka :menuselection:`aplikasi "
"Pengaturan --> Pengguna & Perusahaan --> Perusahaan`, dan klik perusahaan "
"yang diinginkan untuk membuka formulir perusahaan. Pastikan kolom "
":guilabel:`Alamat` sudah dikonfigurasi secara lengkap di tab "
":guilabel:`Informasi Umum`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/united_states.rst:None
msgid "The company record with address information completed."
msgstr "Catatan perusahaan dengan informasi alamat yang telah dilengkapi."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/united_states.rst:1010
msgid "Recipient information"
msgstr "Informasi penerima"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/united_states.rst:1012
msgid ""
"The XML file generated contains the address and banking information for "
"*all* recipients. Open the **Contacts** app and ensure every contact record "
"that receives payments, both persons and companies, includes "
"complete :guilabel:`Address` information in the top-half of the contact form."
msgstr ""
"File XML yang dihasilkan berisi informasi alamat dan perbankan untuk *semua* "
"penerima. Buka aplikasi **Kontak** dan pastikan setiap catatan kontak yang "
"menerima pembayaran, baik perorangan maupun perusahaan, mencakup informasi "
":guilabel:`Alamat` yang lengkap di bagian atas formulir kontak."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/united_states.rst:None
msgid "The contact record for a company with address information completed."
msgstr ""
"Catatan kontak untuk perusahaan dengan informasi alamat yang telah "
"dilengkapi."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/united_states.rst:1019
msgid ""
"Next, click into the :guilabel:`Accounting` tab, and ensure at least one "
"trusted bank account populates the :guilabel:`Banks` field. If no bank is "
"listed, add a :ref:`new bank account <l10n_us/add-bank>`."
msgstr ""
"Selanjutnya, klik ke tab :guilabel:`Akuntansi`, dan pastikan setidaknya satu "
"rekening bank tepercaya mengisi kolom :guilabel:`Bank`. Jika tidak ada bank "
"yang terdaftar, tambahkan :ref:`rekening bank baru <l10n_us/add-bank>`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/united_states.rst:1026
msgid "Add a bank account"
msgstr "Tambah akun bank"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/united_states.rst:1028
msgid ""
"To add a bank account on a contact record, open the **Contacts** app and "
"click on the contact record, and click into the :guilabel:`Accounting` tab. "
"Click into the blank field next to :guilabel:`Banks`, "
"click :guilabel:`Create...`, and a :guilabel:`Create Banks` pop-up window "
"loads. Fill out the following fields on the form, then "
"click :guilabel:`Save`:"
msgstr ""
"Untuk menambahkan rekening bank pada catatan kontak, buka aplikasi "
"**Kontak** dan klik catatan kontak, lalu klik ke tab :guilabel:`Akuntansi`. "
"Klik ke kolom kosong di sebelah :guilabel:`Bank`, klik :guilabel:`Buat...`, "
"dan jendela pop-up :guilabel:`Buat Bank` akan muncul. Isi kolom-kolom "
"berikut pada formulir, kemudian klik :guilabel:`Simpan`:"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/united_states.rst:1033
msgid ":guilabel:`Account Number`: Enter the bank account number."
msgstr ":guilabel:`Nomor Rekening`: Masukkan nomor rekening bank."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/united_states.rst:1034
msgid ""
":guilabel:`ABA/Routing Number`: Enter the ABA or routing number for the "
"account."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Nomor ABA/Routing`: Masukkan nomor ABA atau routing untuk "
"rekening."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/united_states.rst:1035
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Account Holder`: Using the drop-down menu, select the owner of "
"the bank account. The contact name (person or company) populates this field "
"by default."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Pemegang Rekening`: Menggunakan menu drop-down, pilih pemilik "
"rekening bank. Nama kontak (perorangan atau perusahaan) mengisi kolom ini "
"secara default."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/united_states.rst:1037
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Bank`: Using the drop-down menu, select the bank for the account. "
"If the bank does not appear in the list, add a new bank by "
"clicking :guilabel:`Search more...` then click :guilabel:`New`, and fill out "
"the :guilabel:`Create Bank` form."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Bank`: Menggunakan menu drop-down, pilih bank untuk rekening. "
"Jika bank tidak muncul dalam daftar, tambahkan bank baru dengan mengklik "
":guilabel:`Cari lebih banyak...` kemudian klik :guilabel:`Baru`, dan isi "
"formulir :guilabel:`Buat Bank`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/united_states.rst:1040
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Send Money`: Ensure this slider is set to :guilabel:`Trusted`. "
"The slider and text appears green if the bank account is trusted. If this is "
"**not** set to trusted, an error appears when attempting to make a payment "
"to the contact."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Kirim Uang`: Pastikan penggeser ini diatur ke "
":guilabel:`Tepercaya`. Penggeser dan teks akan berwarna hijau jika rekening "
"bank tepercaya. Jika ini **tidak** diatur ke tepercaya, kesalahan akan "
"muncul saat mencoba melakukan pembayaran ke kontak."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/united_states.rst:None
msgid "Bank information on the Create Banks form."
msgstr "Informasi bank pada formulir Buat Bank."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/united_states.rst:1048
msgid ""
"Trusted bank accounts appear in green in the :guilabel:`Accounting` tab."
msgstr ""
"Rekening bank tepercaya muncul dalam warna hijau di tab "
":guilabel:`Akuntansi`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/united_states.rst:0
msgid "A trusted bank account on a contact form."
msgstr "Rekening bank tepercaya pada formulir kontak."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/united_states.rst:1054
msgid "Bank journal settings"
msgstr "Pengaturan jurnal bank"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/united_states.rst:1056
msgid ""
"Ensure the ISO payment methods appear in the bank journal, and are "
"configured correctly. Navigate to :menuselection:`Accounting app --> "
"Configurations --> Journals` and click on the journal :guilabel:`Bank`. "
"Click into the :guilabel:`Outgoing Payments` tab, and ensure that in "
"the :guilabel:`Payment Method` column, both `ISO20022` and `U.S. ISO20022` "
"appear."
msgstr ""
"Pastikan metode pembayaran ISO muncul di jurnal bank, dan dikonfigurasi "
"dengan benar. Buka :menuselection:`aplikasi Akuntansi --> Konfigurasi --> "
"Jurnal` dan klik jurnal :guilabel:`Bank`. Klik ke tab :guilabel:`Pembayaran "
"Keluar`, dan pastikan bahwa di kolom :guilabel:`Metode Pembayaran`, "
"`ISO20022` dan `U.S. ISO20022` keduanya muncul."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/united_states.rst:1061
msgid ""
"Next, ensure all entries listed have the :guilabel:`101404 Outstanding "
"Payments` account selected in the :guilabel:`Outstanding Payments accounts` "
"column. This allows Odoo to create journal entries for payments."
msgstr ""
"Selanjutnya, pastikan semua entri yang terdaftar memiliki akun "
":guilabel:`101404 Pembayaran Tertunda` yang dipilih di kolom :guilabel:`Akun "
"Pembayaran Tertunda`. Hal ini memungkinkan Odoo untuk membuat entri jurnal "
"untuk pembayaran."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/united_states.rst:1066
msgid "ISO20022 vs U.S. ISO20022"
msgstr "ISO20022 vs U.S. ISO20022"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/united_states.rst:1068
msgid ""
"The U.S. ISO20022 is similar to the ISO standard, with some U.S.-specific "
"rules and formatting."
msgstr ""
"U.S. ISO20022 mirip dengan standar ISO, dengan beberapa aturan dan format "
"khusus AS."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/united_states.rst:1071
msgid ""
"The U.S. ISO20022 uses ABA routing numbers, which are specific to the U.S., "
"while the generic ISO20022 uses IBAN numbers."
msgstr ""
"ISO20022 AS menggunakan nomor routing ABA yang khusus untuk AS, sedangkan "
"ISO20022 generik menggunakan nomor IBAN."

