msgstr ""
"Sebagai bagian dari modul lokalisasi Uruguay, pajak dibuat secara otomatis "
"dengan konfigurasi dan akun keuangan terkaitnya."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/uruguay.rst:None
msgid "Taxes for Uruguay."
msgstr "Pajak untuk Uruguay."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/uruguay.rst:256
msgid ""
"Some accounting transactions, like *customer invoices* and *vendor bills* "
"are classified by document types. These are defined by the government fiscal "
"authorities, in this case by the |DGI|."
msgstr ""
"Beberapa transaksi akuntansi, seperti *faktur pelanggan* dan *tagihan "
"vendor* diklasifikasikan berdasarkan jenis dokumen. Ini ditentukan oleh "
"otoritas fiskal pemerintah, dalam hal ini oleh |DGI|."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/uruguay.rst:259
msgid ""
"Each document type can have a unique sequence per journal where it is "
"assigned. The data is created automatically when the localization module is "
"installed, and the information required for the document types is included "
"by default."
msgstr ""
"Setiap jenis dokumen dapat memiliki urutan unik per jurnal tempat dokumen "
"tersebut ditetapkan. Data dibuat secara otomatis ketika modul lokalisasi "
"diinstal, dan informasi yang diperlukan untuk jenis dokumen sudah disertakan "
"secara default."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/uruguay.rst:263
msgid ""
"To review the document types included in the localization, navigate "
"to :menuselection:`Accounting --> Configuration --> Document Types`."
msgstr ""
"Untuk meninjau jenis dokumen yang disertakan dalam lokalisasi, navigasikan "
"ke :menuselection:`Akuntansi --> Konfigurasi --> Jenis Dokumen`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/uruguay.rst:267
msgid ""
"In Uruguay, |CAEs| **must** be uploaded in Uruware. Sequences (and PDFs) are "
"received in Odoo from Uruware, based on their |CAEs|. |CAEs| are **only** "
"used in production. When testing, only a range of sequences used in Uruware "
"need to be set."
msgstr ""
"Di Uruguay, |CAEs| **harus** diunggah di Uruware. Urutan (dan PDF) diterima "
"di Odoo dari Uruware, berdasarkan |CAEs| mereka. |CAEs| **hanya** digunakan "
"dalam produksi. Saat pengujian, hanya rentang urutan yang digunakan di "
"Uruware yang perlu diatur."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/uruguay.rst:None
msgid "Document types for Uruguay."
msgstr "Jenis dokumen untuk Uruguay."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/uruguay.rst:277
msgid ""
"To generate and confirm an electronic document that will be validated by |"
"DGI|, the sales journal needs to be configured with the following:"
msgstr ""
"Untuk menghasilkan dan mengonfirmasi dokumen elektronik yang akan divalidasi "
"oleh |DGI|, jurnal penjualan perlu dikonfigurasi dengan hal-hal berikut:"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/uruguay.rst:280
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Invoicing Type`: by default :guilabel:`Electronic` option is set. "
"This is necessary to send electronic documents via web service to the "
"Uruguayan government through Uruware. The other option, :guilabel:`Manual`, "
"is for open invoices previously stamped in another system, for example, in "
"the |DGI|."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Tipe Penagihan`: secara default opsi :guilabel:`Elektronik` "
"diatur. Ini diperlukan untuk mengirim dokumen elektronik melalui layanan web "
"ke pemerintah Uruguay melalui Uruware. Opsi lainnya, :guilabel:`Manual`, "
"untuk faktur terbuka yang sebelumnya dicap di sistem lain, misalnya, di "
"|DGI|."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/uruguay.rst:284
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Use Documents?`: Activate this option if this journal will use "
"documents from the list of document types in Odoo."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Gunakan Dokumen?`: Aktifkan opsi ini jika jurnal ini akan "
"menggunakan dokumen dari daftar jenis dokumen di Odoo."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/uruguay.rst:288
msgid "Workflows"
msgstr "Workflow"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/uruguay.rst:290
msgid "Once you have configured your database, you can create your documents."
msgstr ""
"Setelah Anda mengonfigurasi database Anda, Anda dapat membuat dokumen Anda."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/uruguay.rst:298
msgid ""
":doc:`Customer invoices <../accounting/customer_invoices>` are electronic "
"documents that, when validated, are sent to |DGI| via Uruware. These "
"documents can be created from your sales order or manually. They must "
"contain the following data:"
msgstr ""
":doc:`Faktur pelanggan <../accounting/customer_invoices>` adalah dokumen "
"elektronik yang, ketika divalidasi, dikirim ke |DGI| melalui Uruware. "
"Dokumen ini dapat dibuat dari Sales Order Anda atau secara manual. Dokumen "
"ini harus berisi data berikut:"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/uruguay.rst:302
msgid ":guilabel:`Customer`: type the customer's information."
msgstr ":guilabel:`Pelanggan`: ketik informasi pelanggan."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/uruguay.rst:303
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Due date`: to compute if the invoice is due now or later "
"(*contado* or *crédito*, respectively)."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Tanggal Jatuh Tempo`: untuk menghitung apakah faktur jatuh tempo "
"sekarang atau nanti (*contado* atau *crédito*, masing-masing)."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/uruguay.rst:305
msgid ":guilabel:`Journal`: select the electronic sales journal."
msgstr ":guilabel:`Jurnal`: pilih jurnal penjualan elektronik."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/uruguay.rst:306
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Document Type`: document type in this format, for example, `(111) "
"e-Invoice`."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Jenis Dokumen`: jenis dokumen dalam format ini, misalnya, `(111) "
"e-Invoice`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/uruguay.rst:307
msgid ":guilabel:`Products`: specify the product(s) with the correct taxes."
msgstr ":guilabel:`Produk`: tentukan produk dengan pajak yang benar."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/uruguay.rst:310
msgid ""
"Every document type has a specific credit note and debit note (e.g., the "
"document type :guilabel:`(111) e-Invoice` has an :guilabel:`(112) e-Invoice "
"Credit Note`)."
msgstr ""
"Setiap jenis dokumen memiliki nota kredit dan nota debit tertentu (misalnya, "
"jenis dokumen :guilabel:`(111) e-Invoice` memiliki :guilabel:`(112) e-"
"Invoice Credit Note`)."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/uruguay.rst:316
msgid ""
"The :doc:`Customer credit note <../accounting/customer_invoices/"
"credit_notes>` is an electronic document that, when validated, is sent to |"
"DGI| via Uruware. It is necessary to have a validated (posted) invoice to "
"register a credit note. On the invoice, click the :guilabel:`Credit note` "
"button to access the :guilabel:`Create credit note` form, then complete the "
"following information:"
msgstr ""
":doc:`Nota kredit pelanggan <../accounting/customer_invoices/credit_notes>` "
"adalah dokumen elektronik yang, ketika divalidasi, dikirim ke |DGI| melalui "
"Uruware. Perlu memiliki faktur yang sudah divalidasi (diposting) untuk "
"mendaftarkan nota kredit. Pada faktur, klik tombol :guilabel:`Nota kredit` "
"untuk mengakses formulir :guilabel:`Buat nota kredit`, lalu lengkapi "
"informasi berikut:"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/uruguay.rst:321
msgid ":guilabel:`Reason`: type the reason for the credit note."
msgstr ":guilabel:`Alasan`: ketik alasan untuk nota kredit."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/uruguay.rst:322
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Journal`: select the journal that has to be electronic and has "
"the :guilabel:`Use Documents?` option active."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Jurnal`: pilih jurnal yang harus elektronik dan memiliki opsi "
":guilabel:`Gunakan Dokumen?` aktif."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/uruguay.rst:324
msgid ":guilabel:`Document Type`: select the credit note document type."
msgstr ":guilabel:`Tipe Dokumen`: pilih tipe dokumen nota kredit."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/uruguay.rst:325
msgid ":guilabel:`Reversal Date`: type the date."
msgstr ":guilabel:`Tanggal Pembalikan`: ketik tanggal."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/uruguay.rst:330
msgid ""
"The :doc:`Customer debit note <../accounting/customer_invoices/"
"credit_notes>` is an electronic document that, when validated, is sent to |"
"DGI| via Uruware. It is necessary to have a validated (posted) invoice to "
"register a debit note. On the invoice, click the :icon:`fa-cog` "
"(:guilabel:`action menu`) icon, select the :guilabel:`Debit note` option to "
"access the :guilabel:`Create credit note` form, then complete the following "
"information:"
msgstr ""
":doc:`Nota debit pelanggan <../accounting/customer_invoices/credit_notes>` "
"adalah dokumen elektronik yang, ketika divalidasi, dikirim ke |DGI| melalui "
"Uruware. Diperlukan faktur yang divalidasi (diposting) untuk mendaftarkan "
"nota debit. Pada faktur, klik ikon :icon:`fa-cog` (:guilabel:`menu tindakan`)"
", pilih opsi :guilabel:`Nota debit` untuk mengakses formulir :guilabel:`Buat "
"nota kredit`, kemudian lengkapi informasi berikut:"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/uruguay.rst:337
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Journal`: Select the journal that has to be electronic and has "
"the :guilabel:`Use Documents?` option active."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Jurnal`: Pilih jurnal yang harus elektronik dan memiliki opsi "
":guilabel:`Gunakan Dokumen?` aktif."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/uruguay.rst:339
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Copy lines`: Tick the checkbox to copy the invoice lines to the "
"debit note."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Salin baris`: Centang kotak untuk menyalin baris faktur ke nota "
"debit."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/uruguay.rst:340
msgid ":guilabel:`Debit note date`: Type the date."
msgstr ":guilabel:`Tanggal nota debit`: Ketik tanggal."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/uruguay.rst:343
msgid ""
"Confirm the invoice to create it with an internal reference. To send the "
"document to |DGI| via Uruware, click :guilabel:`Send` and select the "
"checkbox :guilabel:`Create CFE`. The legal document sequence (number) is "
"brought from Uruware once the document has been processed. Make sure you "
"have |CAEs| available in Uruware."
msgstr ""
"Konfirmasi invoice untuk membuatnya dengan referensi internal. Untuk "
"mengirim dokumen ke |DGI| melalui Uruware, klik :guilabel:`Kirim` dan pilih "
"kotak centang :guilabel:`Create CFE`. Urutan dokumen legal (nomor) diambil "
"dari Uruware setelah dokumen diproses. Pastikan Anda memiliki |CAEs| yang "
"tersedia di Uruware."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/uruguay.rst:349
msgid ""
"The PDF of the validated document is pulled from Uruware following the "
"specification by the Uruguayan government (DGI)."
msgstr ""
"PDF dokumen yang divalidasi diambil dari Uruware mengikuti spesifikasi oleh "
"pemerintah Uruguay (DGI)."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/uruguay.rst:353
msgid "Addendas and disclosures"
msgstr "Adenda dan pengungkapan"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/uruguay.rst:355
msgid ""
"*Addendas* and *disclosures* are additional notes and comments added to an "
"electronic document that can be mandatory or optional. To create a new "
"addenda, go to :menuselection:`Accounting --> Configuration --> Addendas and "
"disclosures` and click :guilabel:`New`."
msgstr ""
"*Adenda* dan *pengungkapan* adalah catatan tambahan dan komentar yang "
"ditambahkan ke dokumen elektronik yang dapat bersifat wajib atau opsional. "
"Untuk membuat adenda baru, buka :menuselection:`Akuntansi --> "
"Konfigurasi --> Adenda dan pengungkapan` dan klik :guilabel:`Baru`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/uruguay.rst:359
msgid "Enter the following information:"
msgstr "Masukkan informasi berikut:"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/uruguay.rst:361
msgid ":guilabel:`Name`: name of the addenda or mandatory disclosure."
msgstr ":guilabel:`Nama`: nama adenda atau pengungkapan wajib."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/uruguay.rst:362
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Type`: Select the type of remark, this will add it to the "
"specific section in the XML."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Tipe`: Pilih tipe keterangan, ini akan menambahkannya ke bagian "
"spesifik dalam XML."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/uruguay.rst:363
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Is legend`: Select this box if the text is a mandatory "
"disclosure, leave it blank if it is additional information."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Adalah legenda`: Pilih kotak ini jika teks adalah pengungkapan "
"wajib, biarkan kosong jika itu adalah informasi tambahan."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/uruguay.rst:365
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Content`: Add the complete text of the addenda or disclosure."
msgstr ":guilabel:`Konten`: Tambahkan teks lengkap adenda atau pengungkapan."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/uruguay.rst:368
msgid "Leyenda and additional information in product"
msgstr "Leyenda dan informasi tambahan di produk"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/uruguay.rst:370
msgid ""
"To add a *leyenda* or additional information to the product and XML, it is "
"necessary to add the preconfigured addenda and disclosure to the product in "
"the invoice line. Add the *leyenda* in the :guilabel:`Disclosure` field of "
"the product specified in the line."
msgstr ""
"Untuk menambahkan *leyenda* atau informasi tambahan ke produk dan XML, "
"diperlukan menambahkan adenda dan pengungkapan yang telah dikonfigurasi "
"sebelumnya ke produk di baris faktur. Tambahkan *leyenda* di bidang "
":guilabel:`Pengungkapan` produk yang ditentukan di baris."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/uruguay.rst:375
msgid "Leyenda and additional information"
msgstr "Leyenda dan informasi tambahan"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/uruguay.rst:377
msgid ""
"To add a *leyenda* or additional information to the electronic invoice and "
"XML, access the invoice, go to the :guilabel:`Other Info` tab, and select "
"the desired addenda in the :guilabel:`Addenda and Disclosure` field. The "
"addenda and disclosures added here will appear in the XML and visibly in the "
"PDF document."
msgstr ""
"Untuk menambahkan *leyenda* atau informasi tambahan ke faktur elektronik dan "
"XML, akses faktur, buka tab :guilabel:`Info Lain`, dan pilih adenda yang "
"diinginkan di bidang :guilabel:`Adenda dan Pengungkapan`. Adenda dan "
"pengungkapan yang ditambahkan di sini akan muncul dalam XML dan terlihat di "
"dokumen PDF."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/uruguay.rst:382
msgid "This applies to the following types of *addendas*:"
msgstr "Ini berlaku untuk tipe *adenda* berikut:"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/uruguay.rst:384
msgid "Document"
msgstr "Dokumen"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/uruguay.rst:385
msgid "Issuer"
msgstr "Penerbit"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/uruguay.rst:386
msgid "Receiver"
msgstr "Penerima"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/uruguay.rst:387
msgid "Addendas"
msgstr "Addenda"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/uruguay.rst:390
msgid ""
"To add a temporary note to the electronic document, use the :guilabel:`Terms "
"and Conditions` field. This information will be sent in the addenda of the "
"invoice, but it won't be saved for future documents."
msgstr ""
"Untuk menambahkan catatan sementara ke dokumen elektronik, gunakan kolom "
":guilabel:`Syarat dan Ketentuan`. Informasi ini akan dikirim dalam addenda "
"faktur, tetapi tidak akan disimpan untuk dokumen di masa mendatang."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/uzbekistan.rst:3
msgid "Uzbekistan"
msgstr "Uzbekistan"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/uzbekistan.rst:12
msgid ""
"The following modules are installed automatically with the Uzbek "
"localization:"
msgstr "Modul berikut diinstal secara otomatis dengan lokalisasi Uzbek:"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/uzbekistan.rst:21
msgid "Uzbekistan - Accounting"
msgstr "Uzbekistan - Akuntansi"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/uzbekistan.rst:22
msgid "l10n_uz"
msgstr "l10n_uz"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/uzbekistan.rst:23
msgid ""
"Default fiscal localization package for Uzbekistan. Includes the chart of "
"accounts and core accounting configuration aligned with local requirements."
msgstr ""
"Paket lokalisasi fiskal default untuk Uzbekistan. Mencakup bagan akun dan "
"konfigurasi akuntansi inti yang diselaraskan dengan persyaratan lokal."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/uzbekistan.rst:25
msgid "Uzbekistan - Accounting Reports"
msgstr "Uzbekistan - Laporan Akuntansi"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/uzbekistan.rst:26
msgid "l10n_uz_reports"
msgstr "l10n_uz_reports"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/uzbekistan.rst:27
msgid ""
"Provides localized financial reports, including the balance sheet and profit "
"and loss statement based on an |IFRS|-style structure."
msgstr ""
"Menyediakan laporan keuangan terlokalisasi, termasuk neraca keuangan dan "
"laporan laba rugi berdasarkan struktur bergaya |IFRS|."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/uzbekistan.rst:35
msgid ""
"The Uzbekistan localization assists companies in meeting local accounting "
"requirements by providing a structured and compliant accounting setup. It "
"contains the following core components:"
msgstr ""
"Lokalisasi Uzbekistan membantu perusahaan memenuhi persyaratan akuntansi "
"lokal dengan menyediakan pengaturan akuntansi yang terstruktur dan sesuai. "
"Ini berisi komponen inti berikut:"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/uzbekistan.rst:38
msgid ""
":ref:`Taxes <localizations/uz/taxes>`: preconfigured tax rates, including "
"standard 12% VAT, zero-rated export, and exempt options"
msgstr ""
":ref:`Pajak <localizations/uz/taxes>`: tarif pajak yang telah dikonfigurasi "
"sebelumnya, termasuk PPN standar 12%, ekspor dengan tarif nol, dan opsi "
"bebas pajak"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/uzbekistan.rst:40
msgid ""
":ref:`Chart of accounts <localizations/uz/coa>`: preconfigured structure "
"aligned with Uzbek standards"
msgstr ""
":ref:`Bagan akun <localizations/uz/coa>`: struktur yang telah dikonfigurasi "
"sebelumnya yang diselaraskan dengan standar Uzbek"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/uzbekistan.rst:42
msgid ""
":ref:`Financial reports <localizations/uz/taxes>`: |IFRS|-style balance "
"sheet and profit and loss reports with a tag-based linking of accounts to "
"report lines"
msgstr ""
":ref:`Laporan keuangan <localizations/uz/taxes>`: neraca keuangan bergaya "
"|IFRS| dan laporan laba rugi dengan penautan akun berbasis tag ke baris "
"laporan"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/uzbekistan.rst:50
msgid "The Uzbek localization includes preconfigured sales and purchase taxes:"
msgstr ""
"Lokalisasi Uzbek mencakup pajak penjualan dan pembelian yang telah "
"dikonfigurasi sebelumnya:"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/uzbekistan.rst:52
msgid ""
"**Standard VAT (12%):** This standard VAT is applied to most goods and "
"services. The supplier charges 12% VAT on the sale (VAT output) and is "
"generally entitled to deduct the VAT paid on business purchases (VAT input)."
msgstr ""
"**PPN Standar (12%):** PPN standar ini diterapkan pada sebagian besar barang "
"dan jasa. Pemasok membebankan PPN 12% pada penjualan (output PPN) dan "
"umumnya berhak mengurangi PPN yang dibayarkan pada pembelian bisnis (input "
"PPN)."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/uzbekistan.rst:57
msgid ""
"Most commercial sales and general supply of goods and services within "
"Uzbekistan use the **Standard VAT (12%)** tax."
msgstr ""
"Sebagian besar penjualan komersial dan penyediaan barang serta jasa secara "
"umum di Uzbekistan menggunakan pajak **PPN Standar (12%)**."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/uzbekistan.rst:60
msgid ""
"**Export VAT (0%):** The export tax is applied on taxable supplies where the "
"VAT rate applied is 0%. The supplier does not charge VAT on the sale."
msgstr ""
"**PPN Ekspor (0%):** Pajak ekspor diterapkan pada penyediaan kena pajak di "
"mana tarif PPN yang diterapkan adalah 0%. Pemasok tidak membebankan PPN pada "
"penjualan."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/uzbekistan.rst:64
msgid ""
"Exports of goods and services to customers outside Uzbekistan use the "
"**Export VAT (0%)** tax."
msgstr ""
"Ekspor barang dan jasa kepada pelanggan di luar Uzbekistan menggunakan pajak "
"**Ekspor PPN (0%)**."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/uzbekistan.rst:66
msgid ""
"**Exempt transactions (0%):** The exempt tax applies to transactions that "
"fall outside the scope of VAT and are not subject to tax."
msgstr ""
"**Transaksi bebas pajak (0%):** Pajak bebas berlaku untuk transaksi yang "
"berada di luar cakupan PPN dan tidak dikenakan pajak."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/uzbekistan.rst:70
msgid ""
"Transactions that are legally exempt from VAT under local regulations, such "
"as essential food products (meat, fish, potatoes, rice), pharmaceuticals, "
"and financial/insurance services, use the **Exempt transactions (0%)** tax."
msgstr ""
"Transaksi yang secara hukum dibebaskan dari PPN berdasarkan peraturan lokal, "
"seperti produk makanan pokok (daging, ikan, kentang, beras), obat-obatan, "
"dan layanan keuangan/asuransi, menggunakan pajak **Transaksi bebas pajak (0%)"
"**."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/uzbekistan.rst:79
msgid ""
"The Uzbek :doc:`chart of accounts <../accounting/get_started/"
"chart_of_accounts>` is preconfigured according to Uzbek accounting standards "
"and requirements. When :ref:`creating new accounts <chart-of-account/"
"create>`, it is important to use :ref:`account tags <localizations/uz/tags>`."
msgstr ""
":doc:`Bagan akun <../accounting/get_started/chart_of_accounts>` Uzbek telah "
"dikonfigurasi sebelumnya sesuai dengan standar dan persyaratan akuntansi "
"Uzbek. Ketika :ref:`membuat akun baru <chart-of-account/create>`, penting "
"untuk menggunakan :ref:`tag akun <localizations/uz/tags>`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/uzbekistan.rst:86
msgid "Account tags"
msgstr "Tag akun"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/uzbekistan.rst:88
msgid ""
"The Uzbek localization uses account tags to determine where accounts appear "
"in :ref:`financial reports <localizations/uz/financial-reports>`. Each tag "
"links the account to a specific report line."
msgstr ""
