msgstr ":guilabel:`Jurnal`"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/vietnam.rst:212
msgid ":guilabel:`Reversal date`"
msgstr ":guilabel:`Tanggal Pembalikan`"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/vietnam.rst:214
msgid ""
"Click :guilabel:`Reverse and Create Invoice` to issue a replacement invoice, "
"or :guilabel:`Reverse` to issue an adjustment invoice."
msgstr ""
"Klik :guilabel:`Balik dan Buat Faktur` untuk menerbitkan faktur pengganti, "
"atau :guilabel:`Balik` untuk menerbitkan faktur penyesuaian."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/vietnam.rst:217
msgid ""
"The :guilabel:`SInvoice Status` in the :guilabel:`SInvoice` invoice tab is "
"updated to :guilabel:`Replaced` for a replacement invoice "
"or :guilabel:`Adjusted` for an adjustment invoice."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Status SInvoice` pada tab faktur :guilabel:`SInvoice` diperbarui "
"menjadi :guilabel:`Diganti` untuk faktur pengganti atau "
":guilabel:`Disesuaikan` untuk faktur penyesuaian."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/vietnam.rst:223
msgid ""
"If an invoice needs to be canceled, open the invoice and "
"click :guilabel:`Request Cancel`. In the :guilabel:`Invoice Cancellation` "
"popup, enter the cancellation :guilabel:`Reason`, :guilabel:`Agreement "
"Name`, and :guilabel:`Agreement Date`, and click :guilabel:`Request "
"Cancellation`."
msgstr ""
"Jika faktur perlu dibatalkan, buka faktur dan klik :guilabel:`Minta "
"Pembatalan`. Pada popup :guilabel:`Pembatalan Faktur`, masukkan "
":guilabel:`Alasan` pembatalan, :guilabel:`Nama Perjanjian`, dan "
":guilabel:`Tanggal Perjanjian`, lalu klik :guilabel:`Minta Pembatalan`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/vietnam.rst:228
msgid ""
"The :guilabel:`SInvoice Status` in the :guilabel:`SInvoice` invoice tab is "
"updated to :guilabel:`Canceled`."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Status SInvoice` pada tab faktur :guilabel:`SInvoice` diperbarui "
"menjadi :guilabel:`Dibatalkan`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/vietnam.rst:234
msgid "QR banking codes"
msgstr "Kode perbankan QR"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/vietnam.rst:236
msgid ""
"Vietnamese QR banking is a payment service platform that allows customers to "
"make instant domestic payments to individuals and merchants in Vietnamese "
"dong via online and mobile banking."
msgstr ""
"Perbankan QR Vietnam adalah platform layanan pembayaran yang memungkinkan "
"pelanggan melakukan pembayaran domestik instan kepada individu dan pedagang "
"dalam dong Vietnam melalui perbankan online dan seluler."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/vietnam.rst:242
msgid ""
"To activate QR banking codes, go to :menuselection:`Accounting --> "
"Configuration --> Settings` and enable :guilabel:`QR Codes` in "
"the :guilabel:`Customer Payments` section."
msgstr ""
"Untuk mengaktifkan kode perbankan QR, buka :menuselection:`Akuntansi --> "
"Konfigurasi --> Pengaturan` dan aktifkan :guilabel:`Kode QR` di bagian "
":guilabel:`Pembayaran Pelanggan`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/vietnam.rst:246
msgid "Bank account"
msgstr "Akun bank"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/vietnam.rst:248
msgid ""
"To activate QR banking for a bank account, go to :menuselection:`Contacts --"
"> Configuration --> Bank Accounts` and select the bank account. Fill in "
"the :guilabel:`Bank Identifier Code`, :guilabel:`Proxy Type` (based on the "
"information used to identify the :guilabel:`Merchant Account`, such as the "
"card number and bank account numbers), and :guilabel:`Proxy Value` fields."
msgstr ""
"Untuk mengaktifkan perbankan QR untuk rekening bank, buka "
":menuselection:`Kontak --> Konfigurasi --> Rekening Bank` dan pilih rekening "
"bank. Isi kolom :guilabel:`Kode Identifikasi Bank`, :guilabel:`Jenis Proxy` "
"(berdasarkan informasi yang digunakan untuk mengidentifikasi "
":guilabel:`Rekening Pedagang`, seperti nomor kartu dan nomor rekening bank), "
"dan :guilabel:`Nilai Proxy`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/vietnam.rst:253
msgid ""
"Enable :guilabel:`Include Reference` to include the invoice number in the QR "
"code."
msgstr ""
"Aktifkan :guilabel:`Sertakan Referensi` untuk menyertakan nomor faktur dalam "
"kode QR."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/vietnam.rst:256
msgid ""
"The account holder's country must be set to `Vietnam`, and their city must "
"be specified on the contact form."
msgstr ""
"Negara pemegang rekening harus diatur ke `Vietnam`, dan kotanya harus "
"ditentukan pada formulir kontak."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/vietnam.rst:258
msgid ""
"The :ref:`account number <accounting/journals/bank>` and bank must be set on "
"the :guilabel:`Bank` journal."
msgstr ""
":ref:`Nomor akun <accounting/journals/bank>` dan bank harus diatur pada "
"jurnal :guilabel:`Bank`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/vietnam.rst:265
msgid "Generating QR codes on invoices"
msgstr "Membuat kode QR pada faktur"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/vietnam.rst:267
msgid ""
"When creating a new invoice, open the :guilabel:`Other Info` tab and "
"select :guilabel:`EMV Merchant-Presented QR-code` in the :guilabel:`Payment "
"QR-code` field."
msgstr ""
"Saat membuat faktur baru, buka tab :guilabel:`Info Lainnya` dan pilih "
":guilabel:`Kode QR yang Ditampilkan Pedagang EMV` di kolom :guilabel:`Kode "
"QR Pembayaran`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/vietnam.rst:271
msgid ""
"Ensure the :guilabel:`Recipient Bank` is configured, as Odoo uses this field "
"to generate QR codes."
msgstr ""
"Pastikan :guilabel:`Bank Penerima` dikonfigurasi, karena Odoo menggunakan "
"bidang ini untuk menghasilkan kode QR."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/payment_providers.rst:34
msgid ""
"Odoo embeds several **payment providers** that allow your customers to pay "
"online, on their *customer portals*, or on your *eCommerce website*. They "
"can pay sales orders, invoices, or subscriptions with recurring payments "
"using their favorite payment methods, such as **credit cards**."
msgstr ""
"Odoo menyematkan beberapa **penyedia pembayaran** yang memungkinkan "
"pelanggan Anda untuk membayar secara online, di *portal pelanggan* mereka, "
"atau di *website eCommerce* Anda. Mereka dapat membayar pesanan penjualan, "
"faktur, atau langganan dengan pembayaran berulang menggunakan metode "
"pembayaran favorit mereka, seperti **kartu kredit**."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/payment_providers.rst:39
msgid ""
"Each payment provider is linked to a list of supported :ref:`payment methods "
"<payment_providers/payment_methods>` that can be (de)activated based on your "
"needs."
msgstr ""
"Setiap penyedia pembayaran terhubung ke daftar :ref:`metode pembayaran "
"<payment_providers/payment_methods>` yang didukung yang dapat diaktifkan "
"atau dinonaktifkan berdasarkan kebutuhan Anda."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/payment_providers.rst:None
msgid "Online payment form"
msgstr "Formulir pembayaran online"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/payment_providers.rst:46
msgid ""
"Odoo apps delegate the handling of sensitive information to the certified "
"payment provider so that you don't ever have to worry about PCI compliance. "
"No sensitive information (such as credit card numbers) is stored on Odoo "
"servers or Odoo databases hosted elsewhere. Instead, Odoo apps use a unique "
"reference number for the data stored safely in the payment providers' "
"systems."
msgstr ""
"Aplikasi Odoo mendelegasikan penanganan informasi sensitif kepada penyedia "
"pembayaran bersertifikat sehingga Anda tidak perlu khawatir tentang "
"kepatuhan PCI. Tidak ada informasi sensitif (seperti nomor kartu kredit) "
"yang disimpan di server Odoo atau database Odoo yang dihosting di tempat "
"lain. Sebaliknya, aplikasi Odoo menggunakan nomor referensi unik untuk data "
"yang disimpan dengan aman di sistem penyedia pembayaran."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/payment_providers.rst:54
msgid "Supported payment providers"
msgstr "Penyedia pembayaran yang didukung"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/payment_providers.rst:56
msgid ""
"To access the supported payment providers, go to :menuselection:`Accounting "
"--> Configuration --> Payment Providers`, :menuselection:`Website --> "
"Configuration --> Payment Providers`, or :menuselection:`Sales --> "
"Configuration --> Payment Providers`. Click the relevant payment provider "
"card to access and configure the related provider."
msgstr ""
"Untuk mengakses penyedia pembayaran yang didukung, buka "
":menuselection:`Akuntansi --> Konfigurasi --> Payment Providers`, "
":menuselection:`Website --> Konfigurasi --> Payment Providers`, atau "
":menuselection:`Penjualan --> Konfigurasi --> Payment Providers`. Klik kartu "
"penyedia pembayaran yang relevan untuk mengakses dan mengonfigurasi penyedia "
"terkait."

