#: ../../content/applications/finance/payment_providers/inperson_payments.rst:11
msgid "Pay on site"
msgstr "Bayar di Tempat"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/payment_providers/inperson_payments.rst:13
msgid ""
"To allow customers to reserve products online and pay when collecting them "
"in-store, enable and configure the :ref:`Click & Collect feature <ecommerce/"
"shipping/instore-pickup>`. The **Pay on Site** payment provider is "
"automatically enabled and published. To edit the default instructions shown "
"to customers, :ref:`access the payment provider form <payment_providers/"
"supported_providers>` and go to the :guilabel:`Messages` tab."
msgstr ""
"Untuk memungkinkan pelanggan memesan produk secara online dan membayar saat "
"mengambilnya di toko, aktifkan dan konfigurasikan :ref:`fitur Click & "
"Collect <ecommerce/shipping/instore-pickup>`. Penyedia pembayaran **Pay on "
"Site** secara otomatis diaktifkan dan dipublikasikan. Untuk mengedit "
"instruksi default yang ditampilkan kepada pelanggan, :ref:`akses formulir "
"penyedia pembayaran <payment_providers/supported_providers>` dan buka tab "
":guilabel:`Messages`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/payment_providers/inperson_payments.rst:20
msgid ""
"The method is only available at checkout for customers who select the **Pick "
"up in store** delivery method."
msgstr ""
"Metode ini hanya tersedia saat checkout untuk pelanggan yang memilih metode "
"pengiriman **Pick up in store**."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/payment_providers/inperson_payments.rst:26
msgid "Cash on delivery"
msgstr "Bayar di Tempat saat Pengiriman"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/payment_providers/inperson_payments.rst:28
msgid ""
"The **Cash on Delivery** payment method allows customers to pay for their "
"order at the time of delivery. To make it available to "
"customers, :doc:`navigate to the relevant delivery method form </"
"applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/"
"setup_configuration/new_delivery_method>` and enable :guilabel:`Cash on "
"Delivery`. The **Cash on Delivery** payment provider is automatically "
"enabled and published. To edit the default instructions shown to "
"customers, :ref:`access the payment provider form <payment_providers/"
"supported_providers>` and go to the :guilabel:`Messages` tab."
msgstr ""
"Metode pembayaran **Cash on Delivery** memungkinkan pelanggan membayar "
"pesanan mereka pada saat pengiriman. Untuk menyediakannya kepada pelanggan, "
":doc:`navigasi ke formulir metode pengiriman yang relevan </applications/"
"inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/setup_configuration/"
"new_delivery_method>` dan aktifkan :guilabel:`Cash on Delivery`. Penyedia "
"pembayaran **Cash on Delivery** secara otomatis diaktifkan dan "
"dipublikasikan. Untuk mengedit instruksi default yang ditampilkan kepada "
"pelanggan, :ref:`akses formulir penyedia pembayaran <payment_providers/"
"supported_providers>` dan buka tab :guilabel:`Messages`."

