"<payment_providers/paypal/testing>` and `configure the encoding format for "
"your sandbox account <https://sandbox.paypal.com/cgi-bin/customerprofileweb?"
"cmd=_profile-language-encoding>`_."
msgstr ""
"Jika Anda mencoba PayPal sebagai pengujian, akses :ref:`akun PayPal Sandbox "
"<payment_providers/paypal/testing>` Anda dan `konfigurasikan format encoding "
"untuk akun sandbox Anda <https://sandbox.paypal.com/cgi-bin/"
"customerprofileweb?cmd=_profile-language-encoding>`_."

